(1, '<p>The <strong>Ajax Burglar Alarm System</strong> is a cutting-edge security solution designed to provide both residential and commercial properties with comprehensive protection. Its wireless architecture ensures easy installation without the need for invasive wiring, making it a versatile and user-friendly choice for modern security needs. The system features a wide array of sensors, including motion detectors, door/window contact sensors, glass break detectors, and smoke alarms, all of which communicate seamlessly with the central Hub unit. This hub acts as the command center, allowing users to control and monitor the entire system remotely via the Ajax mobile app. With its long battery life and reliable performance, the Ajax system offers a dependable and low-maintenance security solution for any property.</p>', '<p>One of the standout features of the Ajax Burglar Alarm System is its advanced technology, which includes encrypted communication to ensure the security of all transmitted data. The system offers real-time notifications, so users are immediately alerted in case of a breach or emergency. The system&rsquo;s motion detectors also feature pet immunity, reducing the likelihood of false alarms triggered by animals. Additionally, Ajax can integrate with other smart home devices, enhancing the overall automation and convenience. With professional monitoring options and a loud siren that activates during an alarm, the Ajax system not only safeguards against intruders but also serves as a powerful deterrent, providing peace of mind to property owners.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ajax_1-BAzQdFGSGR.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ajax_2-aTMiizmJd9.jpg', '2024-11-21 05:36:15.079535', '2024-11-21 05:36:15.084294', 1, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NaXH2Ke8Y7Q?si=yA61yt0R3IZOaxWu\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(2, '<p><strong>Hikvision CCTV</strong> systems are among the most trusted and advanced security solutions available, known for their high-quality video surveillance technology. Offering a wide range of cameras, from basic to sophisticated models, Hikvision delivers exceptional image clarity, even in low-light conditions, through advanced features like infrared night vision and high-definition video resolution. With options such as PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom) cameras and fixed cameras, the system caters to various security needs, whether for residential, commercial, or industrial purposes. Hikvision cameras can capture detailed footage over vast areas, providing comprehensive surveillance and ensuring that every corner of a property is monitored effectively.</p>', '<p><strong>Hikvision CCTV</strong> integrates seamlessly with cutting-edge software that allows for easy remote access and monitoring. Using mobile apps or desktop platforms, users can view live feeds, playback footage, and receive real-time alerts, all while maintaining complete control of their security network. The system\'s intelligent video analytics offer features such as motion detection, line crossing, and facial recognition, enhancing the efficiency of threat detection. Whether you are securing a home, business, or large-scale facility, Hikvision CCTV systems combine innovation, reliability, and scalability to meet the needs of any security operation.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-HIKVISION_PICTURE-S12JFwRe5I.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-HIKVISION_PICTURE_2-KpluEYeQJr.jpg', '2024-11-21 06:11:24.627785', '2024-11-22 02:56:44.010687', 2, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qI4LrEa4CoY?si=W1D5wttOoDdRMXgc\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(3, '<p><strong>Imou CCTV</strong> systems provide innovative, high-performance video surveillance solutions designed to offer both ease of use and advanced security features. Imou cameras are known for their smart technology, including HD video quality, infrared night vision, and motion detection, ensuring that your property is monitored around the clock. Whether for residential or business use, Imou offers a wide range of cameras, including indoor and outdoor models, as well as specialized options like pan-tilt-zoom (PTZ) cameras for enhanced flexibility. The intuitive design of Imou systems allows for easy installation and setup, making them accessible for users with varying levels of technical expertise.</p>', '<p><strong>Imou CCTV</strong> apart is its seamless integration with mobile devices and smart home systems. Through the Imou app, users can easily monitor live video feeds, receive instant push notifications, and access recorded footage from anywhere in the world. The system also features cloud storage options, providing secure, off-site data storage for peace of mind. With advanced features like two-way audio, smart motion tracking, and person detection, Imou ensures that security is both comprehensive and user-friendly. Imou CCTV systems offer a powerful combination of smart technology, reliability, and user-centric design, making them an ideal choice for modern surveillance needs.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-imou_picture_1-yI5CATTRIW.PNG', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-imou_pic_2-DGoiK3ZdIp.webp', '2024-11-21 06:26:50.617449', '2024-11-22 02:56:37.698899', 3, '<p><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-qUv85jqgck?si=j6YX_qpQGe68wamG\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(4, '<p><strong>Dahua CCTV</strong> systems are renowned for their cutting-edge security technology and high-quality surveillance solutions. With a diverse range of cameras, including PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom), dome, bullet, and fisheye models, Dahua delivers exceptional video clarity, whether it&rsquo;s in high-definition or 4K resolution. Equipped with advanced features such as infrared night vision, wide dynamic range (WDR), and motion detection, Dahua cameras provide clear, detailed footage in all lighting conditions, ensuring continuous monitoring 24/7. Designed for both indoor and outdoor use, these cameras offer reliability and durability, even in harsh environmental conditions, making them suitable for residential, commercial, and industrial applications.</p>', '<p><strong>Dahua CCTV</strong> systems also integrate with advanced video management software and cloud-based platforms, offering powerful analytics like facial recognition, vehicle number plate recognition, and intrusion detection. These intelligent features enhance security by providing real-time alerts and actionable insights, enabling faster response times to potential threats. Dahua&rsquo;s flexible and scalable solutions allow for easy expansion of the system, making it ideal for both small-scale installations and large, multi-site deployments. With its robust performance, cutting-edge technology, and user-friendly interface, Dahua CCTV systems are a top choice for anyone looking to secure their property with modern, reliable surveillance.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-pic_1-fbDKd91Tgn.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-dauha-dH4mq8f4HE.jpg', '2024-11-21 06:33:24.769713', '2024-11-22 02:56:30.882747', 4, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0yr92MxfEpQ?si=w-bdcfPXSbiAPUrR\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(5, '<p><strong>Honeywell CCTV</strong> systems are designed to provide high-quality, reliable surveillance solutions for both residential and commercial properties. Known for their exceptional image clarity, Honeywell cameras offer advanced features like high-definition resolution, infrared night vision, and wide dynamic range (WDR), ensuring that every detail is captured clearly, day or night. With a variety of camera types, including dome, bullet, and PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom), Honeywell provides a versatile range of options to suit different security needs. Whether for monitoring large outdoor areas or securing indoor spaces, Honeywell&rsquo;s cameras are built to perform consistently in a variety of conditions, offering peace of mind to users around the clock.</p>', '<p><strong>Honeywell CCTV</strong> systems integrate with intuitive video management software that enables easy monitoring and control. With features like motion detection, remote access, and cloud storage, Honeywell&rsquo;s solutions are designed to be user-friendly and efficient. Their systems support mobile apps, allowing users to view live footage, review recorded clips, and receive alerts directly on their smartphones, providing convenience and real-time responsiveness. Honeywell&rsquo;s advanced analytics, such as face detection, intrusion detection, and people counting, enhance the system&rsquo;s ability to identify potential threats and provide actionable insights, making it an ideal choice for those looking for sophisticated, scalable surveillance solutions.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-honeywell_pic_1-uTAxVz3Ch0.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-honeywell_pic_2-8ksJMHlsyE.avif', '2024-11-21 06:39:57.805124', '2024-11-21 06:39:57.810930', 5, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/onJTPrPuIK4?si=MPKkX-NyaUPUvfqF\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(6, '<p><strong>Hiviz CCTV</strong> systems are designed to deliver high-performance security solutions with an emphasis on advanced surveillance technology and user-friendly features. Known for their reliable image quality, Hiviz cameras offer full high-definition video resolution, ensuring clear and sharp images for both daytime and nighttime monitoring. Equipped with features such as infrared night vision, motion detection, and wide dynamic range (WDR), Hiviz cameras can capture detailed footage in diverse lighting conditions. Whether for residential, commercial, or industrial use, Hiviz offers a variety of camera types, including bullet, dome, and PTZ models, providing a flexible and scalable solution for a wide range of security needs.</p>', '<p><strong>Hiviz CCTV</strong> apart is its focus on intelligent video analytics and seamless integration with modern security platforms. The system supports advanced features like motion tracking, facial recognition, and real-time alerts, which help users identify potential threats quickly and efficiently. Through mobile apps and cloud storage options, users can access live video feeds, review footage remotely, and store data securely off-site. With a reputation for reliable performance and easy installation, Hiviz CCTV systems offer a comprehensive, cost-effective solution for enhancing security, making them a top choice for both home and business security needs.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ezviz_1-jpivWscH1b.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ezviz-wP182XhkRT.webp', '2024-11-21 06:47:37.047322', '2024-11-22 02:56:22.286740', 6, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0Mqfi_oSZLI?si=WXJ5aRD8I_4wJThe\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(7, '<p><strong>Matrix CCTV</strong> systems are known for delivering advanced, high-performance video surveillance solutions tailored to meet the needs of modern security environments. With a range of cameras offering high-definition video quality, including options like dome, bullet, and PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom) models, Matrix ensures detailed and clear surveillance both during the day and night. The system is equipped with infrared night vision, wide dynamic range (WDR), and motion detection, enabling it to adapt to a variety of lighting conditions and provide round-the-clock monitoring. Whether used in residential, commercial, or industrial settings, Matrix CCTV is designed to offer reliable performance, with durable and weatherproof cameras that can handle challenging environments.</p>', '<p><strong>Matrix CCTV</strong> apart is its integration with cutting-edge video management software, providing users with a powerful tool for surveillance monitoring and analysis. The system&rsquo;s intelligent features include motion tracking, facial recognition, and advanced analytics, which help users detect and respond to security threats quickly and efficiently. Matrix CCTV also supports remote access, allowing users to view live feeds, receive alerts, and review recorded footage from anywhere via mobile apps or desktop interfaces. With flexible storage options, including cloud and local storage, Matrix offers both convenience and reliability. Whether you\'re protecting a small business or a large-scale facility, Matrix CCTV delivers comprehensive, scalable security solutions that ensure your property is monitored and protected at all times.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-matrix_pic_1-K5Y8dyLwI8.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-matrix_pic_2-L1FBYwtXBx.jpg', '2024-11-21 06:55:12.948364', '2024-11-22 02:54:53.304865', 7, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I-0-X1UfS1s?si=VfChbCbT-CH4nPoq\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(8, '<p><strong>Matrix AVTech CCTV</strong> systems are known for their robust and reliable video surveillance solutions, combining cutting-edge technology with ease of use. AVTech cameras deliver high-definition video quality, providing sharp and clear images for both daytime and nighttime monitoring. Equipped with advanced features such as infrared night vision, wide dynamic range (WDR), and motion detection, Matrix AVTech ensures that every detail is captured accurately, regardless of lighting conditions. With a variety of camera models, including dome, bullet, and PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom), the system is adaptable to various security needs, whether for residential, commercial, or industrial environments. The system&rsquo;s durability and reliable performance make it a popular choice for long-term, 24/7 surveillance.</p>', '<p><strong>Matrix AVTech CCTV</strong> is its advanced video management software, which provides users with a user-friendly interface to manage and monitor their surveillance system. The system supports intelligent analytics, such as motion detection, intrusion detection, and facial recognition, to enhance security and reduce false alarms. Additionally, Matrix AVTech offers seamless remote access via mobile apps, allowing users to view live feeds, receive real-time notifications, and access stored footage from anywhere in the world. With options for cloud storage and local backup, Matrix AVTech ensures that recorded footage is secure and easily retrievable. Whether you\'re looking for a cost-effective solution for home security or a scalable system for a business, Matrix AVTech CCTV delivers reliable, intelligent surveillance that gives you peace of mind.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-avtech_pic_2-E2v5TGzult.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-avtech_1-6u9Xt2AyO2.jpg', '2024-11-21 07:02:08.581624', '2024-11-22 02:54:20.686480', 8, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_xmrG9afv5s?si=NTwDvO9uU1gjBoE_\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(9, '<p><strong>Panasonic CCTV</strong> systems are renowned for their high-quality video surveillance solutions, combining advanced technology with superior reliability. Known for offering exceptional clarity, Panasonic cameras deliver high-definition video, providing crisp and clear images even in low-light conditions, thanks to features like infrared night vision and wide dynamic range (WDR). Whether for residential, commercial, or industrial use, Panasonic&rsquo;s range of cameras&mdash;including dome, bullet, and PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom) models&mdash;ensures comprehensive coverage of any space. Built for durability and longevity, Panasonic CCTV systems are designed to withstand challenging environments, offering robust performance for continuous 24/7 surveillance.</p>', '<p><strong>Panasonic CCTV</strong> is its integration of cutting-edge video analytics and smart technologies. The system features intelligent capabilities like motion detection, people counting, and face recognition, allowing for more effective monitoring and threat detection. With the ability to remotely access and control the system via mobile apps or desktop platforms, Panasonic makes it easy for users to stay connected to their security network from anywhere. The system supports both local and cloud storage options, ensuring that recorded footage is securely stored and easily accessible when needed. Combining ease of use, superior video quality, and advanced security features, Panasonic CCTV provides an ideal solution for anyone seeking reliable, high-performance video surveillance.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-panasonic_2-vLgE9vYUfR.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-panasonic_1-n5G9iJAVE1.jpg', '2024-11-21 07:05:34.551732', '2024-11-22 02:54:09.178371', 9, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RW0Bh9uHms4?si=zNG-owOJ0yVDnt2I\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(10, '<p><strong>Axis CCTV</strong> systems are recognized for their high-performance surveillance solutions, designed to provide superior video quality and reliable security for various environments. Axis cameras deliver exceptional clarity with high-definition resolution, offering crisp and clear images even in challenging lighting conditions thanks to features like infrared night vision and wide dynamic range (WDR). The range includes flexible camera options, from fixed cameras to advanced pan-tilt-zoom (PTZ) models, allowing users to customize their security setup for residential, commercial, or industrial use. Built with durability in mind, Axis CCTV systems are designed to withstand harsh outdoor conditions, providing reliable, 24/7 monitoring.</p>', '<p><strong>Axis CCTV</strong> apart is its integration with cutting-edge network video technology, offering advanced video management software and powerful analytics. Axis systems come equipped with intelligent features such as motion detection, audio detection, and people counting, enabling smarter, more efficient surveillance. With easy remote access via mobile apps or desktop platforms, users can view live feeds, receive instant alerts, and review recorded footage from anywhere. Additionally, Axis provides flexible storage options, including cloud and network video recorders (NVRs), ensuring that footage is securely stored and readily available. For those seeking a robust, scalable, and innovative security solution, Axis CCTV offers exceptional performance and peace of mind.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-axis_1-GYt8rDyYNp.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-axis_2-Ssl0tK2PPe.jpg', '2024-11-21 07:09:59.773579', '2024-11-22 02:53:54.716771', 10, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eeTFkrHsCIM?si=bGwf9Y4YhCw1tcYK\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(11, '<p><strong>ZKTeco Biometrics Access Control</strong> systems offer cutting-edge security solutions that leverage advanced biometric technology to provide secure, efficient, and convenient access management. Using fingerprint, facial recognition, or palm vein scanning, ZKTeco systems ensure that only authorized individuals can access restricted areas, eliminating the need for traditional keycards or PIN codes. These systems are designed for high accuracy and reliability, with fast processing speeds that can handle large volumes of users, making them ideal for both small businesses and large enterprises. ZKTeco\'s biometric access control systems also feature multi-modal authentication options, allowing for added layers of security when required, ensuring a higher level of protection.</p>', '<p><strong>ZKTeco Biometrics Access Control</strong> apart is its seamless integration with other security systems, such as video surveillance and time attendance solutions, to provide a comprehensive security ecosystem. The systems are equipped with user-friendly interfaces and cloud-based management options, allowing administrators to easily configure, monitor, and control access from anywhere. With robust data encryption and the ability to store large amounts of user data securely, ZKTeco&rsquo;s solutions offer scalable and customizable access control for various industries, including corporate offices, government facilities, and educational institutions. Designed to improve both security and operational efficiency, ZKTeco provides a next-level solution for managing access with precision and ease.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_1-IjxFlgViob.png', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_pic_2-mSS8KV1p4x.webp', '2024-11-21 07:15:39.476123', '2024-11-22 02:43:49.016338', 11, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wvEl1mqLYQ0?si=41kJnBfoN686qKBk\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(12, '<p><strong>Anviz Biometrics Access Control</strong> systems provide innovative and secure solutions for managing access to sensitive areas using advanced biometric technology. Featuring cutting-edge fingerprint recognition, facial recognition, and palm-vein scanning, Anviz systems offer highly accurate and reliable identification to ensure only authorized personnel can enter restricted spaces. Designed for both high-traffic and high-security environments, these systems provide fast processing times and can support large user databases, making them ideal for businesses of all sizes. The intuitive interface and customizable settings allow for seamless integration with existing security infrastructure, offering a smooth user experience while enhancing overall security.</p>', '<p><strong>Anviz Biometrics Access Control</strong> apart is its versatility and scalability, allowing it to meet the needs of various industries, from corporate offices and educational institutions to government and healthcare facilities. The system supports multi-modal authentication for added security and provides cloud-based management for remote monitoring and control. With robust features like real-time access logs, data encryption, and a user-friendly software interface, Anviz ensures that your access control system is both secure and easy to manage. Whether you\'re looking to improve security or streamline access processes, Anviz offers an efficient, reliable, and future-proof solution for biometric access control.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ANVIZ-dZL3sfbB9x.png', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ANVIZ_1-4RwabnJ99D.png', '2024-11-21 07:21:34.835121', '2024-11-22 02:51:20.477182', 12, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FNA8ncQqUDk?si=ry6W5IaVuAojpTLG\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(13, '<p><strong>Anson Biometrics Access Control</strong> systems provide state-of-the-art security solutions that utilize advanced biometric technologies for precise and reliable access management. Equipped with fingerprint, facial recognition, and palm-vein scanning capabilities, Anson systems ensure secure and contactless authentication, eliminating the need for traditional PINs or access cards. Designed for efficiency and accuracy, these systems can process large user databases swiftly, making them suitable for a wide range of applications from small offices to large enterprise environments. Anson&rsquo;s biometric solutions not only enhance security but also streamline access control, providing seamless entry for authorized personnel while preventing unauthorized access.</p>', '<div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"h-full\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wvnem-79elbk h-full\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wvnem-1n7m0yu\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9\">\r\n<article class=\"w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-43\" data-scroll-anchor=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\">\r\n<div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl\">\r\n<div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"13f4d911-11d9-48a2-b04e-b2c9620d5209\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\