(15, '<p><strong>ITC Paging System</strong> is a versatile and reliable communication solution designed to provide clear, real-time audio announcements in a wide variety of environments. Whether for schools, hospitals, factories, or shopping malls, the ITC Paging System ensures high-quality sound distribution, allowing messages to be heard clearly across large spaces or noisy areas. The system supports multiple zones, enabling users to broadcast announcements to specific areas or the entire facility, depending on the need. With features like adjustable volume control, zone selection, and the ability to integrate with emergency alert systems, the ITC Paging System ensures that important messages reach their intended audience quickly and efficiently.</p>', '<p><strong>ITC Paging System</strong> apart is its scalability and ease of integration with other communication systems. The system can be customized to fit different facility sizes, from small offices to large, multi-building complexes. It is designed to be user-friendly, with intuitive controls that make it easy to operate, whether through a centralized control panel or remote access. The ITC system is also highly durable and reliable, ensuring consistent performance over time. With options for wired and wireless configurations, it offers flexibility for various installation environments. Whether used for routine announcements, emergency notifications, or public address functions, the ITC Paging System delivers exceptional performance and seamless communication in any setting.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-itc_pic_2-83itTXMOCl.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-itc_pic_1-az6hEKpn22.jpg', '2024-11-21 07:58:00.411075', '2024-11-22 02:52:13.543626', 15, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/tl8CKunyNTA?si=DNAnhPD4gOU7mYms\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(16, '<p><strong>Farfisa Intercom System</strong> offers a sophisticated and reliable communication solution for both residential and commercial settings. Known for its high-quality audio and video capabilities, the Farfisa intercom system allows seamless communication between different areas of a building, providing enhanced security and convenience. Featuring user-friendly designs, the system includes a wide range of options, from basic audio-only models to advanced video intercoms with high-definition screens, allowing users to visually identify visitors before granting access. Whether for apartments, offices, or gated communities, the Farfisa Intercom System ensures clear and secure communication, making it an essential tool for modern access control and home automation.</p>', '<div class=\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"h-full\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wvnem-79elbk h-full\">\r\n<div class=\"react-scroll-to-bottom--css-wvnem-1n7m0yu\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9\">\r\n<article class=\"w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-55\" data-scroll-anchor=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\">\r\n<div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl\">\r\n<div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\">\r\n<div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\">\r\n<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"624f2911-1c27-40ba-ad77-f699b1ca73c6\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Farfisa Intercom System</strong> apart is its versatility and integration capabilities. The system is compatible with other home automation technologies, allowing users to integrate it with security cameras, access control systems, and smart home devices. With multiple indoor units that can be installed in various rooms or offices, Farfisa provides flexibility in how communication is managed within a building. Additionally, Farfisa intercom systems offer easy-to-use interfaces with features like touch-screen control, remote unlocking, and the ability to store visitor records, providing both convenience and security. Designed with both functionality and aesthetics in mind, the Farfisa system adds a touch of modern elegance to any environment while enhancing communication and safety.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mt-3 w-full empty:hidden\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"absolute\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-farfisa_1-81UEg0wZrt.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-farfisa_2-3eqp8hzvsa.jpg', '2024-11-21 08:02:24.534655', '2024-11-22 02:53:06.444794', 16, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CJ3o39I0Q1k?si=cAUdPLgcNewS-AU7\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(17, '<p><strong>Aiphone Intercom System</strong> is a premium solution designed to provide secure, clear, and efficient communication for both residential and commercial properties. Known for its high-quality audio and video capabilities, Aiphone systems allow users to interact with visitors remotely, whether for a single-family home or a multi-tenant building. Aiphone&rsquo;s video intercom models offer high-definition screens with clear images, while the audio systems deliver crisp, distortion-free sound, ensuring effective communication. Whether answering the door at home, managing access in a corporate building, or providing a convenient communication solution in hospitals or schools, Aiphone systems enhance security and streamline day-to-day operations.</p>', '<p><strong>Aiphone Intercom System</strong> stand out is its versatility and advanced integration options. The system is designed to integrate seamlessly with existing security and access control systems, such as door entry systems, surveillance cameras, and alarm systems. Aiphone offers both wired and wireless intercom solutions, ensuring flexibility in installation and usage for a wide range of building layouts. Additionally, Aiphone systems are known for their user-friendly interfaces, with touch-screen models and mobile app compatibility that allow users to manage communication remotely. With a focus on durability, ease of use, and seamless connectivity, Aiphone provides a comprehensive intercom solution that enhances both security and convenience in any environment.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-AIPHONE_1-3YWgqv1LP8.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-AIPHONE_2-oFqnfY0MB2.jpg', '2024-11-21 08:06:44.810830', '2024-11-22 02:53:34.307207', 17, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NiHi73yaJ5M?si=3J49L82GBCJaac41\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(18, '<p><strong>AVTech Rool Alert</strong> is an advanced security feature designed to enhance video surveillance systems with proactive real-time alerts. This intelligent system uses a combination of motion detection, video analytics, and AI-driven algorithms to identify potential threats or unusual activities in the monitored area. The Rool Alert system can automatically notify users via mobile apps or email when specific events occur, such as motion detection, tampering, or unauthorized access. By providing instant alerts, the Rool Alert system allows users to respond quickly to potential security breaches, enhancing overall safety and minimizing response time in critical situations.</p>', '<p><strong>AVTech Rool Alert</strong> is its seamless integration with AVTech&rsquo;s range of surveillance cameras and video recorders, offering a complete and cohesive security solution. The system is designed to be user-friendly, with an intuitive interface that allows users to customize alert settings based on specific needs and preferences. It also supports remote monitoring, enabling users to view live footage and receive alerts from anywhere, whether in the office, at home, or on the go. With its reliable performance, real-time notifications, and easy integration with existing security infrastructure, AVTech&rsquo;s Rool Alert system provides an intelligent and effective tool for monitoring and protecting properties.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-avtech_1_picture-xDrk57uFNN.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-avtech_2-jL8eD9LnLc.jpg', '2024-11-21 08:59:52.123664', '2024-11-21 09:00:14.072765', 18, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mquA6ZpJk_c?si=z3fOLVzfN2aDtmEw\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(19, '<p><strong>Honeywell&rsquo;s biometrics access control</strong> systems offer cutting-edge security solutions that leverage advanced biometric technology to ensure safe and efficient access management. These systems utilize fingerprint, facial recognition, and iris scanning to authenticate individuals, providing an extra layer of security beyond traditional methods like passwords or access cards. With biometric authentication, organizations can prevent unauthorized access and enhance security by ensuring that only approved personnel can enter restricted areas. The systems are highly customizable, supporting various authentication modes, and are designed to integrate seamlessly with existing security infrastructures.</p>', '<p><strong>Honeywell\'s biometrics access control </strong>systems are built for ease of use and scalability. They are equipped with advanced software for real-time monitoring and reporting, giving security personnel the tools to track and manage access activity efficiently. The systems are also designed to be user-friendly, allowing for fast enrollment of users and smooth authentication processes. Whether for a small office or a large enterprise, Honeywell&rsquo;s biometric access control solutions are highly adaptable, ensuring optimal protection across diverse environments.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-honeywell_bio_1-VuZ0FjiJSf.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-honey_well_bio_2-XM2orkNqE3.jpg', '2024-11-22 03:05:39.973713', '2024-11-22 03:05:53.582053', 19, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kjWSlx1HfKs?si=ecO4tYVarnBh3ZNj\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(20, '<p><strong>The Matrix biometrics access control system</strong> is a state-of-the-art security solution that utilizes cutting-edge biometric technology to provide secure and reliable access management. Designed to enhance physical security, HMatrix uses advanced biometric modalities such as fingerprint recognition, facial recognition, and iris scanning to authenticate users with high accuracy. This system ensures that only authorized individuals are granted access to sensitive areas, eliminating the risks associated with traditional access control methods like PIN codes or ID cards. With its high level of precision and sophisticated algorithms, HMatrix provides a secure and efficient solution for businesses, government institutions, and other high-security environments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Matrix access control system</strong> is designed for ease of use and integration. The system supports real-time monitoring and data collection, allowing administrators to track user activity and generate detailed reports for compliance and auditing purposes. The user-friendly interface simplifies enrollment and management of user data, making it easy to add or remove users from the system. HMatrix&rsquo;s flexible design allows it to scale according to the size of the organization, whether it\'s a small office or a large, multi-site enterprise. By combining security with scalability and convenience, HMatrix delivers a comprehensive biometric solution for modern access control needs.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-matrix_biometrics_1-OLibUx4TzT.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-matrix_2-kPiioR1y6o.jpeg', '2024-11-22 03:12:56.469684', '2024-11-22 03:12:56.478119', 20, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cwfYUITr18Q?si=G6PK2cn08_oCugnC\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_branddetail` (`id`, `brand_description_1`, `brand_description_2`, `brand_image_1`, `brand_image_2`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `brand_id`, `other_details`) VALUES
(21, '<p><strong>Uniqscan X-ray baggage scanner</strong> is an advanced security solution designed to provide thorough and efficient screening for a wide range of environments, from airports to government buildings and high-security facilities. Featuring cutting-edge imaging technology, this scanner delivers crystal-clear, high-resolution X-ray images that allow operators to quickly identify potentially hazardous or prohibited items hidden within baggage. The Uniqscan system uses a dual-energy X-ray mechanism that offers superior detection capabilities, enabling the differentiation of materials such as explosives, metals, and organic substances. Its intuitive interface and user-friendly controls ensure that security personnel can operate it with ease, reducing the chances of human error and increasing throughput during busy periods.</p>', '<p><strong>Uniqscan X-ray baggage scanner</strong> apart is its blend of speed, accuracy, and versatility. The system is designed to process bags and packages quickly while providing operators with detailed, easy-to-interpret images. Advanced features like automatic threat detection and suspicious item alerts enhance security efficiency, allowing for quicker decision-making and reducing bottlenecks in high-traffic areas. Furthermore, the system&rsquo;s ergonomic design and compact footprint make it suitable for a variety of settings, from bustling transport hubs to smaller, constrained spaces. With a robust set of safety features, including radiation protection and compliance with international standards, the Uniqscan X-ray baggage scanner offers a reliable, scalable solution for ensuring the safety and security of both personnel and facilities.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-uniq-ZPDcytBSSH.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-uniq_2-7Vsd66oFjh.jpg', '2024-11-22 03:19:42.476657', '2024-11-22 03:19:56.629872', 21, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ag1aMZdQu04?si=usGihwfhr6_VJwa3\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(22, '<p><strong>Dahua X-ray baggage scanner</strong> stand out is its combination of high throughput, user-friendly interface, and compact design. The intuitive touchscreen controls and real-time imaging allow operators to navigate the system effortlessly, reducing training time and minimizing operational errors. Its space-efficient design makes it ideal for use in environments where floor space is limited, without compromising performance. The scanner is also equipped with advanced safety features, including radiation shielding, ensuring a safe working environment for operators while meeting international regulatory standards. Whether used in airports, train stations, or secure facilities, the Dahua X-ray baggage scanner offers a reliable and scalable solution to meet the evolving security needs of modern infrastructure.</p>', '<p><strong>Dahua X-ray baggage scanner </strong>is a high-performance security solution designed to provide superior imaging and fast, reliable detection of hidden threats within bags and packages. With its advanced dual-energy X-ray technology, the Dahua scanner offers highly detailed, color-coded images that help security personnel quickly identify various materials such as explosives, contraband, and other hazardous objects. The system&rsquo;s ability to differentiate between organic and inorganic materials enhances detection accuracy, allowing for faster and more precise screening. Additionally, the Dahua scanner is equipped with automated threat detection algorithms that flag suspicious items in real-time, streamlining the screening process and improving overall security effectiveness.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-1-vj11P975gm.png', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-2-hCqZDyWGmc.png', '2024-11-22 03:22:34.613657', '2024-11-22 03:22:34.617983', 22, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AUK8UAmMBsw?si=yM1m5Zu5gdzm1nsN\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(23, '<p><strong>ZKTeco X-ray baggage scanner</strong> is a cutting-edge security solution designed to deliver exceptional screening performance in a wide variety of high-security environments. Utilizing advanced dual-energy X-ray technology, the scanner produces detailed, high-resolution images that help security personnel swiftly identify concealed threats such as weapons, explosives, and illicit substances. The system\'s ability to differentiate between materials with remarkable precision&mdash;using color-coded images and intuitive displays&mdash;ensures a more efficient and accurate screening process. With its smart automatic threat detection system, the ZKTeco scanner highlights suspicious items, enabling quick decision-making and reducing the time needed to process each bag.</p>', '<p><strong>ZKTeco X-ray baggage scanner</strong> is designed with user-friendliness and operational efficiency in mind. Featuring an intuitive touchscreen interface, it allows operators to easily control and adjust settings, making it simple for security personnel to respond to threats. Its compact and ergonomic design ensures the scanner can be integrated into various settings, from busy airports to smaller, high-security facilities. The system also includes essential safety features such as radiation protection and compliance with international standards, ensuring a secure environment for both operators and passengers. With its robust build and scalable features, the ZKTeco X-ray baggage scanner is a versatile and reliable solution for modern security challenges.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_baggage_2-l5TKYnAvvW.png', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_baggage_1-QudI8qBY74.jpg', '2024-11-22 03:26:07.076384', '2024-11-22 03:26:07.081855', 23, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3Dx49LczHnQ?si=WowfAQ0_xVtPJHOP\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(24, '<p>ZKTeco boom barriers provide a robust and efficient solution for controlling vehicle access in a wide range of settings, including parking lots, toll gates, and secure facility entrances. Designed for both durability and high performance, these barriers are built to handle high traffic volumes with ease. Featuring a sleek, modern design, the ZKTeco boom barriers come equipped with powerful motors that ensure smooth and quick operation, even under demanding conditions. With adjustable arm lengths and customizable options, the barriers can be tailored to fit the specific needs of any site, ensuring both security and ease of access for authorized vehicles.</p>', '<p>ZKTeco boom barriers are equipped with advanced technology to enhance security and convenience. They support integration with a variety of access control systems, such as RFID readers, license plate recognition (LPR) systems, and biometric scanners, allowing for seamless, automated vehicle management. The barriers also feature anti-collision mechanisms to prevent damage from accidental impacts, ensuring longevity and reliability. With user-friendly controls and optional features like remote management and real-time monitoring, the ZKTeco boom barriers offer a sophisticated solution for managing vehicle access with both efficiency and high levels of security.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_barrier_1-MDrb8AOL9m.png', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_teco_barrier_2-nW8d0jk5e2.png', '2024-11-22 03:35:58.900748', '2024-11-22 03:35:58.904924', 24, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nNUyvKopmuc?si=8PTu-A9kfKxGl5pU\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(25, '<p>MAG boom barriers are high-quality, efficient solutions designed to control and regulate vehicle access in both high-traffic and secure environments. Ideal for use in parking lots, entry gates, toll booths, and industrial facilities, MAG boom barriers are engineered for durability and smooth operation. Featuring a sturdy construction and advanced motor technology, these barriers provide fast, reliable performance, ensuring vehicles can pass through swiftly while maintaining robust security. The barriers\' long, adjustable arms can be customized to suit different widths and environments, making them versatile and adaptable to various access control needs.</p>', '<p>MAG boom barriers are equipped with cutting-edge technology to offer enhanced security and ease of use. They integrate seamlessly with a wide range of access control systems, such as RFID, license plate recognition, and biometric scanners, allowing for automatic vehicle identification and secure entry management. MAG barriers also come with built-in safety features, including anti-collision protection, to prevent damage during operation. Additionally, their user-friendly controls, remote management capabilities, and real-time monitoring options make them an excellent choice for both automated and manual vehicle access control. Combining functionality with sleek aesthetics, MAG boom barriers provide a secure, efficient solution for modern vehicle management.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-MAG_1-4nRE5Z22r8.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-MAG_2-cu58YvaHr4.jpg', '2024-11-22 03:40:01.562950', '2024-11-22 03:40:01.569341', 25, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WSTEQg8fKeg?si=aCi7vL04egmFi4py\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(26, '<p><strong>Beninca boom barriers </strong>are cutting-edge access control solutions designed to offer seamless management of vehicle entry and exit in various high-traffic and secure environments. Known for their robust build and reliable performance, these barriers are engineered to withstand continuous use while maintaining smooth and rapid operation. Featuring high-quality materials and advanced motor technology, Beninca boom barriers provide swift arm movement, allowing vehicles to pass through efficiently while ensuring optimal security. Their versatile design includes adjustable arm lengths and customizable options, making them ideal for a range of settings such as parking lots, toll booths, gated communities, and commercial entrances.</p>', '<p><strong>Beninca boom barriers</strong> apart is their integration of advanced safety and automation features. These barriers support a wide range of access control systems, including RFID readers, license plate recognition (LPR), and remote management capabilities, ensuring secure and contactless vehicle entry. With built-in anti-crash mechanisms, Beninca boom barriers are designed to prevent damage from accidental impacts, ensuring long-term durability and reduced maintenance costs. Additionally, their user-friendly interface and real-time monitoring options allow for easy operation and management, making them a convenient solution for both high-security sites and everyday traffic control. Combining reliability, flexibility, and ease of use, Beninca boom barriers offer a sophisticated solution for managing vehicle access in modern infrastructure.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ben_2-wpbDsR8t37.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ben_1-lMnsVtHe56.png', '2024-11-22 03:43:10.192011', '2024-11-22 03:43:10.196411', 26, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BnIviiKV2rk?si=mDwKPoCoyAh_Kroo\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" fram