(27, '<p><strong>Aiphone Nurse Call System</strong> is an advanced communication solution designed to enhance patient care and streamline communication in healthcare settings, such as hospitals, clinics, and nursing homes. This system allows patients to easily call for assistance by pressing a button on a bedside unit, ensuring quick and reliable communication with nursing staff. With features like visual and audible alerts, the system helps reduce response times and ensures that no patient request goes unnoticed. Additionally, the Aiphone Nurse Call System integrates seamlessly with other healthcare technologies, providing a cohesive and efficient workflow for caregivers.</p>', '<p><strong>Aiphone Nurse Call System</strong> is its flexibility and customization options. The system can be tailored to meet the specific needs of a facility, with options for integrating patient monitoring, room status updates, and emergency alerts. Its user-friendly interface ensures that both patients and staff can navigate the system with ease. The nurse call units can be equipped with features like two-way communication, allowing real-time conversation between the patient and caregiver, improving response times and enhancing patient satisfaction. The system\'s robust design and scalability also make it a reliable choice for healthcare environments of all sizes, from small clinics to large hospitals.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-aiphone_1-PHFt7wgZ7E.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-aiphone_2-vs5vglMydy.webp', '2024-11-22 06:43:20.453555', '2024-11-22 06:43:20.459707', 27, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/obv10vDjggk?si=5Om6NPWrb0o5PJ5L\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
