(29, '<p><strong>Fire Pro Pentiar Aurora </strong>is a striking fusion of sleek modern design and innovative engineering, capturing the essence of high-performance tech with an artistic flair. Its body is crafted from a refined, matte black alloy, sleek yet durable, giving it a sophisticated edge. The aurora aesthetic comes to life through dynamic LED accents that trace the contours of the device, shifting colors in response to usage. When powered up, the subtle, ethereal glow of the aurora lighting creates an immersive visual experience that complements the device&rsquo;s high-speed capabilities. Beneath the surface, the Pentiar Aurora boasts a state-of-the-art processor, allowing it to handle intensive tasks with remarkable precision and efficiency. Whether for gaming, creative work, or multitasking, the device stands as a perfect blend of form and function, delivering an elevated user experience.</p>', '<p><strong>Fire Pro Pentiar Aurora</strong> is a beast, integrating cutting-edge cooling systems to ensure peak efficiency during heavy usage. Its innovative heat-dissipation technology developed to maximize airflow while keeping noise to a minimum ensures the device stays cool under pressure, even during long hours of high-intensity activity. The responsive touch interface is intuitive and immersive, while its seamless connectivity options provide versatility for any setup. Crafted for those who demand power, but also value design, the Pentiar Aurora is as much a piece of art as it is a tool for performance. Whether in a dark room with the gentle flicker of its aurora lights or under the bright glare of daylight, it commands attention with its breathtaking presence and unparalleled capabilities.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_2-iwpaO0lT80.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_1-inuRROBePV.jpg', '2024-11-25 05:11:39.486196', '2024-11-25 05:11:39.504348', 29, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\