(30, '<p><strong>Kidde Fire Protection System</strong> is a robust and cutting-edge solution designed to safeguard lives and property with unrivaled reliability and precision. Engineered with advanced fire detection and suppression technologies, this system is a cornerstone of safety in both residential and commercial spaces. Its sleek, unobtrusive design belies the powerful capabilities hidden within, offering both visual and audible alerts with sophisticated sensors that respond to even the faintest trace of smoke or heat. The system is equipped with an array of strategically placed detectors, from smoke and CO sensors to heat detectors, that work seamlessly together to create a real-time, adaptive network of protection. Whether installed in a high-rise building or a family home, the Kidde system\'s integration with smart technologies ensures swift alerts, allowing for immediate response and peace of mind.</p>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"b025d679-d1f4-4574-9f38-3631050e33a5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Kidde Fire Protection System</strong> doesn&rsquo;t just react; it actively adapts to changing conditions, improving its sensitivity and response times as needed. Its fire suppression mechanism powered by state-of-the-art suppression agents neutralizes flames quickly and efficiently, without compromising the surrounding environment. Through its innovative hybrid approach, combining both active suppression and passive protection, the system minimizes damage while maximizing safety. The Kidde system&rsquo;s ability to integrate with other smart home technologies means it&rsquo;s not only a guardian in times of crisis, but a forward-thinking solution that evolves alongside modern living spaces. From the reassuring &ldquo;chirp&rdquo; of a smoke detector during a routine check to the cutting-edge fire extinguishing capabilities in an emergency, Kidde ensures that every moment is backed by security, sophistication, and advanced safety engineering.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\r\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_4-ICCtdzZA3N.webp', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_3-hwhmwPoS1S.jpg', '2024-11-25 05:19:33.402034', '2024-11-25 05:19:33.409363', 30, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JWLJ_fShFTI?si=DGvYZ0GPZ_WeopbL\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(31, '<p><strong>Fairbanks Morse Fire Protection System</strong> stands as a testament to engineering excellence, providing comprehensive fire safety solutions for both industrial and commercial environments. Designed with resilience in mind, the system features an array of advanced detection and suppression technologies that offer unparalleled protection against the unpredictable dangers of fire. With its powerful, high-sensitivity smoke and heat detectors, the Fairbanks Morse system is capable of identifying threats in real time, whether in vast manufacturing facilities or in intricate, high-risk zones such as power plants and chemical storage areas. The system integrates seamlessly with automated building controls, offering instant alerts and direct responses to emerging fire hazards, allowing for swift intervention and minimizing the risk of property damage and personal harm. Its rugged, industrial-grade construction ensures that it remains reliable even in the most challenging environments, maintaining peak performance under pressure.</p>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f0808105-07f7-4912-9dc3-81c72a3097ba\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Fairbanks Morse Fire Protection System</strong> apart is its cutting-edge suppression technology, engineered for efficiency and environmental consideration. The system utilizes a range of suppression agents ranging from water-based systems to advanced clean agents tailored to the specific needs of each facility. This versatility ensures that fires are quickly extinguished without causing additional harm to sensitive equipment or operations. Fairbanks Morse\'s sophisticated integration of both active and passive fire protection strategies allows for adaptive, site-specific solutions, responding dynamically to different risk profiles. Whether it\'s a large-scale industrial plant or a specialized data center, this system offers peace of mind by combining intelligent detection with fast-acting suppression, all wrapped in a durable, high-performance package. The result is a fire protection solution that not only meets regulatory requirements but sets new standards for safety, efficiency, and technological innovation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\r\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_po-grqXylgKvC.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ss_mo_po-GDflGUE1lI.jpg', '2024-11-25 05:27:14.745069', '2024-11-25 05:27:14.753322', 31, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rcnajiZ46Ww?si=7nb24-trD21ruQX9\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(32, '<p><strong>Honeywell Fire Detection Alarm System</strong> is a cutting-edge solution that blends precision engineering with advanced technology to provide unmatched fire safety for both commercial and residential applications. Designed with a keen focus on early detection and rapid response, this system uses a network of highly sensitive smoke, heat, and CO detectors to identify potential hazards at their earliest stages. Its seamless integration with building management systems ensures that alerts are triggered instantly, with real-time notifications sent to both on-site personnel and emergency responders. The sleek, modern design of the Honeywell system allows for unobtrusive installation, yet it never compromises on its life-saving capabilities. From the moment a threat is detected, the system springs into action, ensuring swift evacuation and minimal damage to property. With easy-to-use interfaces and customizable settings, Honeywell provides a reliable safety net that adapts to any environment, be it a high-rise office tower, industrial complex, or a hospital.</p>', '<p><strong>Honeywell Fire Detection Alarm System</strong> apart is its unmatched scalability and precision. Whether deployed in a small building or a large, multi-site operation, this system can be expanded and adapted to meet the unique needs of each space. Honeywell&rsquo;s intuitive alarm panels allow for instant assessment and control, offering advanced diagnostics and fault detection to ensure continuous, optimal performance. The system also integrates seamlessly with advanced suppression systems, offering both automatic fire suppression and alarm notifications to minimize the impact of a fire. In the event of an emergency, the alarms not only notify occupants but also activate pre-programmed safety measures such as ventilation shutdowns or sprinkler systems. With Honeywell, fire safety is no longer just a precaution&mdash;it\'s a fully integrated, intelligent response designed to protec