to every corner of a building.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ES_2-HEEqzr3W0W.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-ES_1-z8kp3tYU4U.jpg', '2024-11-25 06:11:56.643278', '2024-11-25 06:11:56.648368', 41, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZFz6CMTL3x4?si=N2OkeCf73m5yBZQa\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(42, '<p><strong>Orena Fire Detection Alarm System</strong> is an advanced, high-performance solution designed to provide unparalleled fire safety for both residential and commercial environments. Built with cutting-edge detection technologies, Orena integrates a combination of smoke, heat, and multi-sensor detectors to deliver swift, accurate identification of fire hazards. The system\'s sophisticated algorithms ensure that even the smallest traces of smoke or heat are detected with precision, while minimizing the risk of false alarms. Its sleek, modern design allows for seamless integration into a wide range of building types, offering unobtrusive protection that blends perfectly with the surrounding environment. The Orena system also boasts an intuitive control panel that provides real-time data, diagnostics, and instant alerts to keep both occupants and emergency responders informed during a fire event, ensuring that timely action can be taken to protect lives and property.</p>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"c540f181-efe3-43b8-aeb1-c92155cde8a7\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Orena Fire Detection Alarm System</strong> apart is its scalability and adaptability, designed to meet the needs of both small-scale installations and large, complex systems. Whether deployed in a single residential unit or an expansive multi-site facility, Orena offers a flexible solution that can be easily customized to suit any environment. The system&rsquo;s advanced communication features, including remote monitoring and cloud integration, provide building managers with constant access to rea