(43, '<p><strong>Garrett Handheld Metal Detector</strong> is a powerful and compact security tool designed for precision detection in a wide range of environments, from high-security venues to casual event settings. Known for its durability and reliability, this handheld device quickly and efficiently detects metal objects, making it an essential tool for security personnel, law enforcement, and event organizers. The detector&rsquo;s ergonomic design ensures comfort during extended use, while its lightweight build allows for easy handling and portability. Featuring both audible and visual indicators, the Garrett metal detector provides immediate feedback when metal is detected, ensuring a fast and seamless security process. Whether used for screening individuals at airports, concerts, or public events, the Garrett Handheld Metal Detector provides high sensitivity and reliability in a simple-to-use package.</p>', '<p><strong>Garrett Handheld Metal Detector</strong> is its versatility and adaptability to various security needs. With adjustable sensitivity settings, the device can be fine-tuned to detect a wide range of metal objects, from large weapons to smaller, concealed items. The system&rsquo;s wide detection area allows for efficient and thorough screening, while its rugged construction ensures it can withstand tough environments and repeated use. Designed for efficiency, the Garrett detector includes features such as a low battery indicator and a streamlined power-on mechanism for quick deployment. Whether used in high-traffic locations or more controlled settings, the Garrett Handheld Metal Detector provides enhanced security with ease of use, ensuring effective and rapid detection while maintaining the safety and comfort of those being screened.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-garret_2-vz3ophjUOB.webp', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-garret_1-OkLj1fsQrd.jpg', '2024-11-25 06:45:19.062899', '2024-11-25 06:48:19.722747', 43, '<p style=\"te