(44, '<p><strong><em>ZKTeco Handheld Metal Detector</em></strong> is a state-of-the-art security tool designed for precise and efficient metal detection in a variety of settings, from high-risk environments to everyday security operations. Lightweight yet durable, the ZKTeco detector is built for comfort and ease of use, featuring an ergonomic handle that allows security personnel to conduct thorough screenings without fatigue. Equipped with advanced sensor technology, the device offers high sensitivity, detecting even the smallest metal objects, whether it\'s concealed weapons, tools, or everyday items. The system provides both audible and visual alerts, ensuring quick feedback to the user when metal is detected, facilitating faster and more efficient security checks. Whether used at airports, stadiums, or large public events, the ZKTeco Handheld Metal Detector delivers reliable and consistent performance, ensuring enhanced security without compromising speed.</p>', '<p><strong>ZKTeco Handheld Metal Detector</strong> apart is its versatility and user-friendly design. With adjustable sensitivity settings, the device can be fine-tuned to detect a wide range of metal objects, allowing security personnel to tailor their screening process based on the specific threat level or environment. The device&rsquo;s high-performance design also includes features such as low battery indicators and quick power-up capabilities, making it a reliable tool in high-demand situations. Its lightweight build and compact size make it easy to carry and deploy, while its rugged construction ensures it can endure frequent use in various weather conditions. Whether you\'re securing an airport, conducting a routine search at a concert, or ensuring safety at a government building, the ZKTeco Handheld Metal Detector offers powerful, efficient, and portable security solutions, giving peace of mind with every sweep.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_1-oE1TrP9ljT.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_2-2q7EEBzJD9.png', '2024-11-25 06:48:06.916491', '2024-11-25 06:48:06.920037', 44, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zz60MmGxhqE?si=YJbKI9sNu6S55hJe\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
