(46, '<p><strong>ZKTeco Turns Style</strong> is a cutting-edge, high-performance turnstile designed to enhance access control and streamline security in a variety of settings, from corporate offices and airports to entertainment venues and public buildings. With its sleek, modern design, the ZKTeco Turnstile seamlessly blends advanced technology with aesthetic appeal, making it a versatile and stylish addition to any entrance. Equipped with optical sensors, the turnstile ensures smooth and secure passage, automatically detecting and controlling the flow of individuals while preventing unauthorized access. Whether in high-traffic environments or in spaces requiring high-security, the ZKTeco Turnstile provides both efficiency and safety, offering real-time monitoring and automatic adjustments based on traffic patterns. It features robust construction and low maintenance requirements, ensuring durability and long-term performance without sacrificing style or functionality.</p>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"d25ee4a6-db83-4582-968c-629c65c7c85d\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>ZKTeco Turnstile</strong> is its seamless integration with a wide range of access control systems, including biometric, RFID, and QR code scanners, providing a flexible, adaptable solution for any facility. The turnstile\'s intuitive design allows for smooth entry and exit, with both single and double-lane models available to accommodate varying levels of traffic. Its advanced control options enable customization, allowing operators to set parameters such as speed, direction, and access policies, ensuring maximum security and convenience. Designed with user experience in mind, the ZKTeco Turnstile offers a highly responsive, fast, and secure passage solution, reducing congestion while improving operational efficiency. Whether securing a corporate office building, an airport terminal, or a large event venue, the ZKTeco Turnstile combines cutting-edge security features with sleek, modern design, offering the perfect balance of safety and style.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\r\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_11-YkO9lfVTPu.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-zk_111-T01WxQhQw2.jpg', '2024-11-25 06:59:49.586311', '2024-11-25 06:59:49.592125', 46, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EtztGEP6auk?si=vuDxQl_Xj-P7h72l\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(47, '<p><strong>MAG Turnstile</strong> is a premium access control solution designed to provide seamless security and efficient crowd management in a variety of high-traffic environments. With its sleek, modern aesthetic and robust construction, the MAG Turnstile combines cutting-edge technology with a user-friendly experience, making it ideal for corporate offices, government buildings, transportation hubs, and entertainment venues. Built to withstand the demands of constant use, the MAG Turnstile offers smooth, precise operation with minimal maintenance, ensuring both security and longevity. Featuring integrated optical sensors, the turnstile detects movement in real-time, allowing for secure, one-way passage while preventing unauthorized entry. Its advanced anti-tailgating capabilities further enhance security, ensuring that only one person can pass at a time, even in busy, fast-paced settings.</p>', '<p><strong>MAG Turnstile </strong>apart is its versatility and adaptability to various access control systems. The turnstile easily integrates with biometric, RFID, and QR code-based authentication methods, providing flexibility and ease of use for both staff and visitors. The intuitive interface allows for smooth operation and real-time monitoring, enabling security personnel to customize settings such as passage speed, access policies, and directional flow to suit the specific needs of the facility. Available in both single and double-lane models, the MAG Turnstile is designed to handle high volumes of foot traffic without compromising security or efficiency. Whether you\'re managing access at an office building, a stadium, or a transport terminal, the MAG Turnstile provides a reliable, stylish, and high-performance solution that elevates both security and user experience in any space.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-mag_12-hdrpqcv9f2.jpg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-mag_13-zY4C2VFm1N.jpg', '2024-11-25 07:05:18.280152', '2024-11-25 07:05:29.477713', 47, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9-ASDskefGk?si=vtmQQYzQ5A8Y0VEd\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(48, '<p><strong>Hikvision Turnstile</strong> is a state-of-the-art access control solution that combines advanced security features with sleek, modern design to streamline entry management in high-traffic environments. Whether installed in corporate offices, airports, or large public venues, this turnstile offers smooth and efficient passage while ensuring robust security. Equipped with cutting edge optical sensors, the Hikvision Turnstile provides precise control of access, preventing unauthorized entry and ensuring that only one person can pass at a time. Its durable construction is built to withstand frequent use, while its minimalistic design integrates seamlessly into any architectural style, elevating the aesthetics of any entryway. The turnstile&rsquo;s high reliability and easy-to-use interface make it the ideal choice for environments where security and efficiency are paramount.</p>', '<p><strong>Hikvision Turnstile</strong> is its seamless integration with a wide range of access control systems, including biometric, RFID, and facial recognition technologies, providing flexible, high-security solutions for any application. The turnstile can be configured to match specific user needs, from controlling access to restricted areas to managing large crowds at events. With its intelligent algorithms, the Hikvision Turnstile detects and prevents tailgating and piggybacking, ensuring that only authorized individuals gain access. Additionally, the system supports real-time monitoring, allowing security personnel to manage and track foot traffic effortlessly. With customizable features, enhanced security protocols, and a sleek, contemporary design, the Hikvision Turnstile offers an ideal balance of technology, style, and security, making it a premium choice for any facility seeking to improve both its safety and user experience.</p>', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-hik_2-z0DYfp1fyj.jpeg', 'brands/2024-11-BrandDetail_object_None-hik_1-Ae11UJ9ckm.jpg', '2024-11-25 07:08:33.260945', '2024-11-25 07:08:33.266568', 48, '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KRMFG4lam7M?si=5NGBGtWtdbKayfeg\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>'),
(50, '<p><strong>HONEYWELL Paging System</strong> delivers cutting-edge communication solutions tailored for seamless and efficient message broadcasting in various environments. Designed with advanced technology, HONEYWELL\'s paging systems ensure crystal-clear audio transmission and reliability, making them ideal for commercial buildings, healthcare facilities, educational institutions, and industrial complexes. Known for their durability and user-friendly interfaces, HONEYWELL Paging Systems integrate effortlessly with existing infrastructure, providing scalable solutions that enhance safety and operational efficiency. With a commitment to innovation and quality, HONEYWELL continues to set the standard in paging and communication systems.</p>', '<p><strong>HONEYWELL Paging System</strong> represents a synthesis of superior engineering and functionality, offering comprehensive paging solutions for diverse sectors. These systems are renowned for their robust performance, ease of use, and high-quality audio output, which facilitate effective communication across vast spaces. The HONEYWELL Paging System\'s adaptability ensures it meets the unique demands of each environment, whether it\'s for emergency alerts or routine announcements. Emphasizing safety and convenience, HONEYWELL\'s innovative paging technologies are a trusted choice for organizations seeking dependable and efficient communication tools.</p>', 'brands/2025-01-BrandDetail_object_None-000-X1P6apCOiI.PNG', 'brands/2025-01-BrandDetail_object_None-0000-zVvN4APJZ5.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:21:39.954941', '2025-01-22 02:21:39.961870', 50, '<p><a title=\"HONEYWELL Paging System\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whFGoP8M_ZE\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whFGoP8M_ZE</a></p>'),
(51, '<p><strong>DAOSAFE Turnstile Gate</strong>&nbsp;offer an advanced solution for secure and efficient access control. Designed with state-of-the-art technology, these gates provide seamless integration into modern security systems. DAOSAFE Turnstile Gates are known for their robust construction, sleek design, and reliable performance, making them ideal for high-traffic environments such as corporate offices, government buildings, and transportation hubs. With features like biometric authentication, RFID card access, and real-time monitoring, DAOSAFE ensures both safety and convenience for users.</p>', '<p><strong>DAOSAFE Turnstile Gates</strong> are engineered to deliver superior security with a focus on user-friendly operation. These gates combine durability with aesthetic appeal, ensuring they fit seamlessly into any environment. Equipped with cutting-edge technology, DAOSAFE Turnstile Gates support various access control methods, including facial recognition, fingerprint scanning, and mobile credentialing. Their efficient throughput and minimal maintenance requirements make them a preferred choice for enhancing security without compromising on style or functionality.</p>', 'brands/2025-01-BrandDetail_object_None-00-hOEhvM6ENr.PNG', 'brands/2025-01-BrandDetail_object_None-000-sKxGB3NtOe.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:55:42.509684', '2025-01-22 03:00:00.553039', 51, '<p><a title=\"DAOSAFE Turnstile Gates\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kQEsMvlQMk\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kQEsMvlQMk</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"DAOSAFE Turnstile Gates\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kQEsMvlQMk\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9kQEsMvlQMk</a></p>');
