(22, '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"910e7db8-49c5-4212-b751-489d3a53cf45\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Garrett Multi Zone Walk-Through </strong>Metal Detector offers a sleek, user-friendly interface with clear LED indicators and an intuitive control panel. Its robust construction ensures long-term reliability in busy environments, while its high detection capabilities provide superior threat detection without compromising on throughput. The detector is capable of screening large volumes of people quickly, making it ideal for venues with high security needs. Additionally, its low maintenance and energy-efficient design contribute to reduced operational costs, making the Garrett Multi Zone a trusted and cost-effective solution for organizations seeking advanced, reliable metal detection technology.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'products/garrett-multi-zone-walk-through-metal-detector/features/202411-11-key_4-6rIGGJaven.jpg', '2024-11-26 08:44:04.166854', '2024-11-26 08:44:40.322116', 11),
(23, '<p><strong>ZKTeco PB4000 Boom Barrier</strong> is a top-tier traffic control solution that combines advanced technology with robust design to offer seamless vehicle access management. Featuring a powerful motor, the PB4000 ensures rapid and smooth operation, allowing the boom arm to open and close quickly to optimize traffic flow. Its durable build is engineered to withstand harsh environmental conditions, making it ideal for outdoor use in parking lots, toll booths, and restricted access areas. With a customizable boom arm length, the ZKTeco PB4000 provides flexibility for a wide range of applications, ensuring it meets the needs of both high and low traffic areas.</p>', 'products/pb4000-boom-barrier/features/202411-12-key_feature_1-SvWHedMLrA.jpg', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.736012', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.740220', 12),
(24, '<p><strong>ZKTeco PB4000</strong> is its integration with modern access control systems, making it easy to manage and monitor vehicle movement. The barrier supports various control options, including RFID, remote control, and vehicle detection systems, offering flexibility and convenience. Additionally, the boom barrier is designed for easy installation and low maintenance, reducing downtime and operational costs. Whether for residential, commercial, or industrial applications, the ZKTeco PB4000 ensures a reliable, secure, and efficient solution for vehicle access management, contributing to enhanced security and smooth traffic control at all times.</p>', 'products/pb4000-boom-barrier/features/202411-12-key_feaure_1-dPYM8UphrO.png', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.742080', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.744243', 12),
(25, '<p>The <strong>ZKTeco CMP200 Boom Barrier</strong> is an advanced, high-performance vehicle access control solution designed to offer efficient and secure management of vehicle flow. Built with a powerful motor and a robust chassis, the CMP200 ensures smooth and reliable operation even in high-traffic areas. Its high-speed opening and closing mechanism helps minimize wait times, enhancing overall traffic flow at entrances and exits. With a range of customizable boom arm lengths, the CMP200 is versatile and can be adapted to a variety of applications, including parking lots, toll stations, and industrial sites, offering both security and convenience.</p>', 'products/zkteco-cmp200-boom-barrier/features/202411-13-ss_12-levJ5VJSCy.PNG', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.300835', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.303567', 13),
(26, '<p><strong>ZKTeco CMP200</strong> comes with multiple access control options, including RFID, remote control, and vehicle detection systems, providing seamless and flexible management of vehicle entry. The boom barrier&rsquo;s weather-resistant design ensures durability in all conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor environments. Furthermore, its low-maintenance operation reduces the total cost of ownership, while its simple installation process ensures quick deployment. With its advanced features, reliable performance, and sleek design, the ZKTeco CMP200 is the ideal choice for businesses seeking a durable and efficient solution for controlling vehicle access.</p>', 'products/zkteco-cmp200-boom-barrier/features/202411-13-ss_13-4QghrF2d3w.PNG', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.305292', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.307924', 13),
(29, '<p>The <strong>ZKTeco ProBG3000 Boom Barrier</strong> is a high-performance vehicle access solution designed for heavy-duty traffic control in both commercial and industrial settings. Built with a powerful motor and an ultra-durable casing, the ProBG3000 offers smooth, reliable operation even under high usage conditions. Its fast opening and closing times ensure efficient vehicle flow, making it ideal for parking facilities, toll stations, and entry points with high traffic volumes. The ProBG3000 features an adjustable boom arm, allowing customization based on specific application needs, providing flexibility for a wide range of vehicle access scenarios. Whether in extreme weather conditions or heavy traffic areas, this barrier is engineered to offer long-lasting performance.</p>', 'products/bgm1000-boom-barrier/features/202411-15-ss_24-wrZITLg6dG.PNG', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.543331', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.546443', 15),
(30, '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"8ac96f55-7032-4d30-bb7a-cd5c50994aab\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>ZKTeco ProBG3000</strong> is equipped with advanced access control capabilities, including support for RFID, remote control, and vehicle detection systems, enabling seamless integration into existing security setups. The barrier&rsquo;s intelligent design also ensures low maintenance requirements, reducing operational costs and downtime. Its weatherproof construction guarantees reliable performance in outdoor environments, making it suitable for both residential and commercial use. Easy to install and configure, the ProBG3000 is a highly efficient solution for managing vehicle access, offering both security and convenience while enhancing the overall management of vehicle traffic flow.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\r\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\r\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'products/bgm1000-boom-barrier/features/202411-15-ss_122-A2IYyVsgfj.PNG', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.548679', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.551353', 15),
(31, '<p>The <strong>Avtech Room Alert 32S</strong> is an advanced environmental monitoring solution designed to protect critical infrastructure from potential risks such as temperature fluctuations, humidity changes, and power failures. Equipped with 32 sensor inputs, the Room Alert 32S allows users to monitor a wide range of environmental conditions in real-time. Its scalable design makes it suitable for monitoring small server rooms or large data centers. The device offers detailed alerts and notifications, helping users take immediate action to prevent equipment damage, downtime, or data loss, making it an essential tool for businesses that rely on sensitive equipment and data storage.</p>', 'products/avtech-room-alert-32s/features/202412-16-32_2-I2u8j3IovT.webp', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.935132', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.938661', 16),
(32, '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\r\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"e383c5a8-c580-4766-84d8-79c9bcaf7f80\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\r\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\r\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\r\n<p><strong>Avtech Room Alert 32S</strong> provides easy access to environmental data and sensor readings from anywhere. The device is compatible with a variety of sensors and supports integration with third-party systems, allowing for customized monitoring solutions. It also offers secure remote monitoring capabilities, ensuring that users can keep track of their environments 24/7. With its robust performance, low maintenance needs, and reliable alerts, the Room Alert 32S helps businesses ensure operational continuity, reduce downtime, and maintain compliance with industry standards.<button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'products/avtech-room-alert-32s/features/202412-16-32_1-lIPrvJUiKW.jpg', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.940212', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.942280', 16),
(33, '<p>The <strong>LX50 Fingerprint and RFID Time-Keeping Device</strong> offers a range of key features to enhance your time and attendance management. &nbsp;Self-Service Reporting (SSR) allows small chain stores to easily access and manage employee time records directly from the device. &nbsp;Data Redaction ensures employee privacy by enabling the redaction of sensitive information in Excel format. &nbsp;USB Host &amp; USB Client capabilities facilitate seamless data transfer and integration with other systems. &nbsp;The smart shape design offers a user-friendly and visually appealing design.</p>', 'products/lx50-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-devices/features/202501-17-Zkteco_LX50-l_fREjwEs.PNG', '2025-01-02 05:49:57.564073', '2025-01-02 05:55:56.101977', 17),
(34, '<p>Fingerprint &amp; RFID technology provides accurate and reliable employee identification and access control. &nbsp;The LX50 is equipped with advanced fingerprint technology for fast and accurate identification, minimizing time theft and streamlining payroll processing. Its RFID capabilities offer added flexibility for businesses using employee ID cards or other RFID-enabled devices. &nbsp;The LX50 is built to be durable and reliable, withstanding the demands of everyday use in a variety of environments.</p>', 'products/lx50-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-devices/features/202501-17-Zkteco_key_fe_pMA1cfa.PNG', '2025-01-02 05:49:57.570506', '2025-01-02 05:55:56.105435', 17),
(35, '<p>Experience the future of time and attendance management with the <strong>K14-ID Fingerprint and RFID Time Keeping Device</strong>. This state-of-the-art device combines fingerprint and RFID capabilities to provide a comprehensive and secure solution for tracking employee hours. The K14-ID boasts advanced technology that ensures accurate and rapid fingerprint recognition, minimizing errors and streamlining the timekeeping process. Its compact and durable design makes it suitable for various workplace environments, while its versatile features cater to the specific needs of businesses of all sizes.</p>', 'products/k14-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-device/features/202501-18-4-6DHufzF6yu.PNG', '2025-01-02 06:31:36.703541', '2025-01-03 01:18:36.411579', 18),
(36, '<p>The <strong>K14-ID Fingerprint and RFID Time Keeping Device</strong>&nbsp;is packed with features that make it a standout choice for businesses seeking a reliable and efficient time and attendance solution. At its core lies advanced fingerprint technology that ensures fast and accurate identification, minimizing the risk of \"buddy punching\" and ensuring accurate payroll calculations. The integrated RFID reader offers added convenience and security, allowing employees to quickly and easily clock in and out using their unique RFID cards. The K14-ID also boasts a robust and durable design, making it suitable for even the most demanding work environments.</p>', 'products/k14-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-device/features/202501-18-5-3dtVWYtLKv.PNG', '2025-01-02 06:31:36.708155', '2025-01-03 01:18:36.416237', 18),
(37, '<p>Empower your workforce with the <strong>IN02A-ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Contro</strong>l, a pioneering time and attendance terminal that seamlessly blends advanced biometric technology with robust access control features. This compact and versatile device redefines efficiency and security, delivering a comprehensive solution for businesses of all sizes. At the heart of IN02A-ID\'s excellence lies its state-of-the-art fingerprint recognition technology. With lightning-fast response times and exceptional accuracy, it ensures seamless identification of authorized personnel, eliminating the risk of unauthorized access. The system\'s robust algorithm and high-resolution sensor guarantee unparalleled reliability, even in challenging lighting conditions.</p>', 'products/in02a-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control/features/202501-19-99_Hm20rq8.jpg', '2025-01-02 07:08:40.549767', '2025-01-03 01:19:07.602182', 19),
(38, '<p><strong>IN02A-ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Contro</strong> offers unparalleled connectivity options, empowering you to seamlessly integrate it into your existing IT infrastructure. Whether you prefer wired or wireless communication, the device supports a range of protocols, including TCP/IP, USB, and RS485. This flexibility ensures effortless data transfer and seamless integration with existing access control systems and time and attendance software.IN02A-ID boasts a sleek and compact design that blends seamlessly into any environment. <span class=\"citation-1 recitation citation-end-1\">Its intuitive user interface and large, high-resolution display make it easy to operate, even for non-technical users.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></span> The device\'s ergonomic design and durable construction ensure long-lasting reliability and minimal maintenance requirements.</p>', 'products/in02a-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control/features/202501-19-10_8NGLbJa.jpg', '2025-01-02 07:08:40.556269', '2025-01-03 01:19:07.606739', 19),
(39, '<p>At the heart of the <span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\"><strong>ZKTeco F7-C ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control</strong></span> lies its advanced fingerprint recognition capabilities. <span class=\"citation-5 recitation citation-end-5\">Equipped with a high-resolution optical sensor, the device captures clear and detailed fingerprint images, ensuring accurate and reliable identification.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></span> <span class=\"citation-6 recitation citation-end-6\">Its advanced algorithms analyze fingerprint minutiae with precision, minimizing false rejection and acceptance rates.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></span> This combination of hardware and software delivers exceptional performance, making it ideal for high-traffic environments and applications where security is paramount.</p>', 'products/f7-c-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control/features/202501-20-s-l_Y0YM2Lz.jpg', '2025-01-02 07:57:27.164747', '2025-01-03 01:19:57.485275', 20),
(40, '<p><span class=\"citation-10 recitation citation-end-10\">Beyond fingerprint recognition, the <span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\"><strong>ZKTeco F7-C ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control</strong></span> supports various access control methods, enhancing its versatility.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"11\"><!----></sup></span> It can be configured to accept RFID cards, providing an alternative or supplementary access method. This multi-factor authentication approach enhances security by adding an extra layer of protection. <span class=\"citation-11 recitation citation-end-11\">Furthermore, the F7-C supports various user management features, including user enrollment, access level assignment, and event logs.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"12\"><!----></sup></span> These features facilitate efficient user management and provide valuable insights into access control activities.</p>', 'products/f7-c-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control/features/202501-20-BKW_iVVZ09k.jpg', '2025-01-02 07:57:27.169326', '2025-01-03 01:19:57.489499', 20),
(47, '<p>The Ajax Hub Protect is an advanced security system designed to offer top-tier protection for both residential and commercial properties. Equipped with cutting-edge wireless technology, this hub ensures seamless integration with a range of Ajax devices, providing comprehensive coverage for all entry points. Its high-grade encryption guarantees secure communication between connected devices, preventing any unauthorized access or tampering. The Hub Protect is also designed to work efficiently in various environments, from homes to larger commercial spaces, ensuring reliable performance even in demanding conditions. With its user-friendly interface, the system allows for easy setup and management via the Ajax app, giving users full control over their security settings. The system also features a built-in backup battery that ensures continuous protection even during power outages.</p>', 'products/hub-protect/features/202501-31-hub_12-3vEV42EHrd.jpg', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.896752', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.899592', 31),
(48, '<p>Ajax Hub Protect include its robust wireless capabilities, offering enhanced range and stability for connecting to sensors and other devices. The system also benefits from a powerful processor that ensures rapid response times and effective management of security alerts. Another key feature is its adaptability, with the hub being compatible with a wide range of Ajax devices, including motion detectors, cameras, and door/window sensors. The Hub Protect also supports remote control and monitoring, allowing users to access real-time data and updates from anywhere using a mobile device. Furthermore, the device is designed with a sleek, compact structure that can easily blend into any interior setting. Lastly, the system offers scalability, making it ideal for future expansion as security needs evolve.</p>', 'products/hub-protect/features/202501-31-ss-HIXqJkPVdW.PNG', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.901144', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.903964', 31),
(49, '<p>Motion Protect Plus is designed to provide unparalleled motion detection accuracy, ensuring reliable security without false alarms. Its advanced sensor technology distinguishes between genuine threats and harmless movements, such as pets or environmental factors like wind. This precision minimizes unnecessary alerts, allowing users to focus on real security concerns. Ideal for both residential and commercial settings, Motion Protect Plus offers peace of mind with its smart detection capabilities, ensuring consistent and dependable performance.</p>', 'products/security-systems/motion-protect-plus/features/202501-32-motion_7-8C55gWko1o.jpg', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.504781', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.507900', 32),
(50, '<p>The device integrates dual-motion detection technologies infrared and microwave sensors for enhanced protection against intrusion. This dual-layer system ensures that any detected motion undergoes a rigorous verification process, eliminating potential errors from a single-sensor setup. The addition of microwave sensing not only improves detection accuracy but also enhances the device\'s ability to perform in challenging environments, such as areas with high heat or humidity. This robust system makes Motion Protect Plus an indispensable component of any modern security setup.</p>', 'products/security-systems/motion-protect-plus/features/202501-32-motion_8-3l73eNDGl2.jpg', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.509687', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.512138', 32),
(51, '<p><strong>Combi Protect Plus</strong> offers comprehensive protection with its advanced combination of security and performance features. Designed to safeguard your website against cyber threats, it provides real-time monitoring and automated security updates, ensuring that your online presence is always secure. With built-in malware scanning and vulnerability assessments, Combi Protect Plus proactively identifies and eliminates potential risks, preventing any disruptions to your business operations. This all-encompassing protection ensures that your website remains safe, providing peace of mind and boosting customer trust.</p>', 'products/Combi-Protect/features/202501-33-motion_7-JqCU9EQEas.jpg', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.868564', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.871439', 33),
(52, '<p><strong>Combi Protect Plus</strong> enhances website performance by optimizing load speeds and reducing downtime. It includes advanced caching mechanisms and content delivery network (CDN) integration, helping your website load faster and perform more efficiently across global locations. This not only improves user experience but also contributes to higher SEO rankings, making your site more visible to search engines. With its user-friendly interface and seamless integration, Combi Protect Plus is the ideal solution for businesses looking to improve both security and site performance.</p>', 'products/Combi-Protect/features/202501-33-motion_8-dC2qkD8LK2.jpg', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.873067', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.875568', 33),
(53, '<p><strong>Multi-Verification Authentication</strong>: The ZKTeco MultiBio 800 ID offers a comprehensive access control solution with multi-verification capabilities, including fingerprint recognition, facial identification, and RFID card support. This flexibility ensures high security and convenience, allowing organizations to choose the most suitable method for different users and environments.</p>', 'products/multibio-800-id/features/202501-34-3-BR2JLPrMyw.PNG', '2025-01-06 02:47:49.923407', '2025-01-10 05:11:34.978764', 34),
