(261, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EDC-M9102 + EDBM01 Edwards Conventional Fire Alarm System provides reliable and efficient fire detection solutions for a variety of commercial and industrial applications. Featuring a state-of-the-art, user-friendly design, this system supports up to 10 zones, ensuring comprehensive coverage across large areas. Its versatile panel offers easy integration with a wide range of detectors and accessories, providing flexibility for customized installations. The system also includes advanced diagnostic capabilities, allowing for quick identification of issues and minimizing downtime during maintenance.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-edc-m9102-edbm01/features/202501-139-A-6XT4qby6qM.PNG', '2025-01-16 08:23:54.732433', '2025-01-16 08:23:54.735440', 139),
(262, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">EDC-M9102 + EDBM01 system is designed for simplicity and ease of operation. With clear visual and audible alerts, it ensures fast and reliable communication during emergencies. The system is engineered with compliance to national safety standards, guaranteeing a high level of protection. Its robust construction and proven performance make it an ideal choice for ensuring safety in schools, office buildings, hospitals, and other public facilities.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-edc-m9102-edbm01/features/202501-139-C-OnnghN5TUH.PNG', '2025-01-16 08:23:54.737489', '2025-01-16 08:23:54.739731', 139),
(263, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EDBM01 Edwards Conventional Fire Alarm System is designed to provide reliable and efficient fire detection for commercial and industrial environments. This system offers exceptional functionality with its easy-to-use interface, ensuring quick setup and seamless operation. The system is engineered with high-sensitivity detection capabilities, delivering rapid and accurate alerts for potential fire hazards. Its compatibility with a wide range of Edwards devices allows for flexible configuration tailored to your facility\'s unique safety needs.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-edbm01/features/202501-140-F-8Za6cmFJZS.PNG', '2025-01-16 08:32:08.027473', '2025-01-16 08:32:08.030243', 140),
(264, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">the EDBM01 is housed in a robust enclosure to withstand challenging environments. The system also features advanced noise immunity, reducing the risk of false alarms and ensuring dependable performance in high-interference areas. Its modular design supports easy expansion, making it a scalable solution for growing facilities. Whether for a small business or a large industrial complex, the EDBM01 Edwards Conventional System is a reliable choice to ensure maximum safety and peace of mind.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-edbm01/features/202501-140-E-2ePpJp8q5q.PNG', '2025-01-16 08:32:08.031814', '2025-01-16 08:32:08.034808', 140),
(265, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SIGA-OSD Edwards Addressable Smoke Detector is a cutting-edge solution designed to enhance fire safety through advanced addressable technology. This device offers pinpoint accuracy in detecting smoke, enabling faster and more precise responses during emergencies. Its addressable feature allows seamless integration into fire alarm systems, providing real-time identification of the exact location of potential hazards. With its modern design and robust performance, the SIGA-OSD ensures optimal functionality in diverse environments, from commercial buildings to industrial facilities.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-osd/features/202501-141-D-g30uCUxWaE.png', '2025-01-16 08:41:57.049840', '2025-01-16 08:41:57.053049', 141),
(266, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">SIGA-OSD is equipped with self-diagnostic capabilities that reduce maintenance downtime and enhance overall system longevity. Its advanced sensitivity settings minimize false alarms, ensuring uninterrupted operation and peace of mind. Additionally, the device supports a wide range of network configurations, offering scalability for large and small setups alike. With compliance to industry standards and an easy installation process, the SIGA-OSD Edwards Addressable Smoke Detector is a superior choice for fire safety professionals seeking innovative and dependable solutions.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-osd/features/202501-141-image-removebg-preview-GYS3JqpPBN.png', '2025-01-16 08:41:57.055142', '2025-01-16 08:41:57.057458', 141),
(267, '<p><strong> Energy-Efficient Design</strong></p>\r\n<p>The EDWARDS ADDRESSABLE G4AVRF + GRSW is designed with energy efficiency at its core. Its use of high-performance LEDs reduces the need for extensive power supplies, backup power, and batteries. This not only lowers operational costs but also contributes to a greener, more sustainable environment. The low power consumption makes it ideal for buildings aiming to reduce their carbon footprint while ensuring robust fire safety.</p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-g4avrf-grsw/features/202501-142-edwards-est-g1avrf-fire-al_02VT5BP.webp', '2025-01-17 00:35:31.346934', '2025-01-17 00:35:31.350642', 142),
(268, '<p><strong>Advanced Addressable Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>Equipped with advanced addressable technology, the G4AVRF + GRSW allows for precise monitoring and rapid identification of alarm locations. This feature is critical in enhancing the speed and accuracy of emergency responses, enabling quicker evacuations and reducing potential damage. The device&rsquo;s ability to integrate with a variety of fire alarm control panels makes it a flexible and essential component in modern fire safety systems.</p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-g4avrf-grsw/features/202501-142-s-l1600-rkFhkoevtV.png', '2025-01-17 00:35:31.352609', '2025-01-17 00:35:31.355600', 142),
(269, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SIGA-278 Edwards Addressable Heat Detector is an advanced fire detection device designed to provide accurate and reliable temperature monitoring in a wide range of environments. Utilizing addressable technology, the SIGA-278 offers precise identification of the heat source, allowing for faster emergency responses. This intelligent device integrates seamlessly with existing fire alarm systems, enabling real-time data transmission to pinpoint the exact location of fire hazards. Its high-performance capabilities make it ideal for installations in areas prone to temperature fluctuations, such as industrial facilities, warehouses, and commercial buildings.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-278/features/202501-143-siga-278-lQSJbckfN9.jpg', '2025-01-17 00:40:17.252319', '2025-01-17 00:40:17.255639', 143),
(270, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">the SIGA-278 is equipped with advanced features such as adjustable sensitivity settings to reduce false alarms and optimize detection efficiency. The device supports easy installation and is fully compatible with various fire control panels, offering flexibility and scalability for any project size. Designed to meet the highest industry standards, the SIGA-278 Edwards Addressable Heat Detector ensures long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance, providing peace of mind and enhanced safety for both residential and commercial properties.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-278/features/202501-143-81ypu-zsjjl-sl1500--500x500-B_NQqyS9k.webp', '2025-01-17 00:40:17.257498', '2025-01-17 00:40:17.260131', 143),
(271, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The iO64G-2 Edwards Addressable Input/Output Module is an advanced and reliable device designed to integrate seamlessly into fire alarm systems for enhanced monitoring and control. This versatile module provides both input and output capabilities, making it ideal for managing various field devices like smoke detectors, manual call points, and other alarm system peripherals. With its addressable technology, the iO64G-2 ensures quick identification of connected devices, streamlining system management and enabling precise emergency responses. It is especially useful in large and complex fire safety systems where multiple devices need to be effectively monitored and controlled.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-io64g-2/features/202501-144-IO64G-SP__25084-96VVeX6kiU.jpg', '2025-01-17 00:50:37.759245', '2025-01-17 00:50:37.762016', 144),
(272, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">the iO64G-2 offers flexibility by supporting up to 64 devices on a single module. Its robust design ensures consistent performance in challenging environments, providing reliable input/output functionality for effective system operation. Compatible with a wide range of Edwards fire control panels, the iO64G-2 guarantees efficient system integration and scalability for both new installations and system upgrades. With its advanced features and high reliability, this module is the ideal choice for fire safety professionals seeking a high-performance solution for large-scale and multi-device fire alarm systems</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-io64g-2/features/202501-144-Edwards-iO64---iO1000-qo9Et1zlRL.jpg', '2025-01-17 00:50:37.763800', '2025-01-17 00:50:37.766801', 144),
(273, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SIGA-SB Edwards Addressable Smoke Beacon is a cutting-edge fire alarm notification device designed to provide clear and reliable visual alerts in smoke detection systems. Featuring advanced addressable technology, this beacon offers precise identification of alarm zones, allowing for faster and more effective response times in case of a fire emergency. Its high-visibility LED strobe light ensures that occupants can quickly identify the location of a fire hazard, even in noisy or high-traffic environments. Ideal for commercial, industrial, and residential applications, the SIGA-SB is an essential component of modern fire alarm systems.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-sb/features/202501-145-SIGA-SB-0GwUJbPeWc.webp', '2025-01-17 00:55:00.676741', '2025-01-17 00:55:00.679802', 145),
(274, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">the SIGA-SB provides consistent and reliable performance while reducing the likelihood of false alarms. The device is compatible with various Edwards fire control panels and is designed for easy installation and integration into existing addressable fire alarm systems. The compact and weather-resistant design makes it suitable for a wide range of indoor and outdoor settings. Whether you\'re managing large-scale buildings or smaller properties, the SIGA-SB Edwards Addressable Smoke Beacon offers enhanced safety and dependable notification capabilities, ensuring optimal fire protection for any environment</span></p>', 'products/edwards-addressable-siga-sb/features/202501-145-est_siga-sb-300x281-2Udy14mmu1.webp', '2025-01-17 00:55:00.681769', '2025-01-17 00:55:00.683825', 145),
