(286, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">2099-9103 is constructed from rugged materials that ensure reliable performance even in challenging environments. The pull station is UL-listed and meets stringent industry standards, guaranteeing dependable operation in commercial, industrial, and residential settings. Its straightforward installation process and compatibility with conventional fire alarm systems make it a practical and effective choice for enhancing fire safety measures. Whether for offices, schools, or manufacturing facilities, the 2099-9103 Simplex Manual Pull Station is a trusted solution for reliable manual fire alarm activation.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-2099-9103/features/202501-152-77-EVnEKAwlXg.PNG', '2025-01-17 01:46:07.376829', '2025-01-17 01:46:07.380782', 152),
(287, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 4902-9716 Simplex Conventional Audible Notification Appliance is a high-performance fire alarm device designed to deliver clear and reliable auditory alerts in emergency situations. This powerful notification appliance ensures that building occupants are promptly informed of potential fire hazards, enhancing overall safety and evacuation efficiency. Its conventional design allows seamless integration into existing fire alarm systems, making it a versatile solution for a wide range of applications, including commercial, industrial, and residential buildings.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4902-9716/features/202501-153-22-JDK8WYV7uG.PNG', '2025-01-17 01:59:12.914385', '2025-01-17 01:59:12.917180', 153),
(288, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">4902-9716 is engineered to perform consistently even in challenging environments. The device meets industry standards for fire safety, ensuring dependable operation during critical moments. Its efficient design minimizes power consumption while maintaining high sound output, making it an energy-efficient choice for fire notification systems. With an easy installation process and a robust construction, the 4902-9716 Simplex Audible Notification Appliance is the ideal choice for enhancing fire safety in any conventional fire alarm setup.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4902-9716/features/202501-153-44-NStLKghxAf.png', '2025-01-17 01:59:12.919138', '2025-01-17 01:59:12.922516', 153),
(289, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 4007-9801 Simplex Conventional Fire Alarm Control Panel offers a reliable and efficient solution for managing fire detection systems in a wide range of environments. Designed for ease of use and installation, this control panel integrates seamlessly with conventional fire alarm devices such as smoke detectors, manual pull stations, and notification appliances. The 4007-9801 provides a centralized point for monitoring and controlling fire alarm systems, ensuring that potential fire hazards are quickly detected and reported. Its simple interface and clear alarm indicators make it an ideal choice for commercial, residential, and industrial applications.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4007-9801/features/202501-154-55-9K297h1Ar9.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:12:44.418098', '2025-01-17 02:12:44.421023', 154),
(290, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">4007-9801 Simplex Conventional Fire Alarm Control Panel ensures dependable operation and minimal downtime. The panel supports flexible configuration options, allowing for scalability and adaptability to suit various building layouts and system requirements. With robust features such as fault detection, system diagnostics, and clear status indicators, the 4007-9801 offers peace of mind and enhanced fire safety. Designed to meet industry standards, it provides an efficient, cost-effective solution for those seeking reliable fire alarm management in any setting.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4007-9801/features/202501-154-66-kKIGZ0WZZw.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:12:44.422650', '2025-01-17 02:12:44.425544', 154),
(291, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 4606-9202 Simplex Conventional Smoke Detector is a reliable and highly effective fire detection device designed to provide early warnings in a variety of commercial and residential environments. Equipped with advanced smoke sensing technology, this detector is built to identify smoke particles in the air and trigger alarm signals, ensuring fast and accurate fire detection. Its conventional design allows for easy integration with existing fire alarm systems, making it an ideal solution for both new installations and upgrades. With the 4606-9202, users can count on a dependable and affordable smoke detection solution that meets the safety needs of any building.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4606-9202/features/202501-155-44-RnjzDIMdAy.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:26:14.394472', '2025-01-17 02:26:14.397167', 155),
(292, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">4606-9202 Simplex Conventional Smoke Detector is engineered for minimal maintenance and consistent performance. It features high sensitivity to smoke while minimizing the risk of false alarms, offering optimal functionality in a variety of environments. Designed to meet industry safety standards, this smoke detector provides peace of mind, knowing that your property is protected by a trusted and proven fire safety solution. Its simple installation process, low maintenance, and reliable performance make the 4606-9202 an excellent choice for anyone looking to enhance fire safety with a conventional smoke detection device.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4606-9202/features/202501-155-55-8hx01o02C6.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:26:14.398796', '2025-01-17 02:26:14.401393', 155),
(293, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MBA-624C Simplex Conventional Manual Pull Station is a high-quality, reliable device designed to provide easy manual activation of fire alarm systems in case of an emergency. Featuring a durable, weather-resistant construction, the MBA-624C is suitable for use in both indoor and outdoor environments, offering flexibility and dependable performance. Its simple operation requires only a pull to trigger the alarm, making it an intuitive and accessible option for buildings of all sizes. With a user-friendly design, the MBA-624C ensures that occupants can quickly and efficiently alert emergency responders in the event of a fire or other emergency.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-convention-mba-624c/features/202501-156-7-OH4yycRnFO.png', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.853400', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.856134', 156),
(294, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MBA-624C is built to last, with a rugged and tamper-resistant design that ensures long-term durability and reliable functionality in high-traffic areas. This manual pull station integrates seamlessly with existing conventional fire alarm systems, offering an easy upgrade or addition to any building\'s fire safety setup. Designed to meet the latest safety standards, the MBA-624C Simplex Manual Pull Station provides essential support to comprehensive fire alarm systems, enhancing safety and ensuring peace of mind for building occupants. Whether in a commercial, industrial, or residential setting, this pull station is a trusted component in maintaining a safe environment.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-convention-mba-624c/features/202501-156-5-pYQClk1HAG.png', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.857786', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.860194', 156),
(295, '<p><strong>Advanced Photoelectric Sensing Technology</strong><br>The Simplex 4098-9714 uses advanced photoelectric sensing technology that combines a stable, pulsed infrared LED light source with a silicon photodiode receiver. This system ensures consistent and precise smoke detection by providing low-power, high-accuracy performance. The sensor\'s photoelectric design makes it highly sensitive to smoke particles, enhancing its ability to detect early signs of fire before it becomes a serious threat. This feature is ideal for environments where early detection is crucial for safety.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9714/features/202501-157-6-3NhA3IRgtT.png', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.905350', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.908372', 157),
(296, '<p><strong>Adjustable Sensitivity Levels for Customization</strong><br>The Simplex 4098-9714 offers seven adjustable sensitivity levels, ranging from 0.2% to 3.7% per foot of smoke obscuration. This flexibility allows users to tailor the sensor&rsquo;s sensitivity based on the specific requirements of their environment, ensuring optimal performance. Whether in an area prone to dust or smoke, or in highly sensitive locations, the ability to adjust sensitivity helps minimize false alarms while maintaining accurate smoke detection. Sensitivity settings are easily selected and monitored through the fire alarm control panel, providing full control over system parameters.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9714/features/202501-157-7-9gB0TCF6cj.png', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.910815', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.914844', 157),
(297, '<p>The self-restoring design of the SIMPLEX 4098-9733 heat sensor ensures minimal maintenance requirements. This feature allows the sensor to reset after detecting a temperature shift, reducing the need for repairs or replacements. This reliable and low-maintenance functionality guarantees consistent operation over time, providing long-lasting value in both commercial and residential fire detection systems. The sensor\'s ability to restore itself ensures continued performance without interruptions, contributing to the overall reliability of the fire alarm system.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9733/features/202501-158-6-Xfs89oJiiV.png', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.918254', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.921616', 158),
(298, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4098-9733 sensor&rsquo;s small thermal mass allows for quick and precise temperature measurements. This results in a rapid response to temperature changes, which is essential in early fire detection systems. The sensor\'s ability to measure temperature accurately ensures that the fire alarm control panel receives timely and accurate data, enabling a faster reaction to potential fire hazards. With this advanced thermal response, the 4098-9733 provides reliable and swift fire detection for improved safety.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9733/features/202501-158-7-2DwoViLEHs.png', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.923498', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.925771', 158),
(299, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4100ES Fire Detection and Control Panel offers extensive point and module capacities, allowing it to adapt to a wide range of fire protection applications. With its scalable configuration, the system can be easily expanded to accommodate growing needs and complex fire safety requirements. This feature provides exceptional flexibility for both new installations and future upgrades, ensuring that your fire detection system can evolve as needed.</p>\r\n<p>The point and module capacities make the 4100ES ideal for both small and large-scale applications, including commercial, industrial, and institutional buildings. This feature ensures comprehensive fire protection across diverse environments, from single-building installations to multi-building complexes.</p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4100es/features/202501-159-66-z7blH5XQ83.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.272594', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.276557', 159),
(300, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4100ES series offers extensive installation, operator, and service features, making it an excellent choice for a variety of environments. Its intuitive user interface and streamlined controls allow for easy installation and quick system setup, reducing the time and cost involved in system deployment. Additionally, the system&rsquo;s enhanced serviceability makes maintenance efficient, minimizing downtime and ensuring continuous protection.</p>\r\n<p>The SIMPLEX 4100ES is engineered for optimal performance, offering an advanced, dependable solution for fire detection. With its comprehensive service features, it enables seamless upgrades, troubleshooting, and system diagnostics, ensuring that it remains operational and reliable throughout its lifespan.</p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4100es/features/202501-159-77-kMWfoAppdJ.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.279329', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.282183', 159),
(301, '<p>The SIMPLEX Addressable Sensor 4098-9792 offers exceptional precision in fire detection through its advanced addressable technology. Each sensor is individually identified within the system, ensuring that the exact location of a fire hazard can be quickly pinpointed. This capability enhances overall safety by enabling rapid and accurate responses, minimizing the time it takes for emergency responders to reach the affected area. With this technology, fire protection is significantly more effective, particularly in larger or more complex environments.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9792/features/202501-160-66-CvL8oWlNT7.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.360717', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.363425', 160),
(302, '<p>This sensor is equipped with dual detection technologies, utilizing both smoke and heat sensors to provide reliable and timely fire alerts. The combination ensures that all potential fire scenarios are covered, from slow-burning fires to those with intense heat buildup. By using configurable detection thresholds, the 4098-9792 can be fine-tuned to suit specific environments, further reducing the risk of false alarms. This flexibility makes it ideal for use in varied applications, from industrial spaces to residential settings.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9792/features/202501-160-77-QTClBVgAZe.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.365036', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.367528', 160),
(303, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4099-9002 is engineered with advanced addressable functionality, making it an essential component of modern fire alarm systems. This technology allows the system to quickly identify and pinpoint the location of faults or alarms, which drastically reduces troubleshooting time. This precise identification means that any potential issues can be resolved without delay, preventing unnecessary disruptions to the fire alarm network. The device&rsquo;s ability to communicate with the control panel ensures that system errors are detected early, enabling rapid response and minimizing the risk of damage or safety hazards in the event of an emergency.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4099-9002/features/202501-161-11-tYBHXVGiU3.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.441418', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.444562', 161),
(304, '<p>Another standout feature of the SIMPLEX 4099-9002 is its sophisticated communication protocols, designed to support fast and reliable data transmission across the addressable network. These protocols allow the system to quickly relay alarm or fault signals to the central control panel, ensuring immediate attention. By facilitating efficient communication, the device improves the overall reliability and performance of the fire alarm system. This results in faster reaction times during an emergency and ensures that the system remains in optimal working condition at all times, enhancing the overall safety of the facility.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4099-9002/features/202501-161-77-pvqNGYCIXa.png', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.446529', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.449376', 161),
(305, '<p><strong>Advanced Addressable Protocol:</strong> The SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 49AV-WRF leverages an advanced addressable protocol to enhance fire detection accuracy. This technology allows each device to communicate directly with the fire alarm control panel, enabling precise identification of the alarm location. The direct communication streamlines system monitoring and maintenance, ensuring that potential issues are identified and resolved swiftly.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-49av-wrf/features/202501-162-55-CYdp2RSNYt.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.764741', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.767390', 162),
(306, '<p><strong>Comprehensive Audio and Visual Alerts:</strong> The 49AV-WRF is equipped with both audio and visual alert systems to ensure thorough emergency communication. The audio alerts provide loud, clear warnings, while the visual alerts offer bright, attention-grabbing signals. This dual-alert system ensures that all building occupants are effectively notified during emergencies, improving overall safety and evacuation efficiency.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-49av-wrf/features/202501-162-66-exqhxsM40b.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.768918', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.771195', 162),
(307, '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SD-651 Plug-in Smoke Detector features a highly sensitive photoelectric sensor that provides superior detection capabilities. This sensor is designed to detect smoke particles in the air, allowing for early alerts and improving the overall effectiveness of fire safety systems. The quick response time of the SD-651 makes it a reliable option for preventing small fires from growing into larger, more dangerous ones. The photoelectric technology is particularly effective at detecting smoldering fires, offering an added layer of safety for both residential and commercial properties.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sd-651/features/202501-163-66-6iQNY5Fz5q.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.779334', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.782032', 163),
(308, '<p>One of the standout features of the SD-651 is its flexibility in installation. The detector is compatible with a wide variety of adapter bases, allowing for different wiring configurations and voltage setups. This flexibility ensures that the SD-651 can be easily integrated into most existing fire alarm systems, making it an excellent choice for both new installations and upgrades. Its shallow depth of only 2 inches (5.1 cm) allows it to fit into tight spaces without compromising on performance, making it a versatile option for various building types.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sd-651/features/202501-163-77-xpWoVnBLO0.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.783782', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.785945', 163),
(309, '<h3>Dual Detection Capability</h3>\r\n<p>The NOTIFIER 5601P offers dual detection through its fixed temperature and rate-of-rise (ROR) activation, providing comprehensive fire safety. The fixed temperature component activates when the ambient temperature reaches 135&deg;F, while the ROR element responds to rapid temperature increases, ensuring early detection of potential fire hazards. The restorable ROR feature allows for regular field testing without compromising the detector\'s effectiveness, making it a durable and reliable option for long-term use.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-5601p/features/202501-164-77-QTDVo9hyyq.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.720170', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.723124', 164),
(310, '<h3>Flexible Installation and Clear Identification</h3>\r\n<p>The 5601P is designed for versatility, with mounting options that accommodate various back box configurations, including single-gang, octagonal, and four-square setups. Its reversible mounting bracket enables both flush and surface mount installations, ensuring it fits seamlessly into any environment. The detector also features alphanumeric markings and a post-activation indicator, simplifying the identification and maintenance process. These features make the 5601P not only easy to install but also straightforward to manage, enhancing its overall utility and reliability.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-5601p/features/202501-164-55-20SRvwqGMH.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.725219', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.728211', 164),
(311, '<h3>Alarm Initiation Compatibility</h3>\r\n<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional NBG-12 series excels in providing a reliable alarm initiating input signal compatible with various conventional Fire Alarm Control Panels and Monitor Modules. Its precision-engineered components ensure accurate signal transmission, crucial for prompt emergency response. This compatibility extends to a wide range of models, each designed to fit specific fire safety needs, ensuring comprehensive coverage and system integration.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-nbg-12/features/202501-165-55-yr1hfD8zLb.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.405904', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.408502', 165),
(312, '<h3>Innovative Design and Versatile Installation</h3>\r\n<p>The NBG-12 series features an innovative design that prioritizes ease of use and durability. Its robust construction ensures longevity and reliable performance even in challenging environments. The series\' multiple mounting options facilitate flexible installation, allowing it to be easily adapted to different architectural settings. This versatility makes the NBG-12 an ideal choice for both new installations and retrofitting existing systems, ensuring a broad scope of application across various industries.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-nbg-12/features/202501-165-77-VdPirTCCkF.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.410548', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.413330', 165),
(313, '<p><strong>Ten Class B Initiating Device Circuits (IDCs) with Class A Optional Configuration</strong><br>The NOTIFIER SFP-10UDE comes equipped with ten Class B IDCs, ensuring extensive coverage and flexibility in configuring fire detection zones. For installations requiring enhanced circuit reliability, the panel supports an optional Class A configuration using the N-CAC-5X converter module. This feature provides an additional layer of safety by allowing the system to maintain functionality even if a single wire in the loop is compromised.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sfp-10ude/features/202501-166-22-PFaQ17w4mj.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.250415', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.253553', 166),
(314, '<p><strong>Built-in Digital Alarm Communicator Transmitter (DACT) and Remote Site Capabilities</strong><br>A standout feature of the SFP-10UDE is its built-in DACT, which ensures immediate transmission of alarm signals to remote monitoring centers. This capability is vital for timely emergency response, significantly reducing potential damages. Additionally, the panel supports remote site upload/download, enabling technicians to perform updates and diagnostics remotely, streamlining system maintenance and reducing on-site visits.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sfp-10ude/features/202501-166-11-XGkvIgTdpv.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.255615', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.259049', 166),
(315, '<p><strong>Simplified Installation</strong></p>\r\n<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL is designed to streamline installation processes, saving time and reducing costs. Its plug-in design and universal mounting plate with an onboard shorting spring facilitate quick and easy setup, ensuring continuity testing can be completed efficiently before the device is fully installed. This feature helps eliminate common installation errors, such as ground faults, making it a reliable choice for contractors and technicians.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-p2rl/features/202501-167-33-ID37jgkmii.png', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.362377', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.365217', 167),
(316, '<p><strong>Versatile Functionality</strong></p>\r\n<p>The P2RL offers versatile functionality with its field-selectable candela settings and automatic 12- or 24-volt operation. This adaptability ensures the device can meet a wide range of application requirements, from small residential settings to large commercial installations. Additionally, the rotary switch allows for easy selection of horn tones and volume levels, providing customizable alerts to suit various environmental needs.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-p2rl/features/202501-167-44-McIV5zD9bC.png', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.366832', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.369002', 167),
(317, '<p><strong>Advanced Reflected Beam Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>The NOTIFIER FSB2000 utilizes advanced reflected beam technology to provide superior smoke detection in large, open areas. This technology allows the detector to project a beam across a wide space, reflecting off a strategically placed reflector to detect smoke particles in the air. This approach ensures comprehensive coverage with fewer devices, making it ideal for environments with high ceilings and wide spaces.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-fsb2000/features/202501-168-11-zRbKN2bDPR.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.060141', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.062867', 168),
(318, '<p><strong>Intelligent, Addressable Design</strong></p>\r\n<p>Equipped with an intelligent, addressable design, the FSB2000 integrates seamlessly into modern fire safety systems. It offers precise location tracking and real-time data, allowing for quick identification and response to potential fire hazards. This feature not only enhances the efficiency of fire detection but also simplifies maintenance by providing detailed diagnostics and reducing the time required for troubleshooting.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-fsb2000/features/202501-168-22-FwrgTUWt7z.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.064457', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.067775', 168),
(319, '<p>The enhanced optical sensing chamber of the NOTIFIER&reg; FSP-951 is a standout feature, designed to detect smoke from a broad range of combustion sources. This advanced technology ensures that the detector meets more stringent code standards, providing reliable and accurate smoke detection. The improved chamber design not only increases sensitivity but also minimizes the occurrence of false alarms, delivering peace of mind to building occupants and property managers alike.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fsp-951/features/202501-169-22-QyZXquRtol.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.211667', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.214803', 169),
(320, '<p>The addressable technology of the FSP-951 allows for precise location identification within a fire detection system. This feature enhances the overall efficiency of emergency response by enabling first responders to quickly locate and address the source of the smoke. The detector&rsquo;s compatibility with NOTIFIER systems ensures that it integrates smoothly into existing setups, offering a scalable solution for both small and large-scale applications.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fsp-951/features/202501-169-33-ZU5hSsmbzL.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.217110', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.220612', 169),
(321, '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; FST-951 Series intelligent thermal detectors are equipped with advanced thermal technology that ensures rapid and accurate temperature detection. This technology makes the FST-951 ideal for environments where early detection of temperature changes can prevent potential fire hazards. The detector\'s intelligent system automatically adjusts to temperature shifts in the surrounding area, providing reliable protection. With its high-performance capabilities, the FST-951 is designed for use in both commercial and residential buildings, offering an optimal balance of safety and reliability.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fst-951/features/202501-170-33-qpud9sw2kV.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.855850', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.858529', 170),
(322, '<p>The FST-951 Series thermal detectors feature a unique point ID address system, allowing precise detector location identification. By using rotary decimal switches, users can easily assign specific locations to each device within the fire safety system. This feature simplifies the process of managing fire alarm systems and makes maintenance and troubleshooting more efficient. The point ID addressing system also helps reduce installation time and enhances system accuracy, ensuring that each detector is optimally positioned for effective fire detection.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fst-951/features/202501-170-44-RHjG277lWH.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.860061', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.862560', 170),
(323, '<p><strong>Dual-Action Activation Mechanism</strong><br>The Notifier NBG-12LX pull station incorporates a dual-action activation mechanism, requiring two distinct actions to trigger the alarm. This design significantly reduces the possibility of accidental activations, ensuring that the pull station is only engaged in genuine emergency situations. The dual-action system provides an additional layer of protection, making it especially useful in environments where false alarms could lead to unnecessary disruptions and safety concerns. This feature ensures reliability, making the NBG-12LX an ideal choice for critical infrastructure, industrial sites, and public buildings.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nbg-12lx/features/202501-171-22-xBnAEq0CTW.png', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.574527', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.578227', 171),
(324, '<p><strong>Addressable Interface for Precise Location Identification</strong><br>One of the standout features of the Notifier NBG-12LX is its addressable interface, which allows for precise identification of the station location when activated. Unlike traditional manual pull stations, which may only alert the central system of an alarm, the addressable nature of the NBG-12LX ensures that the exact location of the activated station is immediately displayed on the control panel. This feature is crucial for rapid emergency response, especially in large or complex facilities, where knowing the exact point of activation can help responders take swift action to mitigate fire risks effectively.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nbg-12lx/features/202501-171-77-twGtmcz8aI.png', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.580347', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.582766', 171);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(325, '<h3>Plug-In Design</h3>\r\n<p>The plug-in design of the Notifier SPSRL speaker strobe simplifies installation by allowing installers to pre-wire the device before connecting it to the system. This feature significantly reduces the chance of costly ground faults, as wiring continuity can be tested before the speakers are plugged in. By allowing pre-wiring, the plug-in design helps installers work more efficiently, saving valuable time on the job site. Additionally, it supports better wire management and ensures the device is securely installed with minimal risk of wiring errors, making it an ideal choice for both new installations and system upgrades.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-spsrl/features/202501-172-55-LoQkuzwHhe.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.760785', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.763679', 172),
(326, '<h3>Protective Plastic Cover</h3>\r\n<p>The protective plastic cover on the Notifier SPSRL speaker strobe plays a crucial role in safeguarding the device during installation. By covering exposed speaker components, the plastic cover prevents the possibility of nicked wires, ensuring that the unit remains intact and fully functional. This protective feature adds an extra layer of durability to the device, minimizing the risk of damage during the handling and installation process. As a result, the Notifier SPSRL delivers consistent and reliable performance over time, contributing to the overall effectiveness of the fire alarm system in providing safety and emergency notifications.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-spsrl/features/202501-172-77-WYAZR4i9p5.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.765400', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.767617', 172),
(327, '<p>The NFS2-3030\'s extensive device support is a standout feature, accommodating over 3,000 intelligent devices across ten SLCs. This capacity makes it ideal for large-scale applications where expansive coverage is necessary. Its compatibility with NOTI-FIRE-NET and ONYXWorks allows for network integration of up to 200 nodes, facilitating a comprehensive and interconnected fire detection system. This scalability ensures that the NFS2-3030 can meet the needs of growing facilities, providing a future-proof fire safety solution.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nfs-3030/features/202501-173-33-MEvJuHnzl8.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:46:55.704137', '2025-01-20 00:49:50.578289', 173),
(328, '<p>The NFS2-3030\'s optional Digital Voice Command (DVC) significantly enhances emergency communication capabilities. By providing clear, pre-recorded messages and live voice instructions, it ensures that occupants are well-informed during emergencies, improving evacuation efficiency and safety. The inclusion of EIA-485 annunciators with custom graphics offers a visually intuitive alert system, enabling quick and effective response to fire incidents. These features make the NFS2-3030 an invaluable tool in emergency management.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nfs-3030/features/202501-173-77-xZb03WYGOX.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:46:55.709133', '2025-01-20 00:49:50.581604', 173),
(329, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 721U also offers enhanced compatibility with various fire safety devices, including detectors, alarms, and control panels, providing a flexible and scalable fire protection solution. Its robust design supports both audible and visual alarms, ensuring effective warning in emergencies. Furthermore, the system features a comprehensive set of integrated features, such as zone identification and fault detection, which significantly improve response times and building safety. With its proven track record and superior performance, the Edwards 721U Conventional Fire Alarm System is an essential component of any fire safety strategy.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-721u/features/202501-174-11-8JDRsk4X3U.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.959736', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.962324', 174),
(330, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Edwards 721U Conventional Fire Alarm System is designed to provide reliable and efficient fire detection and alarm solutions for a wide range of commercial and industrial applications. With its easy-to-install configuration, this system supports up to eight zones, ensuring broad coverage for diverse building layouts. The 721U is equipped with a user-friendly interface, allowing quick setup and simplified operation, while its advanced diagnostic tools help identify potential issues and enhance maintenance efficiency. The system&rsquo;s high-quality components ensure consistent performance and long-lasting reliability, making it a trusted choice for fire safety.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-721u/features/202501-174-22-1OgISwUBWm.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.965165', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.967621', 174),
(331, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Superior Video and Audio Performance</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ALBA CV2124AB features an ultra-wide-angle 2.3 mm lens with a 110&deg; vision angle, ensuring maximum coverage of entry points. Its built-in electric door speaker provides crystal-clear audio communication, making it easy to identify and manage visitors. With a focal length of 2.7 mm, the module delivers sharp and detailed visuals, ensuring reliable monitoring and identification in any scenario.</span></p>', 'products/alba-cv2124ab-outdoor/features/202501-175-44-6bhg89zDSB.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:22:42.565666', '2025-01-20 01:24:33.972330', 175),
(332, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Adaptable Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Crafted from anodized aluminum, the ALBA CV2124AB is built to withstand the elements while maintaining a sleek and modern appearance. Its grey finish complements various architectural styles, and its modular design allows for flexible configurations. The white LED backlighting enhances usability, ensuring that buttons remain visible and accessible even in dim lighting conditions. This compact yet powerful module is designed to meet the demands of both residential and commercial environments.</span></p>', 'products/alba-cv2124ab-outdoor/features/202501-175-77-u9WDSIgK7W.png', '2025-01-20 01:22:42.570068', '2025-01-20 01:24:33.974841', 175),
(333, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> Flexible Button Configuration<br>The ALBA CT2138AB supports up to eight buttons in a double-call setup or four in a single-call configuration, making it adaptable for different access needs. This modular design allows it to seamlessly integrate with compatible modules like the CV2124AB or CA2124AB, enhancing the system\'s scalability. Ideal for multi-unit residential or commercial properties, the flexible configuration provides a practical solution for managing multiple users.</span></p>', 'products/alba-ct2138ab-outdoor/features/202501-176-11-YnBKER4M6M.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.646022', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.649230', 176),
(334, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Durable and User-Friendly Design<br>Built with anodized aluminum, the CT2138AB is designed for durability while maintaining an elegant, modern look. The grey finish complements a variety of building styles, and the compact dimensions allow it to fit effortlessly into existing systems. Its white LED backlighting ensures that buttons remain visible and easy to use, even in low-light conditions, offering an optimal user experience.</span></p>', 'products/alba-ct2138ab-outdoor/features/202501-176-22-VmYuhzImrg.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.651691', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.654966', 176),
(335, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Robust Design and Versatile Mounting<br>Crafted from durable steel and finished in a sophisticated grey color, the SOLVO TD2000R is built to last. Its design supports both wall and flush mounting, offering flexibility for various installation scenarios. With a compact form factor and lightweight build, this proximity reader is easy to handle during installation. The IP45 protection rating ensures resistance to dust and water, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor environments.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000r-outdoor/features/202501-177-22-1vw60ON5zV.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.953015', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.956211', 177),
(336, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Advanced Camera and Display Technology<br>The TD2000R features a high-quality CMOS 1/3\" camera with 440,000 pixels and a fixed 3.7 mm focal length lens, delivering reliable visuals for security monitoring. The alphanumeric LCD display provides clear, real-time information, while the 16-button interface ensures smooth user interaction. These advanced technological features are complemented by efficient power usage, operating on a Duo line with a maximum current consumption of 0.40 A.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000r-outdoor/features/202501-177-66-gicIQObBuR.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.958981', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.970025', 177),
(337, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Versatile Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The SOLVO TD2000RA is crafted from high-grade steel, ensuring long-term durability and resilience. Its grey finish provides a neutral, professional look, making it compatible with a wide range of environments. The compact dimensions (30.6 cm height, 17 cm width, 6 cm depth) and lightweight construction (2.2 kg) simplify installation and maintenance. With support for both wall and flush mounting, the panel offers flexible installation options tailored to architectural requirements. Its IP45 rating guarantees protection against dust and light water sprays, ensuring reliable operation in various conditions.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000ra-outdoor/features/202501-178-33-omU5LaTbXr.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.450052', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.453090', 178),
(338, '<p><strong><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Advanced User Interface and Efficient Power Usage</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The TD2000RA is equipped with a 16-button keypad a</span><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">nd an alphanumeric LCD display for intuitive user interaction and navigation. The clear visual feedback provided by the display enhances functionality, ensuring a seamless user experience. Powered by the efficient Duo Line system, the device operates with a maximum current consumption of just 0.30 A, promoting energy savings and reducing overall operational costs. These features make the TD2000RA an energy-efficient, user-friendly choice for managing access control with ease.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000ra-outdoor/features/202501-178-11-rXplFv5pPX.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.454892', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.457152', 178),
(339, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Modern Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The AGORA VD2121CAGL boasts a durable aluminum and plastic construction that ensures longevity and resistance to environmental factors. Its aluminum and light grey color finish enhances its aesthetic appeal, making it a stylish yet functional addition to your property. Compact in size, it fits easily into any entryway without compromising space or design.</span></p>', 'products/agora-vd2121cagl-outdoor/features/202501-179-66-5TEA6eu0vE.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.064746', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.067368', 179),
(340, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Advanced Security and Communication</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Equipped with a high-resolution color camera and&nbsp;</span><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">a reliable electric door speaker, this device ensures clear video and audio communication with visitors. The ability to handle up to two calls simultaneously offers added convenience, particularly in multi-occupancy settings. Its 12 Vac power supply provides consistent and efficient operation, while the protective cover safeguards the unit from potential damage.</span></p>', 'products/agora-vd2121cagl-outdoor/features/202501-179-22-u0hRk57t7w.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.068910', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.071351', 179),
(341, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Modular Compatibility:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The AGORA AGL100TS is designed to integrate seamlessly with VD2121CAGL and AD2121CAGL systems, enhancing their capacity with support for up to 8 call buttons. This modular approach allows users to expand their intercom or access control systems as their needs evolve, offering a cost-effective and scalable solution. Its compatibility ensures that it can be easily added to existing setups without requiring extensive modifications.</span></p>', 'products/agora-agl100ts-outdoor/features/202501-180-55-Tkl717xTGr.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.547215', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.550946', 180),
(342, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Compact Design:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Constructed from high-quality aluminum and plastic, the AGORA AGL100TS balances durability with a sleek, modern aesthetic. The aluminum and light grey finish ensures it blends well with a variety of architectural styles. Measuring 20.8 cm in height, 9.9 cm in width, and 3 cm in depth, this module is compact yet robust, making it ideal for installations where space is at a premium.</span></p>', 'products/agora-agl100ts-outdoor/features/202501-180-44-jZN80e5fN2.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.552899', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.555631', 180),
(343, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>High-Quality Video Camera</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MATRIX VD2120CMAS features a fixed 3.6 mm lens color video camera, delivering sharp and clear visuals. Its advanced imaging technology ensures high-definition output, making it suitable for security monitoring and intercom systems. With consistent video performance, it provides users with a reliable visual feed for various applications, from access control to surveillance.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-vd2120cmas-outdoor/features/202501-181-44-2MFats5cYP.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.751893', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.754924', 181),
(344, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Durable and Compact Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Crafted from premium stainless steel, the MATRIX VD2120CMAS audio-video module is designed to last. Its compact 11.5 cm by 11.5 cm dimensions allow for versatile installation in both small and large spaces. The metal grey finish not only enhances its visual appeal but also provides added resistance to wear and environmental factors, making it a perfect fit for indoor and outdoor use.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/matrix-vd2120cmas-outdoor/features/202501-181-11-voKN52cN2w.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.756874', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.759344', 181),
(345, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Stylish Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MATRIX MAS24S features a stainless steel construction, offering exceptional durability and resistance to wear. Its modern metal grey finish adds a sleek, professional look, ensuring the module complements any environment. Measuring just 11.5 cm x 11.5 cm, it is compact yet functional, fitting seamlessly into a wide range of intercom setups. This robust design makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, providing reliable operation in various conditions.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-mas24s-outdoor/features/202501-182-44-tCgGmR1bEz.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.172931', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.176529', 182),
(346, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Enhanced Functionality</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>With four call buttons and integrated encoder keys circuit technology, the MAS24S delivers precise and efficient communication. The module is optimized for use with the CD213&hellip;MAS series, enhancing overall system performance. Each button is designed for easy access and responsiveness, ensuring smooth user interaction. Whether for residential complexes or commercial spaces, this feature-rich module is engineered to meet the demands of modern intercom systems with ease.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-mas24s-outdoor/features/202501-182-11-GZ0xArKCzT.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.179030', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.182029', 182),
(347, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">High-Quality Display and Hands-Free Design<br>The SE4252 monitor features a 7-inch LCD TFT display, delivering bright, high-definition visuals for optimal clarity. Whether you\'re checking a visitor at your door or using intercommunication features, the vivid display ensures an exceptional viewing experience. Its hands-free operation enhances convenience, allowing effortless communication without the need to pick up a handset. This combination of high-quality visuals and ergonomic design makes it a must-have for modern living or workspaces.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/se4252-indoor/features/202501-183-44-zGxIM28Avt.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.457475', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.460574', 183),
(348, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Advanced Functionality and Expandability<br>The SE4252 is more than just a monitor; it\'s a multifunctional tool with video memory, memo capabilities, and block notes for better organization. Its ability to control electrical loads and manage actuators for remote apparatus activation brings smart home compatibility to your fingertips. With memory expansion options via memory cards and support for data import/export, the SE4252 ensures that your system can grow with your needs. This versatility and future-proofing make it an excellent choice for those seeking a scalable and efficient communication solution.</span></p>', 'products/se4252-indoor/features/202501-183-11-v9vmg8I5Rz.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.462885', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.465733', 183),
(349, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE400 Handset offers superior sound quality that ensures a crystal-clear audio experience. It is engineered with advanced sound technology to provide high-definition voice clarity, making it ideal for private conversations that require precise communication. The handset&rsquo;s noise-isolation feature reduces background interference, allowing users to focus on the conversation without distractions. Whether for business or personal use, this feature ensures clear and effective communication in any environment.</span></p>', 'products/se400-indoor/features/202501-184-88-3sYJYCaWil.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.421004', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.424207', 184),
(350, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Seamless integration with the Sette monitor system makes the SE400 Handset easy to set up and use. The intuitive connection process allows users to instantly switch between the monitor\'s speakers and the handset with minimal effort. This convenience ensures that users can focus on their conversation without worrying about technical issues. The handset is also designed to be comfortable to hold for extended periods, making it a practical choice for those who need to engage in long or frequent private conversations.</span></p>', 'products/se400-indoor/features/202501-184-99-bFGCG8kH10.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.426109', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.428499', 184),
(351, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262W features a 3.5\" LCD screen that provides high-definition video output, offering clear and sharp visuals of visitors. This screen size is perfect for small to medium-sized environments, ensuring that the user can easily see and interact with those at the door. The screen&rsquo;s color accuracy and contrast make it ideal for both residential and commercial use. Whether used in a brightly lit area or a dimly lit one, the display ensures excellent visibility. Its compact size also ensures it can be installed seamlessly into various spaces without being intrusive.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262w-indoor/features/202501-185-99-2xNAPOWnOV.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:32:50.900342', '2025-01-20 03:35:33.109840', 185),
(352, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The soft touch control system of the ZHERO ZH1262W enhances user experience by offering responsive and effortless navigation. The controls are simple to use, ensuring that all functions are accessible with just a gentle tap. This system reduces the complexity of operating a video intercom, making it user-friendly for people of all ages. Additionally, the OSD configuration allows for easy customization of settings such as volume, brightness, and contrast, giving users full control over the system. This feature ensures that the intercom can adapt to different environments and preferences. </span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262w-indoor/features/202501-185-66-Hf5iZQbgrC.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:32:50.904970', '2025-01-20 03:35:33.112609', 185),
(353, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262B features a 3.5\" LCD screen that offers a clear, high-resolution display, providing users with a detailed and sharp view of visitors. This screen is designed to make identification easier and more accurate, enhancing security and allowing you to communicate with visitors more effectively. The screen\'s compact size ensures that it fits into a variety of environments without taking up too much space, making it a versatile choice for both homes and businesses. Whether you&rsquo;re looking for a high-definition view for safety or convenience, this screen delivers on both fronts.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262b-indoor/features/202501-186-55-FmUHntEel9.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.096735', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.100470', 186),
(354, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Another standout feature of the ZHERO ZH1262B is its soft touch control interface, which provides a smooth and intuitive user experience. The soft touch technology makes navigating the system and adjusting settings, such as volume or brightness, incredibly easy and responsive. Additionally, the On-Screen Display (OSD) configuration allows users to customize settings according to their preferences, making the system flexible and adaptable to different needs. This combination of simplicity and advanced functionality makes the ZHERO ZH1262B an excellent choice for anyone seeking a modern, easy-to-use video intercom system.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262b-indoor/features/202501-186-99-WFlhWCMX0A.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.102728', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.105173', 186),
(355, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ZHERO ZH1252W features a 4-inch screen, providing users with a clear and sharp visual display for optimal communication. This compact yet efficient screen allows users to easily see visitors at the door, improving both security and convenience. The screen\'s quality ensures that video clarity is maintained, even in different lighting conditions, for a reliable experience. With a high-resolution display, it enhances your ability to interact with visitors and is an essential feature for anyone looking for a high-quality video intercom.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1252w-zheros-indoor/features/202501-187-66-oX7fMFKufy.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.334528', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.337138', 187),
(356, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 4-button interface on the ZHERO ZH1252W ensures that the intercom system is both easy to navigate and user-friendly. Each button is designed to perform a specific function, making it straightforward for users to control the system. Whether you\'re adjusting the volume, viewing the video feed, or communicating with a visitor, the 4-button interface ensures simple, quick operation. Additionally, the programming through the DIP switch adds further customization, allowing users to personalize their experience to suit their needs.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1252w-zheros-indoor/features/202501-187-11-0E0bYZ2hdo.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.338663', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.341320', 187),
(357, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX362 Intercom is equipped with seven easy-to-use buttons, with six of them being fully programmable to suit a variety of user needs. This flexibility ensures that the intercom can be customized for different environments, such as homes, offices, or commercial settings. The door opening button provides added convenience, allowing users to easily grant access to visitors or employees with a simple press of a button. This programmable feature not only streamlines communication but also improves security by enabling quick, controlled access.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex362-indoor/features/202501-188-11-yhqxVatRy3.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.916169', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.919522', 188),
(358, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Constructed from high-quality plastic, the EX362 Intercom is both lightweight and durable, ensuring long-term reliability. The device&rsquo;s compact size (83 x 218 x 62 mm) makes it perfect for installations in spaces where traditional, bulkier intercoms would not fit. Despite its small size, it does not compromise on functionality, offering an efficient and straightforward way to manage communication and access control. Its clean white color complements various interiors, making it both a practical and aesthetic addition to any environment.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex362-indoor/features/202501-188-55-ydp98xP6Ne.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.921299', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.923711', 188),
(359, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">One of the standout features of the EXHITO EX352 Intercom is its three-button layout, which includes a dedicated door opening button for easy access control. This allows you to quickly grant visitors entry with a simple press, enhancing both convenience and security. The two additional programmable buttons can be customized to suit various functions, such as connecting to other rooms or controlling additional systems within your home or office. This flexibility makes the EX352 Intercom an excellent choice for users seeking a system that can adapt to their unique needs. Its intuitive interface ensures a smooth and hassle-free experience.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex352-indoor/features/202501-189-77-Z5dMnml7yn.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.596905', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.599634', 189),
(360, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EX352 Intercom&rsquo;s compact and durable design is another key feature that sets it apart. Measuring just 21.8 cm in height, 6.5 cm in width, and 6.2 cm in depth, it fits seamlessly into any space, whether in a home, office, or shared building. The intercom is crafted from high-quality plastic in a sleek white finish, ensuring that it remains both sturdy and aesthetically pleasing. The minimalist design allows it to blend effortlessly with various interior styles, while its durable construction guarantees long-term performance, making it a reliable addition to any setting.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex352-indoor/features/202501-189-66-uLmEQjFVM6.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.601194', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.603224', 189),
(361, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Communication Flexibility<br>The Aiphone AX Series provides two distinct communication modes, PTT (push-to-talk) and VOX (voice-activated), allowing users to choose the method that best suits their environment. The system supports up to 8 master stations and 120 remote stations, ensuring seamless communication across large facilities. Selective calling between master stations, as well as priority and standard call levels, guarantees that important communications are never overlooked. With these features, the AX Series is adaptable to a wide range of security and communication scenarios.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ax-series/features/202501-190-66-SaQjIYF1ow.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.882857', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.885901', 190),
(362, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> Integration and Control<br>The AX Series excels in system integration with features that allow connection to CCTV and electronic access control systems, enhancing both security and operational efficiency. The system supports composite video output, making it easy to incorporate video surveillance. Additionally, it offers selective remote control for features like door release and PC interface for event logging, making it highly customizable and user-friendly. These integrations provide a streamlined approach to managing building security and communication in one cohesive system.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ax-series/features/202501-190-55-GkVKkprZAZ.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.887617', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.891266', 190),
(363, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">LCD Color Monitor The AIPHONE GT Series features a 3.5&Prime; LCD color monitor that delivers high-quality video with clear, vibrant colors. This display ensures users can easily view visitors and confirm their identity before engaging in conversation. The compact size of the monitor makes it suitable for a wide range of installations, while the LCD technology ensures durability and sharpness. This feature is ideal for anyone looking for an efficient and easy-to-use visual communication system.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-gt-series/features/202501-191-66-4cQhgpsuqp.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.289174', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.292800', 191),
(364, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Hands-Free Audio Communication The AIPHONE GT Series allows for hands-free audio communication, enabling users to speak with visitors without the need to hold a handset. This feature provides convenience, especially for individuals who need to multitask or prefer a more effortless interaction. The system also includes optional privacy through the GT-HS handset, which is sold separately. This flexibility allows users to choose their preferred mode of communication, offering both hands-free convenience and private communication when needed.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/aiphone-gt-series/features/202501-191-77-cIaIXiSnLv.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.294559', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.297356', 191),
(365, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Touchscreen Panel and Hands-Free Communication<br>The AIPHONE JM Series features a 7&rdquo; touchscreen panel that provides a clear and intuitive interface for all your video intercom needs. It supports hands-free (VOX) communication, allowing for effortless conversations without the need to pick up a handset. Alternatively, users can choose to use the handset for more private communication. The high-resolution TFT LCD screen delivers vibrant color visuals, ensuring crisp video quality for every interaction. Whether you&rsquo;re in a bright or dark environment, the camera&rsquo;s auto-adjustment capabilities help provide optimal video clarity.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jm-series/features/202501-192-66-FKAYlBMIqa.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.563605', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.566368', 192),
(366, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Customizable Camera and Multiple Access Control Options<br>The camera in the AIPHONE JM Series can be easily adjusted to suit your preferred viewing angle, and features Digital PanTilt and Zoom functions, which ensure that there are no blind spots in the monitored area. The 170&deg; wide-angle lens captures a broad view, offering full coverage of the entry point. With up to 1,000 recorded calls on an SD/SDHC card (sold separately), you&rsquo;ll have a comprehensive log of entry interactions. Furthermore, the system offers integration with additional devices such as gates, lights, and doors, providing enhanced security and convenience. The ability to manage up to four door stations and connect to eight internal locations makes the system highly scalable.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jm-series/features/202501-192-77-UwNEkQEYpv.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.568061', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.570421', 192),
(367, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JO Series features a 7&rdquo; screen that provides clear, sharp video quality, making it easy to identify visitors with precision. The high-resolution display enhances security by allowing users to view detailed images of the person at the door. Coupled with the intuitive touch buttons, users can easily operate the system without any technical knowledge. The combination of a large screen and user-friendly interface makes the JO Series a reliable choice for anyone seeking advanced, simple-to-use security technology.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jo-series/features/202501-193-55-Gv6RVjVh4l.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.497083', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.500371', 193),
(368, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Another standout feature of the AIPHONE JO Series is its elegant and slim design, with the video master measuring just 13/16&rdquo; in depth. This compact design ensures that the unit blends into any environment without being obtrusive, while still offering high performance. The system&rsquo;s 2-conductor wiring setup makes installation quick and easy, reducing the complexity often associated with intercom systems. With a complete ready-to-install box set, including a door station, inside station, and power supply, the JO Series is a convenient and efficient solution for enhancing security at your home or office.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jo-series/features/202501-193-88-HJqM4cTRVy.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.503058', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.506461', 193),
(369, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE NA-AN Series features a privacy function that blocks unwanted monitoring from the master station. This ensures that only the individuals involved in the communication are able to listen in, protecting the privacy of all parties. With this feature, the system offers a secure communication channel for sensitive conversations. This functionality is especially beneficial in both residential and business settings, where confidentiality is crucial.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-na-an-series/features/202501-194-22-HrFxyfxtQZ.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.936688', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.939956', 194),
(370, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Hands-free communication is another standout feature of the AIPHONE NA-AN Series. Once the master station answers, users can communicate hands-free, making the system efficient and practical for multitasking environments. This feature is ideal for businesses or homes where users need to keep their hands free for other tasks while still engaging in clear and efficient communication. The added convenience of not needing to hold a receiver or device ensures that communication remains streamlined and effortless.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-na-an-series/features/202501-194-44-KXu9M0doaF.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.942502', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.945327', 194),
(371, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Weather-Resistant Design The Aiphone NE-JA Series Sub Station is built to endure outdoor environments, with a weather-resistant stainless-steel faceplate that ensures durability and long-lasting performance. Whether installed in a residential or commercial setting, the weatherproof construction allows the device to operate reliably in varying weather conditions. This feature is essential for areas exposed to the elements, such as entryways, gates, or security checkpoints, ensuring that communication remains functional even during rain, snow, or extreme temperatures.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ne-ja-series/features/202501-195-33-e2IR0IF8Om.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.931038', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.933894', 195),
(372, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> Remote Device Activation One of the standout features of the NE-JA Series Sub Station is its ability to activate remote devices, such as gates or security systems, via an external output contact closure. This feature, available with the optional RY-PA relay, allows the sub station to trigger remote actions during a call, providing flexibility and control for users. Whether you\'re managing a building entrance, securing a property, or integrating with a larger security system, this added functionality ensures the Aiphone NE-JA Sub Station enhances both communication and access control seamlessly.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ne-ja-series/features/202501-195-11-0yOXp18wEX.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.935655', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.937752', 195),
(373, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR PD6500i offers an exceptional 33 detection zones, providing comprehensive coverage for both lateral and vertical detection. This feature allows security professionals to precisely pinpoint the location of a detected item, enhancing response times and reducing the risk of undetected threats. The zones are strategically designed to identify objects on the left, right, and center of the body, as well as height-based detection with vertical zones, ensuring that all potential threats are thoroughly examined. The use of these zones enables accurate assessment and helps optimize the flow of individuals through security checkpoints, making it an ideal choice for busy public venues and critical infrastructure.</span></p>', 'products/pd6500i/features/202501-196-55-VHsy9jJeXu.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.617432', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.624479', 196),
(374, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The PD6500i&rsquo;s Multi-Unit Synchronization feature provides seamless coordination between multiple units for large-scale security operations. This synchronization can be achieved through either wired AC power lines or wireless operation with manual frequency selection. This feature ensures that all detectors in a group operate in harmony without interference, allowing security personnel to manage large groups of units efficiently. With the ability to monitor and control multiple detectors from a central location, this system offers scalability and flexibility for managing high-volume security situations, such as international events, airports, and government facilities. The result is enhanced operational efficiency and streamlined security management.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/pd6500i/features/202501-196-66-mA6TTeCDKi.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.627126', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.631052', 196),
(375, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR Multi Zone boasts 20 independent detection zones, providing precise and accurate localization of potential threats. These zones enable security personnel to quickly and effectively identify the exact location of metal objects, which is crucial in high-traffic areas like airports, event venues, and transportation hubs. This advanced feature significantly reduces false alarms by allowing for more refined detection, ensuring that security teams can focus on the most critical threats. Additionally, the multi-zone setup ensures that multiple objects can be detected simultaneously, offering higher efficiency during security screenings.The Multi Zone detector features an Auto-Scan function that automatically selects the optimal operating frequency, helping to eliminate interference from environmental noise. This function simplifies setup and ensures that the detector operates at peak efficiency in any setting. Along with the Auto-Scan, the detector includes intuitive menu navigation and a convenient slider bar for adjusting settings, enabling security personnel to make quick, precise adjustments. Pre-set programs for different security applications, such as mass transit or special events, allow the system to be easily tailored to meet specific needs, providing maximum security with minimal effort from operators.<br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/multi-zone/features/202501-197-66-pLSSPZSLnL.png', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.908323', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.912162', 197),
(376, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Multi Zone detector features an Auto-Scan function that automatically selects the optimal operating frequency, helping to eliminate interference from environmental noise. This function simplifies setup and ensures that the detector operates at peak efficiency in any setting. Along with the Auto-Scan, the detector includes intuitive menu navigation and a convenient slider bar for adjusting settings, enabling security personnel to make quick, precise adjustments. Pre-set programs for different security applications, such as mass transit or special events, allow the system to be easily tailored to meet specific needs, providing maximum security with minimal effort from operators.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/multi-zone/features/202501-197-44-FgdG1YLZDQ.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.914092', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.916439', 197),
(377, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG features an 8-zone paging station that allows for targeted announcements and alarms, enhancing communication during emergencies. This feature is particularly beneficial in large buildings where different zones may need to be addressed separately for efficient evacuation. The system integrates seamlessly with existing fire alarm panels, ensuring that it responds automatically in case of an emergency. The ability to activate alarms and provide real-time voice instructions improves safety by helping occupants navigate evacuations with clear, precise guidance.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-evaclite-pkg/features/202501-198-33-NcMV1XHFV9.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:41:16.426618', '2025-01-22 02:25:44.736932', 198),
(378, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG delivers superior sound quality with a frequency response range of 20Hz to 20KHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 70 dB, ensuring that voice announcements are crystal clear. This high-quality audio performance is complemented by the system\'s long-distance communication capabilities, with transmission distances of up to 300 meters. The built-in loudspeaker and remote microphone with zone selection enable flexible and effective communication across large areas, making it a reliable solution for environments that demand constant attention to safety. With a total harmonic distortion of less than 0.01%, the system guarantees that sound is delivered accurately without unwanted noise.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-evaclite-pkg/features/202501-198-44-EkfWWmyyCx.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:41:16.431127', '2025-01-22 02:25:44.739408', 198),
(379, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL X-NPMS Configurable Network Paging Station offers effortless operation with its 7-inch TFT LCD touchscreen. The intuitive interface simplifies paging and alarm control, enabling users to make quick adjustments without complicated procedures. The high-resolution screen (800x480) ensures clear visibility and makes the entire system more user-friendly, reducing training time for operators. This streamlined control system ensures ease of use, enhancing operational efficiency in environments where timely and accurate communication is essential.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npms-configurable-network-paging-station/features/202501-199-66-i8bDxz1g9k.PNG', '2025-01-22 00:44:02.219726', '2025-01-22 02:23:50.715446', 199),
(380, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL X-NPMS delivers superior audio quality with a wide frequency response range from 50Hz to 15kHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 85dB. These specifications ensure that the audio produced by the paging station is clear, crisp, and reliable, making it ideal for use in public spaces where clarity is vital. With a low total harmonic distortion (THD) of less than 0.05%, the system guarantees distortion-free sound, further enhancing the quality of communication. This makes the X-NPMS an excellent choice for environments where high-quality voice alarm and paging systems are necessary, such as hospitals, airports, and educational facilities.<br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npms-configurable-network-paging-station/features/202501-199-33-SSvlWEoPtJ.PNG', '2025-01-22 00:44:02.225902', '2025-01-22 02:23:50.718270', 199),
(381, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: Full Duplex Communication and Monitoring<br>The Honeywell X-NPMI Configurable Network Paging Console enables full duplex communication, allowing two-way conversations without delays, which is crucial in environments where real-time communication is essential. In addition to this, it includes built-in monitoring features to ensure the system is functioning correctly at all times. The console supports continuous monitoring of audio output levels and system status, providing instant feedback to users and helping to identify potential issues before they become critical. This makes the X-NPMI a highly reliable choice for businesses that require clear, efficient, and uninterrupted communication.<br><br>With a powerful monitoring loudspeaker offering a wide sound range of 65 dB to 115 dB, the console guarantees that every message is heard, even in large or noisy environments. This feature is particularly valuable in emergency situations, where the ability to instantly convey critical information is paramount.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npmi-configurable-network-paging-console/features/202501-200-22-xo58xcm0in.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:10:12.684909', '2025-01-22 02:23:36.551345', 200),
(382, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Customizable Paging and Audio Configuration<br>The Honeywell X-NPMI Configurable Network Paging Console offers extensive customization options, allowing businesses to configure paging zones, audio output levels, and system settings according to their specific needs. With its flexible audio input capabilities, including a 10 K&Omega; impedance and frequency range of 60 Hz to 16 kHz, users can fine-tune the console for optimal sound performance in various environments. The console supports various audio devices, ensuring compatibility with both analog and digital systems, making it ideal for diverse applications such as public announcements, emergency alerts, or daily communications.<br><br>In addition to its audio configuration options, the X-NPMI Console features a user-friendly touchscreen interface for quick adjustments and monitoring, ensuring that your communication system can be easily managed with minimal training. This adaptability ensures that your communication infrastructure can evolve as your needs grow, making it a long-term investment for any organization.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npmi-configurable-network-paging-console/features/202501-200-77-IUSeapOcVz.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:10:12.690596', '2025-01-22 02:23:36.556039', 200),
(383, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: High Power Output and Excellent Sound Pressure Level<br>The Honeywell L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker is designed to deliver exceptional sound quality, offering a rated power of 15W with a maximum power of 25W. Its high sound pressure level of 115 dB at 15W ensures clear, loud audio performance even in challenging environments. This makes it ideal for use in public spaces or outdoor environments where audio must travel over long distances or through background noise. The loudspeaker\'s superior output guarantees that your message will be heard with clarity, whether for an emergency alert or public announcement.<br><br>Its power tapping capabilities at 15W and 7.5W further provide flexibility, allowing users to adjust power output based on their specific needs. Whether you\'re in a small area or need coverage across a wide-open space, the L-PHP15A can be tailored to ensure optimal performance.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-php15a-horn-loudspeaker/features/202501-201-66-EqhK2n0RVE.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:17:33.962601', '2025-01-22 02:23:22.047461', 201),
(384, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Wide Frequency Range and Broad Sound Dispersion<br>The Honeywell L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker provides an extensive frequency range from 350 Hz to 8 kHz, ensuring that both voice and music are reproduced with clarity and detail. This wide frequency range is crucial for various applications, from public speaking to audio announcements. With a 140&deg; dispersion angle at 1 kHz, the speaker delivers even sound distribution, ensuring that your message reaches a large audience without dead spots.<br><br>This feature is especially beneficial in outdoor environments where audio coverage needs to be maximized, such as campuses, factories, and parks. The L-PHP15A guarantees uniform sound delivery across a wide area, making it an ideal choice for public address and alarm systems where clarity and reach are essential.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-php15a-horn-loudspeaker/features/202501-201-22-0zkbjPkAUq.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:17:33.967512', '2025-01-22 02:23:22.049785', 201),
(385, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: High Sound Pressure Level and Wide Frequency Range<br>The Honeywell L-PWP10A Cabinet Loudspeaker delivers a high sound pressure level (SPL) of 102 dB at 10W, ensuring that audio is clear and audible even in large or noisy environments. This makes it an ideal choice for public address systems where sound clarity is critical, whether for announcements in a supermarket, hotel, or office building. With a broad frequency range of 150 Hz to 17 kHz (-10dB), the speaker reproduces both low and high frequencies with precision, ensuring excellent sound quality across various applications, including voice communication and music playback.<br><br>Its ability to deliver clear sound over a wide frequency range ensures that speech is intelligible and music sounds natural, making it perfect for a wide range of commercial and public spaces.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pwp10a-cabinet-loudspeaker/features/202501-202-77-nOK4GibZ6Y.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:28:26.576411', '2025-01-22 02:23:10.040787', 202);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(386, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Anti-Fatigue Rubber for Distortion-Free Bass<br>One of the standout features of the Honeywell L-PWP10A Cabinet Loudspeaker is its use of high linearity anti-fatigue rubber, which helps maintain clear, distortion-free bass audio performance even during prolonged low-frequency operation. This feature ensures that the speaker produces consistent, high-quality sound throughout its use, without degradation of bass frequencies. Whether the speaker is used for long-duration announcements, background music, or other low-frequency tasks, it will maintain clarity and prevent any audio distortion, making it perfect for environments requiring continuous, high-quality sound.<br><br>This robust design ensures longevity and reliability, particularly in public spaces where speakers are in constant use, making the L-PWP10A an investment in both sound quality and durability.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pwp10a-cabinet-loudspeaker/features/202501-202-22-NmzcRVZPnh.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:28:26.581578', '2025-01-22 02:23:10.044219', 202),
(387, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: Wide Frequency Response and High Sound Pressure Level<br>The Honeywell L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker offers a wide frequency response range from 110 Hz to 20 kHz, ensuring the reproduction of clear and full-range audio across both low and high frequencies. With sound pressure levels of 100 dB at 6W and 102 dB at 10W, this speaker ensures excellent sound clarity and intelligibility, even in large or acoustically challenging spaces. Its ability to deliver clear and powerful audio, from deep bass to crisp high-end tones, makes it suitable for various applications, including announcements, background music, and more.<br><br>Whether in a large office, restaurant, or school, the speaker ensures the audio is clear and audible across the entire space, providing a consistent listening experience for all occupants.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pcm06b-ceiling-loudspeaker/features/202501-203-77-U0CGjxbPbz.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:38:45.755283', '2025-01-22 02:22:54.877327', 203),
(388, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Flexible Power Taps and Wide Dispersion Angle<br>The Honeywell L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker features adjustable power taps of 6W, 3W, and 1.5W, providing flexibility for different installation environments. This feature allows users to customize the power output based on the size of the area and the desired sound coverage. Additionally, with a 180&deg; dispersion angle at 1 kHz, the L-PCM06B ensures even audio distribution across large areas, eliminating dead spots and ensuring that sound reaches every corner of the room.<br><br>These features make the L-PCM06B ideal for commercial environments such as hotels, office buildings, and schools, where consistent and reliable sound coverage is essential. Its wide dispersion angle ensures that the speaker provides a uniform sound experience across a wide area, enhancing its effectiveness in public address and entertainment applications.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pcm06b-ceiling-loudspeaker/features/202501-203-88-cHoY1punbr.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:38:45.760591', '2025-01-22 02:22:54.879739', 203),
(389, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: High Sound Pressure Level and Wide Frequency Range<br>The Honeywell L-POM20A Column Speaker features an impressive sound pressure level of 105 dB at 20W, ensuring that audio broadcasts can be heard clearly and loudly even in large or noisy environments. Its wide frequency response range of 110 Hz to 20 kHz guarantees accurate and full-range sound reproduction, allowing it to handle everything from low-frequency audio to high-pitched tones with precision. This makes the speaker perfect for public address systems in spaces such as factories, theme parks, and hotels, where high-quality sound is essential for effective communication.<br><br>The speaker\'s excellent sound clarity ensures that critical announcements, including evacuation messages, are intelligible and easily understood, regardless of background noise.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pom20a-column-speaker/features/202501-204-33-Zok2KQby7W.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:51:02.506406', '2025-01-22 02:22:32.427126', 204);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(390, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Fire-Resistant Design and Durable Construction<br>The Honeywell L-POM20A Column Speaker is designed with safety in mind, featuring a fire-resistant cable and high-temperature ceramic wiring connector that allow it to continue functioning in the event of a fire emergency. The speaker&rsquo;s durable aluminum enclosure provides additional protection from heat and environmental factors, ensuring that it remains operational even in extreme conditions. The speaker is also equipped with a temperature fuse to prevent overheating due to excessive power loading, making it a reliable choice for both normal and emergency use.<br><br>With its corrosion-resistant aluminum swivel bracket, the L-POM20A is also designed to withstand long-term exposure to outdoor elements, ensuring durability in various settings. These safety and durability features make the L-POM20A an ideal choice for use in fire-prone environments where reliable communication is critical.</span><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pom20a-column-speaker/features/202501-204-77-AKFOzY8gPP.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:51:02.510642', '2025-01-22 02:22:32.430035', 204);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(391, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Multiple Audio Source Integration</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The Honeywell X-MAP4P Digital Audio Player integrates a variety of audio sources, including Bluetooth, USB, SD cards, and FM tuners, offering exceptional flexibility for commercial audio systems. Whether playing music from a USB drive, broadcasting live radio through an FM tuner, or streaming wirelessly via Bluetooth, the X-MAP4P handles it all. This versatility ensures that businesses can easily manage and distribute a wide array of audio content, from background music to emergency messages, all through one device.<br><br>Its compatibility with popular file formats such as MP3 and WAV ensures seamless playback, allowing businesses to use the device in diverse settings, including retail, hospitality, and public facilities.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-map4p-digital-audio-player/features/202501-205-11-YD5ifIbnzG.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:07:21.008254', '2025-01-22 02:22:17.944533', 205),
(392, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Dual Zone Output and Voice Alarm Integration</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The Honeywell X-MAP4P is equipped with two-line outputs on the rear panel, allowing simultaneous audio distribution to two separate zones. This feature makes it perfect for larger installations where different areas require independent sound management. Additionally, the X-MAP4P offers a Cinch audio connection for easy integration with Voice Alarm systems, ensuring that the device can be used for critical emergency broadcasts. Whether for evacuation messages or general announcements, this functionality provides businesses with the flexibility to manage both regular and emergency audio needs effectively.<br><br>This dual-zone and alarm integration capability enhances the device&rsquo;s usefulness, ensuring it is not only a reliable solution for music but also a valuable tool for maintaining safety and communication in various environments.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-map4p-digital-audio-player/features/202501-205-44-Dmy5BKqs56.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:07:21.013381', '2025-01-22 02:22:17.947194', 205),
(393, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ACO2-MF&rsquo;s use of high-quality 304# stainless steel not only gives it a premium appearance but also guarantees its durability and resistance to wear and tear. This material is ideal for environments like hotels, where the equipment is used frequently and exposed to the elements. The strength and corrosion resistance of stainless steel make it a lasting investment for hotels seeking to upgrade their security infrastructure with a modern and reliable system. This feature ensures that the ACO2-MF maintains its sleek look and high performance over time, even in high-traffic areas.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-aco2-mf/features/202501-206-22-YRjPrpLJqf.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.618247', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.621033', 206),
(394, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The RFID Access Control system works by allowing only authorized guests to enter the hotel, with each RFID card assigned a valid time to ensure access is limited to approved individuals. This feature is crucial for preventing unauthorized access, as expired or invalid cards will not be able to open the door. By integrating seamlessly with the hotel&rsquo;s locking software and working with electric drop bolts or electromagnetic locks, the ACO2-MF provides enhanced security and flexibility. It&rsquo;s a critical component in hotel management, improving both guest experience and overall safety.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-aco2-mf/features/202501-206-11-ZDFT91LZcw.png', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.622569', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.625144', 206),
(395, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Single User Passage Design</strong><br><br>The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q10 features a highly effective single-user passage design, allowing only one person to pass through at a time. This design eliminates the risk of unauthorized trailing, ensuring maximum security in any environment. This feature is especially beneficial in high-security settings where controlling the flow of individuals is essential, such as office buildings, stadiums, and government facilities. Its efficient design helps maintain orderly access while preventing the possibility of multiple individuals sneaking through unauthorized. This makes the DS-Q10 an excellent choice for businesses that prioritize safety and security.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q10/features/202501-207-77-YFP8wkeENd.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.062625', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.065702', 207),
(396, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Customization Options</strong><br><br>The DS-Q10 offers a high degree of customization, ensuring it fits seamlessly into any environment. The turnstile can be customized with different logos, colors, and dimensions to meet the specific aesthetic and functional needs of your installation space. Whether you\'re outfitting a corporate office, a luxury building, or a public space, the ability to tailor the design makes this tripod turnstile a versatile solution. Customization not only enhances the visual appeal of your turnstile but also ensures that it integrates perfectly with existing access control systems, providing both a secure and attractive solution to access management.<br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q10/features/202501-207-55-as88Kw41SM.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.067446', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.069947', 207),
(397, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Compact and Slim Design</strong><br><br>The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q50 is one of the slimmest models available, with a compact size of just 3802801000mm. This makes it an ideal solution for environments where space is limited but security needs to remain high. Despite its small footprint, the DS-Q50 maintains all the core features of larger models, such as the ability to restrict passage to one person at a time to prevent illegal trailing. Its sleek and unobtrusive design allows it to blend seamlessly into any installation, from corporate offices to high-traffic public spaces, offering both functionality and elegance in a small package.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q50/features/202501-208-22-j71vfDvj3B.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.535779', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.539235', 208),
(398, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Customizable Appearance and Integration</strong><br><br>The DS-Q50 offers exceptional flexibility with customization options for its logo, appearance color, and dimensions, allowing it to fit perfectly with its installation environment. Whether it&rsquo;s a high-end office building or a more functional public space, you can tailor the turnstile to match the aesthetic and functional needs of the space. Additionally, the DS-Q50 supports integration with any type of access control system, ensuring compatibility with your existing security infrastructure. This customization capability makes the DS-Q50 not only a secure and efficient solution but also a versatile choice that can be tailored to the unique requirements of any location.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q50/features/202501-208-33-hwTleeavBU.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.541796', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.544392', 208),
(399, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: Robust Construction with Stainless Steel<br><br>The DS112 Tripod Turnstile is built with full brushed stainless steel, offering a robust, durable construction that can withstand the test of time and harsh conditions. This high-quality material is resistant to rust, corrosion, and damage from exposure to outdoor elements, making it a perfect choice for both indoor and outdoor installations. The sleek stainless steel body not only enhances the aesthetic appeal of the turnstile but also ensures that it remains durable and functional even in challenging environments. The anti-rust and waterproof properties ensure that the DS112 provides long-lasting, reliable service.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds112/features/202501-209-77-PIyo7gVhqG.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.069444', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.072770', 209),
(400, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Visual LED Indication Strips for Enhanced Visibility<br><br>One of the standout features of the DS112 Tripod Turnstile is its visual LED indication strips, which are located at both the front and back of the turnstile. These LED strips provide clear, color-coded signals to indicate access status, improving the user experience and ensuring smooth pedestrian flow. The glowing visual effect also enhances the turnstile\'s aesthetic appeal, making it more attractive and noticeable. This feature is especially beneficial in high-traffic areas, as it offers instant feedback to users, allowing them to quickly understand whether access is granted or denied.<br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds112/features/202501-209-66-BYULBiRAUQ.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.074933', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.077583', 209),
(401, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Wide Passageway for Accessibility</strong><br><br>The DS-Q20 Quantum Optical Swing Turnstile features a 1100mm wide passageway, making it an ideal solution for environments that require wheelchair accessibility or the accommodation of large packages and carts. This feature ensures that the turnstile can handle a variety of users and needs, from individuals with mobility impairments to those carrying large items, making it a versatile option for both standard and emergency situations. The generous width enhances the turnstile\'s usability in busy, high-traffic environments, ensuring smooth and efficient access for everyone.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds-q20/features/202501-211-55-BV401VY69j.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.486107', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.488996', 211),
(402, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Fire Safety and Emergency Functionality</strong><br><br>The DS-Q20 is equipped with an automatic arm-opening feature to meet fire safety regulations, ensuring that the turnstile provides safe and efficient egress during an emergency. In the event of a fire or emergency, the arms of the turnstile will automatically open, allowing for rapid evacuation. This feature is critical in high-traffic areas like office buildings, airports, and public venues, where the safety and swift movement of people are paramount. Additionally, this functionality adds another layer of security, giving building managers and safety personnel peace of mind knowing the turnstile will operate in accordance with safety requirements.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds-q20/features/202501-211-77-fB4vAyGZFC.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.490782', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.493684', 211),
(403, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Bi-Directional Functionality</strong><br><br>The DS205A Optical Swing Turnstile is equipped with bi-directional functionality, which means it can efficiently control access in both directions. This feature is particularly useful in areas with fluctuating foot traffic, as it allows for both entry and exit through the same turnstile. By offering two-way operation, this turnstile ensures smooth and efficient pedestrian flow, making it ideal for use in busy public spaces, retail environments, and other high-traffic areas. Whether controlling access to a store or managing entry and exit in a restricted facility, the bi-directional design of the DS205A ensures a seamless experience for all users.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds205a/features/202501-212-22-eF9SxohS2I.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.447866', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.450493', 212),
(404, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Wide Passage for Accessibility</strong><br><br>One of the standout features of the DS205A Optical Swing Turnstile is its 900mm-wide passage, which accommodates a wide range of users. This expanded width allows the turnstile to be used by wheelchair users, people with large luggage, bicycles, and prams, ensuring that everyone can pass through the turnstile with ease. The accessibility feature makes the DS205A ideal for environments such as shopping centers, supermarkets, and public transport terminals, where accommodating a diverse range of users is essential. The wide passage also adds flexibility, ensuring that the turnstile can be used in various settings without compromising on security or efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds205a/features/202501-212-55-iXIkGROeHz.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.452446', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.455317', 212),
(405, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: Wide Passage for Accessibility<br><br>The DSN-20 Nebula Optical Swing Turnstile features an adjustable passage width ranging from 650mm to 1100mm, making it an excellent choice for environments where accessibility is a top priority. This wide passage ensures that individuals with wheelchairs, large luggage, or prams can pass through the turnstile easily, without any hindrance. The flexible design of the DSN-20 allows it to cater to a diverse range of users, ensuring that everyone can access the area securely and comfortably. This makes it ideal for facilities like airports, shopping malls, and corporate buildings, where accessibility for all pedestrians is essential.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-dsn-20/features/202501-213-66-58b7zjQ03m.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.354384', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.357846', 213),
(406, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: High-Quality Build and Modern Design<br><br>The DSN-20 is built with a combination of brushed stainless steel and a high-end black painting process, providing both durability and a sleek appearance. The turnstile\'s solid body crate ensures long-lasting reliability, even in high-traffic environments. Additionally, its modern, urban design features attractive blue LED strips, adding a stylish touch that complements any contemporary setting. Superior production techniques, including integrated mold production and robot-assisted welding, further enhance the quality of the DSN-20, guaranteeing high precision and longevity. This makes the DSN-20 an excellent option for businesses looking for a durable, aesthetically pleasing, and efficient access control solution.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-dsn-20/features/202501-213-77-6FDsSFBz6y.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.359634', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.362349', 213),
(407, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 1: High Throughput Rate for Efficient Traffic Flow<br><br>The DS-Q30 Quantum Optical Flap Turnstile is capable of processing up to 45 persons per minute, making it a perfect solution for high-traffic areas such as metro stations, office buildings, and commercial complexes. This high throughput ensures that pedestrian flow remains uninterrupted, even in locations where large volumes of people pass through regularly. Whether for managing entry and exit in busy environments or maintaining a smooth flow of visitors, the DS-Q30 offers the speed and reliability necessary for effective access control.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds-q30/features/202501-214-77-sXNvxm735R.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.497875', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.502093', 214),
(408, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Key Feature 2: Fire Safety and Emergency Functionality<br><br>The DS-Q30 is equipped with retractable arms that automatically open in the event of an emergency, meeting fire safety regulations and ensuring rapid evacuation in case of danger. This feature provides users with safe and immediate access during emergencies, preventing any delays that could hinder evacuation efforts. With the ability to comply with fire safety requirements while maintaining security during normal operations, the DS-Q30 ensures peace of mind in high-traffic settings where safety is a priority. This emergency functionality makes the DS-Q30 ideal for public spaces and buildings that require both security and quick emergency access.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds-q30/features/202501-214-88-ZvfOrE08ba.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.504147', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.506741', 214),
(409, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;High-Speed Throughput</strong><br><br>The DSN-30 Nebula Optical Flap Turnstile is designed for environments with high pedestrian traffic, offering a throughput of up to 45 persons per minute. This impressive speed ensures that large volumes of people can pass through without delays, making it ideal for crowded public spaces such as metro stations, airports, and office buildings. The high-speed access control provided by the DSN-30 is crucial for maintaining a smooth flow of visitors while ensuring that security is not compromised. Whether for controlling entry or exit, the turnstile ensures fast, efficient access, even in high-demand settings.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-dsn-30/features/202501-215-66-r6hEQgsdGc.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.435983', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.438953', 215),
(410, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Seamless Third-Party Integration</strong><br><br>The DSN-30 Optical Flap Turnstile is equipped with a standard relay signal, allowing it to integrate seamlessly with a wide range of third-party access control systems. This feature provides flexibility in configuring the turnstile to work with RFID readers, fingerprint scanners, or other security devices, ensuring compatibility with existing systems. The ability to integrate with various access control technologies makes the DSN-30 a versatile solution for businesses and organizations with diverse security needs. This integration also enhances the overall security infrastructure, ensuring smooth and efficient management of pedestrian access across multiple entry points.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-dsn-30/features/202501-215-77-eZfcGablUw.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.440782', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.443223', 215),
(411, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;High-Speed Throughput and Flexibility</strong><br><br>The DS3000 Optical Flap Turnstile boasts a throughput rate of 40-45 persons per minute, allowing for smooth and efficient pedestrian flow in high-traffic environments. This speed is ideal for busy public areas like office buildings, college campuses, or commercial spaces, ensuring minimal wait times and efficient access control. Additionally, the turnstile offers the option for single or bi-directional settings, providing flexibility to suit different access needs. Whether controlling access in one direction or both, the DS3000 ensures that security and efficiency are maintained at all times.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds3000/features/202501-216-55-7TugSJMkP5.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.389816', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.393472', 216),
(412, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Advanced Security and Easy Integration</strong><br><br>The DS3000 Optical Flap Turnstile is equipped with four pairs of infrared sensors, enhancing security by detecting unauthorized passage attempts and triggering an alarm when necessary. This robust security feature helps prevent unauthorized access and ensures the safety of restricted areas. Furthermore, the DS3000 includes a standard relay signal that allows easy integration with various third-party access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint, and biometric readers. This seamless integration ensures that the turnstile can be adapted to existing security setups, making it a versatile choice for diverse environments.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds3000/features/202501-216-66-DPXpmGEIwF.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.395577', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.398958', 216),
(413, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>High-Security Full-Height Design</strong><br><br>The DS411 Full Height Turnstile is designed to offer maximum security for high-risk environments, including prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. Its full-height barrier ensures that unauthorized individuals cannot bypass the system, providing an additional layer of protection for restricted areas. This robust design is ideal for sites that require controlled access, preventing tailgating and unauthorized entry. The DS411 is an essential solution for areas where security is a top priority, offering peace of mind for both personnel and facility managers.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds411/features/202501-217-66-AY2ujFkLrY.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.582517', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.585677', 217),
(414, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Durable and Weather-Resistant Construction</strong><br><br>Constructed from finished and brushed stainless steel, the DS411 Full Height Turnstile is built to endure harsh weather conditions and physical wear. This durable material provides resistance to corrosion and rust, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. Whether exposed to rain, snow, or extreme temperatures, the DS411 maintains its functionality and appearance, ensuring reliable performance over time. Its robust design makes it an ideal choice for high-traffic and high-risk locations, offering long-lasting security and peace of mind.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds411/features/202501-217-77-v50MG1V2SX.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.588279', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.591845', 217),
(415, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Bi-Directional Passage Control with LED Indicators</strong><br><br>The DS412 Full Height Turnstile features bi-directional passage control, offering flexibility for both entry and exit points in high-traffic and high-security areas. The turnstile includes clearly visible LED indicators on the side front and top, which indicate whether entry is accepted or denied. These indicators improve both user experience and operational efficiency, ensuring a smooth and secure flow of pedestrian traffic. This feature is especially useful in environments like stadiums, industrial sites, or event venues, where controlling the movement of people in both directions is critical.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds412/features/202501-218-77-9AtTrumYN0.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.423662', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.426984', 218),
(416, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable Stainless Steel Construction with Flexible Rotor Options</strong><br><br>Built from high-quality, full brushed stainless steel, the DS412 Full Height Turnstile is designed for long-lasting durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. This robust material makes the turnstile suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations, ensuring reliable performance in challenging environments. The DS412 offers flexibility with rotor options, allowing users to select between 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotors, making it adaptable to various site needs. Additionally, the turnstile provides ample space to install a variety of access control devices, including RFID, fingerprint scanners, or barcode readers, enhancing its versatility for diverse security applications.<br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds412/features/202501-218-66-d1TSfzT2bR.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.428995', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.432068', 218),
(417, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Weather-Resistant Design with Rain Protection Roof</strong><br><br>The DS401FS Full Height Turnstile is specifically designed for outdoor use with a solid rain protection roof, making it resistant to harsh weather conditions such as rain, snow, and extreme temperatures. Available in either 304 or 316 stainless steel, it ensures long-lasting durability, rust resistance, and waterproof performance. This robust construction makes it an ideal solution for locations like stadiums, construction sites, and prisons, where environmental exposure and heavy use are common. The rain protection roof ensures that the turnstile remains fully operational and secure, even in challenging weather.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds401fs/features/202501-219-66-Cn9WympZlh.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:06:21.000851', '2025-01-22 07:06:21.005092', 219),
(418, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Flexible Rotor Options and LED Indicators</strong><br><br>The DS401FS Full Height Turnstile offers customizable rotor arm options with either 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotation, allowing users to select the ideal configuration based on their specific pedestrian traffic flow needs. This flexibility ensures that the turnstile can efficiently manage entry and exit in both high-security and high-traffic environments. Additionally, the turnstile features LED indicators on both the top cover and the body side, which clearly display whether entry is accepted or denied. These visual signals enhance user experience, improving the overall efficiency of access control and reducing confusion.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds401fs/features/202501-219-77-O6QBIVXiId.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:06:21.007322', '2025-01-22 07:06:21.010555', 219),
(419, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Weather-Resistant Design with Rain Protection Roof</strong><br><br>The DS402FS Full Height Turnstile is built to withstand extreme outdoor conditions, thanks to its solid rain protection roof. This feature ensures the turnstile remains operational in all weather, from heavy rain to snow, protecting the internal components from the elements. Constructed from either 304 or 316 stainless steel, it offers long-lasting durability, rust resistance, and the ability to perform reliably even in harsh environments. The rain protection roof is an essential feature for high-security outdoor sites like stadiums, construction sites, and prisons, where both security and weather resistance are paramount.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds402fs/features/202501-220-66-803Ov1Gmf8.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.224335', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.227576', 220),
(420, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Flexible Rotor Options and LED Indicators</strong><br><br>The DS402FS Full Height Turnstile offers flexibility with its rotor arm options, allowing for either 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotation based on user preferences and traffic flow requirements. This adaptability ensures efficient and secure pedestrian movement, whether the turnstile is used for single or bi-directional access control. Additionally, the turnstile includes four LED indicators&mdash;two on the side front and two on the top&mdash;that clearly communicate whether access is granted or denied. This visual feedback enhances the user experience by ensuring clear and intuitive navigation, while improving overall security by signaling entry status at all times.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds402fs/features/202501-220-77-0dGetaCWi6.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.229457', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.232466', 220),
(421, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Portable and Compact Design</strong><br><br>The FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher boasts a portable and compact design, making it an ideal solution for various environments, from homes and offices to vehicles. Its lightweight construction ensures ease of use, allowing users to handle the extinguisher confidently in the event of a small fire. The compact size also makes it convenient to store without occupying too much space, ensuring it\'s always readily accessible when needed most. This design makes the FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher a versatile tool for fire safety in tight spaces.</span></p>', 'products/fire-extinguisher/features/202501-221-44-52eIrZ98jt.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.950432', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.953346', 221),
(422, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Effective for Small Fire Emergencies</strong><br><br>The FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher is specifically designed to handle small fire emergencies, providing an immediate response to prevent fire spread. Whether it\'s a grease fire in the kitchen, a small electrical fire, or a paper fire, this extinguisher is equipped with the right fire suppression agents to safely and effectively put out flames. By targeting small fires at the initial stage, the FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher helps to reduce damage and prevent more significant fire hazards, making it an essential safety device for any setting.</span></p>', 'products/fire-extinguisher/features/202501-221-77-9iZXIjlkIM.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.955044', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.957560', 221),
(423, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Clean and Safe FM-200 Agent</strong><br><br>The FM-200 Suppression System uses FM-200, a clean, gaseous agent that is safe for human exposure and highly effective in extinguishing fires. Unlike water or foam-based systems, FM-200 leaves no residue, eliminating the need for costly cleanup after discharge. The agent is non-toxic in the concentrations used and does not pose a health risk to occupants, making it ideal for environments like data centers, server rooms, and museums, where both human safety and equipment protection are priorities. This clean suppression ensures minimal disruption to operations, making it a trusted fire safety solution for high-value spaces.</span></p>', 'products/fm-200-suppression-system/features/202501-222-44-wd6z5DqYW2.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.517915', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.520755', 222),
(424, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Fast Fire Suppression with Minimal Damage</strong><br><br>The FM-200 Suppression System is engineered for rapid fire suppression, quickly detecting fire and releasing the FM-200 agent to suppress the flames in seconds. Its speed of response is critical in environments where fire spread can cause significant damage to expensive equipment or data. The system is especially beneficial in high-risk areas such as data centers, where traditional fire suppression methods could destroy valuable technology. By extinguishing fires swiftly and cleanly, the system prevents the escalation of damage while allowing for quick recovery and minimal downtime.</span></p>', 'products/fm-200-suppression-system/features/202501-222-11-Tz7JgzvLQ5.png', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.522375', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.524487', 222),
(425, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Automatic Heat Detection and Activation</strong><br><br>The Sprinklers are equipped with an automatic heat detection system, ensuring that the sprinklers activate when the temperature rises above a preset threshold. This immediate response helps suppress fires at their inception, limiting damage and preventing further spread. By providing rapid activation, the sprinklers ensure that fire hazards are controlled efficiently and that occupants have time to evacuate safely. This feature is essential for protecting commercial and residential properties from the devastating effects of fire, offering peace of mind and effective fire suppression when needed most.</span></p>', 'products/sprinklers/features/202501-223-55-yKXGDxIXku.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.422569', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.425300', 223),
(426, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Easy Installation and Low Maintenance</strong><br><br>Designed for convenience, the Sprinklers are easy to install and maintain, making them a reliable choice for both commercial and residential properties. Installed in an upright position within the water piping system, they are simple to integrate into existing fire safety setups. The sprinklers require minimal maintenance, offering consistent and dependable performance over time. This low-maintenance design ensures that building owners and property managers can focus on other priorities while having confidence in the ongoing protection provided by the FIRE PRO Sprinklers.</span></p>', 'products/sprinklers/features/202501-223-66-l7IJz1cc8M.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.427714', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.430792', 223),
(427, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Wide Compatibility with Various Fluids</strong><br><br>The Signal Gate Valve is engineered to handle a wide range of fluids, including water, air, steam, oil, liquid metals, and corrosive or radioactive materials. Its versatility makes it suitable for diverse industries, from energy and manufacturing to chemical processing. This wide compatibility ensures that the valve can maintain smooth and reliable operation even when dealing with highly complex or hazardous mediums. The ability to control such varied substances without compromising performance is one of the key strengths of this valve.</span></p>', 'products/signal-gate-valve/features/202501-224-66-JYk63ma2Hd.PNG', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.839859', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.843142', 224),
(428, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Real-Time Monitoring and Flow Control</strong><br><br>Equipped with an integrated signal system, the Signal Gate Valve allows for real-time monitoring of fluid flow, providing immediate feedback and allowing for quick intervention if necessary. This feature ensures that operators can closely monitor fluid dynamics and detect any issues promptly, reducing the risk of accidents or equipment damage. The signal mechanism enhances the valve\'s effectiveness, ensuring that the flow is managed efficiently and that the system remains safe and operational in all circumstances.</span></p>', 'products/signal-gate-valve/features/202501-224-77-5wCBIb5ukc.PNG', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.844958', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.847461', 224),
(429, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Dynamic Pressure Regulation</strong><br><br>The&nbsp; Pressure Reducing Valve is designed to dynamically regulate outlet pressure, ensuring that it remains within a set range, even with fluctuating inlet pressures. This ability to automatically adjust the valve&rsquo;s opening and closing mechanism provides real-time pressure control, preventing equipment damage from pressure surges. The valve&rsquo;s precision helps maintain consistent pressure levels for sensitive systems, enhancing the safety and operational efficiency of industries such as manufacturing, water treatment, and power generation.<br></span></p>', 'products/pressure-reducing-valve/features/202501-225-66-1sm5b1pfQk.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:36:23.873245', '2025-01-23 00:49:51.020139', 225),
(430, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Protection for Sensitive Equipment</strong><br><br>By maintaining outlet pressure within a specified range, the Pressure Reducing Valve offers crucial protection to downstream equipment and appliances. This reduces the risk of overpressure damage, enhancing the longevity of pumps, pipes, and machinery. The valve is essential in protecting sensitive components from high-pressure environments, ensuring the system\'s stability and minimizing downtime for maintenance or repairs. Its robust design makes it an ideal solution for industries that rely on consistent pressure regulation for the optimal performance of their equipment.</span></p>', 'products/pressure-reducing-valve/features/202501-225-77-ghRASagbzr.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:36:23.877470', '2025-01-23 00:49:51.022640', 225),
(431, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Automatic Fire Detection and Suppression</strong><br><br>The&nbsp; Kitchen Suppression System is equipped with advanced sensors that automatically detect fires as soon as they occur. Upon detection, the system releases a fast-acting fire suppressant directly onto the source of the fire, preventing it from spreading. This immediate response minimizes fire damage and protects kitchen equipment, inventory, and staff. The system&rsquo;s ability to automatically activate ensures that kitchens are continuously protected, even during off-hours or when staff is unavailable.<br></span></p>', 'products/kitchen-suppression-system/features/202501-226-77-rnVz6bzJvK.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:48:10.804982', '2025-01-23 00:50:18.799171', 226),
(432, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Coverage for High-Risk Areas</strong><br><br>Kitchen Suppression System is designed with strategically placed nozzles that target high-risk cooking areas such as fryers, grills, and stoves. This precise and focused coverage ensures that the fire-suppressing agent is directed where it&rsquo;s most needed, extinguishing flames quickly and effectively. By offering tailored protection for the most fire-prone areas, the system provides comprehensive safety for kitchens, ensuring the fast suppression of fires without damaging the surrounding environment or equipment.</span></p>', 'products/kitchen-suppression-system/features/202501-226-44-bs8v3FXrwI.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:48:10.810028', '2025-01-23 00:50:18.801421', 226),
(433, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;High-Performance Water Flow and Pressure</strong><br><br>The Fire Pump is designed to provide an efficient and reliable water supply to fire protection systems, ensuring that the necessary flow and pressure are available for firefighting purposes. It is capable of supporting sprinkler systems, hydrants, and standpipes, delivering the required pressure to quickly suppress fires. This high-performance capability ensures that buildings, industrial facilities, and residential areas are equipped with the water supply needed to effectively combat fires in emergencies.</span></p>', 'products/fire-pump/features/202501-227-33-nlpqul1oRF.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.054725', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.057589', 227),
(434, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Reliable Construction</strong><br><br>Built with durability in mind, the Fire Pump is designed to withstand demanding environments and operate effectively during emergencies. Its robust construction ensures long-term performance, even under high-pressure conditions. This reliable pump is an essential part of any fire protection system, providing continuous support during a fire emergency to safeguard both life and property.</span></p>', 'products/fire-pump/features/202501-227-44-HvFuwu0vSp.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.059938', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.063474', 227),
(435, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Constant Pressure Maintenance</strong><br><br>The primary function of the Jockey Pump is to maintain a constant pressure in the fire protection system, ensuring that pressure drops do not trigger unnecessary activation of the main fire pump. By automatically restoring pressure when needed, this pump guarantees that the system remains ready for action at all times. This pressure maintenance capability prevents damage to the fire pump and reduces wear, leading to lower operational costs and longer system lifespan.<br></span></p>', 'products/jockey-pump/features/202501-228-44-KbiHx2kD6i.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.701379', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.704087', 228),
(436, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Energy Efficiency and System Longevity</strong><br><br>The Jockey Pump helps conserve energy by preventing frequent cycling of the main fire pump. When the pressure fluctuates slightly, the jockey pump corrects the pressure levels, allowing the primary fire pump to stay inactive until truly necessary. This efficient operation not only saves energy but also reduces the wear on the larger fire pump, enhancing the overall longevity of the fire protection system and lowering maintenance costs.</span></p>', 'products/jockey-pump/features/202501-228-55-5mSiyae6t5.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.705614', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.708357', 228),
(437, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Dry-Type Design with Low-Pressure Air or Nitrogen</strong><br><br>The Preaction Alarm Valve Group features a dry-type design that fills the system pipes with low-pressure air or nitrogen during testing. This ensures that the sprinklers remain closed until a fire is detected, minimizing the risk of accidental water discharge. This feature is particularly useful for environments where water damage is a significant concern, providing enhanced protection without compromising the system&rsquo;s effectiveness during a fire emergency.<br></span></p>', 'products/preaction-alarm-valve-group/features/202501-229-66-Jcc1LzCFaP.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.486064', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.488723', 229),
(438, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Dry-Type Design with Low-Pressure Air or Nitrogen</strong><br><br>The Preaction Alarm Valve Group features a dry-type design that fills the system pipes with low-pressure air or nitrogen during testing. This ensures that the sprinklers remain closed until a fire is detected, minimizing the risk of accidental water discharge. This feature is particularly useful for environments where water damage is a significant concern, providing enhanced protection without compromising the system&rsquo;s effectiveness during a fire emergency.<br></span></p>', 'products/preaction-alarm-valve-group/features/202501-229-77-K44cbHu3zF.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.490398', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.493510', 229),
(439, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Weather-Resistant Construction</strong><br><br>The Outdoor Fire Hydrants are engineered to withstand a range of weather conditions, ensuring that they function optimally in both extreme cold and heat. Their robust construction is made from durable materials, designed to resist corrosion and other forms of damage caused by harsh environmental factors. This makes them ideal for use in areas where weather conditions fluctuate significantly, guaranteeing that firefighters always have access to a reliable water source, regardless of external conditions.</span></p>', 'products/outdoor-fire-hydrants/features/202501-230-66-gsKKnDT3UH.PNG', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.352823', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.367035', 230),
(440, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>&nbsp;Easy Hose Connection and Efficient Operation</strong><br><br>Outdoor Fire Hydrants are equipped with multiple outlets for quick hose connections, allowing firefighters to efficiently manage water flow during emergencies. The valve mechanism is designed for ease of use, enabling rapid activation and immediate water access. With a straightforward, efficient design, these fire hydrants help ensure that firefighting operations can commence without delay, optimizing response times and boosting the effectiveness of fire suppression efforts.</span></p>', 'products/outdoor-fire-hydrants/features/202501-230-77-xJM4gCAmxK.PNG', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.370607', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.373801', 230),
(441, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>High User and Log Capacity</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The SF400 supports a user capacity ranging from 1,000 to 5,000, making it suitable for small to large organizations. Its 8,000-log storage ensures reliable record-keeping for attendance and access data. The ample capacity reduces the need for frequent data transfers, streamlining administrative processes and ensuring uninterrupted operation.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-sf400/features/202501-231-ZK5-dKrNjzDiCZ.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:01:19.222289', '2025-01-24 01:15:40.826974', 231),
(442, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Flexible Authentication Methods</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Offering a fingerprint capacity of 1,500 and a card capacity of 5,000, the SF400 provides versatile authentication options. Users can choose between biometric recognition and card-based access, catering to varying organizational requirements. This flexibility enhances convenience, security, and user satisfaction, making it a reliable solution for modern workplaces.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-sf400/features/202501-231-ZK6-gZuzu8Qbt8.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:01:19.228214', '2025-01-24 01:15:40.829511', 231),
(443, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V3L&rsquo;s dual authentication system offers an advanced combination of facial recognition and fingerprint verification. This ensures that access is granted only to authorized individuals, providing an extra layer of security for organizations. The facial recognition technology uses visible light to accurately identify users, even in low-light conditions, while the fingerprint scanner ensures reliable and swift identification. This dual approach minimizes the risk of unauthorized access, making it an ideal solution for high-security environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v3l/features/202501-232-6-fGHh9cpJPV.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:04:24.729378', '2025-01-24 01:14:39.655004', 232),
(444, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> With its impressive capacity features, the SpeedFace V3L can support up to 500 facial recognition templates, 3,000 fingerprints, and 3,000 access cards, providing flexibility for a range of business sizes. It also offers a large log storage capacity of 200,000 records, allowing organizations to keep detailed track of access events and monitor security in real-time. This makes the SpeedFace V3L not only an effective access control solution but also a reliable time-keeping tool, helping businesses optimize their workforce management.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v3l/features/202501-232-7-dRRm7LVBAG.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:04:24.733755', '2025-01-24 01:14:39.658349', 232),
(445, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V5L offers multi-verification capabilities that provide robust security for access control and time-keeping. Users can authenticate their identity using facial recognition, fingerprint scanning, palm recognition, or even QR code scanning via the Mobile App. This flexibility ensures that organizations can choose the most appropriate method for their specific needs. With a user capacity of 1,000 and the ability to accommodate 1,000 fingerprints and faces, the system is ideal for medium to large businesses. Additionally, the 150,000 log capacity ensures that the device can handle high-volume data storage without compromising performance, making it perfect for high-traffic environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v5l/features/202501-233-6-E6113qTaNa.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.616040', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.619621', 233),
(446, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V5L&rsquo;s advanced facial recognition algorithms are complemented by intelligent engineering, ensuring accurate and rapid verification. The device is designed for quick recognition and response times, even in busy environments. It integrates cutting-edge computer vision technology, providing a seamless experience for users while maintaining high levels of security. With its ability to store large amounts of data (up to 150,000 logs) and manage up to 1,000 users, this device is suitable for businesses looking to implement a secure and efficient time-keeping and access control solution.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v5l/features/202501-233-5-4CSW9rnz2T.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.621740', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.624643', 233),
(447, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The INBIO PRO PLUS stands out with its impressive biometric capabilities. With support for both facial and fingerprint authentication, the system allows for secure and efficient access for a large number of users. The facial recognition capacity of up to 3,000 faces ensures fast, touch-free access, while fingerprint recognition supports up to 20,000 individuals, providing an additional layer of security. This makes the INBIO PRO PLUS ideal for environments where multiple forms of access control are required for large user bases.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-inbio-pro-plus/features/202501-234-6-s8vhr7HfQt.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.426861', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.429981', 234),
(448, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> Another key feature of the INBIO PRO PLUS is its expansive user and log capacity, making it a powerful solution for large-scale operations. The system can manage up to 100,000 users, including cardholders and those using QR codes for entry. With the ability to store up to 100,000 logs, it ensures that all access events are captured, providing thorough tracking and auditing. This makes it perfect for organizations needing to monitor activity across large facilities or multiple locations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-inbio-pro-plus/features/202501-234-7-UEinZkXMet.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.432046', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.434786', 234),
(449, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Advanced Fingerprint Recognition Technology<br>The FR1200 Fingerprint Reader utilizes cutting-edge fingerprint recognition technology to ensure fast, accurate, and secure identification. It captures and transfers high-quality fingerprint samples to the connected access control panel, offering a seamless and reliable authentication process. This technology eliminates the risk of unauthorized access, improving security and enhancing the efficiency of your access control system. Whether used in high-traffic areas or at critical entry points, it provides consistent performance and superior accuracy.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-fr1200/features/202501-235-4_1-ijG0IY1fUc.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.955081', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.958415', 235);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(450, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Durable, Weather-Resistant Construction<br>Designed for durability, the FR1200 features an IP65-rated rugged structure that can withstand extreme weather conditions. Whether exposed to rain, dust, or harsh temperatures, this fingerprint reader continues to operate effectively. Its rugged construction makes it an ideal choice for outdoor installations, such as gates or external doors, where environmental factors are a concern. The FR1200&rsquo;s weather-resistant design ensures long-lasting performance and minimal maintenance, providing a dependable solution for any installation location.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-fr1200/features/202501-235-7-phc3dDZ6G9.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.960236', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.963530', 235),
(451, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">ZKBioHLMS Lock Management Application The ZL600 is compatible with the ZKBioHLMS lock management system, a robust solution for managing hotel door locks efficiently. This system allows hotel administrators to monitor and control access across multiple locations, ensuring security and operational efficiency. The ZKBioHLMS application provides real-time updates, access logs, and detailed reports, enabling hotel management to track and manage door access from anywhere. Whether on-site or remotely, this feature ensures flexibility and better control over the entire hotel security infrastructure.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl600/features/202501-236-6-lcJYZILmKh.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.109200', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.112190', 236),
(452, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZL600 features Zigbee communication technology, which enhances both local and remote access control. Zigbee offers reliable, low-power communication between the lock and central management systems, ensuring consistent performance and efficiency. With Zigbee, users can easily control the locks through mobile applications or centralized management platforms, making it convenient to manage access for hotel staff and guests alike. This feature also ensures that the system is scalable, allowing it to grow alongside a hotel\'s needs.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl600/features/202501-236-7-EzCPrLWHMi.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.114166', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.116699', 236),
(453, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZL700 Wireless Hotel Lock features the advanced ZKBIOHLMS lock management application, which offers hotels enhanced control over their security system. With this application, hotel administrators can easily manage access rights, monitor lock status, and ensure guest security from anywhere. The system supports real-time updates, giving operators the ability to track and respond to any changes or security breaches instantly. This advanced management system streamlines operations, making it more efficient to oversee room access without the need for physical key handling.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl700/features/202501-237-6-Tj8cr3wRO6.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.526595', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.529556', 237),
(454, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Built with SAE 304 stainless steel, the ZL700 Wireless Hotel Lock boasts superior durability and resistance to corrosion. Its stainless steel construction makes it highly resistant to rust, extending the lock\'s lifespan even in coastal or humid environments. The 96-hour salt spray test ensures the lock can withstand harsh conditions and still maintain its functionality. This makes the ZL700 a reliable choice for hotels located in challenging climates where traditional locks may fail due to corrosion or wear.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl700/features/202501-237-7-CtUZKArILZ.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.531863', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.534262', 237),
(455, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Advanced Software Integration</strong><br>The LH6500 is fully compatible with ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, offering hotel operators an all-in-one solution for managing access control. The software simplifies keycard issuance, room management, and real-time activity tracking, enhancing operational efficiency. This integration ensures seamless synchronization between the lock and the hotel\'s management systems, providing a secure and smooth experience for both staff and guests.Advanced Software Integration<br>The LH6500 is fully compatible with ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, offering hotel operators an all-in-one solution for managing access control. The software simplifies keycard issuance, room management, and real-time activity tracking, enhancing operational efficiency. This integration ensures seamless synchronization between the lock and the hotel\'s management systems, providing a secure and smooth experience for both staff and guests.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6500/features/202501-238-7-0NoyljIgFR.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.216494', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.219465', 238),
(456, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Durable and Versatile Design</strong><br>Constructed with high-quality zinc alloy, the LH6500 is designed to withstand the demands of high-traffic environments. Its slim and modern profile fits door thicknesses ranging from 40mm to 50mm, making it versatile for different hotel door types. The lock supports ISO14443 RFID cards, which are known for their security and ease of use, ensuring a reliable access solution for hotels of all sizes.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6500/features/202501-238-6-YOA9iU3Cdf.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.221046', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.223182', 238),
(457, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Advanced Technology &amp; Security</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The LH6800 is equipped with 13.56 MHz Mifare card technology, offering secure and rapid access for guests and staff. Its American standard mortise with 5 latches provides a robust locking mechanism, enhancing security and ensuring the safety of hotel rooms. With compatibility for ISO14443 RFID cards, the lock delivers a smooth and reliable access experience, aligning with the latest advancements in smart security.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6800/features/202501-239-5-oa3vFGkl75.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.888491', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.891596', 239),
(458, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Seamless Integration &amp; Premium Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Supporting ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, the LH6800 integrates seamlessly into advanced security systems, allowing centralized management and monitoring. Its zinc alloy construction offers exceptional durability, making it suitable for high-usage environments without compromising on style. Designed to fit doors with thicknesses ranging from 35mm to 45mm, this lock ensures adaptability and elegance for various hotel setups.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6800/features/202501-239-7-NB1Yduyv54.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.894136', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.897542', 239),
(459, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">One of the standout features of the MARS-S1000 Series is its advanced anti-tailgate system, supported by up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors in the Mars-Pro version. These sensors detect unauthorized individuals attempting to enter behind an authorized person, effectively preventing tailgating. This high level of security ensures that only one person can pass through at a time, keeping your premises safe from unauthorized access. The increased sensor count boosts detection accuracy, making it an ideal choice for high-traffic environments where security is a top priority.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1000-series/features/202501-240-6-hYKU0oRxQJ.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.886684', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.889516', 240),
(460, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The modular, snap-fit, screwless design of the MARS-S1000 Series allows for easy installation and maintenance, cutting production lead time by up to 30%. This innovative design not only saves time but also reduces the complexity of setup, making it a cost-effective solution for businesses. With its customizable options, such as the inclusion of controllers, RFID readers, or biometric systems, the MARS-S1000 Series can be tailored to suit any access control requirement. Additionally, its low-maintenance design ensures long-term reliability, providing a smooth user experience throughout its operational life.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1000-series/features/202501-240-7-wHm3A6AMBa.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.891184', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.894281', 240),
(461, '<p><strong><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Advanced Anti-Tailgate Performance</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">&nbsp;The MARS-S1200 Series features up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors that enhance its anti-tailgate performance. This advanced sensor technology ensures that individuals who attempt to tailgate or sneak through unauthorized are immediately detected and prevented from accessing the secure area. This feature makes it an ideal solution for high-security environments, where preventing unauthorized access is crucial. With real-time monitoring, the system ensures that only one person can pass through at a time, protecting your premises from security breaches.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1200-series/features/202501-241-6-MyVG3wekVb.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.398731', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.402088', 241),
(462, '<p><strong><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> Modularized and Easy-to-Maintain Design</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">One of the standout features of the MARS-S1200 Series is its creative snap-fit, screwless modular design, which makes installation and maintenance both easier and faster. This design reduces the time required for setup and ongoing maintenance, saving up to 30% on production lead times. The modular structure allows for quick adjustments and updates to meet evolving security needs, making it an ideal choice for facilities that require high flexibility and minimal downtime.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1200-series/features/202501-241-7-jPzdJ8nXqS.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.403955', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.406308', 241),
(463, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS PRO-S1200 Series offers up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors for superior anti-tailgate performance. This advanced feature enables the gate to accurately detect any unauthorized attempts to tailgate or bypass the gate, ensuring that only authorized individuals are granted access. The combination of multiple sensors positioned strategically along the barrier optimizes detection accuracy, providing a high level of security in fast-paced environments. The ability to tailor the gate&rsquo;s settings for varying levels of sensitivity allows for enhanced control over access points, significantly reducing the risk of security breaches.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1200-series/features/202501-242-6-sAFTl1JijA.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.672305', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.675350', 242),
(464, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The snap-fit, screwless modular design of the MARS PRO-S1200 Series makes installation and maintenance incredibly easy. This innovative design reduces production lead time by up to 30%, allowing for faster deployment and less downtime during installation. The modular structure also enables quick replacements or upgrades, minimizing maintenance costs and efforts. With this design, the system can be easily integrated into a variety of environments and existing security infrastructures, offering a highly flexible and user-friendly solution for businesses and facilities of all sizes.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1200-series/features/202501-242-7-KyguWpe8Ez.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.676972', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.679111', 242),
(465, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS PRO-S1000 Series is equipped with up to 22 pairs of advanced infrared sensors, making it highly effective in anti-tailgate performance. This feature allows the gate to detect and prevent unauthorized entry by identifying when someone tries to \"tailgate\" or sneak in behind an authorized person. The increased sensor coverage significantly enhances the gate\'s reliability, ensuring that only those with proper authorization are granted access.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1000-series/features/202501-243-5-YS0QrAqfaG.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.220810', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.224220', 243),
(466, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The series&rsquo; creative snap-fit, screwless, modularized design is a game-changer in the installation and maintenance of access gates. This feature makes the MARS PRO-S1000 Series easier to install and maintain, allowing for a faster setup process and reducing production lead time by up to 30%. The modular design also allows for quick upgrades, ensuring that the gate remains adaptable to evolving security needs without extensive rework.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1000-series/features/202501-243-6-xHWqc5njof.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.225782', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.227929', 243),
(467, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-B1000 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate</strong> is equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, significantly boosting its anti-tailgate performance. These sensors detect and prevent unauthorized access, ensuring that only authorized individuals can pass through the gate. By improving detection accuracy and response time, this advanced technology enhances both security and user experience, making it suitable for high-traffic areas that require quick and efficient access control.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1000-series/features/202501-244-7-T9JskJ2jTK.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.580953', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.583932', 244),
(468, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-B1000 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate </strong>is equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, significantly boosting its anti-tailgate performance. These sensors detect and prevent unauthorized access, ensuring that only authorized individuals can pass through the gate. By improving detection accuracy and response time, this advanced technology enhances both security and user experience, making it suitable for high-traffic areas that require quick and efficient access control.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1000-series/features/202501-244-6-2OsA7oPo9e.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.585483', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.588901', 244),
(469, '<p><strong><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Anti-Tailgating Performance</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MARS-B1200 Series incorporates up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, providing exceptional anti-tailgating performance. These sensors detect the presence of individuals as they pass through the gate and ensure that only one person can pass at a time. The system automatically alerts when an unauthorized second person attempts to follow. This feature is crucial for preventing unauthorized access and ensuring the safety of sensitive environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1200-series/features/202501-245-5-9eR4XHN5mI.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.758445', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.761566', 245),
(470, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Modular, Snap-Fit Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MARS-B1200 features a unique, modular, snap-fit design that eliminates the need for screws, simplifying both installation and maintenance. This innovative design allows for faster assembly and reduces production lead times by up to 30%. It also makes servicing the gate more straightforward, allowing for quick replacement of components when needed. This ease of maintenance helps reduce downtime and keeps the system operational with minimal disruption.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1200-series/features/202501-245-6-n9DmRIrxlG.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.763339', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.766055', 245),
(471, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-F1000 Series</strong> is equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors (Mars-Pro Series) that significantly enhance its anti-tailgate performance. This feature ensures that the gate can effectively detect any unauthorized attempts to follow an authorized person through the gate, improving overall security. These sensors allow for precise tracking and provide real-time feedback, ensuring that only one person passes through at a time. This anti-tailgate technology is especially beneficial in high-security areas such as offices, airports, and government buildings.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-f1000-series/features/202501-246-6-gUHitnUlxF.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.072488', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.076273', 246),
