(478, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Modular, Screwless Design for Easy Installation and Maintenance</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MARS PRO-F1200 Series is designed with a modular, screwless structure that simplifies both installation and maintenance. This feature reduces production lead time by up to 30%, making the setup process faster and more efficient. The snap-fit design allows components to be easily replaced or repaired without the need for specialized tools or extensive downtime. This innovation not only cuts costs but also ensures that the system remains operational with minimal disruption.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-f1200-series/features/202501-249-55-PP9j1f0lxY.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.173011', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.175569', 249),
(479, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS1000 Pro Series Tripod Turnstiles</strong> come with a robust design and a simple tripod mechanism that enhances security while maintaining an efficient flow of foot traffic. This feature ensures that only one person can pass at a time, reducing the risk of unauthorized access. Additionally, the units are made from high-quality materials, providing durability and resistance to tampering. This makes the TS1000 Pro Series suitable for a wide range of indoor applications, including office buildings, public facilities, and corporate environments. Whether used in high-traffic areas or locations with more limited access, these turnstiles offer a dependable solution.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts1000-pro-series/features/202501-250-66-fjom1GOMhX.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.033326', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.035866', 250),
(480, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> TS1000 Pro Series Tripod Turnstiles</strong> come with a robust design and a simple tripod mechanism that enhances security while maintaining an efficient flow of foot traffic. This feature ensures that only one person can pass at a time, reducing the risk of unauthorized access. Additionally, the units are made from high-quality materials, providing durability and resistance to tampering. This makes the TS1000 Pro Series suitable for a wide range of indoor applications, including office buildings, public facilities, and corporate environments. Whether used in high-traffic areas or locations with more limited access, these turnstiles offer a dependable solution.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts1000-pro-series/features/202501-250-77-9tl1ytI35H.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.037603', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.040686', 250),
(481, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TS2000 PRO Series Tripod Turnstile combines practicality with enhanced security features to protect your premises. Its robust construction makes it a durable choice for controlling access in high-traffic areas while maintaining smooth operation. The turnstile\'s tripod design minimizes space requirements, making it ideal for environments where space is at a premium. Whether you need a simple control mechanism or a more complex system, the TS2000 provides a scalable solution that meets various security standards.<br><br>Each model in the TS2000 PRO Series can be customized with different access control options. The TS2011 model incorporates RFID readers for fast and contactless entry, while the TS2022 goes a step further with fingerprint scanning for biometric verification. With these features, the TS2000 PRO Series ensures both security and convenience for employees, visitors, and other authorized individuals.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts2000-pro-series/features/202501-251-66-2DhrDkWJXs.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.751568', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.754224', 251),
(482, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TS2000 PRO Series Tripod Turnstile is designed for durability and long-term reliability. Its sturdy construction ensures that it can handle both high-traffic and low-traffic areas without compromising performance. The tripod design allows for smooth and efficient passage control while preventing unauthorized access or tailgating. Additionally, the turnstile is easy to maintain, with minimal upkeep required to keep it functioning at its best.<br><br>These features make the TS2000 ideal for busy environments where access control and security are top priorities. Whether you\'re outfitting an office building, a government facility, or a corporate campus, the TS2000 PRO Series provides a dependable, low-maintenance solution to meet your security needs.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts2000-pro-series/features/202501-251-77-ouSRekZ63d.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.756016', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.758910', 251),
(483, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZK-D1065 is equipped with 6 detection zones that provide precise and thorough screening of individuals. Each zone operates independently to detect metallic objects at various points on the body, ensuring that security personnel can pinpoint the location of any hidden items. This multi-zone detection system enhances the overall accuracy of the device and reduces the chance of missed threats, offering a higher level of protection in busy or crowded environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d1065/features/202501-252-55-xVGWPWGvvJ.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.168046', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.172266', 252),
(484, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZK-D1065 includes a 3.5&rdquo; LCD display that offers real-time information about the security screening process. The display shows important metrics such as the number of people passing through and the count of any alarms triggered, making it easy for security staff to monitor activity. This intuitive interface also provides clear alerts when a detection occurs, combining visual and auditory signals for immediate action. The display&rsquo;s user-friendly design makes it easy to operate and integrate into existing security systems.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d1065/features/202501-252-77-2l2O69rA4v.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.174321', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.177186', 252),
(485, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D2180</strong> Walk-Through Metal Detector offers 18 detection zones, each of which can be independently customized to adjust the sensitivity for various types of metal objects. This zoning system provides exceptional accuracy, allowing security teams to pinpoint exactly where a detected item is located. The 256 sensitivity levels further enhance the precision of the screening process, making it adaptable for a wide range of environments, from high-security government buildings to crowded event venues. The flexibility of these features ensures that users can tailor the system to meet specific security requirements.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d2180/features/202501-253-66-EF1neOLW95.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.452410', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.456230', 253),
(486, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D2180</strong> includes a comprehensive alarm system with synchronous sound and LED indicators to immediately alert security personnel of any potential threats. This dual-alarm system is highly effective in high-traffic areas, as it ensures that the alarm is both audible and visible to the staff monitoring the detector. Additionally, the device features people and alarm counting, which helps operators track the flow of individuals through the checkpoint and keep an accurate record of any alarms triggered. This combination of real-time tracking and immediate alerting makes the ZK-D2180 an invaluable tool for security operations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d2180/features/202501-253-77-YZ2E3QombD.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.459575', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.463399', 253),
(487, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZK-D3180 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> comes with 18 detection zones, allowing for precise and targeted screening of individuals. This multi-zone design enhances security by providing more accurate detection, reducing false alarms and ensuring that all areas of a person are screened thoroughly. Each zone can be independently adjusted for sensitivity, allowing operators to tailor the system to their specific security needs.<br><br>Additionally, the detector features a 7-inch LCD display that provides real-time status updates, including the number of people passing through and the number of alarms triggered. This functionality streamlines security operations and helps staff maintain an efficient flow of people while ensuring high-level security at all times.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180/features/202501-254-55-k7XhiU9IJc.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.224924', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.227822', 254),
(488, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D3180</strong> offers up to 500 adjustable sensitivity levels, providing users with the flexibility to customize the detection range based on the environment. Whether used in a busy airport or a secure government building, the detector can be fine-tuned to detect metal objects accurately at different thresholds, ensuring optimal security without unnecessary alerts. This adjustability makes it highly versatile, suitable for both low and high-security settings.<br><br>In addition to its sensitivity levels, the ZK-D3180 features a remote control that allows for easy operation from a distance, reducing the need for physical adjustments. This feature adds to the convenience of managing the system, especially in environments where access to the unit may be restricted or difficult.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180/features/202501-254-66-cqqi05Fvp9.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.229508', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.232421', 254),
(489, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Body Temperature Measurement</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>One of the standout features of the ZK-D3180S is its built-in body temperature measurement function. This function helps monitor passengers&rsquo; body temperatures at both the forehead and wrist, providing a simple yet effective way to detect potential health risks, such as high fever. With the ability to identify individuals with elevated temperatures, this device plays a critical role in preventing the spread of diseases in crowded or public areas. If a person\'s temperature exceeds the set threshold of 37.3&deg;C, the system raises an alarm to alert security personnel for immediate action.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180s-td/features/202501-255-66-E9TNAeKTHa.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.484373', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.487564', 255),
(490, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Detection Zones and 500 Sensitivity Levels</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZK-D3180S offers 18 detection zones, providing highly detailed and targeted scanning capabilities. With 500 adjustable sensitivity levels, the detector can be fine-tuned to meet specific security requirements, allowing for optimal performance in any environment. Whether detecting small metal objects or larger, more obvious metallic threats, the detector ensures that all potential security risks are identified. This flexibility makes it ideal for use in a wide range of settings, from airports to stadiums, offering both comprehensive coverage and precision.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180s-td/features/202501-255-44-XgsVkIambn.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.489564', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.492062', 255),
(491, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Sound &amp; Light Alarm Simultaneously</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZK-D100S Portable Metal Detector is equipped with both sound and light alarms that trigger simultaneously when it detects metal objects. This dual alarm system ensures that security personnel are promptly alerted, enhancing response times. The sound alarm is loud enough to be heard in busy environments, while the light alarm serves as a visual cue for additional clarity. Whether in noisy factories or crowded educational settings, this feature guarantees that no alerts are missed.<br><br>This dual alert system makes the ZK-D100S especially effective in high-traffic areas, where audible alarms alone may not be sufficient. It also ensures that the detector\'s alerts are noticeable from a distance, providing an extra layer of security for those monitoring entrances or exits.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d100s/features/202501-256-55-5knfSkAoOl.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:23:29.021643', '2025-01-27 01:23:29.025442', 256),
(492, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Compact &amp; Waterproof Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZK-D100S is designed to be both compact and durable, with dimensions of 410mm (L) x 85mm (W) x 45mm (H), making it easy to carry and store. Its lightweight structure allows it to be easily maneuvered in tight spaces or around crowded areas. Additionally, the detector features an IP31 waterproof rating, meaning it can be used in a variety of environmental conditions without worrying about damage from moisture or light rain.<br><br>The robust construction of the ZK-D100S ensures that it remains functional and reliable even in challenging work environments, whether indoors or outdoors. Its waterproof feature further extends its lifespan, making it a great investment for long-term security needs.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d100s/features/202501-256-77-9K6kuA25Ox.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:23:29.028401', '2025-01-27 01:23:29.032440', 256),
(493, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>TRUE-COLOR SCANNING IMAGE:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZKX5030C offers a true-color scanning image, providing an accurate and detailed representation of the scanned items inside baggage or parcels. This high-quality imaging capability allows operators to see a clear differentiation between materials, which is essential for detecting potential threats. The true-color feature enhances the scanning process, enabling operators to make more informed decisions and act faster. This innovative scanning technology ensures that no detail is overlooked, and the clear images help prevent false alarms, saving valuable time during security checks.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030c/features/202501-257-44-Mp5ppAlqzq.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.864773', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.867521', 257),
(494, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>ENERGY SAVING MODE:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZKX5030C X-ray scanner includes an energy-saving mode that automatically reduces power consumption when the device is idle. This feature is designed to promote sustainability and lower operational costs while maintaining the scanner&rsquo;s full functionality during active use. The energy-saving mode is activated when the system detects periods of inactivity, making the device more eco-friendly without compromising on performance. This feature is ideal for businesses and institutions looking to reduce their environmental footprint while maintaining the highest level of security and operational efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030c/features/202501-257-77-dWhTGPEnYb.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.869266', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.872180', 257),
(495, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX5030A </strong>features pseudo-color scanning images, enhancing visual clarity and aiding operators in identifying threats with ease. This advanced imaging technology converts scanned objects into a high-contrast, color-coded format, making it easier to distinguish between different materials. The clarity of the pseudo-color display significantly reduces the chances of missing potential threats, ensuring a higher level of security. Operators can quickly identify suspicious items, facilitating a more efficient and timely screening process. This feature improves the accuracy of decision-making and minimizes false positives in security assessments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030a/features/202501-258-66-JM0ep2gnsD.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.739314', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.742184', 258),
(496, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX5030A </strong>is designed for energy efficiency, featuring an energy-saving mode that optimizes power consumption during use. This functionality helps to reduce overall energy costs, making the scanner a more sustainable option for businesses with high-volume screening needs. By automatically adjusting power levels, the scanner operates efficiently without sacrificing performance. This energy-saving feature also extends the device\'s lifespan by reducing wear and tear on internal components, ultimately saving costs for the operator while supporting eco-friendly initiatives.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030a/features/202501-258-77-O1FAVoQGfs.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.744166', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.746627', 258),
(497, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Steel Penetration Up to 35mm</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZKX6040 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner offers impressive steel penetration of up to 35mm, allowing for deep inspection of complex objects. This advanced feature ensures that even densely packed or reinforced items can be thoroughly analyzed, providing greater reliability in identifying potential threats. Whether dealing with heavy-duty luggage or suspicious packages, the ZKX6040&rsquo;s high penetration capacity guarantees accurate detection of both organic and inorganic substances. This feature makes it an ideal choice for environments that require comprehensive security checks, such as airports, government facilities, and transportation hubs.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6040/features/202501-259-66-pz5NDe5Coq.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.532146', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.535032', 259),
(498, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Display of Cluttered Bag Images</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>One of the standout features of the ZKX6040 is its ability to display detailed images of cluttered bags. This advanced imaging capability allows security personnel to identify and assess items even when the contents of the bag are disorganized or packed in a way that might hide suspicious objects. By highlighting key areas of concern, the scanner enables operators to quickly spot anomalies, improving overall efficiency and effectiveness during the screening process. This feature is crucial in high-volume security checkpoints where speed and accuracy are essential to maintaining safety.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6040/features/202501-259-77-Va1U3Nd9NU.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.538962', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.541678', 259),
(499, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550A </strong>features pseudo-color scanning images, which enhance the clarity of scanned images by providing a spectrum of colors to represent different materials. This innovation helps operators easily distinguish between different types of objects within the luggage, making the process of identifying potential threats more intuitive and effective. The use of pseudo-color scanning improves detection accuracy, especially when looking for items that could be concealed within complex materials. This system also provides enhanced contrast, making suspicious items more visible against the background of everyday objects.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550a/features/202501-260-44-CKqmRhemQW.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.924276', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.927072', 260),
(500, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">One of the standout features of the <strong>ZKX6550A </strong>is its innovative fingerprint identification system, which increases the security of the scanning process. By requiring biometric authentication, this system ensures that only authorized personnel can operate the machine, preventing unauthorized access and misuse. This added layer of security is crucial in high-risk environments, where confidentiality and the integrity of the screening process are paramount. The fingerprint identification system not only secures the machine but also contributes to a more efficient workflow, as operators can quickly and easily authenticate their identity without the need for passwords.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550a/features/202501-260-33-ZVjdpWGfqt.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.928876', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.931071', 260),
(501, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>TRUE-COLOR SCANNING IMAGE</strong><br><br>The ZKX6550 Dual Energy X-ray Scanner offers true-color scanning, providing operators with highly accurate and detailed imaging of scanned items. This innovative feature ensures that materials with varying densities are clearly visible, making it easier to detect concealed threats such as explosives or weapons. By offering true-to-life color representation, the system minimizes the chances of false alarms, ensuring that operators can make more informed decisions during the scanning process. The true-color imaging also reduces the potential for operator fatigue, as it allows for a faster, more accurate evaluation of the contents.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550/features/202501-261-44-YTkvOaohBX.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.407126', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.410240', 261),
(502, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> INNOVATIVE FINGERPRINT IDENTIFICATION</strong><br><br>The ZKX6550 is equipped with an innovative fingerprint identification system, enhancing security and ensuring that only authorized personnel can operate the scanner. This biometric feature adds an extra layer of protection, preventing unauthorized access and ensuring that only trained and certified operators can access the system. The fingerprint identification system improves overall operational security, reducing the risk of human error or intentional tampering. It also allows for efficient and secure operator verification, streamlining the user login process. By integrating biometric technology, the ZKX6550 ensures a higher level of security in high-risk environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550/features/202501-261-77-2hYhgOQyed.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.412070', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.415308', 261),
(503, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">&nbsp;The <strong>ZKX6550D\'s </strong>dual-view technology allows for both horizontal and vertical scanning images through two independent generators. This gives operators a comprehensive view of the items being scanned, significantly improving detection accuracy. By offering different perspectives of an object, the system helps identify hidden threats that may be missed with a single view. This feature ensures more thorough and precise security screening, particularly useful when assessing complex or overlapping items. Dual-view technology also supports faster decision-making, allowing security personnel to act swiftly in high-pressure situations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550d/features/202501-262-66-RT9qoOMRUM.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.620828', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.624434', 262),
(504, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The bi-directional scanning feature of the <strong>ZKX6550D </strong>adds flexibility and enhances the inspection process by allowing items to be scanned from multiple angles. This is particularly beneficial in detecting contraband or hidden threats within carry-on baggage or other types of cargo. By offering a broader scanning range, the system improves the chances of spotting concealed items that might be missed by traditional scanning methods. Additionally, bi-directional scanning helps reduce the risk of delays in high-traffic environments, ensuring that security operations run smoothly and efficiently. This makes the ZKX6550D an ideal choice for areas requiring fast, reliable security screening.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550d/features/202501-262-77-DL6iJus7mR.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.626569', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.629477', 262),
(505, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Adjustable Belt Speed</strong><br><br>The ZKX10080 X-ray scanner comes with an adjustable belt speed feature, allowing operators to control the flow of items based on the specific inspection requirements. This feature improves efficiency and helps in reducing the time spent on scanning while maintaining a high level of accuracy. With the ability to adjust speed, operators can adapt the system to handle different volumes of items and various security needs, making the ZKX10080 a flexible and versatile tool in any security setting. Whether scanning large parcels or smaller bags, this feature ensures optimal performance at all times.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx10080/features/202501-263-77-kGC8AoPTZm.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.306259', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.308812', 263),
(506, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Foldable Conveyor Design</strong><br><br>The ZKX10080&rsquo;s foldable conveyor design is another unique feature that provides significant logistical advantages. This design allows the conveyor to be collapsed when not in use, reducing the overall size of the unit and making it easier to store and transport. By minimizing the footprint, organizations can save on transportation costs, especially when moving multiple units. This space-saving feature is perfect for environments with limited storage space and allows for more efficient use of resources, making the ZKX10080 both practical and cost-effective.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx10080/features/202501-263-44-It7kYzbzPc.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.310362', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.312486', 263),
(507, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong> Adjustable Belt Speed</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZKX100100 X-ray scanner features an adjustable belt speed, allowing operators to customize the flow rate of items being screened. This feature ensures that the scanner can handle a variety of scanning tasks, from high-volume environments to more specific, slower checks. Adjusting the belt speed improves efficiency and ensures that each item is thoroughly examined without unnecessary delay. This level of flexibility makes the ZKX100100 an ideal solution for environments where different types of luggage and parcels are regularly processed.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx100100/features/202501-264-66-U8uFPZUSne.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.133503', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.136335', 264),
(508, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Biometric Identification for Operators</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The ZKX100100 comes equipped with an innovative biometric identification system, providing enhanced security for both the scanner and the operator. This feature prevents unauthorized access by requiring the operator to authenticate using biometric data, such as fingerprints. This not only ensures that only authorized personnel can operate the system but also eliminates the risk of password-related issues, such as forgotten passwords. By integrating this security feature, the ZKX100100 offers peace of mind, knowing that the system is being operated securely and by the appropriate personnel.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx100100/features/202501-264-77-ykrTeVsGxP.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.137967', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.140376', 264),
(509, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Steel Penetration<br>The BLADE6040 X-ray Scanner offers exceptional steel penetration capabilities, allowing it to detect hidden threats behind up to 35mm of steel (with typical penetration reaching 40mm). This feature ensures that even well-concealed objects, such as weapons or explosives hidden within metallic containers, can be accurately identified. With high penetration, security personnel are equipped to handle a wide variety of threat scenarios, making the BLADE6040 an ideal solution for high-security environments where the detection of hidden dangers is crucial.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-blade6040/features/202501-265-44-2stxuG0ZI3.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.756788', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.759400', 265);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_keyfeature` (`id`, `key_feature`, `key_feature_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(510, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Steel Penetration<br>The BLADE6040 X-ray Scanner offers exceptional steel penetration capabilities, allowing it to detect hidden threats behind up to 35mm of steel (with typical penetration reaching 40mm). This feature ensures that even well-concealed objects, such as weapons or explosives hidden within metallic containers, can be accurately identified. With high penetration, security personnel are equipped to handle a wide variety of threat scenarios, making the BLADE6040 an ideal solution for high-security environments where the detection of hidden dangers is crucial.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-blade6040/features/202501-265-33-BEFuTJ2FRi.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.761053', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.763809', 265),
(511, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The die-casting aluminum alloy motor of the <strong>PB4000 Series </strong>is designed to withstand the test of time, offering high reliability and minimal maintenance. This feature reduces the need for frequent repairs and servicing, providing users with a cost-effective solution for long-term vehicle access management. Additionally, the robust motor ensures smooth operation even in heavy-duty environments, making the PB4000 Series an excellent choice for both residential and commercial installations. Its strong build guarantees performance and reduces downtime, enhancing operational efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-pb4000-series/features/202501-266-66-41WSURjnOY.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.185857', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.188658', 266),
(512, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>PB4000 Series </strong>comes with a range of boom options, including the telescopic PB4060 6M boom and the LED-enhanced PB4030-LED model, allowing users to choose the perfect configuration for their specific needs. The telescopic boom design provides a space-saving solution for areas with limited room, while the folding boom option offers flexibility for smaller entrances. The PB4030-LED boom incorporates integrated LED lights, ensuring optimal visibility and safety, especially in low-light conditions. These versatile options provide adaptable solutions for various vehicle access points.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-pb4000-series/features/202501-266-77-TQXPu4D76W.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.190410', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.193325', 266),
(513, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UHF 10 Series Long Distance Card Reader </strong>boasts an impressive reading range of up to 12 meters, allowing for highly efficient access control systems. This extended range significantly reduces the need for users to approach the reader closely, streamlining workflows in environments where high traffic or large distances are involved. Ideal for managing personnel, goods, and vehicles, this feature provides convenience and increases operational efficiency while ensuring that the system remains secure and functional over long distances. The system&rsquo;s ability to read at such a long range makes it particularly suitable for areas such as large warehouses, parking lots, and facilities with high throughput.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-uhf-10-series/features/202501-267-55-9qUzD3PwTY.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.215619', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.218817', 267),
(514, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UHF 10 Series</strong> is designed with an IP66-rated weatherproof casing, ensuring durability and reliable operation in diverse environmental conditions. This rugged design protects the card reader from exposure to dust, water, and extreme weather conditions, making it perfect for both indoor and outdoor applications. The waterproof and dustproof features help to extend the lifespan of the device, while maintaining its consistent performance in harsh climates. Whether used in a construction site, vehicle parking lot, or outdoor facility, the UHF 10 Series stands up to tough environmental factors, providing long-lasting and secure access control.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-uhf-10-series/features/202501-267-66-j57ZF7iA3e.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.220360', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.222559', 267),
(515, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UR20RW-F </strong>supports both UHF tags and UHF cards, providing businesses with the flexibility to use a variety of tracking and identification systems. This feature ensures compatibility with a wide range of EPC global UHF Class1 Gen 2 and ISO 18000-6C compliant tags and cards. Whether for asset management, inventory control, or access management, the device can handle a variety of UHF applications, making it ideal for industries that rely on UHF technology.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ur20rw-f/features/202501-268-66-qFBm5FcPom.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.137068', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.139744', 268),
(516, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Operating within the frequency range of 902MHz to 928MHz, the <strong>UR20RW-F</strong> ensures stable and efficient performance in multiple regions worldwide. The device offers a valid reading distance ranging from 0 to 5 cm, which is perfect for applications where precise, short-range scans are essential. Its high-frequency capabilities enable fast data reading and writing, ensuring that your operations remain efficient and up to speed in demanding environments. The reliable connectivity and flexible range make it an indispensable tool for modern businesses looking to implement UHF technology.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ur20rw-f/features/202501-268-77-nxZLTH7RnR.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.141455', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.143773', 268),
(517, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">One of the standout features of the<strong> VR10 PRO Parking Barrier Radar</strong> is its adjustable detection range, which can be customized from 1 meter to 6 meters. This flexibility allows users to optimize the radar for a wide range of environments, from narrow parking spaces to expansive parking lots. By fine-tuning the detection distance, the system ensures that only vehicles or pedestrians within the defined area are detected, reducing the likelihood of false alarms and unnecessary gate closures. This feature makes it ideal for locations with varying traffic flow and space configurations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-vr10-pro/features/202501-269-66-nZXUB2Ofag.PNG', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.510257', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.513614', 269),
(518, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> VR10 PRO Parking Barrier Radar</strong> is equipped with an easy-to-use app that allows for quick and efficient parameter settings. This app simplifies the installation and configuration process, enabling users to adjust detection distances and other settings with ease. The user-friendly interface ensures that the radar system can be customized without the need for complex tools or expert installation. By offering simple app-based control, the VR10 PRO ensures a smooth and hassle-free setup, making it accessible for both technical and non-technical users.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-vr10-pro/features/202501-269-77-ndZMRK135e.PNG', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.515870', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.519095', 269),
(519, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Superior Image Quality &amp; Advanced WDR</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX Project Series Bullet Network Cameras are equipped with a 2MP resolution and a 1/2.8\" SONY STARVIS CMOS sensor, delivering high-definition video with exceptional clarity. True WDR technology ensures well-balanced images in challenging lighting conditions, effectively managing bright and dark areas within the frame. With a noise reduction of &gt;70dB SNR, these cameras provide crisp visuals with minimal distortion. Whether monitoring sunlit streets or shadowed alleys, these cameras capture every detail with precision. Their adaptive streaming technology further enhances performance by optimizing bandwidth and storage without compromising quality.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-project-series-bullet-network-cameras/features/202501-270-66-6461ODDFke.PNG', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.613635', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.616913', 270),
(520, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><strong>Rugged Durability &amp; Cyber-Secure Design</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed for tough outdoor conditions, the MATRIX Project Series Bullet Cameras feature a robust metal body with IK10 impact resistance and an IP67 weatherproof rating. They can withstand extreme weather, dust, and vandalism, making them perfect for demanding security applications. The advanced infrared system extends visibility up to 50m in low-light environments, ensuring reliable surveillance at night. Additionally, these cameras are NDAA-compliant and incorporate cutting-edge cybersecurity measures to protect sensitive data from unauthorized access. With certifications including BIS, CE, FCC, RoHS, UL, and NEMA 4X, they meet global security and safety standards, providing a trusted solution for modern surveillance needs.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-project-series-bullet-network-cameras/features/202501-270-77-gN3niSnsX3.PNG', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.619215', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.622233', 270);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(1, 'Hub 2 Plus', '2024-11-21 06:01:12.776366', '2024-11-21 06:01:12.776569', 5, 1, 41, 'hub-2-plus', '<p>The <strong>Ajax Hub 2 Plus</strong> is the central control panel of the Ajax security system, designed to manage and communicate with all connected devices. It supports a wide range of wireless sensors and accessories, ensuring seamless operation across the entire security network. With its advanced GSM and Wi-Fi connectivity, the Hub 2 Plus offers reliable, real-time communication, enabling users to monitor and control their security system remotely via the Ajax app. It features encrypted data transmission for maximum security and can be easily integrated with other smart home devices. Compact and powerful, the Hub 2 Plus provides enhanced coverage and reliability, making it the heart of any Ajax alarm system.</p>'),
(2, 'SF5030A ', '2024-11-25 07:45:46.915119', '2024-11-25 07:45:46.915369', 10, 21, 90, 'sf5030a', '<p><strong>X-ray Baggage Scanner SF5030A by Uniqscan</strong> is a high-performance security screening solution designed to provide detailed, reliable, and efficient baggage inspection for a variety of settings, including airports, train stations, and government buildings. Equipped with advanced imaging technology, the SF5030A delivers clear, high-resolution X-ray images, allowing security personnel to quickly identify concealed threats or prohibited items within bags and packages. Its user-friendly interface and intuitive controls ensure ease of operation, while the system&rsquo;s automatic detection capabilities enhance threat identification, improving security and reducing inspection times. With its robust construction and customizable features, the SF5030A X-ray Baggage Scanner offers a perfect blend of security, efficiency, and reliability, making it an essential tool for maintaining safety in high-traffic environments.</p>'),
(3, 'SF5030C PRO', '2024-11-25 08:01:37.212793', '2024-11-25 08:01:37.212954', 10, 21, 90, 'sf5030c-pro', '<p><strong>X-ray Baggage Scanner SF5030C PRO by Uniqscan</strong> is a cutting-edge security solution designed for fast, reliable, and high-resolution baggage inspection in various high-security environments, such as airports, government buildings, and transportation hubs. Featuring advanced X-ray imaging technology, the SF5030C PRO delivers crystal-clear images that help security personnel identify potential threats or contraband with precision. Its enhanced detection capabilities, including automatic threat detection and high penetration power, ensure thorough inspection of both large and small items. With a user-friendly interface, customizable settings, and robust construction, the SF5030C PRO provides an efficient and scalable security screening solution, improving operational efficiency while maintaining the highest standards of safety. Perfect for environments requiring fast-paced security checks, this X-ray Baggage Scanner is a vital tool for protecting public spaces and assets.</p>'),
(4, 'SF6550', '2024-11-25 08:17:25.485815', '2024-11-25 08:17:25.486321', 10, 21, 90, 'sf6550', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"5b3f4726-86a8-4f7b-9e7c-b98a51df0f8c\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<p><strong>X-ray Baggage Scanner SF6550</strong> is a high-performance security screening solution designed for efficient, precise, and reliable baggage inspection in a variety of high-security environments such as airports, transit hubs, and government buildings. Equipped with advanced dual-energy X-ray imaging technology, the SF6550 provides detailed, high-resolution images that enable security personnel to detect hidden threats, contraband, or prohibited items with exceptional clarity. Its robust design, combined with high penetration power, ensures effective scanning of a wide range of baggage sizes, from carry-on luggage to large parcels. The SF6550 is also equipped with intuitive software features, including automatic threat detection, enhancing operational efficiency and reducing inspection time. With its reliable performance and ease of use, the SF6550 X-ray Baggage Scanner is an ideal solution for improving security and streamlining the screening process in busy, high-traffic areas.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
(5, 'SF6550D', '2024-11-25 08:33:01.229941', '2024-11-25 08:33:01.230109', 10, 21, 90, 'sf6550d', '<p>The <strong><em>X-ray Baggage Scanner SF6550D</em></strong> is a top-tier security screening solution designed for high-security environments, including airports, government buildings, and transportation hubs. Featuring advanced dual-energy X-ray imaging technology, the SF6550D delivers exceptional image clarity and high penetration power, allowing security personnel to detect concealed threats, contraband, and other prohibited items within baggage and packages with ease. Its large tunnel size accommodates a wide range of baggage, from carry-on luggage to bulky items, ensuring thorough inspection. The SF6550D is equipped with user-friendly software that includes automatic threat detection, enhancing both efficiency and accuracy while reducing inspection times. With its robust construction and cutting-edge features, the SF6550D X-ray Baggage Scanner offers a reliable, scalable security solution that improves operational effectiveness and ensures the safety of high-traffic, public areas.</p>'),
(6, 'SF8065', '2024-11-25 09:09:21.918792', '2025-01-15 02:14:43.031256', 10, 21, 90, 'sf8065', '<p>The UNIQSAN SF8065 X-ray Baggage Scanner is a state-of-the-art security solution designed to meet the rigorous demands of public safety in high-traffic areas such as airports, train stations, and government buildings. This advanced scanner is renowned for its precision and efficiency, ensuring that potential threats are identified swiftly and accurately. With its robust design and cutting-edge technology, the SF8065 enhances security operations by providing clear, detailed images that facilitate thorough inspections.</p>\n<p>Equipped with a high-resolution 19-inch color LCD display, the SF8065 offers superior image quality, allowing operators to distinguish between different materials easily. Its ability to identify organic, inorganic, and mixed substances in distinct colors ensures that security personnel can make quick, informed decisions. The scanner\'s multi-energy imaging technology, along with features such as super image enhancement and brightness control, make it a versatile tool for any security setup.</p>'),
(7, 'SF8065D', '2024-11-26 06:49:23.013726', '2024-11-26 06:49:23.013962', 10, 21, 90, 'sf8065d', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"5916be34-b4da-40e6-80cd-17b735ba3c3c\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<p>The X-ray Baggage Scanner SF8065D is a cutting-edge security screening solution designed to enhance safety at airports, government buildings, and high-security facilities. Equipped with dual energy X-ray technology, the SF8065D offers high-resolution imaging that allows security personnel to easily identify threats such as weapons, explosives, and illegal items hidden within baggage. Featuring a spacious tunnel size of 800mm x 650mm, this scanner efficiently processes various bag sizes while ensuring quick and accurate results. With advanced image processing capabilities and an intuitive user interface, the SF8065D ensures optimal performance, making it an ideal choice for organizations prioritizing security and efficiency.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><span class=\"overflow-hidden text-clip whitespace-nowrap text-sm\">4o mini</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
(8, 'Super Scanner V Hand-Held Metal Detector', '2024-11-26 07:09:07.782994', '2024-11-26 07:09:07.783145', 7, 43, 61, 'super-scanner-v-hand-held-metal-detector', '<p>The <strong>Super Scanner Hand-Held Metal Detector</strong> is a high-performance security tool designed for quick and reliable detection of metal objects in a variety of environments, including airports, events, and public spaces. Compact and lightweight, this portable device is ideal for security personnel to scan individuals for concealed weapons, knives, or other metallic threats. Offering precise sensitivity and audible or vibrating alarms for easy detection, the Super Scanner ensures efficient screening without delay. With a durable design and easy-to-use features, it provides enhanced safety while maintaining a streamlined security process. Whether for high-security areas or general crowd management, the Super Scanner Hand-Held Metal Detector delivers dependable performance every time.</p>'),
(9, 'PD 6500', '2024-11-26 08:14:43.475590', '2024-11-26 08:14:43.475755', 7, 43, 61, 'pd-6500', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"9406c3ef-6654-4f1e-a3ec-d84e5c58780b\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<p>The <strong>PD 6500i Walk Through Metal Detector</strong> is a top-of-the-line security solution designed to deliver fast and accurate metal detection in high-traffic environments such as airports, stadiums, and government buildings. Featuring advanced technology and superior sensitivity, the PD 6500i can detect even the smallest metal objects, including weapons, knives, and electronics, ensuring a high level of security. With multiple detection zones, customizable settings, and a user-friendly interface, this walk-through metal detector offers enhanced accuracy and minimized false alarms. Its durable design and seamless integration into security systems make the PD 6500i the ideal choice for organizations looking to maintain safety while optimizing efficiency.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\">\n<div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 flex\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center\"><button class=\"rounded-lg text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\" aria-label=\"Copy\" data-testid=\"copy-turn-action-button\"></button>\n<div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
