(12, 'PB4000 Boom Barrier ', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.673876', '2024-11-27 05:56:38.674099', 8, 24, 70, 'pb4000-boom-barrier', '<p>The ZKTeco PB4000 Boom Barrier is a high-performance access control solution designed for vehicle entry and exit management. Ideal for parking lots, gated communities, and industrial facilities, the PB4000 features a robust and reliable barrier arm system, ensuring smooth traffic flow and enhanced security. Equipped with advanced technology, the PB4000 offers fast operation, durability, and easy integration with existing access control systems. Its sleek design and weather-resistant materials make it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. With customizable features and high-speed performance, the ZKTeco PB4000 Boom Barrier is a trusted choice for efficient traffic management and secure access control.</p>'),
(13, 'ZKTeco CMP200 Boom Barrier', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.236068', '2024-11-27 06:16:14.236254', 8, 24, 70, 'zkteco-cmp200-boom-barrier', '<p>The <strong>ZKTeco CMP200 Boom Barrie</strong>r is a cutting-edge access control solution designed to provide seamless traffic management and secure vehicle entry and exit. Perfect for parking lots, commercial complexes, and gated facilities, the CMP200 offers fast, reliable operation with a robust design for long-lasting performance. Featuring a powerful motor and advanced control technology, this boom barrier ensures smooth and efficient barrier arm movement, even in high-traffic environments. Its durable, weather-resistant construction makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, while its easy integration with other access control systems enhances security and convenience. The ZKTeco CMP200 Boom Barrier is the ideal choice for businesses looking for a reliable, high-speed traffic control solution.</p>'),
(15, 'BGM1000 Boom Barrier ', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.479429', '2024-11-27 07:02:02.479805', 8, 24, 70, 'bgm1000-boom-barrier', '<p>The <strong>ZKTeco BGM1000 Boom Barrier </strong>is a high-performance traffic control solution designed for efficient vehicle access management in high-traffic areas. Featuring advanced technology, the BGM1000 offers fast and reliable barrier arm operation, ensuring smooth traffic flow while enhancing security. Its durable construction and weather-resistant design make it ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations, including parking lots, gated communities, and industrial facilities. The ZKTeco BGM1000 integrates seamlessly with other access control systems, providing flexible options for vehicle entry and exit management. With its robust motor and sleek design, the BGM1000 is the perfect choice for businesses and organizations seeking a reliable, high-speed boom barrier solution.</p>'),
(16, 'Avtech Room Alert 32S', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.874154', '2024-12-02 05:47:08.874366', 12, 18, 110, 'avtech-room-alert-32s', '<p>The <strong>Avtech Room Alert 32S</strong> is a state-of-the-art environmental monitoring solution designed to ensure the optimal performance of critical IT infrastructure. This compact device monitors temperature, humidity, water leaks, and power conditions, providing real-time alerts to prevent potential system failures. With its advanced sensors and customizable notification features, the Room Alert 32S helps businesses maintain uptime and protect their data centers, server rooms, and other sensitive environments. Compatible with a wide range of equipment and easily integrated into existing monitoring systems, the Avtech Room Alert 32S delivers reliable, proactive monitoring to safeguard your valuable assets and prevent costly downtime.</p>'),
(17, 'LX50 Fingerprint and RFID Time-Keeping Devices', '2025-01-02 05:49:57.417198', '2025-01-02 05:55:56.021875', 4, 11, 33, 'lx50-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-devices', '<p>The <strong>LX50 Fingerprint and RFID Time-Keeping Device</strong> is a comprehensive solution for businesses seeking to streamline their time and attendance management. &nbsp;With Self-Service Reporting (SSR) stored directly on the device, small chain stores can easily access and manage employee time records. &nbsp;Data privacy is ensured through redaction capabilities in Excel format. &nbsp;The LX50 is equipped with USB Host and USB Client capabilities for seamless data transfer and integration. &nbsp;Its user-friendly design, featuring a 2.8-inch TFT display and smart shape, enhances ease of use. &nbsp;The vivid interface provides real-time feedback on fingerprint image quality and verification results, ensuring accurate and reliable time tracking. &nbsp;The LX50 is the perfect solution for businesses of all sizes, offering a range of features to simplify your timekeeping and improve efficiency.</p>'),
(18, 'K14-ID Fingerprint and RFID Time Keeping Device', '2025-01-02 06:31:36.618052', '2025-01-03 01:18:36.363725', 4, 11, 33, 'k14-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-time-keeping-device', '<p>The <strong>K14-ID Fingerprint and RFID Time Keeping Device </strong>is a advance time and attendance solution designed for businesses of all sizes. This innovative device seamlessly integrates fingerprint and RFID technologies, delivering unparalleled accuracy and efficiency in employee time tracking. <span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\">Powered by advanced algorithms, the K14-ID ensures reliable and precise fingerprint recognition with exceptional matching speeds.<sup class=\"superscript visible\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\">&nbsp;<!----></sup></span>Its user-friendly interface and robust construction make it an ideal choice for streamlining daily operations and enhancing productivity within your organization.<span class=\"button-container hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"> &nbsp; </span></p>'),
(19, 'IN02A-ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control', '2025-01-02 07:08:40.482244', '2025-01-03 01:19:07.553557', 4, 11, 33, 'in02a-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control', '<p><span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\">The <strong>IN02A-ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control</strong> is a compact and versatile 3-inch Fingerprint Time Attendance &amp; Access Control Terminal designed to streamline your workforce management.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></span> <span class=\"citation-1 recitation citation-end-1\">This user-friendly device boasts a range of essential features, including Wi-Fi and GPRS connectivity for seamless data transfer and remote management.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></span> <span class=\"citation-2 recitation citation-end-2\">Additionally, it incorporates a built-in battery for uninterrupted operation, even during power outages.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"3\"><!----></sup></span> <span class=\"citation-3 recitation citation-end-3\">Furthermore, the IN02A-ID features intuitive keypads that simplify interaction and enhance the overall user experience</span></p>'),
(20, 'F7-C ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control', '2025-01-02 07:57:27.082364', '2025-01-03 01:19:57.441757', 4, 11, 33, 'f7-c-id-fingerprint-and-rfid-devices-with-access-control', '<p><span class=\"citation-0 recitation citation-end-0\">The <strong>ZKTeco F7-C ID Fingerprint and RFID Devices with Access Control</strong> is a innovative IP-based fingerprint terminal designed to enhance security and streamline access control.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></span> <span class=\"citation-1 recitation citation-end-1\">This versatile device seamlessly integrates into various environments, offering both standalone and network operation modes.<sup class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></span> With its sleek and compact design, the F7-C is easily adaptable to diverse installation scenarios. Engineered with user-friendliness in mind, the F7-C boasts a simple and intuitive interface. Its robust construction ensures durability and reliable performance in demanding conditions. Whether deployed for small businesses, residential complexes, or large enterprises, the F7-C provides a dependable and efficient solution for managing access control needs.&nbsp;</p>'),
(31, 'Hub Protect', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.824646', '2025-01-03 06:51:11.824869', 5, 1, 41, 'hub-protect', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f3430a0f-123f-4e26-b949-1fc3361fe323\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o-mini\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<p>The Ajax Hub Protect is a powerful, user-friendly security solution designed to keep your property safe. It serves as the central control unit for the Ajax alarm system, offering seamless integration with other Ajax devices. Equipped with an advanced communication protocol, the Hub Protect ensures quick and reliable alerts in the event of a security breach. Whether you\'re at home or on the go, it provides remote access and monitoring via a mobile app. Its sleek, compact design makes it easy to install in any location without compromising on performance. Ideal for both residential and commercial properties, the Ajax Hub Protect delivers peace of mind with state-of-the-art security features.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),
(32, 'Motion Protect Plus', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.436394', '2025-01-06 01:56:41.436662', 5, 1, 41, 'motion-protect-plus', '<p><strong>Motion Protect Plus</strong> is a highly advanced motion detection system designed to provide top-tier security for both homes and businesses. Equipped with dual-sensor technology, it combines PIR and microwave sensors to accurately detect movement while minimizing false alarms. With a sleek, modern design, it easily integrates into smart home systems, offering real-time alerts and remote monitoring via a user-friendly app. The system is built for durability, with energy-efficient features and long-lasting battery life for continuous protection. Its wide coverage range ensures every corner of your property is safeguarded. Trust Motion Protect Plus to deliver reliable, precise motion detection and keep your space secure.</p>'),
(33, 'Combi Protect', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.807657', '2025-01-06 02:02:12.807827', 5, 1, 42, 'Combi-Protect', '<p><strong>Combi Protect</strong> is an advanced security solution designed to provide reliable protection for your home or business. Featuring a combination of motion detection and glass break sensors, it offers comprehensive coverage against a wide range of potential threats. With its high-tech dual-sensor system, Combi Protect Plus can accurately differentiate between actual intrusions and harmless movements. The device integrates seamlessly with smart home systems, allowing you to monitor activity remotely and receive instant alerts via your smartphone. Its sleek, easy-to-install design ensures that it fits perfectly into any environment, enhancing both security and aesthetics. Trust Combi Protect Plus for ultimate peace of mind, knowing your property is safeguarded 24/7.</p>'),
(34, 'MultiBio 800 ID', '2025-01-06 02:47:49.863383', '2025-01-10 05:11:34.924424', 4, 11, 33, 'multibio-800-id', '<p><strong>MultiBio 800 ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control</strong></p>\n<p>The MultiBio 800 ID is a cutting-edge multi-verification device that integrates multiple security technologies to provide the highest level of access control. Designed for both residential and commercial use, it supports a range of biometric verification methods, including fingerprint, facial recognition, and RFID, ensuring robust security for any facility. With this innovative device, you can ensure that only authorized personnel gain access to your premises, offering unparalleled peace of mind.</p>\n<p>Equipped with advanced biometric algorithms, the MultiBio 800 ID ensures fast and accurate identification, allowing for seamless access without compromising security. Its user-friendly interface and quick response time make it ideal for busy environments, such as offices, factories, and residential complexes. Whether you are verifying identity through a fingerprint scan or facial recognition, this device provides reliable and efficient performance.</p>\n<p>The MultiBio 800 ID integrates smoothly with existing access control systems, offering seamless connectivity and easy setup. Whether you\'re managing a single entry point or an entire building, the device can be configured to meet your specific needs. It also features real-time monitoring, allowing administrators to track who enters and exits the premises, providing valuable data for security audits and event tracking.</p>\n<p>For added convenience, the MultiBio 800 ID allows for remote access management, enabling administrators to update user permissions and monitor activity from anywhere using an intuitive web interface. This functionality ensures you can control access to your property at all times, even when you\'re not physically on-site. With customizable access levels, the system adapts to the security needs of any business or organization.</p>\n<p>Built with durability in mind, the MultiBio 800 ID is engineered to withstand demanding environments. Whether it\'s exposed to extreme weather conditions or high-traffic areas, this device is designed for long-lasting performance. It also supports multi-language interfaces, making it a versatile solution for businesses and organizations with international staff.</p>\n<p>For the highest level of security, efficiency, and convenience, the MultiBio 800 ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control is the ideal solution. Whether you\'re protecting a sensitive area or simply looking to enhance your existing security infrastructure, this advanced device ensures that access is granted only to those who have been verified, offering ultimate protection for your property.</p>'),
(35, 'VF380-ID', '2025-01-06 02:55:11.720174', '2025-01-06 03:02:29.156065', 4, 11, 33, 'vf380-id', '<p><strong>VF380-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control: Unmatched Security for Your Property</strong></p>\n<p>The VF380-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control is an advanced security solution designed to enhance safety and streamline access management for residential and commercial spaces. Combining multiple verification methods, including fingerprint recognition, RFID, and password authentication, it provides an adaptable and secure approach to controlling entry points. With its versatile design, the VF380-ID ensures only authorized individuals can access your premises, giving you peace of mind 24/7.</p>\n<p>Featuring fast and accurate biometric identification, the VF380-ID ensures a smooth and efficient access process. Its multi-verification capabilities allow for added security by verifying users through different methods, reducing the risk of unauthorized entry. Whether it\'s a fingerprint scan, RFID card, or a passcode, the device offers a highly secure and reliable solution for any environment, from offices to high-security areas.</p>\n<p>The VF380-ID integrates effortlessly with existing access control systems, offering a seamless setup and user-friendly experience. Administrators can easily configure the device to suit the specific security needs of their property, whether that includes limiting access to certain areas or setting time-based permissions. With real-time monitoring features, you can track entry logs and maintain full control over who enters your facility at all times.</p>\n<p>Designed for efficiency, the VF380-ID allows remote access management, enabling administrators to modify user access rights and monitor activity from anywhere. This remote functionality is ideal for busy businesses or organizations that require constant monitoring and control over access points. With its customizable settings and flexible configuration options, it provides a tailored security solution for various types of establishments.</p>\n<p>Durability is key with the VF380-ID, as it is built to perform in both indoor and outdoor environments. Whether exposed to harsh weather conditions or high traffic, this device maintains top-tier functionality. Its sleek, modern design ensures that it blends seamlessly into any environment, offering both security and aesthetic appeal. The device also supports multiple languages, making it a versatile solution for businesses with international teams.</p>\n<p>For enhanced security, efficiency, and ease of use, the VF380-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control is the ultimate choice. Whether you\'re securing sensitive areas, managing employee access, or simply upgrading your security infrastructure, the VF380-ID ensures a reliable and comprehensive access control system for your property. Trust this advanced solution for the protection of your most valuable assets.</p>'),
(36, 'MB460-ID', '2025-01-06 03:15:46.910766', '2025-01-06 03:15:46.910934', 4, 11, 33, 'mb460-id', '<p><strong>MB460-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control: Ultimate Security Solution</strong></p>\n<p>The MB460-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control offers a sophisticated, all-in-one security solution designed to enhance the safety and efficiency of both residential and commercial properties. With its multi-layered verification options&mdash;including fingerprint scanning, facial recognition, and RFID technology&mdash;the MB460-ID ensures that only authorized individuals gain access to your premises. This comprehensive security approach provides peace of mind, knowing that your property is protected by the latest in biometric and smart technology.</p>\n<p>The MB460-ID features advanced biometric algorithms for quick and accurate identification, making it an ideal choice for busy environments. Whether it&rsquo;s a high-traffic office or a secure facility, the device supports seamless and fast access with minimal wait times. This multi-verification system reduces the risk of unauthorized entry, ensuring that your property remains safe while improving the user experience for those authorized to enter.</p>\n<p>Integration with existing security and access control systems is made simple with the MB460-ID. It is designed to work smoothly with your current setup, offering easy configuration and control of user permissions. The device supports real-time monitoring, providing administrators with valuable data on who enters and exits your facility. This feature is critical for security audits, compliance purposes, and maintaining a high level of accountability.</p>\n<p>The MB460-ID is designed for remote management, enabling administrators to update user access rights and monitor activity from anywhere. The intuitive web interface makes it easy to adjust settings, track usage, and maintain full control of the system, even when you are off-site. With customizable access levels and time-based permissions, the device offers a flexible and tailored security solution for any organization or property type.</p>\n<p>Built to withstand various environmental conditions, the MB460-ID is a durable, reliable access control device. It can operate effectively in both indoor and outdoor settings, maintaining its functionality in high-traffic areas or harsh weather conditions. Additionally, the sleek and modern design ensures that the device blends well into any space, while its multi-language support makes it a versatile choice for global businesses and diverse user groups.</p>\n<p>For those seeking a top-tier security solution, the MB460-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control is the perfect choice. With its combination of biometric technology, easy integration, and remote management features, it delivers high-level security and efficient access control, making it the ideal solution for securing your property and managing access to sensitive areas.</p>'),
(37, 'MB160-ID', '2025-01-06 03:25:23.062379', '2025-01-06 03:25:23.062545', 4, 11, 33, 'mb160-id', '<p><strong>MB160-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control: Advanced Security Technology</strong></p>\n<p>The MB160-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control offers a highly secure and flexible solution for controlling access to your property. Featuring a combination of fingerprint recognition, RFID, and password authentication, this device ensures that only authorized individuals can enter restricted areas. Perfect for both residential and commercial use, the MB160-ID enhances the safety of your premises with state-of-the-art biometric verification technologies.</p>\n<p>With its fast and accurate multi-verification methods, the MB160-ID streamlines the access process without compromising security. By integrating multiple forms of authentication, the device reduces the risk of unauthorized access and ensures only verified personnel are granted entry. Whether used for an office, warehouse, or residential building, the MB160-ID guarantees a secure and efficient access control system.</p>\n<p>The MB160-ID is designed to seamlessly integrate with existing access control systems, making setup and configuration simple and straightforward. Administrators can customize user permissions and monitor access in real-time, ensuring full control over who enters and exits your premises. This device supports advanced features like time-based permissions and event tracking, providing valuable insights into security activity.</p>\n<p>With remote access management capabilities, the MB160-ID allows administrators to update settings, review access logs, and adjust user permissions from anywhere, using an intuitive web interface. This flexibility is especially useful for large organizations or businesses with multiple locations, where maintaining security across various sites is essential. The device ensures that security protocols can be managed efficiently and remotely.</p>\n<p>Built for reliability, the MB160-ID is designed to withstand various environmental conditions. Its robust construction ensures long-lasting performance, whether it is used indoors or exposed to outdoor elements. The sleek, compact design fits seamlessly into any environment, offering both security and aesthetic appeal. Additionally, it supports multiple languages, making it an ideal solution for businesses with diverse, global workforces.</p>\n<p>For those seeking a reliable, high-performance access control system, the MB160-ID Multi-Verification Device is the perfect solution. Combining cutting-edge biometric technology, ease of use, and seamless integration, it provides a comprehensive security solution that meets the needs of any property. Trust the MB160-ID for robust, multi-layered security that you can rely on to protect your assets and manage access with ease.</p>'),
(38, 'UA860 ID', '2025-01-06 03:36:48.447159', '2025-01-06 03:36:48.447350', 4, 11, 33, 'ua860-id', '<p><strong>UA860-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control: Advanced Security for Your Facility</strong></p>\n<p>The UA860-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control offers a next-generation security solution for both residential and commercial properties. Featuring multiple authentication methods&mdash;such as fingerprint recognition, RFID, and password entry&mdash;this device ensures that only authorized individuals can access secure areas. With its versatile multi-verification system, the UA860-ID enhances security and streamlines access management, providing peace of mind to property owners and businesses alike.</p>\n<p>With fast and accurate biometric identification, the UA860-ID ensures quick access without compromising on security. The device offers multiple authentication options, allowing users to choose the most convenient method for their needs while ensuring unauthorized individuals are prevented from entering restricted areas. Its intuitive design makes it easy to use, making it perfect for offices, factories, and high-security environments.</p>\n<p>The UA860-ID seamlessly integrates with existing access control systems, offering a simple and effective way to enhance your security infrastructure. Whether you&rsquo;re managing a single entry point or an entire facility, the device can be customized to meet your security requirements. Administrators can easily configure user access rights and set time-based permissions, providing enhanced control over who enters and exits the premises.</p>\n<p>Designed for convenience, the UA860-ID offers remote access management, allowing administrators to monitor and modify user permissions from anywhere. This remote functionality is perfect for organizations with multiple locations or businesses with high demands for monitoring and control. The device also supports real-time access logs, making it easier to track and audit entry activity, which is essential for both security and compliance.</p>\n<p>Built with durability and reliability in mind, the UA860-ID performs in a wide range of environments. Its rugged design ensures it can withstand both indoor and outdoor conditions, maintaining optimal performance even in high-traffic or extreme weather settings. The device&rsquo;s modern, sleek appearance also ensures it fits seamlessly into any space, offering both functional security and aesthetic appeal.</p>\n<p>For ultimate access control and enhanced security, the UA860-ID Multi-Verification Device with Access Control is the ideal choice. With its powerful combination of biometric technologies, seamless integration, and remote management capabilities, it ensures your property is secured efficiently and effectively. Trust the UA860-ID to provide reliable, scalable security for your business or home.</p>'),
(39, 'MB560-VL ID WIFI', '2025-01-06 03:48:18.908612', '2025-01-06 03:48:18.909548', 4, 11, 33, 'mb560-vl-id-wifi', '<p>The MB560-VL ID WiFi Visible Light Device is an advanced time attendance system combined with basic access control functionality, offering an all-in-one solution for modern workplaces. Equipped with visible light facial recognition technology, it ensures fast and accurate identification for employees and visitors. This innovative device streamlines attendance tracking and enhances security, making it ideal for businesses seeking efficiency and reliability.</p>\n<p>With its state-of-the-art facial recognition algorithm, the MB560-VL ID can accurately identify individuals even in dynamic lighting conditions. The visible light technology ensures higher precision compared to traditional infrared-based systems, while its dual-verification options, including RFID and passcodes, add an extra layer of security. This versatility makes it suitable for various industries, from offices to factories and educational institutions.</p>\n<p>The device is WiFi-enabled, allowing seamless connectivity and remote management. Administrators can effortlessly track attendance records, manage user permissions, and generate detailed reports via a user-friendly web interface. Its wireless capability simplifies installation and eliminates the need for complex wiring, ensuring hassle-free deployment in any environment.</p>\n<p>Designed for practicality, the MB560-VL ID integrates time attendance and basic access control into a single system. It enables businesses to monitor employee punctuality, calculate work hours, and manage shifts efficiently while restricting unauthorized access to sensitive areas. This dual-purpose functionality helps companies optimize operations and maintain a secure work environment.</p>\n<p>The MB560-VL ID boasts a modern and sleek design that complements any workplace setting. Its durable build ensures reliable performance in high-traffic environments, while its multilingual interface supports diverse teams and global operations. The intuitive touchscreen display enhances user interaction, making it simple for employees to clock in and out.</p>\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re looking to streamline time tracking or add basic access control to your facility, the MB560-VL ID WiFi Visible Light Device is the perfect solution. Combining cutting-edge technology, remote accessibility, and user-friendly features, it offers unparalleled convenience and security for businesses of all sizes. Invest in the MB560-VL ID to enhance your workplace&rsquo;s efficiency and safety.</p>'),
(40, 'IMOU Cue 2-D', '2025-01-08 05:32:04.397068', '2025-01-08 07:52:28.759512', 3, 3, 22, 'imou-cue-2-d', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Cue 2-D is a high-performance indoor security camera designed for enhanced home surveillance. Equipped with a 2.0 Mpx 1/2.9\" CMOS sensor, it delivers crystal-clear 1080p video at 20 fps. The camera features a 124&deg; wide-angle lens, ensuring comprehensive coverage of your space. With built-in infrared LEDs, it offers clear night vision up to 10 meters. The IMOU Cue 2-D supports Wi-Fi connectivity, allowing for seamless remote access and real-time monitoring through its user-friendly app. It also features H.264 video compression for efficient storage and streaming. The integrated microphone and speaker facilitate two-way audio communication, adding an extra layer of security. Additionally, it includes a microSD card slot, supporting up to 256 GB of storage for video recordings. Compact and easy to install, the IMOU Cue 2-D is an ideal solution for modern home security needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(41, ' IMOU CUE 2C-D', '2025-01-08 05:54:04.963963', '2025-01-08 07:52:01.592469', 3, 3, 22, 'imou-cue-2c-d', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Cue 2C-D is a compact and intelligent security camera designed to keep your home safe with ease. Equipped with a 1/2.8&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it delivers sharp 1080p HD video for clear monitoring. The camera features a 3.6mm fixed lens offering an impressive 108&deg; field of view, ensuring wide coverage. With night vision capability up to 10 meters, it keeps your premises secure even in low-light conditions. The Cue 2C-D supports Wi-Fi connectivity, making it easy to set up and monitor via the Imou Life App on both iOS and Android devices. Its H.265 video compression ensures efficient storage use without compromising video quality. The built-in microphone allows for real-time audio monitoring. ONVIF compatibility ensures seamless integration with other security systems. The camera\'s 16x digital zoom allows for close-up views of key areas. Perfect for both indoor and outdoor use, the IMOU Cue 2C-D provides reliable and comprehensive security.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(42, 'IMOU Ranger 2-D', '2025-01-08 06:16:42.923814', '2025-01-08 07:51:34.479820', 3, 3, 24, 'imou-ranger-2-d', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2-D is a versatile, high-performance security camera designed for both home and business use. It features a 2.0 MP sensor resolution with a 1/2.9\" CMOS sensor, delivering crisp 1080p video at 20 fps. Equipped with infrared LEDs, it ensures clear night vision up to 10 meters. The fixed lens offers an 86&deg; horizontal, 45&deg; vertical, and 105&deg; diagonal field of view. With built-in Wi-Fi and a 100 Mbps RJ-45 port, connectivity is seamless. The camera supports H.264 video compression for efficient storage, with a microSD slot accommodating up to 256 GB. Integrated audio features include a built-in microphone and speaker for two-way communication. Compact and sleek, the Ranger 2-D offers advanced surveillance capabilities, making it an ideal choice for secure monitoring.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(43, ' IMOU Ranger 2 4MP-D', '2025-01-08 06:29:12.674014', '2025-01-08 07:50:57.440521', 3, 3, 24, 'imou-ranger-2-4mp-d', '<p>The IMOU Ranger 2 4MP-D is a versatile security camera offering high-resolution 4MP (2560 x 1440) video quality. Equipped with a 1/2.7&rdquo; 4 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it captures clear and detailed footage. Its 3.6mm fixed lens and wide field of view ensure comprehensive coverage. The camera\'s 355&deg; pan and -5~80&deg; tilt capabilities allow for extensive area monitoring. Night vision up to 10 meters ensures security even in low light. Connectivity is seamless with Wi-Fi support (IEEE802.11b/g/n) for up to 50 meters in open fields. The IMOU App is available on both iOS and Android, enabling remote access and control. ONVIF compliance ensures compatibility with other devices. The camera\'s compact design fits seamlessly into various environments. It\'s an ideal solution for both home and small business security.</p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(44, ' IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D', '2025-01-08 06:38:16.034148', '2025-01-08 07:50:17.886039', 3, 3, 22, 'imou-ranger-2c-4mp-d', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D is a cutting-edge smart security camera designed to enhance home and office security with its high-definition 4-megapixel resolution and advanced night vision capabilities. Featuring a 1/2.7&rdquo; 4MP Progressive CMOS sensor, this camera delivers crystal-clear video quality, even in low-light conditions up to a distance of 10 meters. Its 3.6mm fixed lens offers a wide 92&deg; horizontal field of view, while the 355&deg; pan and -5~80&deg; tilt functions provide comprehensive coverage. Connectivity is seamless with Wi-Fi IEEE802.11b/g/n support and compatibility with the Imou App for iOS and Android, allowing for remote monitoring. The camera supports H.265/H.264 video compression, ensuring efficient storage and smooth streaming. Equipped with two-way audio, users can communicate directly through the camera. The IMOU Ranger 2C also features an 8x digital zoom for detailed close-ups and ONVIF compatibility for integration with other security systems. It&rsquo;s an all-in-one solution for modern security needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(45, ' IMOU Turret', '2025-01-08 06:45:54.736269', '2025-01-08 07:49:39.631729', 3, 3, 22, 'imou-turret', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret is a high-performance security camera designed for optimal surveillance and monitoring. Equipped with a 1/2.7&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it captures crystal-clear 1080p video. Its night vision capability extends up to 30 meters, ensuring reliable security around the clock. The camera offers multiple lens options (2.8mm, 3.6mm, 6mm) for various field-of-view preferences. With dual internal antennas and a 100Mbps Ethernet port, it provides robust connectivity through Wi-Fi or wired network. Featuring advanced H.265/H.264 video compression, it delivers smooth footage with efficient storage use. The built-in mic, speaker, and 110dB siren enhance communication and deterrence. The IMOU Turret is compatible with iOS and Android through the imou app, offering convenient remote access and control.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(46, ' IMOU Turret SE', '2025-01-08 06:57:27.288051', '2025-01-08 07:49:02.170918', 3, 3, 22, 'imou-turret-se', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret SE is a high-performance security camera designed to enhance home and business surveillance. With a 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it delivers crystal-clear 1080p resolution video, ensuring every detail is captured. The camera features an impressive night vision range of up to 30 meters, allowing for reliable monitoring even in complete darkness. Its fixed lens options (2.8mm and 3.6mm) offer varying fields of view to suit different surveillance needs. Equipped with dual antenna Wi-Fi and ONVIF support, it ensures seamless connectivity and integration. The IMOU Turret SE also boasts advanced video compression technology (H.265/H.264), an 8x digital zoom, and a built-in microphone for audio recording. Compatible with both iOS and Android via the Imou App, it provides easy access to live feeds and recordings. The camera\'s sturdy build and reliable performance make it an ideal choice for comprehensive security coverage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(47, 'Turret SE 4MP', '2025-01-08 07:14:19.663820', '2025-01-08 07:47:22.920520', 3, 3, 22, 'turret-se-4mp', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret SE 4MP is a high-performance security camera designed to provide superior surveillance with its 4MP resolution, delivering crystal-clear video. Equipped with a 1/2.8&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it offers enhanced image quality and detail. The camera supports night vision up to 30 meters, ensuring round-the-clock security. With a choice of 2.8mm or 3.6mm fixed lenses, it offers flexible field of view options. Dual antenna Wi-Fi connectivity and ONVIF compliance ensure seamless integration into existing networks. The IMOU App for iOS and Android offers easy remote access and management. Video is compressed using H.265/H.264 for efficient storage and streaming. A built-in microphone adds audio surveillance capabilities. This camera is an ideal choice for both residential and commercial security needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(48, 'HONEYWELL HBL2R1', '2025-01-08 07:46:12.177878', '2025-01-09 07:50:14.556010', 3, 5, 26, 'honeywell-hbl2r1', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is an advanced high-definition security camera designed to deliver exceptional performance for surveillance needs. Equipped with a 1080p real-time live view, this camera ensures crystal-clear visuals, providing a sharp, detailed image for various applications. Featuring a 1/2.7\" CMOS progressive scan, the HBL2R1 offers excellent image quality even in low light conditions, making it perfect for both day and night use. With its minimum illumination of 0 Lux (IR on), this camera guarantees visibility even in complete darkness. The camera also supports TDN (IR-Cut), AGC, and DWDR for enhanced image clarity in challenging lighting conditions. The 3.6mm lens provides an optimal field of view for detailed monitoring. It has an impressive IR distance of up to 20 meters, ensuring consistent image quality over a wide area. Designed with 12VDC power support, it integrates easily into existing security systems. The AHD/CVBS output allows compatibility with a wide range of surveillance equipment. Ideal for both residential and commercial installations, the HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is a robust, versatile camera that delivers reliable security.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(49, 'HONEYWELL HED3PR3', '2025-01-08 07:56:18.221251', '2025-01-10 03:50:58.415418', 3, 5, 22, 'honeywell-hed3pr3', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HED3PR3 is a high-performance security camera designed for reliable surveillance in both indoor and outdoor environments. Equipped with advanced IR LEDs, it offers exceptional night vision with a range of up to 30 meters. The camera features Smart IR technology to ensure consistent and even IR distribution for clear images in low-light conditions. Its IP66-rated waterproof housing guarantees durability and protection against harsh weather conditions. With a 2.8mm F2.1 fixed lens, it provides a wide field of view, ensuring comprehensive coverage of monitored areas. The HED3PR3 is equipped with motion detection capabilities and camera tamper detection to improve security and provide customizable alarm notifications. Whether it\'s day or night, this camera delivers reliable performance with a clear and crisp image. It\'s perfect for home, business, and industrial installations, offering peace of mind with every use. The camera can be easily configured, making it an excellent choice for both novice and professional users. HONEYWELL\'s HED3PR3 provides a smart solution for those looking for high-quality video surveillance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(50, ' HONEYWELL HBD3PR1', '2025-01-08 07:59:37.211738', '2025-01-10 03:49:26.150796', 3, 5, 22, 'honeywell-hbd3pr1', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBD3PR1 is a high-performance security camera that delivers clear and reliable surveillance footage for both residential and commercial use. With a 2304 x 1296 resolution, it ensures crisp, detailed images at 20 fps, even in low-light environments. Featuring infrared (IR) LEDs, this camera provides night vision up to 100 feet, making it suitable for 24/7 monitoring. The camera comes equipped with a 3.6mm fixed lens and an 81&deg; horizontal field of view, ensuring a broad and clear perspective of your property. Its RJ45 Ethernet connection with PoE (Power over Ethernet) simplifies installation by delivering both power and data over a single cable. Onvif compliance ensures seamless integration with other security systems. The camera is also equipped with an IR cut filter, enhancing its ability to capture accurate color images in varying lighting conditions. Compatible with the HonView Touch app for both iOS and Android, it allows for convenient remote monitoring. The IP66 rating ensures that it can withstand tough outdoor conditions, offering durability and weatherproofing. Whether for home or business use, the Honeywell HBD3PR1 is a reliable and advanced solution for your surveillance needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(51, 'HONEYWELL HBW4PR1 ', '2025-01-08 08:03:58.773689', '2025-01-10 03:47:12.031130', 3, 5, 22, 'honeywell-hbw4pr1', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBW4PR1 is a high-performance surveillance camera designed for exceptional image clarity and reliability in various lighting conditions. It features a 2 MP progressive scan imager with a 3.6 mm fixed lens for clear, detailed video capture. With true day/night functionality, including an IR-cut filter, the HBW4PR1 ensures reliable performance in both day and night settings. Its wide dynamic range of up to 120 dB helps enhance image quality in challenging lighting situations. The camera excels in low-light environments, providing color images down to 0.01 lux and complete darkness with IR LEDs on, offering up to 130 ft (40 m) of IR illumination.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The HBW4PR1 supports H.264 Main Profile compression and triple stream capabilities, making it a versatile solution for high-quality video surveillance. It can support up to 20 connections simultaneously, offering flexibility for various security setups. The camera features corridor mode, making it ideal for monitoring narrow spaces like hallways. With PoE and 12 VDC support, it is easy to integrate into existing systems, while the plug-and-play compatibility with Honeywell Performance Series Embedded NVRs simplifies installation. The weatherproof housing, rated at IP66, ensures durability and protection against harsh weather conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(52, 'HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3', '2025-01-08 08:08:42.508550', '2025-01-10 03:44:24.878876', 3, 5, 22, 'honeywell-hew4prw3', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 is a high-performance IP security camera designed to provide clear and detailed surveillance in various environments. Equipped with a 1/2.7\" 2 MP or 1/3\" 4 MP progressive scan imager, this camera offers excellent image quality. It features a fixed lens in either 3.6 mm or 2.8 mm for versatile viewing angles. With true day/night functionality and an IR-cut filter, this camera ensures clear vision in all lighting conditions. It provides wide dynamic range (WDR) up to 120 dB, enhancing visibility in both bright and dark areas. The HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 excels in low-light conditions, capturing footage down to 0.01 lux in color or 0 lux with IR LEDs activated. It supports up to 130 feet (40 meters) of IR illumination, ensuring clear video even in complete darkness. Offering H.264 Main Profile compression and triple stream support, the camera ensures efficient and reliable video streaming. It supports up to 20 connections, making it a robust choice for large security systems. Its weatherproof housing with an IP66 rating guarantees protection against harsh environments, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor use.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(53, 'HIKVISION E-HWIB', '2025-01-08 08:14:50.445590', '2025-01-09 02:08:47.941585', 3, 2, 21, 'hikvision-e-hwib', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION E-HWIB is a cutting-edge surveillance camera designed to provide superior security for both residential and commercial properties. With advanced image clarity and smart features, this device ensures round-the-clock protection. It boasts high-definition video capture, motion detection, and night vision capabilities. The E-HWIB is weather-resistant, making it ideal for outdoor installations. Easy to install and integrate with existing security systems, it offers a user-friendly interface and remote monitoring through a dedicated app. Its sleek design blends seamlessly with any environment, ensuring both functionality and aesthetics. The camera\'s AI-powered analytics enhance security by providing real-time alerts. Its robust construction and reliable performance make it a preferred choice for many. With HIKVISION\'s commitment to innovation, the E-HWIB redefines security standards.</p>'),
(54, 'HIKVISION E-HWID', '2025-01-08 08:17:11.979662', '2025-01-09 02:12:49.100369', 3, 2, 29, 'hikvision-e-hwid', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION E-HWID is an advanced electronic hardware identification device designed to enhance security and streamline authentication processes. It leverages cutting-edge technology to provide reliable, high-speed identification and access control for various applications. Its robust design ensures durability and performance in both indoor and outdoor environments. The device integrates seamlessly with existing security systems, offering a versatile solution for businesses and organizations. Equipped with multiple interfaces, it supports flexible connectivity options. The HIKVISION E-HWID is ideal for sectors requiring stringent security measures, including corporate offices, government buildings, and industrial facilities. Its user-friendly interface and easy installation process make it accessible for both small and large-scale deployments. Additionally, the device is designed to be energy-efficient, ensuring minimal operational costs. With HIKVISION\'s commitment to innovation and quality, the E-HWID represents a reliable and future-proof investment in security technology.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(55, 'HIKVISION E-HWIT', '2025-01-08 08:20:07.450886', '2025-01-09 02:16:00.075866', 3, 2, 21, 'hikvision-e-hwit', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION E-HWIT is a cutting-edge surveillance solution designed to deliver exceptional security and monitoring capabilities. Engineered with advanced technology, it offers high-definition video quality, robust storage options, and seamless integration with existing security systems. This product is ideal for both residential and commercial settings, ensuring reliable performance in various environments. Its intuitive interface and user-friendly design make it accessible to users of all technical levels. With features like motion detection, remote access, and real-time alerts, the HIKVISION E-HWIT enhances safety and operational efficiency. It also supports a wide range of devices, allowing for flexible deployment and scalability. The durable build ensures long-term reliability and minimal maintenance. Equipped with smart analytics, it provides valuable insights to enhance security measures. HIKVISION E-HWIT stands out as a versatile and comprehensive solution for modern surveillance needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(56, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0E-I', '2025-01-08 08:23:07.284916', '2025-01-09 02:19:57.910237', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0e-i', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0E-I is a high-performance 2 MP bullet network camera designed for enhanced security and surveillance. It features a robust build, superior image quality, and advanced infrared night vision. The camera is equipped with a 2.8mm fixed lens, delivering crystal-clear images even in low-light conditions. Its IP67-rated weatherproof housing makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. With support for H.265+ video compression, it reduces bandwidth and storage requirements without compromising quality. The camera offers a wide dynamic range (WDR) of 120 dB for improved visibility in high-contrast environments. Easy to install and integrate with various security systems, the HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0E-I is an ideal solution for small to medium-sized businesses. It supports motion detection, intrusion detection, and line crossing detection for proactive security measures. This camera ensures reliable and continuous surveillance with its advanced features and durable design.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(57, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IU', '2025-01-08 08:28:53.645995', '2025-01-09 02:24:01.596249', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iu', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IU is a high-performance network bullet camera designed for reliable security surveillance. Equipped with a 2MP sensor, it captures crisp, high-resolution images even in low-light conditions, thanks to its advanced infrared (IR) technology. Its compact design makes it ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations, offering versatility for various security needs. The camera supports H.265+ compression, reducing bandwidth and storage requirements without compromising image quality. It features a built-in microphone for audio recording, enhancing the monitoring capabilities. With IP67 weatherproofing, it withstands harsh environmental conditions. The DS-2CD1023G0-IU also supports motion detection and line crossing detection, providing intelligent alerts. Easy to install and configure, it integrates seamlessly with existing security systems. This camera is perfect for small to medium-sized businesses looking to enhance their security infrastructure.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(58, ' HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) ', '2025-01-08 08:34:00.612868', '2025-01-09 02:31:12.054258', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iuf-c', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) is a high-performance network bullet camera designed for robust security surveillance. With a 2MP resolution, it delivers clear and detailed images, even in low-light conditions, thanks to its advanced infrared night vision technology. This camera supports intelligent video analytics, making it ideal for both residential and commercial security applications. Its IP67-rated weatherproof design ensures reliable operation in various environmental conditions. The compact and durable construction allows for easy installation and maintenance. Featuring H.265+ compression, it significantly reduces bandwidth and storage requirements. The DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) integrates seamlessly with other HIKVISION products, providing a comprehensive security solution. Equipped with a built-in microphone, it captures high-quality audio, enhancing surveillance capabilities. This camera is perfect for users looking for a reliable, cost-effective security solution.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(59, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IU ', '2025-01-08 08:38:43.835472', '2025-01-09 02:37:31.910055', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iu', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IU is a high-performance, compact network camera designed for superior surveillance and security needs. Featuring a 2MP resolution, it delivers crystal-clear video quality for various monitoring applications. With its built-in microphone, the camera captures high-quality audio alongside video, providing a more complete security solution. The DS-2CD1323G0-IU is equipped with a wide dynamic range (WDR) for enhanced performance in challenging lighting conditions, ensuring clear footage even in backlit environments. This camera supports H.265+ compression technology, offering optimized bandwidth and storage efficiency while maintaining high-quality video. Its 4mm lens offers a wide field of view, ideal for both indoor and outdoor settings. The camera also features a built-in PoE (Power over Ethernet) functionality for simpler installation and reduced cabling requirements. With a rugged design, it is suitable for both residential and commercial applications. Integrated with the Hik-Connect app, the camera allows for seamless remote monitoring from anywhere. The DS-2CD1323G0-IU is a versatile and reliable solution for anyone looking to enhance their security system.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(60, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1123G0-I ', '2025-01-09 01:38:24.449921', '2025-01-09 02:41:15.219855', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1123g0-i', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1123G0-I is a 2MP fixed bullet network camera designed to provide high-quality surveillance with advanced features. Featuring a 1/2.8\" Progressive Scan CMOS sensor, it delivers clear images and excellent video quality in both bright and low-light conditions. With a 4mm fixed lens, the camera provides a wide field of view, ensuring comprehensive coverage of surveillance areas. Equipped with a robust IR range of up to 30 meters, it ensures effective monitoring even in the dark. The camera supports H.265+ compression, providing high-efficiency video encoding that reduces storage requirements without sacrificing image quality. It also supports the latest security protocols, including HTTPS, for secure video transmission. The HIKVISION DS-2CD1123G0-I is suitable for a wide range of indoor and outdoor security applications, such as in commercial, residential, and public areas. Its IP67-rated weatherproof design ensures durability in harsh weather conditions. The camera&rsquo;s compact size and discreet design make it easy to install while maintaining a low profile. With motion detection, alarm support, and easy integration with other security systems, the DS-2CD1123G0-I is an ideal choice for reliable video surveillance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(61, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1143G0-I', '2025-01-09 01:43:10.004523', '2025-01-09 02:44:20.650541', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1143g0-i', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1143G0-I is a high-performance 2.0 MP IP security camera designed to deliver clear and reliable surveillance footage. Equipped with a 1/3\" progressive scan CMOS sensor, it captures high-quality images with up to 2.0 megapixel resolution. This camera features a 2.8mm fixed focal lens, allowing for wide-angle views, and an impressive IR range of up to 30 meters for effective night vision. With dual stream capabilities, the DS-2CD1143G0-I ensures smooth video transmission without compromising quality. The camera also supports Digital WDR and 3D DNR for enhanced image clarity in challenging lighting conditions. Its Power over Ethernet (PoE) compatibility ensures easy installation, reducing the need for additional power cables. Built to withstand harsh outdoor conditions, the DS-2CD1143G0-I is rated IP67 for water and dust resistance and IK10 for impact resistance. It supports H.265+, H.265, H.264+, and H.264 compression formats for efficient video storage. This camera is ideal for a wide range of applications, offering security and peace of mind for both residential and commercial properties. Its robust performance, combined with advanced features, makes it a versatile solution for any surveillance setup.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(63, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IUF', '2025-01-09 02:00:21.633206', '2025-01-09 02:46:28.043022', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iuf', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IUF is a high-performance 2MP network camera, designed to provide reliable and high-quality surveillance in various environments. Featuring a 1/2.8\" progressive scan CMOS sensor, it captures crystal-clear images at 1920x1080 resolution at 30fps. The camera is equipped with a 2.8mm fixed focal lens that delivers wide-angle views, ensuring maximum coverage. With an infrared (IR) range of up to 30 meters, the DS-2CD1323G0-IUF can provide clear video footage even in low-light conditions. Additionally, the camera supports dual-streaming, allowing for efficient bandwidth management. Digital WDR and 3D DNR technologies help deliver clear images in challenging lighting environments, reducing noise and distortion. Its PoE (Power over Ethernet) capability ensures easy installation and reduces the need for additional power cables. Built-in microphone functionality enhances its surveillance capabilities by enabling audio recording. The DS-2CD1323G0-IUF is IP67 rated, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations. With advanced compression standards, including H.265+, H.265, H.264+, and H.264, this camera offers efficient storage and bandwidth usage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(64, ' HIKVISION DS-2CD2021G1-I(B)', '2025-01-09 02:53:01.286829', '2025-01-09 02:55:21.089975', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd2021g1-i-b', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) is a high-performance 2MP IP camera designed for reliable surveillance in various environments. Equipped with a 1/3\" Progressive CMOS sensor, it ensures clear and detailed image capture, even in low light. The camera features ICR for enhanced infrared sensitivity, with an impressive IR range of up to 30 meters, allowing for clear vision in complete darkness. It supports resolutions of 1920x1080 at 25fps(P) or 30fps(N), providing smooth video playback. Offering flexible video compression formats including H.265+, H.265, H.264, and MJPEG, it guarantees high-quality footage while reducing bandwidth usage. The DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) also features 3D DNR (Digital Noise Reduction) and BLC (Backlight Compensation) for optimal image quality under varying lighting conditions. Powered by either DC12V or PoE, it ensures hassle-free installation in diverse setups. The camera integrates with HIK-Connect cloud service for easy remote monitoring and management. With its durable design and robust features, this camera is a great addition to any security system. Ideal for both indoor and outdoor use, it offers a cost-effective yet high-quality solution for your surveillance needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(65, 'HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I', '2025-01-09 03:00:00.118122', '2025-01-09 03:01:08.424418', 3, 2, 22, 'hikvision-ds-2cd2043g2-i', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I is a high-performance 4 MP bullet camera designed for surveillance in both indoor and outdoor environments. Equipped with cutting-edge 120 dB WDR technology, it offers clear imaging even under challenging backlighting conditions. This camera utilizes H.265+ compression technology to deliver high-quality footage with reduced storage requirements. Built with IP67 rating, it is water and dust-resistant, ensuring reliable performance in various weather conditions. The camera also includes advanced deep learning algorithms that enhance its ability to classify human and vehicle targets accurately. Its compact and durable design makes it ideal for a range of security applications, from residential to commercial use. Offering enhanced image quality and a robust set of features, this camera provides an excellent surveillance solution. The HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I supports remote monitoring through mobile apps and web browsers, allowing users to access live footage anytime, anywhere. Its user-friendly interface ensures ease of installation and setup. Trust the HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I for reliable security and high-definition surveillance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(66, 'DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-Z', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.183289', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.183706', 3, 4, 22, 'dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-z', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-Z is a high-performance Starlight HDCVI IR Eyeball Camera designed for superior video surveillance in various lighting conditions. It features a 2.7-12mm motorized lens and supports up to 1080P resolution at 30fps. With HD and SD output switchable options, this camera provides flexibility for different security needs. Its advanced Starlight technology ensures clear images in low-light environments. The camera is equipped with Smart IR technology, offering an impressive maximum IR length of 60m for enhanced night vision. Built to withstand harsh weather, the DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-Z boasts an IP67 rating for dust and water resistance. Operating on DC12V, this camera is a reliable and efficient solution for both indoor and outdoor surveillance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(67, 'DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.445383', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.445547', 3, 4, 22, 'dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-za', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA is a high-performance security camera designed for superior surveillance in various lighting conditions. Equipped with Starlight technology, it delivers exceptional image quality even in low-light environments. It supports up to 30 frames per second at 1080P resolution, ensuring smooth and detailed video capture. With a motorized 2.7-12mm lens, users can easily adjust the focus remotely for optimal coverage. The built-in microphone provides audio capture to complement video surveillance. It features a switchable HD and SD output, offering flexible compatibility with different systems. The Smart IR function ensures clear night vision up to 60 meters. Its robust IP67 rating makes it suitable for outdoor use, offering resistance to dust and water. The camera operates efficiently on a DC12V power supply. Ideal for both residential and commercial use, the DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA is a reliable solution for comprehensive security monitoring.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(68, 'DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.916506', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.916670', 3, 4, 22, 'dahua-dh-hfw2241t-za', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA is a high-performance surveillance camera designed to deliver exceptional video quality and reliability in various environments. Equipped with Starlight technology, it offers superior low-light performance, ensuring clear images even in dim conditions. The camera supports 120dB True WDR and 3DNR, providing balanced and noise-free visuals. With a maximum resolution of 1080P at 30fps, it delivers crisp and detailed footage. The HD/SD switchable feature allows flexible output options to suit different needs. Integrated audio input and a built-in mic enhance its monitoring capabilities. Its motorized 2.7-13.5mm lens ensures versatile focus adjustments. The Smart IR technology extends IR coverage up to 80 meters for night-time surveillance. Built to withstand harsh environments, it boasts an IP67 rating and operates efficiently with a DC12V&plusmn;30% power supply. The DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA is an ideal choice for comprehensive and reliable security monitoring.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(69, 'DAHUA DH-HFW1230T', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.930901', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.931069', 3, 4, 22, 'dahua-dh-hfw1230t', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1230T is a high-performance security camera designed for reliable and clear surveillance. Featuring advanced Starlight technology, it delivers superior low-light performance, capturing crisp images even in near darkness. The camera supports a maximum resolution of 1080P at 30fps, ensuring smooth and detailed video playback. With HD and SD output switchable options, users can easily adapt the camera to their specific monitoring needs. The 3.6mm fixed lens, with optional 2.8mm and 6mm variants, provides flexible viewing angles. Equipped with Smart IR technology, it can achieve a maximum IR distance of 30m, ensuring visibility in complete darkness. The camera\'s robust IP67-rated aluminum housing protects it from harsh weather conditions, making it suitable for outdoor use. Powered by DC12V, it offers stable and energy-efficient operation. This versatile security solution is ideal for residential, commercial, and industrial applications. Trust the DAHUA DH-HFW1230T for enhanced security and peace of mind.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
