(71, 'DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.724353', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.724525', 3, 4, 22, 'dahua-dh-hdw1239tln-a-led', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED is a high-performance security camera designed to offer unparalleled clarity and reliability. Equipped with Full-color Starlight technology, it provides vivid color images even in low-light conditions. The camera boasts a 20-meter LED distance, ensuring excellent visibility even in complete darkness. With a maximum resolution of 1080P and 30fps, it captures smooth and detailed video footage. The camera supports CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI switchable formats, making it highly versatile for different surveillance systems. Featuring a built-in microphone, it allows for audio monitoring, enhancing its surveillance capabilities. The 3.6mm fixed lens (with an optional 2.8mm lens) ensures a wide field of view, perfect for capturing expansive areas. Its IP67 rating guarantees superior weather resistance, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. Operating on a 12V DC power supply, it offers easy installation with minimal setup complexity. This camera combines cutting-edge technology with user-friendly features to deliver a comprehensive security solution.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(72, ' DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED', '2025-01-10 02:27:33.567272', '2025-01-10 02:44:36.171138', 3, 4, 26, 'dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-a-led', '<p>The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is a high-performance, full-color starlight security camera designed to deliver clear and vibrant video surveillance. It boasts a 40-meter LED distance, ensuring optimal coverage in various lighting conditions. The camera supports a maximum of 30fps at 1080P resolution and is switchable between CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI formats, making it versatile for different system configurations. With its built-in microphone (-A model), the camera also captures audio, enhancing its surveillance capabilities. Equipped with a 3.6mm fixed lens, this camera delivers a wide field of view, perfect for both residential and commercial surveillance applications. Its IP67 rating ensures protection against dust and water, making it durable for outdoor use. The camera is powered by a 12V&plusmn;30% DC supply and is housed in a combination of metal and plastic for added robustness. Offering advanced security features and excellent video quality, the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is a reliable choice for modern surveillance needs.</p>'),
(73, 'DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED', '2025-01-10 02:44:07.078943', '2025-01-10 02:48:32.385805', 3, 4, 26, 'dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-led', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED is a high-performance security camera offering full-color starlight capabilities for clear imaging in low-light conditions. It features a 40-meter LED distance, allowing for excellent visibility in various lighting environments. With a maximum resolution of 1080P and a frame rate of up to 30fps, this camera delivers smooth and detailed footage. The camera supports multiple video output formats, including CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI, providing versatility in different security systems. It is equipped with a built-in microphone (minus model), offering audio capture in addition to video surveillance. The camera comes with a 3.6mm fixed lens, with an optional 2.8mm lens for varied viewing angles. Its IP67 rating ensures durability in outdoor environments, resisting dust and water. Operating on a 12V &plusmn;30% DC input, this camera is energy-efficient. It is perfect for both residential and commercial properties, offering superior quality and reliability. The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED is an ideal choice for anyone seeking a high-quality security camera for all-weather, all-light surveillance.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(74, ' DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.167541', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.167689', 3, 4, 27, 'dahua-dh-hdbw1100r-vf-s3', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3 is a high-performance security camera designed for reliable surveillance in various environments. It supports a maximum resolution of 720P at 30fps, ensuring clear and smooth video footage. Equipped with a 2.7-12mm vari-focal lens, this camera offers flexible zoom options for optimized coverage. The camera\'s smart IR technology allows for enhanced visibility at night, with an infrared range of up to 30 meters. It is built to withstand harsh conditions, with an IP67 weatherproof rating and an IK10 vandal-proof rating for maximum durability. The camera features a switchable HD and SD&nbsp; output, making it versatile for different surveillance setups. Powered by DC 12V, it ensures consistent performance with low energy consumption. Ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations, it is perfect for monitoring entrances, parking lots, or any other high-security area. With advanced features and high-quality video output, this camera is a top choice for businesses and homeowners alike. The DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3 provides both flexibility and reliability for modern security needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(75, 'DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.441191', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.441342', 3, 4, 27, 'dahua-dh-hdbw1200r-vf-s3', '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3 is a high-performance 2MP network camera designed to provide exceptional image quality for surveillance needs. Equipped with a 1/2.7\" 2 Megapixel CMOS sensor, this camera offers a resolution of 1080P at 25/30fps and 720P at 25/30/50/60fps, ensuring clear and detailed video recording. It features a 2.7~12mm vari-focal lens, providing versatile zoom capabilities for various surveillance applications. The camera&rsquo;s advanced technologies include DWDR, Day/Night (ICR), AWB, AGC, BLC, and 2DNR, allowing it to perform well in different lighting conditions. With a maximum IR LEDs length of 30 meters and Smart IR technology, the camera ensures high-quality footage even in low light. Its IP67 rating ensures durability and protection from the elements, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor use. The camera also supports HD and SD switchable output and offers easy control over coaxial cables via the OSD Menu. Designed for seamless integration, it operates on DC12V power, making it suitable for various security setups. Whether used for monitoring parking lots, entrances, or perimeters, the DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3 delivers reliable and real-time performance with long-distance transmission capabilities.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(76, 'DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.801905', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.802055', 3, 4, 27, 'dahua-dh-hdbw3231e-z', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z is a high-performance surveillance camera designed to provide exceptional video quality in various environments. With Starlight technology, it delivers clear and vibrant images even in low-light conditions. Equipped with 120dB True WDR (Wide Dynamic Range) and 3DNR (3D Noise Reduction), it ensures superior image clarity, even in challenging lighting situations. The camera supports a maximum 30fps at 1080p resolution, offering crisp and smooth video playback. Additionally, it features HD and SD dual-output for versatile compatibility. The 2.7-12mm motorized lens provides flexible focal length adjustments, allowing for optimized field-of-view and image detail. With a maximum IR length of 50 meters and Smart IR technology, it ensures effective night vision in dark environments. The camera is built to withstand harsh conditions, with an IP67 rating for dust and water resistance and IK10 for impact protection. Powered by AC24V/DC12V, it ensures reliability and versatility in various power setups. Whether for commercial or residential security applications, the DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z delivers reliable performance with top-tier features.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(77, 'DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.825904', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.826060', 3, 4, 27, 'dahua-dh-hdw1200r-vf-s3', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3 is a high-performance surveillance camera designed for both residential and commercial security needs. Featuring a 2-megapixel CMOS sensor, it delivers crystal-clear 1080p video at 25/30fps and 720p at 25/30/50/60fps. With a 2.7-12mm vari-focal lens, the camera offers adjustable viewing angles to suit a wide range of surveillance scenarios. It also supports real-time transmission over long distances and has HD/SD switchable modes. The camera is equipped with advanced features such as DWDR, Day/Night(ICR), AWB, AGC, BLC, and 2DNR, which ensure high-quality footage in various lighting conditions. It also boasts a powerful IR LED range of up to 30 meters with Smart IR for enhanced night vision. Built for durability, the DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3 is rated IP67, making it resistant to dust and water. The camera is powered by DC12V and is compatible with coaxial control through OSD menus. With its advanced specifications and robust build, this camera is ideal for a wide variety of security applications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(78, 'DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.778798', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.778976', 3, 4, 27, 'dahua-dh-hdw1239tn-a-led', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED is a high-performance full-color starlight surveillance camera designed for both day and night security monitoring. Featuring a 3.6mm fixed lens (with an optional 2.8mm lens), it offers clear and crisp 1080p resolution at a maximum of 30 frames per second. With its advanced LED technology, it ensures excellent visibility even in low light conditions, providing up to 40 meters of LED distance. The camera supports CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI switchable formats, offering compatibility with various video surveillance systems. Additionally, the built-in microphone provides audio recording capabilities. The IP67 rating ensures the camera&rsquo;s durability and protection against the elements, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations. It is powered by a 12V&plusmn;30% DC input, delivering reliable performance for extended periods. This model is perfect for users who require a high-quality, versatile, and durable security solution. Whether used for residential or commercial properties, the DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED stands as a trusted option for secure surveillance. Experience enhanced security with this robust and feature-rich camera.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(79, 'MB10-VL Time & Attendance and Access Control', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.639927', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.640122', 4, 11, 33, 'mb10-vl-time-attendance-and-access-control', '<p>The ZKTeco MB10-VL Time &amp; Attendance and Access Control system is a highly advanced, touchless multi-biometric identification terminal, offering cutting-edge Visible Light Facial Recognition technology. This Linux-based system allows businesses to streamline their attendance tracking and access control while ensuring enhanced security and convenience for employees. With the ability to support multiple verification methods including facial recognition and fingerprint scanning, the ZKTeco MB10-VL provides an efficient solution for timekeeping and facility access.</p>\n<p>Equipped with a 2.8-inch TFT display and robust internal memory of 256MB RAM and 256MB Flash, the ZKTeco MB10-VL ensures fast, reliable performance. It can store up to 100 faces, 500 fingerprints, and 50,000 transaction records, making it suitable for medium to large-sized businesses. With communication options like TCP/IP, USB Host, and optional Wi-Fi, it provides flexible connectivity for seamless integration into existing systems. The ZKTeco MB10-VL also includes advanced functions such as ADMS, DST, self-service query, automatic status switch, and bell scheduling for greater operational efficiency.</p>\n<p>Designed for ease of use, the MB10-VL features an innovative combination of hardware and software for managing employee access and time tracking. Its touchless biometric identification makes it ideal for reducing physical contact, promoting hygiene, and speeding up the user authentication process. Whether it&rsquo;s used in offices, factories, or warehouses, this device simplifies workforce management and helps businesses maintain a secure, paperless environment.</p>'),
(80, 'EFace10/ID/WIFI', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.134237', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.134366', 4, 11, 33, 'eface10-id-wifi', '<p>The ZKTECO EFace10/ID/WIFI is a state-of-the-art, touchless facial recognition terminal designed to elevate security and efficiency in various applications, including access control and time attendance. Utilizing ZKTeco&rsquo;s cutting-edge Visible Light Facial Recognition technology, the EFace10 delivers superior accuracy and speed by automatically recognizing faces from a long distance. This innovative technology outperforms traditional near-infrared facial recognition systems, offering enhanced recognition quality, even in challenging lighting conditions. It&rsquo;s designed to streamline operations by offering easy integration and multiple verification methods, ensuring reliable performance in both secure and high-traffic environments.</p>\n<p>The device features a 4.3-inch TFT display, providing a clear and user-friendly interface for easier operation and status monitoring. Powered by a robust Linux operating system, the EFace10 supports up to 1,000 user cards, 500 facial templates, and can store up to 150,000 transactions. The system&rsquo;s advanced communication capabilities, including TCP/IP, Wi-Fi (optional), and USB Host, ensure flexible connectivity for seamless integration with other systems. Its practical features, such as automatic status switching and work code input, make it an excellent choice for businesses looking for a reliable, touchless security solution that also reduces user interaction for hygiene and convenience.</p>'),
(81, 'SpeedFace-V4L', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.657078', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.657239', 4, 11, 33, 'speedface-v4l', '<p>The ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L is a cutting-edge hybrid-biometric access control and time attendance terminal designed for both high security and ease of use. With a compact form factor and advanced features, this terminal offers a powerful combination of visible light facial recognition, palm verification, and intelligent engineering algorithms. The SpeedFace-V4L leverages the latest computer vision technology to deliver high-speed and accurate identification, ensuring seamless access control and time tracking for businesses of all sizes. Its intuitive interface is complemented by a 4&rdquo; touch screen, making it user-friendly for employees and administrators alike.</p>\n<p>In addition to its high-performance recognition capabilities, the ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L supports a variety of verification methods, offering flexibility in access control solutions. It can accommodate up to 800 facial templates, 800 palm templates, and 1,000 card templates, making it ideal for medium to large-scale enterprises. The terminal also features a large transaction capacity, with the ability to store up to 150,000 transactions, ensuring reliability even in high-traffic environments. The device is equipped with multiple communication options, including TCP/IP, USB Host, and optional Wi-Fi, for easy integration into existing security infrastructure.</p>\n<p>With enhanced security features like anti-passback, tamper switch alarm, and customizable access levels, the ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L provides robust protection for both physical access and time tracking. It also offers seamless integration with ID cards, ADMS, and other security systems to meet diverse organizational needs. Whether you are upgrading an existing access control system or deploying a new one, the SpeedFace-V4L offers a future-proof solution that adapts to your business needs.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(82, 'SA40', '2025-01-10 06:53:28.311460', '2025-01-10 06:54:23.483773', 4, 11, 33, 'sa40', '<p>The ZKTeco SA40 is a versatile standalone access control device designed to enhance security through multiple authentication methods. It supports three verification modes: password, RFID card, and a combination of both, providing flexibility to meet various security requirements. With a user capacity of up to 2,000 users and a password capacity of 2,000 (ranging from 4 to 6 digits), the SA40 is suitable for small to medium-sized facilities. Its compact design, measuring 103.5 x 86 x 19 mm, ensures easy installation in diverse environments.</p>\n<div class=\"relative inline-flex items-center\">&nbsp;</div>'),
(83, 'NIR-31 Corridor Light with One Magnetic Nameplate', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.243620', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.243766', 6, 27, 53, 'nir-31-corridor-light-with-one-magnetic-nameplate', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-31 Corridor Light with One Magnetic Nameplate is a sleek, reliable corridor indicator designed for seamless integration in various settings. Constructed from fire-resistant ABS plastic, it offers safety and durability. This light mounts directly to the wall, simplifying installation. The magnetic nameplate ensures easy identification and adaptability. Ideal for healthcare facilities, schools, and office buildings, it enhances visibility and communication. The NIR-31 is a cost-effective solution that combines functionality with modern aesthetics. Its robust design and intuitive features make it a standout choice for those needing reliable corridor indicators. With its surface-mount design, it fits effortlessly into any space. Enhance your environment&rsquo;s efficiency with the AIPHONE NIR-31 Corridor Light.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(84, 'NI-RC Bedside Handheld Sub Station', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.956401', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.956560', 6, 27, 53, 'ni-rc-bedside-handheld-sub-station', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NI-RC Bedside Handheld Sub Station is an essential communication device designed for seamless interaction between patients and caregivers. This bedside substation allows call-ins and hands-free communication with the NIM master station, enhancing patient safety and convenience. The handheld unit can clip onto a bed or hang from a hook on the NIR-HPF, providing flexible mounting options. Constructed with durable plastic, it offers reliable performance in medical environments. The device supports up to 650 feet of communication distance with a 3-conductor overall shield wire, ensuring stable and clear audio transmission. Ideal for hospitals and care facilities, the NI-RC substation enhances responsiveness and care efficiency. With easy-to-use functionality and robust construction, it&rsquo;s a valuable addition to any healthcare setting. Its compact design integrates seamlessly with existing infrastructure, offering a practical and efficient communication solution. Trust the AIPHONE NI-RC to deliver dependable, patient-focused communication in critical environments.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(85, 'NIR-7HW Bathroom Call Button with Pull Cord', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.355913', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.356056', 6, 27, 53, 'nir-7hw-bathroom-call-button-with-pull-cord', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-7HW Bathroom Call Button with Pull Cord is an essential safety device designed for use in bathrooms and restrooms in both residential and commercial settings. Featuring a sleek flush mount design, it seamlessly integrates into a 1-gang box for a clean, unobtrusive installation. Constructed from fire-resistant ABS plastic, this call button ensures durability and safety in any environment. The pull cord mechanism provides an easy-to-use emergency alert system, making it ideal for individuals with mobility issues or other vulnerabilities. Its reliable functionality offers peace of mind, ensuring that help is just a pull away. This call button is suitable for hospitals, care homes, and public restrooms, where user safety is paramount. Its modern design and robust build make it a versatile addition to any bathroom. The AIPHONE NIR-7HW not only enhances safety but also contributes to a worry-free experience for users and caregivers alike. Easy installation and low maintenance requirements make this product a smart choice for any safety-conscious establishment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(86, 'NIR-8 Bedside Call Button', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.346534', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.346730', 6, 27, 53, 'nir-8-bedside-call-button', '<p>The AIPHONE NIR-8 Bedside Call Button is a reliable and essential communication device designed for healthcare environments. This handheld unit enhances patient safety by providing a quick and efficient way to call for assistance. Compatible with NIR-1, NIR-MB, or NIR-7BS systems, it seamlessly integrates into existing setups. Made from fire-resistant ABS plastic, the NIR-8 is built to endure rigorous daily use while ensuring safety standards. Its ergonomic design offers ease of use for patients of all ages and abilities. Ideal for hospitals, nursing homes, and assisted living facilities, this device prioritizes both functionality and durability. The NIR-8&rsquo;s intuitive design and robust construction make it a preferred choice for healthcare providers aiming to enhance patient care and communication. Its fire-resistant material ensures long-lasting performance and compliance with safety regulations. With its reliable connection and compatibility, the AIPHONE NIR-8 Bedside Call Button is a vital addition to any healthcare communication system.</p>'),
(87, 'NIM-20B 20-Call Master Station with Handset', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.919403', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.919560', 6, 27, 53, 'nim-20b-20-call-master-station-with-handset', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIM-20B 20-Call Master Station with Handset is a versatile communication system designed for optimal control and convenience in various settings. Supporting up to 20 door stations, sub stations, ceiling speakers, and wall jacks, this master station ensures seamless communication across your facility. It offers selective call, group call, and all call functions, providing flexibility in message dissemination. The handset enables private conversations, enhancing confidentiality in sensitive environments. Built with a durable, fire-resistant ABS plastic panel and a sturdy SPCC chassis, the NIM-20B is designed for long-lasting performance. Easy to install, it requires minimal wiring with a 3-conductor overall shield wire, making it suitable for both small and large-scale setups. The device also features volume controls, allowing users to adjust the sound according to their preferences. With a communication range of up to 650 feet, it ensures connectivity across extensive areas. The power supply distance of 33 feet simplifies installation, ensuring the station operates efficiently. The AIPHONE NIM-20B is an ideal solution for enhancing communication in offices, schools, hospitals, and other large facilities.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(88, 'TB-SE Handset Sub Station', '2025-01-10 08:10:12.974345', '2025-01-10 08:10:12.974491', 6, 27, 53, 'tb-se-handset-sub-station', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE TB-SE Handset Sub Station is a reliable communication device designed for seamless integration into your intercom system. It features easy call initiation by simply picking up the handset, with tone and LED annunciation at the master station. This substation allows direct communication between handset subs via the master, ensuring clear and efficient communication across your facility. With a substantial wire distance capability of up to 2,950 feet with 18AWG wiring, it offers flexible installation options. Its compact dimensions of 8-1/4\" H x 3-1/8\" W x 3\" D make it suitable for various environments. The TB-SE is ideal for enhancing communication in residential, commercial, and industrial settings, offering durability and ease of use. Its streamlined design and functionality ensure it meets the demands of modern intercom systems. The AIPHONE TB-SE is an excellent choice for upgrading or expanding your communication network. It provides reliable performance, reducing communication delays and improving overall operational efficiency.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(89, 'NIR-2 Call Reset Button', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.654259', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.654396', 6, 27, 53, 'nir-2-call-reset-button', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-2 Call Reset Button is an essential accessory designed for efficient communication and safety in healthcare and other critical environments. Its sleek design ensures seamless integration into any setting, while the flush mount capability allows it to fit snugly into a standard 1-gang box. Constructed from fire-resistant ABS plastic, the NIR-2 offers durability and peace of mind. The intuitive call reset functionality enhances operational efficiency, ensuring quick response times. Ideal for hospitals, nursing homes, and similar facilities, this button is a key component in patient care systems. Its robust build ensures long-term reliability, while the clean design suits modern interiors. The AIPHONE NIR-2 is easy to install, making it a convenient choice for retrofitting or new installations. Its user-friendly interface simplifies the reset process, reducing the likelihood of errors. This device is a dependable choice for enhancing communication and safety in critical environments.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(90, 'TOA A-2060D-EB Digital Mixer Amplifier', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.314514', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.314728', 6, 14, 55, 'toa-a-2060d-eb-digital-mixer-amplifier', '<p>The TOA A-2060D-EB Digital Mixer Amplifier is a versatile and high-performance amplifier designed for professional audio applications. It features 3 microphone inputs, 2 AUX inputs, and 1 recording output, ensuring seamless integration with a wide range of audio devices. The amplifier is available in various output capacities, including 30 W, 60 W, 120 W, and 240 W, catering to different sound system requirements. It is equipped with advanced tone control for both high and low frequencies, offering boost and cut options to fine-tune audio quality. With a speaker output designed for constant voltage distribution systems (100 V), it ensures clear and reliable sound distribution. The amplifier also includes phantom power and a mute function for microphone input 1. To safeguard against overloads, it features a current limiter and excess heat protection, preventing potential damage to the system. The amplifier&rsquo;s design includes both DD- and D-varieties, with multiple phone jacks and a 5-pin DIN input. It is a robust and durable solution for venues that demand high-quality audio amplification and protection for sensitive equipment. With the TOA A-2060D-EB, you can achieve excellent audio performance with peace of mind</p>'),
(91, 'TOA MX-113-AS PRE-AMPLIFIER MIXER', '2025-01-13 01:26:02.970451', '2025-01-13 01:26:02.970601', 6, 14, 55, 'toa-mx-113-as-pre-amplifier-mixer', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA MX-113-AS Pre-Amplifier Mixer is a versatile audio solution designed for a wide range of audio mixing applications. With its slim and compact 1U size, it fits easily into any audio setup, offering flexible mounting options. Featuring 6 microphone inputs, 4 AUX inputs, and 2 monaural outputs, it delivers excellent audio quality and extensive connectivity. The mixer includes a signal noise gate circuit for microphone inputs 1-5, allowing a signal to pass only when above a specified threshold, ensuring clearer sound with minimal interference. Remote control contact functionality adds convenience for operation from a distance. Its adaptability is further enhanced with the option for both desk and rack mounting, with an optional rack mount bracket for easy integration into a professional setup. Ideal for both small and large-scale venues, this pre-amplifier mixer offers exceptional performance. It is perfect for use in public address systems, conferences, and live sound applications. Whether in the studio or on stage, the TOA MX-113-AS provides precise control over audio signals. Its user-friendly features make it an essential tool for enhancing sound clarity and ease of operation.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(92, 'TOA CA-115 CAR AMPLIFIERS', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.578593', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.578796', 6, 14, 55, 'toa-ca-115-car-amplifiers', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CA-115 Car Amplifier is a high-quality mobile amplifier designed for easy installation in vehicles. Powered by a 12V DC battery, this amplifier offers flexibility in power output with ratings of 15W, 30W, or 60W to meet different audio needs. It features two microphone inputs for added convenience, ideal for hands-free communication or voice amplification. The amplifier also includes an AUX input, making it compatible with CD players, radios, and other external devices. Equipped with a unidirectional dynamic microphone with a talk switch, it ensures clear, effective communication. The front pause function allows for easy control during operation, providing enhanced functionality. Its compact DIN size design makes in-dash installation a breeze, while its rugged construction ensures long-lasting durability. Whether you need a reliable audio solution for your vehicle or require amplified sound for communication, the TOA CA-115 is a versatile and powerful choice.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(93, 'TOA VM-2120 SYSTEM AMPLIFIER', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.060414', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.060552', 6, 14, 55, 'toa-vm-2120-system-amplifier', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA VM-2120 System Amplifier is a versatile and multifunctional amplifier designed to be mounted in a 3-unit EIA-Standard equipment rack. It is equipped with 4 audio inputs, including a background music (BGM) input, and supports up to 5 selectable speaker zones with adjustable attenuators. This amplifier is built for both general-purpose broadcasting and emergency communication, meeting the EN60849 standard for emergency broadcasts. With the optional EV-200M, the system can provide pre-recorded voice instructions during emergencies. Remote control of broadcasts can be managed through external equipment or an optional RM-200M remote microphone. Additionally, for 100 V application systems, the VM-2120 features a surveillance function that monitors for system failures (optional SV-200MA required). The unit includes volume, bass, and treble controls for each of the 4 input channels, along with pre-adjustable BGM input levels. The amplifier\'s modular design allows up to 9 units to be combined for expanded output power and more zones. Built-in features also include emergency power input, remote power control, and 4 chimes for system integration. The TOA VM-2120 is perfect for managing audio in large-scale environments requiring clear and reliable communication.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(94, 'TOA ER-3215S HAND GRIP TYPE MEGAPHONE WITH SIREN SIGNAL', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.251606', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.251757', 6, 14, 53, 'toa-er-3215s-hand-grip-type-megaphone-with-siren-signal', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA ER-3215S Hand Grip Type Megaphone with Siren Signal is a versatile and powerful 15 W megaphone designed for clear sound transmission over long distances. It features a removable microphone, allowing it to be converted into a shoulder-type megaphone for hands-free use. Equipped with a newly developed polyimide diaphragm, the megaphone ensures high sound quality, even in challenging environments. The siren function is ideal for emergency situations, producing a loud sound at 5-second intervals, with an audible range of up to 500 meters. Powered by six R14P (SUM-2) size \"C\" batteries, the megaphone offers up to 9 hours of continuous voice use. The ergonomic handgrip and adjustable nylon strap provide easy handling and comfort during use. Built with durable ABS resin material, it ensures long-lasting performance. The compact design makes it easy to transport, and the clear, strong sound output makes it ideal for outdoor events, emergencies, or public announcements. This megaphone combines convenience and reliability, making it an excellent choice for a wide range of users. With its high output and long battery life, the TOA ER-3215S ensures optimal performance when you need it most.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(95, 'TOA DM-1300 UNIDIRECTIONAL MICROPHONE ', '2025-01-13 02:08:27.938067', '2025-01-13 02:08:27.938245', 6, 14, 53, 'toa-dm-1300-unidirectional-microphone', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA DM-1300 Unidirectional Microphone is a high-quality, durable microphone designed for professional audio applications. It features a moving coil type design with unidirectional directivity, ideal for capturing sound from a specific direction. With a rated impedance of 600 &Omega;, this microphone ensures clear and precise sound transmission. It offers a broad frequency response range from 70 Hz to 15,000 Hz, making it suitable for various vocal and instrumental recordings. The microphone has a rated sensitivity of -54 dB (1 kHz), ensuring optimal performance in sound-sensitive environments. It is equipped with a 10-meter single-core shielded cable with an unbalanced connection and a phone plug terminal. A talk switch with short-off slide functionality adds to the user-friendliness of the device. The microphone is housed in a robust die-cast zinc body finished with metallic gray paint, offering both durability and a professional appearance. The steel/zinc-plated steel wire head is also painted in metallic gray for added resilience. With an accessory microphone holder included, this versatile microphone is ready for a variety of sound recording or amplification tasks.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(96, 'TOA TS-682L DELEGATE UNIT WITH LONG MICROPHONE', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.001627', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.001802', 6, 14, 53, 'toa-ts-682l-delegate-unit-with-long-microphone', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA TS-682L Delegate Unit with Long Microphone is a key component of the TOA conference system, TS-680 Series, offering a compact, lightweight, and easy-to-install solution for professional conference settings. The unit includes an integrated electret condenser microphone with a unidirectional pick-up pattern, ensuring clear audio during discussions. With a simple \"Talk Key\" control, the microphone can be easily switched on and off, allowing seamless interaction while preventing feedback. The TS-682L&rsquo;s internal speaker and headphone output provide versatile audio monitoring options, with volume control for personalized sound levels. Designed to withstand operating conditions from 0&deg;C to +40&deg;C and up to 90% humidity, this unit offers reliable performance in various environments. The unit is powered by the central unit, drawing 36V DC, and consumes a low 30mA, ensuring energy efficiency. The long microphone, a standard accessory, facilitates clear and hands-free communication. The TS-682L is ideal for conference rooms, meetings, and events where precise audio control and clarity are critical. It is compatible with TOA&rsquo;s TS-680 series, ensuring integration with a variety of conference configurations. Its robust ABS resin construction guarantees durability while maintaining a professional aesthetic.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(97, 'TOA BS-680FC WALL MOUNT SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.769468', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.769660', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-bs-680fc-wall-mount-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-680FC Wall Mount Speaker is a robust and high-quality speaker designed for use in voice alarm systems. Its versatile installation options allow it to be mounted both surface- and flush-mounted on walls, providing flexibility in various environments. This speaker is engineered with a 16 cm double-cone speaker unit, delivering exceptional sound quality and clear voice transmission. It features a metal enclosure that enhances durability and ensures the speaker stays securely in place, even when exposed to outward forces. The impedance is adjustable, making it easy to adapt to different systems, and the speaker offers simple wiring options with bridge wiring compatibility. Certified according to EN 54-24 and compliant with BS-5839-8: 2013, this speaker guarantees safety and performance in professional installations. The TOA BS-680FC has a frequency response range from 150 Hz to 20 kHz and delivers a sensitivity of 94 dB at 1 W, 1 m. The speaker also supports high sound pressure levels and is equipped with two steatite screw terminal blocks, ensuring a reliable connection. It is ideal for settings that demand clear, high-quality audio for alarm and public address systems. With a sleek off-white finish, it seamlessly integrates into any environment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(98, 'TOA PJ-100W PROJECTION SPEAKERS', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.382622', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.383006', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-pj-100w-projection-speakers', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PJ-100W Projection Speakers deliver high-quality sound with a compact design, perfect for professional audio applications. With a wide frequency response of 65 Hz to 15 kHz, it provides clear and accurate sound reproduction for a variety of environments. Designed with flexibility in mind, the speakers offer multiple impedance options for 100 V, 70 V, and 50 V lines, ensuring compatibility with various sound systems. The 12 cm speaker component ensures robust audio performance, while the 92 dB sound pressure level delivers clear and powerful sound at a distance. The speakers are housed in a durable ABS resin cabinet with an off-white finish, making them suitable for discreet installations in various settings. With a lightweight design of just 1.8 kg, they are easy to mount and position. Ideal for commercial, public address, and background music applications, the TOA PJ-100W speakers provide reliable sound performance for any environment. The included SPCC bracket allows for flexible installation options, whether on walls or ceilings. The speaker\'s compact size ensures it can fit in a variety of locations without compromising on sound quality. The TOA PJ-100W speakers are an excellent choice for anyone looking for dependable, high-performance projection speakers.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(99, 'TOA CS-64 PROJECTION SPEAKERS', '2025-01-13 04:17:13.221043', '2025-01-13 04:19:51.262361', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-cs-64-projection-speakers', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CS-64 Projection Speakers are the ultimate solution for clear, high-quality audio in outdoor environments. With stainless steel hardware, these speakers are built to withstand the harshest weather conditions, ensuring longevity and durability. Featuring a combination of weather-resistant horns and dynamic speaker technology, the CS-64 delivers superior sound quality. Its rotary switch allows easy impedance adjustments for flexibility across various setups. The wide-range, exponential horn design enhances sound directivity and uniform dispersion, making it perfect for paging, background music, and tone signaling. Designed to operate in extreme temperatures, the CS-64 performs efficiently from -20&deg;C to +55&deg;C. The 12 cm cone-type speaker offers a broad frequency response of 130 - 13,000 Hz, ensuring a rich and clear sound. Its splash-proof treatment adds an extra layer of protection for outdoor use. The speaker is compatible with both 100V and 70V line systems, offering various impedance options for different installations. Whether for commercial or residential use, the TOA CS-64 Projection Speaker guarantees reliable, high-quality audio performance in any environment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(100, 'TOA PC-658R CEILING SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.036992', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.037294', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-pc-658r-ceiling-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-658R Ceiling Speaker is designed for high-quality sound reproduction in ceiling installations, offering a 6\" cone-type speaker with a broad frequency response range of 65 Hz to 18 kHz. Featuring an integrated resin panel and speaker frame, it also includes a metal attachment for secure and stable mounting. The spring clamp mechanism simplifies the installation process, allowing for easy ceiling mounting. The speaker\'s impedance can be adjusted via the tap position of its transformer, offering flexibility for different systems. The PC-658R delivers rated input of 6 W (100 V line) and 3 W (70 V line), ensuring compatibility with a variety of audio systems. Its sensitivity of 90 dB and frequency response of 65 Hz to 18 kHz ensures clear and detailed sound. The polypropylene resin baffle and surface-treated steel plate grille ensure durability while maintaining an aesthetically pleasing design. With a weight of just 500 g, this speaker is lightweight yet robust. The mounting hole is designed for a precise fit, and the product comes with a paper pattern to assist in installation. Ideal for commercial and residential environments, the TOA PC-658R Ceiling Speaker guarantees optimal performance and ease of use.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(101, 'TOA PC-668R CEILING MOUNT SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.528075', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.528234', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-pc-668r-ceiling-mount-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-668R Ceiling Mount Speaker is an exceptional audio solution for both commercial and residential applications. With a sleek, slim design, this ceiling-mounted speaker blends seamlessly into any interior decor. It features a durable polypropylene resin panel and a spring clamp mechanism for easy and secure installation. The speaker is equipped with an 8-inch double cone-type speaker component that provides clear and powerful sound. Offering a wide frequency response range of 65 Hz to 20,000 Hz, it delivers high-quality audio for a variety of environments. The TOA PC-668R comes with adjustable impedance options for both 100V and 70V line systems, making it versatile for different setups. This speaker also features a high sensitivity rating of 96 dB for optimal performance. The durable, white-painted grille and polypropylene panel ensure the speaker maintains its appearance while offering excellent sound quality. The spring clamp mechanism simplifies the installation process, making it suitable for both experienced and DIY installers. With a mounting hole of &Phi;250 mm, this speaker is perfect for ceiling installations in various commercial and professional spaces.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(102, 'TOA SC-610M PAGING HORN SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 06:40:22.997572', '2025-01-13 06:40:22.997716', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-sc-610m-paging-horn-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA SC-610M Paging Horn Speaker is a compact, rugged speaker designed for high intelligibility in public address applications. Constructed with durable materials, it features a weatherproof finish, ensuring reliable performance even in challenging environments. Equipped with a shock-resistant oval horn, the speaker delivers high-quality sound with a sound pressure level (SPL) of 110 dB. Its frequency response range of 315 Hz to 12.5 kHz ensures clear and crisp announcements. The easy impedance selection switch allows for versatile usage in various audio systems, with both 100V and 70V line configurations. Additionally, the TOA SC-610M is IP65 rated, making it dust and water-resistant, ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations. Designed for long-term operation, it maintains high performance even under extreme temperatures ranging from -20&deg;C to +55&deg;C. This speaker\'s powder-coated finish and stainless steel brackets ensure durability in various weather conditions. The TOA SC-610M Paging Horn Speaker is the perfect solution for effective public address announcements, combining high durability, ease of use, and exceptional audio quality. With its compact size and advanced features, it is an ideal choice for any paging system setup.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(103, 'TOA EC-100M CHIME MICROPHONE', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.864858', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.865010', 6, 14, 53, 'toa-ec-100m-chime-microphone', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA EC-100M Chime Microphone is a versatile and durable device designed for locations that require both microphone and chime functionality. Equipped with a four-tone chime and unidirectional dynamic microphone, this product ensures clear audio transmission and distinct chime sounds. The microphone&rsquo;s power-saving design allows it to operate for up to 2 years on two R14P batteries, assuming 150 uses per day. Its robust zinc die-cast metallic gold case ensures durability, while the unbalanced chime and microphone signals offer reliable performance. The EC-100M is ideal for applications where clear communication and chime alerts are needed, such as in schools, churches, and businesses. Its simple operation makes it accessible for users of all levels. Additionally, the microphone features a frequency response range of 200 Hz to 10 kHz, ensuring high-quality sound reproduction. The product comes with essential accessories like a connection cord, slotted-head screwdriver, and a windscreen for optimal usage. Whether used in a busy environment or for special occasions, the TOA EC-100M is engineered for consistent and effective performance. With a recommended battery replacement every two years, users can rely on this microphone for long-term use.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(104, 'TOA BS-301BCOMPACT SATELLITE SPEAKER SYSTEM', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.393485', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.393650', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-bs-301bcompact-satellite-speaker-system', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-301B Compact Satellite Speaker System is a versatile audio solution designed for commercial spaces like restaurants, caf&eacute;s, and retail stores. It includes four small satellite speakers and a subwoofer, each equipped with its own mounting brackets. The system\'s compact design ensures it fits seamlessly into various environments without compromising on sound quality. The satellite speakers can be installed individually or in pairs, allowing for flexible placement in complex spaces. The subwoofer enhances the overall audio experience, delivering ideal sound reinforcement, whether temporarily or permanently installed. With a frequency response range from 40 Hz to 20 kHz, the system covers a broad spectrum of sound for clear, rich audio output. The 81 dB sensitivity ensures effective sound projection throughout the space. Built for efficiency, the system delivers exceptional performance with a continuous power rating of 160W per channel. Constructed with durable HIPS resin and finished in black, the speakers are both sturdy and aesthetically suited to commercial environments. Complete with all necessary installation accessories, the TOA BS-301B is easy to set up and offers lasting value for any commercial audio setup.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(105, 'TOA BS-10WL SPLASHPROOF WALL-MOUNTED SPEAKERS', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.072630', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.072794', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-bs-10wl-splashproof-wall-mounted-speakers', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-10WL Splashproof Wall-Mounted Speakers offer high-quality sound for both indoor and outdoor environments. Featuring a 10 cm full-range dynamic speaker, these compact, splashproof speakers are designed for use in locations where exposure to water or high humidity is a concern. Ideal for locker rooms, bathrooms, swimming pools, and outdoor areas under eaves, the BS-10WL provides clear and reliable audio even in challenging environments. With a rated power of 5W and a wide frequency response range from 120Hz to 18kHz, these speakers deliver powerful and consistent sound performance. Their magnetic shielding ensures they won\'t interfere with nearby television sets, making them perfect for installations close to electronics. The BS-10WL features a sealed enclosure to prevent moisture infiltration, making it a reliable choice for public spaces. Constructed with durable polypropylene and aluminum materials, the speakers offer both performance and aesthetics. These wall-mounted speakers are lightweight at just 1.4 kg, allowing for easy installation. Whether you\'re enhancing sound in a gym, poolside, or locker room, the TOA BS-10WL is built to endure and perform.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(106, 'TOA BS-678 CABINET SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 07:35:59.800570', '2025-01-13 07:39:50.009600', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-bs-678-cabinet-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-678 Cabinet Speaker is a durable, versatile speaker system designed for paging systems. It features high-quality sound output, with two built-in 6-inch double cone speaker units that provide excellent audio performance. The speaker is constructed from wood and designed to be mounted vertically or horizontally, ensuring flexible installation options for various environments. It supports both concealed in-wall wiring and exposed wiring for easy cable connections. The speaker\'s structure ensures it can be directly wall-mounted using screws, preventing it from falling even when subjected to outward forces. The input impedance is adjustable via the transformer tap position for optimal sound configuration. This speaker is ideal for commercial use and offers a rated input of 6 W for 100 V line systems and 3 W for 70 V line systems. It provides a frequency response range from 150 Hz to 20 kHz, ensuring clear and precise sound reproduction. The TOA BS-678 is a reliable choice for anyone needing a high-performance, easy-to-install paging system speaker.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(107, 'TOA PC-2668 CEILING SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 07:45:46.417305', '2025-01-13 07:48:58.620946', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-pc-2668-ceiling-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-2668 Ceiling Speaker is a high-quality audio device designed for paging systems where flush mounting is not possible. It features a spring catch mounting method, making installation quick and easy. The push-in connector allows for fast wire connections, and the bridging terminals offer flexibility by enabling speaker line bridging. This speaker is perfect for areas that require a ceiling-mounted speaker solution without the need for flush installation. It provides reliable sound performance with a frequency response of 100 Hz to 16 kHz and a sound pressure level of 90 dB. The 12 cm dynamic cone-type speaker ensures clear and high-quality audio reproduction. The speaker is compatible with both 70V and 100V lines, offering adjustable impedance options to suit various setups. Its compact design (&phi;260 &times; 92 mm) makes it versatile for different ceiling types. The TOA PC-2668 is an excellent choice for paging and announcement applications. Its off-white ABS resin finish ensures a sleek and modern look, blending seamlessly with most ceiling styles.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(108, 'TOA CP-73 CEILING SPEAKER', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.939868', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.940127', 6, 14, 54, 'toa-cp-73-ceiling-speaker', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CP-73 Ceiling Speaker is designed to provide high-quality sound while seamlessly blending into any ceiling space. Featuring an easy spring catch mounting method, it can be quickly attached to the TOA CM-760 speaker for a secure fit. The speaker\'s compact, thin design ensures it remains discreet while delivering optimal audio performance. Its off-white ABS resin frame and aluminum net give it a sleek, modern look that suits a variety of settings. The painted metal net also makes cleaning easy and hassle-free. Lightweight at just 70g, the CP-73 is ideal for installations where space and aesthetics are important. Perfect for paging systems, it provides clear, reliable sound for any commercial or professional space. Its compatibility with the CM-760 speaker makes it an excellent choice for those looking to upgrade or expand their existing setup. The TOA CP-73 is built to last, offering durability and excellent sound quality for years. Whether you\'re outfitting a retail space, office, or conference room, this ceiling speaker ensures superior performance with minimal visual impact.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(109, 'TOA AT-063AP FLUSH-MOUNTED WALL ATTENUATOR', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.349204', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.349386', 6, 14, 59, 'toa-at-063ap-flush-mounted-wall-attenuator', '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA AT-063AP Flush-Mounted Wall Attenuator is a high-quality, reliable component designed for paging systems. This unit features an easy-to-use flush-mounted design and comes equipped with a transformer that supports various load connections of up to 6W. The volume can be adjusted in five distinct steps, offering versatile control over sound levels. A push-in terminal block is provided for effortless installation and secure connections. Constructed with durable ABS resin, the device offers both white and black finishes for the knob, panel, and case. This attenuator is compatible with a range of indoor cables, ensuring broad compatibility with different systems. It offers easy maintenance and is ideal for indoor installations. The compact size (70 x 120 x 52.4 mm) ensures a streamlined fit in your setup. The AT-063AP is suitable for use in both commercial and residential paging systems. It is a cost-effective solution for efficient volume control in high-quality sound systems.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(110, 'SF5636', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.411902', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.412113', 10, 21, 90, 'sf5636', '<p>The XRAY Baggage Scanner SF5636 is an advanced security screening solution designed to meet the rigorous demands of high-security environments such as airports, train stations, government buildings, and other sensitive facilities. This state-of-the-art scanner offers efficient and reliable detection of prohibited items, ensuring the safety and security of both passengers and staff. Its compact design, combined with powerful imaging capabilities, makes it a versatile choice for various security applications.</p>\n<p>Equipped with a spacious tunnel size of 560mm by 360mm, the SF5636 can accommodate a wide range of baggage sizes. Its conveyor system operates at a speed of 0.22m/s and can handle loads up to 150 kg, making it ideal for high-traffic environments. With advanced features such as a wire resolution of 40AWG and steel penetration of up to 36mm, the XRAY Baggage Scanner SF5636 delivers exceptional imaging performance, ensuring thorough inspection with minimal radiation exposure.</p>'),
(111, 'SF6040 PRO', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.588689', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.588850', 10, 21, 90, 'sf6040-pro', '<p>The UNIQSCAN SF6040 PRO is an advanced X-ray baggage scanner designed to enhance security screening in high-traffic and high-security environments such as airports, train stations, and government buildings. With its robust construction and spacious scanning tunnel, it efficiently accommodates various baggage sizes and shapes, ensuring thorough inspection. Utilizing cutting-edge X-ray imaging technology, the SF6040 PRO delivers high-resolution images, displayed on a 19-inch color LCD monitor, allowing operators to swiftly and accurately analyze the contents of luggage.</p>\n<p>This model is engineered with user-friendly features such as emergency stops for added safety, a one-key turn-off mechanism for quick power-down, and image brightness control for optimal viewing under different conditions. Its capability to detect contraband like drugs and explosives makes it an invaluable tool for security personnel. The SF6040 PRO stands out for its reliability, ease of use, and precision in high-demand security settings.</p>'),
(112, 'SF10080', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.757370', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.757519', 10, 21, 90, 'sf10080', '<p>The UNIQSAN SF10080 is a state-of-the-art X-ray baggage scanner designed to enhance security measures in high-traffic and high-security environments. With a spacious tunnel size of 1000mm (W) x 800mm (H), this scanner efficiently inspects large bags and various items, ensuring thorough security screening. Commonly used in airports, train stations, government buildings, and other critical facilities, the SF10080 excels in identifying threats like drugs and explosive powders. Equipped with a high-resolution 19-inch color LCD display, the system provides users with clear, vibrant images and improved detail for accurate screening. The device also features advanced material identification, distinguishing between organic, inorganic, and mixed materials.</p>\n<p>In addition to its impressive detection capabilities, the SF10080 offers versatile functionality with multi-energy settings, allowing users to switch between high and low energy modes for better object analysis. The color material identification system enhances user experience, with organic materials appearing in orange, inorganic materials in blue, and mixtures in green. For optimal visibility, the device includes a brightening/dimming function to adjust image brightness according to lighting conditions. Certified with CE, ISO, FCC, and ROHS, the SF10080 is reliable and meets international safety standards. Designed for long-lasting performance, it comes with a two-year warranty and operates with sealed oil bath cooling with forced air for efficient temperature regulation.</p>'),
(113, 'AVTECH 12SR', '2025-01-15 02:46:39.808307', '2025-01-15 02:55:30.196026', 12, 18, 113, 'avtech-12sr', '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is a compact and cost-effective monitoring solution designed to keep your facility safe by tracking critical environmental conditions. It is a scaled-down version of AVTECH&rsquo;s flagship Room Alert 32S, offering the same high-performance monitoring capabilities at a lower price point. Equipped with internal and external temperature sensors, this device ensures your facility&rsquo;s temperature and humidity levels are consistently within safe operating parameters. Ideal for monitoring sensitive environments, the Room Alert 12S/12SR supports up to 8 additional sensors, making it flexible for various monitoring needs. The standard package includes a digital temperature and humidity sensor, which helps monitor temperature, humidity, heat index, and dew point with high accuracy.</p>\n<p>This versatile monitoring system includes multiple connectivity options, including RJ-45 Ethernet with Power over Ethernet (PoE) capabilities, ensuring seamless integration into your network. It also provides convenient ports for additional external sensors and accessories, allowing for customizable monitoring setups. The system is housed in a small, durable form factor, with the 12S model designed for non-rack mounting and the 12SR version being rack-mountable for easy installation in server rooms or data centers. It is equipped with a relay output and light tower adapter port, providing alerts for any environmental irregularities. With operating tolerances from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C) and a humidity range of 5%-85%, the Room Alert 12S/12SR ensures reliable and consistent performance in diverse environments.</p>'),
(114, 'AVTECH 12S', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.123358', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.123526', 12, 18, 116, 'avtech-12s', '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is a compact yet powerful environmental monitoring solution designed for businesses and facilities that require temperature and humidity monitoring at an affordable price. It builds on the capabilities of the flagship Room Alert 32S model, offering a more cost-effective option with the same reliable performance. The device is equipped with a high-accuracy internal temperature sensor, and it comes with an external Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor that can be extended with up to 8 additional sensors. This allows businesses to monitor a wide range of environmental conditions, including temperature, humidity, heat index, and dew point. The Room Alert 12S/12SR is perfect for data centers, server rooms, warehouses, and more.</p>\n<p>The unit is built to offer flexibility and ease of use with a variety of ports for connecting external sensors and accessories, including digital, switch, and analog sensor ports. With its Power over Ethernet (PoE) compatibility, installation is straightforward and efficient. The Room Alert 12S/12SR is designed to withstand diverse environments, with an operational range from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C) and humidity tolerances between 5% to 85% RH, non-condensing. Additionally, its compact size and lightweight design make it a versatile choice for any facility in need of reliable environmental monitoring.</p>'),
(115, 'AVTECH 3S', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.076017', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.076188', 12, 18, 116, 'avtech-3s', '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 3S is a versatile, compact environmental monitoring device designed to help businesses ensure optimal conditions for their equipment and facilities. It is equipped with an internal temperature sensor and a digital port that can connect to various sensors and accessories, making it a flexible solution for monitoring various environmental parameters. The device&rsquo;s 3S model can measure temperature from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C) with an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. Additionally, it can support external sensors for expanded monitoring capabilities, offering business owners the peace of mind that their critical systems are operating within safe conditions. The Room Alert 3S is perfect for small to medium-sized facilities, with its efficient power supply options via PoE or an external 5V adapter.</p>\n<p>With easy setup and robust features, the AVTECH Room Alert 3S supports proactive environmental monitoring and emergency response. It connects to a Light Tower &amp; Relay Adapter, enabling automatic responses to environmental changes, such as turning on air conditioning when temperatures rise. The built-in alerting system can notify on-site personnel with audible alarms and visual signals, ensuring that the right action is taken in time. The device\'s compact size and wide range of operating temperatures make it an ideal choice for monitoring sensitive areas like server rooms, IT equipment, or other critical infrastructure.</p>'),
(116, 'Digital Active Power Sensor w/Temperature', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.093886', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.094055', 12, 18, 114, 'digital-active-power-sensor-w-temperature', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Active Power Sensor with Temperature offers an advanced solution for real-time environmental monitoring. Designed for precise temperature tracking, this sensor is ideal for facilities needing accurate climate control and power management. It measures temperatures ranging from -67&deg;F to 257&deg;F (-55&deg;C to 125&deg;C) with a remarkable accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. Compatible with various Room Alert devices, it ensures seamless integration into existing monitoring systems. The sensor\'s digital accuracy and wide range make it an essential tool for data centers, industrial environments, and critical infrastructure.</p>\n<p>Equipped with a durable RJ-11 cable that extends up to 100 feet, the AVTECH Digital Active Power Sensor delivers flexibility in deployment. Its high-resolution temperature readings, accurate to 0.0625&deg;C, provide precise data to safeguard sensitive equipment and environments. With the ability to recognize real-time temperature fluctuations, this sensor supports proactive management, ensuring operational stability and efficiency.</p>'),
(117, 'Digital Temperature Sensor ', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.146984', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.147140', 12, 18, 110, 'digital-temperature-sensor', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Temperature Sensor is an advanced device designed to provide accurate, real-time temperature monitoring across a wide range of environments. With a temperature range from -67 to 257&deg;F (-55 to 125&deg;C), it offers precise readings with an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. This sensor is ideal for use in monitoring critical areas where temperature fluctuations need to be tracked closely. Whether used in industrial, commercial, or home settings, the sensor ensures reliable performance, helping to prevent potential damage caused by temperature changes.</p>\n<p>Its compatibility with Room Alert products like 32S, 12S, and 3S makes it a versatile tool for any monitoring system. The sensor&rsquo;s resolution of 0.0625&deg;C ensures fine-tuned detection, and it is powered through the monitoring unit for convenience. With a choice of 25\' (7.62 m), 50\' (15.24 m), or 100\' (30.48 m) cables, this digital temperature sensor is adaptable to various spatial requirements, ensuring optimal placement and performance in a wide range of installations.</p>'),
(118, 'Digital Outdoor Temperature Sensor', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.069534', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.069688', 12, 18, 110, 'digital-outdoor-temperature-sensor', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Outdoor Temperature Sensor provides real-time temperature measurements ranging from -67&deg;F to 257&deg;F (-55&deg;C to 125&deg;C), with an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. Its rugged external silicon coating ensures reliability in harsh outdoor environments, making it ideal for various applications requiring precise temperature monitoring. With a resolution of 0.0625&deg;C, this sensor is capable of detecting even the smallest fluctuations in temperature, ensuring accurate and timely data.</p>\n<p>This temperature sensor is compatible with a wide range of monitoring systems, including Room Alert models 32S, 12S, 3S, 32E/W, 12E, 4E, 3E, and 3W. It is available with flexible cable options of 25\', 50\', or 100\' lengths, giving users the flexibility to monitor temperatures over extended distances. The sensor is powered through a monitoring unit, and the RJ-11 cable ensures reliable data transmission, making this sensor a perfect solution for businesses or facilities needing outdoor temperature monitoring in challenging conditions.</p>'),
(119, 'Digital Fluid Temperature Sensor', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.159651', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.159849', 12, 18, 110, 'digital-fluid-temperature-sensor', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Fluid Temperature Sensor is an advanced solution designed to monitor and report real-time fluid temperature with exceptional accuracy and reliability. Capable of measuring temperatures ranging from -67 to 257&deg; Fahrenheit (-55 to 125&deg; Celsius), this sensor is ideal for environments that require precise temperature regulation, such as laboratories, aquariums, and refrigeration systems. Its accuracy within +/- 2&deg;C ensures dependable readings, making it a trusted tool in critical applications.</p>\n<p>Encased in a sealed tube containing Propylene Glycol, the sensor is specifically designed to thrive in extreme conditions. Propylene Glycol\'s non-conductive, colorless properties, coupled with its low freezing and high boiling points, make it an ideal medium for fluid temperature monitoring. This robust design allows for seamless integration into environments where temperature control is vital, ensuring the safety and stability of sensitive materials such as vaccines, plasma, and IV bags.</p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(120, 'Digital Temperature & Humidity', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.385883', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.386047', 12, 18, 110, 'digital-temperature-humidity', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor is a state-of-the-art monitoring solution designed to provide real-time temperature and humidity data with exceptional accuracy and reliability. Capable of measuring temperatures ranging from -40 to 185&deg;F (-40 to 85&deg;C) and humidity levels from 5% to 95% RH, this sensor ensures precise environmental monitoring across a wide range of conditions. Its robust design and high accuracy make it an ideal choice for various environments, from data centers to industrial facilities.</p>\n<p>This digital sensor integrates seamlessly with AVTECH&rsquo;s Room Alert systems, providing continuous monitoring and immediate alerts to ensure critical environments remain within safe parameters. With a resolution of 0.03125&deg;C for temperature and highly accurate humidity readings, the AVTECH Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor is essential for maintaining optimal environmental conditions, preventing potential damages due to fluctuations in temperature and humidity.</p>'),
(121, 'Digital Shielded Temperature & Humidity', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.396314', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.396483', 12, 18, 110, 'digital-shielded-temperature-humidity', '<p>The AVTECH Digital Shielded Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor is a cutting-edge monitoring tool designed to deliver real-time data on environmental conditions, making it an essential component for any Room Alert monitoring system. This dynamic sensor provides precise temperature readings from -40 to 185&deg;F (-40 to 85&deg;C) with an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C, and humidity measurements ranging from 5% to 95% relative humidity (RH) with accuracy within +/- 4.5% at lower humidity levels and +/- 6.5% at higher levels. Ideal for environments with high electrical noise or electromagnetic interference (EMI), the shielded cable ensures reliable data transmission.</p>\n<p>This plug-and-play sensor connects effortlessly to Room Alert monitors via an RJ-11 jack, making setup quick and straightforward. Its robust design and reliable performance make it a valuable asset for maintaining optimal environmental conditions in server rooms, data centers, and other sensitive areas. By logging data and triggering alerts or corrective actions when thresholds are breached, this sensor helps prevent potential damage to equipment and maintains the integrity of monitored spaces.</p>'),
(122, 'HONEYWELL SYSTEM SENSOR 882', '2025-01-16 01:15:35.572332', '2025-01-16 01:15:35.572521', 1, 32, 6, 'honeywell-system-sensor-882', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell System Sensor 882 is a highly reliable and efficient beam smoke detector designed for large open areas where standard smoke detectors may not be practical. Featuring advanced optics and a user-friendly interface, it ensures rapid smoke detection with minimal false alarms. Perfect for warehouses, atriums, and other expansive spaces, this innovative device supports integration into modern fire alarm systems for comprehensive fire protection. Whether for commercial or industrial use, the System Sensor 882 provides an optimal solution for safeguarding your environment.</span></p>'),
(123, 'HONEYWELL SYSTEM SENSOR 885', '2025-01-16 01:36:17.233629', '2025-01-16 01:36:17.233806', 1, 32, 6, 'honeywell-system-sensor-885', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell System Sensor 885 is a highly efficient and durable conventional audible/visual device designed to enhance fire safety systems. Known for its reliable performance, the device provides both sound and visual alerts, ensuring prompt evacuation during emergencies. Its robust design and compatibility with various fire alarm systems make it an ideal choice for commercial and industrial applications in the Philippines. As a trusted supplier and contractor of fire detection and alarm systems nationwide, we offer the System Sensor 885 to help you meet safety compliance standards while protecting lives and property.</span></p>'),
(124, 'HONEYWELL M400K', '2025-01-16 02:08:34.502672', '2025-01-16 02:08:34.502845', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-m400k', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell M400K Conventional Fire Alarm Control Panel offers reliable and efficient fire detection for small to medium-sized installations. Designed for optimal performance, it integrates advanced monitoring with easy-to-use features, ensuring quick response times during emergencies. As a trusted choice for fire protection, this panel delivers superior safety, durability, and seamless compatibility with Honeywell\'s wide range of fire detection devices. Ideal for contractors and suppliers in the Philippines, it meets the stringent demands of various industries while promoting peace of mind.</span></p>'),
(125, 'HONEYWELL SYS-HS', '2025-01-16 02:20:41.819563', '2025-01-16 02:20:41.819725', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-sys-hs', '<p>The <strong>HONEYWELL SYS-HS</strong> is a state-of-the-art notification device designed to meet the highest safety standards in fire alarm and emergency systems. It integrates seamlessly into any environment, providing clear and effective audible and visual alerts through its advanced horns and strobes. The SYS-HS ensures timely evacuation and alert notifications, making it a critical component for safety in commercial, industrial, and residential buildings.</p>\n<p>With a focus on flexibility and ease of use, the HONEYWELL SYS-HS stands out as a leader in the industry. Its innovative design allows for quick installation and compatibility with various fire alarm systems. Whether you need a standalone unit or a system-wide integration, the SYS-HS delivers reliable performance and peace of mind in emergencies.</p>'),
(126, 'HONEYWELL 002-492-222', '2025-01-16 02:29:27.420691', '2025-01-16 02:29:27.420865', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-002-492-222', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>Honeywell 002-492-222 Conventional Fire Alarm Systems are designed to provide reliable and efficient fire detection for various applications. These systems feature advanced conventional technology, ensuring accurate detection and rapid response to fire hazards, making them ideal for small to medium-sized facilities. With Honeywell\'s trusted reputation for safety and innovation, the 002-492-222 Conventional Fire Alarm System offers robust performance, easy installation, and integration capabilities, providing peace of mind for businesses across the Philippines.</span></p>'),
(127, 'HONEYWELL HM-FHSE-UL', '2025-01-16 02:40:46.543331', '2025-01-16 02:40:46.543538', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-hm-fhse-ul', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HM-FHSE-UL Honeywell Addressable Smoke Detector is a high-performance, reliable safety solution designed for advanced fire detection in commercial and residential settings. Featuring an addressable interface, this smoke detector provides precise location identification, ensuring quicker response times during emergencies. It is UL-listed for optimal safety and compliance, making it an essential choice for those seeking dependable fire protection. With its advanced sensing technology and easy integration into existing fire alarm systems, the HM-FHSE-UL ensures enhanced safety and peace of mind. Ideal for both new installations and upgrades, it offers exceptional performance in diverse environments.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>'),
(128, 'HONEYWELL MHR/1', '2025-01-16 02:48:56.285166', '2025-01-16 02:48:56.285324', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-mhr-1', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MHR/1 Honeywell Addressable System offers advanced fire alarm detection and control for commercial and industrial applications. Known for its high reliability and precise detection capabilities, this addressable fire alarm system enables quick identification and location of fire hazards. The MHR/1 ensures rapid response times and enhanced safety, offering users the flexibility of integration with various building systems. Its customizable features make it ideal for large-scale installations, providing continuous monitoring and robust protection. Perfect for businesses that prioritize the safety and security of their buildings, the Honeywell MHR/1 delivers peace of mind with cutting-edge technology.</span></p>'),
(129, 'HONEYWELL HM/MCP/GLASS/UL', '2025-01-16 03:03:19.487370', '2025-01-16 03:03:19.487511', 1, 32, 5, 'honeywell-hm-mcp-glass-ul', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell Addressable HM/MCP/GLASS/UL system offers advanced fire alarm technology with superior reliability and performance. This high-quality, addressable control panel integrates seamlessly with Honeywell&rsquo;s range of detectors and devices, providing precise monitoring and rapid response in commercial and industrial environments. Designed with UL certification, the system ensures compliance with the highest safety standards. Featuring a glass design for enhanced durability and an intuitive user interface, the Honeywell Addressable system delivers optimized control, robust security, and seamless integration for a wide range of applications. Ideal for modern fire safety needs, it enhances safety, efficiency, and peace of mind.</span></p>'),
(130, 'HONEYWELL HML/PTSE', '2025-01-16 03:14:44.530887', '2025-01-16 03:14:44.531140', 1, 32, 2, 'honeywell-hml-ptse', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Honeywell Addressable systems offer advanced fire detection solutions, providing precise monitoring and control for fire safety. These systems utilize cutting-edge technology, enabling real-time communication between detectors and the central panel. Ideal for large and complex buildings, Honeywell\'s addressable systems enhance efficiency by pinpointing the exact location of a fire or hazard, ensuring faster response times and minimizing potential damage. Trusted by industries worldwide, these systems are designed for reliability, scalability, and compliance with stringent safety standards, making them an essential choice for modern fire safety management.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>'),
(131, 'HONEYWELL B/401 ', '2025-01-16 03:22:26.458094', '2025-01-16 03:22:26.458348', 1, 32, 1, 'honeywell-b-401', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell B/401 Addressable system offers advanced, reliable solutions for fire detection and control, providing businesses with precise monitoring and quick response times. Designed for easy integration, this addressable fire alarm system ensures improved safety and operational efficiency. With its advanced technology, the B/401 allows for pinpoint detection and real-time reporting, making it ideal for commercial and industrial properties. Its customizable features, including network connectivity and compatibility with other Honeywell devices, ensure seamless operation and enhanced protection. Choose the Honeywell B/401 for a dependable, future-ready fire detection solution.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>'),
