(156, 'SIMPLEX CONVENTION MBA-624C', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.796980', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.797114', 1, 34, 1, 'simplex-convention-mba-624c', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The MBA-624C Simplex Conventional Manual Pull Station is a durable and user-friendly fire alarm activation device designed to provide a reliable means of initiating an emergency response. Featuring a sturdy construction and a clear, intuitive design, this pull station is ideal for use in commercial and industrial settings. When integrated into a conventional fire alarm system, the MBA-624C allows users to quickly and easily trigger the alarm, ensuring prompt notification in case of a fire emergency. Its straightforward installation and maintenance make it a cost-effective solution for enhancing fire safety and protecting both people and property from fire-related dangers.</span></p>'),
(157, 'SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4098-9714', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.845398', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.845584', 1, 34, 7, 'simplex-addressable-4098-9714', '<p>The Simplex 4098-9714 Addressable TrueAlarm Photoelectric Smoke Sensor is designed to provide reliable and accurate smoke detection in various environments. Utilizing a stable, pulsed infrared LED light source and a silicon photodiode receiver, the sensor delivers consistent low power smoke sensing to enhance safety. The sensor features seven selectable sensitivity levels, ranging from 0.2% to 3.7% per foot of smoke obscuration, which ensures precision in detecting potential smoke conditions. The selected sensitivity level is monitored through the fire alarm control panel, offering flexibility and ease of use for system operators. This sensor is ideal for use in buildings where rapid detection and response are crucial, contributing to enhanced fire safety measures.</p>\n<p>With its advanced photoelectric sensing technology, the Simplex 4098-9714 provides a high level of reliability and low maintenance requirements. The ability to adjust sensitivity levels allows the sensor to adapt to different environmental conditions, making it suitable for various applications, including commercial and industrial buildings. Its accuracy in smoke detection ensures that fire alarms are triggered in a timely manner, reducing the risk of fire-related hazards. The Simplex 4098-9714 is engineered for easy integration into addressable fire alarm systems, improving the overall effectiveness of fire safety infrastructure.</p>'),
(158, 'SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4098-9733', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.862593', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.862763', 1, 34, 7, 'simplex-addressable-4098-9733', '<p>The SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4098-9733 is an advanced TrueAlarm heat sensor designed to offer high reliability and rapid response in detecting heat variations in fire alarm systems. This self-restoring sensor is engineered with a fixed temperature sensing capability, making it ideal for environments where accurate temperature monitoring is crucial. Equipped with the option for rate-of-rise temperature sensing, the 4098-9733 adapts to various fire detection requirements, providing versatility in both residential and commercial settings.</p>\n<p>With its small thermal mass, the SIMPLEX 4098-9733 heat sensor can quickly and precisely measure the surrounding temperature, ensuring timely alerts to the fire alarm control panel. Its ability to restore itself after detecting a temperature anomaly allows for minimal maintenance and ensures long-term performance. As part of the SIMPLEX Addressable series, the 4098-9733 is compatible with a wide range of fire detection systems, contributing to enhanced safety and operational efficiency.</p>'),
(159, 'SIMPLEX CONVENTIONAL 4100ES', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.201236', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.201515', 1, 34, 1, 'simplex-conventional-4100es', '<p>The SIMPLEX CONVENTIONAL 4100ES is a fire detection and control panel that provides exceptional flexibility and reliability for a variety of fire protection needs. With a wide range of installation, operator, and service features, this system is designed to offer reliable fire safety solutions for both small and large-scale applications. The 4100ES Series is equipped with advanced point and module capacities, making it a versatile choice for a wide array of fire detection and alarm systems.</p>\n<p>Whether you\'re designing a system for a commercial building, industrial site, or other facilities, the SIMPLEX 4100ES offers user-friendly operation and efficient serviceability. It combines high-performance capabilities with intuitive controls, allowing seamless installation and operation. With its extensive features, this fire control panel offers peace of mind, knowing your environment is safeguarded with cutting-edge fire protection technology.</p>'),
(160, 'SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4098-9792', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.304360', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.304539', 1, 34, 7, 'simplex-addressable-4098-9792', '<p>The SIMPLEX Addressable Sensor 4098-9792 is a cutting-edge fire detection device designed for superior performance in modern fire alarm systems. Its addressable capability allows each sensor to be precisely identified within an integrated network, providing real-time monitoring and swift pinpointing of potential fire hazards. This sensor uses advanced smoke and heat detection technology to ensure the utmost accuracy in identifying fire threats, providing timely alerts to mitigate damage and save lives.</p>\n<p>The 4098-9792 is engineered to minimize false alarms, offering configurable detection thresholds that can be tailored to meet the unique needs of different environments. Whether installed in commercial buildings, industrial facilities, or residential complexes, the sensor delivers reliable and efficient fire detection, enhancing the overall safety and effectiveness of fire protection systems. Its user-friendly addressable system ensures ease of maintenance and quick diagnostics, making it an essential component in any advanced fire detection infrastructure.</p>'),
(161, 'SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4099-9002', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.378655', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.378819', 1, 34, 7, 'simplex-addressable-4099-9002', '<p>The SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 4099-9002 is a state-of-the-art device designed for use in advanced fire detection and alarm systems. Engineered to integrate seamlessly into addressable fire alarm networks, it provides precise identification and real-time monitoring of individual components. This device supports advanced communication protocols, which allow for rapid fault detection and alarm transmission to the central control panel. With its addressable capability, the 4099-9002 eliminates the need for manual troubleshooting, reducing maintenance time and improving system reliability. Whether in large-scale commercial or industrial installations, this device is built to ensure effective fire safety management.</p>\n<p>Designed for both ease of installation and operational reliability, the 4099-9002 is an indispensable part of modern fire alarm systems. It is specifically crafted to support the needs of complex fire detection networks where speed and accuracy are crucial. The robust construction and advanced technology make this device a long-lasting and dependable component in any fire safety infrastructure. Ideal for enhancing the performance and reliability of addressable fire alarm systems, the SIMPLEX 4099-9002 is a must-have for facilities requiring precision, efficiency, and quick response times in fire emergencies.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(162, 'SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 49AV-WRF ', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.708386', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.708572', 1, 34, 6, 'simplex-addressable-49av-wrf', '<p>The SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 49AV-WRF is a cutting-edge fire alarm device designed to enhance safety and streamline communication in modern fire protection systems. This wall-mounted unit integrates seamlessly into addressable fire alarm networks, providing precise and dependable fire detection. Its robust design ensures durability, making it ideal for a range of environments, from commercial spaces to industrial facilities. Equipped with both audio and visual alert mechanisms, the 49AV-WRF ensures comprehensive and immediate notifications, enhancing occupant safety during emergencies.</p>\n<p>Engineered with an advanced addressable protocol, the 49AV-WRF allows direct communication with the fire alarm control panel, facilitating quick and accurate responses to fire events. The sleek design of the device not only complements various architectural settings but also withstands the rigors of industrial use. By offering reliable performance and comprehensive alerts, the SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 49AV-WRF stands out as an essential component in modern fire safety systems.</p>'),
(163, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SD-651', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.724259', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.724565', 1, 35, 2, 'notifier-conventional-sd-651', '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SD-651 Plug-in Smoke Detector offers exceptional performance in a compact design, making it an ideal choice for various fire alarm systems. With a depth of only 2 inches (5.1 cm), it provides an efficient and reliable solution for smoke detection without taking up unnecessary space. Featuring a photoelectric sensor, the SD-651 is designed to respond quickly to the presence of smoke, providing crucial time for alerts and ensuring safety in residential, commercial, and industrial spaces. This detector is compatible with various adapter bases, offering versatility in wiring configurations and voltages.</p>\n<p>The SD-651&rsquo;s reliability and ease of installation make it a go-to choice for fire alarm systems, providing peace of mind with its high-performance capabilities. Designed for both new installations and system upgrades, it&rsquo;s built to last and deliver consistent results. The detector meets the highest industry standards, ensuring superior detection accuracy. It is an excellent addition to any fire safety plan, offering long-lasting protection and optimal performance.</p>'),
(164, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL 5601P', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.659199', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.659390', 1, 35, 4, 'notifier-conventional-5601p', '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL 5601P is a reliable and versatile 135&deg;F Fixed Temperature/Rate-of-Rise, Single-Circuit Mechanical Heat Detector designed to ensure optimal safety in various environments. Its plain housing and robust construction make it a perfect fit for both commercial and residential applications. As part of the 5600 series, the 5601P is engineered to accommodate diverse installation needs, offering flexibility with its mounting options and compatibility with multiple back box configurations.</p>\n<p>This heat detector features a combination of fixed temperature and rate-of-rise (ROR) activation, ensuring rapid response to sudden temperature changes while also providing restorable ROR elements for efficient field-testing. The 5600 series&rsquo; clear exterior markings, alphanumeric identifiers, and post-activation indicators enhance usability and maintenance, making it an essential component of any comprehensive fire detection system.</p>'),
(165, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL NBG-12', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.336472', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.336646', 1, 35, 5, 'notifier-conventional-nbg-12', '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional NBG-12 is a top-tier manual pull station designed to provide a reliable alarm initiating input signal to conventional Fire Alarm Control Panels and Monitor Modules. Known for its innovative design and durable construction, the NBG-12 series is easy to install, maintain, and operate, making it a preferred choice for various fire safety systems. Its versatile design includes multiple mounting options, ensuring seamless integration into diverse environments.</p>\n<p>With a range of models, including the NBG-12S, NBG-12, NBG-12L, and more, the NBG-12 series caters to specific needs, offering enhanced safety features and operational efficiency. This product ensures immediate and accurate fire alarm activation, contributing to faster emergency responses and increased safety for occupants in residential, commercial, and industrial settings.</p>'),
(166, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SFP-10UDE', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.165833', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.166182', 1, 35, 1, 'notifier-conventional-sfp-10ude', '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional SFP-10UDE is a robust, 10-zone fire alarm control panel designed to provide superior fire protection in commercial and industrial settings. This UL-listed device integrates a digital alarm communicator transmitter (DACT) for seamless communication with remote monitoring sites, ensuring rapid response during emergencies. The panel&rsquo;s user-friendly interface, combined with its remote site upload/download capability, makes it a top choice for safety professionals.</p>\n<p>With its red backbox variant, the SFP-10UDE offers both aesthetic and functional versatility. It features ten Class B Initiating Device Circuits (IDCs) and four Class B Notification Appliance Circuits (NACs), each capable of handling up to 3.0 amps. The system\'s total power capacity of 7.0 amps and compatibility with up to eight ANN-BUS devices highlight its adaptability and scalability. Whether for new installations or upgrades, the SFP-10UDE ensures comprehensive fire detection and alarm communication, making it an indispensable asset for any fire safety strategy.</p>'),
(167, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL P2RL', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.302466', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.302630', 1, 35, 6, 'notifier-conventional-p2rl', '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL is an advanced fire alarm notification device designed to enhance safety with its modern features and ease of installation. Part of the System Sensor L-Series, the P2RL offers a combination of auditory and visual alerts with its integrated horn and strobe functionality, ensuring effective communication during emergencies. Its sleek, modern aesthetics, available in white and red housings, seamlessly blend into various environments while providing reliable performance. The P2RL\'s low current draw ensures energy efficiency, making it a cost-effective solution for a wide range of applications.</p>\n<p>Designed for versatility, the NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL meets diverse application requirements with features like field-selectable candela settings and automatic voltage selection. Its plug-in design with a universal mounting plate simplifies installation, reducing labor costs and the potential for errors. The P2RL is ideal for both new installations and retrofits, offering robust protection with minimal maintenance. With its user-friendly design and advanced functionality, the NOTIFIER P2RL is a top choice for building safety and compliance.</p>'),
(168, 'NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL FSB2000 ', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.003205', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.003378', 1, 35, 1, 'notifier-conventional-fsb2000', '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional FSB2000 is a state-of-the-art, intelligent, addressable reflected beam smoke detector designed to provide exceptional protection in open areas with challenging architectural features. Its innovative design makes it ideal for environments with high and sloping ceilings, as well as wide-open spaces where traditional spot-type smoke detectors are impractical. Engineered for reliability and ease of maintenance, the FSB2000 ensures comprehensive fire detection coverage in locations such as atriums, warehouses, aircraft hangars, and concert halls. With advanced sensing technology, it minimizes false alarms while delivering fast and accurate smoke detection.</p>\n<p>This detector is a critical addition to any fire safety system, offering a robust solution for areas with unique architectural challenges. The NOTIFIER FSB2000 stands out with its durable construction and high-performance capabilities, making it a trusted choice for safeguarding lives and property. Whether for large sporting arenas or enclosed parking facilities, this device provides peace of mind with its dependable and efficient operation.</p>'),
(169, 'NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE FSP-951', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.149520', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.149684', 1, 35, 2, 'notifier-addressable-fsp-951', '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; ADDRESSABLE FSP-951 is a state-of-the-art intelligent plug-in smoke detector designed to deliver superior performance and visual appeal. This advanced detector is a direct replacement for the FSP-851 Series, offering enhanced functionality with a modern, sleek design that seamlessly blends into contemporary settings. The FSP-951 is equipped with an enhanced optical sensing chamber, engineered to detect smoke from a wide range of combustion sources, ensuring compliance with stringent code standards. Its addressable technology allows for precise monitoring and swift response, making it an ideal choice for various applications, from commercial buildings to residential complexes.</p>\n<p>Designed for both performance and aesthetics, the FSP-951 is easy to install and maintain, providing reliable protection without compromising on style. Its advanced sensing technology reduces false alarms while enhancing detection capabilities, ensuring a safer environment. The detector&rsquo;s compatibility with existing NOTIFIER systems makes it a cost-effective upgrade, delivering cutting-edge safety features in a compact, visually appealing package.</p>'),
(170, 'NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE FST-951', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.782436', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.782630', 1, 35, 7, 'notifier-addressable-fst-951', '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; FST-951 Series intelligent thermal detectors offer a perfect blend of performance and aesthetics, making them an ideal choice for modern building systems. Designed as a direct replacement for the FST-851 Series, the FST-951 Series boasts a sleek, contemporary design and advanced thermal detection technology. With its ability to seamlessly integrate into existing systems, this thermal detector is engineered for reliable operation in a variety of environments, ensuring optimal fire safety. The point ID address, set via rotary decimal switches, allows precise detector location identification, contributing to a more efficient safety system.</p>\n<p>These intelligent detectors not only enhance the functionality of fire safety systems but also complement the aesthetics of the building design. Whether retrofitting older systems or incorporating into new builds, the FST-951 provides cutting-edge detection and streamlined integration. The modern design of the FST-951 Series ensures it remains unobtrusive while delivering superior thermal detection. Its advanced technology and ease of installation make it an invaluable asset in maintaining building safety standards.</p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(171, 'NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE NBG-12LX', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.508759', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.508928', 1, 35, 1, 'notifier-addressable-nbg-12lx', '<p>The Notifier NBG-12LX is an advanced, dual-action pull station that features an addressable interface for use with Notifier intelligent control panels, except for the FireWarden series and the NSP25 panel. This pull station requires two motions to activate, ensuring safety by reducing the likelihood of accidental activation. Thanks to its addressable capabilities, the NBG-12LX enables precise location identification of the activated manual station, providing real-time data to the control panel. Designed for reliable and efficient operation, it is an essential component for any fire alarm system seeking advanced features and ease of use.</p>\n<p>The NBG-12LX integrates seamlessly with Notifier\'s intelligent control panels, offering an intuitive and responsive manual activation solution for fire alarm systems. With its dual-action design, the pull station ensures safety and security in high-risk environments. The addressable feature adds a layer of sophistication, allowing fire safety personnel to pinpoint the exact location of an alarm at any given moment. This makes it an ideal choice for commercial and industrial spaces, where precision and reliability are crucial for emergency management.</p>'),
(172, 'NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE SPSRL', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.690084', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.690276', 1, 35, 1, 'notifier-addressable-spsrl', '<p>The Notifier Addressable SPSRL is a high-performance speaker strobe designed for use in fire alarm systems. It combines advanced technology with practical installation features to provide reliable notification and enhanced safety. Featuring a plug-in design, the SPSRL reduces costly ground faults by simplifying installation and improving continuity checks before speakers are plugged in. The device\'s universal mounting plate allows pre-wiring, making the setup process more efficient, while a protective plastic cover helps safeguard the speaker components from potential damage. Ideal for a variety of commercial and industrial applications, the Notifier SPSRL ensures both clear audible alerts and visual notification in the event of an emergency.</p>\n<p>This speaker strobe is engineered to offer superior performance with a focus on ease of installation and longevity. Its design minimizes the risk of installation errors, which can lead to expensive repairs. The Notifier SPSRL&rsquo;s features make it an essential part of any modern fire alarm system, delivering reliable notifications while supporting efficient, hassle-free installation processes. The protective features and advanced technology integrated into the SPSRL ensure it will continue to perform consistently over time, even in demanding environments.</p>'),
(173, 'NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE NFS-3030', '2025-01-20 00:46:55.643253', '2025-01-20 00:49:50.530778', 1, 35, 1, 'notifier-addressable-nfs-3030', '<p>The NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE NFS2-3030 is a state-of-the-art intelligent fire alarm control panel, ideal for large-scale applications requiring robust and reliable fire detection solutions. Part of NOTIFIER\'s renowned ONYX Series, this UL-listed control panel can manage over 3,000 intelligent devices across ten Signaling Line Circuits (SLCs), ensuring comprehensive coverage and protection. Designed for versatility, the NFS2-3030 features a large 640-character LCD backlit display or a displayless option to suit various operational needs.</p>\n<p>With network compatibility through NOTI-FIRE-NET and ONYXWorks, the NFS2-3030 supports up to 200 nodes, making it perfect for complex, interconnected systems. Its built-in degraded mode ensures continued operation during faults, and the optional integrated Digital Voice Command (DVC) enhances emergency communication. Certified for seismic activity and marine applications, this control panel meets diverse industry standards, including FM6320 approved gas detection and Intertek listed FSAE functionality for fire service access elevators.</p>'),
(174, 'EDWARDS CONVENTIONAL 721U ', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.899515', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.899685', 1, 33, 1, 'edwards-conventional-721u', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 721U Edwards Conventional Fire Alarm System is a reliable and cost-effective solution designed to provide essential fire detection and protection for various commercial and industrial settings. Featuring easy-to-install conventional fire alarm panels, the 721U ensures a quick response to fire emergencies through its advanced detection technology. This system is ideal for smaller to mid-sized buildings, offering efficient fire monitoring, reliable alerts, and user-friendly interfaces. With the 721U Edwards Conventional system, businesses can safeguard their property and personnel while maintaining compliance with safety standards.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>'),
(175, 'ALBA CV2124AB OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 01:22:42.508829', '2025-01-20 01:24:33.927338', 6, 16, 56, 'alba-cv2124ab-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ALBA CV2124AB Audio-Video Module is a modern and versatile solution for residential and commercial entry systems. Featuring an ultra-wide-angle 2.3 mm lens, it delivers a vision angle of approximately 110&deg;, ensuring optimal video coverage for enhanced security. Its anodized aluminum construction offers durability and a sleek, modern appearance in a neutral grey finish, making it a seamless addition to any environment. Equipped with a built-in electric door speaker, it allows for efficient communication between visitors and occupants.<br><br>This module supports up to four buttons arranged in two rows, making it ideal for multi-unit residences or offices. Its modular design allows for easy integration into larger systems, while white LED backlighting ensures excellent visibility even in low-light conditions. Measuring 9.1 cm in height, 9.9 cm in width, and 3.7 cm in depth, it is compact yet functional. The ALBA CV2124AB combines sophisticated technology with practical features to provide a reliable and stylish access control solution.</span></p>'),
(176, 'ALBA CT2138AB OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.563602', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.563763', 6, 16, 56, 'alba-ct2138ab-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ALBA CT2138AB Button Module is a versatile and durable accessory designed to expand the functionality of entry systems. Compatible with the ALBA CV2124AB and CA2124AB modules, it supports up to eight additional buttons in a double-call configuration or four in a single-call setup. This modular button module is ideal for multi-residential or commercial properties, offering flexibility and scalability to meet various needs.<br><br>Constructed from anodized aluminum in an elegant grey finish, the CT2138AB ensures durability and a modern aesthetic. It features white LED backlighting for excellent visibility, even in low-light conditions, enhancing usability for all users. Measuring 9.1 cm in height, 9.9 cm in width, and 3.7 cm in depth, this compact module seamlessly integrates into existing systems, combining practicality and style.</span></p>'),
(177, 'SOLVO TD2000R OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.893412', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.893588', 6, 16, 56, 'solvo-td2000r-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000R is a high-performance proximity reader designed for seamless integration with the VIGIK system, offering advanced access control solutions for residential and commercial applications. Constructed with durable steel and coated in an elegant grey finish, this device combines style and functionality to complement any modern environment. It features wall and flush mounting options, ensuring flexibility during installation.<br><br>Equipped with a CMOS 1/3\" camera delivering a resolution of 440,000 pixels and a fixed 3.7 mm focal length lens, the TD2000R ensures reliable visual monitoring. The LCD alphanumeric display and 16 intuitive buttons make navigation and operation straightforward. With an IP45 protection rating, this robust device is built to withstand challenging environmental conditions. Powered via Duo line with a maximum current consumption of 0.40 A, the SOLVO TD2000R is an efficient and reliable solution for your access control needs.</span></p>'),
(178, 'SOLVO TD2000RA OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.388153', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.388312', 6, 16, 56, 'solvo-td2000ra-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000RA is a robust and reliable audio-only access control panel designed for efficiency and durability. Constructed with a high-quality steel body and finished in a sleek grey color, it seamlessly blends into a variety of environments. With its compact dimensions (30.6 cm height, 17 cm width, and 6 cm depth) and wall or flush mounting options, it provides a space-saving and versatile installation solution.<br><br>Equipped with a 16-button keypad and an LCD alphanumeric display, the TD2000RA offers intuitive user interaction and enhanced functionality. Designed with an IP45 rating, it resists dust and splashes, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor applications. Its compatibility with the Duo Line supply system and low current consumption (0.30 A) ensures energy efficiency. At just 2.2 kg, it offers a lightweight yet durable access control solution for residential and commercial use.</span></p>'),
(179, 'AGORA VD2121CAGL OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.007211', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.007396', 6, 16, 56, 'agora-vd2121cagl-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AGORA VD2121CAGL is a compact and sophisticated video door entry system designed for both residential and small commercial spaces. It comes with a durable aluminum and plastic construction, ensuring long-lasting use in various environments. Featuring a sleek aluminum and light grey finish, this modern unit complements any exterior decor. The device includes a built-in color camera, electric door speaker, and a convenient single-button operation, making it user-friendly and efficient for securing your property.<br><br>With its ability to handle up to two calls simultaneously, the AGORA VD2121CAGL provides flexible communication options for homeowners or office settings. Its 20.8 cm height, 9.9 cm width, and 3 cm depth allow for space-saving installation. Powered by a 12 Vac supply voltage, this device offers reliable performance while maintaining energy efficiency. The system also includes a protective cover for added durability and a clear, high-resolution camera feed for optimal security monitoring.</span></p>'),
(180, 'AGORA AGL100TS OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.492154', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.492307', 6, 16, 56, 'agora-agl100ts-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AGORA AGL100TS is a versatile additional module designed to seamlessly integrate with VD2121CAGL or AD2121CAGL systems. Built to support up to 8 call buttons, this module expands the functionality and capacity of your intercom or access control system, making it ideal for residential, commercial, or industrial applications. The AGL100TS comes complete with all necessary connection cables, ensuring a hassle-free installation experience.<br><br>Constructed with premium aluminum and plastic materials, the module features a sleek aluminum and light grey finish, combining durability with modern aesthetics. Its compact dimensions&mdash;20.8 cm in height, 9.9 cm in width, and 3 cm in depth&mdash;allow for easy integration into existing setups. Powered by a reliable 12 Vac supply voltage, this module offers consistent performance for enhanced communication and accessibility.</span></p>'),
(181, 'MATRIX	VD2120CMAS OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.693502', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.693645', 6, 16, 56, 'matrix-vd2120cmas-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX VD2120CMAS audio-video module is a sleek and reliable device designed for modern communication systems. Featuring a fixed 3.6 mm lens color video camera, it offers sharp video quality and enhanced visibility in various environments. This module does not include call buttons, making it ideal for integration into systems where simplicity and streamlined design are prioritized. Constructed from durable stainless steel, it ensures longevity and resistance to wear and tear. Its compact dimensions, measuring 11.5 cm in height and width, allow for easy installation in confined spaces or on sleek surfaces.<br><br>The metal grey finish adds a professional aesthetic, blending seamlessly into contemporary architectural designs. With its robust build and cutting-edge technology, the MATRIX VD2120CMAS is perfect for commercial and residential installations. Whether used for security, access control, or intercom systems, this module delivers exceptional performance and style. It&rsquo;s a dependable solution for customers seeking functionality without unnecessary complexity.</span></p>'),
(182, 'MATRIX MAS24S OUTDOOR', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.106355', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.107553', 6, 16, 56, 'matrix-mas24s-outdoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX MAS24S Additional Call Module is an advanced, durable communication accessory designed for seamless integration with the CD213&hellip;MAS series. Featuring four call buttons, it ensures efficient user interaction and enhances the functionality of intercom systems. Crafted with high-quality stainless steel and finished in sleek metal grey, the module delivers a modern and professional aesthetic. Its compact design, measuring 11.5 cm in height and width, makes it versatile and easy to install in a variety of settings.<br><br>This call module integrates an encoder keys circuit for reliable performance and precise signal transmission. Built to endure daily use in commercial or residential environments, the stainless steel construction ensures durability and resistance to wear. Whether installed in office buildings, residential complexes, or industrial facilities, the MATRIX MAS24S is engineered to provide user-friendly operation and superior functionality in intercom and communication systems.</span></p>'),
(183, 'SE4252 INDOOR', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.389024', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.389477', 6, 16, 56, 'se4252-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE4252 Monitor with Videointercom Functions is a sleek and versatile device designed to enhance modern living spaces with its blend of high-quality design and advanced functionality. Its 7-inch LCD TFT display ensures crystal-clear visuals, making it ideal for managing communication and monitoring security. This hands-free system provides convenience, offering seamless intercommunication calls, auto switch-on activation, and a dedicated door-opening button.<br><br>Engineered for flexibility, the SE4252 features video memory, memo capabilities, and block notes for streamlined operations. With the option to control electrical loads and manage actuators for remote apparatus activation, it integrates effortlessly into smart home setups. Additional expansion possibilities through memory cards and data import/export functions provide adaptability for evolving needs. The SE4252 is not only functional but also aesthetically pleasing, with a clean white finish and compact dimensions that fit into any interior design.</span></p>'),
(184, 'SE400 INDOOR', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.362766', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.362919', 6, 16, 56, 'se400-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE400 Handset accessory is designed to enhance the Sette monitor system by providing a reliable, private communication solution. This versatile handset allows users to engage in confidential conversations while maintaining high-quality audio clarity. Ideal for environments where privacy and discretion are paramount, the SE400 is seamlessly integrated into the Sette system, ensuring smooth connectivity. With a sleek, ergonomic design, the SE400 offers comfort and ease of use, making it a perfect addition to any professional or personal workspace.<br><br>The handset&rsquo;s easy-to-use interface ensures effortless control, and it works with the Sette monitor to provide a clear, uninterrupted audio experience. Whether for business calls, secure discussions, or personal use, the SE400 delivers excellent sound quality. This accessory is essential for those who need a dedicated communication tool for confidential exchanges while working in environments with potential distractions or noise.</span></p>'),
(185, 'ZHERO ZH1262W INDOOR', '2025-01-20 03:32:50.837238', '2025-01-20 03:35:33.047310', 6, 16, 56, 'zhero-zh1262w-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262W White Video Intercom provides a sophisticated, easy-to-use solution for home and office security. Designed with a sleek white exterior, it features a 3.5\" LCD display that delivers clear and vibrant video quality, making it an ideal choice for modern living spaces. The intercom is equipped with soft touch controls, providing a smooth and responsive user experience. Its OSD (On-Screen Display) configuration enables simple customization of the system&rsquo;s settings, ensuring it meets your specific security needs. This system combines style, functionality, and reliability, offering peace of mind with every use.<br><br>With a focus on both practicality and aesthetics, the ZHERO ZH1262W is a perfect addition to any home or workplace. Its intuitive interface and advanced technology ensure seamless communication, whether for security or daily convenience. The video intercom&rsquo;s compact design fits seamlessly into your environment, while its advanced features make it an essential tool for enhanced safety and monitoring. With clear video, easy installation, and user-friendly features, it is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable video intercom solution.</span></p>'),
(186, 'ZHERO ZH1262B INDOOR', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.032863', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.033032', 6, 16, 56, 'zhero-zh1262b-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262B Black Colour Video Intercom is a high-quality communication device designed to enhance security and convenience in both residential and commercial spaces. Featuring a 3.5\" LCD screen, this intercom allows for clear video and audio communication with visitors, ensuring a safe environment. The device comes in a sleek black color that blends well with any modern interior. With soft touch controls and an intuitive OSD (On-Screen Display) configuration, this video intercom is user-friendly and easy to set up. It is a reliable solution for anyone seeking to improve security without compromising on style or functionality.<br><br>This video intercom system offers a range of advanced features, including high-resolution video, making it ideal for clear identification of visitors. The compact design ensures it fits seamlessly into any space, while the soft touch controls enhance usability. The 3.5\" display provides a crisp, detailed image, enabling users to interact with visitors effectively. Designed for ease of use, the OSD configuration allows simple system customization. Whether for home or office use, the ZHERO ZH1262B video intercom is an excellent choice for those seeking a blend of practicality and aesthetics in their security system.</span></p>'),
(187, 'ZHERO ZH1252W (ZHEROS) INDOOR', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.271311', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.271476', 6, 16, 56, 'zhero-zh1252w-zheros-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1252W (ZHEROS) White Color Video Intercom is designed to bring convenience and security to any modern home or office. Featuring a 4-inch display screen, this intercom allows users to communicate and see visitors with clear video quality. The system is easy to set up and use, with a simple 4-button interface for easy navigation and control. The white color design ensures that it will seamlessly blend with any interior decor, adding a sleek and modern touch. The intercom system is programmable through a DIP switch, making customization simple and efficient for a personalized user experience.<br><br>Perfect for a wide range of environments, the ZHERO ZH1252W video intercom is a reliable choice for those seeking both functionality and style. Its compact size, alongside the intuitive 4-inch screen, ensures that users can interact with ease. Whether it\'s for a home or office, the system delivers exceptional video and audio clarity, promoting effective communication. With its straightforward installation and operation, the ZHERO ZH1252W is a top choice for those looking for a practical and stylish video intercom solution. </span></p>'),
(188, 'EXHITO EX362 INDOOR', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.855359', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.855534', 6, 16, 53, 'exhito-ex362-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX362 Intercom is a sleek, modern communication solution designed for convenience and security in any environment. Featuring a compact size with dimensions of 83 x 218 x 62 mm, it offers a clean white plastic finish that easily complements a variety of settings. This intercom comes with seven buttons, six of which are fully programmable, allowing users to tailor the system to meet their specific needs. One of the buttons is dedicated to door opening, enhancing security and ease of access. With its user-friendly design, the EX362 is perfect for both residential and commercial use.<br><br>Equipped with customizable features, the EXHITO EX362 makes communication simple and efficient. Its programmable keys enable quick access to frequently used functions, improving the overall user experience. The intercom&rsquo;s compact size ensures it can fit easily into tight spaces without sacrificing functionality. Whether used for home security or as part of a larger communication network, the EX362 offers reliability and flexibility. The EX362 stands out for its practicality, modern design, and ability to adapt to various user requirements.</span></p>'),
(189, 'EXHITO EX352 INDOOR', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.543630', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.543809', 6, 16, 53, 'exhito-ex352-indoor', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX352 Intercom is a sleek and modern communication device designed to enhance your home or office security and ease of access. Featuring a compact plastic construction in a clean white color, this intercom measures 21.8 cm in height, 6.5 cm in width, and 6.2 cm in depth, making it ideal for a variety of spaces. The EX352 comes equipped with three buttons, including a door opening button for added convenience, ensuring that you can easily communicate and control access to your premises with just a few simple presses. Two of the three buttons are programmable, giving you the flexibility to assign custom functions as per your needs. Whether you\'re at home, in the office, or in a shared space, the EX352 provides reliable, straightforward operation with an emphasis on security.<br><br>With its modern aesthetic and practical features, the EX352 is a perfect choice for those looking to integrate a secure intercom system without compromising on design. Its white color ensures that it blends seamlessly with various interior styles, while the durable plastic material guarantees long-lasting performance. This intercom is not only easy to install but also user-friendly, providing a reliable and convenient way to manage visitors and security. Whether you\'re receiving guests or ensuring safety, the EX352 Intercom delivers optimal performance with simple functionality.</span></p>'),
(190, 'AIPHONE AX SERIES', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.823296', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.823469', 6, 17, 51, 'aiphone-ax-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone AX Series is a versatile intercom and communication system designed to enhance security and efficiency in a wide range of applications. With the ability to connect up to 8 masters and 120 remote stations, the system ensures seamless communication through both PTT (push-to-talk) or VOX (voice-activated) modes. Its advanced features include selective master-to-master calling, priority and standard call levels, and integration with electronic access control and CCTV systems. Offering full privacy during communication and the option for call queuing, the AX Series provides a secure and organized communication environment. Additionally, it supports remote control features, including door release and call transfer to telephones, making it a highly adaptable solution for modern security needs.<br><br>The AX Series is built for flexibility and scalability, ideal for large buildings, campuses, or complexes that require both reliability and customization. It supports composite video output, scan monitoring of remote stations, and a PC interface for programming and event logging. The system can be mounted in a rack or on the wall, and integrates seamlessly with other Aiphone systems such as the IE Series door stations. With optional accessories like headsets, footswitches, and remote PC control, the AX Series is engineered to meet the needs of varied environments while ensuring ease of use and setup. Whether for secure access control, communication privacy, or general convenience, the Aiphone AX Series is a reliable, future-proof solution for sophisticated security systems.</span></p>'),
(191, 'AIPHONE GT SERIES', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.231264', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.231413', 6, 17, 56, 'aiphone-gt-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The AIPHONE GT Series offers an advanced security and communication solution, combining cutting-edge technology with ease of use. Featuring a 3.5&Prime; LCD color monitor, the system ensures clear, high-quality video and audio transmission for home and office security. With hands-free audio communication, users can speak with visitors without needing to pick up a handset, although an optional handset (GT-HS) can be added for privacy. Additional features include door release, PTZ (pan-tilt-zoom) control, and brightness control to adjust video settings for optimal viewing. The system is designed with user convenience in mind, with adjustable call tone and communication volume controls, allowing for customization to suit different environments.<br><br>The sleek white finish of the AIPHONE GT Series blends seamlessly with modern interiors, providing a stylish addition to any space. The system is ideal for residential and commercial properties looking to enhance security, communication, and privacy. The PTZ control and brightness adjustment ensure the system adapts to various lighting conditions, while the door release button provides an added layer of convenience for users. With robust features and simple operation, the AIPHONE GT Series is a perfect solution for those looking for a reliable, high-quality intercom system.</span></p>'),
(192, 'AIPHONE JM SERIES', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.502623', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.502774', 6, 17, 56, 'aiphone-jm-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JM Series is an advanced video intercom system designed for both residential and commercial environments. Equipped with a 7-inch touchscreen panel, the system allows for seamless hands-free (VOX) or handset communication. The high-resolution color TFT LCD screen offers clear video footage with the ability to adjust the camera for optimal positioning and zoom, even compensating for bright lighting conditions. The video system includes memory for up to 20 call records in internal storage, and can store up to 1,000 calls on an SD/SDHC card (sold separately). With a digital PanTilt and Zoom camera featuring a wide-angle 170&deg; lens, blind spots are minimized, ensuring complete coverage.<br><br>For enhanced convenience and control, the JM Series offers integration with additional devices like gates, lights, or extra doors. It also includes 2 N/O door release contacts, with optional expansion for up to four doors. The video out feature allows for easy connection to DVR systems. Whether you need to monitor entries discreetly at night or manage multiple access points, the AIPHONE JM Series delivers security, flexibility, and clarity, making it an ideal solution for modern entry systems. With both homerun or daisy chain wiring options, the system supports up to four door stations and eight internal locations.</span></p>'),
(193, ' AIPHONE JO SERIES', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.428009', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.428151', 6, 17, 56, 'aiphone-jo-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JO Series is an advanced video intercom system designed to streamline visitor identification and enhance security at your door. Featuring a sleek, slim design, the JO Series includes a large 7&rdquo; video screen and touch buttons for easy system control, making it an ideal solution for homes and small businesses. It can accommodate one door station and up to two inside stations, providing flexibility for various setups. With its elegant styling and simple installation, the JO Series ensures both security and convenience.<br><br>The system comes with a ready-to-install box set that includes one door station, one inside station, and a power supply. The 7&rdquo; screen delivers high-quality video, allowing you to clearly identify visitors at locked doors. The 2-conductor wiring simplifies installation, reducing setup time and effort. Ideal for those who need a reliable and user-friendly intercom system, the JO Series is a perfect blend of functionality and modern design.</span></p>'),
(194, 'AIPHONE NA-AN SERIES', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.871511', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.871681', 6, 14, 51, 'aiphone-na-an-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE NA-AN Series is a cutting-edge intercom system designed to enhance communication while maintaining privacy and security. Ideal for residential or commercial settings, this system allows users to connect seamlessly with a master station using a push button to initiate calls. The system features a privacy setting that blocks unwanted monitoring, ensuring confidential conversations remain secure. With hands-free communication upon the master&rsquo;s response, the NA-AN Series ensures ease of use and enhanced functionality. It is also equipped with a latching tone and light that stays active at the master station until the call is answered.<br><br>This intercom system offers both desk and wall-mount options for versatile installation, accommodating various spaces and preferences. Whether mounted to a single gang box or a ring (wall mount), it delivers efficient communication solutions. The call-in LED on the substation stays illuminated until the master answers, providing clear visual cues for users. The system is also equipped with a pre-tone feature when the master station calls any substation, providing an intuitive alert system for incoming communications. AIPHONE\'s NA-AN Series combines reliability, privacy, and convenience in one sleek intercom solution. </span></p>'),
(195, 'AIPHONE NE-JA SERIES', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.871892', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.872125', 6, 17, 56, 'aiphone-ne-ja-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone NE-JA Series Weather-Resistant Stainless Steel Flush-Mount Audio Door Sub Station offers a durable, high-performance solution for outdoor communication in a wide range of environments. Designed for use with the NEM system, this sub station features a sleek stainless-steel faceplate and a slim, flush-mount design that fits seamlessly into a 2-gang box or ring. The weather-resistant construction ensures reliable performance in harsh outdoor conditions, providing clear hands-free communication when the master station answers. The sub station includes an LED indicator that stays lit while the master station is ringing, ensuring clear visibility of incoming calls.<br><br>In addition to its robust design, the NE-JA Series Sub Station includes an optional external output contact closure for activating remote devices, such as a gate or security system, during a call. This feature, available with the separate RY-PA relay, ensures added flexibility for various installations. The push-button operation makes it easy to place a call, while the hands-free communication ensures convenience for the user. The Aiphone NE-JA Series is ideal for residential or commercial applications where secure and clear communication is required at the door or entry point.</span></p>'),
(196, 'PD6500i', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.522211', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.522398', 7, 43, 61, 'pd6500i', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR PD6500i is a top-of-the-line walk-through security solution designed for high-traffic environments. With advanced pinpoint technology and unmatched discrimination features, it excels in providing accurate threat detection while moving large crowds efficiently. Trusted globally in prestigious venues like the Olympic Games, World Cup Events, and Pan-American Games, the PD6500i is also a proven choice for securing international airports, hotels, government buildings, and other sensitive areas. The detector&rsquo;s 33 detection zones, including three laterally and 11 vertically, allow for precise target identification, making it the ultimate choice for security professionals worldwide.<br><br>Built for durability and ease of use, the PD6500i features visual and audible alarms, LED zone indicators, and multi-unit synchronization capabilities. It offers robust performance under various environmental conditions with an operating temperature range of -4&ordm; F to 149&ordm; F and humidity tolerance up to 95%. With a wide range of customizable features including access control and remote management options, this detector ensures optimal safety and efficiency. Additionally, its weatherproof construction and compliance with international safety standards make it a reliable solution for any high-security setting.</span></p>'),
(197, ' Multi Zone', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.833805', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.834142', 7, 43, 62, 'multi-zone', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR Multi Zone is a state-of-the-art walkthrough security solution designed to enhance threat detection while maintaining high throughput. Featuring 20 independent detection zones, this system allows for precise location identification of one or more metal objects simultaneously. Ideal for environments with high traffic, such as airports, public events, and mass transit stations, it ensures optimal security without slowing down pedestrian flow. With user-friendly features like Auto-Scan for environmental noise cancellation and intuitive controls, it delivers accurate and efficient results in any setting.<br><br>The Multi Zone detector also offers advanced functions such as Multi-Unit Synchronization, which allows multiple units to operate in harmony, and customizable visual displays that ensure clear communication with security personnel. Its weatherproof design, robust construction, and compliance with industry standards make it a reliable choice for various security applications. With customizable access control, backup power, and the option for remote management, the GARRETT Multi Zone detector is a versatile and high-performance solution for any high-security venue.</span></p>'),
(198, 'HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG', '2025-01-20 08:41:16.368095', '2025-01-22 02:25:44.693702', 6, 50, 57, 'honeywell-evaclite-pkg', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG is a state-of-the-art voice alarm controller designed for efficient emergency communication in complex environments. Featuring an 8-zone paging station, it integrates seamlessly with fire alarm panels, providing clear, real-time voice communication during emergencies. This system is equipped with a built-in loudspeaker, ensuring that evacuation announcements and alarms are heard clearly throughout the entire area. The EVACLITE PKG is ideal for large buildings, industrial sites, and public spaces, offering critical support in emergency evacuation scenarios.<br><br>Designed for reliable performance, the HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG boasts high-quality sound output with a frequency response range from 20Hz to 20KHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 70 dB. The system supports remote paging via microphone and can handle communication distances of up to 300 meters. With its robust 5A power output capability and low total harmonic distortion, this voice alarm controller provides clear and undistorted audio. Additionally, the unit&rsquo;s compact design makes it a versatile solution that fits into a variety of environments while meeting international safety standards.</span></p>'),
(199, 'HONEYWELL X-NPMS CONFIGURABLE NETWORK PAGING STATION', '2025-01-22 00:44:02.154648', '2025-01-22 02:23:50.668843', 6, 50, 51, 'honeywell-x-npms-configurable-network-paging-station', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL X-NPMS Configurable Network Paging Station is a cutting-edge solution for public address and voice alarm systems, offering powerful communication capabilities in a versatile, user-friendly design. Featuring a 7-inch TFT LCD touchscreen with an intuitive interface, this paging station allows for easy operation and quick setup. With a frequency response range from 50Hz to 15kHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 85dB, the X-NPMS ensures high-quality sound for clear, reliable announcements in any environment. Ideal for a range of applications including schools, hospitals, airports, and other large facilities, the X-NPMS brings advanced voice communication into one compact unit.<br><br>This network-based system operates on a DC 24V power supply and has a low total harmonic distortion (THD) of less than 0.05%, ensuring distortion-free audio performance. The system also includes a built-in 2W monitoring loudspeaker, as well as line input and output capabilities for seamless integration into existing networks. The X-NPMS is designed for reliability, with an operating temperature range from -10&deg;C to 55&deg;C, making it suitable for use in diverse environments. Its sleek design, efficient operation, and superior sound quality make it an excellent choice for any organization in need of a configurable network paging solution.</span></p>'),
(200, 'HONEYWELL X-NPMI CONFIGURABLE NETWORK PAGING CONSOLE', '2025-01-22 01:10:12.612026', '2025-01-22 02:23:36.507236', 6, 50, 57, 'honeywell-x-npmi-configurable-network-paging-console', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell X-NPMI Configurable Network Paging Console is a versatile and essential component of the X-618 Digital Public Address and Voice Alarm System. Designed for seamless communication and monitoring in complex environments, this console offers full duplex communication, paging capabilities, and customizable functions that enhance operational efficiency. Equipped with a touch screen interface, the console provides intuitive controls for adjusting settings such as audio input, frequency response, and microphone levels. Whether used for emergency alerts, public announcements, or routine communications, the X-NPMI ensures that your messages are delivered with clarity and precision.</span></p>'),
(201, 'HONEYWELL L-PHP15A HORN LOUDSPEAKER', '2025-01-22 01:17:33.907234', '2025-01-22 02:23:22.005614', 6, 50, 54, 'honeywell-l-php15a-horn-loudspeaker', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker is a compact, high-performance sound system designed for outdoor environments. With a rated power of 15W and a maximum power output of 25W, this horn loudspeaker delivers clear, powerful sound while maintaining an unobtrusive appearance. Its low-profile design and white cover allow it to blend seamlessly into a variety of outdoor settings, making it an ideal choice for applications where aesthetics and performance must go hand-in-hand. This versatile loudspeaker is perfect for public address systems, alert notifications, and general audio broadcasting in open-air locations such as parks, campuses, and building exteriors.<br><br>Featuring a wide frequency range of 350 Hz to 8 kHz and a sound pressure level of 115 dB at 15W, the L-PHP15A ensures your message will be heard with clarity, even in noisy environments. Its dispersion angle of 140&deg; at 1 kHz ensures broad coverage, allowing for even distribution of sound across large areas. Designed for reliable outdoor performance, the speaker supports both 100V and 70V systems and offers adjustable power tapping for flexible installation. Whether used for emergency alerts or public announcements, the Honeywell L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker guarantees exceptional sound quality and durability.<br></span></p>'),
(202, 'HONEYWELL L-PWP10A  CABINET LOUDSPEAKER', '2025-01-22 01:28:26.515750', '2025-01-22 02:23:09.996238', 6, 50, 54, 'honeywell-l-pwp10a-cabinet-loudspeaker', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PWP10A Cabinet Loudspeaker is a 10W speaker designed for general public address applications, making it perfect for use in environments like shopping malls, supermarkets, office buildings, educational institutions, hotels, and restaurants. This loudspeaker offers high sound pressure levels and a broad frequency range, ensuring clear and natural audio reproduction for both voice and music. Whether used for background music, public announcements, or emergency alerts, the L-PWP10A guarantees excellent sound quality even in larger spaces or noisy environments. The speaker features power taps for both 100V and 70V systems, offering flexibility in various installations and helping businesses customize their audio setup for different requirements.<br><br>In addition to its outstanding sound capabilities, the L-PWP10A is built with durability and reliability in mind. Its high linearity anti-fatigue rubber construction enhances bass performance and prevents distortion during extended low-frequency operation. The speaker&rsquo;s wide dispersion angle of 170&deg; ensures that audio reaches a large area, making it ideal for spaces where sound coverage is important. Whether you\'re installing it in a restaurant, office, or retail environment, the Honeywell L-PWP10A offers an exceptional audio experience with long-lasting performance.</span></p>'),
(203, 'HONEYWELL L-PCM06B  CEILING LOUDSPEAKER ', '2025-01-22 01:38:45.699714', '2025-01-22 02:22:54.836333', 6, 50, 54, 'honeywell-l-pcm06b-ceiling-loudspeaker', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker offers a cost-effective and high-performance audio solution for a variety of indoor environments. Designed to deliver clear and full-range sound, it features a sleek, low-profile, white enclosure that seamlessly blends into various interior designs, making it ideal for hotels, warehouses, schools, office buildings, stadiums, and restaurants. With a rated power of 6W and a maximum power of 9W, this speaker ensures high-quality audio without distortion, even in larger spaces or areas with background noise. The speaker also offers a wide frequency response range of 110 Hz to 20 kHz, ensuring it can reproduce a broad spectrum of sound, from deep bass to crisp high frequencies.<br><br>The L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker is equipped with power taps for both 100V and 70V systems, providing flexibility for various installation requirements. With a dispersion angle of 180&deg; at 1 kHz, it delivers wide, even coverage, ensuring that audio reaches all corners of the room. The speaker&rsquo;s high sound pressure levels, up to 102 dB at 10W, guarantee that audio is audible and clear, even in larger, more acoustically challenging environments. Combining affordability with impressive audio performance, the Honeywell L-PCM06B is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable and aesthetically pleasing ceiling-mounted speaker for commercial spaces.<br></span></p>'),
(204, 'HONEYWELL L-POM20A  COLUMN SPEAKER ', '2025-01-22 01:51:02.441536', '2025-01-22 02:22:32.376634', 6, 50, 54, 'honeywell-l-pom20a-column-speaker', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-POM20A Column Speaker is a high-performance 20W public address loudspeaker designed for outdoor use and emergency broadcasting. With a robust construction, it offers superior sound quality, a broad frequency response range, and high sound pressure levels, ensuring clear and intelligible broadcasts of evacuation messages and high-fidelity sound reproduction. The speaker&rsquo;s low-profile, white design allows it to blend seamlessly into a variety of interior environments, including hotels, conference rooms, cinemas, and exhibitions. Its rugged, aluminum enclosure ensures durability, while its fire-resistant cable and high-temperature ceramic wiring connector provide additional protection during fire emergencies.<br><br>In addition to its premium audio performance, the L-POM20A Column Speaker is built with safety and reliability in mind. Its aluminum swivel bracket is corrosion-resistant, adding to the speaker\'s durability in challenging environments. The speaker also features multiple power taps at 100V (20W, 10W, 5W, and 2.5W) for flexible installation options, allowing it to adapt to various sound distribution needs. The integrated temperature fuse ensures protection against overheating, extending the speaker&rsquo;s operational life and safeguarding it from potential damage. With its excellent sound performance and safety features, the Honeywell L-POM20A is a perfect choice for critical communication in both normal and emergency situations.<br></span></p>'),
(205, 'HONEYWELL X-MAP4P  DIGITAL AUDIO PLAYER ', '2025-01-22 02:07:20.951834', '2025-01-22 02:22:17.901971', 6, 50, 54, 'honeywell-x-map4p-digital-audio-player', '<p>The HONEYWELL X-MAP4P Digital Audio Player is a versatile and powerful audio solution designed to integrate seamlessly with modern audio systems. It supports a wide range of audio sources, including SD cards, USB drives, and an FM tuner, along with up-to-date Bluetooth connectivity. This makes it ideal for both professional and personal use, allowing users to play music across two separate zones simultaneously. With its support for popular file formats like MP3 and WAV, it ensures high-quality audio playback for diverse media needs.</p>\n<p>Equipped with dual stereo sound RCA outputs and a mix audio RCA output, the X-MAP4P offers flexible audio distribution options. It connects easily to voice alarm systems via a Cinch audio connection, enhancing its utility in commercial settings. The unit is designed for easy integration with existing systems, featuring a compact and durable build that fits conveniently in standard audio racks. Its robust power supply and precise output controls make it a reliable choice for consistent audio performance.</p>'),
(206, 'AIPHONE ACO2-MF', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.554971', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.555128', 6, 17, 56, 'aiphone-aco2-mf', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ACO2-MF is an advanced RFID Access Control system designed to elevate security and management in hotel environments. Made from high-quality 304# stainless steel, this sleek and modern reader ensures durability and a premium aesthetic. It seamlessly integrates with hotel locking systems and is fully compatible with existing hotel locking software. The ACO2-MF provides an easy and secure way for authorized guests to access hotel doors using RFID technology. With the added benefit of a valid guest card, only those with permission can enter, preventing unauthorized access and boosting overall hotel security.<br><br>The RFID Access Control system works in tandem with electric drop bolts or electromagnetic locks, offering versatility and flexibility in access control solutions. Its intuitive design and robust features ensure that it meets the security needs of modern hotels. The system&rsquo;s compatibility with the hotel&rsquo;s lock software makes it a hassle-free addition, while the durable stainless steel construction ensures that it will stand the test of time. The ACO2-MF is an essential tool for any hotel looking to provide a safe, secure, and modern environment for its guests.</span></p>'),
(207, 'DAOSAFE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q10', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.003984', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.004132', 8, 51, 70, 'daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q10', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q10 is a high-security, durable access control solution designed to manage pedestrian flow with ease. This tripod turnstile ensures that only one person can pass at a time, preventing unauthorized trailing and enhancing security. Featuring a sleek, classic design in black and white, it suits both high-end commercial environments and modern installations. The DS-Q10 is equipped with a clear LED indicator, with green and red lights that show whether entry is permitted or denied. Its waterproof construction makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, ensuring versatility in various settings.<br><br>This turnstile integrates seamlessly with any type of access control system, offering smooth integration for enhanced security and convenience. It can be customized with different logos, appearance colors, and dimensions to suit specific installation environments. Ideal for offices, stadiums, corporate buildings, and other high-traffic areas, the DS-Q10 stands out as a reliable solution for controlling access while maintaining aesthetic appeal.<br></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_product` (`id`, `product_name`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `system_id`, `brand_id`, `category_id`, `product_slug`, `short_description`) VALUES
(208, 'DAOSAFE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q50', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.476475', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.476668', 8, 51, 70, 'daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q50', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q50 is a compact, cost-effective solution designed to provide high security while maintaining an elegant, slim profile. At only 3802801000mm, the DS-Q50 is ideal for installations in tight spaces, offering an efficient way to control access without compromising on security. Its sleek black and white design fits seamlessly into modern or high-end environments, making it perfect for a wide range of applications. The turnstile ensures that only one person can pass at a time, effectively preventing unauthorized trailing.<br><br>Built to be versatile and durable, the DS-Q50 features a waterproof design that allows it to be used both indoors and outdoors. It integrates easily with any type of access control system, providing a smooth and secure entry experience. Customization options for the logo, appearance color, and dimensions allow it to adapt perfectly to the specific needs of your installation environment, whether for corporate offices, luxury buildings, or other high-traffic areas.</span></p>'),
(209, 'DAOSAFE Tripod Turnstile DS112', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.009977', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.010124', 8, 51, 70, 'daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds112', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Tripod Turnstile DS112 offers a perfect blend of high security and elegant access control, making it an ideal solution for both high-traffic and upscale environments. With a throughput rate of 35-40 persons per minute, it efficiently manages pedestrian flow while ensuring secure, single-user access. The turnstile&rsquo;s robust construction features full brushed stainless steel for a sleek, anti-rust, and durable body that can withstand harsh weather conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications.<br><br>Designed for easy integration, the DS112 allows for the mounting of access control devices and controllers on the flat top area, offering convenience and flexibility for installation. The visual LED indication strips on both the front and back enhance visibility, making it not only functional but also an attractive addition to any space. The turnstile supports both single-direction and bi-directional modes, providing versatility for various security needs. This durable and stylish turnstile is the perfect choice for any facility looking for efficient, secure, and aesthetically pleasing access control solutions.<br></span></p>'),
(211, 'DAOSAFE Optical Turnstile DS-Q20', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.413965', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.414132', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds-q20', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q20 Quantum Optical Swing Turnstile is a sophisticated access control solution designed to manage pedestrian traffic in high-traffic areas with ease and efficiency. Featuring a 1100mm wide passageway, the DS-Q20 allows for wheelchair access, large packages, and emergency situations, making it versatile for a variety of environments. With its sleek and timeless design in classic black and white, it fits seamlessly into upscale applications, offering both functionality and elegance. This turnstile features LED indicators that clearly display whether passage is allowed or denied, enhancing the user experience.<br><br>The DS-Q20 is designed for both indoor and outdoor use and supports integration with a variety of access control systems for seamless security management. It meets fire safety requirements, with arms that automatically open in the event of an emergency. The turnstile can also be customized with different logos, colors, and dimensions to suit specific installation environments. Ideal for offices, airports, and other high-traffic facilities, the DS-Q20 offers both security and convenience in managing pedestrian flow.</span></p>'),
(212, 'DAOSAFE Optical Turnstile DS205A', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.390786', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.390950', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds205a', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Optical Swing Turnstile DS205A is a sleek and efficient access control solution designed for both indoor and outdoor restricted areas. With its bi-directional functionality, this turnstile effectively manages the flow of pedestrians in both directions, ensuring smooth entry and exit in high-traffic areas. Constructed from brushed stainless steel for durability and aesthetic appeal, the DS205A offers a compact design that fits seamlessly into any modern facility. The turnstile&rsquo;s arms are made of either plexiglas or stainless steel, based on customer preference, offering versatility and customization.<br><br>The DS205A also accommodates a variety of users, with a passage width of up to 900mm, allowing for easy access for wheelchair users, people with large luggage, bicycles, and prams. Though it features a slim and compact body, which limits the installation of external devices such as biometric scanners or card collectors, this turnstile is typically used in manual settings for more straightforward access control. Its simplicity and functionality make it an excellent choice for applications in retail environments like shops and supermarkets, where pedestrian flow management and security are essential.<br></span></p>'),
(213, 'DAOSAFE Optical Turnstile DSN-20', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.292261', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.292409', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-turnstile-dsn-20', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Optical Swing Turnstile DSN-20, also known as the Nebula model, offers a sophisticated and efficient solution for managing pedestrian access in both indoor and outdoor settings. With a passage width ranging from 650mm to 1100mm, this turnstile accommodates a wide variety of users, including individuals with wheelchairs, people carrying luggage, or other large items. The DSN-20 combines modern, stylish design elements, such as a sleek cabinet, brushed stainless steel body, and attractive blue LED strips, with high-quality materials and cutting-edge technology for reliable security management.<br><br>This turnstile integrates seamlessly with a variety of third-party access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint, or biometric reader devices, making it a versatile option for facilities with advanced security needs. The DSN-20 features a high-end black painting process and superior production techniques, ensuring a premium finish and long-lasting durability. Ideal for locations such as airports, corporate buildings, and other high-traffic areas, the DSN-20 provides both functionality and aesthetic appeal, all while ensuring a smooth and secure passage for all users.</span></p>'),
(214, 'DAOSAFE Optical Flap Turnstile DS-Q30', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.392681', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.392968', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds-q30', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q30 Quantum Optical Flap Turnstile is a robust and reliable access control solution designed for high-traffic areas. Capable of processing up to 45 persons per minute, it is ideal for locations like metro stations, office buildings, and other venues with large numbers of visitors. The turnstile&rsquo;s sleek design, available in classic black and white, is both elegant and timeless, making it suitable for upscale environments. Equipped with green and red LED indicators, the DS-Q30 ensures clear communication of access status, enhancing user experience.<br><br>The DS-Q30 also meets fire safety regulations, with its arms automatically retracting in the event of an emergency to allow quick evacuation. It supports integration with various access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint, and biometric devices, offering flexibility for diverse security needs. Additionally, the turnstile can be customized with different logos, appearance colors, and dimensions, making it adaptable to any installation environment while maintaining a high standard of security and functionality.</span></p>'),
(215, 'DAOSAFE Optical Flap Turnstile DSN-30', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.369086', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.369259', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-dsn-30', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DSN-30 Nebula Optical Flap Turnstile is a high-performance access control solution designed for environments with heavy pedestrian traffic. With an impressive throughput of up to 45 persons per minute, it ensures smooth and fast access, making it ideal for locations with high visitor flow such as metro stations, airports, and office buildings. Featuring a sleek, modern design with a stylish urban cabinet, brushed stainless steel body, and high-end black painting, the DSN-30 is both functional and aesthetically pleasing, enhancing the look of any installation.<br><br>This turnstile supports bi-directional operation, allowing for controlled entry and exit in both directions, further increasing its versatility. Equipped with an attractive blue LED strip and a standard relay signal, it is easily integrated with various third-party access control systems, including RFID and fingerprint readers. The DSN-30 is built with durability in mind, ensuring reliable performance even in the most demanding environments. Its sleek design and advanced features make it a top choice for facilities looking for an efficient and stylish security solution.</span></p>'),
(216, 'DAOSAFE Optical Flap Turnstile DS3000', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.325629', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.325879', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds3000', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS3000 Optical Flap Turnstile offers a sophisticated and highly functional solution for managing pedestrian access in high-end environments. Designed for both indoor and outdoor use, this turnstile is perfect for locations such as college campuses, office buildings, and corporate headquarters. With a throughput rate of 40-45 persons per minute, the DS3000 ensures smooth and efficient access control, even in high-traffic areas. Its sleek design, made from full brushed stainless steel with black accents, combines durability and elegance, making it suitable for upscale installations.<br><br>This turnstile is equipped with a range of advanced features, including a bright, long, slim LED indication bar for clear access status signaling. The DS3000 is also fitted with infrared sensors for enhanced security, which help prevent unauthorized access or tampering. The system supports both single and bi-directional functionality, allowing for flexible use depending on the specific access requirements of your site. Additionally, the DS3000 features seamless integration with third-party access control systems, such as RFID or fingerprint scanners, offering a high level of adaptability for various security setups.</span></p>'),
(217, 'DAOSAFE Full Height Turnstile DS411', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.515822', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.515989', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds411', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS411 Full Height Turnstile is a robust access control solution designed to provide maximum security in high-risk environments such as prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. Built for both indoor and outdoor use, it features a strong construction made of finished and brushed stainless steel, ensuring resistance to corrosion, weather conditions, and physical wear. The DS411 provides single or bi-directional passage control, making it versatile for a wide range of applications. The system is designed to integrate seamlessly with various access control devices like RFID readers, fingerprint scanners, coin inserts, and more, ensuring flexibility and adaptability for different security needs.<br><br>Equipped with LED indicators on the top cover and side, the DS411 provides clear visual feedback on access status, indicating whether entry is accepted or denied. The turnstile\'s arm can rotate either 120&deg; or 90&deg;, depending on the configuration chosen, allowing for efficient and secure management of pedestrian flow. This full-height turnstile is ideal for high-security sites, offering both safety and ease of integration with other security technologies, making it an essential solution for environments requiring strict access control.<br></span></p>'),
(218, 'DAOSAFE Full Height Turnstile DS412', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.353440', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.353603', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds412', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS412 Full Height Turnstile is a highly secure access control solution, ideal for environments with strict security needs such as industrial enterprises, stadiums, and high-profile events. Featuring a double-door design, this turnstile offers bi-directional passage control, providing flexibility for controlling entry and exit in both directions. Made from durable, anti-rust, and waterproof full brushed stainless steel, the DS412 is built to withstand both indoor and outdoor conditions, making it a reliable choice for high-traffic and challenging environments.<br><br>With visible LED indicators placed on the side front and top of the turnstile, the DS412 provides clear feedback on whether entry is accepted or denied. The arm of the turnstile can be configured with either 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotors, allowing for customizable passage control. Designed with ample space for integrating various access control devices such as RFID readers, fingerprint scanners, and more, the DS412 is both versatile and secure, ensuring a high level of protection at any facility.</span></p>'),
(219, 'DAOSAFE Full Height Turnstile DS401FS ', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.937368', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.937550', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds401fs', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS401FS Full Height Turnstile offers a robust and secure access control solution for high-security areas such as prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. Designed for both outdoor and indoor applications, this turnstile is built with a solid rain protection roof to withstand harsh weather conditions, ensuring reliable operation even in challenging environments. Constructed from durable finished and brushed stainless steel, it is resistant to corrosion, rust, and physical damage, making it ideal for locations that require long-lasting performance.<br><br>Equipped with LED indicators on both the top cover and the body side, the DS401FS clearly communicates whether entry is permitted or denied, ensuring smooth and efficient access control. It features a flexible rotor system, offering either 120&deg; or 90&deg; arm rotation to accommodate different traffic control needs. With ample space for integrating various third-party access control systems such as RFID, fingerprint scanners, and biometric readers, the DS401FS provides versatile solutions for any security requirement, making it a top choice for securing restricted areas.</span></p>'),
(220, 'DAOSAFE Full Height Turnstile DS402FS ', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.141403', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.141635', 8, 51, 74, 'daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds402fs', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS402FS Full Height Turnstile is a high-security access control solution specifically designed for environments that require strict security measures, such as prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. Featuring a solid rain protection roof, it provides enhanced weather resistance, ensuring reliable operation even in harsh outdoor conditions. Made from high-quality 304 or 316 stainless steel, this turnstile is resistant to corrosion, rust, and physical damage, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor installations. The turnstile is customizable, with standard dimensions of 2.2m (L) x 1.5m (W) that can be tailored to fit specific site requirements.<br><br>The DS402FS turnstile offers flexible rotor options, including 120&deg; or 90&deg; arm rotations, making it suitable for various traffic flow needs. Equipped with four LED indicators&mdash;two on the side front and two on the top&mdash;the system provides clear visual signals to indicate whether access is granted or denied. This full-height turnstile can be integrated with third-party access control systems such as RFID, fingerprint, or biometric readers, ensuring a comprehensive and customizable security solution. The DS402FS is perfect for sites that require both high security and easy integration with existing access control systems.</span></p>'),
(221, 'Fire extinguisher', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.886967', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.887133', 2, NULL, 12, 'fire-extinguisher', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Fire Extinguisher is a portable and essential safety device designed to control and extinguish small fires quickly and effectively. Compact and easy to use, this extinguisher is ideal for both residential and commercial environments, providing peace of mind in the event of a fire emergency. Whether placed in homes, offices, schools, or vehicles, the FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher is an indispensable tool that can help prevent the escalation of fire hazards, making it a crucial part of any fire safety plan.<br><br>Equipped with a user-friendly design, the FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher allows for fast and effective operation. Its compact size ensures it can be easily stored in various settings without taking up much space, yet it still provides ample fire-fighting power. The extinguisher is designed to handle small fires, offering immediate response in critical moments and significantly improving fire safety wherever it is deployed.</span></p>'),
(222, 'FM-200 Suppression System', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.457610', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.457772', 2, NULL, 12, 'fm-200-suppression-system', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FM-200 Suppression System is a state-of-the-art fire protection solution designed to safeguard critical environments such as data centers, server rooms, and high-value facilities. Utilizing FM-200, a clean gaseous agent, this system offers a rapid response to fires without causing any harm to people or leaving residue behind. The FIRE PRO FM-200 Suppression System is ideal for locations where traditional fire suppression methods, such as water-based sprinklers, would cause significant damage to sensitive equipment or property.<br><br>This advanced system detects fires quickly and discharges FM-200 to suppress fires effectively, preventing further damage and ensuring business continuity. Its clean and environmentally friendly nature makes it a preferred choice for environments that require both fast fire suppression and minimal impact on operations. Easy to integrate into existing fire protection infrastructures, the FIRE PRO FM-200 Suppression System provides reliable, efficient, and safe fire suppression for high-risk areas.<br></span></p>'),
(223, 'Sprinklers', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.365072', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.365221', 2, NULL, 16, 'sprinklers', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Sprinklers are a highly effective fire suppression solution designed for both commercial and residential buildings. These sprinklers are engineered to detect heat and automatically activate to suppress and control fires, preventing further damage to property and ensuring occupant safety. Installed in an upright position within a water piping system, they are strategically placed to respond swiftly to the presence of heat, distributing water to suppress flames before they spread.<br><br>Built with reliability and efficiency in mind, FIRE PRO Sprinklers offer a simple yet powerful solution to fire safety. Whether in offices, schools, homes, or large commercial properties, these sprinklers provide essential protection against fire hazards. By responding quickly to heat, FIRE PRO Sprinklers help mitigate the damage caused by fires and support a safer environment for occupants. Designed for ease of installation and low maintenance, these sprinklers provide long-term fire protection for any building.<br></span></p>'),
(224, 'Signal Gate Valve', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.781686', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.781843', 2, NULL, 16, 'signal-gate-valve', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Signal Gate Valve is a versatile and reliable valve designed to control the flow of various fluids, including water, air, steam, oil, mud, liquid metals, and even corrosive and radioactive mediums. Perfect for use in industries that handle a wide range of fluids, this valve provides precise control over fluid flow, ensuring the smooth operation of critical systems. Its robust construction and durable materials make it ideal for use in extreme conditions, offering long-term performance and safety across different industries, including manufacturing, chemical, and energy sectors.<br><br>With its easy integration into various fluid systems, the FIRE PRO Signal Gate Valve is engineered to provide optimal flow regulation. It can handle a wide array of mediums, including corrosive substances, ensuring that the valve maintains its functionality and performance even in harsh environments. The valve is equipped with a signal mechanism that provides real-time monitoring of fluid flow, allowing operators to respond quickly to any changes or issues. This reliable valve is an essential component for maintaining the safety and efficiency of fluid-based systems across industries.</span></p>'),
(225, 'Pressure Reducing Valve', '2025-01-23 00:36:23.809740', '2025-01-23 00:49:50.937244', 2, NULL, 17, 'pressure-reducing-valve', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Pressure Reducing Valve is a critical component for controlling and stabilizing pressure in fluid systems. This valve is designed to reduce incoming high pressure and maintain a steady, predetermined pressure level on the outlet side, ensuring that downstream equipment is protected from pressure fluctuations. Whether used in water, steam, or gas systems, this valve ensures consistent pressure regulation, enhancing the efficiency and safety of industrial and commercial operations. By adjusting the valve\'s opening and closing mechanisms, the system dynamically maintains outlet pressure within a set range, regardless of fluctuations in inlet pressure.<br><br>This pressure-reducing valve is ideal for protecting appliances and equipment from damage caused by pressure surges, preventing potential downtime and reducing maintenance costs. It provides reliable protection for sensitive equipment in various applications, including manufacturing, power generation, and water treatment facilities. Designed with precision engineering, the FIRE PRO Pressure Reducing Valve offers both efficiency and durability in demanding environments, ensuring the long-term functionality of the system.</span></p>'),
(226, 'Kitchen Suppression System', '2025-01-23 00:48:10.726354', '2025-01-23 00:50:18.760278', 2, NULL, 12, 'kitchen-suppression-system', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Kitchen Suppression System is a state-of-the-art fire protection solution designed to safeguard commercial kitchens and cooking areas. This system is specifically engineered to suppress fires in high-risk environments, such as restaurants, cafeterias, and other food preparation facilities, where cooking equipment poses a constant fire hazard. By targeting common sources of kitchen fires, such as deep fryers, grills, and stovetops, the system ensures rapid suppression and minimizes damage to property and equipment.<br><br>Equipped with advanced sensors and nozzles, the FIRE PRO Kitchen Suppression System provides reliable fire detection and suppression. Once a fire is detected, the system automatically releases a fire-suppressing agent, extinguishing the flames quickly and preventing the fire from spreading. The system is easy to integrate into existing kitchen setups and complies with industry fire safety standards, making it an essential tool for ensuring the safety of staff and customers in food service environments.<br></span></p>'),
(227, 'Fire pump', '2025-01-23 01:01:58.993602', '2025-01-23 01:01:58.993796', 2, NULL, 11, 'fire-pump', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Fire Pump is a vital component of any fire protection system, designed to ensure an adequate water supply for fire suppression needs. It delivers the necessary water flow and pressure to effectively combat fires in buildings, industrial facilities, and other high-risk environments. This high-performance pump is engineered to operate under demanding conditions, ensuring that firefighting efforts are never compromised, even in emergencies. With its durable construction and reliable operation, the&nbsp; Fire Pump is essential for maintaining the safety and security of commercial, industrial, and residential spaces.<br><br>Built to meet the highest safety standards, the Fire Pump is capable of providing a consistent and dependable water supply, whether it&rsquo;s used in sprinkler systems, hydrants, or other firefighting applications. Its robust design ensures longevity and performance, making it a critical investment for facilities that require a reliable and efficient firefighting solution. The Fire Pump can be seamlessly integrated into existing fire protection systems, ensuring full coverage and rapid response in case of fire emergencies.</span></p>'),
(228, 'Jockey pump', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.646563', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.646720', 2, NULL, 17, 'jockey-pump', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Jockey Pump is a compact, high-pressure pump designed to ensure the optimal performance of a fire protection system. It plays a crucial role in maintaining consistent water pressure within the system, allowing fire pumps to operate efficiently when required. Ideal for use in facilities with a fire pump system, this jockey pump ensures that the required pressure is always available, preventing system failure or pressure loss during emergencies. With its small size and powerful capabilities, the FIRE PRO Jockey Pump is essential for maintaining the reliability of fire suppression systems, especially in critical areas such as industrial plants, commercial buildings, and residential complexes.<br><br>Built for efficiency, the FIRE PRO Jockey Pump is designed to automatically engage when the system pressure drops below a set threshold, restoring the necessary pressure levels. This prevents the need for the fire pump to activate during minor pressure fluctuations, saving energy and extending the lifespan of the system. Reliable and easy to maintain, the FIRE PRO Jockey Pump ensures your fire protection system remains fully operational and ready for emergencies.<br></span></p>'),
(229, 'Preaction Alarm Valve Group', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.423609', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.423768', 2, NULL, 20, 'preaction-alarm-valve-group', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Preaction Alarm Valve Group is an essential component of a modern fire protection system, combining automatic fire detection with a reliable sprinkler system. This system operates with a closed sprinkler installation, and it utilizes preaction technology to ensure that water is only released in the event of an actual fire. The system&rsquo;s dry-type design, where the pipe is filled with low-pressure air or nitrogen during testing, helps maintain safety and efficiency by reducing the risk of accidental water discharge. As a result, the Preaction Alarm Valve Group is ideal for environments where water damage must be minimized, such as data centers, museums, and industrial facilities.<br><br>The preaction valve group ensures rapid and accurate response to fire incidents, combining the reliability of an automatic sprinkler system with the advantages of preaction activation. The integration of automatic detection technology provides early warning capabilities, ensuring that the system responds swiftly to fire events. Additionally, the system&rsquo;s dry-type design prevents water from entering the pipe until a fire is detected, making it a highly efficient and safe fire suppression solution for sensitive environments.<br></span></p>'),
(230, 'Outdoor Fire Hydrants', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.266091', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.266290', 2, NULL, 17, 'outdoor-fire-hydrants', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Outdoor Fire Hydrants are a critical part of any fire safety infrastructure, designed to provide firefighters with immediate access to water during emergencies. Built to withstand a range of weather conditions, these hydrants are engineered for durability and reliability, ensuring they perform optimally in both extreme heat and cold. Comprising a vertical pipe with a valve mechanism, the hydrant includes one or more outlets where hoses can be attached to access water from the underground distribution system.<br><br>These fire hydrants are an essential tool in urban, industrial, and rural firefighting operations, offering a fast and efficient way to draw water during emergencies. The robust design ensures longevity and minimizes the need for frequent maintenance. With a simple valve mechanism, firefighters can quickly connect hoses to gain access to a consistent and reliable water supply, helping to save lives and property during fires.<br><br></span></p>'),
(231, 'ZKTECO SF400', '2025-01-24 01:01:19.158354', '2025-01-24 01:15:40.785748', 4, 11, 33, 'zkteco-sf400', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>SF400 TIME-KEEPING &amp; ACCESS CONTROL&nbsp;</strong>is an advanced time-keeping and access control device designed for organizations that require efficient, secure, and scalable solutions. With a user capacity ranging from 1,000 to 5,000, this device caters to businesses of various sizes. Its fingerprint capacity of 1,500 and card capacity of 5,000 make it versatile for both biometric and card-based authentication methods. The SF400 boasts a robust logs capacity of 8,000, ensuring reliable record-keeping for attendance and access data.<br><br>Ideal for offices, factories, and secure facilities, the SF400 provides accurate time tracking and access control functionality in a single compact device. Its user-friendly interface and high authentication speed enhance operational efficiency. Additionally, the SF400 integrates seamlessly with existing security systems and attendance management software, offering a comprehensive solution for businesses seeking to streamline their operations.</span></p>'),
(232, 'ZKTECO SPEEDFACE V3L', '2025-01-24 01:04:24.672022', '2025-01-24 01:14:39.612624', 4, 11, 33, 'zkteco-speedface-v3l', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>SpeedFace V3L MULTI-VERIFICATION BIOMETRICS </strong><strong>TIME-KEEPING &amp; ACCESS CONTROL </strong>is a cutting-edge access control and time-keeping solution designed to provide secure and seamless verification for a range of applications. This Linux-based terminal utilizes advanced visible light technology for biometric authentication, offering both facial recognition and fingerprint verification for dual authentication. With an integrated anti-spoofing algorithm, it effectively safeguards against fraudulent attempts using fake photos or videos, ensuring only legitimate access is granted.<br><br>Equipped with impressive capacity features, the SpeedFace V3L supports up to 500 facial recognition entries, 3,000 fingerprints, and 3,000 access cards, making it ideal for medium to large businesses. It can store up to 200,000 logs, providing robust tracking and reporting capabilities. This terminal is the perfect combination of security and efficiency, offering reliable performance for time-keeping and access control needs.</span></p>'),
(233, 'ZKTECO SPEEDFACE V5L ', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.559884', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.560037', 4, 11, 33, 'zkteco-speedface-v5l', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>SpeedFace V5L MULTI-VERIFICATION BIOMETRICS&nbsp;TIME-KEEPING &amp; ACCESS CONTROL</strong>&nbsp;is an advanced biometric verification device designed for time-keeping and access control. It integrates cutting-edge facial recognition algorithms with fingerprint, palm, and QR code verification for enhanced security. With a large user capacity, the SpeedFace V5L supports up to 1,000 users, making it ideal for medium-to-large businesses that require fast, accurate, and secure authentication methods. The device uses intelligent engineering to ensure quick recognition, providing a seamless user experience. Additionally, the large log capacity (150,000 logs) ensures the device can handle high-volume usage efficiently.<br><br>This device supports multi-verification methods for increased security and convenience. The SpeedFace V5L is equipped with a user-friendly interface and mobile app support, allowing QR code scanning for authentication. Its scalability makes it a flexible solution for businesses that need to manage diverse access levels and track employee attendance. With its versatile verification methods and high-performance capabilities, the SpeedFace V5L is the perfect choice for organizations looking to implement advanced access control and time-keeping systems.</span></p>'),
(234, 'ZKTECO INBIO PRO PLUS', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.367851', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.368000', 4, 11, 31, 'zkteco-inbio-pro-plus', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> INBIO PRO PLUS IP-Based Control Pane</strong>l is a high-end, project-oriented solution designed to meet the needs of modern access control systems. It integrates advanced facial recognition and fingerprint authentication technologies, providing secure, seamless entry methods for users. With robust TCP/IP support, it facilitates remote management over both local area networks (LAN) and wide area networks (WAN), ensuring that deployment is flexible and scalable. Its sophisticated design is ideal for a range of applications, from small to large-scale projects, offering excellent performance with a high user capacity.<br><br>Designed for scalability, the INBIO PRO PLUS can support up to 100,000 users, including face and fingerprint data for up to 3,000 and 20,000 individuals respectively. The system also accommodates up to 100,000 card users and QR codes for easy access management. With a high log capacity of 100,000, it ensures comprehensive data tracking and storage. This combination of features ensures that INBIO PRO PLUS is a versatile and future-proof access control solution suitable for a variety of security environments.</span></p>'),
(235, 'ZKTECO FR1200', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.887583', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.887731', 4, 11, 33, 'zkteco-fr1200', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>FR1200 Fingerprint Reader</strong> is a high-performance biometric access control device designed to enhance security and streamline user authentication. With its RS485 communication interface, the FR1200 seamlessly integrates with biometric access controllers and standalone systems like the inBIO series controllers and F8. This fingerprint reader specializes in capturing and transferring fingerprint samples directly to an access control panel, ensuring secure and accurate identification. The IP65-rated rugged structure of the FR1200 guarantees its reliability even in harsh weather conditions, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor environments. Whether used for residential, commercial, or industrial applications, the FR1200 provides an efficient and durable solution to your access control needs.<br><br>The FR1200 is built to support a wide range of biometric applications, including high-security entry points and facilities with heavy foot traffic. Its advanced technology ensures quick and accurate fingerprint recognition, enhancing both convenience and safety. The device offers standard functions like fingerprint capturing and transfer to the access control panel, with optional functions to further expand its versatility. With a focus on reliability and durability, the FR1200 delivers long-lasting performance, reducing the need for frequent maintenance or replacement. Designed for easy integration, it provides an optimal solution for modern access control systems.</span></p>'),
(236, 'ZKTECO ZL600', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.055298', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.055440', 4, 11, 35, 'zkteco-zl600', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZL600 Deluxe Design Hotel Lock</strong> is a state-of-the-art wireless hotel door lock designed to meet the needs of modern hospitality. Constructed from durable SAE 304 stainless steel, it ensures long-lasting strength and resistance to corrosion, even in harsh weather conditions. The lock has passed a 96-hour salt spray test, which demonstrates its ability to withstand extreme environmental factors. Featuring an advanced European Standard Mortise lock body, the ZL600 is compatible with both IC S50 and S70 cards. The lock can be effortlessly unlocked through a smartphone using HTML5 (H5) and supports the ZKBioHLMS lock management application for streamlined operations.<br><br>With Zigbee communication, the ZL600 offers both local and remote control for ease of management. It is powered by four AAA alkaline batteries, providing reliable performance with a low-maintenance design. The ZL600&rsquo;s advanced security features and sleek, modern design make it the ideal solution for hotels seeking to enhance guest experience while maintaining high standards of security. Whether managing a single location or multiple sites, the ZL600 is a secure, efficient, and user-friendly solution for hospitality businesses.</span></p>'),
(237, 'ZKTECO ZL700', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.471062', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.471201', 4, 11, 35, 'zkteco-zl700', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZL700 Wireless Hotel Lock</strong> provides modern security with the added convenience of wireless connectivity. Designed with SAE 304 stainless steel, this lock offers both strength and corrosion resistance, making it a durable option for hotel environments. It has passed rigorous testing, including a 96-hour salt spray test, ensuring long-lasting performance even in harsh conditions. The ZL700 is equipped with the advanced ZKBIOHLMS lock management application, which facilitates easy control and monitoring. Supporting IC S50/S70 cards, it ensures secure and efficient access for guests and staff alike. With the ability to fit door thicknesses from 36mm to 55mm, this lock is versatile for a range of installations.<br><br>Powered by four AAA alkaline batteries, the ZL700 offers reliability with minimal maintenance. Its wireless design simplifies installation, eliminating the need for complex wiring and enabling quicker setup in any hotel room or facility. The sleek design of the ZL700 complements modern hotel aesthetics, providing both security and style. Perfect for a wide range of establishments, from boutique hotels to large chains, the ZL700 wireless hotel lock ensures safety while offering convenience and user-friendly operation.</span></p>'),
(238, 'ZKTECO LH6500', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.159741', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.159882', 4, 11, 35, 'zkteco-lh6500', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> LH6500 SUPER THIN HOTEL LOCK</strong> is a cutting-edge door lock solution tailored for the hospitality industry. This sleek, modern lock operates on advanced 13.56MHz card technology, ensuring seamless and secure access for guests. Crafted from durable zinc alloy, the lock is designed to withstand daily use while maintaining its elegant appearance. Its compatibility with professional hotel lock management software like ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity makes it a highly efficient choice for hotel operations.<br><br>Equipped with an American standard mortise featuring five latches, the LH6500 provides superior security and durability. Its slim profile and compatibility with door thicknesses ranging from 40mm to 50mm make it an ideal fit for a variety of hotel door types. The ISO14443 RFID card type ensures a smooth check-in experience, enhancing guest satisfaction. The LH6500 is a blend of sophistication, security, and practicality, making it a valuable addition to modern hotel facilities.</span></p>'),
(239, 'ZKTECO LH6800', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.829443', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.829753', 4, 11, 35, 'zkteco-lh6800', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The&nbsp;<strong>LH6800 Modern Design Hotel Lock</strong> combines cutting-edge technology with a sleek, contemporary design to provide unmatched security and convenience for hotels. Featuring advanced 13.56 MHz Mifare card technology, this lock ensures fast, reliable, and secure access. Its robust American standard mortise with 5 latches delivers enhanced durability and protection, making it ideal for busy hospitality environments. The LH6800 is supported by professional hotel lock management software that simplifies installation and operation, enabling hoteliers to implement secure access control with a single click.<br><br>Crafted from premium zinc alloy, the LH6800 is built to withstand heavy usage while maintaining its modern aesthetic. It is compatible with ISO14443 RFID cards, offering a seamless user experience for guests and staff alike. With support for ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, the lock integrates effortlessly into comprehensive security systems. Designed for doors with a thickness of 35mm to 45mm, the LH6800 provides flexibility for a wide range of installations, ensuring security and elegance in any hotel setting.</span></p>'),
(240, 'ZKTECO MARS-S1000 SERIES', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.831452', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.831599', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-s1000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-S1000 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate</strong> by ZKTeco offers a cutting-edge solution to access control, combining high-level security with superior user experience. Designed to provide seamless integration, the Mars Series boasts up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors in the Mars-Pro Series, which significantly enhance its anti-tailgate functionality, making unauthorized access more difficult. This advanced security system is built with a modular, snap-fit, screwless design, ensuring easy installation and maintenance, while also reducing production lead times by up to 30%. Whether you\'re managing high-traffic areas or securing sensitive zones, this sleek and reliable system offers versatility and peace of mind.<br><br>In addition to its robust security features, the MARS-S1000 Series offers flexible options to suit various environments. Models like the MARS-S1000 Single-Lane Speed Gate and the MARS-S1011 and MARS-S1022 variants with built-in controllers and RFID or biometric readers provide comprehensive access control for different needs. Ideal for office buildings, airports, and other high-security locations, this series guarantees an intelligent, adaptable solution that can be customized to specific requirements. The Mars Series sets a new benchmark in access control technology by offering a powerful blend of performance, security, and convenience.</span></p>'),
(241, 'ZKTECO MARS-S1200 SERIES', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.342766', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.342905', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-s1200-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-S1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate</strong> from ZKTeco represents the cutting-edge in security and user experience. With a range of features designed for maximum safety and ease of use, this series is engineered to meet the needs of modern security environments. The system includes up to 22 pairs of advanced infrared sensors, improving anti-tailgate performance significantly, ensuring that only authorized individuals can pass. With a modularized design, installation and maintenance are made simpler and more efficient, reducing production lead time by up to 30%.<br><br>Available in several configurations, the MARS-S1200 Series caters to a variety of user needs. The MARS-S1200, MARS-S1211, and MARS-S1222 models all offer distinct options, such as integration with RFID and fingerprint readers. These gates provide a seamless integration with existing access control systems, making them ideal for high-traffic areas like office buildings, airports, and commercial establishments. Their sleek, modern design ensures that security does not come at the expense of aesthetic appeal, providing a smooth and secure user experience.</span></p>'),
(242, 'ZKTECO MARS PRO-S1200 SERIES', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.615783', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.615925', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-pro-s1200-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-S1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate</strong> by ZKTeco offers cutting-edge technology in user experience, safety, and seamless integration. Designed with advanced functionality and easy maintenance in mind, this innovative product boasts a modularized, screwless design, reducing installation time by up to 30%. Featuring up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, the Mars Series enhances anti-tailgate performance, providing high-security access control. With multiple versions available, including the MARS PRO-S1200, PRO-S1211 with RFID reader and controller, and PRO-S1222 with fingerprint and RFID reader, this versatile speed gate solution caters to various security needs.<br><br>The Mars PRO-S1200 Series is ideal for high-traffic environments where security and speed are crucial. Its sleek design ensures smooth operation while maintaining a low-profile aesthetic. The advanced sensors ensure reliable, rapid detection of unauthorized access attempts, preventing tailgating and enhancing overall security. The range of models available ensures flexibility for different access control requirements, whether for a standard gate, or for a more sophisticated setup with RFID and biometric authentication. Whether for commercial buildings, government facilities, or high-end private access points, the MARS PRO-S1200 Series sets a new standard for automated security solutions.</span></p>'),
(243, 'ZKTECO MARS PRO-S1000 SERIES', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.166469', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.166622', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-pro-s1000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-S1000 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate</strong> is an advanced security solution from ZKTeco, designed to offer superior user experience, safety, and seamless integration with various systems. This next-generation swing barrier speed gate is equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors to significantly enhance anti-tailgate performance, ensuring greater accuracy in monitoring and controlling access. With its creative snap-fit, screwless, modular design, installation and maintenance become easier, reducing production lead time by up to 30%.<br><br>The MARS PRO-S1000 Series is available in different configurations, including the MARS PRO-S1000 for single-lane access, the MARS PRO-S1011 with a controller and RFID reader for added functionality, and the MARS PRO-S1022, which includes both a controller and fingerprint &amp; RFID reader for higher security requirements. Its sleek design, ease of installation, and advanced features make the MARS PRO-S1000 Series a top choice for securing commercial, industrial, and office environments.</span></p>'),
(244, 'ZKTECO MARS-B1000 SERIES', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.522575', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.522751', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-b1000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-B1000 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate </strong>from ZKTeco offers top-tier security, cutting-edge technology, and seamless integration. Designed with user experience and safety as a priority, this series incorporates up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, enhancing its anti-tailgate capabilities to ensure only authorized individuals gain access. With a modularized design featuring a snap-fit, screwless structure, installation and maintenance are simplified, reducing production lead time by up to 30%. The series is available in multiple configurations, including models with controllers, RFID readers, and fingerprint scanners for versatile access control solutions.<br><br>The MARS-B1000 Series not only delivers robust security but also prioritizes aesthetics and durability. Its sleek design and easy integration with other security systems make it an ideal choice for a wide range of applications, including corporate offices, government facilities, and public spaces. Whether you choose the standard MARS-B1000, the MARS-B1011 with RFID capabilities, or the advanced MARS-B1022 model with both RFID and fingerprint access, this series guarantees reliability, flexibility, and high performance. With ZKTeco&rsquo;s advanced features and streamlined design, the MARS-B1000 Series is the next generation of speed gates for modern security systems. </span></p>');
