(246, 'ZKTECO MARS-F1000 SERIES', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.016411', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.016570', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-f1000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> MARS-F1000 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> from ZKTeco offers a cutting-edge solution for secure, efficient access control. Designed with advanced technology, this speed gate provides an unparalleled user experience with a focus on safety and integration. The MARS-F1000 series features up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors in the Mars-Pro Series, ensuring superior anti-tailgate performance. Its innovative modular design eliminates the need for screws, making both installation and maintenance seamless, reducing production lead times by up to 30%. The range includes three models: MARS-F1000 for basic needs, MARS-F1011 with an integrated RFID reader and controller, and the MARS-F1022 featuring both fingerprint and RFID reader integration for a higher level of security.<br><br>This speed gate series is perfect for environments where safety, accessibility, and high performance are critical. Ideal for commercial buildings, office complexes, and high-security areas, the MARS-F1000 Series is engineered to meet modern access control requirements. Whether you are looking for a basic, RFID-enabled, or fingerprint-recognizing solution, this series is designed to suit a wide range of needs. The MARS-F1000 Series combines sleek, modern aesthetics with functionality, ensuring that each installation enhances both security and user convenience.</span></p>'),
(247, 'ZKTECO MARS-F1200 SERIES', '2025-01-24 02:50:29.976237', '2025-01-24 02:50:29.976393', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-f1200-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-F1200 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate </strong>by ZKTeco is a cutting-edge solution designed to offer superior user experience, enhanced safety, and seamless integration with various systems. This series features advanced anti-tailgate functionality, incorporating up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors (Mars-Pro Series) that significantly improve security. Its creative snap-fit, screwless, modularized design streamlines installation and maintenance, reducing production lead time by up to 30%. Available in several configurations, including the MARS-F1200 Dual-Lane Speed Gate, MARS-F1211 Dual-Lane Speed Gate with Controller and RFID Reader, and MARS-F1222 Dual-Lane Speed Gate with Controller, RFID, and Fingerprint Reader, this system is versatile for various access control needs.<br><br>The MARS-F1200 Series is designed with both performance and aesthetics in mind, providing a sleek and efficient solution for controlling pedestrian flow in high-security areas. Whether for office buildings, commercial spaces, or industrial facilities, these gates ensure smooth and secure access while enhancing overall building security. With its robust features and modular design, the MARS-F1200 Series not only meets but exceeds industry standards for safety and functionality, making it an ideal choice for both small and large-scale installations.</span></p>'),
(248, 'ZKTECO MARS PRO-F1000 SERIES', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.575951', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.576102', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-pro-f1000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-F1000 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> from ZKTeco is designed to elevate user experience with its innovative features and high safety standards. Equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, the Mars-Pro Series significantly improves anti-tailgate performance, ensuring secure and efficient access control. Its creative snap-fit, screwless modular design simplifies installation and maintenance, cutting production lead time by up to 30%. This series delivers top-tier integration capabilities, making it an ideal choice for modern access control systems that require ease of use, durability, and seamless functionality.<br><br>Available in multiple configurations, including the MARS PRO-F1000 single-lane gate, the MARS PRO-F1011 with controller and RFID reader, and the MARS PRO-F1022 with both fingerprint and RFID readers, the Mars Pro Series offers tailored solutions to meet diverse security needs. Whether it&rsquo;s for office buildings, high-security zones, or public spaces, these gates provide an efficient, secure, and user-friendly experience. The robust construction ensures long-lasting performance, while the advanced security features protect against unauthorized access and tailgating.</span></p>'),
(249, 'ZKTECO MARS PRO-F1200 SERIES', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.112633', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.112836', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-mars-pro-f1200-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-F1200 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> by ZKTeco represents the pinnacle of access control technology, offering exceptional user experience, advanced safety, and seamless integration. Featuring up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, this series significantly enhances anti-tailgating capabilities, ensuring secure and efficient passage for authorized individuals. The innovative modular design eliminates the need for screws, making installation and maintenance simpler and more cost-effective, while reducing production lead time by up to 30%. The series includes several configurations tailored to meet varying security needs: the MARS PRO-F1200, MARS PRO-F1211 (with controller and RFID reader), and MARS PRO-F1222 (with controller, fingerprint, and RFID reader). Whether for corporate offices, public spaces, or secure facilities, the MARS PRO-F1200 Series ensures reliable and streamlined access control.<br><br>The MARS PRO-F1200 Series is engineered to meet the diverse requirements of modern access control systems, combining cutting-edge technology with user-friendly design. Its dual-lane configuration allows for fast, simultaneous passage, ideal for high-traffic areas, while the integrated sensors and smart features ensure top-tier security. Designed to integrate seamlessly with existing systems, the MARS PRO Series supports RFID and fingerprint readers, offering flexible options to suit various organizational needs. From improved anti-tailgate protection to its minimalist, sleek design, the MARS PRO-F1200 Series is a top choice for organizations seeking security without compromising aesthetics or ease of use.</span></p>'),
(250, 'ZKTECO TS1000 PRO SERIES', '2025-01-24 03:22:41.976622', '2025-01-24 03:22:41.976786', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-ts1000-pro-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS1000 Pro Series Tripod Turnstiles </strong>offer a reliable, secure, and economical access control solution designed for various indoor applications. Ideal for office buildings, corporate environments, and public facilities, these turnstiles combine advanced technology with a user-friendly interface to manage foot traffic efficiently. Available in multiple models&mdash;TS1000, TS1011, and TS1022&mdash;each unit provides a robust structure and versatility for different security requirements. With options ranging from simple RFID access control to more advanced fingerprint and RFID integration, the TS1000 Pro Series caters to a wide array of security needs.<br><br>Built to enhance safety while maintaining the flow of people, these turnstiles are designed for durability and ease of use. The TS1000 series is equipped with a sturdy tripod mechanism that resists tampering and ensures only authorized access. Whether you\'re looking for basic security or a more sophisticated access control system, the Pro Series turnstiles can be seamlessly integrated into any facility. The TS1000 Pro Series is the ideal solution for businesses looking for a cost-effective yet high-performance security measure.</span></p>'),
(251, 'ZKTECO TS2000 PRO SERIES', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.696650', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.696810', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-ts2000-pro-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS2000 PRO Series Tripod Turnstile</strong> is an ideal security solution for protecting your premises, offering a classic and safe design. It is perfect for a wide range of indoor environments, particularly in office buildings and other commercial settings. This turnstile system provides a cost-effective method of managing access, ensuring that only authorized individuals are allowed entry. The TS2000 series comes with several configurations, including options with controllers, RFID readers, and even advanced biometric systems like fingerprint scanning.<br><br>Whether you\'re seeking basic access control or more sophisticated security features, the TS2000 PRO Series provides a reliable and customizable solution. Its high-quality construction ensures durability and longevity, making it suitable for both low-traffic and high-traffic areas. The turnstiles are easy to install and maintain, and the added security features help enhance the overall protection of your premises.<br><br></span></p>'),
(252, 'ZKTECO ZK-D1065', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.093391', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.094171', 7, 44, 62, 'zkteco-zk-d1065', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D1065 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> offers reliable and efficient security screening with advanced features. Equipped with 6 detection zones, this metal detector can accurately detect metallic objects on the body, enhancing safety at high-traffic locations. Its 100 sensitivity levels allow users to fine-tune detection to their requirements, minimizing false alarms while ensuring thorough screening. With a 3.5&rdquo; LCD display, it provides clear, real-time data, including the count of people passing through and alarm occurrences. The device also features synchronous sound and LED alarms to alert security personnel instantly when a metal object is detected.<br><br>Ideal for airports, schools, stadiums, and other public facilities, the ZK-D1065 ensures efficient screening without hindering the flow of people. Its intuitive design and robust functionality make it a top choice for maintaining security in busy environments. The detector&rsquo;s ability to track both people and alarm counts adds another layer of monitoring for administrators. With a sleek and modern design, this walk-through metal detector is as functional as it is user-friendly, providing peace of mind in any high-traffic setting.</span></p>'),
(253, 'ZKTECO ZK-D2180 ', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.373274', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.373651', 7, 43, 62, 'zkteco-zk-d2180', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D2180 Walk-Through Metal Detecto</strong>r is designed to provide reliable, efficient, and advanced security screening for various high-security areas, including airports, stadiums, government buildings, and event venues. It boasts 18 detection zones and 256 sensitivity levels, offering customized security settings that cater to different environments. With its intuitive 3.5&rdquo; LCD display, users can easily monitor real-time activity and access detailed security data. The detector also features people and alarm counting, ensuring precise management of foot traffic and instant alerts. The integrated synchronous sound and LED alarm system immediately notifies security personnel of any potential threats.<br><br>In addition, the ZK-D2180 supports TCP/IP communication, enabling seamless connection to external systems for centralized control and monitoring. Remote control capability ensures that security personnel can manage the detector from a distance, enhancing convenience. This walk-through metal detector is also designed to link with turnstiles, allowing for smooth and secure access control. The device supports integration with mobile apps, giving security teams flexibility in monitoring and managing security from their devices. With its combination of advanced features and user-friendly design, the ZK-D2180 provides an exceptional solution for high-level security needs.</span></p>'),
(254, 'ZKTECO ZK-D3180', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.161485', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.161698', 7, 44, 61, 'zkteco-zk-d3180', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZK-D3180 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> is a highly advanced security solution designed to provide precise detection and effective monitoring in high-traffic areas. Equipped with 18 detection zones and 500 adjustable sensitivity levels, this detector can effectively identify metallic objects on individuals, ensuring thorough security screening. It features a 7-inch LCD display for clear and convenient monitoring, along with the ability to count people and alarms for enhanced efficiency and tracking. The ZK-D3180 is built with fireproof materials, offering durability and safety, and is designed to be harmless to the human body, making it a reliable choice for various environments.<br><br>With excellent anti-interference capabilities, the ZK-D3180 ensures minimal disruptions and optimal performance even in challenging conditions. The synchronous sound and LED alarm system provides a clear indication of any security threats, while the remote control feature allows for easy adjustments and operation. Whether used at airports, public events, or secure facilities, this metal detector provides comprehensive security and user-friendly functionality, ensuring safety and efficiency for both operators and visitors.</span></p>'),
(255, 'ZKTECO ZK-D3180S TD', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.430231', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.430389', 7, 44, 61, 'zkteco-zk-d3180s-td', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D3180S TD Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> is a cutting-edge security device designed to enhance safety and health measures in public spaces. Featuring 18 detection zones and 500 sensitivity levels, this detector offers highly accurate and reliable metal detection capabilities. It is equipped with a built-in body temperature measurement function, allowing for the monitoring of passengers\' temperatures at both the forehead and wrist. If an individual&rsquo;s temperature exceeds 37.3&deg;C, the ZK-D3180S triggers an alarm, alerting security personnel immediately. This makes the ZK-D3180S ideal for high-traffic areas such as airports, schools, hospitals, and public events.<br><br>Additionally, the ZK-D3180S boasts a user-friendly interface with a 7&rdquo; LCD display, allowing for easy monitoring and management of security operations. The system also includes people and alarm counting features, providing real-time tracking of individuals passing through the detector and any triggered alarms. Its synchronized sound and LED alarms ensure that both visual and auditory cues are given when threats or health concerns arise. With a focus on safety, hygiene, and operational efficiency, the ZK-D3180S is an invaluable tool for modern security systems.</span></p>'),
(256, 'ZKTECO ZK-D100S', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.946812', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.946983', 7, 44, 62, 'zkteco-zk-d100s', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D100S Portable Metal Detecto</strong>r is a high-performance security device designed to ensure safety and prevent the entry or theft of contraband in various environments. This detector is versatile and ideal for use in factories, educational institutions, and security checkpoints, where it can effectively detect items like knives, guns, mobile phones, and electronic cheat tools. The ZK-D100S provides both sound and light alarms simultaneously to alert users about the presence of unwanted items.<br><br>With its sleek and portable design, this metal detector operates with a voltage range of 7V-9V, making it energy-efficient and easy to use in different locations. It is also built to be durable and resistant to the elements, featuring an IP31 waterproof rating. Measuring 410mm in length, 85mm in width, and 45mm in height, the ZK-D100S is compact yet robust enough for daily use in a wide range of environments, from factories to educational settings.</span></p>'),
(257, 'ZKTECO ZKX5030C', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.807712', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.807859', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx5030c', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX5030C Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is an advanced security system designed for the precise inspection of briefcases, carry-on baggage, and small cargo parcels. Utilizing a high-quality dual energy X-ray generator, the ZKX5030C offers clear and detailed scanning images that enable operators to easily identify potential threats. The device&rsquo;s superb image algorithm ensures that images are sharp and visually clear, providing quick and accurate identification of any suspicious items. Its innovative biometric identification system enhances security by preventing unauthorized access, eliminating the risk of operators forgetting passwords. The ergonomic, modern design of the ZKX5030C helps operators scan items efficiently, reducing fatigue while maintaining high levels of accuracy. Perfect for a wide range of security applications, the ZKX5030C is a reliable and intuitive tool for modern security operations.<br><br>The <strong>ZKX5030C </strong>is ideal for use in airports, transportation hubs, government buildings, and other high-security areas. With its easy-to-navigate interface and energy-saving features, it allows operators to monitor and manage security threats effectively while minimizing environmental impact. This X-ray scanner provides a dependable solution for users who require a balance between functionality and operational ease. Whether for scanning luggage or smaller cargo, the ZKX5030C is built to support high throughput and deliver reliable results with every use. The incorporation of the latest in X-ray technology and security features makes this scanner an essential asset for ensuring the safety of both personnel and property.</span></p>'),
(258, 'ZKTECO ZKX5030A', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.678834', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.678993', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx5030a', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX5030A Single Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a high-performance inspection system designed to enhance security screening by enabling operators to easily identify potential threats in briefcases, carry-on baggage, and small cargo parcels. Equipped with a reliable single-energy X-ray generator, this scanner delivers clear and detailed scanning images to effectively pinpoint dangerous items. The ZKX5030A is designed with an ergonomic, modern interface to facilitate faster and more accurate identification of suspicious objects, ensuring swift responses in security-sensitive environments. Ideal for airports, courthouses, and transportation hubs, this system offers high security without compromising efficiency.<br><br>Utilizing advanced image algorithms, the ZKX5030A produces vivid pseudo-color scanning images that provide superior visualization of the scanned contents. In addition, it is energy-efficient, with an energy-saving mode that reduces power consumption during prolonged use. The compact design and versatile scanning capabilities make the ZKX5030A an essential tool for organizations needing fast, reliable, and environmentally conscious security measures. This system provides a dependable solution for securing small to medium-sized parcels and ensuring a streamlined security process.</span></p>'),
(259, 'ZKTECO ZKX6040', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.465390', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.465554', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx6040', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6040 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a high-performance baggage inspection system designed to deliver accurate detection of both organic and inorganic materials. With a steel penetration capacity of up to 35mm, it ensures a thorough inspection even for the most complex objects. The scanner features a spacious tunnel opening of 600mm by 400mm, providing ample space for various types of baggage and parcels. ZKX6040 uses advanced algorithms to analyze the atomic numbers of materials, enabling it to distinguish between organic, inorganic, and mixed substances. This ability makes it ideal for diverse applications, including airports, government offices, hotels, and transportation hubs.<br><br>Its compact design, combined with a foldable keyboard, enhances portability and flexibility. The system can be easily moved to different locations as needed, offering convenience without compromising performance. The fingerprint verification function ensures secure access, while the input/output roller conveyor streamlines baggage handling. With the added feature of displaying cluttered bag images, ZKX6040 helps operators quickly identify potential threats or items of interest, improving efficiency in high-volume environments. The combination of these features makes the ZKX6040 a versatile and reliable solution for any security checkpoint.</span></p>'),
(260, 'ZKTECO ZKX6550A', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.863074', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.863223', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx6550a', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX6550A SINGLE ENERGY X-RAY SCANNER</strong> is a cost-effective, high-performance security solution for inspecting carry-on luggage. Equipped with a reliable X-ray generator, it delivers clear, high-quality scanning images, enabling operators to quickly identify potential threats. The advanced image algorithm further enhances the accuracy of the scans, providing detailed views for thorough inspections. Additionally, the ZKX6550A includes innovative biometric fingerprint identification, improving system security by ensuring only authorized personnel can access the system. Its ergonomic design ensures comfort for operators, helping them process luggage more efficiently while minimizing fatigue.<br><br>With its bi-directional scanning capability, the <strong>ZKX6550A </strong>can effectively scan items in multiple orientations, enhancing its versatility. The scanner is suitable for a wide range of environments, from airports to secure facilities, where luggage inspection is a critical part of security procedures. The integration of pseudo-color scanning images aids in highlighting suspicious objects, making the detection process more intuitive. This modern X-ray screening system offers a reliable, secure, and user-friendly solution for efficient carry-on baggage screening.</span></p>'),
(261, 'ZKTECO ZKX6550', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.343929', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.344071', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx6550', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a cutting-edge security solution designed to enhance threat detection capabilities for operators. This state-of-the-art device is perfect for scanning briefcases, carry-on baggage, and small cargo parcels, offering clear and detailed imaging to identify potential threats. Utilizing a high-quality dual energy X-ray generator and advanced image algorithms, the ZKX6550 delivers sharp, reliable images that enable operators to quickly and accurately spot dangerous items. The scanner\'s ergonomic design ensures ease of use, reducing operator fatigue during prolonged scanning sessions. Additionally, it incorporates an innovative biometric fingerprint identification feature to improve security and prevent unauthorized access.<br><br>The ZKX6550 is built to handle a wide range of security needs, offering bi-directional scanning for increased flexibility. Its true-color scanning technology enhances image clarity, providing operators with a visual advantage when assessing scanned objects. The device&rsquo;s modern design not only prioritizes user comfort but also streamlines the scanning process, ensuring rapid and precise threat detection. Its reliability and ease of operation make the ZKX6550 an invaluable tool for high-security environments. Whether in airports, government buildings, or other high-risk areas, this scanner delivers exceptional performance for critical security applications.</span></p>'),
(262, 'ZKTECO ZKX6550D', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.558703', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.558920', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx6550d', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550D Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is an advanced security inspection system designed to offer superior detection and screening capabilities. Utilizing dual-view technology, this scanner presents both horizontal and vertical images through two independent generators, providing a comprehensive and clear view of scanned objects. It efficiently detects organic, inorganic, and mixed materials by analyzing their effective atomic numbers, allowing for the quick identification of potential threats or contraband. The system excels at distinguishing overlapping items and accurately identifying potential risks. This makes it an ideal solution for screening carry-on baggage in airports, government buildings, and other high-security areas.<br><br>The <strong>ZKX6550D </strong>is equipped with a dual monitor operation desk, allowing operators to simultaneously monitor both views for enhanced situational awareness. The bi-directional scanning feature provides flexibility, making it easier to detect items from multiple angles. This X-ray scanner is highly efficient, ensuring a faster, more reliable inspection process. Whether used for security screening at airports or other checkpoints, the ZKX6550D is a powerful tool in maintaining safety and security.</span></p>'),
(263, 'ZKTECO ZKX10080 ', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.247760', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.247910', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx10080', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX10080 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a cutting-edge security solution designed to enhance the detection and identification of potential threats. With a scanning area of 100 &times; 80 cm, this system can efficiently scan large bags and parcels. It features a high-quality dual-energy X-ray generator, which, combined with a sophisticated image algorithm, produces clear and detailed images, ensuring that operators can identify threats with ease. The lowered conveyor height makes it simple for operators to load luggage, while the foldable conveyor design offers compact storage, reducing transportation costs.<br><br>Additionally, the <strong>ZKX10080 </strong>is equipped with an innovative biometric identity function, enhancing security by ensuring that only authorized operators can access the system. The modern side door design simplifies maintenance, ensuring that the device remains operational with minimal downtime. With features like adjustable belt speed, bi-directional scanning, and large baggage screening capabilities, the ZKX10080 is the ideal choice for security environments requiring fast, reliable, and precise X-ray inspection.</span></p>'),
(264, 'ZKTECO ZKX100100', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.063495', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.063656', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-zkx100100', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX100100 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanne</strong>r is a state-of-the-art inspection system designed to enhance the operator&rsquo;s ability to detect potential threats quickly and accurately. With a scanning capacity of up to 100 &times; 100 cm, this advanced device utilizes a high-quality dual-energy X-ray generator, ensuring reliable and clear scanning images. The scanner&rsquo;s superior image algorithm allows operators to visually identify suspicious items with ease, offering a higher level of security. The ZKX100100 also features a lowered conveyor height, facilitating easier handling of luggage and parcels. This modern scanner is equipped with a biometric identification system to ensure secure access for operators, preventing unauthorized use and eliminating the risk of password forgetfulness. The ergonomic design of the ZKX100100 contributes to improved efficiency and accuracy, allowing operators to swiftly detect threats while ensuring comfort and ease of use.</span></p>'),
(265, 'ZKTECO BLADE6040', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.700444', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.700580', 10, 23, 90, 'zkteco-blade6040', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The BLADE6040 Dual Energy X-ray Scanner is a state-of-the-art security solution designed for the effective inspection of mail, hand-held baggage, luggage, and other items. With a tunnel size of 610*420mm, this system delivers high-quality imaging and precise detection capabilities for a wide range of threats. It is specifically engineered to identify suspicious objects such as weapons, explosives, drugs, and toxic substances, using atomic number identification to detect dangerous materials. This ensures a rapid and accurate assessment of baggage content for enhanced security.<br><br>Equipped with advanced features, the BLADE6040 X-ray Scanner provides unparalleled reliability in detecting hidden threats. Its steel penetration capabilities of up to 35mm (with typical penetration reaching 40mm) make it effective against a variety of materials, while the four layers of lead curtains ensure optimal radiation safety. The system also includes an uninterruptible power supply for continuous operation in critical security environments, making it ideal for airports, government buildings, and high-security facilities.</span></p>'),
(266, 'ZKTECO PB4000 SERIES', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.127813', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.127984', 8, 24, 70, 'zkteco-pb4000-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>PB4000 Series Telescopic Parking Barrier</strong> is designed to deliver reliable and long-lasting performance for vehicle entrance control management. Crafted from die-casting aluminum alloy, this barrier features a high-quality motor and advanced structural design, ensuring durability and reduced maintenance requirements. The PB4000 is highly efficient, offering smooth operation and high reliability in various environments, making it an ideal choice for secure vehicle access management. With a range of boom options, including telescopic, folding, and LED-enhanced models, this series is adaptable to different installation needs, from compact urban parking areas to large-scale facilities.<br><br>Available in multiple boom configurations, such as the PB4130 3M 90&deg; Folding Boom and PB4030-LED 4M Straight Boom with LED, the PB4000 Series offers versatile solutions to meet various parking control requirements. Its user-friendly design makes it easy to install and operate, while its robust build ensures minimal maintenance. The telescopic design allows for easy expansion and retraction, making it a practical choice for dynamic access control. Whether for residential, commercial, or industrial purposes, the PB4000 Series provides a reliable and efficient solution to manage vehicle entrances securely.</span></p>'),
(267, 'ZKTECO UHF 10 SERIES', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.160010', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.160170', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-uhf-10-series', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UHF 10 Series Long Distance Card Reader System</strong> is designed to meet the demands of personnel management, goods management, and vehicle management. It offers impressive reading performance with a range of up to 12 meters, ensuring seamless operations in environments where long-range access control is crucial. The system operates with low power consumption, maintaining stable performance even under varying temperatures. Featuring a weatherproof, IP66-rated shell, it is built to endure harsh environmental conditions while delivering consistent, reliable service. The system also supports Wiegand 26-bit communication, which ensures compatibility with various access control systems.<br><br>Engineered for long service life and minimal external interference, the UHF 10 Series is an ideal solution for businesses seeking efficient and durable access management. Whether you are managing employees, assets, or vehicles, this system offers the convenience of a maximum cable distance of 100 meters, providing flexibility in installation. Its robust design and ease of use make it a valuable addition to any security or asset tracking system, offering both reliability and durability for a range of professional applications.</span></p>'),
(268, 'ZKTECO UR20RW-F', '2025-01-27 03:56:06.999259', '2025-01-27 03:56:06.999448', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-ur20rw-f', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> UR20RW-F UHF Card Issue Reade</strong>r is a cutting-edge device designed to offer fast and efficient read/write capabilities for ultra-high frequency (UHF) tags and cards. This versatile tool supports both User Area and EPC Area of UHF tags, ensuring reliable data transfer and management. It works seamlessly with UHF labels and cards that meet the EPC global UHF Class1 Gen 2 and ISO 18000-6C standards, providing superior performance for a range of applications. The USB interface, equipped with advanced plug-and-play technology, ensures easy connectivity without the need for additional drivers, making it highly convenient and user-friendly.<br><br>With a working frequency range of 902MHz-928MHz, the UR20RW-F offers a read/write distance of 0 to 5 cm, making it ideal for short-range scanning in environments that require quick and precise data exchange. Whether used for inventory management, asset tracking, or any application involving UHF cards or tags, the UR20RW-F ensures efficiency and accuracy. Its compact design and high compatibility with various systems make it an excellent choice for businesses looking to integrate UHF technology into their operations.</span></p>'),
(269, 'ZKTECO VR10 PRO ', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.437858', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.438022', 8, 24, 74, 'zkteco-vr10-pro', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> VR10 PRO Parking Barrier Radar </strong>by ZKTeco is a second-generation radar designed to enhance the efficiency and safety of barrier gates. Equipped with advanced technology, it detects and identifies various vehicles, including motorcycles, cars, trucks, and pedestrians, near the gate. The system ensures precise detection and eliminates the risk of accidents by monitoring movements around the gate. Its adjustable detection distance, ranging from 1 meter to 6 meters, allows for customization based on specific needs and environments.<br><br>This radar provides an intuitive setup process with the app-based parameter settings, making installation and configuration simple and user-friendly. The<strong> VR10 PRO</strong> is ideal for use in parking lots, residential areas, or commercial spaces where vehicle and pedestrian movement needs to be monitored effectively. With its robust detection capabilities, this radar significantly improves barrier gate operations by preventing premature gate closures and collisions.</span></p>'),
(270, 'MATRIX Project Series Bullet Network Cameras', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.545642', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.545900', 3, 7, 26, 'matrix-project-series-bullet-network-cameras', '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX Project Series Bullet Network Cameras are engineered for high-performance outdoor surveillance, delivering crystal-clear images even in challenging environments. Designed with a durable metal body, these cameras withstand extreme weather conditions, ensuring reliable security around the clock. Featuring 2MP resolution and a 1/2.8\" SONY STARVIS CMOS sensor, they capture detailed and high-quality video footage. Their True WDR technology balances lighting in high-contrast scenes, providing clear images in both bright and dim conditions.<br><br>With an impressive 50m IR range, these cameras offer exceptional night vision, making them ideal for securing large outdoor areas such as parking lots, campuses, and industrial sites. Their adaptive streaming technology optimizes bandwidth and storage without compromising video quality. Additionally, these cameras are NDAA-compliant and cyber-secure, ensuring the protection of sensitive data. Certified with BIS, CE, FCC, RoHS, IK10, IP67, UL, and NEMA 4X ratings, they are built to meet global security standards. Whether for commercial or industrial applications, the MATRIX Project Series Bullet Network Cameras provide superior reliability and performance.</span></p>');
