(66, '<p><strong>MB560-VL ID WiFi Visible Light Devices Time Attendance Devices with Basic Access Control</strong> offer a state-of-the-art solution for time tracking and secure access management. Leveraging visible light facial recognition technology, the device ensures highly accurate and speedy identification, even under varying light conditions. It also supports fingerprint and RFID card verification, providing businesses with multiple options for attendance recording and access control. The <strong>MB560-VL</strong> is designed to enhance efficiency and security, making it an ideal choice for offices, schools, factories, and other environments requiring reliable time attendance systems.</p>\r\n<p>With built-in WiFi functionality, the <strong>MB560-VL</strong> simplifies data management by allowing seamless real-time data synchronization across your network. The device supports remote access, enabling administrators to monitor and manage attendance logs effortlessly. Its sleek design and robust construction make it suitable for high-traffic areas, while the basic access control feature adds an extra layer of security to your premises. For businesses seeking an all-in-one solution to manage time attendance and basic access control, the <strong>MB560-VL ID WiFi Visible Light Device</strong> delivers unparalleled performance and reliability.</p>', 'products/mb560-vl-id-wifi/descriptions/202501-39-1_5-j6rLAZdZYg.png', '2025-01-06 03:48:18.950796', '2025-01-06 03:48:18.953902', 39),
(67, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Cue 2-D is a sleek and efficient home security camera that ensures your property is always under watchful eyes. Its 2.0 Mpx 1/2.9\" CMOS sensor captures vibrant 1080p full HD videos, delivering sharp and detailed images for accurate surveillance. With a frame rate of 20 fps, you can expect smooth and clear video playback, even in fast-moving scenes. The camera&rsquo;s fixed lens with a 124&deg; field of view covers a wide area, reducing blind spots and ensuring comprehensive monitoring of your indoor spaces. Infrared LEDs provide powerful night vision capabilities, allowing you to see clearly up to 10 meters even in total darkness.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Installing and managing the IMOU Cue 2-D is a breeze thanks to its built-in Wi-Fi functionality. You can easily connect it to your home network and access live footage from anywhere via the intuitive mobile app. The camera uses H.264 video compression technology to minimize storage requirements without compromising video quality. For added convenience, it supports a microSD card up to 256 GB, providing ample space for local video storage. With its integrated microphone and speaker, you can communicate with family members or ward off intruders directly through the camera, making it a versatile addition to any smart home setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-cue-2-d/descriptions/202501-40-7-Xk1Mj6ZLNb.png', '2025-01-08 05:32:04.434305', '2025-01-08 07:52:28.785542', 40),
(68, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Cue 2-D security camera combines advanced features with ease of use, making it an excellent choice for home monitoring. Its high-resolution 2.0 Mpx sensor and 1080p video capability ensure you never miss any details. Whether it\'s capturing moments during the day or monitoring your home at night, the camera&rsquo;s IR LEDs offer night vision up to 10 meters, ensuring reliable performance in low-light conditions. The wide 124&deg; viewing angle minimizes the number of cameras needed to cover large areas, providing more coverage with less equipment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Connectivity is a key feature of the IMOU Cue 2-D, with support for IEEE 802.1b/g/n Wi-Fi standards, enabling a stable and fast connection to your home network. The camera&rsquo;s compact design makes it easy to install on walls or ceilings, blending seamlessly into any interior. Its H.264 compression format reduces bandwidth usage, ensuring smooth streaming without sacrificing video quality. The built-in microphone and speaker offer two-way audio communication, making it a perfect tool for checking in on loved ones or deterring potential threats. Store your recordings locally on a microSD card or stream them securely to your preferred cloud service for peace of mind.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-cue-2-d/descriptions/202501-40-2_6-1pwLM6Mi1d.png', '2025-01-08 05:32:04.442402', '2025-01-08 07:52:28.788232', 40),
(69, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Cue 2C-D is a state-of-the-art home security camera designed to bring peace of mind with its advanced features. Boasting a 1/2.8&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it delivers crystal-clear 1080p Full HD video quality, ensuring you don&rsquo;t miss a single detail. Its 3.6mm fixed lens provides an expansive 108&deg; field of view, making it suitable for wide-area surveillance. Equipped with enhanced night vision capabilities, it can monitor up to 10 meters in complete darkness, making it a perfect choice for round-the-clock security. With its sleek, compact design, the Cue 2C-D seamlessly blends into any home d&eacute;cor while providing powerful security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Connectivity is effortless with the IMOU Cue 2C-D, thanks to its Wi-Fi compatibility, supporting IEEE802.11b/g/n standards. The camera can be easily controlled and monitored through the Imou Life App, available on both iOS and Android platforms. ONVIF support ensures that it integrates smoothly with other security devices, enhancing your home security network. Whether you\'re at home or away, the Cue 2C-D provides a reliable way to keep an eye on your property. Its H.265 video compression technology saves storage space without compromising video quality, making it a smart choice for any homeowner.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-cue-2c-d/descriptions/202501-41-2c6-n4e3YFTChE.png', '2025-01-08 05:54:05.001659', '2025-01-08 07:52:01.617393', 41),
(70, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Experience next-level home security with the IMOU Cue 2C-D, a versatile and user-friendly camera designed to provide comprehensive surveillance. Its 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor captures sharp, detailed images at 1920 x 1080 resolution. The camera&rsquo;s wide field of view, measuring 89&deg; horizontally, 46&deg; vertically, and 108&deg; diagonally, ensures that every corner of your space is covered. Its robust night vision capability extends up to 10 meters, providing clear images even in complete darkness. The Cue 2C-D is a perfect fit for those who value security and convenience, delivering high-quality surveillance in a compact package.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a built-in microphone, the IMOU Cue 2C-D allows for real-time audio monitoring, adding an extra layer of security. Its 16x digital zoom lets you focus on specific areas, ensuring nothing goes unnoticed. The camera supports H.265 and H.264 video compression formats, which reduces bandwidth and storage requirements while maintaining high-quality footage. Its compatibility with the Imou Life App allows for easy access to live feeds and recorded videos from anywhere, making it an ideal solution for modern smart homes. The IMOU Cue 2C-D combines advanced technology with simplicity, offering a secure, user-friendly surveillance solution.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-cue-2c-d/descriptions/202501-41-2c4-lUIVLtSFpR.png', '2025-01-08 05:54:05.010186', '2025-01-08 07:52:01.619709', 41),
(71, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2-D is engineered to provide superior security surveillance with its 2.0 MP resolution, ensuring detailed and vibrant video quality. Its 1/2.9\" CMOS sensor captures clear footage even in low light conditions, complemented by infrared LEDs that enable night vision up to 10 meters. The camera\'s fixed 3.6 mm lens delivers a comprehensive field of view, allowing you to monitor a wide area effortlessly. Its sleek, modern design makes it suitable for any setting, blending seamlessly into your home or office environment.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Connectivity is a breeze with the IMOU Ranger 2-D, offering both Wi-Fi and Ethernet options to suit your network setup. The device supports H.264 video compression, optimizing storage space without compromising video quality. With a microSD slot supporting up to 256 GB, you can store extensive footage locally. Additionally, the built-in microphone and speaker provide two-way audio, enabling real-time communication with anyone on the premises.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2-d/descriptions/202501-42-5_1-0G7YyeaYku.png', '2025-01-08 06:16:42.959308', '2025-01-08 07:51:34.504877', 42),
(72, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Elevate your security setup with the IMOU Ranger 2-D, a camera designed for precision and reliability. Its high-resolution 2.0 MP sensor, coupled with a 1/2.9\" CMOS sensor, ensures every detail is captured in vivid clarity. The fixed lens offers an impressive field of view, making it perfect for both small and large spaces. Enhanced night vision capabilities allow for round-the-clock monitoring, with infrared LEDs providing visibility up to 10 meters in complete darkness.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2-D is built with user convenience in mind, featuring easy setup and versatile connectivity options. Whether you prefer a wired or wireless connection, the camera adapts to your network preferences. Its compact form factor does not compromise on functionality, offering robust features like two-way audio for interactive monitoring. The expandable storage through microSD cards ensures you have ample space to store your security footage, giving you peace of mind.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2-d/descriptions/202501-42-4_3-Fc73ummqEl.png', '2025-01-08 06:16:42.966904', '2025-01-08 07:51:34.507948', 42),
(73, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2 4MP-D is designed for those who demand high-quality security solutions. Featuring a 1/2.7&rdquo; 4 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it delivers crisp and clear video resolution at 2560 x 1440 pixels. Its 3.6mm fixed lens offers a broad field of view, with 92&deg; horizontal, 48&deg; vertical, and 109&deg; diagonal angles, making it perfect for wide-area surveillance. The camera\'s 355&deg; pan and -5~80&deg; tilt capabilities allow users to adjust the view remotely for comprehensive monitoring. Night vision functionality ensures visibility up to 10 meters, providing peace of mind even in total darkness.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2-4mp-d/descriptions/202501-43-241-JuxzMvnCnl.png', '2025-01-08 06:29:12.711268', '2025-01-08 07:50:57.464008', 43),
(74, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Connectivity is a breeze with the IMOU Ranger 2 4MP-D, thanks to its support for Wi-Fi IEEE802.11b/g/n, which offers a range of up to 50 meters in open fields. This makes it an excellent choice for both indoor and outdoor settings. The IMOU App, available for iOS and Android, provides easy access to live feeds, recorded footage, and camera settings, all from your smartphone. Additionally, its ONVIF compliance ensures that it integrates smoothly with other networked devices, offering flexibility and scalability in your security system setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2-4mp-d/descriptions/202501-43-247-Aex5D5dOoH.png', '2025-01-08 06:29:12.719162', '2025-01-08 07:50:57.468228', 43),
(75, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D is a versatile security camera that redefines home and office surveillance with its advanced imaging and connectivity features. Equipped with a 4-megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it captures detailed, high-resolution video at 2560 x 1440, ensuring every critical detail is visible. Its night vision capabilities extend up to 10 meters, providing reliable security even in complete darkness. The camera&rsquo;s wide-angle 3.6mm fixed lens offers a comprehensive view with a 92&deg; horizontal field of vision, while its 355&deg; pan and -5~80&deg; tilt functions allow for extensive area coverage. This ensures no blind spots, making it an ideal choice for monitoring large spaces or multiple areas.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D also excels in connectivity, featuring Wi-Fi IEEE802.11b/g/n support with a 50-meter open field range, ensuring a stable and reliable connection. Users can easily access live feeds and recorded footage through the Imou App available on both iOS and Android devices, providing on-the-go surveillance. The camera is also ONVIF compatible, allowing it to integrate seamlessly with existing security systems. Its sleek design and user-friendly interface make it a perfect addition to any security setup, offering peace of mind with state-of-the-art technology.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2c-4mp-d/descriptions/202501-44-3_7-4U7Y6r9q5J.png', '2025-01-08 06:38:16.068154', '2025-01-08 07:50:17.923607', 44),
(76, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for modern security needs, the IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D offers exceptional video quality and functionality. Its H.265/H.264 video compression technology ensures that footage is stored efficiently without compromising on quality, saving valuable storage space while providing smooth video playback. With up to 25/30fps frame rate, the camera delivers clear, fluid video, ideal for capturing fast-moving subjects or detailed scenes. The 8x digital zoom allows users to focus on specific areas of interest, providing enhanced detail and clarity for critical surveillance tasks.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D also features two-way audio, enabling real-time communication between the camera and the connected device. This is particularly useful for interacting with family members, employees, or even deterring potential intruders. The camera&rsquo;s durable build and sleek design make it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, while its intuitive installation process ensures that users can set up their surveillance system with minimal hassle. With its combination of high-tech features and ease of use, the IMOU Ranger 2C 4MP-D is an essential tool for comprehensive security management.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-ranger-2c-4mp-d/descriptions/202501-44-5_2-G3Ij4by2in.png', '2025-01-08 06:38:16.074985', '2025-01-08 07:50:17.926801', 44),
(77, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret stands out as a versatile security solution with its 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, delivering sharp and detailed 1080p video. Its night vision capability covers up to 30 meters, making it ideal for monitoring both indoor and outdoor spaces. With lens options of 2.8mm, 3.6mm, and 6mm, users can choose their preferred field of view to cover wide areas or focus on specific zones. The camera\'s durable design ensures reliable performance in various environments, while its sleek aesthetic blends seamlessly with modern decor.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Connectivity is at the heart of the IMOU Turret, featuring a 100Mbps Ethernet port and Wi-Fi support through dual internal antennas. This ensures stable and fast data transmission for real-time video streaming and alerts. The imou app enhances user experience by offering intuitive control, live view, and playback from anywhere. With ONVIF compatibility, the IMOU Turret easily integrates into existing security systems, providing a comprehensive surveillance solution.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-turret/descriptions/202501-45-6_3-2ZiafeKwtC.png', '2025-01-08 06:45:54.771043', '2025-01-08 07:49:39.656022', 45),
(78, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for convenience and security, the IMOU Turret comes equipped with advanced features such as built-in spotlight and 110dB siren. These functionalities not only illuminate dark areas but also deter intruders, enhancing the overall security setup. The camera\'s video compression technology (H.265/H.264) ensures high-quality video recording while optimizing storage space. Whether you\'re monitoring your home or business, the IMOU Turret delivers reliable performance with its up to 25/30fps frame rate and 8x digital zoom.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret&rsquo;s built-in microphone and speaker enable two-way communication, making it easy to interact with visitors or family members. Its compatibility with both iOS and Android through the imou app provides flexibility and ease of use, allowing you to monitor your property anytime, anywhere. With features like Soft AP for direct device connection, the IMOU Turret ensures a seamless setup and user experience, making it a top choice for comprehensive surveillance needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-turret/descriptions/202501-45-1_9-i7xCFMX2C9.png', '2025-01-08 06:45:54.777729', '2025-01-08 07:49:39.659516', 45),
(79, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret SE is a cutting-edge security camera tailored for modern surveillance needs. Featuring a 1/2.8&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor, it provides high-definition 1920 x 1080 resolution, capturing vivid and detailed images. Its night vision capability extends up to 30 meters (98 feet), ensuring continuous monitoring even in low-light conditions. The camera comes with two fixed lens options, 2.8mm and 3.6mm, offering wide-angle views of 92&deg; and 78&deg; respectively, to cover large areas with minimal blind spots. Designed for both indoor and outdoor use, the IMOU Turret SE is robust and reliable, making it a top choice for home and business security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret SE integrates seamlessly into existing networks with its Wi-Fi (IEEE802.11b/g/n) dual antenna setup and a 100Mbps Ethernet port. Its ONVIF compatibility allows for easy integration with other security systems, providing flexibility in system upgrades and expansions. Users can remotely access the camera via the Imou App on both iOS and Android devices, enabling real-time monitoring and playback of recorded footage. The camera\'s advanced video compression, H.265/H.264, ensures efficient storage without compromising video quality. Additionally, its built-in microphone allows for audio capture, adding an extra layer of security through sound monitoring.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-turret-se/descriptions/202501-46-se4-V6ejqb0Arh.png', '2025-01-08 06:57:27.323887', '2025-01-08 07:49:02.197055', 46),
(80, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Elevate your security system with the IMOU Turret SE, a feature-rich surveillance camera designed for dependable performance. Its 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor delivers superior 1080p HD resolution, ensuring clear and crisp video recordings. The camera excels in nighttime surveillance with its robust night vision capability, reaching up to 30 meters, which is ideal for monitoring vast outdoor spaces or poorly lit interiors. The available 2.8mm and 3.6mm fixed lenses provide flexibility in field of view, allowing you to choose the perfect lens for your specific surveillance needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Connectivity and ease of use are at the forefront of the IMOU Turret SE\'s design. With dual antenna Wi-Fi and a 100Mbps Ethernet port, it offers stable and versatile network options. The ONVIF protocol support ensures compatibility with a wide range of third-party devices, making it a flexible addition to any existing security setup. The Imou App provides intuitive remote access, enabling users to manage their security system from anywhere using their smartphone. Its advanced video compression technology and built-in microphone further enhance the overall surveillance experience, delivering high-quality video and audio for comprehensive security coverage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/imou-turret-se/descriptions/202501-46-se5-d5WYsiO7IA.png', '2025-01-08 06:57:27.330866', '2025-01-08 07:49:02.199593', 46),
(81, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The IMOU Turret SE 4MP stands out with its exceptional 4MP resolution, capturing detailed footage at 2560 x 1440 pixels. Its advanced 1/2.8&rdquo; 2 Megapixel Progressive CMOS sensor ensures vibrant and sharp images, making it perfect for identifying faces and objects even from a distance. This security camera excels in low-light conditions with a night vision range of up to 30 meters, providing peace of mind during nighttime or in dark environments. The camera is equipped with a choice of 2.8mm or 3.6mm fixed lenses, offering flexibility in field of view to suit various monitoring needs. With a 90&deg; horizontal view for the 2.8mm lens and a 76&deg; horizontal view for the 3.6mm lens, it covers a broad area effectively.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/turret-se-4mp/descriptions/202501-47-4_2-TFrYQu7UrZ.png', '2025-01-08 07:14:19.695964', '2025-01-08 07:47:22.949087', 47),
(82, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Designed for seamless connectivity, the IMOU Turret SE 4MP features Wi-Fi support with IEEE802.11b/g/n and dual antennas, ensuring stable and robust wireless performance. It also includes a 100Mbps Ethernet port for wired connections, catering to different installation scenarios. This camera supports ONVIF protocol, making it compatible with a wide range of third-party devices for enhanced flexibility. The IMOU App, available on both iOS and Android, enables users to monitor live feeds, review recorded footage, and manage camera settings remotely, making security management effortless. Additionally, the camera\'s video compression technology, utilizing H.265/H.264 codecs, ensures high-quality video streams with efficient bandwidth usage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/turret-se-4mp/descriptions/202501-47-5-6Go8jL8oD5.png', '2025-01-08 07:14:19.703118', '2025-01-08 07:47:22.953421', 47),
(83, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is a cutting-edge security camera designed for high-definition surveillance. With its 1080p real-time live view, users can monitor their premises with outstanding image clarity, ensuring they never miss a crucial moment. The camera\'s 1/2.7\" CMOS progressive scan sensor allows for high-quality video capture, even in low-light environments, offering clear and accurate visuals at all times. Its advanced TDN (IR-Cut) technology and features like AGC and DWDR enhance image quality in various lighting conditions, ensuring the camera performs well in both bright and dark settings. Additionally, the 3.6mm lens provides a wide-angle view, making the camera suitable for monitoring large areas without compromising detail.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with an IR distance of up to 20 meters, the HONEYWELL HBL2R1 guarantees consistent surveillance performance, even in total darkness. Whether you\'re protecting a home or business, this camera provides superior nighttime visibility, thanks to its minimum illumination of 0 Lux when the infrared (IR) feature is active. The camera is powered by 12VDC, which ensures compatibility with a wide range of power sources. With AHD/CVBS output, users can easily integrate this camera into their existing surveillance systems. Offering both versatility and reliability, the HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is the ideal choice for anyone looking to enhance their security setup with a high-performance, user-friendly camera.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbl2r1/descriptions/202501-48-hb1-F6OVrtTuq9.png', '2025-01-08 07:46:12.211153', '2025-01-09 07:50:14.584679', 48),
(84, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is designed to deliver high-quality video surveillance with a range of advanced features to ensure optimal performance. This security camera supports 1080p real-time live viewing, ensuring that every image is captured in stunning clarity for effective monitoring. With its 1/2.7&rdquo; CMOS progressive scan sensor, the camera delivers excellent image quality, even in challenging lighting situations. The built-in TDN (IR-Cut), AGC, and DWDR features work together to provide superior contrast and sharpness, even in low-light or high-contrast environments. The camera\'s 3.6mm lens offers an expansive field of view, making it suitable for various surveillance applications.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">For nighttime monitoring, the HONEYWELL HBL2R1 excels with its 0 Lux minimum illumination when the IR is activated, ensuring visibility even in complete darkness. The camera also features an impressive IR distance of up to 20 meters, providing clear and detailed images over a large area during the night. Designed to be easy to integrate, it supports 12VDC power, making it compatible with many different systems. Additionally, its AHD/CVBS output provides flexibility when connecting to various surveillance equipment. With all of these features combined, the HONEYWELL HBL2R1 is a high-performing, reliable solution for any surveillance needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbl2r1/descriptions/202501-48-hb4-vSY8xNQyrY.png', '2025-01-08 07:46:12.218586', '2025-01-09 07:50:14.588299', 48),
(85, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HED3PR3 security camera is a robust solution for both residential and commercial surveillance needs. Its advanced IR LEDs, which provide coverage up to 30 meters, ensure you can monitor areas even in complete darkness. The Smart IR technology adapts to varying lighting conditions to provide uniform infrared illumination, resulting in sharp, clear images no matter the time of day. Its IP66-rated waterproof housing makes it an ideal choice for outdoor installations, standing strong against rain, dust, and harsh weather. This camera is designed to withstand the rigors of everyday use while providing continuous protection, ensuring that both the security of your property and the reliability of the system are never compromised.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Perfect for any security setup, the HED3PR3 features a 2.8mm F2.1 fixed lens, providing a wide field of view for monitoring large areas with fewer cameras. It also supports configurable motion detection settings, allowing users to customize the system to fit their unique needs. The camera tamper detection feature alerts you in the event of any attempts to disrupt or damage the camera. This, combined with the alarm notification system, enhances the security and peace of mind offered by the camera. Ideal for both novice users and professional installers, the HONEYWELL HED3PR3 offers an intelligent and user-friendly surveillance experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hed3pr3/descriptions/202501-49-HE3-gBQIdKDEAd.png', '2025-01-08 07:56:18.254350', '2025-01-10 03:50:58.441565', 49),
(86, '<p dir=\"ltr\">HONEYWELL\'s HED3PR3 camera is designed to meet the growing demand for high-quality, reliable, and durable security surveillance. Its IR LEDs are powerful enough to provide up to 30 meters of visibility in low light, ensuring that you don&rsquo;t miss any important events, even after dark. With Smart IR technology, the camera optimizes the distribution of infrared light, ensuring even and detailed images without overexposure or underexposure. Whether monitoring a home, office, or industrial space, the camera&rsquo;s rugged IP66 waterproof housing makes it suitable for use in all kinds of outdoor environments, providing durability that can withstand rain, wind, and extreme temperatures.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The HED3PR3 is equipped with a fixed 2.8mm F2.1 lens for a wide field of view, so you can monitor larger areas with fewer devices. The camera also boasts advanced motion detection and tamper detection capabilities, ensuring that any suspicious activity is quickly detected. With configurable alarm settings, users can tailor the system to their specific needs, receiving real-time alerts whenever the camera senses any unusual activity. Whether you\'re concerned about intruders or ensuring the security of a remote location, the HONEYWELL HED3PR3 is the perfect choice for comprehensive surveillance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hed3pr3/descriptions/202501-49-HE4-o20YgleV1j.png', '2025-01-08 07:56:18.261588', '2025-01-10 03:50:58.444562', 49),
(87, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBD3PR1 is a high-performance security camera that delivers clear and reliable surveillance footage for both residential and commercial use. With a 2304 x 1296 resolution, it ensures crisp, detailed images at 20 fps, even in low-light environments. Featuring infrared (IR) LEDs, this camera provides night vision up to 100 feet, making it suitable for 24/7 monitoring. The camera comes equipped with a 3.6mm fixed lens and an 81&deg; horizontal field of view, ensuring a broad and clear perspective of your property. Its RJ45 Ethernet connection with PoE (Power over Ethernet) simplifies installation by delivering both power and data over a single cable. Onvif compliance ensures seamless integration with other security systems. The camera is also equipped with an IR cut filter, enhancing its ability to capture accurate color images in varying lighting conditions. Compatible with the HonView Touch app for both iOS and Android, it allows for convenient remote monitoring. The IP66 rating ensures that it can withstand tough outdoor conditions, offering durability and weatherproofing. Whether for home or business use, the Honeywell HBD3PR1 is a reliable and advanced solution for your surveillance needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbd3pr1/descriptions/202501-50-HB3-rNxlq4vF9g.png', '2025-01-08 07:59:37.246014', '2025-01-10 03:49:26.174200', 50),
(88, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBD3PR1 is engineered for those seeking superior security performance and convenience. Offering impressive 2304 x 1296 resolution at 20 fps, it provides clear, high-definition images even under low light conditions, making it perfect for monitoring key areas. The camera&rsquo;s built-in IR cut filter enhances image accuracy by reducing color distortion, ensuring true-to-life footage. With its 3.6mm fixed lens and a wide 81&deg; horizontal field of view, it captures a broad area, providing comprehensive surveillance coverage.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you\'re protecting a commercial property or your home, the Honeywell HBD3PR1 ensures reliable performance with its IP66 weatherproof rating, making it ideal for outdoor use in any environment. Its PoE capability simplifies installation, offering an easy plug-and-play setup with no need for a separate power supply. The camera integrates seamlessly with your existing security system thanks to its ONVIF compatibility, and remote monitoring is made simple with the HonView Touch app for iOS and Android. With night vision capabilities extending up to 100 feet, the Honeywell HBD3PR1 ensures that your property is secure around the clock.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbd3pr1/descriptions/202501-50-HB4-5N6AaMzcJw.png', '2025-01-08 07:59:37.253198', '2025-01-10 03:49:26.177450', 50),
(89, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBW4PR1 is a robust, high-definition surveillance camera built to meet the demands of modern security systems. Equipped with a 2 MP or 4 MP progressive scan imager, it provides exceptional video clarity and detailed imaging. The camera includes a 3.6 mm fixed lens for a wide field of view, and its true day/night feature, powered by an IR-cut filter, enables reliable performance under varying lighting conditions. With a wide dynamic range of up to 120 dB, this camera excels in environments with contrasting light levels, ensuring detailed images even in challenging conditions. It is designed to capture high-quality footage in low-light settings, offering color video down to 0.01 lux and full IR functionality in total darkness, providing up to 130 ft (40 m) of IR illumination.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether used for commercial or residential surveillance, the HBW4PR1 is engineered for seamless integration into existing systems. It features H.264 Main Profile compression, allowing for efficient video storage without sacrificing quality. Triple stream support allows for multiple video feeds to be customized, and the camera can handle up to 20 simultaneous connections. The device also supports corridor mode, a unique feature that optimizes the image capture for narrow, vertical spaces like hallways. Additionally, it is powered by PoE or 12 VDC, and its weatherproof housing, with an IP66 ingress protection rating, ensures reliable operation even in harsh weather conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbw4pr1/descriptions/202501-51-HB1-D9w7Z5UrVw.png', '2025-01-08 08:03:58.808673', '2025-01-10 03:47:12.059525', 51),
(90, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The Honeywell HBW4PR1 camera combines powerful surveillance features with user-friendly integration. Its advanced imaging capabilities, including a choice of 2 MP or 4 MP sensors, provide clear, sharp video that is ideal for monitoring critical areas. The camera&rsquo;s true day/night performance ensures it continues to deliver high-quality images regardless of the lighting conditions. Equipped with IR-cut filter technology, the HBW4PR1 automatically adjusts to provide optimal performance in both daylight and nighttime environments. The camera&rsquo;s wide dynamic range (up to 120 dB) makes it ideal for capturing high-contrast scenes, ensuring that important details are visible in both bright and shadowed areas.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Additionally, the HBW4PR1 is designed for flexibility and ease of use. With H.264 Main Profile compression, the camera helps conserve bandwidth and storage while maintaining excellent video quality. Its triple stream capability allows for customized video streaming, ensuring the right footage is accessible in different formats. Supporting up to 20 simultaneous connections, the HBW4PR1 is perfect for high-demand environments. The camera also includes PoE and 12 VDC support, making installation quick and efficient. Its weatherproof IP66 housing ensures protection from harsh elements, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications, all while offering a plug-and-play experience with Honeywell Performance Series Embedded NVRs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hbw4pr1/descriptions/202501-51-HB3-ChsQif5NtF.png', '2025-01-08 08:03:58.818068', '2025-01-10 03:47:12.062030', 51),
(91, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 security camera is designed to deliver exceptional video surveillance in all lighting conditions. Equipped with advanced imaging technology, it supports both 2 MP (1/2.7&rdquo;) and 4 MP (1/3&rdquo;) resolutions, ensuring high-quality footage. With its true day/night functionality and wide dynamic range, this camera can capture fine details even in challenging lighting environments. The built-in 3.6 mm or 2.8 mm fixed lens allows for flexible installation and wide coverage, while the IR-cut filter ensures accurate color reproduction in both day and night conditions. Whether in daylight or total darkness, the HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 guarantees reliable video footage with low-light performance down to 0.01 lux in color or 0 lux with the IR LEDs on.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hew4prw3/descriptions/202501-52-HE1-jXbsoHk4FE.png', '2025-01-08 08:08:42.540478', '2025-01-10 03:44:24.901385', 52),
(92, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 is perfect for both residential and commercial security systems, offering exceptional durability and performance. Its weatherproof housing with an IP66 ingress protection rating ensures that the camera can withstand the harshest weather conditions. It supports Power over Ethernet (PoE) and 12 VDC power, allowing for flexible installation options and simplifying wiring needs. This camera is also compatible with Honeywell Performance Series Embedded NVRs, providing a seamless plug-and-play experience. With features like corridor mode and support for up to 20 simultaneous connections, the HONEYWELL HEW4PRW3 is designed to meet the needs of both small and large surveillance systems, offering excellent scalability and ease of use.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/honeywell-hew4prw3/descriptions/202501-52-HE2-Qt3Sr1LlW1.png', '2025-01-08 08:08:42.548085', '2025-01-10 03:44:24.904467', 52),
(93, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION E-HWIB is a state-of-the-art surveillance camera that combines high-performance technology with ease of use. Featuring high-definition video quality, it captures every detail with precision, ensuring you never miss a moment. Its motion detection technology sends instant alerts to your smartphone, keeping you informed about any activity around your premises. Designed for outdoor use, this camera is weather-resistant and can withstand extreme conditions, providing reliable performance year-round. With its night vision capabilities, the E-HWIB delivers clear images even in complete darkness, ensuring your property is protected 24/7.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwib/descriptions/202501-53-HV4-uq53wrUm7I.png', '2025-01-08 08:14:50.479670', '2025-01-09 02:08:47.967325', 53);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(94, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Installation of the HIKVISION E-HWIB is a breeze, thanks to its user-friendly design and comprehensive installation guide. The camera seamlessly integrates with existing security systems and offers remote monitoring via a dedicated app, allowing you to check on your property from anywhere. Its AI-powered analytics not only detect motion but also distinguish between different types of movements, reducing false alarms and enhancing security accuracy. The E-HWIB\'s sleek and compact design ensures it can be discreetly installed without compromising on its powerful capabilities. HIKVISION\'s commitment to delivering top-tier security solutions is evident in every feature of this exceptional surveillance camera.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwib/descriptions/202501-53-HV1-hcWnZIZAax.png', '2025-01-08 08:14:50.486295', '2025-01-09 02:08:47.970561', 53),
(95, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The HIKVISION E-HWID is a state-of-the-art electronic hardware identification device, purpose-built to deliver superior security and authentication services. It incorporates advanced biometric technology, allowing for accurate and quick identification of users, thereby enhancing access control in high-security environments. The device&rsquo;s durable build is suitable for both indoor and outdoor usage, ensuring long-term performance under various conditions. Its compatibility with multiple security systems makes it a versatile choice for businesses looking to upgrade their security infrastructure. The E-HWID&rsquo;s sleek and modern design not only enhances its aesthetic appeal but also ensures it fits seamlessly into any setting, from high-tech corporate offices to critical infrastructure facilities.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwid/descriptions/202501-54-HWID1-JkOJBTbgHP.png', '2025-01-08 08:17:12.011974', '2025-01-09 02:12:49.129618', 54),
(96, '<p dir=\"ltr\">HIKVISION&rsquo;s E-HWID features a user-friendly interface that simplifies the process of managing and configuring security settings. Its intuitive design ensures that users can easily navigate through its features, reducing the need for extensive training or technical support. The device supports a range of connectivity options, including wireless and wired interfaces, providing flexibility in installation and integration. Additionally, the E-HWID&rsquo;s energy-efficient design ensures it operates effectively with minimal power consumption, making it a cost-effective solution for long-term use. With a strong focus on reliability and innovation, HIKVISION has engineered the E-HWID to meet the evolving security needs of modern businesses.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwid/descriptions/202501-54-HWID3-3ffdICPoj7.png', '2025-01-08 08:17:12.018405', '2025-01-09 02:12:49.132927', 54),
(97, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION E-HWIT is designed to redefine the standards of security surveillance with its high-definition imaging and robust functionality. This device captures crystal-clear video, even in low-light conditions, thanks to its advanced night vision capabilities. Its compact design allows for discreet installation, making it suitable for various locations, from small homes to large commercial properties. The E-HWIT is equipped with state-of-the-art motion detection technology that sends instant alerts to users, ensuring prompt responses to any unusual activity. Additionally, the system supports multiple users and devices, providing a collaborative platform for enhanced security management.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwit/descriptions/202501-55-HWIT3-qgYbE3rWC1.png', '2025-01-08 08:20:07.490445', '2025-01-09 02:16:00.106830', 55),
(98, '<p dir=\"ltr\">With HIKVISION E-HWIT, users gain access to a comprehensive surveillance system that integrates seamlessly with existing networks. Its plug-and-play setup simplifies installation, while the intuitive interface ensures easy operation and management. The system offers extensive storage options, accommodating large volumes of video footage with efficient compression technology to save space without compromising quality. Remote access capabilities allow users to monitor their properties from anywhere, providing peace of mind and control over security. Furthermore, HIKVISION E-HWIT features smart analytics, offering insights and data that help in identifying trends and improving overall safety protocols.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-e-hwit/descriptions/202501-55-HWIT4-qAGiSWujCC.png', '2025-01-08 08:20:07.497020', '2025-01-09 02:16:00.110782', 55),
(99, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0E-I is engineered to provide superior surveillance capabilities with its 2 MP high-resolution imaging. Its compact bullet design is both aesthetic and functional, making it a perfect fit for various environments. The camera\'s infrared night vision extends up to 30 meters, ensuring clear visibility in complete darkness. Built with a durable IP67-rated housing, it withstands harsh weather conditions, making it suitable for outdoor installations. The integration of advanced H.265+ compression technology minimizes bandwidth usage and storage space, making it cost-effective without compromising image quality.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The camera&rsquo;s WDR technology delivers excellent performance in challenging lighting conditions, balancing the contrast to provide a clear view of both dark and bright areas. Its motion detection and smart alert features ensure that any unusual activity is immediately flagged, enhancing security responsiveness. The DS-2CD1023G0E-I is easy to install and integrate with existing security systems, thanks to its Power over Ethernet (PoE) support, which simplifies the wiring process. This reliable and high-performance network camera is an ideal choice for ensuring the safety and security of your premises.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0e-i/descriptions/202501-56-DS1-j9ic2boy3w.png', '2025-01-08 08:23:07.324612', '2025-01-09 02:19:57.937713', 56),
(100, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0E-I combines advanced surveillance technology with user-friendly features to offer comprehensive security coverage. This 2 MP network bullet camera captures detailed video footage, making it ideal for monitoring large areas such as parking lots, building entrances, and industrial sites. Its 2.8mm fixed lens provides a wide field of view, while the infrared LEDs ensure clear night vision up to 30 meters, ensuring round-the-clock surveillance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The camera&rsquo;s robust design includes an IP67-rated housing that protects against dust, rain, and other environmental factors, ensuring consistent performance in various weather conditions. The support for H.265+ video compression significantly reduces storage requirements, allowing for extended recording times and lower storage costs. The DS-2CD1023G0E-I also offers intelligent video analytics such as line crossing detection and intrusion detection, enabling proactive threat detection and response. Whether for business or personal use, this camera delivers reliable, high-quality security monitoring.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0e-i/descriptions/202501-56-DS3-ewExZZ0Dtp.png', '2025-01-08 08:23:07.333586', '2025-01-09 02:19:57.941871', 56),
(101, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IU is a robust and reliable network bullet camera that delivers 2MP high-definition video. Its advanced IR technology ensures clear imaging up to 30 meters, even in complete darkness. Designed for flexibility, this camera can be mounted both indoors and outdoors, thanks to its IP67-rated weatherproof housing. The camera features a built-in microphone, allowing for audio recording, which is crucial for comprehensive surveillance. With support for H.265+ video compression, it significantly reduces bandwidth and storage costs while maintaining superior image quality.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iu/descriptions/202501-57-DS1-XdcAehIwT9.png', '2025-01-08 08:28:53.677184', '2025-01-09 02:24:01.628480', 57),
(102, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DS-2CD1023G0-IU comes equipped with intelligent features like motion detection and line crossing detection, providing real-time alerts for any suspicious activity. Its sleek and compact design makes installation simple and unobtrusive, blending seamlessly into various environments. The camera is compatible with a wide range of network protocols, ensuring smooth integration with existing security systems. Whether you need to monitor a retail store, office, or outdoor area, this camera provides a reliable security solution. Its easy-to-use interface and robust construction make it a preferred choice for those seeking high-quality surveillance without the complexity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iu/descriptions/202501-57-DS3-vvEx1MPArX.png', '2025-01-08 08:28:53.684691', '2025-01-09 02:24:01.631049', 57),
(103, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) is a 2MP network bullet camera designed to deliver superior image quality and reliability. With a 1920 x 1080 resolution, it provides crystal-clear video footage, ensuring that every detail is captured. The camera is equipped with an infrared range of up to 30 meters, allowing for effective night-time surveillance. Its IP67-rated weatherproof housing protects it from dust and water, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. This camera supports PoE (Power over Ethernet), simplifying installation by reducing the need for additional wiring.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iuf-c/descriptions/202501-58-DS4-qBLr9TdXok.png', '2025-01-08 08:34:00.644880', '2025-01-09 02:31:12.090845', 58),
(104, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Built for efficiency, the HIKVISION DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) features H.265+ video compression, which reduces bandwidth usage and storage needs without compromising image quality. It also includes advanced motion detection and intrusion detection capabilities, providing users with real-time alerts for any unusual activity. The integrated built-in microphone captures clear audio, adding an extra layer of security to your surveillance system. This camera is compatible with various third-party software, making it versatile and easy to integrate into existing security systems. Ideal for small to medium-sized businesses, the DS-2CD1023G0-IUF (C) offers an affordable yet powerful surveillance solution.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1023g0-iuf-c/descriptions/202501-58-DS2-qDs6NOtDtO.png', '2025-01-08 08:34:00.652364', '2025-01-09 02:31:12.095806', 58),
(105, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IU is a state-of-the-art 2MP network camera perfect for both home and business security. Designed with advanced features like WDR, this camera ensures high-quality video even in challenging lighting conditions. It has a 4mm lens that offers a wide viewing angle, capturing clear footage over large areas. The camera\'s built-in microphone enables high-quality audio capture, providing additional context to security footage. For convenient installation, it comes with Power over Ethernet (PoE), simplifying setup by combining power and data into a single cable.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This camera is designed with long-term durability in mind, offering a robust and reliable solution for continuous surveillance. It utilizes the H.265+ video compression standard, providing high-resolution video with significantly reduced bandwidth consumption, saving on storage costs. The DS-2CD1323G0-IU is also compatible with the Hik-Connect mobile app, enabling users to monitor live footage remotely from their smartphones, tablets, or computers. Whether monitoring a home, office, or retail space, the HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IU is an exceptional choice for a wide range of security needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iu/descriptions/202501-59-DS3-D0SZwRR5io.png', '2025-01-08 08:38:43.866642', '2025-01-09 02:37:31.939200', 59),
(106, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IU is a powerful 2MP surveillance camera equipped with cutting-edge features to enhance security and ease of use. With a wide dynamic range (WDR) for improved visibility in high-contrast environments, it provides sharp and detailed images in both bright and low-light conditions. The camera&rsquo;s 4mm lens offers a broad field of view, making it ideal for covering large areas such as entrances, parking lots, or interior spaces. Thanks to its built-in microphone, it records audio along with video, adding an extra layer of detail to your surveillance footage.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With H.265+ video compression technology, the DS-2CD1323G0-IU reduces the storage space required for video recordings while maintaining high video quality. It also supports Power over Ethernet (PoE), which simplifies installation by using a single cable for both data and power. For easy access and control, the camera integrates with the Hik-Connect app, allowing users to view live video, playback recordings, and receive alerts directly from their mobile devices. This makes it a highly flexible and efficient security solution for both residential and commercial properties.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iu/descriptions/202501-59-DS2-wnGMEOM4om.png', '2025-01-08 08:38:43.873190', '2025-01-09 02:37:31.942153', 59),
(107, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The HIKVISION DS-2CD1123G0-I is a high-performance 2MP network camera designed to offer reliable surveillance for a variety of settings. Featuring a 1/2.7\" CMOS sensor, this camera delivers sharp, crisp images with high resolution, ensuring that fine details are captured clearly. It has a 4mm fixed lens, providing a wide angle of view for enhanced coverage and monitoring. Whether you\'re watching over a large commercial space or securing a residential area, this camera ensures optimal image quality even in low-light environments, thanks to its IR illumination with a range of up to 30 meters. Additionally, the DS-2CD1123G0-I supports H.265+ video compression, enabling high-quality video streaming while minimizing bandwidth and storage needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This camera is built to withstand harsh outdoor conditions, with its IP67-rated weatherproof casing, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor surveillance. The camera supports advanced security protocols, including HTTPS, which ensures secure video transmission, protecting your surveillance data from unauthorized access. For added flexibility, the DS-2CD1123G0-I integrates easily with other security systems, offering seamless connectivity for comprehensive monitoring solutions. With its motion detection functionality, the camera can trigger alarms when suspicious activity is detected, providing immediate alerts to keep your property secure. The compact and discreet design of the DS-2CD1123G0-I makes it an excellent choice for a wide range of surveillance needs, offering high-quality performance and ease of use.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1123g0-i/descriptions/202501-60-DS2-R1Bey3gcmp.png', '2025-01-09 01:38:24.491572', '2025-01-09 02:41:15.254571', 60),
(108, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1123G0-I is a powerful yet compact bullet camera designed to offer high-definition video surveillance. Featuring a 2MP resolution and a 1/2.7\" Progressive Scan CMOS sensor, the camera provides exceptional image clarity, capturing even the smallest details in both daylight and low-light environments. The 4mm fixed lens offers a wide-angle view, making it ideal for monitoring larger areas like parking lots, entrances, and hallways. With its infrared capability, the DS-2CD1123G0-I can illuminate areas up to 30 meters, ensuring that you have clear visibility even in complete darkness. This camera also utilizes H.265+ compression technology, which significantly reduces bandwidth consumption while maintaining high video quality, making it a cost-effective solution for long-term surveillance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed with durability in mind, the DS-2CD1123G0-I is housed in an IP67-rated enclosure, ensuring it can withstand harsh environmental conditions, from rain and snow to extreme temperatures. Its ability to support HTTPS for secure video transmission adds an extra layer of security to your surveillance system. The camera features built-in motion detection, sending immediate alerts if any movement is detected in its field of view. Ideal for use in a variety of settings, including commercial, residential, and industrial environments, the DS-2CD1123G0-I is easy to install and integrate into existing surveillance systems. With its advanced features, reliability, and ease of use, the DS-2CD1123G0-I is a top choice for enhancing your security setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1123g0-i/descriptions/202501-60-DS1-AQ8hqeBZUo.png', '2025-01-09 01:38:24.499472', '2025-01-09 02:41:15.257076', 60),
(109, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1143G0-I is a 2.0 MP IP camera that integrates cutting-edge features for superior surveillance performance. With a 1/3\" progressive scan CMOS sensor, it ensures sharp, clear images even in low-light conditions, while its 2.8mm fixed focal lens provides a wide field of view. This makes the camera suitable for monitoring large areas, both indoors and outdoors. Equipped with up to 30 meters of infrared (IR) range, it offers exceptional night vision capabilities, ensuring security even in complete darkness. The camera&rsquo;s dual stream technology enables efficient data transmission, allowing for both high-definition video recording and smooth live streaming.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for versatility, the DS-2CD1143G0-I also boasts advanced video enhancement technologies, including Digital WDR (Wide Dynamic Range) and 3D DNR (Digital Noise Reduction). These features improve image quality in scenes with both bright and dark areas, ensuring balanced and detailed footage. Its support for Power over Ethernet (PoE) simplifies installation, eliminating the need for separate power cables and providing a more streamlined setup. Built to endure the elements, this camera has an IP67 rating for weatherproofing and an IK10 rating for resistance against physical impacts, making it perfect for both commercial and residential surveillance needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1143g0-i/descriptions/202501-61-DS2-by0wAQUTDd.png', '2025-01-09 01:43:10.039994', '2025-01-09 02:44:20.678797', 61),
(110, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1143G0-I offers professional-grade surveillance features in a compact, reliable design. The camera&rsquo;s 2.0 megapixel resolution provides high-definition video clarity, while its 1/3\" progressive scan CMOS sensor captures detailed images in all lighting conditions. The 2.8mm lens ensures a wide-angle view of up to 115 degrees, which is ideal for monitoring large areas with a single camera. Its night vision capability extends up to 30 meters, giving you peace of mind even in complete darkness. The DS-2CD1143G0-I supports H.265+ compression for reduced bandwidth and storage requirements, ensuring you save on storage costs without compromising on quality.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This camera is equipped with the latest video processing technologies, including Digital WDR for better clarity in high-contrast lighting environments and 3D DNR for minimizing noise in low-light conditions. PoE functionality makes the camera easy to install and operate by allowing both power and data to be transmitted through a single cable. With its robust IP67 and IK10 ratings, the DS-2CD1143G0-I is suitable for a variety of environments, from high-risk urban areas to more serene residential spaces. It is a powerful, flexible surveillance solution for any security setup, providing both quality footage and reliability.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1143g0-i/descriptions/202501-61-DS4-y2uf7pkrYV.png', '2025-01-09 01:43:10.048233', '2025-01-09 02:44:20.681657', 61),
(113, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IUF is a reliable and powerful security solution that combines advanced features for surveillance needs. It offers a 1/2.8\" progressive scan CMOS sensor, providing high-resolution 1080p video at 30fps for clear and sharp images. This camera is perfect for both indoor and outdoor use with its durable design and IP67 weatherproof rating, ensuring it withstands harsh weather conditions. It also includes a built-in microphone, allowing for audio recording alongside the video footage, adding another layer of security. The DS-2CD1323G0-IUF&rsquo;s 2.8mm fixed focal lens provides a wide viewing angle, making it an ideal choice for monitoring large areas, such as parking lots, hallways, or building entrances.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iuf/descriptions/202501-63-DS4-3Qg23A6izQ.png', '2025-01-09 02:00:21.673211', '2025-01-09 02:46:28.069971', 63),
(114, '<p dir=\"ltr\">With impressive technologies like Digital WDR and 3D DNR, the HIKVISION DS-2CD1323G0-IUF performs exceptionally in varied lighting conditions. The Digital WDR technology helps to balance the light and dark areas in the frame, producing detailed and clear images in environments with high contrast lighting. Additionally, the 3D DNR feature reduces digital noise, improving the clarity of the footage, even in low-light situations. The camera&rsquo;s Power over Ethernet (PoE) function simplifies the installation process by eliminating the need for separate power cables. Supporting modern video compression formats like H.265+ and H.264, this camera ensures optimal video quality with reduced storage requirements, making it an excellent option for long-term, cost-effective surveillance systems.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd1323g0-iuf/descriptions/202501-63-DS5-XRK5mqD8sC.png', '2025-01-09 02:00:21.679459', '2025-01-09 02:46:28.073518', 63),
(115, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) is a cutting-edge 2MP IP security camera, designed to provide outstanding image quality in both day and night conditions. Featuring a 1/3\" Progressive CMOS sensor, this camera ensures excellent resolution of 1920x1080, delivering clear and crisp images at 25fps(P) or 30fps(N). Its Infrared (IR) capabilities are particularly impressive, with a range of up to 30 meters, allowing it to capture high-definition footage in total darkness. The camera&rsquo;s ICR (Infrared Cut Filter) enhances color reproduction during the day, while the camera automatically switches to IR mode for optimal night vision.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) is equipped with advanced features like 3D DNR (Digital Noise Reduction) and BLC (Backlight Compensation), ensuring consistent video quality, even in challenging lighting situations. Whether you&rsquo;re monitoring a well-lit environment or a dimly lit area, this camera provides clear footage with minimal distortion. The inclusion of multiple video compression formats such as H.265+, H.265, H.264, and MJPEG ensures that you can store and transmit video with reduced bandwidth usage without sacrificing quality. Compatible with both DC12V power input and PoE (Power over Ethernet), the DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) offers flexible installation options for a wide range of surveillance applications. The integration with HIK-Connect allows for seamless cloud-based management, making it easy to monitor your security system from anywhere at any time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd2021g1-i-b/descriptions/202501-64-DS4-Q9xThA8oaF.png', '2025-01-09 02:53:01.326211', '2025-01-09 02:55:21.117296', 64),
(116, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) is a professional-grade security camera that combines reliable performance with advanced imaging technology. Built with a 1/3\" Progressive CMOS sensor, it captures high-definition 1080p video at up to 30fps, ensuring that every detail is recorded clearly. With its impressive IR range of up to 30 meters, the DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) is perfect for both indoor and outdoor environments, providing round-the-clock surveillance with superior clarity. The camera&rsquo;s ICR (Infrared Cut Filter) helps to improve image quality by adjusting for various lighting conditions, while the 3D DNR feature minimizes digital noise, delivering cleaner footage.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This camera&rsquo;s versatility is enhanced by its support for multiple video codecs including H.265+, H.265, H.264, and MJPEG, which ensure smooth streaming and optimized storage. It also comes with PoE (Power over Ethernet) support, enabling easy setup and eliminating the need for additional power cables. HIKVISION&rsquo;s cloud-based service, HIK-Connect, provides an added layer of convenience, allowing for remote access to camera feeds and control from any internet-enabled device. This makes the DS-2CD2021G1-I(B) an ideal choice for businesses and homes looking for an efficient, cost-effective surveillance solution that doesn&rsquo;t compromise on quality or reliability.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd2021g1-i-b/descriptions/202501-64-DS6-B4UmdKU4Di.png', '2025-01-09 02:53:01.333950', '2025-01-09 02:55:21.120388', 64),
(117, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I 4 MP Bullet Camera is designed to provide exceptional image quality with its high 4 MP resolution, capturing every detail in sharp clarity. The camera&rsquo;s advanced 120 dB WDR (Wide Dynamic Range) technology ensures clear and balanced footage even in challenging lighting conditions, such as bright backlighting or strong shadows. Additionally, the H.265+ compression technology optimizes video storage, reducing bandwidth and saving on storage space without sacrificing image quality. With its IP67 rating, this camera is built to withstand harsh environmental conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, providing reliable performance in any weather. Whether you\'re looking to secure a residential property or a commercial space, the HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I offers robust and efficient surveillance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd2043g2-i/descriptions/202501-65-DS4-fK2avFq5XZ.png', '2025-01-09 03:00:00.153856', '2025-01-09 03:01:08.453357', 65),
(118, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Incorporating cutting-edge deep learning algorithms, the HIKVISION DS-2CD2043G2-I excels in identifying and classifying human and vehicle targets, improving the accuracy and efficiency of security monitoring. This intelligent feature allows the camera to focus on critical objects, reducing false alarms and increasing overall surveillance effectiveness. The camera&rsquo;s ability to deliver high-definition video at all times, regardless of lighting challenges, ensures that it provides reliable monitoring 24/7. Additionally, the camera is equipped with multiple advanced features, including motion detection and remote access capabilities, to enhance security operations. Easy to install and configure, the DS-2CD2043G2-I offers an ideal solution for those looking for a powerful, smart surveillance system.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/hikvision-ds-2cd2043g2-i/descriptions/202501-65-DS5-H7oAv698CA.png', '2025-01-09 03:00:00.160971', '2025-01-09 03:01:08.455793', 65),
(119, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-Z Starlight HDCVI IR Eyeball Camera is a state-of-the-art security solution tailored for environments requiring high-quality video surveillance, even in low-light conditions. Its Starlight technology ensures that even in near darkness, the camera captures detailed and clear images, making it ideal for areas with minimal lighting. The motorized 2.7-12mm lens allows for easy zoom and focus adjustments, providing flexibility for various surveillance needs. This camera supports a maximum resolution of 1080P at 30fps, delivering crisp and smooth video footage. With switchable HD and SD output, users can select the most suitable video quality based on their specific requirements.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-z/descriptions/202501-66-hd1-PiRU2s7cho.png', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.216804', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.222551', 66),
(120, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Built to endure the toughest conditions, the DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-Z is IP67 rated, offering complete protection against dust and water ingress. This durability makes it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use, ensuring long-lasting performance. The camera\'s Smart IR feature enhances night vision by adjusting the infrared intensity based on the proximity of objects, thereby preventing overexposure and ensuring clear images up to 60 meters in complete darkness. Operating on DC12V, this camera is energy-efficient and easy to integrate into existing security systems. Its sleek eyeball design not only provides a modern aesthetic but also allows for versatile mounting options, making it a perfect fit for various installation scenarios.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-z/descriptions/202501-66-hd6-lxjVV1o2IL.PNG', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.224526', '2025-01-09 03:11:59.228283', 66),
(121, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA security camera is engineered to provide unmatched clarity and performance in challenging lighting conditions. Its Starlight technology enhances visibility in low-light scenarios, making it perfect for nighttime surveillance. Capable of capturing high-definition footage at 30fps in 1080P, this camera ensures that every detail is recorded with precision. The motorized 2.7-12mm lens allows for flexible zoom and focus, providing comprehensive coverage without the need for manual adjustments. Additionally, the built-in microphone adds audio surveillance, offering a complete security solution.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for versatility, the DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA features switchable HD and SD outputs, making it compatible with a variety of security systems. The Smart IR technology provides superior night vision, adjusting the infrared intensity to prevent overexposure in dark environments, with a maximum IR range of 60 meters. Its durable construction, rated IP67, ensures that the camera withstands harsh weather conditions, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor applications. Operating on a DC12V power supply, it offers a reliable and energy-efficient security option for your home or business.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-za/descriptions/202501-67-hd6-SVQy5i5eFe.PNG', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.478954', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.484676', 67),
(122, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA camera is a state-of-the-art security solution that excels in both performance and durability. Its Starlight feature is designed to capture high-quality images in low-light conditions, enhancing security during nighttime hours. This camera supports up to 30 frames per second at full HD 1080P resolution, delivering crisp and clear video for accurate monitoring. The motorized zoom lens ranging from 2.7 to 12mm allows for precise focusing, ensuring every corner of the monitored area is covered.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with Smart IR technology, the DAHUA DH-HDW1230TN-ZA adapts its infrared illumination to the surroundings, maintaining image clarity even in complete darkness up to 60 meters. Its robust IP67-rated casing protects against dust and water, making it suitable for outdoor use in various weather conditions. The built-in microphone adds an extra layer of security by recording audio, offering comprehensive monitoring capabilities. Easy to install and maintain, this camera is an excellent choice for those looking to enhance their security system with a reliable and advanced surveillance tool.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1230tn-za/descriptions/202501-67-hd2-QnknmOPzLt.png', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.486503', '2025-01-09 03:18:58.489877', 67),
(123, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA is a robust surveillance camera engineered to meet the demands of modern security systems. Its standout feature, Starlight technology, ensures superior low-light performance, capturing vivid and detailed images in near-dark environments. With 120dB True WDR, the camera excels in challenging lighting conditions, providing balanced exposure in both bright and dark areas of the scene. The 3DNR (3D Noise Reduction) technology minimizes noise, delivering clear and crisp images even in low light. Supporting a resolution of 1080P at 30fps, it offers high-definition video output, suitable for various security applications.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The camera features a motorized 2.7-13.5mm lens, allowing precise control over the viewing angle and focus, adapting to different monitoring requirements. The HD/SD switchable function enhances its flexibility, making it compatible with various system setups. Additionally, the built-in mic and audio input interface enable real-time audio monitoring, adding an extra layer of security. Smart IR technology extends the camera\'s night vision range to 80 meters, ensuring optimal performance in complete darkness. With an IP67 rating, the DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA is designed to withstand harsh weather conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw2241t-za/descriptions/202501-68-HF6-u8Pvc6mFvI.png', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.952514', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.959080', 68),
(124, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for demanding surveillance applications, the DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA offers cutting-edge features for enhanced security coverage. Its Starlight technology is a game-changer for low-light performance, delivering high-quality images in near-total darkness. This capability is bolstered by 120dB True WDR, which corrects exposure to ensure clarity in scenes with variable lighting, such as entrances or windows. The 3D Noise Reduction (3DNR) further refines image quality by reducing visual noise, producing clear and sharp video feeds at all times. With a frame rate of 30fps at 1080P, it ensures smooth and detailed video playback.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The camera&rsquo;s 2.7-13.5mm motorized lens offers the flexibility to adjust the focus and zoom remotely, ensuring optimal coverage for different surveillance needs. It supports HD and SD output, making it adaptable for various system requirements. The built-in microphone and audio input interface enhance situational awareness by capturing high-quality audio, making it a comprehensive security solution. Its Smart IR technology extends night vision capabilities up to 80 meters, ensuring clear visibility in complete darkness. The rugged design, with an IP67 rating, ensures durability and reliability, even in extreme weather conditions, making the DAHUA DH-HFW2241T-ZA a top-tier choice for security professionals.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw2241t-za/descriptions/202501-68-HF2-EHnLbZawg9.png', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.960702', '2025-01-09 05:12:50.964189', 68),
(125, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1230T security camera is engineered to provide exceptional surveillance in various environments. Its Starlight technology ensures superior low-light performance, capturing vivid and clear images even in challenging lighting conditions. The camera supports a maximum resolution of 1080P at 30fps, offering smooth and detailed video footage. With switchable HD and SD output, users can easily adjust the camera\'s settings to match their specific monitoring requirements. The 3.6mm fixed lens provides an optimal viewing angle, with optional 2.8mm and 6mm lenses available for more customized surveillance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for durability and reliability, the DAHUA DH-HFW1230T features an IP67-rated aluminum housing, making it resistant to dust and water ingress. This robust construction ensures the camera operates effectively in various weather conditions, from heavy rain to dust storms. The Smart IR technology enhances night vision capabilities, with an IR range of up to 30 meters, allowing for clear visibility in complete darkness. Powered by DC12V, the camera ensures consistent performance and energy efficiency, making it a dependable choice for long-term security needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1230t/descriptions/202501-69-HF4-geNthlxUhw.png', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.967504', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.973677', 69),
(126, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Experience superior surveillance with the DAHUA DH-HFW1230T, a security camera designed to meet the demands of modern security systems. Its advanced Starlight technology allows it to capture clear images in low-light environments, making it ideal for night-time monitoring. Supporting up to 1080P resolution at 30fps, the camera delivers high-quality video that is both smooth and detailed. The switchable HD and SD output feature provides flexibility in video format, accommodating various installation requirements. The 3.6mm fixed lens offers a balanced field of view, with additional lens options available for tailored coverage.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Built to withstand harsh environmental conditions, the DAHUA DH-HFW1230T boasts an IP67-rated aluminum housing that protects it from water and dust. This durability ensures reliable performance in outdoor settings, whether in residential, commercial, or industrial environments. The Smart IR technology adjusts the intensity of the infrared LEDs to prevent overexposure in low-light scenes, ensuring clear images at night with a range of up to 30 meters. Powered by a stable DC12V supply, the camera offers consistent operation and is a cost-effective solution for enhancing security.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1230t/descriptions/202501-69-HF5-7jROPHdiuM.png', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.975510', '2025-01-09 05:20:11.979270', 69),
(127, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW3231E-Z Starlight Network Bullet Camera is engineered for superior performance in a variety of environments. Its advanced Starlight technology enhances low-light performance, ensuring clear, color-rich images even in near-dark conditions. The 120dB true WDR feature balances light and shadow, providing clarity in scenes with strong backlighting. The 3D Noise Reduction minimizes noise, improving image clarity in low-light settings. With a maximum frame rate of 30fps at 1080P resolution, this camera delivers high-quality, smooth video suitable for various security applications.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The motorized 2.7-12mm lens allows for easy zoom adjustments, offering a wide field of view or focused coverage as needed. Its Smart IR technology optimizes infrared illumination for clear night vision up to 100 meters, ensuring comprehensive monitoring around the clock. Dual-output capabilities enable simultaneous HD and SD streams, providing flexible viewing and recording options. Built to endure, the camera features an IP67-rated weatherproof and IK10-rated vandal-resistant aluminum casing, making it ideal for outdoor and high-risk areas.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw3231e-z/descriptions/202501-70-hf3-WHzrgYSW0n.png', '2025-01-09 05:24:14.309772', '2025-01-09 05:24:14.315482', 70),
(128, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW3231E-Z is designed for optimal performance in diverse surveillance scenarios, from residential properties to commercial premises. Its standout Starlight technology ensures exceptional low-light performance, capturing clear images with accurate colors even in minimal lighting. The 120dB true WDR function enhances visibility in high-contrast environments, making it perfect for areas with fluctuating lighting conditions. The 3DNR feature reduces noise in video footage, improving overall image quality, especially in dimly lit areas.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with a motorized 2.7-12mm lens, the camera allows remote zoom adjustments for precise monitoring. The Smart IR technology adjusts infrared intensity to prevent overexposure in low-light environments, offering up to 100 meters of night vision. With dual HD and SD outputs, the camera caters to diverse connectivity needs, enhancing system flexibility. The robust construction, featuring an IP67 and IK10-rated aluminum housing, ensures the camera withstands harsh weather and vandalism, making it a reliable choice for any security system.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw3231e-z/descriptions/202501-70-hf5-JiNHF6Bd7X.png', '2025-01-09 05:24:14.317071', '2025-01-09 05:24:14.320753', 70),
(129, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED is a state-of-the-art surveillance camera built to deliver exceptional video quality and performance in various environments. Featuring Full-color Starlight technology, this camera ensures vibrant color imaging in low-light settings, allowing users to capture detailed footage even at night. Its 20m LED distance provides clear visibility in complete darkness, making it an ideal choice for outdoor and night-time monitoring. The camera supports up to 30fps at 1080P, ensuring smooth, real-time video recording without any lag. Whether for residential or commercial use, this versatile camera offers excellent performance and adaptability for different surveillance systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED also offers flexible format compatibility, supporting CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI switchable formats. This makes it an ideal solution for upgrading existing security systems without needing to replace other equipment. Additionally, the built-in microphone enhances the camera\'s functionality, enabling audio recording alongside video footage for a complete monitoring solution. With a 3.6mm fixed lens (optional 2.8mm), this camera captures wide-angle views, ensuring comprehensive coverage of any area. With its IP67 rating, the camera is built to withstand harsh weather conditions, providing long-lasting reliability in both indoor and outdoor installations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1239tln-a-led/descriptions/202501-71-hd5-LqSMOnNmlM.png', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.758359', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.763806', 71),
(130, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED offers a sophisticated solution for modern surveillance needs with its advanced features and high-quality performance. The camera&rsquo;s Full-color Starlight technology provides superior low-light performance, allowing users to capture clear, bright images in dark environments. Its 20-meter LED distance ensures that night-time surveillance is equally effective, with minimal reliance on external lighting. With a 1080P resolution and a maximum 30fps frame rate, the camera ensures that all captured footage is sharp, smooth, and detailed, making it an essential tool for security monitoring.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for flexibility, the DAHUA DH-HDW1239TLN-A-LED supports multiple video formats, including CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI. This adaptability allows users to integrate the camera into various security systems, providing cost-effective upgrades. The built-in microphone enhances surveillance by capturing not only video but also audio, providing a more comprehensive monitoring solution. With a 3.6mm fixed lens and the option to switch to a 2.8mm lens, the camera offers a versatile field of view for different installation needs. Its IP67-rated housing ensures that it can withstand the elements, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations, even in extreme weather conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1239tln-a-led/descriptions/202501-71-hd6-x0Ew5x3bNE.png', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.765557', '2025-01-09 05:37:53.769318', 71),
(131, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is engineered to provide crystal-clear full-color starlight imaging, even in low-light conditions, offering superior clarity compared to standard cameras. With a 40-meter LED distance, it ensures reliable night-time surveillance with exceptional illumination. The camera\'s high-definition video quality at 1080P and its ability to operate at 30fps provides smooth, detailed footage, ensuring that every detail is captured. Its switchable CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI compatibility gives users flexibility in connecting the camera to different video systems. Whether you\'re installing a new security setup or upgrading an existing one, this camera delivers optimal performance and versatility.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed with durability in mind, the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is IP67 rated, providing full protection against dust and water, making it perfect for use in harsh weather conditions. The camera is equipped with a 3.6mm fixed lens that offers a wide field of view, covering a larger area with minimal distortion. Furthermore, the built-in microphone captures ambient sound, adding an extra layer of surveillance. Whether monitoring a large outdoor area or a specific entry point, this camera ensures that you can rely on it for both day and night surveillance needs. Powered by a 12V&plusmn;30% DC input, it is easy to install and integrates seamlessly into your existing security infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-a-led/descriptions/202501-72-hf5-2DQh2TQTiB.png', '2025-01-10 02:27:33.605906', '2025-01-10 02:44:36.200402', 72),
(132, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is a high-quality security camera that combines cutting-edge technology with practical features for effective surveillance. It provides full-color starlight performance, delivering bright, clear images even in low-light conditions, which is essential for monitoring at night or in poorly lit environments. The camera\'s 40m LED range ensures that your surveillance system remains effective over a longer distance, illuminating areas that would otherwise be dark. The 1080P resolution and 30fps frame rate guarantee smooth and detailed video, while the switchable CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI modes allow for versatile installation options, regardless of the existing system.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Constructed from a durable combination of metal and plastic, the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-A-LED is designed for longevity and reliability, even in challenging environments. It is IP67 rated, providing resistance to dust and water, so it can withstand outdoor conditions without compromising on performance. The camera also features a built-in microphone for capturing audio, adding to its comprehensive surveillance capabilities. With its easy integration into existing security setups and a 3.6mm fixed lens offering wide coverage, this camera is an excellent choice for a wide range of surveillance needs, providing both quality video and sound recording.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-a-led/descriptions/202501-72-hf6-pZN2fobxJq.png', '2025-01-10 02:27:33.625382', '2025-01-10 02:44:36.202987', 72),
(133, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED is a cutting-edge security camera that boasts full-color starlight technology, providing exceptional video quality even in low-light conditions. Equipped with a 40m LED distance, this camera ensures clear visibility for both day and night surveillance, with no compromise in image quality. The camera captures footage at a maximum resolution of 1080P with a smooth 30fps rate, ensuring crisp, high-definition video for enhanced security monitoring. It also supports multiple video output formats such as CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI, making it a versatile solution for a variety of security systems and configurations. Whether you\'re upgrading an existing setup or installing a new system, the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED is designed to meet your needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-led/descriptions/202501-73-hf3-MBBaH3z4f7.png', '2025-01-10 02:44:07.132135', '2025-01-10 02:48:32.412015', 73),
(134, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Built for outdoor use, the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED features an IP67-rated housing that ensures the camera remains functional even in harsh weather conditions. The camera is powered by a 12V &plusmn;30% DC input, making it a reliable and energy-efficient option for long-term security installations. A built-in microphone (minus model) allows for audio recording, enhancing the surveillance experience by capturing sound along with video. The camera\'s 3.6mm fixed lens provides a wide field of view, with an optional 2.8mm lens available for those requiring a different viewing angle. This combination of advanced features and rugged durability makes the DAHUA DH-HFW1239TLMN-LED a top choice for both residential and commercial security applications.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hfw1239tlmn-led/descriptions/202501-73-hf6-6ynQg5lo4Y.png', '2025-01-10 02:44:07.143792', '2025-01-10 02:48:32.414577', 73);
