(135, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3 is a robust, high-definition security camera designed for efficient surveillance and security monitoring. Featuring a 2.7-12mm vari-focal lens, it provides an adjustable focal range for enhanced image clarity, allowing users to zoom in on important areas for detailed monitoring. Its maximum resolution of 720P at 30fps ensures smooth, high-quality video capture. The camera&rsquo;s infrared capabilities, coupled with Smart IR technology, ensure clear and sharp images even in low-light conditions, with an infrared range of up to 30 meters.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for durability, the DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3 is built to withstand extreme weather conditions with its IP67 rating, ensuring it remains operational in the harshest environments. The camera is also vandal-proof, with an IK10 rating, providing extra protection against tampering or damage. It can be powered by a DC 12V input, making it an efficient choice for both home and business security setups. With its flexible HD and SD output switchability, this camera offers versatile options for various surveillance configurations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw1100r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-74-hd4-oxYtmx47m8.png', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.199464', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.204175', 74),
(136, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW1100R-VF-S3 is ideal for users looking for a versatile and reliable security camera solution. Offering exceptional image quality with a maximum 720P resolution at 30fps, it guarantees that every detail is captured clearly, whether used for monitoring large areas or smaller spaces. The 2.7-12mm vari-focal lens provides users with control over their zoom level, giving them the flexibility to focus on specific regions of interest, making it suitable for diverse monitoring applications. The camera is equipped with Smart IR, which automatically adjusts the intensity of infrared light, ensuring visibility even in complete darkness, with a maximum IR range of 30 meters.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The camera&rsquo;s rugged design includes an IP67 weatherproof rating, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations, even in challenging weather conditions. With an IK10 rating, it can resist vandalism and tampering, making it a reliable choice for high-security areas. The switchable HD and SD output feature allows users to choose between high-definition and standard-definition video, providing flexibility depending on the specific surveillance setup. Powered by DC 12V, the camera ensures consistent performance with minimal power consumption. It&rsquo;s an ideal choice for securing properties, warehouses, parking lots, and more.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw1100r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-74-hd7-DQjAuoqkxO.png', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.205622', '2025-01-10 02:52:09.209496', 74),
(137, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3 network camera offers high-definition surveillance with its 2MP CMOS sensor, providing clear video at up to 1080P resolution. With a flexible 2.7~12mm vari-focal lens, users can adjust the focal length to capture wide-angle or zoomed-in views, making it ideal for a variety of security needs. This camera supports real-time video transmission, including high-speed, long-distance streaming for uninterrupted coverage. The advanced imaging technology features such as Digital Wide Dynamic Range (DWDR), Auto White Balance (AWB), Automatic Gain Control (AGC), Backlight Compensation (BLC), and 2D Noise Reduction (2DNR), ensure crisp and clear footage under different lighting conditions. Additionally, the Smart IR technology enhances night-time visibility with IR LEDs that can reach up to 30 meters.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw1200r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-75-hd3-sElzvHc8Kk.png', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.474438', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.479621', 75),
(138, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Durable and weather-resistant, the DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3 camera is built to withstand challenging environmental conditions, with its IP67 rating offering protection against dust and water. It features the ability to switch between HD and SD video output, providing flexibility for various setups and requirements. The camera can be controlled remotely via the OSD Menu, accessible through coaxial cables, simplifying installation and management. This model is powered by DC12V, ensuring stable operation for extended periods, even in outdoor settings. With its versatile design, high-quality imaging, and long-distance transmission capabilities, the DAHUA DH-HDBW1200R-VF-S3 is a robust solution for enhancing security in various commercial and residential applications.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw1200r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-75-hd4-FR2iO392mM.png', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.481281', '2025-01-10 03:11:32.484459', 75),
(139, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z is a robust surveillance camera built for high-quality monitoring in diverse environments. Featuring Starlight technology, it captures clear, full-color images in ultra-low light conditions, making it ideal for day and night security applications. With a 120dB True WDR (Wide Dynamic Range), this camera adjusts exposure automatically to capture both bright and dark areas simultaneously, ensuring crisp and clear images in high-contrast lighting scenarios. Coupled with 3D Noise Reduction (3DNR), it minimizes visual noise, resulting in clearer and sharper footage. The camera&rsquo;s motorized lens offers a flexible focal length range from 2.7mm to 12mm, making it easy to adjust the field of view to suit any monitoring need.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed to meet the highest standards, the DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z also offers impressive night vision capabilities. With Smart IR technology and a maximum IR range of 50 meters, it ensures visibility even in total darkness, providing excellent coverage for 24/7 surveillance. Its sturdy IP67 weatherproof rating guarantees protection against dust, rain, and snow, while the IK10 impact-resistant housing safeguards the camera from physical tampering. Powered by both AC24V and DC12V, this camera is adaptable to different installation environments, offering reliable, continuous operation in any location.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw3231e-z/descriptions/202501-76-hb5-NCt5F3HWXd.png', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.836109', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.842139', 76),
(140, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z is a feature-packed camera designed to meet the highest standards of security surveillance. Its advanced Starlight technology ensures superior image quality, even in extremely low light, without sacrificing color detail. This makes it perfect for monitoring areas with variable or low lighting. The 120dB True WDR technology optimizes image quality by compensating for both dark and bright lighting conditions simultaneously, providing clear and sharp images. The camera&rsquo;s 3D Noise Reduction technology further enhances image quality by reducing grain and noise, ensuring clarity and detail in every frame.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with a motorized 2.7-12mm lens, the DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z provides a versatile field of view, allowing easy adjustments for optimal coverage. Its IR range of up to 50 meters ensures effective monitoring in total darkness, making it a reliable choice for 24/7 surveillance. The camera is housed in a durable, weather-resistant enclosure, offering IP67 protection against dust and water and IK10 resistance against impact. Powered by AC24V or DC12V, the DAHUA DH-HDBW3231E-Z is flexible for various installations, providing outstanding security in both indoor and outdoor environments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdbw3231e-z/descriptions/202501-76-hb7-hMZupUs0CI.png', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.844291', '2025-01-10 03:16:03.847757', 76),
(141, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3 is a 2MP surveillance camera offering a range of advanced features that ensure optimal video quality and performance. With its 1/2.7\" CMOS sensor, it provides high-definition video at 1080p resolution at 25/30 frames per second, making it an ideal choice for capturing sharp, detailed images. Its 2.7-12mm vari-focal lens provides versatile zoom and focus capabilities, allowing users to adjust the viewing angle to meet specific surveillance needs. Whether you\'re monitoring a large outdoor area or a smaller indoor space, the camera\'s real-time transmission feature ensures high-speed, long-distance data delivery. Additionally, its HD/SD switchable option allows for flexibility in video quality, depending on the installation requirements.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1200r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-77-hd3-qvx0opNi6g.png', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.860521', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.866355', 77),
(142, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed for maximum reliability, the DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3 comes equipped with features that adapt to varying environmental conditions. Its Day/Night (ICR) functionality and DWDR (Digital Wide Dynamic Range) ensure the camera captures clear images in both bright and low-light situations, while its advanced noise reduction technology (2DNR) helps minimize image distortion. With a maximum IR LED range of 30 meters, the camera provides excellent night vision even in total darkness. Built to withstand harsh weather conditions, the DAHUA DH-HDW1200R-VF-S3 is rated IP67, making it dustproof and waterproof for outdoor installations. The camera also supports easy configuration through coaxial control via the OSD menu, offering a user-friendly setup experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1200r-vf-s3/descriptions/202501-77-hd5-wP3oWN7tgg.png', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.868026', '2025-01-10 03:23:24.871348', 77),
(143, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED is a cutting-edge security camera that brings advanced technology and exceptional performance to your surveillance system. Equipped with a 3.6mm fixed lens, this camera delivers a wide field of view and precise image quality. Its full-color starlight technology ensures clear and vivid footage even in the most challenging lighting conditions, making it ideal for round-the-clock surveillance. With the added benefit of 40-meter LED distance, this camera provides excellent visibility even in the dark, ensuring you never miss any critical details. The built-in microphone also allows for audio monitoring, providing an added layer of security.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED supports multiple video formats, including CVI, CVBS, AHD, and TVI, making it highly versatile and compatible with a variety of security systems. Its IP67 rating guarantees reliability in outdoor environments, offering protection against dust and water. Additionally, this camera is powered by a 12V&plusmn;30% DC input, ensuring consistent performance and energy efficiency. Whether you&rsquo;re securing a residential property or a business, the DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED is the perfect solution for clear, detailed, and dependable surveillance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1239tn-a-led/descriptions/202501-78-hd4-G2IX1YvFRP.png', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.811749', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.816983', 78),
(144, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed to provide superior video surveillance in both bright and low-light conditions, the DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED stands out with its full-color starlight feature. This feature allows it to capture vibrant and detailed images even in challenging nighttime environments. With a built-in 3.6mm lens, this camera offers a wide viewing angle for greater coverage. It supports a frame rate of up to 30 frames per second at 1080p resolution, ensuring smooth and high-quality video output for better monitoring.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with a 40-meter LED distance, this camera excels in night vision, providing clear and sharp images without compromising quality. The built-in microphone, available on the -A model, enables audio capture, adding an additional layer of security for monitoring and recording conversations. The DAHUA DH-HDW1239TN-A-LED is also highly durable with its IP67 weather proof rating, making it resistant to dust and water, ideal for both indoor and outdoor environments. With its switchable video formats and efficient power consumption of 12V&plusmn;30% DC, it is a reliable choice for any surveillance setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/dahua-dh-hdw1239tn-a-led/descriptions/202501-78-hd6-quWTQnU1LL.png', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.818837', '2025-01-10 03:28:52.822718', 78),
(145, '<p>The ZKTeco MB10-VL is a state-of-the-art biometric time and attendance system designed to provide touchless, multi-biometric identification. Featuring Visible Light Facial Recognition technology, this terminal ensures seamless and accurate user identification without physical contact, enhancing both security and user experience. With Linux-based software, it boasts reliable performance and high efficiency, making it an ideal choice for businesses looking to upgrade their employee management systems.</p>\r\n<p>The MB10-VL supports various functions like automatic status switching, multiple verification methods, and bell scheduling, allowing businesses to customize it according to their needs. It can handle up to 100 face templates, 500 fingerprints, and store 50,000 transaction records. These features make the device a perfect solution for businesses with diverse employee management needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/mb10-vl-time-attendance-and-access-control/descriptions/202501-79-1_6-VgpV3vUcWj.png', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.675055', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.679934', 79),
(146, '<p>The ZKTeco MB10-VL is equipped with a 2.8-inch TFT display for easy navigation and user interaction. This compact terminal offers multiple communication options including TCP/IP, USB Host, and optional Wi-Fi for flexible integration into your existing systems. The 256MB RAM and 256MB Flash memory ensure fast processing, while the system&rsquo;s capacity for 50,000 transactions guarantees a seamless experience even in high-traffic environments.</p>\r\n<p>Its intuitive interface and user-friendly features, such as self-service queries and T9 input, make it easy for businesses to manage time and attendance without extensive technical knowledge. The system&rsquo;s innovative facial recognition technology, combined with fingerprint authentication, ensures secure and efficient access control, reducing the risks of unauthorized entry.</p>', 'products/mb10-vl-time-attendance-and-access-control/descriptions/202501-79-2-3Mzho1b7ku.jpg', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.681245', '2025-01-10 06:30:03.684141', 79),
(147, '<p>The ZKTECO EFace10/ID/WIFI is a cutting-edge facial recognition terminal built for modern access control and time management needs. The device leverages Visible Light Facial Recognition technology, which allows for accurate and fast recognition at a greater distance than traditional near-infrared systems. This innovation ensures that users are recognized quickly and with high precision, enhancing security while reducing wait times. It&rsquo;s ideal for locations where efficiency, hygiene, and security are top priorities, such as offices, warehouses, and other high-traffic environments.</p>\r\n<p>With its compact design, the ZKTECO EFace10 comes equipped with a 4.3-inch TFT display for easy monitoring and configuration. The system supports up to 500 face templates and 1,000 user cards, making it scalable for various organizational sizes. Additionally, the ZKTECO EFace10 provides real-time synchronization of up to 150,000 transactions, making it a reliable choice for businesses that need to track attendance and access patterns accurately.</p>', 'products/eface10-id-wifi/descriptions/202501-80-4_2-hDze0TYKkC.png', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.167856', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.173082', 80),
(148, '<p>The EFace10 offers versatility in communication, supporting TCP/IP, USB Host, and optional Wi-Fi connectivity, allowing seamless integration with existing systems. The device runs on a Linux-based operating system, ensuring stability and long-term reliability for continuous use. Its intuitive interface also features several standard functions, including self-service queries, bell scheduling, and multiple verification methods, such as face recognition, card scanning, and PIN entry, making it highly adaptable to different security needs. Whether used for employee time tracking or access control, this terminal ensures seamless operation and a high level of security.</p>\r\n<p>The ZKTECO EFace10/ID/WIFI&rsquo;s touchless design is a significant benefit in terms of hygiene, as it reduces physical contact with the device, making it ideal for environments that prioritize cleanliness and health. With its high-quality facial recognition algorithm and multiple verification options, it provides a high level of security while maintaining convenience for end-users. Businesses can rely on this system to streamline attendance, improve security protocols, and maintain an efficient workflow with minimal intervention.</p>', 'products/eface10-id-wifi/descriptions/202501-80-5-CKraz2afKe.PNG', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.174473', '2025-01-10 06:39:51.178106', 80),
(149, '<p>The ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L is an innovative biometric access control and time attendance terminal that integrates facial recognition and palm verification for optimal security. With its 4\" touch screen, this device provides an easy-to-use interface while maintaining the highest level of security with its advanced biometric algorithms. The facial recognition system supports up to 800 faces and 800 palm prints, ensuring smooth and rapid access and attendance tracking, even in high-demand environments. Additionally, its palm verification system adds an extra layer of authentication, reinforcing the device&rsquo;s capability to support multiple verification methods.</p>\r\n<p>This hybrid system is equipped with robust communication features such as TCP/IP, USB Host, and optional Wi-Fi, which ensures seamless integration with existing network infrastructure. With the ability to store up to 150,000 transactions, it is well-suited for businesses with high-volume access and attendance requirements. The ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L also features advanced security functions such as anti-passback, tamper switch alarms, and customizable access levels to further enhance the security of your premises.</p>', 'products/speedface-v4l/descriptions/202501-81-3_5-E8KyNxCF8A.png', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.688394', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.694372', 81),
(150, '<p>The ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L combines visible light facial recognition and palm verification to deliver high-security access control and time attendance management. The device&rsquo;s intelligent algorithms, powered by advanced computer vision technology, ensure fast and precise identification, making it an ideal choice for organizations that require reliable biometric security solutions. It supports up to 1,000 card users and allows businesses to manage employee access and attendance effortlessly.</p>\r\n<p>With a large transaction capacity and diverse communication options, the SpeedFace-V4L is perfect for businesses of all sizes, offering flexibility and scalability. The terminal is designed for easy integration with other security systems, such as ID cards and ADMS, while providing a simple user interface for effortless operation. Whether used for access control or time tracking, the ZKTeco SpeedFace-V4L provides a comprehensive solution to meet modern security and attendance management needs.</p>', 'products/speedface-v4l/descriptions/202501-81-4_2-v4V2WLQlYr.png', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.696201', '2025-01-10 06:46:48.699480', 81),
(151, '<p>The SA40 operates on dual frequencies: 125kHz for EM cards and 13.56MHz for IC cards, including S50, S70, and IC EV1 types. This dual-frequency capability ensures compatibility with a wide range of RFID cards, accommodating existing access control systems and offering flexibility for future upgrades. The device\'s operating voltage ranges from DC 9 to 15V, making it adaptable to various power supply configurations. It functions effectively within an operating temperature range of -20&deg;C to 60&deg;C and a storage temperature range of -20&deg;C to 80&deg;C, ensuring reliable performance in diverse environmental conditions.&nbsp;</p>', 'products/sa40/descriptions/202501-82-4_2-nJQQsSVccN.PNG', '2025-01-10 06:53:28.338989', '2025-01-10 06:54:23.504892', 82),
(152, '<p>Designed for ease of use, the SA40 allows administrators to add or delete users directly on the device, streamlining user management without the need for additional software. It features a built-in relay, door sensor, exit button, and doorbell interface, providing comprehensive access control functionalities. The device\'s scratch-proof plastic construction ensures durability and longevity, maintaining its appearance and functionality over time. Its sleek and compact design allows for seamless integration into various settings, including offices, residential buildings, and public facilities.&nbsp;</p>', 'products/sa40/descriptions/202501-82-3_5-vbmCHmQX0S.PNG', '2025-01-10 06:53:28.346345', '2025-01-10 06:54:23.507270', 82),
(153, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-31 Corridor Light with One Magnetic Nameplate is engineered to improve visibility and communication in busy corridors. It features a fire-resistant ABS plastic construction, ensuring long-lasting performance and safety. This corridor light surface mounts directly to the wall, allowing for quick and hassle-free installation. The magnetic nameplate offers a customizable solution for clear identification, making it ideal for dynamic environments where room names or statuses may frequently change. Its minimalist design blends seamlessly with various interior d&eacute;cors, providing both form and function.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Designed with practicality in mind, the NIR-31 Corridor Light is perfect for healthcare settings, educational institutions, and office buildings. Its fire-resistant material enhances safety standards, while the straightforward surface mounting reduces installation time and costs. The magnetic nameplate can be easily updated, ensuring that information is always current and clearly displayed. Whether you\'re managing a large facility or a small office, this corridor light simplifies operations and improves communication, making it an invaluable addition to any space.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-31-corridor-light-with-one-magnetic-nameplate/descriptions/202501-83-ai3-kTgr93mkml.png', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.278884', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.283974', 83),
(154, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-31 Corridor Light with One Magnetic Nameplate is a versatile and dependable corridor signaling solution. Crafted from high-quality, fire-resistant ABS plastic, it ensures safety without compromising durability. Its surface-mount design allows for quick installation directly onto walls, saving time and reducing the need for additional mounting hardware. The magnetic nameplate adds a level of customization and ease, allowing users to update signage effortlessly to reflect changing room statuses or occupant names.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This corridor light is well-suited for high-traffic areas, where clear communication is crucial. Its durable, fire-resistant construction ensures it can withstand the rigors of daily use in demanding environments like hospitals, schools, and corporate offices. The NIR-31\'s understated design ensures it complements a variety of interior styles while providing essential functionality. Whether for new installations or retrofitting existing spaces, this corridor light delivers a reliable and adaptable solution for improving operational efficiency and safety.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-31-corridor-light-with-one-magnetic-nameplate/descriptions/202501-83-ai2-VlKXCaYYwl.png', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.285388', '2025-01-10 07:32:24.288692', 83),
(155, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NI-RC Bedside Handheld Sub Station is a state-of-the-art communication device designed to improve patient care in medical facilities. This innovative substation allows patients to easily call and communicate with the NIM master station using a handheld device that can be clipped to a bed or hung on a hook. Its hands-free communication capability ensures that patients can quickly and effortlessly reach caregivers, promoting a higher level of safety and care. Built from durable plastic, the NI-RC is designed to withstand the demands of a healthcare environment, offering reliability and longevity. Its compatibility with a 3-conductor overall shield wire ensures clear audio transmission up to 650 feet, making it suitable for various room configurations within a facility.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its robust construction and practical design, the NI-RC substation provides a user-friendly interface that simplifies communication for patients. The hands-free feature ensures that patients with limited mobility can still access help without difficulty, enhancing their comfort and security. The unit\'s flexibility in mounting options means it can be conveniently placed within reach, adapting to the needs of different patients and rooms. This versatility and ease of use make the AIPHONE NI-RC a valuable asset in improving the efficiency and quality of patient care in hospitals, clinics, and other medical settings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/ni-rc-bedside-handheld-sub-station/descriptions/202501-84-ai4-BFk1gppHy1.png', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.987707', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.992962', 84),
(156, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NI-RC Bedside Handheld Sub Station represents the pinnacle of convenience and reliability in patient-care communication systems. Specifically engineered for use in healthcare environments, it allows seamless call-in and two-way communication with the NIM master station. The handheld design provides patients with the flexibility to keep the device at their side, clipped to their bed, or hung securely on a hook via the NIR-HPF mount. This ensures that assistance is always within easy reach, fostering a sense of security and well-being. Made from high-quality plastic, the NI-RC is built to endure the rigors of daily use in busy medical facilities, providing a dependable solution that supports both patients and staff.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Moreover, the hands-free communication feature of the NI-RC enhances its practicality, especially for patients with physical limitations. The ability to initiate contact without needing to hold the device provides an additional layer of convenience and accessibility. With a maximum communication distance of 650 feet using a 3-conductor overall shield wire, this substation ensures that every call for help is heard clearly and promptly. Its design not only prioritizes patient comfort but also improves operational efficiency, making it an indispensable component of modern healthcare communication systems.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/ni-rc-bedside-handheld-sub-station/descriptions/202501-84-ai5-PRDPMCJmi2.png', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.994656', '2025-01-10 07:37:39.998121', 84),
(157, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The AIPHONE NIR-7HW Bathroom Call Button with Pull Cord is a meticulously designed safety device that brings enhanced security to bathroom environments. Its flush mount design fits perfectly into a standard 1-gang box, offering a streamlined appearance that blends effortlessly with modern bathroom aesthetics. Crafted from fire-resistant ABS plastic, this call button is built to withstand harsh conditions, ensuring long-lasting performance and reliability. The pull cord feature is designed for ease of use, allowing individuals to summon help with a simple tug in case of emergencies. Ideal for installation in healthcare facilities, elder care homes, and public restrooms, this call button offers a critical safety feature that can make a significant difference in emergency situations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-7hw-bathroom-call-button-with-pull-cord/descriptions/202501-85-ai6-0TDe4zrlG2.png', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.387521', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.392335', 85),
(158, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Enhancing both functionality and aesthetics, the AIPHONE NIR-7HW Bathroom Call Button with Pull Cord is an invaluable tool for ensuring safety in various bathroom settings. Its compact design makes it an unobtrusive addition to any space, while the flush mount installation allows for a clean, professional finish. The fire-resistant ABS plastic construction not only adds to its durability but also ensures compliance with stringent safety standards. The pull cord mechanism is intuitively designed to be accessible and easy to operate, providing a quick and effective means to call for assistance. Whether in a hospital, hotel, or private home, the AIPHONE NIR-7HW serves as a reliable safety measure, giving users and caregivers added peace of mind.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-7hw-bathroom-call-button-with-pull-cord/descriptions/202501-85-ai3-rrZ2RPRtVg.png', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.394050', '2025-01-10 07:42:23.397806', 85),
(159, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-8 Bedside Call Button is a handheld device designed to enhance patient care in healthcare facilities. This essential tool allows patients to easily call for assistance, ensuring timely responses from caregivers. Crafted from fire-resistant ABS plastic, the NIR-8 is designed to withstand the demands of a healthcare environment, providing both durability and safety. Its compatibility with NIR-1, NIR-MB, or NIR-7BS systems ensures seamless integration, making it a versatile choice for various communication setups. With its user-friendly design, patients can comfortably hold and operate the device, reducing stress and improving their overall experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-8-bedside-call-button/descriptions/202501-86-ai4-waidSzaLUZ.png', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.384229', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.390245', 86),
(160, '<p>The AIPHONE NIR-8 Bedside Call Button is an indispensable component for improving communication between patients and healthcare providers. Its compact, handheld design makes it easy for patients to use, while the fire-resistant ABS plastic construction guarantees safety and reliability. The NIR-8&rsquo;s compatibility with different system units such as NIR-1, NIR-MB, or NIR-7BS enhances its flexibility, allowing it to adapt to various facility needs. This call button not only ensures immediate communication but also contributes to creating a safer environment by meeting strict safety standards. Ideal for hospitals, nursing homes, and other healthcare settings, the NIR-8 is a practical solution to enhance patient care and operational efficiency.</p>', 'products/nir-8-bedside-call-button/descriptions/202501-86-ai5-lXyo8NYVJE.png', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.391996', '2025-01-10 07:51:36.395803', 86),
(161, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIM-20B 20-Call Master Station with Handset is a state-of-the-art communication hub designed for managing multiple points of contact within a facility. Supporting up to 20 door stations, sub stations, ceiling speakers, and wall jacks, this master station offers unparalleled connectivity. Its selective call, group call, and all call functionalities provide flexible communication options, ensuring that messages reach the intended recipients efficiently. The handset facilitates private conversations, making it ideal for environments where confidentiality is paramount. Built with fire-resistant ABS plastic and a robust SPCC chassis, the NIM-20B is both durable and safe, capable of withstanding demanding environments.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Installation of the AIPHONE NIM-20B is straightforward, requiring a 3-conductor overall shield wire, which simplifies the process and reduces setup time. The station supports communication over a distance of 650 feet for door and sub stations, ensuring comprehensive coverage in large buildings. Volume controls allow users to adjust the audio output to suit their needs, enhancing user experience. With its combination of advanced features and durable construction, the NIM-20B is a reliable choice for enhancing communication in various professional settings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nim-20b-20-call-master-station-with-handset/descriptions/202501-87-5-EdK4DGoi9P.png', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.953545', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.958632', 87),
(162, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIM-20B 20-Call Master Station with Handset stands out as a premier solution for centralized communication in expansive facilities. Its ability to connect with up to 20 auxiliary stations, including door and sub stations, ceiling speakers, and wall jacks, ensures that users have extensive communication coverage. The system&rsquo;s selective call feature allows users to target specific stations, while the group call and all call options enable broader announcements, making it versatile for different communication needs. The handset ensures that private conversations remain confidential, a crucial feature for environments such as hospitals or corporate offices.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Constructed with fire-resistant ABS plastic for the panel and a SPCC chassis, the NIM-20B is built to last, offering resilience against environmental challenges. Its practical design includes easy-to-use volume controls, allowing for personalized audio settings. The communication distance of 650 feet between door or sub stations and the master station ensures that even the most remote areas of a facility remain connected. The short 33-foot power supply distance to the master station ensures that installation is efficient and hassle-free. This robust and versatile communication system is ideal for enhancing operational efficiency and ensuring seamless communication in large institutions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nim-20b-20-call-master-station-with-handset/descriptions/202501-87-6-aYH6pumUu2.png', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.960103', '2025-01-10 08:06:03.963612', 87),
(163, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE TB-SE Handset Sub Station is a versatile addition to any intercom system, designed to enhance communication efficiency. This substation enables users to initiate calls by simply picking up the handset, ensuring quick and direct contact. The device features tone and LED annunciation at the master station, providing clear indications of incoming calls. With the ability to facilitate communication between handset subs through the master station, the TB-SE ensures that all conversations are clear and uninterrupted. Its sturdy construction and compact size make it suitable for a variety of settings, from residential to commercial environments.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This substation is built to handle extensive wire distances, supporting up to 1,300 feet with 22AWG wiring and 2,950 feet with 18AWG wiring. This flexibility in installation makes it a convenient option for large buildings or expansive facilities. The TB-SE\'s dimensions of 8-1/4\" H x 3-1/8\" W x 3\" D allow it to be installed in tight spaces without compromising performance. Designed with user convenience in mind, the substation is straightforward to operate and integrates seamlessly with existing AIPHONE systems. Its reliability and ease of use make it a preferred choice for those looking to improve their communication infrastructure.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/tb-se-handset-sub-station/descriptions/202501-88-4_2-RaiR6ONE5K.png', '2025-01-10 08:10:13.007424', '2025-01-10 08:10:13.013014', 88),
(164, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE TB-SE Handset Sub Station is engineered for optimal communication within interconnected systems. This user-friendly substation allows for instant call initiation by lifting the handset, making it intuitive for users. The inclusion of tone and LED annunciation at the master station ensures that users are immediately notified of calls, enhancing responsiveness and communication efficiency. Designed for robust performance, the TB-SE connects handset subs through the master station, facilitating smooth and effective communication across multiple points.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ideal for both small and large-scale applications, the TB-SE supports long wire distances, making it a practical choice for various installation needs. It accommodates up to 2,950 feet with 18AWG wiring, allowing for flexible placement without sacrificing signal integrity. Its compact design, measuring 8-1/4\" H x 3-1/8\" W x 3\" D, ensures that it fits comfortably into different environments while maintaining a sleek and professional appearance. Built to endure daily use, the TB-SE offers a reliable solution for improving communication in residential complexes, office buildings, and industrial facilities alike.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/tb-se-handset-sub-station/descriptions/202501-88-5-q8iPtc3T0I.png', '2025-01-10 08:10:13.014386', '2025-01-10 08:10:13.017910', 88),
(165, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-2 Call Reset Button is meticulously designed to enhance safety and communication in healthcare and institutional environments. Crafted from fire-resistant ABS plastic, it provides both durability and safety, ensuring reliable performance under demanding conditions. The flush mount design fits perfectly into a standard 1-gang box, making installation straightforward and discreet. Its sleek and minimalistic appearance allows it to blend seamlessly into various interior designs without compromising functionality. The NIR-2 is an essential component in emergency and nurse call systems, enabling quick and efficient call resets to enhance response times and improve patient care.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This reset button is engineered to withstand frequent use, a crucial feature in high-traffic environments such as hospitals and nursing homes. Its fire-resistant material adds an extra layer of safety, adhering to stringent safety standards and ensuring longevity. The AIPHONE NIR-2 is not only practical but also aesthetically pleasing, making it an excellent choice for modern facilities looking to upgrade their communication systems. Its simple yet effective design reduces user error, contributing to smoother operations and enhanced safety protocols.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-2-call-reset-button/descriptions/202501-89-2_6-66GgCg1hvU.png', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.685430', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.690144', 89),
(166, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The AIPHONE NIR-2 Call Reset Button is a vital component of any effective communication system in critical environments. Its fire-resistant ABS plastic construction ensures that it can withstand harsh conditions while maintaining optimal functionality. Designed for flush mounting into a 1-gang box, it offers a clean and professional look that suits a variety of settings. This device is particularly beneficial in healthcare facilities, where quick and efficient communication can significantly impact patient outcomes. Its intuitive design allows for easy operation, minimizing the risk of errors during emergency situations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its robust build and practical design, the NIR-2 provides a user-friendly interface that enhances operational efficiency. The flush mount feature not only improves aesthetic appeal but also ensures that the button is securely installed, preventing accidental activations or damage. This call reset button is an indispensable tool for institutions seeking to improve their safety and communication systems. With its combination of durability, ease of use, and sleek design, the AIPHONE NIR-2 is a superior choice for modern facilities aiming to provide the highest level of care and safety.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/nir-2-call-reset-button/descriptions/202501-89-1_6-Yte1xKFa8s.png', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.691539', '2025-01-10 08:13:34.695001', 89),
(167, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA A-2060D-EB Digital Mixer Amplifier is engineered to meet the needs of demanding audio environments, offering superior sound quality and reliability. Its compact design houses powerful features, such as 3 microphone inputs and 2 AUX inputs, making it ideal for various setups, including PA systems, conference rooms, and live performances. The amplifier delivers consistent sound output with a speaker output tailored for constant voltage distribution systems (100 V), ensuring clear and even sound distribution across larger spaces. For optimal audio control, the amplifier features independent tone controls for both high and low frequencies, allowing users to adjust the sound to suit specific acoustics or personal preferences.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Additionally, the TOA A-2060D-EB offers protection mechanisms that help extend the life of the system. It includes a current limiter to prevent damage from overloads and excess heat limit protection to shield the transistor and power transformer from overheating. The device is also equipped with phantom power and a mute function for the first microphone input, adding versatility to various audio input configurations. Available in multiple output power ratings (30 W, 60 W, 120 W, and 240 W), the TOA A-2060D-EB is a highly adaptable and durable amplifier that meets the needs of both small and large-scale audio setups.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-a-2060d-eb-digital-mixer-amplifier/descriptions/202501-90-7-m5y8hfPqPN.png', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.371973', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.380900', 90),
(168, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA A-2060D-EB Digital Mixer Amplifier is built with performance, reliability, and versatility in mind, making it a perfect solution for professional sound systems. It features a robust construction with 3 microphone inputs, 2 AUX inputs, and a recording output, offering multiple connection options for different audio sources. Whether you are using it in a conference room, auditorium, or any other venue, its 100 V constant voltage speaker output ensures consistent and clear audio coverage. The device includes phantom power for microphone input 1, providing the flexibility to connect condenser microphones that require this feature, while the mute function provides additional control during audio sessions.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Equipped with sophisticated protection features, the TOA A-2060D-EB ensures that the amplifier remains safe from damage during high-demand usage. The current limiter protects the unit from overloads, while the excess heat limit mechanism prevents the system from overheating. Available in a range of power outputs (30 W, 60 W, 120 W, and 240 W), it caters to various system requirements, offering flexibility and reliability for small to large-scale applications. With its user-friendly features and high-quality performance, the TOA A-2060D-EB is an essential tool for any professional sound system setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-a-2060d-eb-digital-mixer-amplifier/descriptions/202501-90-6-CIxoUOXddG.png', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.382935', '2025-01-13 01:16:52.391858', 90),
(169, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA MX-113-AS Pre-Amplifier Mixer is engineered for flexibility and reliability in professional audio setups. It offers 6 microphone inputs, 4 AUX inputs, and 2 monaural outputs, providing comprehensive connectivity for a variety of sound sources. Designed for versatility, the mixer includes a signal noise gate circuit that ensures only clean, clear audio is transmitted by filtering out unwanted background noise. This feature is particularly beneficial for microphone channels 1-5, as it helps reduce interference, delivering crisp sound quality even in challenging environments. The unit&rsquo;s slim 1U size ensures it takes up minimal space in your audio system, making it a practical solution for both compact and larger configurations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA MX-113-AS also comes with the added convenience of remote control contact, allowing for easy operation from a distance. This mixer offers the flexibility of desk or rack mounting to suit different installation preferences. The option to rack-mount with an additional bracket provides enhanced versatility for integration into permanent installations. Whether you&rsquo;re mixing live sound for a concert or managing audio for a conference, the TOA MX-113-AS Pre-Amplifier Mixer delivers consistent performance, reliability, and clear sound.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-mx-113-as-pre-amplifier-mixer/descriptions/202501-91-4-8tKvgr9thM.png', '2025-01-13 01:26:03.019640', '2025-01-13 01:26:03.026369', 91),
(170, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA MX-113-AS Pre-Amplifier Mixer is the ideal choice for audio professionals seeking a reliable and efficient mixer with multiple input options. Featuring 6 microphone inputs and 4 AUX inputs, it provides ample connections for microphones, instruments, and other audio devices. The 2 monaural outputs ensure that audio signals can be routed with ease, making this mixer suitable for a wide range of audio setups. The built-in noise gate circuit is an advanced feature that works with microphone channels 1-5, improving sound clarity by preventing unwanted noise from passing through. This is perfect for environments where maintaining clean audio is essential, such as conferences or live events.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Thanks to its compact 1U design, the TOA MX-113-AS is easy to integrate into both portable and fixed installations. The remote control contact feature adds extra convenience for users who need to control the mixer from a distance. The flexibility to mount the mixer on a desk or in a rack provides the adaptability needed to suit various audio system configurations. Whether you need a space-saving audio solution or a powerful mixer for complex sound systems, the TOA MX-113-AS delivers performance and convenience in one sleek package.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-mx-113-as-pre-amplifier-mixer/descriptions/202501-91-5-PgCsWAgMO5.png', '2025-01-13 01:26:03.032477', '2025-01-13 01:26:03.037656', 91),
(171, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CA-115 Car Amplifier is a mobile amplifier designed for simple installation in vehicles, offering robust audio performance with easy functionality. Powered by a 12V DC battery, it operates seamlessly in a vehicle&rsquo;s electrical system, making it a great choice for in-car audio solutions. The amplifier provides three selectable power output options: 15W, 30W, or 60W, allowing for customized audio power depending on your needs. The two microphone inputs support communication or voice amplification, while the AUX input enables compatibility with CD players, radios, or other external audio devices. Its small form factor and rugged design make it ideal for integration into a car\'s dashboard, offering both durability and practicality.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ca-115-car-amplifiers/descriptions/202501-92-3_5-TJbs2WSyhC.png', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.650070', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.657849', 92),
(172, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CA-115 Car Amplifier offers advanced audio functionality in a compact and durable design. With its unidirectional dynamic microphone featuring a talk switch, this amplifier ensures crystal-clear communication, whether for voice amplification or hands-free use. It also comes with a front pause function for easy control during operation, adding extra convenience. The DIN-sized unit is designed for in-dash installation, making it simple to integrate into a vehicle\'s existing system. Built with rugged construction, it can withstand the demands of daily use in vehicles, ensuring a long lifespan and reliable performance, whether you\'re amplifying your voice or enhancing your music experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ca-115-car-amplifiers/descriptions/202501-92-4_2-PUsAphBBaw.png', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.661177', '2025-01-13 01:40:04.669768', 92),
(173, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The TOA VM-2120 System Amplifier is a robust and adaptable solution for managing audio across multiple zones. Featuring 4 audio inputs and 5 switchable high impedance speaker zones, the amplifier offers flexibility and precise control over sound distribution. Its compact design allows for easy mounting in a 3-unit EIA-Standard equipment rack, making it an ideal choice for both commercial and emergency broadcast settings. The amplifier supports general-purpose broadcast and includes the option to integrate emergency voice instructions in accordance with the EN60849 Standard. For added convenience, remote control is available through the RM-200M remote microphone or external equipment, ensuring seamless operation in various environments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-vm-2120-system-amplifier/descriptions/202501-93-7-ZaMJmaJoeY.png', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.134343', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.143264', 93),
(174, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;Designed with versatility in mind, the TOA VM-2120 System Amplifier excels in both everyday audio management and critical emergency communication needs. The unit includes comprehensive input options with control over volume, bass, and treble, as well as pre-adjustable levels for background music (BGM). This allows for optimal sound quality in both public spaces and emergency situations. The optional surveillance function provides peace of mind by monitoring the system for failures, while the amplifier\'s ability to combine up to 9 units ensures scalability for larger installations. Whether for routine broadcasting or ensuring emergency protocols are followed, the TOA VM-2120 offers reliable, high-performance sound management.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-vm-2120-system-amplifier/descriptions/202501-93-1_6-Y5nUeh3mBu.png', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.147301', '2025-01-13 01:46:19.155853', 93);
