(175, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA ER-3215S Hand Grip Type Megaphone with Siren Signal is a professional-grade device designed for maximum performance and portability. Whether used for crowd control, emergency signaling, or public announcements, it offers clear, powerful sound with a 15W rated output and up to 23W maximum output. The megaphone features a removable microphone, allowing the user to transform it into a shoulder-type megaphone for more comfortable use over extended periods. A newly developed polyimide diaphragm enhances the audio quality, ensuring crisp, clear sound even in challenging outdoor environments. Its powerful siren can be activated easily, making it an invaluable tool for emergencies or urgent situations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-er-3215s-hand-grip-type-megaphone-with-siren-signal/descriptions/202501-94-_pceg5G1.png', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.316879', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.328881', 94),
(176, '<p dir=\"ltr\">This megaphone is engineered with user convenience in mind, featuring an ergonomic handgrip and a durable nylon strap for easy carrying. It is powered by six R14P (SUM-2) size \"C\" batteries, providing up to 9 hours of continuous voice operation and 20 minutes of siren usage. The TOA ER-3215S is also built to withstand varying environmental conditions, with an operating temperature range of -10 &deg;C to +40 &deg;C. The ABS resin construction of the horn, microphone, and body ensures durability and resistance to wear and tear. Whether you are leading a group at a large event or needing a reliable tool in an emergency, the TOA ER-3215S offers the performance and quality required for every situation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-er-3215s-hand-grip-type-megaphone-with-siren-signal/descriptions/202501-94-_mHUdmlj.png', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.332535', '2025-01-13 01:52:20.338551', 94),
(177, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The TOA DM-1300 Unidirectional Microphone is designed for audio professionals who require precision and clarity in their recordings. This moving coil microphone features unidirectional directivity, ensuring that sound is captured from a specific direction, making it ideal for vocal performances or focused audio input in loud environments. The microphone\'s wide frequency response of 70 Hz to 15,000 Hz and -54 dB sensitivity ensures high-quality audio transmission across a broad range of frequencies. Its balanced impedance of 600 &Omega; helps maintain sound quality over long cable runs, making it a versatile option for various setups. The microphone\'s durable body is made of die-cast zinc, ensuring longevity and consistent performance in different conditions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-dm-1300-unidirectional-microphone/descriptions/202501-95-2_6-lAUXHZPnye.png', '2025-01-13 02:08:28.002963', '2025-01-13 02:08:28.011603', 95),
(178, '<p dir=\"ltr\">Built for durability and consistent performance, the TOA DM-1300 is the perfect choice for users seeking reliability in their audio equipment. Its 10-meter single-core shielded cable and phone plug terminal make it easy to connect to most audio systems without compromising signal integrity. Whether you&rsquo;re using it for public speaking, recording, or live sound amplification, the microphone&rsquo;s talk switch provides convenient control, allowing for effortless operation. Its sleek metallic gray finish not only enhances its visual appeal but also ensures it blends seamlessly into professional environments. The included microphone holder adds convenience, making the TOA DM-1300 Unidirectional Microphone a complete solution for any sound-related project.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-dm-1300-unidirectional-microphone/descriptions/202501-95-5-sPIaEf4ygN.png', '2025-01-13 02:08:28.015855', '2025-01-13 02:08:28.020722', 95),
(179, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA TS-682L Delegate Unit with Long Microphone is a reliable and professional-grade solution designed for conference and meeting environments. Part of the TS-680 Series, it provides high-quality audio functionality with minimal setup. The unit\'s compact and lightweight design ensures that it is easy to install and store, making it a versatile addition to any conference room. The microphone features a unidirectional electret condenser microphone, providing clear sound capture with a frequency response of 100Hz to 13 kHz.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Its sleek ABS resin body ensures durability while maintaining a modern and professional appearance. The microphone length of 518mm allows for comfortable use during extended discussions. The delegate unit operates on a 36V DC power supply provided by the central unit, with minimal power consumption, making it highly energy-efficient. Its versatile design includes internal speaker control and a headphone output with adjustable volume, offering a comprehensive audio solution for users. Whether used for meetings, conferences, or events, the TOA TS-682L ensures clear communication and professional-grade performance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ts-682l-delegate-unit-with-long-microphone/descriptions/202501-96-4_1-wXktD6WXub.png', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.069222', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.075342', 96),
(180, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA TS-682L Delegate Unit is equipped with a long microphone that enhances user convenience and comfort. Designed for easy handling, it features a simple \"Talk Key\" control that allows users to activate or deactivate the microphone, preventing feedback when not in use. When the talk key is placed in the ON position, the microphone activates, and the speaker is turned off to avoid interference. Conversely, when the key is OFF, the microphone is disabled, but the speaker remains active, ensuring that other units in the conference can still be heard.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This function ensures clear communication with minimal disruption, making it ideal for large meetings and conferences. The delegate unit&rsquo;s internal speaker and headphone output come with volume control, allowing users to adjust the audio levels according to their preferences. The microphone, with a sensitivity of -37dB, is designed to capture speech accurately while rejecting unwanted noise, providing excellent sound quality. Whether used in intimate discussions or large conferences, the TOA TS-682L ensures smooth communication and functionality throughout its operation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ts-682l-delegate-unit-with-long-microphone/descriptions/202501-96-6-u4oXkt2JG6.png', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.079446', '2025-01-13 02:25:31.084716', 96),
(181, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-680FC Wall Mount Speaker is engineered for superior performance in voice alarm systems and public address applications. With a built-in 16 cm double-cone speaker unit, it produces high-quality audio with a frequency response from 150 Hz to 20 kHz, ensuring clear sound transmission across a wide range. The speaker can be mounted on walls either by surface or flush-mounting, offering flexible installation in various environments. Designed for durability, its robust metal enclosure and direct wall-mounting system ensure the speaker remains securely in place, even when exposed to outward force. Additionally, the impedance can be easily adjusted via the transformer tap position, making this speaker a versatile choice for different audio systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-680FC also supports bridge wiring, making it easy to connect multiple speakers in a system. Certified according to EN 54-24, this speaker meets the necessary standards for fire alarm systems, guaranteeing reliable performance during emergencies. It is also compliant with BS-5839-8: 2013, further ensuring its suitability for public safety and alarm applications. The speaker has an excellent sensitivity rating of 94 dB (1 W, 1 m), providing clear audio in both small and large spaces. The sturdy off-white steel plate finish not only enhances its durability but also ensures that it blends seamlessly into any environment, making it an ideal solution for commercial and industrial settings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-680fc-wall-mount-speaker/descriptions/202501-97-4_1-fGbVHGuEpW.png', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.835114', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.846131', 97),
(182, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-680FC Wall Mount Speaker is a professional-grade speaker designed specifically for use in voice alarm and public address systems. Its advanced 16 cm double-cone speaker unit delivers crisp and clear sound quality, with a frequency response that covers 150 Hz to 20 kHz. Whether you need surface or flush-mounting installation, this speaker offers flexibility in setup to suit different environments. The robust metal enclosure ensures that the speaker stays securely mounted, even when external force is applied. The speaker&rsquo;s transformer also allows for easy impedance adjustment, offering a customizable solution for various system needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This speaker is designed with ease of use in mind, featuring two steatite screw terminal blocks for simple bridge wiring and a streamlined connection process. Certified to meet EN 54-24 standards and compliant with BS-5839-8: 2013, it is fully equipped for emergency systems where safety is paramount. With an impressive sensitivity of 94 dB (1 W, 1 m) and high sound pressure, the TOA BS-680FC is capable of delivering clear, intelligible audio across large spaces. The off-white steel finish makes it not only a practical choice for any installation but also a stylish one, integrating smoothly into its surroundings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-680fc-wall-mount-speaker/descriptions/202501-97-5-DM6Dyo3RE6.png', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.847803', '2025-01-13 02:40:22.854538', 97),
(183, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PJ-100W Projection Speakers are engineered to provide superior sound quality in compact installations. They offer a rated input of 10W, with selectable impedance settings for 100V, 70V, and 50V line systems, ensuring versatility for different audio setups. The speakers are equipped with a 12 cm speaker component, which delivers clear sound with a frequency response range of 65 Hz to 15 kHz. Whether for public address systems or background music, these speakers ensure that your audio is heard with clarity and precision. With a sound pressure level of 92 dB at 1m with 1W input, these speakers provide impressive volume output for their size.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The robust ABS resin cabinet with an off-white finish offers both durability and aesthetic appeal, blending easily into any environment. Additionally, the included SPCC bracket provides flexible installation options, allowing for wall or ceiling mounting. The compact dimensions of 160 x 200 x 195 mm and the lightweight design of just 1.8 kg make the speakers easy to handle and position. These projection speakers are designed for professional environments where both performance and reliability are key. The TOA PJ-100W speakers offer the perfect solution for businesses, educational institutions, and public spaces that require high-quality sound with minimal space consumption.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pj-100w-projection-speakers/descriptions/202501-98-5-ZtjeI7owfy.png', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.456447', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.467433', 98),
(184, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PJ-100W Projection Speakers are a perfect choice for installations requiring high-quality sound reproduction in a compact form factor. Designed to be versatile, these speakers support various impedance options to match different audio systems. The 100V, 70V, and 50V line options ensure compatibility with both commercial and residential audio setups. The speaker&rsquo;s frequency response of 65 Hz to 15 kHz and the sound pressure level of 92 dB ensure that audio is delivered with clarity and presence, even in larger spaces. With a 12 cm speaker component, the TOA PJ-100W is ideal for both background music and public announcement systems.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The sturdy ABS resin cabinet and off-white finish ensure long-lasting durability, while blending seamlessly into the surroundings. Its compact size, measuring just 160 x 200 x 195 mm, makes it suitable for tight spaces without compromising on sound output. Weighing just 1.8 kg, the speakers are easy to mount, and the included SPCC bracket offers secure installation options. Whether installed in schools, offices, or retail spaces, the TOA PJ-100W Projection Speakers offer professional-grade sound quality in an easy-to-install package.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pj-100w-projection-speakers/descriptions/202501-98-6-WCpO9k2Cfb.png', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.470083', '2025-01-13 02:57:40.473426', 98),
(185, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CS-64 Projection Speaker is designed for superior sound distribution in challenging outdoor environments. With its stainless steel hardware, this speaker is highly resistant to corrosion, ensuring durability even in the most demanding weather conditions. Its innovative exponential horn improves directivity and guarantees uniform sound coverage, making it ideal for paging, background music, and tone signaling. The 12 cm cone-type speaker, treated for splash proofing, provides a robust frequency response range from 130 to 13,000 Hz. Perfectly suited for both residential and commercial settings, this speaker ensures exceptional audio performance, no matter the weather.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Built with flexibility in mind, the TOA CS-64 comes with an easy-to-use rotary switch for impedance adjustments, allowing it to be tailored for a variety of sound systems. The speaker supports both 100V and 70V line configurations, making it adaptable to different installation setups. Whether used for sound systems in parks, stadiums, or outdoor venues, the TOA CS-64 is engineered for clarity and high intelligibility in all types of applications. Its rugged design, coupled with the high sound quality of dynamic speakers, makes this product a top choice for outdoor audio solutions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-cs-64-projection-speakers/descriptions/202501-99-7-dJ79bt1Mkc.png', '2025-01-13 04:17:13.253826', '2025-01-13 04:19:51.286829', 99),
(186, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CS-64 Projection Speaker stands out for its reliable and consistent performance, even in the harshest environments. Its all-weather durability comes from its stainless steel hardware, which prevents corrosion and ensures the speaker\'s longevity. Designed for high intelligibility, the speaker features a weather-resistant horn combined with dynamic speaker technology for optimal sound clarity. The wide-range speaker is equipped with an exponential horn that not only improves directivity but also ensures a uniform sound distribution across large areas. Whether you need clear announcements or background music in open spaces, this speaker delivers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With its wide operating temperature range of -20&deg;C to +55&deg;C, the TOA CS-64 is ideal for a variety of outdoor applications. The speaker\'s 12 cm cone-type speaker, treated for splash-proofing, guarantees robust audio even in wet or humid conditions. Furthermore, the speaker\'s flexibility is enhanced by its impedance options, which can be adjusted easily via the rotary switch. This allows the speaker to integrate seamlessly into a variety of sound systems. Whether used in public spaces or for professional events, the TOA CS-64 ensures that your sound needs are met with precision and clarity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-cs-64-projection-speakers/descriptions/202501-99-1_3-zeo1xEW6gL.png', '2025-01-13 04:17:13.261021', '2025-01-13 04:19:51.289834', 99),
(187, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-658R Ceiling Speaker is engineered for both professional and residential audio installations where quality sound and easy setup are a priority. This ceiling speaker is equipped with a durable, resin-integrated panel and metal frame, ensuring robust construction and long-lasting performance. The speaker\'s easy-to-install spring clamp mechanism allows for quick and hassle-free mounting in various ceiling types, making it ideal for contractors and DIY installers alike. The PC-658R is suitable for use in a wide range of environments, such as conference rooms, retail stores, and home audio systems. Its versatility in impedance adjustment makes it a great choice for custom audio setups, allowing you to optimize sound quality based on your system\'s needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-658r-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-100-2_3-vw65YuBYVe.png', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.090753', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.096833', 100),
(188, '<p dir=\"ltr\">With a speaker component of a 16 cm (6\") cone-type driver, the TOA PC-658R Ceiling Speaker delivers clear and balanced sound, covering a frequency range from 65 Hz to 18 kHz. Its rated input ensures compatibility with both 100 V and 70 V line systems, with selectable impedance options that can be adjusted to suit your installation. The speaker\'s high sensitivity of 90 dB means that it can provide excellent sound performance even in larger spaces. The white polypropylene resin baffle and painted surface-treated steel plate grille allow the speaker to blend seamlessly into any modern ceiling, offering both functionality and aesthetic appeal. Weighing only 500 g, it is lightweight yet strong enough to stand the test of time in demanding environments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-658r-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-100-6-igboCr012q.png', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.098805', '2025-01-13 04:42:32.102323', 100),
(189, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-668R Ceiling Mount Speaker is designed for easy integration into commercial and residential spaces, offering an efficient audio solution without compromising on aesthetics. Its integrated resin panel and speaker frame are made from high-quality polypropylene material, ensuring durability and a sleek finish that complements any interior. The speaker is designed for quick installation, featuring a spring clamp mechanism that simplifies mounting to ceilings. The slim design of the frame ensures the speaker blends seamlessly with the surrounding decor, providing high-performance sound without being intrusive.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With its impressive frequency response range of 65 Hz to 20,000 Hz, the TOA PC-668R provides crystal-clear audio suitable for a wide range of environments, including conference rooms, classrooms, or retail spaces. It is equipped with a double cone-type 8-inch speaker component, delivering superior sound quality that enhances any audio experience. The speaker\'s impedance can easily be adjusted through the transformer tap, offering flexibility to suit different system configurations. Its high sensitivity rating of 96 dB ensures a consistent and powerful sound output. Whether you\'re looking to install it in a small office or a larger commercial space, the TOA PC-668R offers reliable, high-quality sound for all your needs.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-668r-ceiling-mount-speaker/descriptions/202501-101-3_1-d6cTbPGFus.png', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.568465', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.574261', 101),
(190, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-668R Ceiling Mount Speaker is an excellent choice for those seeking both performance and aesthetics. Designed to offer an unobtrusive look while delivering exceptional sound, this speaker is ideal for professional audio setups. The speaker frame&rsquo;s slim profile allows it to blend effortlessly into any ceiling, while the white polypropylene resin panel and surface-treated steel plate net grille ensure durability and a modern appearance. Its versatile mounting options make it suitable for various applications, including retail, hospitality, and educational environments.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a frequency response range of 65 Hz to 20,000 Hz, the TOA PC-668R delivers clear and dynamic sound, making it a great choice for background music, public address systems, or multimedia presentations. The speaker&rsquo;s adjustable impedance allows it to be fine-tuned for different voltage systems, including 100V and 70V lines. Whether you\'re upgrading an existing audio system or installing a new one, the TOA PC-668R&rsquo;s spring clamp mechanism ensures quick and secure mounting. Its lightweight design, combined with its easy installation process, makes this ceiling speaker both practical and efficient for a wide range of uses.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-668r-ceiling-mount-speaker/descriptions/202501-101-7-2CgwzGA5rt.png', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.576073', '2025-01-13 04:52:38.579921', 101),
(191, '<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;The TOA SC-610M Paging Horn Speaker is a highly durable and reliable speaker designed for public address systems in both indoor and outdoor environments. This compact unit features a rugged construction with a powder-coated aluminum horn flare and stainless steel components, ensuring longevity and protection from the elements. Its shock-resistant oval horn delivers high-quality sound with a peak sound pressure level of 110 dB, making it suitable for environments where clear announcements are crucial. With a frequency response range of 315 Hz to 12.5 kHz, it provides intelligible sound across a broad range of frequencies. The speaker is also equipped with an easy-to-use impedance switch, allowing it to be compatible with 100V or 70V line systems.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-sc-610m-paging-horn-speaker/descriptions/202501-102-3_1-HmLig5S31G.png', '2025-01-13 06:40:23.032866', '2025-01-13 06:40:23.039797', 102),
(192, '<p>Designed for versatility and performance, the TOA SC-610M Paging Horn Speaker offers easy impedance selection to suit various system setups, whether for larger or smaller installations. Its IP65 rating ensures that it is both dust and water-resistant, making it ideal for use in diverse weather conditions. The speaker&rsquo;s high impedance capabilities and multiple input options (10W, 5W, and 1W) further enhance its flexibility for different audio system requirements. Additionally, it can operate in extreme temperature conditions, from as low as -20&deg;C to as high as +55&deg;C, without compromising on performance. This combination of durability, flexibility, and superior sound quality makes the TOA SC-610M an essential component for any paging or public address system.</p>', 'products/toa-sc-610m-paging-horn-speaker/descriptions/202501-102-7-DtbaAQDlHy.png', '2025-01-13 06:40:23.041411', '2025-01-13 06:40:23.044892', 102),
(193, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA EC-100M Chime Microphone offers a unique combination of microphone and chime functions, making it an excellent tool for venues that require both sound clarity and distinct chimes. Featuring a unidirectional dynamic microphone, it ensures clear audio capture, with a frequency response range of 200 Hz to 10 kHz. In addition to its microphone capabilities, the EC-100M is equipped with a four-tone chime (up/down), providing audible alerts for a wide range of settings. Its 2 mA current consumption during operation ensures minimal power use, while the low 10 &mu;A consumption at idle makes it highly efficient. The microphone is powered by two R14P batteries, and with proper care, the device can function for about 2 years with 150 uses per day.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The EC-100M&rsquo;s design emphasizes durability and ease of use, with its zinc die-cast metallic gold case providing both aesthetic appeal and resilience in demanding environments. Ideal for institutions such as schools, religious settings, and commercial spaces, the EC-100M allows for seamless operation and reliability. A convenient connection cord and windscreen are included in the package to enhance functionality. With easy operation and minimal maintenance, the TOA EC-100M is a reliable choice for those looking to integrate a microphone and chime system into their space. Additionally, users are encouraged to replace the batteries every two years to avoid potential leakage and ensure long-term reliability.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ec-100m-chime-microphone/descriptions/202501-103-7-jFstgKnJqy.png', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.902070', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.908000', 103),
(194, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA EC-100M Chime Microphone is a versatile and efficient solution for environments where clear communication and chimes are needed. This microphone features a dynamic unidirectional design with a frequency response from 200 Hz to 10 kHz, ensuring superior sound quality for speech and announcements. The built-in four-tone chime (up/down) delivers clear and distinct sound alerts, which are ideal for schools, churches, and various business settings. Operating on just two R14P batteries, the microphone is energy-efficient, with a 2-year operational lifespan when used 150 times daily. This makes the EC-100M a cost-effective choice for long-term use.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Crafted with a sturdy zinc die-cast metallic gold case, the TOA EC-100M offers a premium look and reliable performance, even in high-traffic areas. The microphone&rsquo;s low current consumption (2 mA during operation, 10 &mu;A at idle) reduces the need for frequent battery changes. Additionally, the microphone and chime signals have unbalanced outputs, with adjustable volume controls to tailor sound levels. The included accessories, such as a 2-meter connection cord, slotted-head screwdriver, and windscreen, make the EC-100M easy to set up and use. Its intuitive design ensures that anyone can operate the microphone and chime functions effortlessly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-ec-100m-chime-microphone/descriptions/202501-103-5-8WN3pWonEF.png', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.909799', '2025-01-13 07:10:06.913606', 103),
(195, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-301B Compact Satellite Speaker System is an ideal solution for businesses looking to improve their audio setup. This system consists of four compact satellite speakers and a subwoofer, each designed to offer high-quality sound while maintaining a small footprint. The satellite speakers come with mounting brackets that allow for flexible installation, whether for a single or dual speaker setup. The system&rsquo;s subwoofer enhances bass output and can be installed either temporarily or permanently to suit different space configurations. The TOA BS-301B system is built to withstand commercial use, with a durable black HIPS resin finish that complements the design of modern retail or dining environments.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Whether you&rsquo;re setting up a sound system for a caf&eacute;, restaurant, or retail space, the TOA BS-301B ensures excellent sound quality that fills the room. The speakers&rsquo; frequency response range of 40 Hz to 20 kHz provides clear, well-balanced sound across all frequencies. The system also boasts a sensitivity of 81 dB, ensuring efficient sound delivery even in larger or acoustically challenging spaces. Thanks to its compact and efficient design, the TOA BS-301B is an unobtrusive yet powerful solution for any commercial space.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-301bcompact-satellite-speaker-system/descriptions/202501-104-6-9pcHGYyI2Q.png', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.428228', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.433442', 104),
(196, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-301B Compact Satellite Speaker System is designed for businesses that require high-quality, space-efficient audio. It includes four satellite speakers, each equipped with a mounting bracket for easy installation and flexibility in positioning. The subwoofer reinforces the sound output, creating a complete, immersive audio experience for commercial settings. The system is ideal for environments where space is limited but excellent sound projection is essential, such as restaurants, caf&eacute;s, and retail stores.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This speaker system is engineered for performance, with a frequency response of 40 Hz to 20 kHz, providing full-range audio that&rsquo;s clear and rich. It features an efficient design that ensures high output even in larger spaces, with a sensitivity rating of 81 dB. The subwoofer&rsquo;s installation options&mdash;either temporary or permanent&mdash;make it a versatile solution for varying business needs. The TOA BS-301B is a reliable choice for any commercial environment, combining compact size, ease of installation, and exceptional sound quality.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-301bcompact-satellite-speaker-system/descriptions/202501-104-7-r5AkrQ5cNL.png', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.435250', '2025-01-13 07:20:59.439482', 104),
(197, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-10WL Splashproof Wall-Mounted Speakers are designed for high-performance sound in environments exposed to water or humidity. Built with a splashproof 10 cm full-range speaker, they are ideal for outdoor locations under eaves or highly humid areas like locker rooms, bathrooms, and swimming pools. The sealed enclosure and durable polypropylene construction ensure the speakers are resistant to moisture, offering consistent sound even in wet conditions. Additionally, the aluminum grill provides an added layer of protection while maintaining a sleek aesthetic. The BS-10WL is engineered to handle challenging environments without compromising on sound quality, making it the go-to option for any public or commercial space requiring clear audio.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-10wl-splashproof-wall-mounted-speakers/descriptions/202501-105-3_1-4w4RLni8fE.png', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.109363', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.115270', 105),
(198, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-10WL Splashproof Wall-Mounted Speakers provide high-quality sound while withstanding the harsh conditions of water exposure and high humidity. Featuring a 10 cm dynamic speaker, the BS-10WL is built to provide a clear and powerful audio experience in locations such as locker rooms, bathrooms, and outdoor areas sheltered from direct water splash. With a frequency response range of 120Hz to 18kHz and a rated power of 5W, these speakers deliver a sound pressure level of 90dB, ensuring clear and audible sound even in large or open spaces. The speakers\' magnetic shielding ensures there is no interference with nearby televisions, even when installed in close proximity. Designed for ease of installation and durability, these wall-mounted speakers offer both aesthetic and functional benefits for any sound system setup.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-10wl-splashproof-wall-mounted-speakers/descriptions/202501-105-5-Ok3ThgIXAQ.png', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.116679', '2025-01-13 07:30:31.121410', 105),
(199, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-678 Cabinet Speaker offers a high-quality audio solution for paging systems in various commercial settings. It features two 6-inch double cone speaker units that deliver clear and dynamic sound reproduction. Its robust wooden construction ensures durability and longevity, and the off-white finish provides a clean, modern aesthetic that blends well with most environments. The speaker can be installed either vertically or horizontally, offering flexibility to suit different space requirements. With the ability to handle both concealed in-wall and exposed wiring, the BS-678 is convenient to integrate into existing systems with ease.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In addition to its flexible installation options, the TOA BS-678 provides an easy-to-adjust input impedance through its transformer tap positions. This feature allows users to tailor the speaker&rsquo;s performance to their specific needs. The built-in push-in type connector simplifies wiring and allows bridge wiring, further streamlining installation. Ideal for both small and large spaces, this speaker ensures high-quality sound output with its broad frequency response of 150 Hz to 20 kHz, making it a perfect choice for clear communication in paging systems.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-678-cabinet-speaker/descriptions/202501-106-2_3-31xliDSQxU.png', '2025-01-13 07:35:59.835436', '2025-01-13 07:39:50.034904', 106),
(200, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA BS-678 Cabinet Speaker is an advanced and dependable solution for paging and sound distribution systems. Its two 6-inch double cone speaker units are specifically designed to deliver full-range sound, ensuring clarity and intelligibility in any environment. The speaker&rsquo;s design allows for easy wall-mounting with a secure screw installation that keeps it in place even under outward pressure. The speaker&rsquo;s versatility extends to its wiring options, with support for both concealed and exposed wiring connections, making it ideal for various setup configurations.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With its 100 V and 70 V line compatibility, the TOA BS-678 provides flexible impedance options to accommodate different systems. The speaker&rsquo;s frequency response range covers the essential 150 Hz to 20 kHz spectrum, which is ideal for paging and voice communication applications. The push-in connector simplifies the installation process, making it a practical and user-friendly option for commercial paging systems. The speaker&rsquo;s HIPS baffle and surface-treated steel grille ensure it stands the test of time while maintaining its sleek, off-white aesthetic that suits a wide range of spaces.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-bs-678-cabinet-speaker/descriptions/202501-106-1_3-nRd2MKkOy4.png', '2025-01-13 07:35:59.842371', '2025-01-13 07:39:50.037252', 106),
(201, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-2668 Ceiling Speaker is designed to meet the needs of paging and announcement systems where flush mounting is not feasible. Featuring an easy-to-install spring catch method, this speaker can be quickly mounted to the ceiling with minimal effort. It includes a push-in connector that allows for swift wiring connections, simplifying the installation process. Additionally, the speaker comes with a bridging terminal that enables you to bridge speaker lines for expanded coverage. The supplied bracket allows for installation in a flush-mount pull box, making it adaptable to various ceiling setups.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With a frequency response range of 100 Hz to 16 kHz and a sound pressure level of 90 dB, the TOA PC-2668 delivers clear and intelligible sound. It is designed for use with both 70V and 100V line systems, offering impedance options that cater to different audio configurations. This ceiling speaker is ideal for environments where consistent, high-quality sound is needed for announcements, such as office buildings, schools, and public spaces.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-2668-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-107-2_3-QplQqjhd26.png', '2025-01-13 07:45:46.449529', '2025-01-13 07:48:58.646255', 107),
(202, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA PC-2668 Ceiling Speaker provides a convenient and efficient audio solution for paging systems. Its exposed installation method ensures ease of setup in places where flush mounting is not an option. This speaker is perfect for those looking to maintain high audio standards without extensive installation requirements. It features a 12 cm dynamic cone-type speaker, designed to reproduce sound with clarity and precision across a wide frequency range. The unit comes with a robust ABS resin baffle, finished in off-white to match most modern ceiling colors.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Not only does the TOA PC-2668 provide superior sound performance, but it also boasts a practical design. It includes a push-in connector for quick wiring and offers the option to bridge speaker lines, ensuring seamless integration with existing systems. Whether you&rsquo;re outfitting a new building or upgrading an existing paging system, the TOA PC-2668 offers the versatility and reliability needed for long-lasting performance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-pc-2668-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-107-4_1-dIXTMPAQmL.png', '2025-01-13 07:45:46.455854', '2025-01-13 07:48:58.649466', 107),
(203, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CP-73 Ceiling Speaker is a versatile and discreet solution for high-quality audio in commercial and professional spaces. With its slim profile and off-white finish, it blends seamlessly into most ceiling environments. The spring catch mounting method makes installation easy and secure, ensuring a quick setup process. This speaker is designed for use with the TOA CM-760 speaker, enhancing your sound system with crystal-clear audio output. Its lightweight design (70g) and durable ABS resin frame ensure that it is easy to install and maintain.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The CP-73 features an aluminum-painted net that not only offers a clean and modern appearance but also simplifies cleaning and maintenance. Whether you\'re using it for paging systems or general audio applications, this speaker is designed to meet the needs of any space requiring discreet yet effective sound solutions. Its compact dimensions ensure it can be installed in a variety of ceiling types without taking up too much room. The CP-73&rsquo;s functionality and sleek design make it an ideal addition to any sound system.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-cp-73-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-108-3_1-44bKHoqfSl.png', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.982348', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.988035', 108),
(204, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA CP-73 Ceiling Speaker offers a high-quality audio experience with a design that is both practical and aesthetically pleasing. Perfect for a wide range of paging systems, it provides clear, effective sound while staying unobtrusive in ceilings. The spring catch mounting method ensures a secure fit with the TOA CM-760 speaker, allowing for a quick and hassle-free installation. Its thin, off-white frame blends into ceiling spaces, making it ideal for environments where visual appeal is just as important as audio performance.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Crafted with an aluminum net and a painted finish, this speaker not only delivers excellent sound but is also easy to clean and maintain. The compact size of the CP-73 means it fits seamlessly into any room, offering a professional look without compromising on sound quality. Whether in offices, retail spaces, or public areas, this speaker ensures that paging announcements and background music are heard clearly without detracting from the surroundings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-cp-73-ceiling-speaker/descriptions/202501-108-5-FZSVftPeA8.png', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.989850', '2025-01-13 08:24:29.993801', 108),
(205, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA AT-063AP Flush-Mounted Wall Attenuator is an excellent addition to any paging system, offering a practical solution for controlling sound volume in a wide variety of environments. Its flush-mount design allows for a clean, professional appearance when installed, while the built-in transformer enables it to handle a wide range of loads up to 6W. This versatility makes it a flexible component that can be used across different setups and system sizes. The device features five attenuation steps, including 0 dB, -6 dB, -12 dB, -18 dB, and an OFF option, allowing users to fine-tune audio output to their specific needs.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The device&rsquo;s easy installation is facilitated by the push-in terminal block, which allows quick and secure connections, saving time and effort during setup. The construction of the AT-063AP includes a durable ABS resin body, which ensures longevity and resilience in both residential and commercial environments. Its compact size of 70 mm x 120 mm x 52.4 mm ensures a minimal footprint, making it easy to integrate into any space. This attenuator is ideal for use in any paging system where precise volume control is needed, such as offices, schools, or public buildings.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-at-063ap-flush-mounted-wall-attenuator/descriptions/202501-109-3_1-ZBawQu1lyD.png', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.389764', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.395482', 109),
(206, '<p dir=\"ltr\">The TOA AT-063AP Flush-Mounted Wall Attenuator is designed for optimal performance and ease of use. It offers a range of features that make it ideal for paging systems requiring reliable volume control. The unit operates within an input range of 0.5W to 6W, providing flexibility for different applications. With five distinct volume steps, users can adjust sound levels to suit various environments, ensuring clarity and comfort. Additionally, the attenuator&rsquo;s push-in terminal block simplifies installation, making it an excellent choice for those who require a hassle-free setup.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The AT-063AP is built for long-lasting durability, featuring a robust ABS resin construction that stands up to everyday wear. The white and black finish options blend seamlessly with most interior designs, enhancing the overall aesthetic of the installation area. Its compact dimensions (41 x 108 x 52.4 mm for the attenuator alone) make it easy to install in tight spaces, while still offering high performance. The product also comes with mounting accessories for easy attachment to the wall, ensuring a secure and stable installation. For those requiring additional options, compatible mounting plates and boxes (YP-1AF and YS-11A) are available for purchase.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/toa-at-063ap-flush-mounted-wall-attenuator/descriptions/202501-109-1_3-mwECHmlae9.png', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.396952', '2025-01-14 00:42:10.400551', 109),
(207, '<p>The XRAY Baggage Scanner SF5636 is specifically engineered to enhance the security screening process in high-traffic and high-risk environments. Its compact yet robust design allows it to fit seamlessly into various security setups without compromising on performance. The scanner\'s tunnel size of 560mm by 360mm ensures that it can handle a diverse range of baggage sizes, from small carry-ons to larger luggage, providing a comprehensive screening solution.</p>\r\n<p>With a conveyor speed of 0.22m/s and a maximum load capacity of 150 kg, the SF5636 is designed for efficiency and durability. Its high-resolution imaging capabilities, including a wire resolution of 40AWG, ensure that even the smallest metallic items are detected, enhancing the overall security and safety of the facility. Additionally, its low radiation leakage of &lt;0.06&mu;Gy/h and film safety standards for ISO 1600 make it a safe and reliable choice for both operators and passengers.</p>', 'products/sf5636/descriptions/202501-110-3_2-n1zTK8kxtR.png', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.448229', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.454183', 110),
(208, '<p>The XRAY Baggage Scanner SF5636 features cutting-edge technology to ensure accurate and efficient security screening. Its impressive steel penetration capability of 36mm allows it to see through dense and layered objects, ensuring that no prohibited items go unnoticed. The scanner\'s zoom functionality, ranging from 1x to 64x, provides operators with the flexibility to closely inspect suspicious items, enhancing the accuracy of the screening process.</p>\r\n<p>This model prioritizes safety and efficiency, offering a single inspection dosage of less than 1.01&mu;Gy, which minimizes radiation exposure without compromising imaging quality. Its user-friendly interface and robust construction make it an essential tool for any security operation, delivering reliable performance under demanding conditions. The SF5636 is the ideal solution for facilities seeking to enhance their security measures with advanced, dependable screening technology.</p>', 'products/sf5636/descriptions/202501-110-4_2-CeT9NRd4WS.png', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.456201', '2025-01-15 01:23:46.459574', 110),
(209, '<p>The UNIQSCAN SF6040 PRO is specifically crafted for environments that demand stringent security measures. Its scanning tunnel, measuring 650 mm in width and 500 mm in height, is suitable for various baggage dimensions, making it a versatile solution for different operational needs. The system\'s high-resolution 19-inch color LCD display ensures that security operators can easily interpret the X-ray images, enhancing the speed and accuracy of the screening process.</p>\r\n<p>Moreover, the SF6040 PRO features a sealed oil bath with forced air cooling, maintaining optimal operating temperatures for the X-ray tube and detector. Its L-shaped array detector enhances image clarity and depth, providing comprehensive views of the scanned items. With a tube current of 0.6MA and an anode voltage of 80KV, the scanner offers consistent performance and durability in demanding security environments.</p>', 'products/sf6040-pro/descriptions/202501-111-d-1nL1OJMVoA.png', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.623246', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.629699', 111),
(210, '<p>Safety and convenience are at the forefront of the UNIQSCAN SF6040 PRO\'s design. The scanner is equipped with emergency stop buttons, allowing immediate cessation of operations in critical situations, and a one-key turn-off function for rapid shutdown when necessary. These features underscore its commitment to safety and efficiency in security operations.</p>\r\n<p>The device\'s advanced capabilities in detecting dangerous substances, including drugs and explosive powders, make it a crucial asset in maintaining security. Operators can adjust the image brightness with ease, ensuring that visibility is optimized regardless of the lighting conditions in the screening area. The upward beam direction further aids in providing clear, detailed images of the contents within each piece of luggage.</p>', 'products/sf6040-pro/descriptions/202501-111-e-SYN0UCwkjb.png', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.631484', '2025-01-15 01:44:36.636527', 111),
(211, '<p>The UNIQSAN SF10080 is a robust and efficient X-ray baggage scanner specifically designed to meet the demanding security needs of high-security areas such as airports, government buildings, and transit stations. It features a wide tunnel size of 1000mm (W) x 800mm (H), making it suitable for screening larger bags and packages. With its advanced multi-energy technology, the scanner switches between high and low energy modes, ensuring comprehensive detection of various materials. The system provides clear images that can reveal hidden threats such as drugs, explosives, and other dangerous items, giving security personnel the ability to respond swiftly.</p>\r\n<p>Moreover, the SF10080&rsquo;s high-resolution 19-inch color LCD display offers exceptional clarity and detail, helping operators detect and assess items more accurately. The built-in image enhancement feature further refines image quality, ensuring that every scan delivers precise results. The color material identification system categorizes materials into organic (orange), inorganic (blue), and mixed (green) for quicker analysis. Backed by a two-year warranty, this X-ray scanner ensures long-term reliability and high performance, making it an essential tool for any high-security environment.</p>', 'products/sf10080/descriptions/202501-112-a-kKXGiI5P76.png', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.791062', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.796849', 112),
(212, '<p>Designed with ease of use in mind, the UNIQSAN SF10080 X-ray scanner is equipped with a variety of features to enhance both performance and user experience. Its intuitive interface and clear 19-inch LCD display allow operators to navigate through scans effortlessly, ensuring high throughput in busy security settings. The scanner&rsquo;s advanced image processing system offers super image enhancement, which makes fine details stand out, improving the detection of even the smallest threats. Additionally, its brightening and dimming feature helps adjust screen visibility depending on the surrounding light conditions, ensuring the best possible image quality.</p>\r\n<p>This X-ray scanner\'s capabilities extend to identifying both organic and inorganic materials through its unique color material identification system. It helps security personnel distinguish between potentially hazardous materials, such as explosives or drugs, and non-threatening objects. The SF10080 is built with international standards in mind, certified by CE, ISO, FCC, and ROHS. With features like sealed oil bath cooling with forced air and reliable performance, this scanner guarantees consistent operation even in high-demand environments.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/sf10080/descriptions/202501-112-f-FdohMoN6Wp.png', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.798465', '2025-01-15 02:26:23.802031', 112),
(213, '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is a robust environmental monitoring system designed for indoor use, offering precise measurement of temperature and humidity. This device comes with an internal temperature sensor that can detect ambient temperatures from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C) with an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. In addition, the Room Alert 12SR includes one external Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor, allowing for expanded monitoring capabilities. The system can accommodate up to 8 additional sensors for customized setups, ensuring that critical conditions are always under control. With features like digital, switch, and analog sensor ports, it&rsquo;s equipped to monitor a wide range of environmental variables, making it ideal for data centers, server rooms, and other sensitive environments.</p>\r\n<p>The unit is designed for ease of installation and operation. It can be powered by either a 5V adapter or PoE, providing flexibility for different network setups. The small yet durable unit fits easily into tight spaces, with the 12S model for non-rack mounting and the 12SR for rack-mounting. It also features a relay output port and a light tower adapter port to trigger alerts, ensuring that users are notified immediately of any environmental anomalies. Whether used in a small office or a large data center, the AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR ensures that you are always aware of your facility&rsquo;s temperature and humidity levels.</p>', 'products/avtech-12sr/descriptions/202501-113-D-L1NRQmef2Q.PNG', '2025-01-15 02:46:39.842754', '2025-01-15 02:55:30.221750', 113);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(214, '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is engineered to provide consistent, reliable monitoring in environments where temperature and humidity control are critical. With its internal temperature sensor and included external Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor, this device can track temperature, humidity, heat index, and dew point. It also allows for the addition of up to 8 more sensors, making it versatile enough for larger facilities or specific monitoring needs. The device offers multiple ports for connecting external sensors and accessories, making it easy to expand its monitoring capabilities to meet your facility&rsquo;s unique requirements. Its operating range of -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C) ensures it can handle extreme temperature fluctuations without compromising performance.</p>\r\n<p>This system is equipped with advanced connectivity options, including an Ethernet port with PoE support, allowing you to integrate it seamlessly into your existing network infrastructure. It can be powered by a 5V adapter or through PoE, offering flexibility in deployment. The AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is designed with durability and ease of use in mind, with the 12SR model being rack-mounted for use in environments such as server rooms and data centers. With its extensive monitoring capabilities and customizable sensor options, the Room Alert 12S/12SR provides peace of mind knowing your facility is being actively monitored for temperature and humidity fluctuations.</p>', 'products/avtech-12sr/descriptions/202501-113-F-liDmRtQak3.PNG', '2025-01-15 02:46:39.850706', '2025-01-15 02:55:30.224221', 113),
(215, '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 12S is an ideal environmental monitoring solution for businesses that require real-time data on temperature and humidity levels. With its internal temperature sensor, the 12S model measures ambient indoor temperatures from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C), ensuring accurate readings within a margin of &plusmn;2&deg;C. The included external Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor further enhances the monitoring capabilities by measuring not only temperature and humidity but also heat index and dew point. This enables businesses to monitor multiple environmental factors that may impact their operations, assets, or equipment.</p>\r\n<p>Equipped with various sensor ports, the Room Alert 12S offers excellent expandability. It supports up to 8 additional sensors for a customizable monitoring experience. The device features 3 digital sensor ports, 4 switch sensor ports, 1 analog sensor port, and even a relay output port for enhanced functionality. This versatile setup allows users to integrate additional environmental sensors as needed, ensuring that critical areas in your facility are monitored without compromise. With its compact design and ease of use, the AVTECH Room Alert 12S is a powerful, cost-effective solution for businesses aiming to maintain optimal environmental conditions.</p>', 'products/avtech-12s/descriptions/202501-114-A-oX2GTL9ZG5.PNG', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.157843', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.163810', 114),
(216, '<p>The Room Alert 12S/12SR is designed to operate efficiently and reliably in a variety of environments, offering monitoring solutions for temperature, humidity, and other environmental variables. The unit&rsquo;s design includes a standard Ethernet port that supports Power over Ethernet (PoE), making installation and power supply more efficient. Whether you choose the 12S model for standalone use or the 12SR model for rack-mounted applications, the Room Alert 12S offers flexibility without compromising performance. Its rugged construction and reliability make it suitable for critical environments such as data centers, server rooms, or any location where environmental conditions need to be closely monitored.</p>\r\n<p>With user-friendly access to key environmental data, the Room Alert 12S can help businesses prevent issues like overheating, humidity-related damage, or equipment failures. The device is equipped with a user-friendly web interface that allows for easy monitoring and configuration, making it accessible to both technical and non-technical personnel. Additionally, the AVTECH Room Alert 12S/12SR is backed by robust customer support and ensures that your facility remains protected against potential environmental hazards. Whether you\'re managing sensitive equipment or maintaining optimal working conditions, the Room Alert 12S provides peace of mind and reliable performance.</p>', 'products/avtech-12s/descriptions/202501-114-F-VFMRSrYymS.png', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.165366', '2025-01-15 03:19:26.168693', 114),
(217, '<p>The AVTECH Room Alert 3S is a high-performance environmental monitor that helps businesses maintain optimal conditions for sensitive equipment. This model features an internal temperature sensor capable of detecting indoor ambient temperatures between -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F (-40&deg;C to 85&deg;C). With a high accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C and a resolution of 0.03125&deg;C, it delivers precise and reliable temperature readings. The device&rsquo;s small size allows it to be easily placed in tight spaces, making it perfect for monitoring areas like server rooms, network closets, or any facility where temperature control is critical.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to its internal temperature monitoring capabilities, the Room Alert 3S can be expanded with external sensors, such as humidity or water sensors, through its digital sensor/accessory port. It also supports an RJ-11 switch sensor port for more customized monitoring setups. This flexibility allows businesses to adapt the system as their monitoring needs grow. With PoE (Power over Ethernet) support or a 5V power adapter, the device offers flexible connectivity and power options to fit your infrastructure.</p>', 'products/avtech-3s/descriptions/202501-115-B-tslzjIPnay.PNG', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.109865', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.115617', 115),
(218, '<p>The Room Alert 3S is designed to help businesses respond quickly to environmental changes that could jeopardize critical systems. When used with the Light Tower &amp; Relay Adapter, it enables automated actions, such as triggering cooling systems or activating alarms when temperature thresholds are exceeded. This makes the Room Alert 3S not only a monitoring tool but also a response system, helping businesses take swift action to prevent damage or downtime. The device&rsquo;s alerting features include visual signals through the Light Tower and audible alerts via a siren, ensuring that all personnel in the area are notified immediately.</p>\r\n<p>Compact and user-friendly, the Room Alert 3S offers an intuitive setup process and easy-to-read digital readings in both Fahrenheit and Celsius. With its ability to operate in extreme temperatures from -40&deg;F to 185&deg;F and its wide humidity tolerance of 5% to 85% RH, it&rsquo;s a reliable tool for monitoring various environments. Whether used in industrial, IT, or sensitive storage areas, the Room Alert 3S ensures your equipment and facilities are always protected from potential environmental hazards.</p>', 'products/avtech-3s/descriptions/202501-115-D-bFygEVX5qO.png', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.117529', '2025-01-15 03:34:53.121032', 115),
(219, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Active Power Sensor with Temperature is a robust and reliable monitoring device designed to provide real-time environmental data. Capable of measuring a wide temperature range from -67&deg;F to 257&deg;F (-55&deg;C to 125&deg;C), it offers versatile applications across various industries. With an accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C, this sensor ensures precise data collection, essential for maintaining optimal conditions in critical environments.</p>\r\n<p>Its digital sensor technology, coupled with a high resolution of 0.0625&deg;C, guarantees detailed and accurate readings. The sensor is compatible with several Room Alert models, including 32S, 12S, 3S, 32E/W, 12E, 4E, 3E, and 3W, making it an adaptable addition to any existing monitoring system. The device\'s real-time recognition capability allows for immediate detection and response to temperature changes, ensuring the safety and efficiency of operations.</p>', 'products/digital-active-power-sensor-w-temperature/descriptions/202501-116-image-removeb_7ysESb7.png', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.127701', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.132993', 116),
(220, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Active Power Sensor is designed for seamless integration into power monitoring systems, providing accurate and real-time temperature monitoring. Its durable RJ-11 cable is available in lengths of 25, 50, or 100 feet, offering flexibility in sensor placement. The maximum cable length of approximately 100 feet ensures that even distant areas can be monitored effectively.</p>\r\n<p>This sensor is an essential tool for any facility looking to enhance its environmental monitoring capabilities. By delivering precise temperature data, it helps prevent overheating and ensures the longevity of critical equipment. Its compatibility with a wide range of Room Alert products makes it a versatile choice for various monitoring needs, from data centers to industrial settings.</p>', 'products/digital-active-power-sensor-w-temperature/descriptions/202501-116-image-removeb_7J2JONI.png', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.134431', '2025-01-15 03:57:25.137613', 116),
(221, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Temperature Sensor offers an impressive temperature monitoring solution for various settings. It is engineered to provide real-time recognition of temperature values with a high degree of accuracy within a range of -67 to 257&deg;F (-55 to 125&deg;C). The sensor boasts a resolution of 0.0625&deg;C, providing users with precise and reliable data. This makes it an excellent choice for industries or businesses that require continuous temperature tracking for their operations. The accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C ensures that the readings remain within a reliable range for all monitoring needs.</p>\r\n<p>With its easy-to-use digital sensor cable, available in lengths of 25\', 50\', or 100\', the AVTECH Digital Temperature Sensor allows for flexible installation. The sensor can be connected to various Room Alert products like the 32S, 12S, 3S, and others, ensuring it seamlessly integrates into your existing monitoring system. Powered through the monitoring unit, it eliminates the need for additional power sources, simplifying setup and maintenance.</p>', 'products/digital-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-117-C-UYwGU2YCAK.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.185130', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.191490', 117),
(222, '<p>This digital temperature sensor provides continuous monitoring of temperature fluctuations, giving users peace of mind knowing that the environment is being consistently checked. Whether it is monitoring a storage facility, data center, or home server room, the AVTECH Digital Temperature Sensor ensures that temperatures remain within optimal conditions. The maximum sensor cable length of 100\' (30.48 m) provides flexibility in installation, allowing the sensor to be placed wherever temperature monitoring is essential.</p>\r\n<p>The AVTECH sensor is compatible with several Room Alert products, making it easy to integrate into an existing infrastructure. Its simple design and functionality, coupled with its precise temperature tracking capabilities, offer a robust solution for temperature-sensitive environments. The sensor is particularly useful in maintaining controlled conditions and preventing potential damage from temperature extremes.</p>', 'products/digital-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-117-D-vSluOpYH4I.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.193069', '2025-01-15 05:18:35.196235', 117),
(223, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Outdoor Temperature Sensor is designed for accurate temperature monitoring in harsh outdoor environments. It provides real-time temperature readings from -67&deg;F to 257&deg;F (-55&deg;C to 125&deg;C), with a high level of precision (&plusmn;2&deg;C) to ensure reliable data. This sensor is equipped with an external silicon coating, offering resilience against outdoor elements like rain, wind, and extreme temperatures. Whether you\'re monitoring a warehouse, greenhouse, or outdoor equipment, this sensor delivers dependable performance.</p>\r\n<p>The sensor is compatible with several Room Alert models, ensuring seamless integration into existing monitoring setups. It features an RJ-11 cable for easy installation, with available lengths of 25\', 50\', and 100\', allowing users to place the sensor in the optimal location. The sensor&rsquo;s 0.0625&deg;C resolution allows for detailed temperature readings, providing invaluable insights into temperature fluctuations in various environments.</p>', 'products/digital-outdoor-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-118-A-3j8hewbj8l.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.106952', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.111754', 118),
(224, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Outdoor Temperature Sensor is engineered for precision and durability, making it an ideal choice for critical temperature monitoring applications. It is built to withstand the demands of outdoor settings, ensuring long-lasting operation in a wide range of conditions. With a temperature range of -67&deg;F to 257&deg;F (-55&deg;C to 125&deg;C), the sensor provides users with real-time data for both high and low-temperature environments. Its accuracy of &plusmn;2&deg;C ensures the temperature readings are reliable, even in challenging conditions.</p>\r\n<p>This digital sensor works with AVTECH\'s Room Alert monitoring systems, offering seamless compatibility with models such as the Room Alert 32S, 12S, and 3S. The included RJ-11 cable ensures easy connection, and users can choose from multiple cable lengths (25&rsquo;, 50&rsquo;, or 100&rsquo;) to meet their specific needs. With its weather-resistant design and high accuracy, the AVTECH Digital Outdoor Temperature Sensor is an essential tool for anyone needing precise temperature monitoring in outdoor or harsh environments.</p>', 'products/digital-outdoor-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-118-B-tReyYOyw1v.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.113394', '2025-01-15 05:33:56.116981', 118),
(225, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Fluid Temperature Sensor delivers unparalleled performance in monitoring fluid temperatures. Designed for versatility, it can accurately measure temperatures from -67 to 257&deg; Fahrenheit (-55 to 125&deg; Celsius), making it suitable for a wide range of applications. With a precision of +/- 2&deg;C, users can rely on consistent and accurate readings to manage their temperature-sensitive environments effectively.</p>\r\n<p>Encased in a sealed tube with Propylene Glycol, the sensor is safeguarded against external influences, providing robust and reliable measurements. Its non-conductive nature ensures that it can operate in harsh conditions without risking electrical interference, making it perfect for use in laboratories, aquariums, and refrigerated storage. The sensor connects to monitoring units via an RJ-11 cable, with options for cable lengths of 25\', 50\', or 100\', allowing for flexible installation.</p>', 'products/digital-fluid-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-119-A-trooIPyvob.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.210383', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.216571', 119),
(226, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Fluid Temperature Sensor is engineered to support critical monitoring systems, providing real-time temperature recognition for a variety of fluids. Its high-precision sensor captures temperature fluctuations with a resolution of 0.0625&deg;C, ensuring that even the smallest changes are detected. This makes it a vital tool in maintaining the integrity of environments where precise temperature control is non-negotiable.</p>\r\n<p>Designed for compatibility with AVTECH\'s Room Alert series, including models 32S, 12S, 3S, 32E/W, 12E, 4E, 3E, and 3W, this sensor seamlessly integrates into existing monitoring setups. Its long cable options and robust build ensure that it can be deployed in diverse settings, from small labs to large-scale industrial applications, providing consistent and accurate temperature monitoring across the board.</p>', 'products/digital-fluid-temperature-sensor/descriptions/202501-119-D-UYxKeOKZuz.PNG', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.217938', '2025-01-15 05:53:25.221044', 119),
(227, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor offers precise environmental monitoring, making it a critical tool for any setting where temperature and humidity control are vital. With a temperature range from -40 to 185&deg;F (-40 to 85&deg;C) and a humidity range of 5% to 95% RH, this sensor is designed to handle a broad spectrum of environmental conditions. Its accuracy, within +/- 2&deg;C for temperature and +/- 4.5% to 6.5% RH for humidity, ensures reliable data for optimal decision-making.</p>\r\n<p>Ideal for use in data centers, warehouses, and sensitive storage environments, the sensor\'s real-time recognition capabilities enable immediate detection of any deviations from set parameters. This prompt detection helps in preventing potential damages and maintaining the integrity of stored goods or sensitive equipment. With its compatibility with Room Alert 32S, 12S, 3S, and other models, this sensor is a versatile addition to any monitoring system.</p>', 'products/digital-temperature-humidity/descriptions/202501-120-image-removebg-preview_4-q_nPzQoR7.png', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.422269', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.427826', 120),
(228, '<p>Designed for durability and ease of use, the AVTECH Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor comes with an RJ-11 cable available in lengths of 25\', 50\', or 100\', ensuring flexible installation options for various setups. The sensor&rsquo;s robust construction allows it to function effectively in non-condensing environments, making it suitable for a wide range of applications. Its ability to provide real-time data helps in immediate response to environmental changes, thereby reducing the risk of costly damages.</p>\r\n<p>The sensor&rsquo;s integration with AVTECH\'s monitoring units enables it to deliver seamless performance and accurate readings that are essential for maintaining controlled environments. Whether you are monitoring a large facility or a small server room, the AVTECH Digital Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor provides the reliability and precision needed to safeguard your assets.</p>', 'products/digital-temperature-humidity/descriptions/202501-120-image-removebg-preview_1-d_K4bKboY.png', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.429674', '2025-01-15 06:32:43.433518', 120),
(229, '<p>The AVTECH Digital Shielded Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor is engineered to provide precise environmental monitoring, crucial for maintaining optimal conditions in critical spaces. This sensor offers real-time temperature readings between -40 to 185&deg;F (-40 to 85&deg;C) with a remarkable accuracy of +/- 2&deg;C. Humidity levels are measured within a range of 5% to 95% RH, ensuring comprehensive environmental oversight. The accuracy of humidity readings is within +/- 4.5% for 5% to 59% RH and within +/- 6.5% for 60% to 95% RH, making it a reliable choice for a wide variety of settings.</p>\r\n<p>Designed with a shielded cable, this sensor minimizes interference from electrical noise or EMI, ensuring accurate data transmission. Its compatibility with various Room Alert monitors allows for seamless integration into existing monitoring systems, providing a dependable solution for environments that demand precise climate control.</p>', 'products/digital-shielded-temperature-humidity/descriptions/202501-121-F-lOacvwWtRT.PNG', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.430728', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.435938', 121),
(230, '<p>AVTECH&rsquo;s Digital Shielded Temperature &amp; Humidity Sensor stands out with its plug-and-play design, simplifying installation and use. The sensor connects via a standard RJ-11 jack to any compatible Room Alert monitor, instantly feeding real-time data for logging and analysis. This immediate feedback enables quick responses to any environmental changes, preventing potential issues before they escalate.</p>\r\n<p>The sensor is available with cable lengths of 25&rsquo;, 50&rsquo;, and 100&rsquo;, offering flexibility for different installation requirements. Its robust design and accuracy make it ideal for environments like server rooms and data centers, where maintaining precise temperature and humidity levels is crucial for equipment longevity and performance.</p>', 'products/digital-shielded-temperature-humidity/descriptions/202501-121-C-odxkUKbxW7.PNG', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.437525', '2025-01-15 07:11:57.440881', 121),
