(295, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MBA-624C SIMPLEX Conventional Heat Detector is an advanced fire safety device designed to detect temperature changes and provide early warning of fire hazards. It offers reliable, accurate performance in both residential and commercial settings, helping protect your property from potential fire damage. The MBA-624C features a durable and compact design, making it easy to install and maintain in various environments. This heat detector is engineered to trigger alarms when temperatures reach pre-set thresholds, ensuring a timely response in emergencies. With its consistent detection capabilities, the MBA-624C contributes to a comprehensive fire safety system, integrating seamlessly with other SIMPLEX Conventional fire alarm products. Its high reliability and performance make it a top choice for ensuring the safety of your building.</span></p>', 'products/simplex-convention-mba-624c/descriptions/202501-156-4_1-HnSGr2iPYW.png', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.830091', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.835418', 156),
(296, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">MBA-624C SIMPLEX Conventional Heat Detector is a versatile solution for fire detection. It is designed to withstand harsh conditions and deliver accurate results over time, requiring minimal maintenance. The heat detector is fully compatible with SIMPLEX fire alarm systems, allowing for a coordinated and efficient response in the event of a fire. Whether in industrial, commercial, or residential applications, the MBA-624C provides an additional layer of safety. This product meets rigorous industry standards, ensuring reliable fire protection across various environments. Trust the MBA-624C for dependable and timely fire detection that enhances your building\'s overall safety plan.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></span></p>', 'products/simplex-convention-mba-624c/descriptions/202501-156-6-U8xV4VmeDI.png', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.837198', '2025-01-17 02:31:59.840497', 156),
(297, '<p>The Simplex 4098-9714 Addressable TrueAlarm Photoelectric Smoke Sensor is built to deliver exceptional smoke detection performance in demanding environments. Featuring an advanced photoelectric sensing system, this sensor utilizes a stable, pulsed infrared LED light source paired with a silicon photodiode receiver for accurate, low-power smoke sensing. The sensor is equipped with seven adjustable sensitivity levels, which range from 0.2% to 3.7% per foot of smoke obscuration. This flexibility enables the sensor to be fine-tuned to meet the specific needs of various applications, ensuring optimal smoke detection in all scenarios.</p>\r\n<p>Designed to integrate seamlessly into addressable fire alarm systems, the Simplex 4098-9714 provides reliable monitoring and control. The sensitivity levels can be selected and monitored directly from the fire alarm control panel, offering real-time feedback and ensuring the system is always functioning at peak performance. The versatile design of this smoke sensor makes it ideal for use in both large-scale commercial facilities and smaller buildings, where precise smoke detection is essential to maintaining a safe environment.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9714/descriptions/202501-157-3_1-4d79fwLEr5.png', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.878481', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.883897', 157),
(298, '<p>The Simplex 4098-9714 Addressable Smoke Sensor is engineered to meet the needs of modern fire alarm systems with its high accuracy and reliability. Its photoelectric sensing technology ensures consistent and low-power smoke detection, making it suitable for a wide range of applications. The sensor&rsquo;s infrared LED light source, combined with a silicon photodiode receiver, ensures long-lasting performance and minimal maintenance requirements. With seven available sensitivity settings, ranging from 0.2% to 3.7% per foot of smoke obscuration, users can customize the sensor to suit specific fire safety needs.</p>\r\n<p>Ease of use and monitoring are key features of the Simplex 4098-9714. Sensitivity settings can be adjusted and monitored directly at the fire alarm control panel, offering a user-friendly interface for building managers and safety personnel. The versatility of this smoke sensor makes it a perfect choice for high-traffic areas, commercial spaces, and other environments that demand reliable and adjustable smoke detection. Its ability to detect even the smallest traces of smoke ensures early fire detection, reducing the risk of damage and enhancing safety.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9714/descriptions/202501-157-5-ZI6ahVRVlq.png', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.886083', '2025-01-17 02:36:42.890374', 157),
(299, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4098-9733 TrueAlarm heat sensor is a top-tier fire detection component known for its precision and durability. Designed for use in a wide variety of environments, the 4098-9733 features fixed temperature sensing and an optional rate-of-rise temperature sensing function. This dual functionality allows for customization based on the specific needs of your fire safety system. Whether for detecting gradual temperature changes or rapid spikes in heat, the SIMPLEX heat sensor excels in providing reliable alerts.</p>\r\n<p>With its self-restoring design, the sensor minimizes the need for constant maintenance and is built to last. The small thermal mass of the 4098-9733 ensures quick and accurate temperature measurements, contributing to the overall speed and effectiveness of your fire alarm system. This sensor\'s high sensitivity ensures that even subtle temperature changes are detected and addressed swiftly, preventing potential fire hazards.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9733/descriptions/202501-158-4_1-7v0UBCQaSc.png', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.894104', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.899025', 158),
(300, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4098-9733 heat sensor is designed to offer superior fire detection performance by utilizing cutting-edge technology. Its self-restoring feature allows it to reset after detecting a temperature shift, ensuring that the sensor continues to function without requiring frequent servicing. The fixed temperature sensing feature ensures that the sensor consistently operates at the desired sensitivity level, while the optional rate-of-rise sensing mode adds flexibility, enabling detection of both gradual and rapid heat increases.</p>\r\n<p>This highly reliable sensor is perfect for use in both residential and commercial settings, offering versatile fire detection. Its small thermal mass allows for fast and accurate local temperature measurements, providing real-time data to the fire alarm control panel for immediate response. The SIMPLEX 4098-9733 TrueAlarm heat sensor ensures that fire safety systems operate at peak performance, enhancing the safety of any environment it is installed in.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9733/descriptions/202501-158-5-I2ryzjiJri.png', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.900583', '2025-01-17 02:44:04.904823', 158),
(301, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4100ES Series Fire Detection and Control Panel is designed to provide reliable and versatile fire alarm solutions. It features advanced point and module capacities, suitable for a wide range of fire detection applications. The system is ideal for both new installations and system upgrades, offering ease of integration and enhanced functionality. The 4100ES is engineered to meet the needs of facilities requiring scalable and flexible fire alarm systems that provide rapid response to emergencies.</p>\r\n<p>This fire control panel is optimized for both small and large-scale installations, offering robust protection across diverse environments. Its user-friendly interface and enhanced serviceability allow for efficient maintenance and easy access to system settings, ensuring minimal downtime in critical situations.</p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4100es/descriptions/202501-159-33-0AMeGMP1dd.png', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.245857', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.251768', 159),
(302, '<p>The SIMPLEX CONVENTIONAL 4100ES Fire Detection and Control Panel delivers unmatched performance and reliability in fire protection systems. With its wide range of point and module capacities, it can be tailored to suit the specific needs of various building types and fire safety requirements. The system integrates seamlessly with other fire safety devices, allowing for a fully coordinated response in case of fire or emergency. Additionally, its flexible configuration options enable it to grow with the changing needs of the facility.</p>\r\n<p>Designed for high efficiency, the SIMPLEX 4100ES is a trusted solution for both commercial and industrial applications. Whether you\'re upgrading an existing system or installing a new one, the system ensures that each element is meticulously monitored and controlled, ensuring the highest standards of fire safety.</p>', 'products/simplex-conventional-4100es/descriptions/202501-159-55-Tmzzoq5XRb.PNG', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.253594', '2025-01-17 02:55:31.258055', 159),
(303, '<p>The SIMPLEX Addressable Sensor 4098-9792 is designed to meet the growing need for efficient and reliable fire detection systems. Utilizing addressable technology, each sensor within the network is individually identified, allowing for faster and more precise responses to fire events. This unique feature not only improves safety by minimizing response times but also enables a more streamlined and effective monitoring system.</p>\r\n<p>With its combination of smoke and heat detection technologies, the 4098-9792 provides enhanced accuracy in identifying fire incidents. The sensor\'s smart design ensures that only real fire threats trigger alerts, reducing the likelihood of false alarms that could disrupt operations. The advanced detection mechanism helps optimize fire protection efforts, making it a dependable choice for both commercial and residential applications.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9792/descriptions/202501-160-33-LK8D0MfFY7.png', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.337192', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.342180', 160),
(304, '<p>The SIMPLEX Addressable Sensor 4098-9792 offers superior flexibility and customization, providing tailored detection thresholds to suit a variety of environments. This capability allows the sensor to adapt to unique conditions, ensuring optimal performance in diverse settings such as office buildings, warehouses, and educational institutions. Its precise addressing feature ensures that the exact location of a fire threat is quickly identified, improving emergency response and safety measures.</p>\r\n<p>Designed with long-term reliability in mind, the 4098-9792 is an essential element of any modern fire alarm system. It seamlessly integrates into a broad range of fire safety networks, offering compatibility with other SIMPLEX addressable devices. This makes it an ideal solution for those seeking a comprehensive, easy-to-maintain, and highly effective fire detection system.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4098-9792/descriptions/202501-160-55-NrVjzaYiby.png', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.344527', '2025-01-17 03:09:39.347776', 160),
(305, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4099-9002 is an addressable fire alarm device that offers exceptional reliability and functionality for fire detection systems. Designed to be integrated within an addressable network, this device allows for accurate identification of each component, ensuring quick response in emergencies. Its ability to communicate fault and alarm signals efficiently to the control panel helps maintain system performance. The device&rsquo;s sophisticated communication protocols ensure that issues are detected and addressed promptly, minimizing system downtime and enhancing overall safety. Its robust design is ideal for both small and large-scale applications, making it versatile in various commercial and industrial settings.</p>\r\n<p>With its advanced features, the 4099-9002 enhances the accuracy of fire detection by ensuring that each device&rsquo;s status can be remotely monitored and diagnosed. The device plays a crucial role in reducing the time and labor needed for troubleshooting, as its addressable nature allows technicians to pinpoint specific problems directly. Additionally, the integration of this module helps improve the system&rsquo;s overall efficiency and reliability, ensuring that the network remains in optimal working condition and capable of quickly responding to fire threats.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4099-9002/descriptions/202501-161-55-kgBZF8MdRn.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.417491', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.423435', 161),
(306, '<p>The SIMPLEX 4099-9002 Addressable device is designed to offer superior performance and reliability in fire detection and alarm systems. It is an integral part of an addressable network, providing precise information about the status of every connected device. This enables faster identification of issues and enhances the response times of the fire alarm system. The 4099-9002 uses advanced communication protocols that help reduce the likelihood of false alarms and ensure that every device is functioning as expected. This device is an essential tool for maintaining an effective fire safety network in any commercial, industrial, or large-scale facility.</p>\r\n<p>One of the standout features of the 4099-9002 is its ability to significantly reduce the time spent on maintenance. Thanks to its addressable functionality, technicians can pinpoint specific locations of faults, which allows for more efficient troubleshooting and repair. This not only ensures the reliability of the system but also helps in cutting down on operational costs over time. With its high level of performance and versatility, the SIMPLEX 4099-9002 stands out as an essential part of any modern fire detection infrastructure.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-4099-9002/descriptions/202501-161-66-0SzZ4PTAfE.png', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.424913', '2025-01-17 03:20:02.428274', 161),
(307, '<p>The SIMPLEX ADDRESSABLE 49AV-WRF is designed for superior fire detection and communication within modern fire alarm systems. Its addressable technology allows each unit to communicate directly with the central fire alarm control panel, ensuring rapid identification and response to potential fire incidents. The device&rsquo;s wall-mounted design is both sleek and durable, making it suitable for deployment in various settings, including commercial buildings, industrial sites, and public institutions.</p>\r\n<p>With a focus on safety and efficiency, the 49AV-WRF incorporates both audio and visual alert mechanisms. This dual-alert system ensures that occupants receive clear and immediate warnings, facilitating a swift and organized evacuation. Its reliable performance and robust construction make it a trusted choice for fire safety professionals seeking to enhance building safety and compliance.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-49av-wrf/descriptions/202501-162-33-j9Im9CJ5Et.png', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.742443', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.747397', 162),
(308, '<p>The 49AV-WRF by SIMPLEX is an advanced fire alarm device that combines innovative technology with practical functionality. Its addressable protocol ensures that each device can be individually identified and monitored, allowing for precise localization and swift response to fire incidents. The device is built with high-quality materials to withstand harsh environments, ensuring long-lasting performance and reliability.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to its technical capabilities, the 49AV-WRF features a sleek, unobtrusive design that blends well with any interior space. The combination of audible and visual alerts provides comprehensive notification, ensuring that all occupants, regardless of hearing or visual impairments, are adequately informed during an emergency. This device is a valuable addition to any fire protection strategy, enhancing overall safety and compliance.</p>', 'products/simplex-addressable-49av-wrf/descriptions/202501-162-77-68IEnJ91i1.PNG', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.749211', '2025-01-17 03:45:47.752571', 162),
(309, '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SD-651 Plug-in Smoke Detector is a high-performance smoke detection device designed to integrate seamlessly with fire alarm systems. Its compact design, measuring only 2 inches (5.1 cm) in depth, allows for installation in areas where space is limited. This device utilizes a photoelectric sensor that responds quickly to the presence of smoke, offering superior reliability in both residential and commercial environments. The SD-651 can be easily connected to a variety of different adapter bases, providing flexibility in wiring and voltage configurations.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks to its advanced design, the SD-651 ensures optimal sensitivity while minimizing false alarms, making it a trusted choice for fire detection. It&rsquo;s compatible with a range of conventional fire alarm control panels, ensuring easy integration into existing systems. The SD-651 is engineered to be durable, ensuring long-term functionality and dependable service. Whether you\'re upgrading an existing system or starting fresh, this smoke detector provides reliable, efficient protection.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sd-651/descriptions/202501-163-44-CzPETfJdWY.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.757304', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.762084', 163);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(310, '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL SD-651 Plug-in Smoke Detector offers reliable and efficient smoke detection with its innovative photoelectric sensing technology. The compact design makes it perfect for installation in areas with limited space. This smoke detector can be used with different adapter bases, offering flexibility for wiring and voltage configurations, which makes it an excellent option for new installations or system upgrades. The SD-651 is designed to provide early detection of smoke, alerting individuals to potential dangers before they escalate into major fires.</p>\r\n<p>The SD-651 is engineered to work seamlessly with conventional fire alarm systems, ensuring that it provides consistent and timely alerts in the event of a fire. Its versatility, combined with high sensitivity, makes it a valuable asset to any fire safety system. Installation and maintenance are straightforward, allowing for easy updates or replacements. As a cost-effective and reliable smoke detection solution, the SD-651 is perfect for anyone looking to enhance their fire safety plan.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sd-651/descriptions/202501-163-55-d69VU6UJkE.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.763473', '2025-01-17 05:24:11.767480', 163),
(311, '<p>The NOTIFIER CONVENTIONAL 5601P is a precision-engineered heat detector that excels in performance and adaptability. With a 135&deg;F fixed temperature threshold and a rate-of-rise activation feature, it offers dual protection against fire hazards by detecting both gradual and rapid temperature increases. The single-circuit design is housed in a plain, discreet casing that blends seamlessly with various interior designs, ensuring it complements rather than disrupts the aesthetics of your space.</p>\r\n<p>Designed for easy installation, the 5601P mounts effortlessly onto single-gang, octagonal, or four-square back boxes, offering flexibility to suit a wide range of setups. Its reversible mounting bracket supports both flush and surface-mount installations, catering to specific architectural requirements. This flexibility makes the 5601P an ideal choice for contractors and safety professionals seeking a reliable, easy-to-install solution.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-5601p/descriptions/202501-164-22-ssn2KENCwY.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.695691', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.702115', 164),
(312, '<p>The 5600 series, including the 5601P, features clear and practical design elements to enhance functionality and ease of use. Alphanumeric characters on the detector\'s exterior indicate the activation method and temperature rating in both Fahrenheit and Celsius, ensuring correct installation and application. The fixed temperature models are marked \'FX\', while the combination fixed temperature/rate-of-rise models are labeled \'FX/ROR\', aiding in quick identification.</p>\r\n<p>One of the standout features of the 5601P is its post-activation indicator&mdash;a collector that visibly drops from the unit upon activation. This feature allows for easy identification of units that have been triggered, streamlining the maintenance and reset process. With these thoughtful design features, the 5601P ensures both safety and convenience, making it a preferred choice in fire detection solutions.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-5601p/descriptions/202501-164-44-qKPLA3YPzo.PNG', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.703729', '2025-01-17 05:36:58.706788', 164),
(313, '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional NBG-12 series is crafted to provide a dependable and user-friendly fire alarm initiation. Designed for seamless compatibility with conventional Fire Alarm Control Panels, it ensures rapid and accurate alarm signaling in emergencies. Its robust construction and intuitive design make it an ideal choice for various applications, from schools and hospitals to office buildings and industrial sites.</p>\r\n<p>Installation is straightforward, thanks to the NBG-12\'s multiple mounting options. The series offers a variety of models to fit specific requirements, such as the NBG-12S for single-action activation and the NBG-12L for dual-action, providing flexibility and enhanced safety features to meet diverse fire safety needs.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-nbg-12/descriptions/202501-165-33-mKNBUwZL8m.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.380923', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.387193', 165),
(314, '<p>The NBG-12 series is engineered for durability and long-term reliability, featuring high-quality materials that withstand harsh environments. Its ergonomic handle and clear instructions ensure ease of use during emergencies, minimizing response time and maximizing efficiency. Maintenance is simplified through its accessible design, allowing for quick inspections and servicing without compromising system integrity.</p>\r\n<p>Each model in the NBG-12 series is designed with specific functionalities to cater to different safety protocols. For example, the NBG-12LSP offers Spanish/English labeling for bilingual environments, while the NBG-12LA includes an auxiliary contact option for additional signaling needs. This diversity ensures that every facility can find a model that aligns perfectly with its fire safety requirements.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-nbg-12/descriptions/202501-165-44-7YYa5cpy7l.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.389248', '2025-01-17 06:05:40.393064', 165),
(315, '<p>The NOTIFIER SFP-10UDE fire alarm control panel is designed to deliver exceptional performance in fire detection and alarm systems. Equipped with ten Class B IDCs, this control panel supports a wide range of initiating devices, providing flexible and reliable coverage across various zones. The built-in digital alarm communicator transmitter (DACT) ensures that critical alarm signals are swiftly transmitted to remote monitoring sites, enhancing the overall safety and response time during emergencies.</p>\r\n<p>This panel also includes four Class B Notification Appliance Circuits (NACs), each rated at 3.0 amps, allowing for powerful and consistent notification appliance operation. The optional Class A configuration, achievable with the N-CAC-5X converter module, provides additional flexibility for installations requiring enhanced circuit integrity. The SFP-10UDE&rsquo;s 7.0 amps total system power and compatibility with a wide range of ANN-BUS devices further underscore its capacity to handle complex fire safety requirements efficiently.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sfp-10ude/descriptions/202501-166-55-Px0b3xFPGO.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.215989', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.226410', 166),
(316, '<p>Designed for both new installations and system upgrades, the NOTIFIER SFP-10UDE offers advanced fire alarm control capabilities with a user-friendly interface. Its 80-character LCD display provides clear, concise information, making system monitoring and maintenance straightforward. The system\'s serial or parallel printer interface allows for convenient record-keeping and documentation of fire alarm events.</p>\r\n<p>The SFP-10UDE\'s remote site upload/download capability enhances its maintenance and update process, reducing downtime and ensuring that the system remains up-to-date with the latest safety protocols. The panel\'s red backbox variant not only adds a distinctive look but also helps in quickly identifying the fire alarm system in an emergency. With its robust features and proven reliability, the SFP-10UDE is a trusted choice for fire safety professionals.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-sfp-10ude/descriptions/202501-166-66-m4svb8WsDR.PNG', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.228407', '2025-01-17 06:32:24.234399', 166),
(317, '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL is a premier notification appliance designed to deliver reliable performance in fire alarm systems. Featuring the System Sensor L-Series technology, it combines a horn and strobe to provide both visual and audible alerts. This device is crafted for efficiency, offering a low current draw that minimizes energy consumption and operational costs. Its modern aesthetic, available in both white and red housings, makes it suitable for various settings, including commercial and residential buildings.</p>\r\n<p>Engineered for easy installation, the P2RL features a plug-in design that significantly reduces installation time. Its universal mounting plate with an onboard shorting spring allows for quick testing of wiring continuity before installation, ensuring a foolproof setup. The device also offers flexibility with field-selectable candela settings and automatic voltage selection, making it adaptable to a variety of application needs. Whether used in a new build or as a retrofit, the NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL delivers dependable performance and peace of mind.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-p2rl/descriptions/202501-167-55-lTBGf2fs8n.png', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.338358', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.343438', 167),
(318, '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional P2RL stands out for its innovative design and user-friendly features. Its integration into the System Sensor L-Series means it benefits from a line known for reducing installation times and maximizing profitability. The P2RL\'s compact design minimizes intrusion into back boxes, simplifying installation and maintenance. Its versatile functionality includes a rotary switch for selecting horn tones and volume, catering to different environments and user preferences.</p>\r\n<p>This device also addresses potential installation challenges with its robust, field-tested features. Its universal mounting plate protects the device from construction damage, making it a durable choice for long-term use. Additionally, the P2RL\'s aesthetic options, including plain, FIRE, and FUEGO-printed devices, allow for customization to meet specific code and design requirements. This adaptability, combined with its high-performance capabilities, positions the P2RL as a superior choice for fire safety solutions.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-p2rl/descriptions/202501-167-22-RW6GhqLnax.png', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.344923', '2025-01-17 07:18:27.349311', 167),
(319, '<p>The NOTIFIER Conventional FSB2000 reflected beam smoke detector is a sophisticated solution for large, open spaces that are difficult to monitor with standard smoke detectors. Its intelligent, addressable design allows it to effectively protect areas with high and sloping ceilings, ensuring early detection of smoke in places where traditional detectors cannot reach. By utilizing reflected beam technology, the FSB2000 covers wide areas with a single device, making it both cost-effective and easy to install.</p>\r\n<p>Ideal for a variety of applications, this detector excels in settings such as warehouses, concert halls, and atriums. It significantly reduces the complexity of installation and maintenance, thanks to its minimal wiring requirements and fewer units needed for coverage. The FSB2000\'s advanced detection capabilities ensure reliable performance, providing critical early warning in the event of a fire.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-fsb2000/descriptions/202501-168-33-6dDv2Zz5Xw.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.036885', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.042197', 168),
(320, '<p>Designed for environments where spot-type smoke detectors are challenging to use, the NOTIFIER Conventional FSB2000 brings advanced fire detection to architectural spaces like aircraft hangars, sporting arenas, and cathedral ceilings. Its reflected beam technology enables it to monitor large areas effectively, offering a streamlined approach to fire safety without compromising on coverage or accuracy.</p>\r\n<p>The FSB2000 is built to endure the demands of expansive and complex environments, providing consistent protection against fire hazards. With its intelligent features, it adapts to environmental changes, reducing false alarms and ensuring only genuine threats trigger a response. This adaptability makes the FSB2000 an essential component of any comprehensive fire detection system.</p>', 'products/notifier-conventional-fsb2000/descriptions/202501-168-77-EvdMWme9kP.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.044158', '2025-01-17 07:29:56.047921', 168),
(321, '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; ADDRESSABLE FSP-951 intelligent plug-in smoke detector is a top-tier solution for modern fire detection needs. Its sleek, contemporary design makes it an ideal choice for spaces that prioritize both safety and aesthetics. Built to replace the FSP-851 Series, the FSP-951 features an enhanced optical sensing chamber that is finely tuned to detect a wide range of combustion sources, meeting the latest code standards for smoke detection.</p>\r\n<p>This detector&rsquo;s addressable functionality allows for pinpoint accuracy in identifying the location of a potential fire, enabling faster and more efficient emergency responses. Its design emphasizes ease of installation and maintenance, with a plug-in mechanism that simplifies the process for technicians. The FSP-951&rsquo;s robust construction ensures long-lasting performance, making it a dependable choice for safeguarding lives and property.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fsp-951/descriptions/202501-169-44-1HKNgET9z4.png', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.185648', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.190400', 169),
(322, '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; ADDRESSABLE FSP-951 is engineered with a focus on superior smoke detection capabilities and user-friendly operation. Its enhanced optical sensing chamber is designed to recognize various combustion sources, providing comprehensive coverage and reducing the likelihood of false alarms. The detector&rsquo;s addressable nature allows it to communicate precise location data to the control panel, enabling targeted and effective fire response strategies.</p>\r\n<p>With a modern, low-profile design, the FSP-951 complements any interior while delivering top-notch fire safety. Its compatibility with existing NOTIFIER systems ensures a seamless integration, making it a perfect upgrade for enhancing the safety infrastructure of any building. The detector&rsquo;s advanced features and contemporary aesthetics make it a valuable addition to both new and retrofit projects.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fsp-951/descriptions/202501-169-77-UNfsVPSCTs.PNG', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.192264', '2025-01-17 07:49:51.196212', 169),
(323, '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; FST-951 Series intelligent thermal detectors combine modern design with superior thermal detection technology. This advanced detector series is engineered to replace the older FST-851 Series, offering improvements in both performance and aesthetics. With its sleek, contemporary appearance, the FST-951 seamlessly integrates into a variety of environments, providing enhanced fire detection without compromising on the visual appeal of the space. The detector features advanced thermal sensing technology that detects temperature changes, ensuring prompt and accurate fire detection.</p>\r\n<p>One of the standout features of the FST-951 Series is its point ID address system, which allows for easy and precise identification of each detector&rsquo;s location. This feature simplifies the management and maintenance of fire safety systems by eliminating the need for complex configurations. The FST-951 Series is also designed for easy integration into existing fire alarm systems, providing an ideal solution for both new installations and retrofits.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fst-951/descriptions/202501-170-66-hhU35fdxIf.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.832383', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.837335', 170),
(324, '<p>The NOTIFIER&reg; FST-951 Series is designed to meet the demanding requirements of modern fire safety systems while offering an aesthetic, streamlined look. These intelligent thermal detectors provide accurate and reliable detection by sensing temperature changes in the environment. The advanced thermal technologies used in the FST-951 Series ensure high-performance operation, which contributes to a safer environment by detecting potential hazards early. Designed with both functionality and style in mind, the FST-951 detectors integrate smoothly into contemporary building designs.</p>\r\n<p>Equipped with a rotary decimal switch for point ID addressing, the FST-951 Series allows users to assign specific locations to each detector. This ensures that the system is easy to manage and that any issues can be pinpointed quickly. The FST-951 is ideal for buildings where both fire safety and design integrity are a priority, making it a popular choice among architects and engineers seeking high-performance fire detection solutions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-fst-951/descriptions/202501-170-77-FDSRuQPkdt.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.839813', '2025-01-17 08:09:49.843374', 170),
(325, '<p>The Notifier NBG-12LX pull station is designed to enhance the safety and performance of fire alarm systems by providing a reliable manual activation method. Its dual-action design requires two separate motions to trigger the alarm, reducing the chances of accidental activation. This feature is especially important in environments where false alarms could cause significant disruptions. By requiring both actions, it ensures that only intentional activation occurs in case of an emergency.</p>\r\n<p>What sets the NBG-12LX apart is its addressable interface, which communicates with any Notifier intelligent control panel, except for the FireWarden series and NSP25 panel. This addressability feature allows the system to identify the exact location of the activated station, ensuring swift and accurate response times during emergencies. Whether used in commercial, industrial, or public spaces, this pull station provides an extra level of security and precision, contributing to more effective fire safety measures.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nbg-12lx/descriptions/202501-171-55-pzlcQKQf5m.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.548508', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.555749', 171),
(326, '<p>The Notifier NBG-12LX is a high-performance addressable pull station that is a key component of advanced fire alarm systems. It is equipped with a dual-action activation mechanism, which requires two motions to trigger, ensuring that accidental pulls are minimized. This feature is critical in environments with high foot traffic or in settings where false alarms are a concern, offering peace of mind to building occupants and safety personnel alike.</p>\r\n<p>With its addressable capability, the NBG-12LX offers real-time location data to Notifier\'s intelligent control panels, making it easier to pinpoint the exact station where the alarm was activated. This level of precision is particularly beneficial in large facilities, where the ability to quickly determine the alarm\'s source can significantly reduce response time and improve safety. The Notifier NBG-12LX is ideal for any space where reliable, quick, and accurate fire alarm activation is necessary.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nbg-12lx/descriptions/202501-171-66-FO9DrUjc3I.PNG', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.557204', '2025-01-17 08:29:33.560757', 171),
(327, '<p>The Notifier Addressable SPSRL speaker strobe is engineered for high efficiency and ease of installation, designed to minimize costly ground faults and reduce installation time. The unique plug-in design, combined with a universal mounting plate, allows installers to pre-wire the device, ensuring that wiring continuity is checked before the speakers are plugged in. This reduces the risk of installation errors and offers the flexibility to dress the wires in advance. The speaker strobe&rsquo;s integrated protective plastic cover provides an additional layer of safety, ensuring that exposed speaker components are shielded from potential damage during installation.</p>\r\n<p>This design innovation not only improves the installation process but also extends the lifespan of the device. The Notifier SPSRL provides both visual and audible notifications, making it a reliable choice for facilities that require clear emergency alerts. Its addressable system allows for easy integration with existing fire alarm systems, enhancing the overall safety of any building. Whether installed in commercial or industrial spaces, the SPSRL ensures compliance with fire safety regulations, providing critical emergency alerts to occupants and helping to prevent potential risks.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-spsrl/descriptions/202501-172-33-hPrBU8DVUu.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.736136', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.741827', 172),
(328, '<p>The Notifier Addressable SPSRL is built with durability and performance in mind, designed to ensure long-lasting functionality in demanding environments. Featuring a plug-in design, it significantly reduces the possibility of costly ground faults, which can be caused by faulty wiring connections. The universal mounting plate allows the system to be pre-wired, offering flexibility during the installation process while reducing labor costs. By allowing installers to check wiring continuity before speakers are plugged in, the SPSRL provides an efficient solution for quick and safe installations.</p>\r\n<p>The device&rsquo;s protective plastic cover is another notable feature, preventing potential damage to exposed wires during installation and handling. This added protection ensures the longevity and reliable operation of the Notifier SPSRL in both commercial and industrial buildings. The speaker strobe is designed to meet stringent safety standards, providing clear, high-quality audio and visual signals during emergency situations. With its advanced features, ease of installation, and robust performance, the Notifier SPSRL is an indispensable part of any fire alarm system.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-spsrl/descriptions/202501-172-22-S608TAk4z3.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.743419', '2025-01-20 00:35:09.747420', 172),
(329, '<p>The NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE NFS2-3030 is an advanced fire alarm control panel engineered for expansive facilities. It offers exceptional scalability, supporting over 3,000 intelligent devices on ten SLCs. This extensive device support makes it suitable for large commercial buildings, industrial complexes, and other vast environments requiring a sophisticated fire alarm system. The NFS2-3030\'s intuitive design allows for seamless integration with other systems, enhancing overall safety and operational efficiency.</p>\r\n<p>The control panel features a choice between a large 640-character LCD backlit display or a displayless variant, providing flexibility to meet different user preferences and installation requirements. Its network capabilities, facilitated through NOTI-FIRE-NET and ONYXWorks, enable integration with up to 200 nodes, ensuring a comprehensive and interconnected fire detection network. The NFS2-3030 is engineered for reliability, offering a built-in degraded mode to maintain critical functions even during partial system failures.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nfs-3030/descriptions/202501-173-55-WovlYCXwZR.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:46:55.679935', '2025-01-20 00:49:50.559099', 173),
(330, '<p>Designed with versatility and advanced functionality, the NOTIFIER ADDRESSABLE NFS2-3030 includes several key features that cater to modern fire safety needs. The optional integrated Digital Voice Command (DVC) allows for clear, centralized emergency communication, which is vital in large, busy facilities. Additionally, the EIA-485 annunciators, including custom graphics, provide clear and accessible alerts, enhancing response times during emergencies.</p>\r\n<p>Certified for a range of specialized applications, the NFS2-3030 boasts FM6320 approval for gas detection and is Intertek listed for FSAE functionality, offering smoke and heat level indications for fire service access elevators. It is also seismic certified and marine approved, ensuring it can perform reliably in challenging environments. These certifications make the NFS2-3030 a trusted choice for various industries, from maritime to high-rise urban buildings.</p>', 'products/notifier-addressable-nfs-3030/descriptions/202501-173-66-QY8sbpiSMO.PNG', '2025-01-20 00:46:55.687749', '2025-01-20 00:49:50.561682', 173),
(331, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 721U Edwards Conventional Fire Alarm Control Panel is engineered to provide long-term protection and peace of mind. It is equipped with advanced features like alarm verification and customizable settings to suit specific needs. The panel&rsquo;s user-friendly operation makes it a top choice for both experienced professionals and those new to fire alarm system management. Additionally, it is built to integrate seamlessly with other Edwards fire alarm components, offering a complete safety solution. Featuring an easily accessible interface, the 721U helps ensure that fire detection is always within reach. Its versatile capabilities make it an ideal choice for safeguarding property and lives against fire hazards.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-721u/descriptions/202501-174-66-eo0IqbxUV2.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.934954', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.941382', 174),
(332, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The 721U Edwards Conventional Fire Alarm Control Panel is a reliable and cost-effective solution for managing fire alarm systems in smaller to medium-sized buildings. Designed for ease of use and installation, it offers flexible configuration options to meet diverse safety requirements. With its intuitive interface, the 721U simplifies the process of managing alarm notifications, while ensuring compliance with regulatory standards. This control panel supports up to 10 initiating circuits, providing efficient coverage across the facility. Its robust design ensures optimal performance and reliability, even in challenging environments. Whether used in commercial, residential, or industrial settings, the Edwards 721U is an excellent choice for dependable fire detection and prevention.</span></p>', 'products/edwards-conventional-721u/descriptions/202501-174-77-Xp9f9ATxby.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.942824', '2025-01-20 01:03:32.946593', 174),
(333, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ALBA CV2124AB Audio-Video Module is engineered for superior performance and style. Its ultra-wide-angle 2.3 mm lens offers a 110&deg; vision angle, providing a comprehensive view of entry points for enhanced monitoring and security. Constructed with anodized aluminum, this module ensures long-lasting durability while maintaining a sleek, grey aesthetic. Integrated with an electric door speaker, it facilitates clear, two-way audio communication, making it easier to manage access in both residential and commercial settings.<br><br>Designed with convenience and adaptability in mind, the module supports up to four buttons arranged in two rows, accommodating multiple users or units. The white LED backlighting ensures the buttons remain visible in all lighting conditions, enhancing usability at any time of the day. Its compact dimensions make it a perfect fit for a variety of installation requirements, blending functionality with modern design.</span></p>', 'products/alba-cv2124ab-outdoor/descriptions/202501-175-66-PQAZVMZypX.png', '2025-01-20 01:22:42.541911', '2025-01-20 01:24:33.953188', 175),
(334, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ALBA CV2124AB Audio-Video Module sets a new standard for entry management systems with its robust and versatile design. The focal length of 2.7 mm ensures sharp, detailed images, while the ultra-wide-angle lens captures a broad view for comprehensive coverage. This module&rsquo;s anodized aluminum construction not only guarantees durability but also adds a touch of sophistication with its neutral grey finish.<br><br>The modularity of the system allows for seamless integration with other components, making it scalable for future needs. Its white LED backlighting adds a refined touch and ensures clear visibility of buttons in any lighting condition. With compact dimensions and advanced features, this module delivers the perfect balance of style, reliability, and security.</span></p>', 'products/alba-cv2124ab-outdoor/descriptions/202501-175-33-AV6p4HXM0h.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:22:42.548343', '2025-01-20 01:24:33.956570', 175),
(335, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ALBA CT2138AB Button Module is a premium solution for expanding entry system capabilities. Designed to integrate with the CV2124AB or CA2124AB modules, it provides up to eight buttons in a double-call setup or four in a single-call configuration. This adaptability makes it ideal for properties with multiple users or tenants, delivering a streamlined solution for access control.<br><br>Crafted from high-quality anodized aluminum, the module is built to endure daily use while maintaining its sleek, grey appearance. The white LED backlighting ensures that buttons remain visible in any lighting condition, improving convenience and accessibility for all users. Its compact design allows for seamless integration, enhancing the overall functionality and aesthetic of the entry system.</span></p>', 'products/alba-ct2138ab-outdoor/descriptions/202501-176-55-zprvT3zXv2.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.618330', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.624589', 176),
(336, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ALBA CT2138AB Button Module is a reliable and stylish addition to any modular entry system. Featuring a sturdy anodized aluminum build, this module ensures long-term durability and a polished appearance. Its grey color complements various architectural designs, making it a versatile choice for residential and commercial installations.<br><br>With support for up to eight buttons in a double-call configuration, the module provides scalability for growing access needs. The white LED backlighting enhances visibility and ease of use, ensuring buttons are clearly identifiable even in dim environments. Compact and thoughtfully designed, the CT2138AB adds functionality and refinement to your access system.</span></p>', 'products/alba-ct2138ab-outdoor/descriptions/202501-176-44_enhanced-MA9PaANOTO.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.626855', '2025-01-20 01:40:25.631221', 176),
(337, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000R proximity reader offers a seamless blend of technology and durability, making it an ideal choice for secure access control. Its robust steel construction ensures long-lasting performance, while the sleek grey finish provides a modern aesthetic. Designed to integrate seamlessly with the VIGIK system, this device enables smooth, contactless access for authorized users. Whether mounted on the wall or installed flush, its versatile design allows it to adapt to various architectural needs.<br><br>In addition to its durable construction, the TD2000R is equipped with a CMOS 1/3\" camera featuring a resolution of 440,000 pixels, providing clear visuals for monitoring entry points. Its IP45 rating ensures resistance to dust and water, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications. With a lightweight design weighing only 2.2 kg, the TD2000R is easy to install and maintain, making it a practical solution for secure access management.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000r-outdoor/descriptions/202501-177-77-5QtGjMb95W.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.928515', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.933998', 177),
(338, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000R is designed with user convenience and security in mind. Its LCD alphanumeric display provides clear, real-time information, while the 16-button interface ensures effortless navigation and control. The device&rsquo;s compatibility with the VIGIK system allows for efficient access management, enhancing the overall security of residential and commercial spaces.<br><br>With a sleek profile measuring 30.6 cm in height, 17 cm in width, and 6 cm in depth, the TD2000R blends unobtrusively into any environment. Its fixed 3.7 mm lens and CMOS camera offer reliable performance for visual identification, while its low power consumption of 0.40 A ensures energy efficiency. Whether you&rsquo;re securing a gated community or a corporate office, the TD2000R delivers the advanced technology and durable design you can depend on.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000r-outdoor/descriptions/202501-177-33-S79x42gFTH.PNG', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.935458', '2025-01-20 01:50:56.938455', 177),
(339, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000RA is a state-of-the-art audio intercom panel designed to streamline access control while prioritizing reliability and durability. Its steel construction ensures long-term resilience, even in demanding environments, while the grey finish provides a professional and modern appearance. With support for both wall and flush mounting, the panel offers flexible installation options to suit various architectural needs. The 16-button keypad allows for secure and straightforward operation, while the alphanumeric LCD display enhances user navigation and communication clarity.<br><br>Thanks to its IP45 protection rating, the TD2000RA can withstand exposure to dust and light water sprays, making it suitable for semi-exposed outdoor locations as well as indoor spaces. The device is powered by the efficient Duo Line system, consuming a maximum current of just 0.30 A, which helps reduce operational costs. Compact and lightweight, the SOLVO TD2000RA is an excellent choice for users seeking an effective and durable audio-only access solution.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000ra-outdoor/descriptions/202501-178-44-Ugvmi6Fa9W.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.424171', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.431147', 178),
(340, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SOLVO TD2000RA combines functionality and design in an audio-only access control panel tailored for both residential and commercial settings. Its alphanumeric LCD display provides clear visual feedback, enhancing user experience, while the 16-button keypad ensures secure and convenient entry management. With dimensions optimized for compact spaces and a lightweight 2.2 kg design, the device is easy to install and maintain.<br><br>Built to withstand environmental challenges, the panel features an IP45-rated construction, offering dust and splash resistance. The dual mounting options allow users to choose between wall or flush installation, providing versatility to suit diverse applications. Whether in an apartment complex, office building, or private residence, the SOLVO TD2000RA delivers reliability and performance with a sleek and modern aesthetic.</span></p>', 'products/solvo-td2000ra-outdoor/descriptions/202501-178-22-n9DtQH3JBH.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.432723', '2025-01-20 02:08:05.435928', 178),
(341, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AGORA VD2121CAGL video door entry system is a sleek and practical solution for enhancing the security of your home or business. Crafted with high-quality aluminum and plastic materials, it ensures both durability and resistance to daily wear and tear. The elegant aluminum and light grey color scheme provides a modern aesthetic, blending seamlessly with most exterior designs.<br><br>This unit is equipped with a high-quality color camera that delivers sharp and clear visuals, allowing you to identify visitors with ease. The built-in electric door speaker ensures clear audio communication, and the single-button operation simplifies interactions. Whether you&rsquo;re at home or away, the AGORA VD2121CAGL ensures you stay connected and secure. </span></p>', 'products/agora-vd2121cagl-outdoor/descriptions/202501-179-44-5wxV4ftDU1.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.041706', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.047166', 179),
(342, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed to combine convenience and security, the AGORA VD2121CAGL stands out with its compact dimensions and robust performance. Measuring 20.8 cm in height, 9.9 cm in width, and only 3 cm in depth, this device is perfect for spaces where installation space is limited. It operates efficiently on a 12 Vac power supply, ensuring consistent functionality without high energy demands.<br><br>This system is ideal for managing up to two calls at a time, making it suitable for small apartments or offices with multiple occupants. Additionally, the included cover protects the unit from external damage, ensuring long-lasting reliability. The user-friendly design, combined with its impressive technical features, makes the AGORA VD2121CAGL a valuable addition to any property.</span></p>', 'products/agora-vd2121cagl-outdoor/descriptions/202501-179-33-1HeRmxQrAA.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.049167', '2025-01-20 02:23:47.052463', 179),
(343, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AGORA AGL100TS additional module is engineered for effortless compatibility with VD2121CAGL or AD2121CAGL systems, expanding their capability to handle up to 8 call buttons. This feature makes it perfect for accommodating multi-unit buildings, shared office spaces, or any environment requiring an intuitive and scalable solution. Its complete set of connection cables ensures that users can quickly and efficiently integrate it into their setup without requiring additional components.<br><br>Designed with practicality and durability in mind, the AGL100TS uses high-quality aluminum and plastic materials, providing excellent resistance to wear and tear. Its aluminum and light grey finish delivers a clean, modern appearance that complements various architectural designs. With a compact and lightweight design, this module fits seamlessly into your existing system while maintaining reliability and ease of use.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/agora-agl100ts-outdoor/descriptions/202501-180-66-xBptHspmeU.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.522191', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.527256', 180),
(344, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AGORA AGL100TS combines functionality and style to meet the needs of both small-scale and large-scale operations. Its ability to handle up to 8 call buttons makes it an excellent choice for environments requiring enhanced communication and streamlined access control. Whether for residential complexes, office buildings, or gated communities, this module provides the flexibility and scalability users demand.<br><br>The compact dimensions of 20.8 cm (height), 9.9 cm (width), and 3 cm (depth) ensure that the AGL100TS is space-efficient while retaining a sturdy build. Powered by a 12 Vac supply voltage, it ensures consistent and reliable performance even in demanding conditions. The inclusion of all necessary connection cables underscores its user-friendly design, allowing for easy installation and operation.</span></p>', 'products/agora-agl100ts-outdoor/descriptions/202501-180-77-PfzR9Gt7OX.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.528665', '2025-01-20 02:39:02.531831', 180),
(345, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX VD2120CMAS audio-video module combines elegance with high performance, featuring a fixed 3.6 mm lens color video camera for capturing clear visuals. Its stainless steel construction ensures durability, making it resistant to corrosion and suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications. The absence of call buttons offers a streamlined design that integrates seamlessly into existing systems without cluttering the interface.<br><br>Measuring 11.5 cm by 11.5 cm, this compact module is easy to install on various surfaces, whether in residential complexes or commercial buildings. Its metal grey finish gives it a polished, professional appearance, complementing modern architectural aesthetics. The MATRIX VD2120CMAS is designed for users who value reliable technology in a minimalist form.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-vd2120cmas-outdoor/descriptions/202501-181-55-KoZzmzYKbA.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.727249', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.733088', 181),
(346, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed to meet modern communication and security needs, the MATRIX VD2120CMAS audio-video module delivers exceptional performance. Its 3.6 mm lens color video camera captures detailed visuals, ensuring enhanced monitoring and security. Crafted from high-quality stainless steel, the module is built to withstand harsh environments, offering reliable operation over time.<br><br>The compact design, paired with the elegant metal grey color, ensures this module fits seamlessly into various environments. Its absence of call buttons makes it ideal for systems where video functionality is the primary requirement. Whether for a corporate office, residential building, or public facility, the MATRIX VD2120CMAS provides an effective and stylish solution.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-vd2120cmas-outdoor/descriptions/202501-181-66-naJEJz2NM6.PNG', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.734702', '2025-01-20 02:47:06.738536', 181),
(347, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX MAS24S Additional Call Module is designed for installations requiring high-performance intercom solutions. Its stainless steel build ensures long-lasting durability, making it an excellent choice for areas with high foot traffic or frequent use. The sleek metal grey finish adds a contemporary touch, complementing modern architectural designs. With dimensions of 11.5 cm x 11.5 cm, the module is compact and suitable for tight spaces or modular setups.<br><br>Equipped with four call buttons, the MAS24S provides efficient communication, perfect for managing multiple users or departments in professional or residential spaces. The integration of the encoder keys circuit ensures seamless operation, enabling precise and reliable communication signals. This module is an ideal addition to the CD213&hellip;MAS series, offering improved usability and a polished aesthetic to any intercom system.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-mas24s-outdoor/descriptions/202501-182-33-lnNPoZlcYq.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.147660', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.153859', 182),
(348, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Upgrade your intercom system with the MATRIX MAS24S Additional Call Module. Built to integrate seamlessly with the CD213&hellip;MAS series, it offers a robust and elegant communication solution. The four-call-button design allows quick access for users, making it perfect for large buildings or facilities requiring organized communication channels.<br><br>The stainless steel material ensures the module resists environmental wear, including scratches and impacts, while the metal grey finish enhances its visual appeal. Compact in size, the MAS24S is easy to install and blends effortlessly into any existing system. With advanced encoder keys circuit integration, it provides reliable and efficient communication, ensuring users experience a smooth, uninterrupted performance.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-mas24s-outdoor/descriptions/202501-182-22-UJZ7Wr3Abg.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.155664', '2025-01-20 03:09:50.158967', 182),
(349, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE4252 Monitor with Basic Videointercom Functions is an intuitive and practical solution for everyday communication and security needs. Its 7-inch LCD TFT display provides sharp, vibrant visuals, making it easy to monitor visitors and communicate effectively. This device features hands-free operation, enhancing convenience for busy users who need a quick, effortless way to manage their home or office communication systems.<br><br>With its auto switch-on activation, the SE4252 is always ready when you need it. It comes equipped with a dedicated door-opening button, allowing instant access control at your fingertips. The monitor\'s white finish and compact size (15.7 cm height, 19.4 cm width, and 2.5 cm depth) make it a stylish and unobtrusive addition to any space, blending functionality with elegance.</span></p>', 'products/se4252-indoor/descriptions/202501-183-55-aDFgd0UoqJ.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.430651', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.436339', 183),
(350, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE4252 Advanced Videointercom Monitor is designed to cater to more sophisticated demands, offering features like video memory, block notes, and memo capabilities. These advanced tools make it easy to record, organize, and recall important information directly on the device. This monitor supports electrical load control and the management of actuators, enabling seamless remote activation of other apparatus, making it a smart choice for connected homes.<br><br>Expandable through memory cards, the SE4252 allows users to import and export data, ensuring adaptability as your needs grow. Whether you\'re enhancing home security or streamlining office communications, this device provides an intuitive and reliable solution. Its hands-free functionality and elegant white finish ensure a perfect blend of modern design and practical usability.</span></p>', 'products/se4252-indoor/descriptions/202501-183-22-bLdNgp4pQf.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.437808', '2025-01-20 03:19:52.441146', 183),
(351, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE400 Handset is a high-performance accessory designed to connect with the Sette monitor system, providing users with an optimal solution for private conversations. With its intuitive interface and seamless integration, users can easily switch from the monitor&rsquo;s speakers to the handset for a more secure and personalized audio experience. The ergonomic design of the handset ensures comfort during extended use, making it ideal for long business calls or personal discussions.<br><br>Equipped with advanced sound technology, the SE400 delivers crisp and clear audio quality, ensuring every word is heard with precision. The robust connection with the Sette monitor ensures that the audio quality remains consistent and reliable throughout the conversation. Whether you are in an office setting or at home, this accessory guarantees privacy, allowing you to engage in conversations without distractions from external noise.</span></p>', 'products/se400-indoor/descriptions/202501-184-11-YG5DzsGlOj.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.396053', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.401785', 184),
(352, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SE400 Handset accessory is designed to seamlessly integrate with the Sette monitor, offering a dedicated tool for private and confidential conversations. Whether you\'re dealing with sensitive business discussions or personal calls, the handset provides a focused listening experience, blocking out surrounding noise and ensuring clear communication. Its compact design allows for easy placement alongside the monitor, while the user-friendly controls provide hassle-free operation.<br><br>This accessory is built with durability in mind, ensuring that it stands up to regular use in professional settings. Its design prioritizes comfort and efficiency, offering a natural fit for your hand, so users can engage in extended conversations without strain. The SE400 Handset is the ideal choice for anyone looking to enhance their communication setup with the Sette system for a secure and private audio experience.</span></p>', 'products/se400-indoor/descriptions/202501-184-22-DuNcjWfeB7.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.403499', '2025-01-20 03:24:32.407110', 184),
(353, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262W White Video Intercom offers a sleek and modern design that enhances both security and aesthetics. Its 3.5&rdquo; LCD display ensures crisp, clear video for easy identification of visitors. This model is equipped with soft touch controls, making it easy to navigate the interface with a simple tap. The intercom also features an OSD configuration, allowing users to adjust settings with ease. Whether for residential or business use, the ZH1262W ensures efficient communication and increased security.<br><br>With its compact design, the ZHERO ZH1262W can be installed seamlessly into any environment, adding functionality without taking up unnecessary space. The system is easy to set up, with clear instructions for installation. The intercom provides a user-friendly experience, making it accessible even for those who are not tech-savvy. It is a versatile solution for anyone looking for a high-quality, reliable video intercom system.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262w-indoor/descriptions/202501-185-44-MbcNbxHMbX.PNG', '2025-01-20 03:32:50.872820', '2025-01-20 03:35:33.086474', 185),
(354, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262W Video Intercom is designed to meet the demands of modern security needs, offering both style and function. Its white color and 3.5\" LCD screen deliver a contemporary look while providing excellent video quality. The soft touch control system is intuitive and responsive, making it easy to adjust settings with minimal effort. The OSD configuration feature provides greater flexibility, allowing users to customize the system to their preferences. This intercom system is ideal for enhancing security in both home and office settings.<br><br>Offering simplicity in design and function, the ZH1262W makes communication with visitors or personnel easier than ever. Its easy-to-navigate menu ensures quick access to settings, and its clear video output ensures users can identify visitors with clarity. Whether you\'re looking for an intercom to improve home security or streamline communication in your office, the ZHERO ZH1262W delivers exceptional value and quality.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262w-indoor/descriptions/202501-185-33-ahW25gzLuC.png', '2025-01-20 03:32:50.881005', '2025-01-20 03:35:33.091452', 185);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(355, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ZHERO ZH1262B Black Colour Video Intercom is the perfect solution for individuals or businesses seeking reliable security and communication features. The system boasts a high-quality 3.5\" LCD screen that delivers clear video footage, ensuring you can identify visitors with ease. It is designed with a soft touch control panel for easy operation, making it simple for anyone to use, regardless of their technical expertise. This intercom system combines sophisticated technology with a sleek black design, blending seamlessly into any modern setting.<br><br>The device also offers OSD configuration, allowing users to customize the system settings to their specific preferences. Whether you need to adjust the volume, brightness, or other functions, the intuitive interface makes these changes quick and straightforward. Perfect for both residential and commercial applications, the ZHERO ZH1262B ensures both security and convenience, giving you peace of mind when interacting with visitors.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262b-indoor/descriptions/202501-186-77-fcCjPHglDz.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.073237', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.078769', 186),
(356, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1262B video intercom is equipped with a 3.5\" LCD screen that guarantees a clear and detailed image of your visitors. The device&rsquo;s black color and compact design allow it to fit into any environment, making it an ideal choice for those looking for a stylish and functional communication system. Soft touch controls make it easy to operate, while the OSD configuration feature allows for seamless system adjustments, ensuring the device meets all your personal or business needs.<br><br>This video intercom is built to deliver superior performance with a combination of high-definition video and reliable audio communication. Whether you are installing it in a home or an office, its user-friendly interface and advanced features ensure that both security and convenience are prioritized. The ZHERO ZH1262B stands out as a sleek, modern solution for anyone in need of an efficient video intercom system.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1262b-indoor/descriptions/202501-186-33-6AOAYh4tmK.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.080178', '2025-01-20 05:07:43.083190', 186),
(357, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZHERO ZH1252W (ZHEROS) White Color Video Intercom is an ideal solution for users who want a simple yet reliable video communication system. Equipped with a 4-inch screen, this intercom provides a clear and vibrant view of your visitors, allowing you to easily identify who is at the door. The 4-button interface is intuitive, making it easy to use for people of all ages. Whether you\'re installing it in a home, office, or apartment, the design fits effortlessly into any room\'s aesthetic with its sleek white finish.<br><br>What makes this intercom even more user-friendly is its DIP switch programming, which allows for simple customization of settings. You can easily adjust and personalize the system to fit your specific needs. This ease of setup and user-friendly functionality makes the ZHERO ZH1252W a practical addition to any space, combining functionality with modern design.</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1252w-zheros-indoor/descriptions/202501-187-44-XMJSLoYv5z.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.308610', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.314986', 187),
(358, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">With a compact 4-inch screen and white color design, the ZHERO ZH1252W is a standout in both style and performance. Its 4-button interface makes it incredibly easy to control, with each button serving a specific function for smooth operation. The intercom\'s video display ensures that users get a high-quality view of the outside, contributing to increased security and peace of mind. Whether you\'re answering a visitor or simply monitoring the entrance, the intercom\'s clarity and performance will not disappoint.<br><br>The DIP switch programming feature adds another layer of customization to this intercom. It allows you to personalize the settings, such as volume, contrast, and more, according to your preferences. This functionality ensures that the ZHERO ZH1252W is adaptable to various user needs, making it a versatile option for different environments</span></p>', 'products/zhero-zh1252w-zheros-indoor/descriptions/202501-187-55-chaT7tVtqK.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.316572', '2025-01-20 05:38:28.320653', 187),
(359, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX362 Intercom is an advanced communication device designed to enhance both security and convenience in homes or businesses. It features seven intuitive buttons, one of which controls door opening, ensuring easy access for visitors. The intercom&rsquo;s plastic body in white adds a clean and contemporary look to any installation, blending seamlessly with its surroundings. With programmable buttons, users can assign specific functions to six of the keys, making it a highly versatile solution for different needs. Its dimensions (83 x 218 x 62 mm) make it compact and easy to install even in limited spaces.<br><br>This intercom is built with a focus on ease of use and durability. The high-quality plastic construction ensures that the device withstands everyday wear and tear, while its compact size allows it to fit discreetly in any setting. Whether it&rsquo;s installed in an office, an apartment building, or a residential complex, the EX362 offers seamless integration with existing security systems. Its practical design and customizability make it an excellent choice for those looking to streamline their communication and access control systems.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex362-indoor/descriptions/202501-188-33-T6ZJCzyPsl.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.891838', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.897199', 188),
(360, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed to cater to both personal and professional communication needs, the EXHITO EX362 Intercom is a user-friendly device that ensures reliable communication. The seven buttons on the intercom provide a range of functions, with one dedicated to door opening, allowing users to easily manage access to their premises. The six programmable keys offer further customization, allowing users to assign specific actions to each button. This feature enhances the intercom&rsquo;s versatility, making it a highly effective tool for diverse applications, from security systems to internal communication networks.<br><br>Compact yet efficient, the EX362 is designed to save space without compromising on functionality. Its white plastic body ensures that the intercom is both lightweight and durable. The intercom is ideal for users looking for a straightforward solution to communication, security, and door control. The EX362&rsquo;s design caters to modern needs while remaining simple enough to operate, providing ease of use for anyone who requires quick and direct access to different functions within their environment.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex362-indoor/descriptions/202501-188-44-XPPi3jhvcS.PNG', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.898784', '2025-01-20 05:54:23.902530', 188),
(361, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX352 Intercom is a practical communication solution designed to provide clear and efficient interaction with visitors. With a compact design measuring 21.8 cm in height, 6.5 cm in width, and 6.2 cm in depth, this intercom easily fits into any environment without taking up too much space. Made of durable plastic material, its sleek white finish offers a contemporary touch to your entryway, hallway, or office. This intercom system features three buttons, one of which functions as a door opening button, providing an easy way to grant access without leaving your space.<br><br>Two of the three buttons are programmable, allowing you to customize the intercom for different uses, such as connecting to specific rooms or functions in your building. The simplicity of the EX352 Intercom makes it ideal for anyone seeking efficient communication and control over their premises with minimal setup. It offers an accessible solution to ensure that your security or communication needs are met with ease and reliability.</span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex352-indoor/descriptions/202501-189-44-BRHxJNjHmS.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.574068', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.579168', 189),
(362, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The EXHITO EX352 Intercom is designed to make your daily communication and security tasks effortless. This intercom combines a modern aesthetic with practical functionality, featuring a white plastic casing that is both durable and stylish. The three-button layout includes a dedicated door-opening button, ensuring that you can easily interact with visitors and grant access with just one press. Additionally, the two programmable buttons allow you to assign personalized functions that suit your specific needs.<br><br>At just 21.8 cm in height, 6.5 cm in width, and 6.2 cm in depth, the EX352 Intercom is compact enough to fit into smaller spaces, making it an ideal choice for homes, offices, or shared spaces. The simple, intuitive design ensures that you can operate it with ease, while the sturdy build ensures long-term use. Perfect for both residential and commercial settings, the EX352 provides a reliable and secure way to manage communication and control access with minimal effort.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/exhito-ex352-indoor/descriptions/202501-189-33-0da54DUMhq.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.580627', '2025-01-20 06:02:37.584553', 189),
(363, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone AX Series is a versatile intercom and communication system designed to enhance security and efficiency in a wide range of applications. With the ability to connect up to 8 masters and 120 remote stations, the system ensures seamless communication through both PTT (push-to-talk) or VOX (voice-activated) modes. Its advanced features include selective master-to-master calling, priority and standard call levels, and integration with electronic access control and CCTV systems. Offering full privacy during communication and the option for call queuing, the AX Series provides a secure and organized communication environment. Additionally, it supports remote control features, including door release and call transfer to telephones, making it a highly adaptable solution for modern security needs.<br><br>The AX Series is built for flexibility and scalability, ideal for large buildings, campuses, or complexes that require both reliability and customization. It supports composite video output, scan monitoring of remote stations, and a PC interface for programming and event logging. The system can be mounted in a rack or on the wall, and integrates seamlessly with other Aiphone systems such as the IE Series door stations. With optional accessories like headsets, footswitches, and remote PC control, the AX Series is engineered to meet the needs of varied environments while ensuring ease of use and setup. Whether for secure access control, communication privacy, or general convenience, the Aiphone AX Series is a reliable, future-proof solution for sophisticated security systems.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ax-series/descriptions/202501-190-44-K3ap0qpore.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.858329', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.864872', 190),
(364, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone AX Series offers a wide range of features tailored to security and communication needs. It supports composite video output from both the CEU and master stations, delivering high-quality video integration. The system includes standard or priority call levels from door stations, allowing you to prioritize communication based on urgency. With the ability to integrate with both CCTV systems and electronic access control, the AX Series streamlines operations for both security personnel and everyday users.<br><br>Designed with scalability in mind, the AX Series is ideal for environments that require high flexibility, including offices, campuses, or industrial facilities. Its PC interface makes programming and event logging easier, while remote control features, such as door release and call transfer to telephones, improve user convenience. Additionally, the system offers optional accessories like headsets and footswitches to further enhance usability.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ax-series/descriptions/202501-190-77-kXSUCxAAYW.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.866614', '2025-01-20 06:43:56.869759', 190),
(365, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE GT Series is an advanced video intercom system designed for clear communication and reliable security. Featuring a high-resolution 3.5&Prime; LCD color monitor, the system allows users to visually confirm visitors before engaging in conversation. The system&rsquo;s hands-free audio communication allows for easy interaction without the need for a physical handset. However, for added privacy, an optional handset (GT-HS) is available, providing flexibility in communication preferences. Whether in a residential or commercial setting, this system offers an elegant and functional solution for modern communication needs.<br><br>With user-friendly features, the AIPHONE GT Series incorporates door release functionality, making it easy to grant access to visitors with a simple press of a button. The PTZ control feature allows for precise video adjustments, while the brightness control ensures the image remains clear in varying light conditions. The system also provides adjustable call tone and communication volume controls to customize sound levels based on the user\'s preference. Its sleek white finish adds a contemporary touch, making it an attractive and practical addition to any space</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-gt-series/descriptions/202501-191-33-uCcoRelFNQ.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.264856', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.270962', 191),
(366, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE GT Series offers a comprehensive intercom system with a focus on security, convenience, and communication quality. The 3.5&Prime; LCD color monitor provides a sharp, detailed display of visitors, while the hands-free audio communication feature ensures ease of use. For privacy during communication, users can opt to add the GT-HS handset, which is sold separately. This makes the GT Series versatile, allowing users to switch between hands-free communication and a more private, traditional setup. Ideal for both residential and business environments, it provides peace of mind with its high-quality video and audio features.<br><br>In addition to its top-tier communication capabilities, the system comes equipped with several customizable controls. The PTZ functionality allows users to adjust the camera view, ensuring full coverage of the entrance area. The brightness control ensures clear images regardless of lighting conditions, while the door release button adds convenience for granting access remotely. With adjustable call tone and communication volume controls, the AIPHONE GT Series allows for a fully personalized experience, catering to different user needs and environments.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-gt-series/descriptions/202501-191-55-CYGbSfvdlP.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.272846', '2025-01-20 06:50:02.276276', 191),
(367, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JM Series is an innovative video intercom system that offers enhanced communication and security features. With a 7-inch touchscreen panel, it provides a user-friendly interface to manage communications effectively. The system supports both hands-free and handset modes, allowing users to choose the mode that best fits their needs. The camera on the door station can be adjusted for optimal viewing, and its high resolution ensures clear video quality. The camera also features a wide 170&deg; angle lens and Digital PanTilt and Zoom functionality, eliminating any blind spots for superior visibility.<br><br>The JM Series also provides practical features like a picture memory function that records up to 20 calls on internal memory, and up to 1,000 calls on an SD/SDHC card for expanded storage. This system allows you to monitor entries discreetly, even in low light conditions, ensuring privacy. With the ability to control additional devices such as lights or gates, the system enhances its role as a comprehensive security solution. It supports up to four door stations and can be connected to as many as eight inside locations, making it perfect for both small and large applications.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jm-series/descriptions/202501-192-44-T0NNn6l18l.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.537111', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.542686', 192),
(368, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JM Series intercom system is designed with flexibility and convenience in mind. Featuring a high-resolution TFT LCD touchscreen, the system provides a crystal-clear visual experience, making it easy to see who is at the door. The camera position is customizable, and users can adjust the zoom to capture the perfect image of visitors or potential threats. It&rsquo;s equipped with a digital PanTilt and Zoom camera with a 170&deg; wide-angle lens, offering complete coverage without any blind spots, even in low lighting conditions.<br><br>With the added capability to record and store up to 1,000 calls on an SD/SDHC card (sold separately), the JM Series ensures that important interactions are captured for later review. The system is compatible with up to four door stations and can connect to as many as eight inside locations. Whether for home or office use, the AIPHONE JM Series is a robust, easy-to-install solution for monitoring and managing entries securely and efficiently.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jm-series/descriptions/202501-192-55-MZOov7GTcW.PNG', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.544893', '2025-01-20 06:55:12.548989', 192),
(369, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JO Series video intercom system combines functionality with sleek, modern design. The system is equipped with a large 7&rdquo; screen and touch buttons that allow for easy control, making it intuitive to use. Its slim design ensures that it fits seamlessly into any interior, providing an elegant touch while offering excellent performance. The 2-conductor wiring simplifies the installation process, allowing for a quick and hassle-free setup.<br><br>Designed to accommodate one door station and up to two inside stations, the JO Series is perfect for small-scale residential or office environments. The high-quality video feature enhances security by providing clear, detailed visuals of visitors. With its ready-to-install box set, users get all the essential components, including a door station, inside station, and power supply, making it an efficient choice for those seeking reliable security.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jo-series/descriptions/202501-193-44-XXbcm9XzdM.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.469276', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.475727', 193),
(370, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE JO Series is a top-tier intercom system that provides effective security solutions for both residential and commercial settings. With a large, high-resolution 7&rdquo; video screen, users can easily identify visitors before allowing access. The touch-sensitive buttons offer intuitive control over the system, while the slim depth of the video master ensures it remains unobtrusive and stylish. The elegant design is further enhanced by a sleek, modern look that complements any space.<br><br>Installation is made easier with the inclusion of 2-conductor wiring and a ready-to-install box set. The system includes one door station, one inside station, and a power supply, making it a complete package for those who need a user-friendly intercom solution. The JO Series is an ideal choice for homeowners or business owners looking to improve security while maintaining a sophisticated aesthetic.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-jo-series/descriptions/202501-193-77-i7GYBz7es2.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.477967', '2025-01-20 07:05:51.481932', 193),
(371, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The AIPHONE NA-AN Series intercom system offers advanced features to support smooth communication while prioritizing privacy. Equipped with a privacy feature, it blocks any unwanted monitoring from the master station, ensuring that personal or confidential conversations are kept private. The system uses a push button to call the master station, with a latching tone and light at the master station remaining active until the call is answered. This ensures that the caller&rsquo;s request is always acknowledged and acted upon promptly.<br><br>In addition to the privacy feature, the AIPHONE NA-AN Series includes a call-in LED indicator on the substation, which stays illuminated until the master answers the call. The hands-free communication feature is activated when the master answers, making the system easy to use and practical for busy environments. Available in both desk and wall-mount options, the NA-AN Series is versatile, with installation flexibility to suit various spaces.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-na-an-series/descriptions/202501-194-66-XH8ZNotFmA.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.911276', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.917954', 194),
(372, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The NA-AN Series is designed with user-friendly features for seamless operation and efficient communication. A pre-tone alerts the substation when the master station is calling, ensuring users are aware of the incoming communication. The system can be easily mounted on a desk or wall, offering mounting options that suit different room layouts. Additionally, the unit mounts to a single gang box or ring, providing further flexibility for installation. This combination of features ensures that the AIPHONE NA-AN Series offers both ease of use and adaptable installation.<br><br>The AIPHONE NA-AN Series is ideal for both home and business environments, providing reliable communication with the convenience of hands-free operation. The intuitive LED indicators ensure that users are aware of the system&rsquo;s status at all times, while the privacy features keep all conversations secure. Its sleek design and easy installation make it a perfect solution for anyone seeking an effective and private intercom system.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-na-an-series/descriptions/202501-194-55-z2fyHNMK8j.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.919657', '2025-01-20 07:36:53.922890', 194),
(373, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone NE-JA Series Weather-Resistant Stainless Steel Flush-Mount Audio Door Sub Station is built for versatility and durability, making it an ideal solution for outdoor communication in residential, commercial, or industrial applications. Featuring a sleek stainless-steel faceplate and slim profile, this sub station is designed to mount easily onto a 2-gang box or ring, allowing for smooth integration into existing systems. With its weather-resistant housing, the NE-JA sub station can withstand various outdoor conditions, ensuring long-lasting reliability.<br><br>Equipped with a push-button interface, the sub station enables users to call the master station with a simple press of a button. When the master station is ringing, the integrated LED stays lit, providing a visual indication of an incoming call. Hands-free communication is available once the master station answers, allowing for clear and easy conversation without the need to hold a receiver.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ne-ja-series/descriptions/202501-195-44-EWvzjzad9n.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.906801', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.912404', 195),
(374, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Aiphone NE-JA Series Sub Station offers added functionality with its optional external output contact closure feature, which can be used to activate a remote device when the call is placed and until it is answered. This capability, facilitated by the RY-PA relay (available separately), is ideal for controlling devices such as gates, door locks, or other remote systems. This makes the NE-JA Sub Station an excellent choice for environments that require not only communication but also access control or security integration.<br><br>The system is designed to offer a user-friendly experience while ensuring high-quality, hands-free audio communication. The sub station is engineered for seamless integration with the NEM system, providing reliability and efficiency for both commercial and residential installations. Its sleek design, combined with practical features like the contact closure capability and clear communication functions, makes the Aiphone NE-JA Series Sub Station a standout choice for modern security and communication systems.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-ne-ja-series/descriptions/202501-195-22-ygWdYfQNVP.PNG', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.914891', '2025-01-20 07:52:11.918182', 195),
(375, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR PD6500i is engineered to meet the rigorous demands of large-scale, high-security environments. Featuring cutting-edge pinpoint technology, this detector provides exceptional accuracy, enabling precise identification of potential threats. With 33 detection zones, including 11 vertical and three lateral zones, it allows security professionals to monitor the exact location of any detected item. The PD6500i excels in high-traffic areas such as international airports, stadiums, and government buildings, providing seamless security without disrupting the flow of people.<br><br>This walk-through detector also includes advanced alarm features, with both visual and audible alerts for immediate detection response. The intuitive LED zone indicator lights and easy-to-use eight-button keypad enhance the user experience, making it easy to operate even in complex security environments. Whether used for general public safety or safeguarding sensitive areas, the PD6500i&rsquo;s powerful technology ensures unmatched performance and reliability, offering peace of mind to security personnel and the public alike.</span></p>', 'products/pd6500i/descriptions/202501-196-77-wDOkQmMndz.png', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.577104', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.587251', 196),
(376, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Ideal for large venues and high-traffic locations, the GARRETT METAL DETECTOR PD6500i sets the standard for security detection technology. Designed with precision, this walk-through detector integrates 33 detection zones that cover both lateral and vertical positions for superior coverage and accuracy. Whether you\'re securing a sporting event or managing access control at a government building, the PD6500i adapts to various security needs while maintaining high throughput. Its sophisticated discrimination features make it capable of distinguishing between different types of threats, significantly reducing false alarms and enhancing overall security efficiency.<br><br>Beyond its superior detection capabilities, the PD6500i is built for durability and ease of maintenance. Its robust construction, weatherproofing, and compliance with industry standards like TSA and ECAC ensure long-term reliability in any environment. With the option for remote control management and multi-unit synchronization, security personnel can manage large networks of detectors seamlessly, making it an ideal choice for large organizations or event coordinators seeking top-tier security solutions.</span></p>', 'products/pd6500i/descriptions/202501-196-44-O2gCwx5P7Z.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.588796', '2025-01-20 08:12:58.593432', 196),
(377, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The GARRETT METAL DETECTOR Multi Zone is engineered for precision and efficiency, equipped with 20 independent detection zones that offer accurate localization of metal objects. This detector&rsquo;s advanced design allows security professionals to easily pinpoint the location of threats without interrupting the flow of individuals. Its Auto-Scan function automatically selects the optimal operating frequency, eliminating interference from environmental noise. The system\'s intuitive menu design and slider bar allow operators to quickly adjust detector settings, ensuring that the device is configured to suit any security environment.<br><br>This walkthrough detector also features pre-set programs tailored for specific security applications, including special events, mass transit, and loss prevention. The detector&rsquo;s visual and audible alarms provide clear alerts to security personnel when a potential threat is detected. With a user-friendly interface, operators can manage and adjust the system effortlessly, making it a powerful yet accessible tool for maintaining safety at large-scale venues.</span></p>', 'products/multi-zone/descriptions/202501-197-77-TmUFpX1GoV.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.879864', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.886277', 197),
(378, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed with versatility and ease of use in mind, the GARRETT METAL DETECTOR Multi Zone offers comprehensive security features for a wide range of high-traffic environments. Featuring 20 detection zones, this system accurately identifies threats by locating metal objects across multiple zones simultaneously. With its customizable LED displays and status lights, the detector ensures clear communication with security teams and can be adjusted to fit various operational needs. The detector\'s robust construction is complemented by its weatherproof design, meeting IP 55 standards for moisture and foreign matter protection, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use.<br><br>Further enhancing security management, the Multi Zone detector offers options for remote control and integration into a larger network of devices. Whether managing a single unit or a group of detectors, security personnel can synchronize multiple units, perform statistical analysis, and monitor throughput effectively. Its ability to adapt to changing environments and its ease of operation make it an ideal choice for venues where safety and efficiency are top priorities.</span></p>', 'products/multi-zone/descriptions/202501-197-55-EXK33Hu1bV.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.888634', '2025-01-20 08:21:21.893067', 197),
(379, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG is a premium voice alarm controller that ensures the safety of occupants in large buildings and industrial spaces. With its 8-zone paging station, this system offers efficient communication during emergency situations, allowing for precise, targeted announcements. Integrated with fire alarm panels, the system activates automatically in the event of an emergency, enabling immediate voice instructions and alarms. The EVACLITE PKG also features a built-in loudspeaker to ensure that alerts are clearly heard throughout the premises.<br><br>Designed for simplicity and ease of use, the system offers remote paging microphone functionality with zone selection capabilities, allowing operators to manage communications with flexibility. With a wide frequency response of 20Hz to 20KHz, the EVACLITE PKG ensures crisp and clear voice quality, making it ideal for environments where clear, timely communication is crucial. Whether used in a large office building, a hospital, or a factory, the HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG is a dependable and powerful solution for emergency voice communication.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-evaclite-pkg/descriptions/202501-198-11-1xixDVjTyK.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:41:16.402929', '2025-01-22 02:25:44.719563', 198),
(380, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG offers a sophisticated solution for emergency voice alarms with its advanced features and high-performance capabilities. This system is designed to integrate seamlessly with existing fire alarm panels and includes an 8-zone paging station, making it highly adaptable for different settings. The built-in loudspeaker ensures that voice alerts are heard clearly across large spaces, while the system&rsquo;s low total harmonic distortion ensures high-quality sound output without interference. The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG operates within a wide frequency range, supporting FM and AM signals, allowing for versatile communication options in various environments.<br><br>Its remote paging microphone supports zone selection, making it an excellent choice for areas requiring flexible communication during emergencies. With a power output capability of 5A and a maximum total power of 1000W, the system can effectively cover large areas. The HONEYWELL EVACLITE PKG&rsquo;s durable design, along with its ability to communicate over distances of up to 300 meters, ensures reliability during critical situations, making it an ideal solution for facilities looking to upgrade their emergency notification systems.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-evaclite-pkg/descriptions/202501-198-22-Acr22VE3gS.PNG', '2025-01-20 08:41:16.410742', '2025-01-22 02:25:44.721813', 198),
(381, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The HONEYWELL X-NPMS Configurable Network Paging Station offers an intuitive and easy-to-use solution for public address systems. Featuring a 7-inch TFT LCD touchscreen, the system provides users with a simple interface for controlling paging and alarm functions. The station&rsquo;s high-quality sound performance is ensured with a frequency response range from 50Hz to 15kHz, delivering clear and crisp audio for announcements. The system operates with a low total harmonic distortion (THD) of less than 0.05%, making it perfect for environments where accurate and distortion-free audio is crucial.<br><br>The X-NPMS is built to work seamlessly within networked environments, offering line input and output compatibility for smooth integration into existing infrastructures. It is powered by a DC 24V supply and provides a monitoring loudspeaker of 2W for local sound verification. The system&rsquo;s wide operating temperature range from -10&deg;C to 55&deg;C ensures it performs reliably in various environments, whether in indoor or outdoor settings. The HONEYWELL X-NPMS is designed to deliver both quality and durability for organizations seeking an efficient network-based paging solution.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npms-configurable-network-paging-station/descriptions/202501-199-44_opMvyg6.PNG', '2025-01-22 00:44:02.193215', '2025-01-22 02:23:50.695809', 199),
(382, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">With the HONEYWELL X-NPMS Configurable Network Paging Station, businesses and organizations gain access to a versatile, high-performance paging system. This unit provides a user-friendly 7-inch TFT LCD touchscreen with an intuitive interface, allowing quick adjustments and control of paging functions. With a frequency response range of 50Hz to 15kHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 85dB, the X-NPMS ensures that announcements are crystal clear, even in noisy environments. The station operates on a DC 24V power supply, ensuring stable, long-term use with low energy consumption.<br><br>Designed to integrate smoothly into larger network systems, the X-NPMS supports both line input and output, making it adaptable to various sound and communication configurations. A 2W monitoring loudspeaker is built into the unit, providing immediate feedback for users. Additionally, the system is engineered for durability, with an operating temperature range of -10&deg;C to 55&deg;C, ensuring it remains reliable under various conditions. Whether for voice alarms or public address functions, the HONEYWELL X-NPMS is a robust solution for any facility\'s communication needs.With the HONEYWELL X-NPMS Configurable Network Paging Station, businesses and organizations gain access to a versatile, high-performance paging system. This unit provides a user-friendly 7-inch TFT LCD touchscreen with an intuitive interface, allowing quick adjustments and control of paging functions. With a frequency response range of 50Hz to 15kHz and a signal-to-noise ratio greater than 85dB, the X-NPMS ensures that announcements are crystal clear, even in noisy environments. The station operates on a DC 24V power supply, ensuring stable, long-term use with low energy consumption.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npms-configurable-network-paging-station/descriptions/202501-199-55_IJdoysn.PNG', '2025-01-22 00:44:02.200847', '2025-01-22 02:23:50.699574', 199),
(383, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell X-NPMI Configurable Network Paging Console is a key module in the X-618 Digital Public Address and Voice Alarm System, designed to deliver seamless and efficient communication in various settings. It provides users with essential features such as full duplex communication, paging, and monitoring functions, all of which can be configured to suit specific operational requirements. Its intuitive touchscreen interface allows users to easily manage and control paging settings, making it ideal for high-traffic areas like airports, hospitals, schools, and factories.<br><br>This versatile console supports a wide array of audio configurations, with an input impedance of 10 K&Omega; and frequency response ranging from 60 Hz to 16 kHz. The system&rsquo;s microphone input is -51 dB, and the audio port operates at 0 dB, ensuring clarity in every communication. Additionally, the unit features a built-in monitoring loudspeaker with a sound output range of 65 dB to 115 dB, ensuring that messages are heard loud and clear throughout the environment. Compact in design, the Honeywell X-NPMI is engineered to perform reliably even under challenging conditions.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npmi-configurable-network-paging-console/descriptions/202501-200-55_TZfHYOM.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:10:12.659443', '2025-01-22 02:23:36.531542', 200),
(384, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed for flexibility and ease of use, the Honeywell X-NPMI Configurable Network Paging Console supports a range of customizable functions to meet the unique needs of any organization. Its full duplex communication ensures two-way conversations can be conducted clearly, and its extensive monitoring capabilities allow users to check system status and adjust settings as needed. With a 12V DC power supply and operating temperatures ranging from -40&deg;C to +70&deg;C, the device can function in diverse environmental conditions, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications.<br><br>The console&rsquo;s audio capabilities include a sampling rate of 44.1 kHz and 16-bit resolution, which ensures high-quality sound output across all types of public address and voice alarm functions. It also features an easy-to-navigate interface and is compatible with a variety of audio devices, offering significant flexibility for different communication needs. Whether used in large-scale public announcements or critical voice alarm systems, the Honeywell X-NPMI provides high reliability and ease of operation.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-x-npmi-configurable-network-paging-console/descriptions/202501-200-66_Dw1NttJ.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:10:12.667045', '2025-01-22 02:23:36.533718', 200),
(385, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker is an ideal solution for environments requiring clear, loud sound projection without compromising on aesthetics. Designed for outdoor use, this 15W horn loudspeaker offers excellent sound quality, with a maximum power output of 25W. The speaker operates within a frequency range of 350 Hz to 8 kHz, ensuring full-range audio coverage that is suitable for announcements, alarms, or background music. Its white low-profile cover makes it unobtrusive, blending easily with various architectural styles and outdoor settings.<br><br>With a sound pressure level of 115 dB at 15W, the L-PHP15A provides ample volume for wide-ranging sound coverage, even in open spaces or noisy areas. The speaker\'s 140&deg; dispersion angle ensures that the sound reaches a large audience, making it a reliable choice for areas that require broad coverage, such as school campuses, factories, and outdoor event spaces. Additionally, the L-PHP15A is designed to be installed in 100V or 70V systems, offering flexibility in various installations.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-php15a-horn-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-201-44-bXBQyPI20N.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:17:33.940255', '2025-01-22 02:23:22.028525', 201),
(386, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The L-PHP15A Horn Loudspeaker by Honeywell is engineered for consistent, high-quality sound reproduction in demanding outdoor environments. With power tapping options at 15W and 7.5W, the speaker is adaptable for different acoustic needs, whether you\'re broadcasting in a smaller area or covering larger spaces. Its frequency response range of 350 Hz to 8 kHz delivers clear and crisp audio, while its sound pressure levels of 115 dB at 15W ensure messages can be heard even in challenging conditions.<br><br>This horn loudspeaker is perfect for public address applications, emergency alarm systems, or general audio broadcasting. With a 140&deg; wide dispersion angle at 1kHz, the L-PHP15A ensures that the sound reaches listeners throughout a broad area. Its white, low-profile cover and sturdy build ensure it can blend into the surroundings while withstanding harsh outdoor conditions.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-php15a-horn-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-201-55-u5F9wPz5Pm.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:17:33.946519', '2025-01-22 02:23:22.033321', 201),
(387, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PWP10A Cabinet Loudspeaker is engineered for general public address applications where clear and consistent audio is required. With a rated power of 10W and a maximum power output of 15W, this speaker delivers high-quality sound without distortion, even in large, open spaces. The speaker features a wide frequency range of 150 Hz to 17 kHz (-10dB), allowing it to reproduce both low and high frequencies with clarity. Its high sound pressure level of 102 dB at 10W ensures that announcements and music can be heard clearly over background noise in busy environments.<br><br>Equipped with 170&deg; dispersion at 1 kHz, the L-PWP10A offers wide coverage, ensuring that the audio reaches a larger audience across an entire room or open space. The speaker also features power taps for flexibility in installation, allowing it to be connected to 100V or 70V systems with different output options, including 10W, 5W, and 2.5W. Its anti-fatigue rubber design ensures that the bass frequencies remain free from distortion during extended use, making it ideal for environments that require consistent audio reproduction over time.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pwp10a-cabinet-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-202-44-b1aPSfZow7.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:28:26.550185', '2025-01-22 02:23:10.024188', 202),
(388, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PWP10A Cabinet Loudspeaker is designed to offer high performance and reliability in a variety of environments, including educational institutions, shopping malls, office buildings, and more. This speaker&rsquo;s robust design ensures that it can handle extended use while delivering excellent sound quality. It supports power tapping at 100V and 70V, offering flexible installation options to suit different system configurations. The L-PWP10A is ideal for locations where audio quality and coverage are essential, including spaces with high foot traffic or varying room layouts.<br><br>The wide frequency range of 150 Hz to 17 kHz provides clear reproduction of both speech and music, while the speaker&rsquo;s dispersion angle of 170&deg; ensures that sound reaches listeners throughout a large area. The durable construction, featuring high linearity anti-fatigue rubber, ensures that bass frequencies remain crisp and distortion-free even during long durations of low-frequency use. Whether it&rsquo;s for background music or public announcements, the Honeywell L-PWP10A offers versatile, high-quality audio performance.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pwp10a-cabinet-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-202-66-LYDhsgGZOt.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:28:26.557861', '2025-01-22 02:23:10.026600', 202),
(389, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker is an ideal choice for businesses and facilities seeking a high-quality, aesthetically pleasing audio solution. This full-range speaker offers superior audio performance with a wide frequency response from 110 Hz to 20 kHz, ensuring a rich and dynamic sound experience. With a maximum power rating of 9W and a rated power of 6W, it provides ample volume and clarity for a range of commercial applications, from announcements to background music.<br><br>Thanks to its low-profile design and white color, the L-PCM06B seamlessly integrates into most modern interior styles, making it the perfect fit for hotels, office buildings, restaurants, and schools. The speaker also features adjustable power taps (6W, 3W, and 1.5W) for flexibility in various sound distribution scenarios, allowing it to be used in both 100V and 70V systems. Its 180&deg; dispersion angle at 1 kHz ensures even coverage across large spaces, providing consistent sound quality from corner to corner, while maintaining high sound pressure levels of up to 102 dB at 10W for clear, audible audio.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pcm06b-ceiling-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-203-33-LI8BCfuCaH.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:38:45.733614', '2025-01-22 02:22:54.861413', 203),
(390, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed with versatility and ease of installation in mind, the Honeywell L-PCM06B Ceiling Loudspeaker is perfect for a wide range of commercial and public spaces. Its 180&deg; dispersion angle ensures that sound is distributed evenly throughout the space, making it ideal for environments that require broad audio coverage, such as classrooms, auditoriums, or retail spaces. Whether you\'re using it for general background music, voice announcements, or more critical audio applications, the speaker&rsquo;s 100 dB SPL at 6W ensures excellent clarity and intelligibility.<br><br>With a frequency response range from 110 Hz to 20 kHz, the L-PCM06B covers a broad spectrum of sound, from the deep tones of bass to the sharpness of high-frequency sounds. Its efficient design makes it an affordable yet high-performance option for those who need a reliable audio system for larger spaces. The speaker&rsquo;s durable construction and simple installation process further enhance its appeal, making it a valuable addition to any ceiling-mounted audio system.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pcm06b-ceiling-loudspeaker/descriptions/202501-203-44-8a5UbfcdOI.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:38:45.740021', '2025-01-22 02:22:54.863826', 203),
(391, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-POM20A Column Speaker is a powerful and versatile loudspeaker designed for public address systems in both commercial and emergency settings. With a rated power of 20W and a maximum power of 30W, this speaker provides exceptional sound output with a frequency response range from 110 Hz to 20 kHz. This broad frequency range ensures the clarity and accuracy of audio broadcasts, making it ideal for environments such as factories, conference rooms, theme parks, and hotels. The speaker&rsquo;s high sound pressure level of 105 dB at 20W guarantees that messages can be heard clearly across large areas, even in noisy environments.<br><br>This column speaker is built for resilience, featuring a durable aluminum enclosure that helps protect the internal components from the heat and humidity often found in outdoor environments. The L-POM20A is also equipped with a fire-resistant cable and high-temperature ceramic wiring connector, ensuring the speaker remains functional during fire emergencies. Its swivel bracket, also made of aluminum, ensures that the speaker remains securely in place while resisting corrosion, making it perfect for long-term use in both indoor and outdoor applications. The speaker also offers power taps at 100V (20W, 10W, 5W, and 2.5W) to accommodate different installation setups.<br></span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pom20a-column-speaker/descriptions/202501-204-44-YyUZ5H0Ab1.PNG', '2025-01-22 01:51:02.476280', '2025-01-22 02:22:32.402565', 204),
(392, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Honeywell L-POM20A Column Speaker combines high-quality sound reproduction with enhanced safety features, making it an ideal solution for both routine audio broadcasts and emergency communication systems. Whether used in large commercial spaces or public venues, this loudspeaker delivers clear, distortion-free sound with a wide frequency range of 250 Hz to 20 kHz. Its high sound pressure level ensures that important announcements, such as evacuation messages, can be heard clearly, even in crowded or noisy environments.<br><br>Designed with emergency situations in mind, the speaker features a temperature fuse to protect it from overheating due to improper loading, making it a reliable option in case of fire. The aluminum construction, coupled with the corrosion-resistant swivel bracket, ensures that the speaker remains durable and operational over time, even in challenging environments. The L-POM20A Column Speaker is equipped with multiple power taps, providing flexibility for different types of installations, whether you need a high-volume broadcast or more subtle sound coverage.</span></p>', 'products/honeywell-l-pom20a-column-speaker/descriptions/202501-204-55-Iz0rh22BXR.png', '2025-01-22 01:51:02.484815', '2025-01-22 02:22:32.405580', 204);
