(393, '<p>The HONEYWELL X-MAP4P Digital Audio Player is built to offer a comprehensive audio experience, integrating traditional and modern audio sources for a versatile sound solution. It features SD, USB, and FM tuner inputs, along with Bluetooth connectivity, ensuring compatibility with a wide array of devices and audio formats. Whether you\'re playing music at a corporate event or setting up a home audio system, the X-MAP4P delivers exceptional sound quality and flexibility.</p>\r\n<p>Its rear panel includes two-line outputs, enabling simultaneous music playback in two different zones, making it perfect for multi-room setups. Additionally, the X-MAP4P supports MP3 and WAV file formats, ensuring high-quality audio reproduction. The connection to voice alarm systems via Cinch audio connection enhances its functionality in safety-critical environments, offering clear and reliable sound for public announcements.</p>', 'products/honeywell-x-map4p-digital-audio-player/descriptions/202501-205-55-Dbvpuid0jW.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:07:20.983765', '2025-01-22 02:22:17.927204', 205),
(394, '<p>Designed with user convenience in mind, the HONEYWELL X-MAP4P boasts a compact yet robust design. Its dimensions ensure it fits seamlessly into standard audio racks, saving space while providing powerful audio capabilities. The power supply ranges from 100-240V AC with minimal power consumption, making it an energy-efficient choice for any audio setup. The device&rsquo;s ability to manage multiple audio sources effortlessly makes it a valuable addition to both small-scale and large-scale audio environments.</p>\r\n<p>For those who need precise audio distribution, the X-MAP4P&rsquo;s multiple output options, including stereo sound RCA outputs for FM/AM tuner and USB/SD/Bluetooth, offer unparalleled flexibility. This, coupled with its easy-to-use interface and sturdy build, makes it a dependable choice for both novice users and audio professionals. The X-MAP4P&rsquo;s superior sound performance is complemented by its user-friendly design, ensuring a smooth audio experience in any setting.</p>', 'products/honeywell-x-map4p-digital-audio-player/descriptions/202501-205-44-kPvd7iHxE2.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:07:20.991431', '2025-01-22 02:22:17.930213', 205),
(395, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ACO2-MF RFID Access Control system is crafted from premium 304# stainless steel, ensuring longevity and a high-end, modern appearance that suits any hotel lobby or entrance. This sleek, durable material is designed to withstand the rigors of everyday use while maintaining its polished look. The RFID technology embedded in the system allows authorized guests to simply swipe their RFID card to gain entry, ensuring that only valid guests can access the hotel doors. This system integrates smoothly with the hotel\'s existing locking software, providing an efficient and seamless access management experience.<br><br>Additionally, the ACO2-MF ensures heightened security by restricting access to unauthorized individuals, making it a critical component for safeguarding the hotel&rsquo;s premises. It works in conjunction with electric drop bolts or electromagnetic locks, providing flexibility in how hotels can set up their security measures. The system is also designed with a valid time for each guest card, meaning that expired or invalid cards will not be able to open the door, further preventing unauthorized access.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-aco2-mf/descriptions/202501-206-44-i8L1IZpCr2.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.592801', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.598980', 206),
(396, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed for hotels looking to enhance security and streamline guest access, the ACO2-MF RFID Access Control system offers a sleek and modern solution. The pure 304# stainless steel material gives the reader a high-end look while ensuring it remains strong and durable, ideal for daily operation in high-traffic areas like hotel entrances. Guests can easily gain entry to the hotel by using their RFID cards, which are synchronized with the hotel&rsquo;s locking software, ensuring only those with authorized access can enter.<br><br>This system provides an added layer of security, as it works with electric drop bolts or electromagnetic locks, allowing for a range of installations depending on the hotel&rsquo;s needs. The integration of the valid time function ensures that expired or unauthorized cards cannot be used, which contributes to the overall management of guest access. In combination with its aesthetic appeal and durability, the ACO2-MF serves as a reliable and secure access control solution for modern hotels.</span></p>', 'products/aiphone-aco2-mf/descriptions/202501-206-33-YcP83KPQOU.PNG', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.601025', '2025-01-22 02:37:41.604481', 206),
(397, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q10 is designed to offer top-tier security and smooth operation in any facility. Its primary feature, the single-user passage design, ensures only one person can pass at a time, preventing illegal trailing and unauthorized access. This makes the DS-Q10 perfect for environments that require strict access control. The turnstile\'s elegant black-and-white design complements both modern and traditional settings, offering versatility while maintaining security standards.<br><br>With integrated green and red LED indicators, the turnstile provides clear visual signals to users, enhancing the ease of use and security. Waterproof and durable, the DS-Q10 is suitable for both indoor and outdoor installations, ensuring reliable performance in any condition. This makes it ideal for high-traffic areas such as airports, office buildings, and stadiums where security and flow control are paramount.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q10/descriptions/202501-207-33-a6soYI66TA.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.038797', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.043959', 207),
(398, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q10 Tripod Turnstile offers outstanding functionality and flexibility for security management in public and private spaces. Built with high-end materials and a sleek, professional appearance, this turnstile is as visually appealing as it is efficient. It supports integration with a variety of access control systems, allowing for customizable setups to match your specific security needs. Additionally, the design is customizable, with options for logos, colors, and dimensions based on the installation environment.<br><br>With its user-friendly LED indicators and waterproof design, the DS-Q10 offers both practicality and durability. Whether you need to manage access in a corporate setting or secure entry points in a more demanding environment, this turnstile can deliver. Its adaptable features ensure it meets the specific requirements of your installation while maintaining high levels of safety and functionality.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q10/descriptions/202501-207-66-zUMfRbmAwz.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.045268', '2025-01-22 03:11:54.048320', 207),
(399, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The TURNSTILE Tripod Turnstile DS-Q50 combines style, security, and space efficiency in one sleek package. Its compact design&mdash;measuring just 3802801000mm&mdash;makes it an ideal choice for environments with limited installation space, allowing easy integration without sacrificing functionality. Despite its slim profile, the DS-Q50 does not compromise on security, offering reliable single-user passage to prevent unauthorized access and illegal trailing. The high-quality black and white color combination gives it a timeless, professional appearance suitable for upscale venues.<br><br>This turnstile is equipped with a waterproof construction, making it versatile enough for both indoor and outdoor use, ensuring long-lasting performance in various environments. The DS-Q50 integrates smoothly with a range of access control systems, making it a flexible addition to any security setup. With customization options available for logos, colors, and dimensions, it can be tailored to meet the specific needs of any installation, whether in a corporate building or a public space.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q50/descriptions/202501-208-44-Z8mCTheMg7.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.511686', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.517020', 208),
(400, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q50 Tripod Turnstile is designed for those who need high security and sophisticated aesthetics in a compact form. Its slim size allows it to fit into small spaces without compromising on the user experience or security features. Like other models in the Quantum series, the DS-Q50 ensures that only one person can pass at a time, preventing tailgating and unauthorized entry. Its elegant, minimalist design, available in black and white, suits high-end applications, from offices to luxury facilities.<br><br>Thanks to its waterproof construction, the DS-Q50 is built to withstand both indoor and outdoor environments. It supports integration with any access control system, making it a versatile option for organizations looking for an efficient access control solution. Additionally, the ability to customize the appearance, logo, and dimensions of the turnstile allows it to fit perfectly with its surroundings, whether in a modern building or a highly secured area.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds-q50/descriptions/202501-208-11-W8AGOWTzsW.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.518639', '2025-01-22 03:23:28.522240', 208),
(401, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS112 Tripod Turnstile is designed to provide a secure and elegant access control solution that enhances the functionality and aesthetics of any installation. Constructed from full brushed stainless steel, this turnstile offers exceptional durability and resistance to rust and weather, ensuring long-lasting performance. It delivers a high throughput rate of 35-40 persons per minute, making it perfect for high-traffic areas that require both efficiency and security. Its sleek, modern appearance with a flat top allows for easy mounting of access control devices and controllers on either side.<br><br>Equipped with visual LED indication strips at both the front and back, the DS112 is not only highly functional but also visually striking. The LED strips add a dazzling effect, improving the visibility of the turnstile and making it an attractive security feature. Whether installed indoors or outdoors, the DS112 is capable of withstanding various environmental conditions, providing reliable service no matter the setting. Additionally, its adjustable settings for both single-direction and bi-directional access ensure that it can meet a wide range of security needs.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds112/descriptions/202501-209-44-2DSl4LlX7j.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.041916', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.046982', 209),
(402, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS112 Tripod Turnstile is the perfect solution for managing pedestrian access while maintaining high security in both private and public spaces. Its elegant design, made from full brushed stainless steel, makes it resistant to rust, corrosion, and weather damage, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. With an impressive throughput rate of 35-40 persons per minute, it efficiently handles large numbers of people while ensuring that only authorized individuals are granted access. This makes it ideal for locations such as corporate offices, stadiums, and transportation hubs.<br><br>The turnstile also features a flat top, which makes it easy to integrate access control devices and controllers, adding an extra layer of customization for your security system. The integrated LED indication strips provide clear visual signals, making the turnstile stand out and enhancing user interaction. Whether you\'re managing a high-security facility or a public venue, the DS112 offers both flexibility and a sleek, durable design that fits seamlessly into any environment.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-tripod-turnstile-ds112/descriptions/202501-209-55-13gsf92eDD.PNG', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.048942', '2025-01-22 03:35:24.053208', 209),
(403, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q20 Quantum Optical Swing Turnstile is an ideal access control solution for environments where high pedestrian traffic needs to be managed smoothly and securely. With a passageway width of 1100mm, the turnstile can accommodate wheelchair users, individuals with large packages, or provide an accessible route during emergencies. Its sleek, modern design in black and white is not only aesthetically pleasing but also well-suited for upscale settings such as corporate offices, hotels, or airports. The green and red LED indicators provide clear visual feedback, ensuring users can quickly determine whether access is granted or denied.<br><br>This turnstile supports integration with any type of access control system, allowing it to seamlessly connect with existing security infrastructure. Additionally, the DS-Q20 meets fire safety regulations, with the ability for its arms to automatically open in the event of an emergency, providing an extra layer of safety. The flexibility to customize the logo, appearance color, and dimensions based on the installation environment ensures that the DS-Q20 can be tailored to meet the unique needs of any facility, further enhancing its functionality and appeal.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds-q20/descriptions/202501-211-44-fHE1CKZr8D.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.454634', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.463472', 211),
(404, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q20 Optical Swing Turnstile combines high functionality with elegant design to offer a reliable access control solution for high-traffic areas. Its 1100mm wide passageway not only facilitates easy access for individuals with disabilities but also accommodates large items, such as packages or carts, making it ideal for settings like office buildings, transportation hubs, and public venues. The turnstile\'s automatic arm opening feature meets fire safety requirements, enhancing its suitability for buildings where emergency evacuation is critical.<br><br>In addition to its safety features, the DS-Q20 boasts a sleek, timeless appearance with a black and white color design that complements various modern architectural styles. The LED indicators at the front and back make it easy for users to understand the access status at a glance, improving the overall flow of pedestrian traffic. Furthermore, the turnstile is customizable in terms of logo, color, and size, making it adaptable to different installation environments and allowing businesses to align it with their branding and aesthetic requirements.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds-q20/descriptions/202501-211-66-OKW8mp8XPb.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.465222', '2025-01-22 05:15:46.470061', 211),
(405, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS205A Optical Swing Turnstile is designed to efficiently manage pedestrian access in both high-traffic and restricted areas. This turnstile features bi-directional settings, allowing for smooth, controlled entry and exit in both directions, ideal for environments that experience fluctuating foot traffic. The body of the turnstile is made from high-quality brushed stainless steel, offering both durability and a sleek, modern appearance that blends into various environments. Additionally, the arms are available in either plexiglas or stainless steel, depending on the customer\'s preferences, adding an extra layer of customization.<br><br>With a passage width of up to 900mm, the DS205A is designed to support individuals with mobility devices, such as wheelchairs, or those carrying large luggage, bicycles, or prams. This feature makes it particularly well-suited for places like shopping malls, supermarkets, and public spaces where accessibility is crucial. Despite its compact design, the DS205A is an effective solution for controlling access and ensuring secure passage while maintaining ease of movement for all types of pedestrians.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds205a/descriptions/202501-212-44-TofSk2ePC5.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.424096', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.429454', 212),
(406, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS205A Optical Swing Turnstile is a versatile and space-saving access control solution. Its slim and compact design makes it easy to install in various locations, while its robust construction ensures it can withstand everyday use in busy environments. While the turnstile body is easy to install in most settings, it does not support the addition of external devices like biometric scanners, card readers, or coin inserts due to its streamlined structure. Typically used in manual settings, the DS205A excels at providing efficient and secure access control with minimal complexity.<br><br>Ideal for use in shops, supermarkets, and similar retail environments, the DS205A ensures both security and smooth pedestrian flow. Its 900mm-wide passage is designed to accommodate various needs, including accessibility for individuals with disabilities and those requiring extra space for luggage or prams. The turnstile&rsquo;s robust materials and functional design make it a durable and reliable option for managing pedestrian traffic in high-traffic areas while maintaining an attractive, professional appearance.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-ds205a/descriptions/202501-212-11-ZLS4BOFBkk.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.431397', '2025-01-22 05:25:37.434961', 212),
(407, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DSN-20 Nebula Optical Swing Turnstile is a state-of-the-art access control solution designed to cater to a wide range of pedestrian needs. With a passage width of 650mm to 1100mm, it allows for easy access for handicapped individuals in wheelchairs or pedestrians with luggage, making it highly adaptable for environments requiring accessibility. The sleek design of the turnstile, featuring a modern urban cabinet and blue LED strips, enhances its visual appeal, making it suitable for both contemporary indoor and outdoor installations.<br><br>Crafted from brushed stainless steel and finished with high-end black painting, the DSN-20 offers durability and a premium look. The system is built with advanced manufacturing techniques, including integrated mold production and robot-assisted welding, ensuring top-notch quality and precision. Its versatility is further enhanced by the ability to integrate with third-party access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint scanners, and biometric readers, offering users a customizable security solution tailored to their needs.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-dsn-20/descriptions/202501-213-55-HafcTyURWA.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.328046', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.333557', 213),
(408, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DSN-20 Nebula Optical Swing Turnstile is engineered for high-traffic areas where both security and accessibility are key priorities. The turnstile\'s broad passage width ensures that users of all abilities, including those with wheelchairs or heavy luggage, can pass through easily and without obstruction. Designed with a stylish modern urban aesthetic, it features an elegant brushed stainless steel body complemented by vibrant blue LED indicators, making it not only functional but visually appealing as well.<br><br>In addition to its design, the DSN-20 offers superior performance and integration capabilities. The turnstile can be easily connected to a variety of access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint scanners, or biometric devices, making it a flexible option for businesses with advanced security needs. With a focus on precision, the turnstile is manufactured using integrated mold production and robot welding, ensuring both high quality and reliability in demanding environments. Ideal for airports, offices, or public spaces, the DSN-20 provides a seamless, efficient, and secure access control solution.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-turnstile-dsn-20/descriptions/202501-213-44-Sl6SiChYIl.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.334995', '2025-01-22 05:31:53.338490', 213),
(409, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS-Q30 Quantum Optical Flap Turnstile offers a fast and reliable solution for controlling pedestrian flow in high-traffic locations. With a throughput rate of up to 45 persons per minute, this turnstile ensures efficient and seamless access, making it ideal for busy environments such as metro stations, office buildings, and commercial spaces. Its advanced design features classic black and white color options, providing an elegant and professional appearance that suits a variety of settings. The integrated LED indicators display clear access status, guiding users to determine when entry is permitted.<br><br>The DS-Q30 is designed with safety in mind, incorporating fire safety features such as retractable arms that automatically open in the event of an emergency, allowing for rapid evacuation. It is compatible with any type of access control system, providing the flexibility to integrate with existing RFID, fingerprint, or biometric systems. The turnstile&rsquo;s construction ensures durability and longevity, making it a reliable choice for managing high volumes of pedestrian traffic while maintaining top-tier security.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds-q30/descriptions/202501-214-44-knN3ozZxAr.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.469574', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.476592', 214),
(410, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Ideal for high-traffic venues where security and efficiency are crucial, the DS-Q30 Quantum Optical Flap Turnstile combines advanced technology with an elegant design. The turnstile&rsquo;s 45-person per minute throughput ensures smooth access flow, preventing bottlenecks in areas with large volumes of foot traffic. The turnstile\'s sleek design, offered in a timeless black-and-white finish, fits seamlessly into both contemporary and high-end applications, providing a sophisticated security solution. With green and red LED indicators, the DS-Q30 helps users easily identify access status, enhancing the overall user experience.<br><br>This turnstile is built to meet fire safety standards, automatically retracting its arms in case of emergency for safe and efficient evacuation. The DS-Q30 is also highly customizable, with options for logo, color, and dimensions to match the specific requirements of your installation environment. Designed to integrate seamlessly with a variety of access control systems, the DS-Q30 is ideal for businesses seeking both style and performance in managing pedestrian access.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds-q30/descriptions/202501-214-55-MH5bzqlRnb.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.478226', '2025-01-22 05:44:23.481454', 214),
(411, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DSN-30 Nebula Optical Flap Turnstile is engineered to provide fast and reliable access control in high-traffic areas. With a throughput rate of 45 persons per minute, it ensures that large volumes of people can pass through efficiently without delays, making it ideal for busy public spaces such as metro stations, airports, and corporate buildings. The turnstile features a modern urban cabinet design, complete with a brushed stainless steel body and high-end black painting, ensuring that it blends seamlessly with any environment.<br><br>Equipped with a standard relay signal, the DSN-30 can be integrated with a wide range of third-party access control systems, including RFID and fingerprint scanners, making it a versatile solution for any security needs. The turnstile\'s bi-directional function allows for entry and exit control in both directions, providing flexibility for various types of facilities. The sleek blue LED strip adds a stylish touch, enhancing the visual appeal of the turnstile while also indicating access status clearly.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-dsn-30/descriptions/202501-215-44-v1eIGDLpeX.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.406039', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.414703', 215),
(412, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DSN-30 Nebula Optical Flap Turnstile offers both high efficiency and security with its advanced features and cutting-edge design. Designed for locations with high pedestrian traffic, it boasts an impressive throughput rate of 45 persons per minute, allowing for rapid access while maintaining secure entry and exit points. The turnstile is constructed from durable materials, including brushed stainless steel and a high-end black paint finish, providing both strength and an attractive aesthetic that fits well in modern environments.<br><br>This optical flap turnstile is perfect for facilities that require both high performance and seamless integration with other security systems. It features bi-directional functionality, allowing easy control of both entry and exit points. The DSN-30&rsquo;s integration with third-party systems, including RFID and fingerprint readers, ensures flexibility and adaptability in various applications, from office buildings to transit stations. Its stylish design, with features like the blue LED strip, enhances both functionality and the visual appeal of any installation.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-dsn-30/descriptions/202501-215-55-kVmcYGIa6o.PNG', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.416192', '2025-01-22 05:59:16.420355', 215),
(413, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS3000 Optical Flap Turnstile is a cutting-edge access control solution designed for high-end sites like educational institutions, corporate offices, and luxury buildings. With a throughput rate of 40-45 persons per minute, it effectively manages the flow of people in busy environments while maintaining a high level of security. Constructed with full brushed stainless steel and accentuated by black decorative painting, the DS3000 boasts a sleek, modern appearance that fits seamlessly into sophisticated settings. Its arc-shaped cabinet, free from any sharp edges, not only enhances the turnstile&rsquo;s aesthetics but also ensures safety by preventing potential injury.<br><br>Incorporating advanced features, the DS3000 is equipped with a long, slim LED indicator bar at the front to clearly display access status, making it easy for users to identify whether entry is permitted. The top of the unit also features a LED indicator to show whether access is denied or accepted. The turnstile includes four pairs of infrared sensors for alarm functions, which further enhance security by detecting unauthorized attempts to pass through. The DS3000 offers the flexibility of single or bi-directional settings to suit different security needs, and its standard relay signal ensures easy integration with a variety of third-party access control systems, including RFID readers and biometric devices.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds3000/descriptions/202501-216-33-rnMmVnnxou.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.360753', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.365846', 216),
(414, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS3000 Optical Flap Turnstile combines security and style, making it an ideal choice for premium locations. This model offers a streamlined design with full brushed stainless steel for durability, complemented by a black-painted finish for a polished, high-end look. Its arc-shaped cabinet eliminates sharp edges, enhancing both its aesthetic appeal and user safety. Whether installed indoors or outdoors, the DS3000 ensures smooth pedestrian flow with its impressive throughput rate of 40-45 persons per minute, making it highly efficient for high-traffic areas.<br><br>In terms of security, the DS3000 is equipped with four pairs of infrared sensors that provide real-time detection and trigger alarms in case of unauthorized access attempts. The system can be configured for either single or bi-directional access control, providing flexibility for various applications. The sleek LED indicator bar and top-mounted LED indicator light clearly show the entry status, helping users navigate the turnstile with ease. Designed for seamless integration with third-party access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint, or other biometric devices, the DS3000 offers adaptable solutions to meet the security needs of any site.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-optical-flap-turnstile-ds3000/descriptions/202501-216-44-ZQ4ki2RN4z.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.367772', '2025-01-22 06:05:53.372237', 216),
(415, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS411 Full Height Turnstile is engineered to provide top-level security in high-risk environments where restricted access is critical. Its sturdy, full-height design ensures that unauthorized individuals cannot bypass the system, making it perfect for use in prisons, construction sites, stadiums, and other high-security areas. The system allows both single and bi-directional passage control, providing flexibility depending on the access control requirements of the site. The DS411\'s body is constructed from high-quality brushed stainless steel, offering resistance to corrosion, rust, and damage from outdoor elements, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor use.<br><br>This turnstile also offers ample space for the integration of access control devices, such as RFID readers, fingerprint scanners, barcode/QR readers, and other security equipment. The DS411\'s design includes LED lights on the top cover and body, which provide clear visual indicators of whether access is granted or denied. This feature ensures users know immediately whether their entry has been authorized, helping to avoid confusion and maintaining smooth access control.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds411/descriptions/202501-217-44-J8aWtLYvZt.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.553443', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.559080', 217),
(416, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS411 Full Height Turnstile is a highly secure and durable access control solution, designed for areas where safety and strict entry management are paramount. Its full-height barrier prevents unauthorized entry and enhances the security of critical areas such as construction sites or prisons. The turnstile is available with a 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotating arm, allowing for efficient control of foot traffic while maintaining security standards. Whether used in a single or bi-directional configuration, the DS411 ensures that only authorized individuals can gain entry, making it ideal for controlling access in high-risk locations.<br><br>Made from finished and brushed stainless steel, the DS411 is built to withstand harsh environmental conditions. The turnstile&rsquo;s robust construction provides long-lasting performance, and its ability to integrate with various access control technologies enhances its functionality. With clear LED lights to indicate the status of entry, this turnstile guarantees ease of use for both security personnel and individuals seeking access. The DS411&rsquo;s adaptable features make it an excellent choice for sites that demand both high security and flexibility in managing pedestrian access.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds411/descriptions/202501-217-55-wTkLpKh3T1.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.561148', '2025-01-22 06:14:00.566511', 217),
(417, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS412 Full Height Turnstile is engineered to provide secure, efficient, and long-lasting access control for high-security locations. With a robust double-door design, it offers bi-directional passage control, ensuring that both entry and exit can be securely managed. This feature makes it ideal for places with high traffic, such as stadiums, industrial sites, and events that require a high level of security. Built from full brushed stainless steel, the DS412 is resistant to corrosion, rust, and weather, ensuring reliable performance both indoors and outdoors.<br><br>Additionally, the DS412 is designed to offer excellent visibility and user guidance through its integrated LED indicators. Located on both the side front and the top, these indicators clearly display whether entry is accepted or denied, improving user experience and operational efficiency. The turnstile can be customized with either 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotor arms, providing flexible options for controlling access. With sufficient space for embedding access control devices, this turnstile supports a variety of security systems, such as RFID, fingerprint devices, or barcode scanners, ensuring a comprehensive security solution.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds412/descriptions/202501-218-44-ZNgNBviDOR.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.393677', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.400342', 218),
(418, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS412 Full Height Turnstile is designed for facilities requiring top-notch security with heavy pedestrian traffic, such as stadiums, industrial enterprises, and high-security events. Its robust, double-door design enables bi-directional passage control, which helps manage foot traffic in both directions, making it an ideal choice for complex access control needs. The full brushed stainless steel construction ensures that the DS412 is not only durable and rust-resistant but also waterproof, making it suitable for use in both indoor and outdoor environments, even under extreme weather conditions.<br><br>With visible LED indicators on the front and top, the DS412 provides clear access status updates, helping users navigate easily and understand whether they are allowed entry. The system allows for easy integration with a wide range of access control devices, including RFID readers, fingerprint scanners, and coin inserts, giving users the flexibility to tailor the system to their specific security requirements. The turnstile also offers the option of 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotors, depending on user preferences, further customizing the flow of pedestrian traffic in high-security areas.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds412/descriptions/202501-218-55-stQHJI5vGF.PNG', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.401789', '2025-01-22 06:37:27.405440', 218),
(419, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS401FS Full Height Turnstile is engineered to deliver optimal security in outdoor environments or high-risk locations, such as prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. With a solid rain protection roof made from optional 304 or 316 stainless steel, this turnstile is specifically designed to resist adverse weather and ensure the protection of pedestrians. The unit\'s standard dimensions of 1.5m (L) X 1.5m (W) provide ample space for secure passage, though custom sizes are available to suit specific site requirements.<br><br>The turnstile is constructed from brushed stainless steel, known for its durability, anti-corrosion, and waterproof properties, making it perfect for both indoor and outdoor installations. This full-height design offers complete security by preventing unauthorized entry, while the turnstile arms can rotate 120&deg; or 90&deg; depending on the selected configuration. The DS401FS also features LED lights that indicate whether access is granted or denied, ensuring clear communication of access status at all times.<br></span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds401fs/descriptions/202501-219-44-iglv9KzD2Q.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.974012', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.980414', 219),
(420, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Ideal for securing high-traffic or restricted access areas, the DS401FS Full Height Turnstile is a reliable solution for environments requiring maximum security. The turnstile&rsquo;s solid construction, featuring a rain protection roof and high-quality stainless steel material, ensures that it stands up to tough conditions, making it an excellent choice for outdoor applications. The DS401FS is engineered to handle high foot traffic while maintaining robust security, with its full-height design preventing tailgating and unauthorized access.<br><br>With its 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotor arm options, the DS401FS can be customized to suit various flow requirements, allowing for smooth access in both directions. It integrates seamlessly with third-party access control systems, such as RFID, fingerprint, or biometric readers, ensuring a high level of security and convenience. The turnstile&rsquo;s LED indicators provide real-time information on access status, enhancing user experience and operational efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds401fs/descriptions/202501-219-55-aLYyOUbSO3.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.981884', '2025-01-22 07:06:20.985317', 219),
(421, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS402FS Full Height Turnstile is designed to meet the highest security demands in high-traffic or high-risk areas. Its durable construction, including a rain protection roof, ensures that the turnstile remains operational in all weather conditions, making it ideal for outdoor installations. The turnstile\'s body is constructed from premium stainless steel, providing excellent resistance to corrosion and physical damage, while maintaining a sleek and professional appearance. The standard dimensions of 2.2m (L) x 1.5m (W) can be customized based on specific site requirements, ensuring that the turnstile fits seamlessly into any installation environment.<br><br>This turnstile features bi-directional access control with flexible rotor arm options. Users can select between 120&deg; or 90&deg; rotation, depending on the desired pedestrian traffic flow. Additionally, the DS402FS includes LED indicators on both the side front and top, which provide clear visual signals about the entry status, making it easier for users to navigate the turnstile. The turnstile can also be integrated with various third-party access control systems such as RFID, fingerprint, or biometric readers, providing a customizable and secure access solution for any facility.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds402fs/descriptions/202501-220-44-RrdO9vYSFs.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.182294', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.187691', 220),
(422, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The DS402FS Full Height Turnstile is the perfect choice for applications that demand high levels of security, including prisons, stadiums, and construction sites. Built for both indoor and outdoor environments, this turnstile features a robust stainless steel body that ensures durability and resistance to the elements. The solid rain protection roof is designed to keep the system operational even in challenging weather, making it ideal for use in outdoor locations that require reliable access control. Its customizable size allows the system to fit a variety of site layouts, providing flexible installation options.<br><br>With a user-friendly design, the DS402FS offers clear LED indicators that inform users whether they are allowed to enter, ensuring smooth and efficient access control. The turnstile is equipped with flexible rotor arm options&mdash;either 120&deg; or 90&deg;&mdash;which allow for optimal traffic management based on the flow requirements of the site. Integration with third-party access control systems, including RFID, fingerprint, or biometric readers, makes the DS402FS a versatile and scalable solution, capable of meeting the specific security needs of any facility.</span></p>', 'products/daosafe-full-height-turnstile-ds402fs/descriptions/202501-220-55-o3rLF6UvLo.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.189058', '2025-01-22 07:14:25.206496', 220),
(423, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Fire Extinguisher is a compact, easy-to-use device designed for quick response to small fires. This portable tool is essential for fire safety in homes, offices, schools, and vehicles, providing an immediate solution for fire outbreaks before they escalate. Made from durable materials, the extinguisher is built to withstand regular use and environmental factors, ensuring it will remain reliable when needed most.<br><br>Its compact and lightweight design makes it easy to handle, even for individuals with no prior fire safety experience. The FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher is specifically engineered for small-scale fire emergencies, allowing users to respond swiftly to common fire sources such as electrical, grease, or paper fires. Whether placed in a kitchen, vehicle, or office, this extinguisher provides reliable fire suppression in a compact, convenient form.</span></p>', 'products/fire-extinguisher/descriptions/202501-221-11-RTNuQJ2NdO.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.924682', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.930134', 221),
(424, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher is a compact, easy-to-use device designed for quick response to small fires. This portable tool is essential for fire safety in homes, offices, schools, and vehicles, providing an immediate solution for fire outbreaks before they escalate. Made from durable materials, the extinguisher is built to withstand regular use and environmental factors, ensuring it will remain reliable when needed most.<br><br>Its compact and lightweight design makes it easy to handle, even for individuals with no prior fire safety experience. The FIRE PRO Fire Extinguisher is specifically engineered for small-scale fire emergencies, allowing users to respond swiftly to common fire sources such as electrical, grease, or paper fires. Whether placed in a kitchen, vehicle, or office, this extinguisher provides reliable fire suppression in a compact, convenient form.</span></p>', 'products/fire-extinguisher/descriptions/202501-221-22-jy5WAroeLo.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.931603', '2025-01-22 07:33:31.935512', 221),
(425, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FM-200 Suppression System is an advanced fire protection solution designed for critical areas where fast response and minimal damage are essential. Utilizing FM-200, a clean gaseous fire suppression agent, this system effectively suppresses fires without causing harm to people or leaving any residue. Ideal for environments like data centers, computer rooms, and laboratories, it is especially suited for spaces containing sensitive electronics or irreplaceable equipment that could be damaged by traditional fire suppression methods such as water or foam.<br><br>The system works by rapidly releasing FM-200 into the protected area, suppressing the fire in its early stages before it can cause significant damage. FM-200 is recognized for its ability to reduce the heat and oxygen needed to sustain a fire, ensuring a quick and efficient suppression process. Unlike water-based systems, the FIRE PRO FM-200 Suppression System leaves no residue behind, eliminating the need for costly cleanup or downtime. Its design is easily integrated into existing fire protection setups, making it a highly effective choice for high-risk, sensitive environments.<br></span></p>', 'products/fm-200-suppression-system/descriptions/202501-222-22-5j9OtmLnYk.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.494224', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.499349', 222),
(426, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FM-200 Suppression System is a high-performance fire safety solution specifically tailored for environments where both human safety and equipment protection are paramount. By using FM-200, a non-toxic and environmentally safe agent, this system effectively suppresses fires without compromising the integrity of the protected environment. With its clean discharge, there is no risk of water or foam damage to delicate machinery or electronics, making it ideal for use in IT centers, telecommunications facilities, and other high-value areas.<br><br>Quickly detecting the presence of fire, the FIRE PRO FM-200 Suppression System activates to release the agent, extinguishing the flames in seconds. This rapid action ensures that potential losses are minimized and that operations can continue without prolonged disruption. Designed for easy installation and maintenance, the FIRE PRO FM-200 Suppression System is the ideal choice for any high-security location that requires advanced fire suppression capabilities without the side effects of traditional methods.<br></span></p>', 'products/fm-200-suppression-system/descriptions/202501-222-33-0BXAubMTpi.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.501098', '2025-01-22 07:48:28.505022', 222),
(427, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Sprinklers are an essential fire protection device designed to suppress fires quickly and effectively in commercial and residential buildings. When a fire is detected, the sprinkler system is activated to release water and control the flames, minimizing damage and reducing fire spread. The sprinklers are mounted in an upright position on a water piping system, ensuring reliable performance in both large and small-scale applications.<br><br>These sprinklers are engineered for quick activation, with water being released as soon as the temperature reaches a predetermined threshold. The system is designed to protect the most vulnerable areas of a building, such as hallways, kitchens, and offices. FIRE PRO Sprinklers offer peace of mind by providing 24/7 fire protection, ensuring that even when you\'re not around, your property and loved ones are safeguarded from potential fire hazards.<br></span></p>', 'products/sprinklers/descriptions/202501-223-33-t7tBdsQ23z.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.398715', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.404665', 223),
(428, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Sprinkler system is an essential component for fire safety in both residential and commercial settings. Installed within a water piping system, these sprinklers automatically activate when the temperature rises above a certain threshold, releasing water to suppress the fire and prevent further damage. The system is ideal for use in a variety of building types, including office buildings, apartments, schools, and warehouses, offering efficient protection in any environment.<br><br>These sprinklers are designed for ease of installation and require minimal maintenance, providing reliable fire protection year-round. By delivering a consistent and immediate water flow, the FIRE PRO Sprinklers control and suppress fires in their early stages, giving occupants time to evacuate safely and limiting the spread of flames. This active suppression system not only protects valuable property but also enhances the overall fire safety of any building.<br></span></p>', 'products/sprinklers/descriptions/202501-223-44-2FPULdoiTg.PNG', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.406208', '2025-01-22 07:57:28.409351', 223),
(429, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Signal Gate Valve is designed for controlling the flow of a wide variety of fluids, from water and steam to more complex substances like liquid metals and radioactive mediums. Constructed from high-quality materials, this valve ensures optimal performance even when handling corrosive or hazardous fluids. It provides precise control over fluid flow, enabling users to manage different processes safely and efficiently in industrial environments.<br><br>This valve is ideal for use in industries such as chemical processing, oil and gas, manufacturing, and power generation. With its robust design and compatibility with various fluid types, the FIRE PRO Signal Gate Valve helps minimize downtime and ensure system integrity. It is designed to provide accurate flow control, making it an essential component in maintaining the safety and efficiency of fluid handling systems.<br></span></p>', 'products/signal-gate-valve/descriptions/202501-224-44-iZnmS5umvD.PNG', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.816094', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.821413', 224),
(430, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Signal Gate Valve offers versatile performance for controlling the flow of numerous mediums, from water to more complex substances like oil, corrosive fluids, and even radioactive materials. Built to withstand extreme conditions, this valve is engineered to perform under high pressure and temperature, ensuring reliable operation in a wide range of industrial applications. The signal feature built into the valve allows for real-time monitoring and quick response to any changes in fluid flow, ensuring safe and efficient operation.<br><br>Designed for both fluid regulation and safety, the FIRE PRO Signal Gate Valve is crucial for preventing leaks or mishandling of hazardous fluids. The valve is suitable for various applications, such as in refineries, chemical plants, and energy production facilities. Its dependable construction and user-friendly design make it a top choice for industries requiring precise flow control in challenging environments.<br></span></p>', 'products/signal-gate-valve/descriptions/202501-224-55-Q6rcjYWrno.PNG', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.823238', '2025-01-22 08:10:50.826701', 224);
