(431, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Pressure Reducing Valve is designed to control and regulate the pressure of various fluids within industrial systems. When high-pressure fluid enters the valve, it is reduced to a safe and manageable level before reaching sensitive equipment or processes. The valve uses a precise mechanism that adjusts the opening and closing of the valve body, maintaining outlet pressure within a predefined range, regardless of any changes in inlet pressure.<br><br>This valve is essential in systems where maintaining consistent pressure is crucial for the safe and effective operation of downstream equipment. It works by controlling the flow of the medium and adjusting the opening based on real-time pressure readings, providing reliable pressure reduction in applications such as water, gas, and steam systems. The FIRE PRO Pressure Reducing Valve plays an important role in preventing overpressure damage and ensuring the protection and longevity of your equipment.</span></p>', 'products/pressure-reducing-valve/descriptions/202501-225-44-u2J3AuS2dj.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:36:23.847423', '2025-01-23 00:49:51.000980', 225),
(432, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The&nbsp; Pressure Reducing Valve is a highly efficient valve used to manage and stabilize fluid pressure in various industrial applications. The valve works by reducing the pressure of the incoming fluid and maintaining a steady outlet pressure within a set range, which is crucial for the protection of downstream systems. Its dynamic pressure regulation capabilities help to keep systems running smoothly, even if the incoming pressure fluctuates.<br><br>Equipped with advanced control mechanisms, the FIRE PRO Pressure Reducing Valve adjusts the opening and closing of the valve body to ensure the outlet pressure remains consistent and within safe operational limits. This precise control prevents damage to appliances, equipment, and pipelines that could result from pressure fluctuations. Ideal for use in diverse industries such as chemical processing, water treatment, and HVAC systems, the valve is designed to offer long-lasting performance and reliability.</span></p>', 'products/pressure-reducing-valve/descriptions/202501-225-55-1Fi8mAcrSS.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:36:23.855302', '2025-01-23 00:49:51.004978', 225),
(433, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Kitchen Suppression System is a specialized fire suppression solution designed for commercial kitchens, cafeterias, and other food preparation areas. It is specifically engineered to address the unique fire hazards present in these environments, where cooking oils, grease, and flammable cooking equipment are common fire risks. This system detects fires in their early stages and releases a fast-acting fire suppressant, effectively controlling and extinguishing flames before they can spread.<br><br>This system is equipped with strategically placed nozzles that direct the suppressant agent directly to the source of the fire, ensuring quick and targeted suppression. The automatic activation mechanism ensures that the system responds immediately when a fire is detected, providing 24/7 protection for kitchens and cooking facilities. The FIRE PRO Kitchen Suppression System is a must-have for any commercial kitchen looking to enhance fire safety and prevent the devastating consequences of a kitchen fire.</span></p>', 'products/kitchen-suppression-system/descriptions/202501-226-55-kZdlxsdQVd.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:48:10.769786', '2025-01-23 00:50:18.782861', 226),
(434, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Kitchen Suppression System is a crucial fire safety feature for kitchens in restaurants, hotels, cafeterias, and other commercial food establishments. The system works by detecting heat or flames in the kitchen area and automatically releasing a fire-suppressing agent. The agent is designed to quickly extinguish fires caused by cooking oils, grease, and other common kitchen hazards, preventing them from escalating and causing significant damage.<br><br>The system is designed to be installed around cooking appliances, including fryers, stoves, and grills, where the risk of fire is highest. By providing rapid suppression, it not only protects equipment but also ensures the safety of kitchen staff and customers. FIRE PRO Kitchen Suppression System complies with relevant safety codes and regulations, offering peace of mind and effective protection for commercial kitchens and food service areas.</span></p>', 'products/kitchen-suppression-system/descriptions/202501-226-66-wPwH9h8DfF.PNG', '2025-01-23 00:48:10.779679', '2025-01-23 00:50:18.785227', 226),
(435, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Fire Pump is a powerful and reliable piece of equipment designed to supply water to fire suppression systems, ensuring that fires are quickly and efficiently extinguished. This pump is a key component in systems such as sprinklers, hydrants, and standpipes, providing the necessary pressure and flow to combat fires. Whether installed in commercial buildings, industrial complexes, or residential areas, the Fire Pump guarantees that firefighting efforts are supported with an adequate and consistent water supply.<br><br>Built to perform under high-pressure conditions, the&nbsp; Fire Pump is engineered for durability and efficiency. It is designed to meet the needs of large facilities and infrastructure, ensuring that fires are contained and suppressed with minimal delay. With its easy installation and seamless integration into fire protection systems, this pump ensures that buildings and facilities are adequately protected against fire risks.</span></p>', 'products/fire-pump/descriptions/202501-227-66-oQjqK7t411.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.029432', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.035779', 227),
(436, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Fire Pump is designed for high-performance firefighting applications, offering a steady and reliable water supply to support suppression efforts. It is engineered to deliver both flow and pressure, essential for keeping firefighting systems operational during critical moments. This pump is commonly used in commercial and industrial facilities, where a large-scale firefighting solution is necessary to protect lives and property.<br><br>Its rugged design makes it capable of operating in demanding environments, providing a reliable water source in emergencies. The Fire Pump is equipped to handle varying water demands, ensuring that the necessary pressure and flow are delivered to fire suppression systems. Whether it\'s used in large-scale industrial applications or within multi-story buildings, this fire pump is engineered to provide consistent and effective firefighting support.</span></p>', 'products/fire-pump/descriptions/202501-227-77-oJUnFPrGO7.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.037133', '2025-01-23 01:01:59.040543', 227),
(437, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"><br>The Jockey Pump is an integral component of fire protection systems, designed to maintain a constant pressure in the water supply. This small, yet powerful pump operates automatically to ensure that pressure levels are maintained even when the system is not actively fighting a fire. By keeping the pressure stable, the jockey pump helps prevent unnecessary activation of the main fire pump, which improves system longevity and reduces wear and tear. It is especially useful in systems that require frequent cycling or systems with varying water demand.<br><br>Typically installed in systems alongside a fire pump, the FIRE PRO Jockey Pump ensures that pressure fluctuations are corrected quickly and automatically. When the pressure in the system drops, the jockey pump kicks in to restore the correct level, allowing the fire pump to remain idle until it is truly needed. This feature not only ensures consistent performance but also maximizes the efficiency and lifespan of the fire protection system.</span></p>', 'products/jockey-pump/descriptions/202501-228-66-qij2nhRaDM.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.677484', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.682239', 228),
(438, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Jockey Pump is a vital part of any fire protection system that relies on a fire pump to supply water at high pressure. By maintaining a stable pressure level, it helps ensure that the fire protection system is always ready for use, even during minor pressure variations. Its small size makes it ideal for installations where space is limited, while its high-pressure capabilities ensure reliable performance in both large and small fire protection systems. The jockey pump is designed to operate quietly and efficiently, offering peace of mind to property owners and managers.<br><br>Incorporating the FIRE PRO Jockey Pump into your fire protection system is a smart choice for maintaining system reliability and performance. The jockey pump helps prevent the need for constant system reactivation and maintains optimal water pressure, reducing maintenance costs and increasing the efficiency of the overall system. It is a cost-effective solution for ensuring that your fire protection system remains operational and ready to respond to emergencies.<br></span></p>', 'products/jockey-pump/descriptions/202501-228-77-HloikPafNP.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.683616', '2025-01-23 01:08:07.688296', 228),
(439, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Preaction Alarm Valve Group is designed to work seamlessly with automatic fire detection and alarm technology to provide rapid fire suppression in sensitive environments. This system utilizes preaction, where the sprinkler heads are closed and filled with low-pressure air or nitrogen during testing, ensuring that water is only released when a fire is detected. By integrating automatic detection systems, the preaction valve group minimizes the risk of accidental discharge, making it a valuable solution for locations where water damage could be detrimental.<br><br>In the event of a fire, the system will automatically detect the fire, and the preaction valve group will allow the release of water through the sprinkler heads to suppress the fire. This system&rsquo;s combination of dry-pipe technology and automatic detection helps protect critical assets in places like data centers, museums, and areas with sensitive equipment. The system also ensures minimal downtime, as it is designed for reliability and quick response in the event of an emergency.<br></span></p>', 'products/preaction-alarm-valve-group/descriptions/202501-229-44-qN6oWmDCHm.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.460209', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.465113', 229),
(440, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Preaction Alarm Valve Group is a state-of-the-art solution for fire protection that integrates fire detection and suppression in a unified system. Designed for environments that require both safety and precision, the system operates on a dry-pipe principle, using low-pressure air or nitrogen in the pipes for testing. This minimizes the chances of accidental water discharge while ensuring that the sprinklers remain inactive until a fire is detected by the alarm system.<br><br>Once the fire detection system senses a fire, the preaction valve group releases water into the sprinkler system, activating the sprinklers to suppress the fire effectively. This advanced system is highly efficient in reducing potential water damage while providing an immediate and reliable response to fire threats. Ideal for applications in sensitive locations, the Preaction Alarm Valve Group is designed to enhance the overall safety and protection of valuable assets.</span></p>', 'products/preaction-alarm-valve-group/descriptions/202501-229-55-CQgGWmvgEl.PNG', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.466490', '2025-01-23 01:18:23.469749', 229),
(441, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Outdoor Fire Hydrants are designed to provide an efficient, reliable water source for firefighting needs, even in harsh weather conditions. Constructed with high-quality materials, these hydrants can withstand the rigors of extreme environments, ensuring long-lasting functionality. The system consists of a vertical pipe with an integrated valve mechanism, allowing firefighters to quickly open the valve to access water when needed. Multiple outlets are available for attaching hoses, ensuring that firefighters can efficiently battle fires from various angles.<br><br>These fire hydrants are connected to an underground water distribution network, which is typically supplied by municipal or industrial sources. By providing a ready-to-use, robust water supply, Outdoor Fire Hydrants play a vital role in enhancing fire response times, especially in areas where the infrastructure is more spread out, such as rural or industrial zones. Their design makes them easy to use, while their resilience ensures that they remain operational when the need for water is most urgent.<br></span></p>', 'products/outdoor-fire-hydrants/descriptions/202501-230-44-szD0pK18jk.PNG', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.311758', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.329245', 230),
(442, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Outdoor Fire Hydrants are essential components in the infrastructure of fire protection, providing a quick and reliable water source for firefighting teams during emergencies. These hydrants are constructed from high-strength materials that can endure exposure to varying weather conditions, from freezing temperatures to intense heat, ensuring optimal performance throughout the year. The hydrants feature a simple valve system that allows firefighters to open and close the water supply as needed, with hose outlets designed for easy connection.<br><br>The design of the Outdoor Fire Hydrants ensures that they are straightforward to use, making them invaluable tools for first responders. They offer a crucial link to the underground water network, giving firefighters access to the necessary water supply to fight fires. Whether in urban, industrial, or rural areas, these hydrants are integral to fire safety operations, providing a fast and reliable means of water access for emergency services.<br></span></p>', 'products/outdoor-fire-hydrants/descriptions/202501-230-55-wFnnfQF0K1.PNG', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.333212', '2025-01-24 00:53:27.337198', 230),
(443, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SF400 is a state-of-the-art device that combines time-keeping and access control into one efficient solution. It supports a broad range of authentication methods, including fingerprints and RFID cards, ensuring flexibility and security. With a fingerprint capacity of 1,500 and a card capacity of 5,000, the SF400 is well-suited for organizations of various sizes, from small businesses to large enterprises.<br><br>Its robust logs capacity of 8,000 ensures accurate and reliable data storage for both attendance and access records, minimizing the risk of data loss. Designed with scalability in mind, the SF400 adapts to growing businesses, making it a future-proof investment. Whether installed in offices, factories, or high-security areas, the SF400 delivers consistent performance, even in demanding environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-sf400/descriptions/202501-231-ZK4-554wIhJce2.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:01:19.195478', '2025-01-24 01:15:40.808923', 231),
(444, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">With its intuitive interface and high-speed processing, the SF400 simplifies employee management and facility security. Its ergonomic design and durable construction ensure long-lasting performance. The device allows for easy integration with existing access control systems, providing a seamless transition for businesses looking to upgrade.<br><br>The SF400 supports real-time data synchronization and reporting, enhancing transparency and decision-making. Its multiple authentication options cater to diverse organizational needs, whether prioritizing convenience or heightened security. Equipped with advanced algorithms, the SF400 delivers accurate fingerprint recognition even under challenging conditions, ensuring reliable access control.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-sf400/descriptions/202501-231-ZK7-9eZJZEDQfP.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:01:19.204268', '2025-01-24 01:15:40.812750', 231),
(445, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">SpeedFace V3L is an advanced access control terminal built to enhance security and streamline time-keeping. Featuring dual verification methods&mdash;facial recognition and fingerprint scanning&mdash;it ensures that only authorized individuals can access secure areas. The terminal\'s integration of visible light technology offers a faster and more accurate biometric identification process, while its sophisticated anti-spoofing algorithm provides reliable protection against fraud, including photos and video manipulation attempts.<br><br>With a capacity to store up to 500 facial templates, 3,000 fingerprints, and 3,000 access cards, the SpeedFace V3L is scalable and adaptable to a wide range of organizations. Its ability to store 200,000 logs ensures comprehensive records of access attempts, providing full visibility into personnel movements. Designed for businesses that require high levels of security, this terminal is a powerful and efficient solution for both time-keeping and access control</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v3l/descriptions/202501-232-4_1-bVVTJf25gb.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:04:24.704069', '2025-01-24 01:14:39.639013', 232),
(446, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V3L access control terminal stands out for its user-friendly design and state-of-the-art biometric verification features. Its dual-authentication system provides enhanced security, giving businesses peace of mind knowing that only authorized individuals can gain access. The terminal is particularly suitable for environments where both high security and ease of use are essential. The advanced anti-spoofing algorithm effectively combats any unauthorized attempts to bypass the system using counterfeit images or videos.<br><br>In addition to its security features, the SpeedFace V3L is built for scalability, supporting up to 500 face templates, 3,000 fingerprint records, and 3,000 card credentials. With a log capacity of 200,000 records, this terminal allows businesses to track access events accurately and manage their security systems efficiently. Whether used for time-keeping or access control, the SpeedFace V3L is designed to meet the growing needs of modern enterprises.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v3l/descriptions/202501-232-5-dqyIQQ8lB0.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:04:24.711345', '2025-01-24 01:14:39.641502', 232),
(447, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V5L offers a multi-verification biometric system that includes fingerprint, facial, and palm recognition. It employs intelligent facial recognition algorithms and advanced computer vision technology to ensure accurate and fast verification. The device is equipped with a user capacity of 1,000 users, making it highly efficient for various business sizes. It also has a fingerprint capacity of 1,000, which adds to the versatility and security of the system. With the added benefit of QR code support through the Mobile App, users can authenticate their identity using their smartphones for even more convenience.<br><br>The SpeedFace V5L&rsquo;s design also emphasizes scalability, with the ability to handle up to 150,000 logs, making it a perfect solution for high-traffic environments. It&rsquo;s tailored to meet the demands of modern businesses with fast-paced operations, where time management and security are critical. The multi-verification feature ensures that organizations can choose the best authentication method suited to their needs, whether through facial recognition or fingerprint scanning, making the SpeedFace V5L a highly adaptable and reliable product.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v5l/descriptions/202501-233-4_1-ID3qheUeI1.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.591489', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.596273', 233),
(448, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The SpeedFace V5L is designed for environments that require seamless, fast, and secure access control and time-keeping. The device features an advanced multi-verification system, allowing businesses to use a combination of facial, fingerprint, palm, and QR code verification. This ensures accurate and secure identification, enhancing both safety and convenience for users. With a capacity of 1,000 for each verification method (face, fingerprint, card), the device can easily accommodate a large number of employees, making it suitable for organizations of all sizes.<br><br>One of the standout features of the SpeedFace V5L is its high log capacity, storing up to 150,000 logs. This allows companies to track employee attendance and access history with ease, without worrying about data overflow or system slowdowns. Whether you\'re managing access to restricted areas or ensuring accurate timekeeping, the SpeedFace V5L provides a comprehensive solution that combines reliability with cutting-edge technology.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-speedface-v5l/descriptions/202501-233-7-gZjTNzSMLc.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.597630', '2025-01-24 01:12:49.601277', 233),
(449, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The INBIO PRO PLUS IP-Based Control Panel is engineered to provide exceptional performance for access control applications. Featuring embedded facial and fingerprint authentication, it delivers a comprehensive security solution. The system allows for fast identification, ensuring that only authorized personnel are granted access, while also enabling a seamless user experience. The integration of TCP/IP technology ensures that users can remotely manage access control across both LAN and WAN networks, enhancing flexibility and deployment options.<br><br>With impressive capacity figures, the INBIO PRO PLUS supports up to 100,000 users, offering scalability for growing businesses or larger projects. Its extensive face, fingerprint, card, and QR code support ensures that the system can accommodate a diverse range of access requirements. Additionally, its robust log storage capacity allows for secure data retention of up to 100,000 logs, which is ideal for monitoring and auditing access events in real time.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-inbio-pro-plus/descriptions/202501-234-4_1-AvfTmLf4xC.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.402019', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.406857', 234),
(450, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">INBIO PRO PLUS is a cutting-edge IP-based control panel designed for high-level access management, combining the latest in facial recognition and fingerprint technology. Its embedded biometric features enable accurate and secure authentication, reducing the risk of unauthorized access. This system is built for flexibility, supporting remote management over both local and wide area networks, allowing administrators to easily control access from any location.<br><br>The system&rsquo;s large capacity allows for the registration of up to 100,000 users, 3,000 faces, 20,000 fingerprints, and 100,000 cards and QR codes. This makes it ideal for large organizations or locations requiring a high level of access management. The INBIO PRO PLUS not only enhances security with its robust features but also offers ease of use with efficient, remote management capabilities, making it a top choice for both security professionals and business owners alike.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-inbio-pro-plus/descriptions/202501-234-5-6TLMQ9jYUZ.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.408257', '2025-01-24 01:23:14.412181', 234),
(451, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FR1200 Fingerprint Reader is a state-of-the-art access control device designed to improve security and user identification. It communicates through an RS485 interface, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of biometric access controllers, including the inBIO series and F8 models. This fingerprint reader is specifically engineered to capture detailed fingerprint samples, which are then transferred securely to the connected access control panel. With its IP65-rated construction, the FR1200 is resistant to dust, dirt, and water, making it ideal for use in both indoor and outdoor environments.<br><br>Incorporating cutting-edge fingerprint recognition technology, the FR1200 provides quick and accurate identification for users. Its rugged and durable design ensures it can withstand various weather conditions, from extreme heat to heavy rainfall, without compromising performance. The device is easy to install and integrates effortlessly with existing access control systems. For facilities requiring enhanced security, the FR1200 offers a reliable and efficient solution for controlling access and monitoring entry.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-fr1200/descriptions/202501-235-3_1-h2b1UjwvOn.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.923531', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.929656', 235),
(452, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The FR1200 Fingerprint Reader offers seamless functionality with biometric access controllers and standalone access control systems, making it an excellent choice for organizations seeking to upgrade their security measures. This device captures and transfers fingerprint data, allowing for smooth and secure access management. It&rsquo;s designed for use with a variety of controllers, including the inBIO series, ensuring versatility and broad compatibility. With its RS485 communication interface, it ensures reliable and continuous data transmission, making it a perfect fit for diverse security needs.<br><br>This device is built to endure harsh environmental conditions, with an IP65 rating that provides protection against dust and water ingress. Whether installed in an outdoor gate or an indoor door, the FR1200 guarantees robust performance in any setting. The simple integration process and compatibility with a wide range of biometric solutions make it an attractive option for businesses looking to enhance security protocols. With optional functions for customization, the FR1200 provides flexibility and adaptability for different user requirements.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-fr1200/descriptions/202501-235-6-pt3RyPdjB5.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.936893', '2025-01-24 01:26:29.940919', 235),
(453, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ZL600 Deluxe Design Hotel Lock combines modern technology with robust durability, making it an ideal choice for high-end hotel environments. Crafted from SAE 304 stainless steel, the lock is designed to endure harsh conditions, offering superior resistance to corrosion and wear. It also passed the 96-hour salt spray test, ensuring it remains functional even in the toughest weather conditions. This hotel lock supports the use of IC S50/S70 cards and offers seamless integration with the ZKBioHLMS lock management system.<br><br>With Zigbee communication technology, the ZL600 allows for both local and remote control, offering flexibility for hotel staff to manage access securely and efficiently. The lock\'s easy-to-use smartphone unlocking feature, powered by HTML5 (H5), makes it an excellent solution for modern, tech-savvy guests who expect convenience and security. The lock is powered by four AAA alkaline batteries, providing long-lasting power while minimizing the need for maintenance.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl600/descriptions/202501-236-4_1-tVoDcuGi4L.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.085891', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.090728', 236),
(454, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZL600 Deluxe Design Hotel Lock is built for reliability and ease of use, making it a perfect addition to any modern hotel. Its European Standard Mortise lock body ensures superior security while offering seamless integration with existing hotel management systems. The lock supports IC S50/S70 cards, providing a high level of access control that is simple to use. Whether unlocking doors via smartphone or traditional key cards, the ZL600 ensures a smooth and secure experience for both guests and hotel staff.<br><br>Equipped with Zigbee communication, the ZL600 enables easy management both locally and remotely. This makes it a versatile option for hotels of all sizes, ensuring that access control is always within reach. With a sleek and stylish design, the ZL600 also adds an element of sophistication to any hotel&rsquo;s d&eacute;cor. The lock is powered by four AAA alkaline batteries, offering longevity without the need for frequent replacements.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl600/descriptions/202501-236-5-KgxtXHnDr3.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.092303', '2025-01-24 01:30:48.096685', 236),
(455, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ZL700 Wireless Hotel Lock is an advanced locking solution designed for modern hospitality environments. Made from SAE 304 stainless steel, it provides enhanced durability and resistance to corrosion, ensuring long-lasting reliability. The lock passes the stringent 96-hour salt spray test, a testament to its robustness even in demanding conditions. With a wireless setup, the ZL700 offers ease of installation and flexibility, making it ideal for hotels seeking efficient and scalable security solutions.<br><br>Equipped with the ZKBIOHLMS lock management application, the ZL700 allows hotel administrators to manage access control remotely. The lock is compatible with IC S50/S70 cards, providing secure keyless entry for guests and staff. The power supply is provided by four AAA alkaline batteries, offering long-lasting energy without the need for frequent replacements. The ZL700 is designed to fit doors with a thickness ranging from 36mm to 55mm, offering versatility for a wide variety of door types and sizes.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl700/descriptions/202501-237-4_1-u8V4VUAXmF.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.503539', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.509120', 237),
(456, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The ZL700 Wireless Hotel Lock combines innovative technology with a stylish, modern design to meet the needs of contemporary hotels. It is built from SAE 304 stainless steel, a material known for its resistance to corrosion and long-term durability. The lock has been rigorously tested, passing the 96-hour salt spray test to ensure it performs well in harsh environments. This makes it an ideal choice for both coastal areas and places with high humidity where rust and corrosion are concerns.<br><br>The wireless capabilities of the ZL700 streamline installation and eliminate the need for complex wiring systems. It uses IC S50/S70 cards for secure guest access, providing both security and convenience. Powered by four AAA alkaline batteries, the lock ensures consistent performance with minimal maintenance. The lock is designed to fit a range of door thicknesses, between 36mm and 55mm, making it adaptable for a variety of installations in hotel properties.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zl700/descriptions/202501-237-5-gKNTYyVtfP.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.510804', '2025-01-24 01:34:36.514025', 237),
(457, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The LH6500 SUPER THIN HOTEL LOCK stands out with its innovative 13.56MHz card technology, offering guests a quick and convenient way to access their rooms. Its slim and contemporary design complements the aesthetics of any hotel, while the zinc alloy construction ensures long-lasting performance and resistance to wear and tear. With compatibility for ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, managing guest access and tracking activity becomes efficient and straightforward.<br><br>This advanced door lock is equipped with an American standard mortise, featuring five latches that deliver enhanced security and peace of mind. It supports ISO14443 RFID cards, which are widely recognized for their reliability and ease of use. Designed to fit door thicknesses between 40mm and 50mm, the LH6500 is versatile and easy to install, making it the perfect solution for modern hospitality needs.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6500/descriptions/202501-238-4_1-mk6sADmzir.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.191725', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.196723', 238),
(458, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Engineered for efficiency and elegance, the LH6500 SUPER THIN HOTEL LOCK is a top-tier choice for hotels aiming to elevate their security systems. Its integration with ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software streamlines the management of guest access, room assignments, and audit trails. This feature not only enhances operational efficiency but also offers a more secure and personalized guest experience.<br><br>The lock&rsquo;s premium zinc alloy build provides durability, ensuring it withstands frequent use while retaining its sophisticated appearance. Supporting the ISO14443 RFID card standard, the LH6500 simplifies guest interactions with a reliable and user-friendly system. Its slim profile and compatibility with various door thicknesses make it adaptable to diverse hotel environments, from luxury resorts to boutique accommodations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6500/descriptions/202501-238-5-ONurIRFA0n.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.198360', '2025-01-24 01:37:27.201905', 238),
(459, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The LH6800 Modern Design Hotel Lock redefines guestroom security and convenience with its advanced features and user-friendly design. Its 13.56 MHz Mifare card technology provides fast and secure access, ensuring guest satisfaction and peace of mind. The American standard mortise with 5 latches enhances the lock&rsquo;s durability and security, providing reliable protection for any hotel room. Hoteliers can benefit from the lock&rsquo;s professional management software, designed to simplify the installation process with just a single click, saving valuable time and resources.<br><br>Built from zinc alloy, the LH6800 is engineered for durability and style. Its sleek, modern design seamlessly complements contemporary hotel interiors, while its compatibility with ISO14443 RFID cards enhances accessibility. Supporting ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software, the lock integrates effortlessly with advanced security systems, providing hoteliers with centralized control and real-time monitoring capabilities. The LH6800 is the perfect blend of functionality, style, and innovation.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6800/descriptions/202501-239-4_1-1Ak9dhJ9DR.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.863665', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.869687', 239),
(460, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The LH6800 Modern Design Hotel Lock is tailored for the modern hotelier seeking state-of-the-art security solutions. Its compatibility with advanced ZKBioLock and ZKBioSecurity software enables seamless integration into a broader security ecosystem, ensuring comprehensive control and monitoring. The lock&rsquo;s 13.56 MHz Mifare card technology allows for quick, secure access, enhancing the guest experience while reducing operational complexities.<br><br>Designed for doors with a thickness range of 35mm to 45mm, the LH6800 provides versatility for various installations. The zinc alloy construction guarantees longevity, even in high-traffic environments, while maintaining a polished, professional look. Whether you\'re upgrading an existing system or building a new property, the LH6800 offers the perfect balance of innovation and reliability for your security needs.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-lh6800/descriptions/202501-239-6-KvD7oWgLSV.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.871288', '2025-01-24 01:40:36.874502', 239),
(461, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-S1000 Single-Lane Speed Gate is a premium access control solution from ZKTeco, designed to streamline user entry while providing top-notch security. Its advanced infrared sensor system, with up to 22 pairs of sensors in the Mars-Pro version, ensures that only authorized users are granted access, while preventing tailgating. The sleek, modern design is made for easy integration into a variety of environments, from corporate offices to transportation hubs, offering both style and functionality.<br><br>This system\'s snap-fit, screwless modular design simplifies installation and reduces maintenance time. With its ability to accommodate RFID and biometric readers, the MARS-S1000 is a versatile and future-proof solution for any modern access control needs. The barrier gates open smoothly upon successful authentication and automatically close to prevent unauthorized entry, providing a seamless user experience without compromising on security.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1000-series/descriptions/202501-240-4_1-5rrJOhDlW6.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.862762', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.868747', 240),
(462, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-S1011 Single-Lane Speed Gate, equipped with both a controller and RFID reader, offers an added layer of security and access management. This model is ideal for areas requiring controlled access, such as office buildings or secured zones in airports. By integrating a reliable RFID system, the gate ensures fast and accurate identification, allowing authorized users to pass while keeping unauthorized individuals out.<br><br>The design features a compact and elegant profile that blends with modern architectural styles, while also maintaining high durability and efficiency. The MARS-S1011 is built to withstand heavy use, with smooth gate operations and minimal maintenance requirements. It is also designed with environmental considerations in mind, offering low energy consumption while delivering maximum performance.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1000-series/descriptions/202501-240-5-Pl68rb5feD.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.870285', '2025-01-24 01:52:56.873606', 240),
(463, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-S1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate from ZKTeco is designed for high-traffic environments, offering robust security with a sleek, modern look. The gate features advanced infrared sensors that provide superior anti-tailgate functionality, ensuring that only authorized individuals are granted access. With the creative snap-fit, screwless modularized design, installation and maintenance are streamlined, saving time and reducing operational costs. The system\'s ability to integrate easily with other access control devices, such as RFID and fingerprint readers, ensures that it meets the security needs of any facility.<br><br>This system is available in several configurations to meet varying security requirements, including the MARS-S1200, MARS-S1211 (with RFID controller), and MARS-S1222 (with both RFID and fingerprint readers). The range of models ensures versatility for diverse use cases, whether for building entrances, airports, or commercial spaces. Each model is designed to operate with efficiency, security, and ease, delivering exceptional performance over time.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1200-series/descriptions/202501-241-4_1-DKVBTl0k8z.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.374349', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.379708', 241),
(464, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed to simplify both installation and maintenance, the MARS-S1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate is a game-changer in the access control industry. Featuring up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, the MARS-S1200 significantly reduces the risk of unauthorized access through its superior anti-tailgate technology. The modular design reduces the time required for both setup and upkeep, making it an ideal choice for facilities looking for a high-performance, low-maintenance solution. With easy integration into existing access systems, this speed gate ensures that your security setup can scale with your needs.<br><br>The MARS-S1200 Series is available in three distinct models, each offering unique features to match different security requirements. The MARS-S1200 offers a streamlined design for basic functionality, while the MARS-S1211 and MARS-S1222 models come with additional security features such as RFID controllers and fingerprint readers. These variations offer flexibility, allowing businesses to choose the system that best meets their security needs and future growth.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-s1200-series/descriptions/202501-241-5-E54aGWVALP.PNG', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.381166', '2025-01-24 01:57:43.384712', 241),
(465, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS PRO-S1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate is a state-of-the-art solution engineered for modern security needs. With up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, the Mars Series provides exceptional anti-tailgate capabilities, making it perfect for high-traffic environments that demand enhanced access control. The innovative snap-fit, screwless modular design not only makes installation quicker and more efficient but also allows for hassle-free maintenance, ultimately reducing downtime. This speed gate solution prioritizes both user convenience and security, offering a smooth and secure experience for all users.<br><br>Multiple models within the MARS PRO-S1200 Series cater to different security levels. The PRO-S1200 is ideal for basic, high-performance security, while the PRO-S1211 and PRO-S1222 versions incorporate advanced features such as RFID and fingerprint readers, providing additional layers of authentication. Whether you need a straightforward access control solution or a comprehensive biometric system, the Mars Series offers versatility and innovation for every scenario.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1200-series/descriptions/202501-242-4_1-7HLUH1Qndn.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.649053', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.653964', 242),
(466, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Designed to deliver the highest level of security without compromising on speed or user experience, the MARS PRO-S1200 Series sets a new benchmark for access control technology. The series features ultra-responsive infrared sensors that increase the accuracy and reliability of the system, particularly in preventing unauthorized access or tailgating. The modular, screwless design reduces the time and effort needed for installation, making it a smart choice for businesses that prioritize efficiency and security. With the ability to integrate seamlessly into various existing systems, this gate is a perfect fit for a wide array of security environments.<br><br>Each model in the Mars Series&mdash;whether it\'s the basic PRO-S1200, the PRO-S1211 with an integrated controller and RFID reader, or the PRO-S1222 with both fingerprint and RFID readers&mdash;ensures top-tier performance. The biometric and RFID solutions cater to high-security applications, making the Mars PRO-S1200 Series a versatile and reliable option for a range of professional environments. The system&rsquo;s intelligent technology and aesthetic design make it both functional and a stylish addition to any space.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1200-series/descriptions/202501-242-5-grkC53I5T4.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.655405', '2025-01-24 02:05:50.658412', 242),
(467, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS PRO-S1000 Series is the cutting edge in access control technology, offering a reliable, fast, and secure method for managing foot traffic. With its modular, screwless design, the gate is not only easy to install but also simple to maintain, reducing overall downtime. The series incorporates advanced infrared sensors, enhancing the gate&rsquo;s ability to detect and prevent unauthorized access, making it an ideal solution for high-security areas.<br><br>Available in different configurations, including options with integrated RFID and fingerprint readers, the MARS PRO-S1000 Series allows for versatile customization to meet varying access control needs. Whether for office buildings, commercial facilities, or industrial complexes, this system ensures optimal safety, flexibility, and user convenience.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1000-series/descriptions/202501-243-4_1-sdnCF1aWQW.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.196726', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.201727', 243),
(468, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Built with modern environments in mind, the MARS PRO-S1000 Series offers a streamlined yet highly effective access control system. The high-performance infrared sensors and anti-tailgate technology provide a heightened level of security, detecting even the most subtle unauthorized attempts. Additionally, its modular structure means that upgrades and maintenance are hassle-free, saving both time and resources.<br><br>For businesses seeking a fully integrated solution, the MARS PRO-S1000 Series provides various options with built-in controllers and readers, offering enhanced functionality for managing access points. The addition of RFID and fingerprint reader compatibility ensures that only authorized personnel gain entry, further reinforcing its status as a top-tier security system.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-s1000-series/descriptions/202501-243-7-JNJRb8YKAj.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.203518', '2025-01-24 02:09:43.207616', 243),
(469, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-B1000 Series Speed Gates</strong> from ZKTeco provide superior security and enhanced anti-tailgate features. Equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, this series delivers an exceptional level of performance to prevent unauthorized access. These sensors improve the system&rsquo;s accuracy and response time, ensuring that only one person passes through the gate at a time. With a creative modular design, the MARS-B1000 offers a screwless, snap-fit structure that makes the installation process both faster and easier, saving up to 30% of production lead time. This makes the MARS-B1000 Series perfect for locations requiring high-security measures and efficient operation.<br><br>The MARS-B1000 Series is available in three configurations, catering to different security needs. The base MARS-B1000 offers a straightforward speed gate solution, while the MARS-B1011 model includes an integrated controller and RFID reader for additional access control features. For more secure applications, the MARS-B1022 model combines both RFID and fingerprint readers, offering multifactor authentication for even more reliable entry management. This versatility makes the MARS-B1000 Series ideal for a range of environments, from office buildings to high-security areas, ensuring smooth and secure passage for authorized users.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1000-series/descriptions/202501-244-4_1-gautmKQBYi.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.555701', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.561732', 244),
(470, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-B1000 Series Speed Gate</strong> is built with a focus on integration and ease of use. Its sleek and modern design fits seamlessly into any facility, complementing existing infrastructure while providing advanced security features. The system&rsquo;s infrared sensors are key to enhancing its anti-tailgate performance, making sure that only one person is allowed through the gate at a time. Additionally, the modular design not only reduces installation time but also simplifies future upgrades, enabling organizations to easily adapt to changing security needs.<br><br>With various models available, the MARS-B1000 Series can be customized to meet specific security requirements. The standard MARS-B1000 is ideal for basic access control, while the MARS-B1011 integrates an RFID reader for automated access management. The advanced MARS-B1022 offers both RFID and fingerprint authentication, offering more robust security options for sensitive areas. These configurations, combined with the system\'s quick installation process, provide flexibility and high performance for any security infrastructure.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1000-series/descriptions/202501-244-6-NbR1YBMjSs.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.563500', '2025-01-24 02:26:46.566931', 244),
(471, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-B1200 Series Swing Barrier Speed Gate is a state-of-the-art solution that combines advanced security features with modern design. Engineered to prevent unauthorized access and tailgating, this speed gate incorporates up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors for superior performance. The high precision of these sensors ensures that individuals cannot follow others through the gate without proper authorization. Whether it\'s for a high-traffic area or a secure location, the MARS-B1200 provides reliable and efficient access control.<br><br>Installation and maintenance are simplified thanks to the MARS-B1200&rsquo;s modular and screwless design, enabling easy setup and reducing downtime. Its sleek, modern aesthetic complements any environment, ensuring it enhances the space&rsquo;s appearance while fulfilling its functional requirements. The gate\'s user-friendly interface and integration capabilities allow it to be connected to a range of access control systems, including RFID, fingerprint readers, and more.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1200-series/descriptions/202501-245-4_1-0lwKQh6P8I.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.735373', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.741060', 245),
(472, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-B1200 Series is an optimal choice for organizations that prioritize both security and ease of use. The advanced anti-tailgating feature, powered by infrared sensors, helps ensure that only authorized users pass through the gate, even in high-traffic environments. With options for RFID, fingerprint, and combined readers, the Mars Series can be tailored to suit diverse security needs, allowing for an enhanced user experience.<br><br>The gate\'s design not only supports security but also provides a smooth and efficient passage for authorized individuals. The modular, snap-fit construction reduces installation time and improves serviceability, providing cost savings on maintenance. The various configurations of the MARS-B1200 Series offer flexibility, whether it\'s for a dual-lane application or a more sophisticated security setup with biometric features.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-b1200-series/descriptions/202501-245-7-aznXHKluYq.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.742432', '2025-01-24 02:35:03.745537', 245);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(473, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-F1000 Single-Lane Speed Gate</strong> is a high-performance access control solution designed for a variety of settings. With up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, this gate provides exceptional anti-tailgate capabilities, enhancing overall security. The modular design ensures easy installation and maintenance, reducing lead times by up to 30%. The MARS-F1000 is an excellent choice for locations requiring a fast, secure, and reliable access system without compromising on design or efficiency.<br><br>This model is ideal for single-lane applications where access control needs are streamlined but still require a strong security presence. It integrates seamlessly with existing access control systems and offers users a smooth experience while maintaining a high level of security. The user-friendly design makes it easy to manage, and its performance ensures that traffic flow remains steady without compromising safety.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-f1000-series/descriptions/202501-246-4_1-r1UMcSXynC.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.049006', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.054044', 246),
(474, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS-F1011 Single-Lane Speed Gate</strong> enhances security by incorporating a built-in controller and RFID reader. This model is perfect for environments where access needs to be restricted based on RFID cards or tags, providing an additional layer of control. With 22 pairs of infrared sensors, it offers superior anti-tailgate protection, ensuring only authorized individuals are allowed entry. Its modular and screwless design allows for easy installation and maintenance, making it a great choice for businesses looking to optimize both their security and operational efficiency.<br><br>This version of the MARS-F1000 Series caters to facilities that require RFID-enabled access control, providing quick and secure entry. The integration of an RFID reader ensures that only registered individuals can gain access, further enhancing security. The advanced design minimizes operational downtime and maintenance costs, making it a practical and reliable solution for high-traffic areas</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-f1000-series/descriptions/202501-246-3_1-zVJInoHp6m.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.055721', '2025-01-24 02:41:31.058880', 246),
(475, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-F1200 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate is a sophisticated, high-performance access control system engineered for maximum security and efficiency. Equipped with up to 22 pairs of infrared sensors, the Mars-Pro Series ensures top-tier anti-tailgate protection, preventing unauthorized access and enhancing security. The modularized, snap-fit design allows for easier installation and maintenance, reducing both time and costs significantly. Its sleek and modern design seamlessly integrates into a variety of settings, ensuring that the gates blend well with the surrounding architecture. Whether you\'re managing a corporate office, a government facility, or a high-traffic commercial space, the MARS-F1200 Series delivers the perfect balance of performance, security, and ease of use.<br><br>This system is available in multiple configurations, catering to different needs. The MARS-F1200 Dual-Lane Speed Gate offers efficient control for two lanes, while the MARS-F1211 adds an RFID reader for enhanced security. The MARS-F1222 model goes a step further, integrating both fingerprint and RFID readers, making it suitable for environments requiring higher levels of access control. With its advanced technology and customizable options, the MARS-F1200 Series provides businesses and organizations with a versatile, scalable solution to manage pedestrian traffic and security seamlessly.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-f1200-series/descriptions/202501-247-4_1-4Sj0ICL5Wz.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:50:30.007626', '2025-01-24 02:50:30.013514', 247),
(476, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MARS-F1200 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate is engineered for ultimate user safety and convenience. Featuring advanced infrared sensor technology, the gate ensures robust anti-tailgate capabilities, improving security by accurately detecting unauthorized access attempts. The system&rsquo;s modular design eliminates the need for screws, making installation faster and more cost-effective. Additionally, it supports smooth integration with third-party access control systems, offering flexibility for various environments. Its versatile design is ideal for both indoor and outdoor use, offering a premium solution to organizations aiming to enhance security while maintaining an aesthetically pleasing space.<br><br>The MARS-F1200 Series includes several variations to meet diverse security requirements. The MARS-F1211 version comes equipped with an RFID reader and controller, ideal for environments that require card-based access control. For more advanced needs, the MARS-F1222 integrates both RFID and fingerprint readers, providing a higher level of verification for more secure premises. With its intelligent design and advanced features, the MARS-F1200 Series guarantees reliable, high-performance pedestrian flow management while ensuring maximum security.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-f1200-series/descriptions/202501-247-5-eFQajl8QVu.PNG', '2025-01-24 02:50:30.015248', '2025-01-24 02:50:30.018380', 247),
(477, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-F1000 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> is a sophisticated access control solution designed to enhance security and streamline access management. Featuring 22 pairs of infrared sensors, this system ensures exceptional anti-tailgating performance, preventing unauthorized individuals from gaining access. Its modular design, free of screws, offers quick installation and maintenance, reducing production lead time by up to 30%. The gate&rsquo;s sleek and modern appearance is complemented by a user-friendly interface that makes managing access simple for both operators and users.<br><br>The system&rsquo;s flexible design options cater to a variety of security needs. The MARS PRO-F1011 includes a controller and RFID reader for secure entry and exit, while the MARS PRO-F1022 provides even more robust capabilities with both RFID and fingerprint recognition. These options ensure that organizations can select the best configuration for their specific requirements, whether for high-traffic areas or high-security zones.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-f1000-series/descriptions/202501-248-66-TXELAn9XM4.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.608926', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.614113', 248),
(478, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-F1000 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> is crafted for those seeking advanced security solutions without compromising on ease of use or aesthetics. It integrates advanced infrared technology for highly accurate detection, making it highly effective against tailgating. The series&rsquo; modular construction eliminates screws, making setup and maintenance more efficient, which is a significant time-saver during installation or upgrades. Its superior build quality guarantees reliability and durability, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor applications.<br><br>Offering a range of features, such as the MARS PRO-F1000 for basic single-lane operation, and the MARS PRO-F1011 and MARS PRO-F1022 with additional biometric capabilities, the Mars Pro Series adapts to various security demands. These gates are designed to function smoothly and provide an intuitive user experience, whether in an office building, airport, or other high-traffic locations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-f1000-series/descriptions/202501-248-77-W6CEfpzaUL.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.615869', '2025-01-24 03:02:53.619991', 248),
(479, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The <strong>MARS PRO-F1200 Series</strong> is ZKTeco\'s most advanced flap barrier speed gate, featuring cutting-edge technology and a sleek, modern design. The dual-lane configuration allows efficient and secure passage for multiple users at once, making it perfect for high-traffic areas like corporate offices, government buildings, and transit terminals. With its robust anti-tailgate sensors, the system detects and prevents unauthorized entry, enhancing overall security. The gate operates smoothly, with fast and quiet opening and closing mechanisms to ensure user convenience and comfort. Additionally, the modular, screwless design of the MARS PRO-F1200 Series simplifies installation and reduces maintenance time, offering long-term reliability.<br><br>With integrated infrared sensors and multiple configurations, including models with RFID and fingerprint readers, this product adapts to a variety of access control needs. Whether managing employee entry, visitor access, or secure areas, the MARS PRO-F1200 Series offers a customizable solution. Designed for integration, it works seamlessly with existing security infrastructure, ensuring hassle-free installation and operation. This barrier gate is engineered to maintain high throughput without compromising security, making it an ideal choice for any facility requiring secure, fast access</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-f1200-series/descriptions/202501-249-44-YWFg5G5meg.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.145026', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.150734', 249),
(480, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>MARS PRO-F1200 Series Flap Barrier Speed Gate</strong> provides a high-tech, reliable solution to access control, featuring 22 pairs of infrared sensors to prevent tailgating and unauthorized access. The product is available in different models, including the standard MARS PRO-F1200, and versions with integrated RFID and fingerprint recognition (MARS PRO-F1211 and MARS PRO-F1222). These advanced features offer versatility for a wide range of security requirements, whether for private or public sector use. Its user-friendly design ensures smooth operation and rapid identification of authorized users, improving both efficiency and security.<br><br>Durability and ease of maintenance are at the heart of the MARS PRO-F1200 Series. The modular design eliminates screws, allowing for quick assembly and repairs, which reduces operational downtime. The flap barrier gates are not only functional but aesthetically pleasing, with a contemporary look that fits well in any modern environment. The series&rsquo; fast installation time and integration capabilities make it a leading choice for organizations looking to enhance access control without disruption.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-mars-pro-f1200-series/descriptions/202501-249-77-EUAkYonBtP.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.152483', '2025-01-24 03:12:46.156043', 249),
(481, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS1000 Pro Series Tripod Turnstiles </strong>provide an efficient way to secure entrances and control pedestrian access. Available in three versions&mdash;TS1000, TS1011, and TS1022&mdash;this series offers scalability for different security requirements. The base TS1000 model features a simple yet secure mechanical tripod mechanism, perfect for low to medium-traffic areas requiring basic access control. For enhanced security, the TS1011 model includes an integrated controller and RFID reader, enabling seamless authentication for authorized users.<br><br>The TS1022 version takes it a step further by combining both fingerprint and RFID technology, offering advanced biometric verification. This makes the TS1022 model ideal for high-security environments where identity verification is critical. Regardless of the model chosen, the TS1000 Pro Series is designed to be durable, offering long-lasting performance with minimal maintenance. With their compact footprint and efficient operation, these turnstiles are perfect for a variety of office and commercial applications.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts1000-pro-series/descriptions/202501-250-44-F6O9itFfBI.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.008432', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.014136', 250),
(482, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS1000 Pro Series</strong> is a set of tripod turnstiles engineered for secure, reliable, and efficient access control. These units are built to withstand daily wear and tear, with a robust design that suits both high-traffic and low-traffic applications. Available in different configurations, the TS1000 Pro Series includes models with integrated access control systems, such as the TS1011 with an RFID reader and the TS1022 with both an RFID reader and fingerprint scanning capabilities.<br><br>For businesses requiring a seamless yet secure solution, these turnstiles offer the flexibility to integrate with existing security infrastructure. The advanced features, like RFID and fingerprint verification, provide a higher level of security, ensuring that only authorized individuals are allowed entry. This makes the TS1000 Pro Series a versatile and future-proof option for organizations looking to bolster their security measures without compromising on user experience.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts1000-pro-series/descriptions/202501-250-55-wkBmiZqjL9.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.015562', '2025-01-24 03:22:42.018625', 250),
(483, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS2000 PRO Series Tripod Turnstile </strong>is designed for indoor use, offering reliable and efficient access control. Built for commercial environments such as office buildings, the TS2000 is an affordable and secure solution for managing foot traffic. It ensures that only authorized personnel can access restricted areas, while preventing tailgating and unauthorized entry. Available in different configurations, this turnstile series allows businesses to select the features that best suit their security needs.<br><br>This product is available in three key models: the TS2000 standard model, the TS2011 with an integrated controller and RFID reader, and the TS2022 with a controller and both fingerprint and RFID readers. These variations make the TS2000 PRO Series versatile and adaptable to different security protocols and user preferences, whether you\'re looking for basic RFID access or more advanced biometric authentication.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts2000-pro-series/descriptions/202501-251-33-8f5vV08X56.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.728982', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.734973', 251),
(484, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>TS2000 PRO Series Tripod Turnstile</strong> combines practicality with enhanced security features to protect your premises. Its robust construction makes it a durable choice for controlling access in high-traffic areas while maintaining smooth operation. The turnstile\'s tripod design minimizes space requirements, making it ideal for environments where space is at a premium. Whether you need a simple control mechanism or a more complex system, the TS2000 provides a scalable solution that meets various security standards.<br><br>Each model in the TS2000 PRO Series can be customized with different access control options. The TS2011 model incorporates RFID readers for fast and contactless entry, while the TS2022 goes a step further with fingerprint scanning for biometric verification. With these features, the TS2000 PRO Series ensures both security and convenience for employees, visitors, and other authorized individuals.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ts2000-pro-series/descriptions/202501-251-55-LBg5KlogXC.PNG', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.736365', '2025-01-24 03:38:27.739637', 251),
(485, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D1065 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> is designed to deliver comprehensive security without compromising ease of use. Its six detection zones provide detailed scanning capabilities, allowing for the precise detection of metals on multiple parts of the body. Whether you\'re securing an event or screening employees and guests, this detector&rsquo;s 100 adjustable sensitivity levels ensure reliable performance in any situation. The high-sensitivity function can detect even small metal objects, offering peace of mind for users and security teams alike.<br><br>With a 3.5&rdquo; LCD display, the ZK-D1065 provides clear and easy-to-read data in real-time, displaying the number of people passing through as well as alarm events. The detector\'s synchronized sound and LED alarm system provide immediate alerts, making it easier for security personnel to respond quickly to potential threats. The intuitive design and advanced technology of the ZK-D1065 make it a valuable addition to any security infrastructure.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d1065/descriptions/202501-252-44-8bAMm9D41K.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.139961', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.147545', 252),
(486, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\"> The <strong>ZK-D1065 Walk-Through Metal Detector </strong>is built for maximum efficiency, with a sleek design that blends seamlessly into high-traffic areas. The metal detector features 6 independent detection zones, each capable of detecting different metallic objects with precision, ensuring that no hidden threats are overlooked. Its 100 sensitivity levels give users full control over the device&rsquo;s performance, allowing for a tailored approach to security. Whether it&rsquo;s a low-risk area or a high-alert environment, the detector adapts to meet specific needs.<br><br>Additionally, the ZK-D1065&rsquo;s synchronization of sound and LED alarms creates a dual-alert system that ensures immediate response from security personnel. The integrated counting function keeps track of the number of people passing through, which can be especially helpful in crowded areas. With its user-friendly interface and efficient operation, the ZK-D1065 offers both reliability and convenience for securing sensitive areas, making it a top choice for venues and organizations that prioritize safety.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d1065/descriptions/202501-252-66-52oRjW09Ur.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.149285', '2025-01-24 08:04:35.152832', 252),
(487, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D2180 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> offers state-of-the-art security with 18 individual detection zones, each customizable to suit specific screening needs. Whether it\'s detecting small metallic objects or large metal masses, this metal detector\'s 256 sensitivity levels allow for precise and tailored security configurations. The 3.5\" LCD display provides clear, real-time data for both security personnel and operators, ensuring that <strong>the</strong> screening process runs smoothly. People and alarm counting features further assist in managing crowd control and monitoring the effectiveness of the device.<br><br>This high-tech detector is designed to operate seamlessly with external systems. It supports TCP/IP communication, allowing the detector to be monitored and controlled remotely, even from a central location. The system also includes synchronous sound and LED alarms, ensuring that security staff are immediately alerted in case of any threats. With its ability to integrate with turnstiles and mobile apps, the ZK-D2180 offers flexibility and convenience for modern security setups, making it a top choice for organizations requiring a high level of protection.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d2180/descriptions/202501-253-44-NWspcHkE6x.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.420050', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.426207', 253),
(488, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The ZK-D2180 Walk-Through Metal Detector is engineered to meet the demands of high-security environments, providing an advanced, reliable solution for screening large volumes of people. Its 18 detection zones allow for detailed scanning, and the 256 adjustable sensitivity levels ensure that even the smallest metallic items can be detected. The 3.5\" LCD display provides an easy-to-read interface, while the built-in people and alarm counting functions offer real-time tracking of the security process. This feature is invaluable for organizations that require detailed access and event monitoring.<br><br>Enhanced with both synchronous sound and LED alarms, the ZK-D2180 guarantees that alerts are timely and clear, ensuring prompt responses from security teams. Furthermore, the device supports integration with turnstiles, ensuring smooth access control. For added convenience, it also connects with mobile apps, offering remote management capabilities that are essential in today&rsquo;s tech-driven security environment. These features make the ZK-D2180 the ideal solution for facilities that require high efficiency and accuracy in metal detection</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d2180/descriptions/202501-253-55-FY0BcN9kPz.PNG', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.428052', '2025-01-24 08:18:13.432201', 253),
(489, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZK-D3180 Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> offers an exceptional level of security with its 18 detection zones, providing comprehensive screening for a wide range of environments. With 500 sensitivity levels, the detector can be adjusted to accommodate different security needs, ensuring accuracy in identifying metallic objects. The 7-inch LCD display provides real-time information on detection status, alarm counts, and people count, giving operators immediate insights into security conditions.<br><br>Designed for high-traffic areas, this metal detector is made from fireproof materials, ensuring reliability in case of emergencies. The ZK-D3180 is safe for human use, with no harmful radiation or effects, making it suitable for various public places. Additionally, the detector\'s excellent anti-interference capabilities ensure smooth operation without disruptions, maintaining high performance even in environments with significant electromagnetic interference.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180/descriptions/202501-254-33-OFQL1QmOUM.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.197888', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.203584', 254),
(490, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZK-D3180</strong> is equipped with advanced technology for accurate detection and effective monitoring. Its ability to count both people and alarms helps operators keep track of security events and manage crowd control. The detector features a synchronous sound and LED alarm system, providing clear and immediate alerts when potential threats are detected. This ensures that security staff can respond quickly and appropriately to any situation.<br><br>The remote control feature allows for easy adjustments, making it simple to configure sensitivity levels and other settings without requiring physical interaction with the unit. This walk-through metal detector is designed to meet the security needs of a wide range of industries, from airports to government buildings, offering high performance, ease of use, and comprehensive coverage</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180/descriptions/202501-254-77-3YTD992Plr.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.205986', '2025-01-27 01:03:15.210691', 254),
(491, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D3180S TD Walk-Through Metal Detector</strong> is designed to provide comprehensive security solutions in environments that require high levels of public safety. It features 18 detection zones and allows for 500 adjustable sensitivity levels, making it highly customizable for different types of environments. Whether in airports, shopping centers, or government buildings, this metal detector ensures that any metallic objects on a person will be detected effectively. This functionality is enhanced by its ability to integrate body temperature measurement, which is crucial in the current global health climate.<br><br>This advanced detector provides a dual function of metal detection and health screening. It accurately measures body temperature at the forehead and wrist, helping to identify individuals who may have elevated body temperatures, a key indicator of illness. If the temperature exceeds the threshold of 37.3&deg;C, an alarm is triggered, ensuring swift action from security personnel. With these advanced features, the ZK-D3180S TD Walk-Through Metal Detector not only contributes to security but also supports health and hygiene protocols in crowded and high-traffic environments.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180s-td/descriptions/202501-255-55-9yiAYfGF8Q.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.462080', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.467359', 255),
(492, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D3180S</strong> is built with both security and user-friendliness in mind, offering a sleek 7&rdquo; LCD display that provides clear and easy-to-read information. Security personnel can track the number of people passing through the detector and monitor any triggered alarms with ease. The detector also counts the number of individuals who pass through, allowing for more efficient monitoring and crowd control. This feature is particularly beneficial in situations where accurate data is crucial, such as managing large public gatherings or ensuring safe entry points in critical infrastructure.<br><br>Additionally, the synchronized sound and LED alarm system ensures that any security or health-related threats are immediately brought to attention. The combination of visual and auditory alerts provides a multi-sensory approach to identifying and responding to potential issues. Whether it&rsquo;s detecting metallic objects or identifying health concerns, the ZK-D3180S ensures that security personnel are equipped with real-time information, making it an indispensable tool for modern safety protocols.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d3180s-td/descriptions/202501-255-77-y4ShneDLpt.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.468858', '2025-01-27 01:15:22.472023', 255),
(493, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D100S Portable Metal Detector</strong> is an essential tool for any security-conscious environment, offering reliable detection capabilities for a variety of contraband materials. Whether used in factories to prevent the loss of valuable objects or in educational settings to detect mobile phones and electronic cheat tools, the ZK-D100S delivers consistent and precise results. The combination of sound and light alarms ensures that security personnel are immediately alerted to any potential threats.<br><br>This metal detector is designed with both functionality and portability in mind. Its compact dimensions make it easy to handle and move between locations, while its waterproof rating (IP31) ensures it performs well under varying environmental conditions. Equipped with an operating voltage range of 7V-9V, it is energy-efficient and capable of sustained use without frequent recharging or maintenance.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d100s/descriptions/202501-256-44-Ta72dcpVg2.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.976187', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.986585', 256),
(494, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZK-D100S</strong> is a versatile metal detector that can be used in a variety of settings, including factories, security checkpoints, and schools. It is particularly valuable in preventing the entry of prohibited items such as weapons, mobile phones, and cheat tools. Its dual alarm system&mdash;comprising both sound and light alerts&mdash;makes it easy for security staff to identify threats and take appropriate action immediately.<br><br>Built to withstand daily wear and tear, the ZK-D100S is designed for longevity, with a durable build and an IP31 waterproof rating. The detector&rsquo;s 7V-9V operating voltage ensures reliability and efficiency, allowing it to function for extended periods without requiring excessive power. With its user-friendly design, it can be easily integrated into existing security procedures to enhance safety and prevent unauthorized access or theft.<br><br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zk-d100s/descriptions/202501-256-66-batUGK1gp3.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.989307', '2025-01-27 01:23:28.996201', 256),
(495, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX5030C Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is engineered to provide superior detection and analysis capabilities. Featuring a dual energy X-ray generator, this device ensures high-quality imaging with precise differentiation between materials. The scanner&rsquo;s superior imaging capabilities are powered by an advanced image algorithm that produces clear, true-color scanning results, giving operators a detailed view of scanned contents. This allows for faster identification of potentially hazardous or prohibited items in carry-on baggage, briefcases, and small parcels. The high-definition scanning images also make it easier to distinguish between harmless items and those that may pose a security risk.<br><br>The ZKX5030C incorporates a highly efficient biometric identification system to enhance security and user convenience. This feature ensures that only authorized personnel can operate the device, significantly reducing the risk of unauthorized access or security breaches. Additionally, the scanner&rsquo;s ergonomic design promotes long-term use without discomfort, optimizing the operator&rsquo;s performance during extended shifts. Combined with an energy-saving mode that reduces the device&rsquo;s power consumption when not in active use, the ZKX5030C provides a sustainable and user-friendly solution for security inspections. The intuitive interface and reliable performance make it an invaluable tool for businesses and institutions in need of a secure, high-quality X-ray scanning system.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030c/descriptions/202501-257-66-2FRHokeDNY.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.841385', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.847368', 257),
(496, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX5030C</strong> X-ray inspection system is designed to meet the demanding requirements of security professionals who need fast, accurate, and detailed analysis of baggage and cargo. The scanner\'s dual energy X-ray technology enhances image contrast, helping to reveal the materials inside the scanned objects more clearly. This is especially crucial when inspecting small cargo parcels, briefcases, or carry-on luggage where quick identification of potential threats is necessary. With a focus on providing high-definition scanning images, the ZKX5030C supports faster and more accurate decision-making, improving security operations and helping to avoid security breaches.<br><br>In addition to its cutting-edge scanning capabilities, the ZKX5030C X-ray scanner is built with an ergonomic design that helps reduce strain and fatigue for the operator, making it ideal for high-volume inspection tasks. Its user-friendly interface, combined with a series of intuitive control features, allows for easy handling and quick training for security staff. Moreover, the scanner features an energy-saving mode that minimizes power usage, making it an environmentally responsible choice for long-term operation. The combination of superior imaging, efficient security features, and ergonomic design makes the ZKX5030C an ideal solution for a wide range of security scanning applications.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030c/descriptions/202501-257-55-EBVKg57bb2.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.849019', '2025-01-27 01:50:30.852467', 257),
(497, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The Z<strong>KX5030A Single Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is built with cutting-edge technology to enhance threat detection and improve security operations. With its high-quality single-energy X-ray generator, the scanner delivers clear, precise images that enable operators to identify hazardous materials or prohibited items quickly and efficiently. This inspection system is perfect for use in locations where small parcels, briefcases, and carry-on luggage need to be screened regularly, such as airports, customs checkpoints, and cargo facilities. Its ergonomic design ensures ease of use, reducing operator fatigue during extended shifts and improving overall operational efficiency.<br><br>The ZKX5030A scanner integrates advanced pseudo-color image processing technology that enhances the visibility of suspicious items. The scanner\'s versatility allows it to handle various package types, from small parcels to personal items, making it an ideal choice for facilities with diverse security screening needs. The system\'s user-friendly interface and precise scanning capabilities ensure that operators can quickly assess potential threats and take necessary actions. Additionally, the energy-saving mode reduces power consumption, making it an environmentally responsible option for energy-conscious businesses.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030a/descriptions/202501-258-44-S5ChdskOBf.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.714264', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.719524', 258),
(498, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">he <strong>ZKX5030A Single Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> combines sophisticated imaging algorithms with a modern, ergonomic design to provide a highly effective security solution. Its ability to generate detailed, pseudo-colored X-ray images ensures operators can visually identify potentially dangerous items with clarity and accuracy. This scanner\'s compact form is optimized for small spaces while maintaining the highest standards of threat detection performance. Its simple, intuitive controls allow operators to focus on identifying threats rather than navigating complex settings or systems.<br><br>With the capability to scan small packages, briefcases, and carry-on baggage, the ZKX5030A provides comprehensive coverage for a variety of applications. The energy-saving mode extends the lifespan of the device while lowering overall energy consumption, offering a cost-effective, sustainable solution for security screening. Whether used in high-traffic airports or other security-sensitive environments, the ZKX5030A ensures the safety and efficiency of daily operations.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx5030a/descriptions/202501-258-55-BYkaNKEnpv.PNG', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.721063', '2025-01-27 01:58:43.725362', 258),
(499, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX6040 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a state-of-the-art security device that uses dual-energy X-ray technology to inspect baggage and parcels. It is equipped with a powerful penetration capacity, capable of scanning materials up to 35mm of steel thickness. This allows the system to identify a wide range of materials with high accuracy. The scanner&rsquo;s large tunnel opening of 600mm by 400mm accommodates a variety of bag sizes, making it highly adaptable to different security needs. ZKX6040 employs advanced algorithms to classify materials based on their atomic numbers, which helps detect both organic and inorganic substances effectively.<br><br>Designed for portability and ease of use, the ZKX6040 features a foldable keyboard, allowing for flexible deployment in various settings, from hotels and offices to transportation hubs. Its high mobility makes it a versatile solution for locations requiring temporary or mobile security checkpoints. With an intuitive user interface and advanced image display capabilities, operators can quickly assess potential threats or anomalies. The scanner&rsquo;s ability to display cluttered bag images further enhances its functionality by helping security personnel to easily identify suspicious items in complex baggage scenarios.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6040/descriptions/202501-259-44-ZPwTwvclSN.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.504250', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.510434', 259),
(500, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6040 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is a comprehensive solution for modern security requirements, combining cutting-edge X-ray technology with user-friendly design. Featuring a robust steel penetration of up to 35mm, it provides deep inspection capabilities for a wide range of objects. The 600mm by 400mm tunnel opening allows for the scanning of large items, making it ideal for use in diverse environments such as airports, government offices, and hotels. The dual-energy X-ray system ensures high-resolution images, while its ability to differentiate materials based on atomic numbers enhances the detection of potential threats, whether organic or inorganic.<br><br>In addition to its impressive technical specifications, the ZKX6040 is designed with practicality in mind. The foldable keyboard offers ease of storage and transport, enhancing the system&rsquo;s portability and flexibility. Operators can utilize the fingerprint verification feature to ensure that only authorized personnel can access the scanner, adding an extra layer of security. The roller conveyor system simplifies the handling of baggage, making the ZKX6040 a valuable tool for high-traffic areas. With its high accuracy, ease of use, and secure operation, the ZKX6040 is an essential component for any security operation looking to enhance its baggage inspection capabilities.<br></span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6040/descriptions/202501-259-55-SJ2uF9BMDX.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.512962', '2025-01-27 02:14:43.516733', 259),
(501, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550A SINGLE ENERGY X-RAY SCANNER</strong> is engineered to provide an economical yet effective solution for the visual inspection of carry-on luggage. Featuring a dependable X-ray generator, it delivers clear and detailed images, allowing security personnel to quickly spot potential threats. The advanced image algorithm incorporated into the system ensures that even the smallest anomalies are highlighted, facilitating fast and accurate identification. With the added benefit of bi-directional scanning, operators can inspect items from different angles, improving the versatility and effectiveness of the scanner.<br><br>Designed with security in mind, the ZKX6550A includes a biometric fingerprint identification system that ensures only authorized users can operate the machine, enhancing overall safety. The ergonomic design of the scanner not only helps operators maintain efficiency and comfort during long shifts but also increases the speed at which items can be checked. Whether in airports, offices, or other high-security areas, the ZKX6550A is an ideal solution for streamlining carry-on luggage screening.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550a/descriptions/202501-260-55-D6u9Fv43Nk.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.900368', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.905313', 260),
(502, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550A SINGLE ENERGY X-RAY SCANNER</strong> is built to meet the rigorous demands of security screening while providing exceptional ease of use. It utilizes a top-quality X-ray generator that ensures clear, high-resolution images for precise identification of potentially dangerous items. The system&rsquo;s pseudo-color scanning capability enhances visual clarity by providing enhanced contrast and better distinction of materials, which aids in detecting suspicious objects with greater accuracy. The bi-directional scanning function offers flexible orientations for effective inspection, making the device suitable for various security environments.<br><br>Security is further enhanced by the innovative fingerprint identification feature, ensuring that only authorized personnel can operate the system, effectively preventing unauthorized access. This function contributes to a secure and efficient screening process, as operators can quickly authenticate their identity, reducing the risk of security breaches. Combining modern technology with user-friendly features, the ZKX6550A is the ideal choice for any setting requiring reliable and efficient carry-on baggage inspection.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550a/descriptions/202501-260-66-DgRvBcErvf.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.907151', '2025-01-27 02:24:02.910855', 260),
(503, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> provides unparalleled imaging quality for detecting potential threats in carry-on baggage, briefcases, and small cargo parcels. Featuring dual energy X-ray technology, it enhances the clarity of scanned items, helping operators easily identify concealed threats. Equipped with a high-quality X-ray generator and sophisticated image algorithms, this system ensures fast and precise scanning of various objects. The system\'s true-color imaging offers vivid and accurate representations of scanned items, significantly improving operator efficiency. In addition, the ZKX6550&rsquo;s bi-directional scanning capability allows for versatile scanning operations from both directions, ensuring optimal flexibility for different scanning environments.<br><br>With a focus on operator security, the ZKX6550 also integrates a biometric fingerprint identification system. This innovative feature provides an additional layer of security, ensuring that only authorized personnel can operate the machine. The scanner\'s ergonomic design reduces operator strain, allowing for long hours of scanning without discomfort. Combined with its superior imaging technology, biometric security, and user-friendly design, the ZKX6550 is the ideal solution for high-security operations requiring fast and accurate threat detection.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550/descriptions/202501-261-55-m6Uo8U4fPd.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.380271', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.385506', 261),
(504, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550 </strong>X-ray inspection system is engineered to optimize threat detection for a wide range of security screening environments. The scanner\'s dual energy X-ray technology produces high-quality images with exceptional clarity, enabling operators to clearly differentiate between materials with varying densities. Whether scanning carry-on luggage or small cargo, this system helps detect weapons, explosives, and other dangerous items with precision. The addition of true-color imaging ensures that items are displayed with vivid clarity, improving accuracy and reducing the likelihood of missing potential threats.<br><br>One of the standout features of the ZKX6550 is its fingerprint identification function, which enhances security by preventing unauthorized access to the system. This biometric feature ensures that only authorized users can operate the machine, enhancing overall security protocols. Furthermore, the ergonomic design of the system ensures that operators can work efficiently without strain, even in high-pressure environments. The ZKX6550 is designed to offer both high performance and ease of use, making it an ideal solution for locations that require fast and accurate security checks.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550/descriptions/202501-261-66-bEyfaySAPj.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.388452', '2025-01-27 02:31:21.392453', 261),
(505, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550D Dual Energy X-Ray Scanne</strong>r offers a state-of-the-art approach to security screening with its innovative dual-view technology. The scanner uses two independent generators, providing both horizontal and vertical images for a more thorough inspection of objects. This dual imaging system enhances detection capabilities by offering detailed views of items, ensuring that potential threats are identified swiftly and accurately. The scanner\'s ability to differentiate between organic and inorganic materials, as well as mixtures, allows for precise identification of suspicious substances, reducing the likelihood of overlooking dangerous objects.<br><br>One of the standout features of the ZKX6550D is its ability to identify overlapping items with ease. This technology allows operators to accurately distinguish between items that might otherwise appear as one due to their proximity. The scanner\'s effectiveness is further enhanced by its dual monitor operation desk, where operators can view both perspectives of the scan simultaneously. This feature ensures that no potential threat goes unnoticed, improving security while maintaining a streamlined screening process.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550d/descriptions/202501-262-44-MWnSCIygjz.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.594768', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.601877', 262),
(506, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX6550D </strong>is designed for versatility and reliability in high-security environments. Equipped with bi-directional scanning, the device offers flexible inspection angles, making it ideal for scanning carry-on baggage and other items in transit. This feature ensures that all items are thoroughly inspected, regardless of their orientation. The ZKX6550D is particularly valuable in environments like airports, government facilities, and transportation hubs, where the need for quick, accurate scans is critical.<br><br>With the capability to analyze both horizontal and vertical images simultaneously, the scanner reduces the time required for inspection without compromising on accuracy. It provides comprehensive threat detection by differentiating between various materials based on their atomic composition. The ZKX6550D ensures security teams can make informed decisions quickly, minimizing delays while maximizing safety and efficiency</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx6550d/descriptions/202501-262-55-BUYdMozj2o.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.603700', '2025-01-27 02:38:22.607224', 262),
(507, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX10080 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner </strong>is a highly efficient security inspection system designed for scanning large bags and parcels. It offers a scanning area of up to 100 &times; 80 cm, making it suitable for a variety of applications such as airports, shipping centers, and large public venues. With the use of a high-quality dual-energy X-ray generator, the ZKX10080 provides clear, high-resolution images, allowing operators to accurately detect potential threats. The device\'s superb image algorithm improves visual clarity, enabling better identification of hazardous items.<br><br>The scanner&rsquo;s design includes a lowered conveyor height, allowing for easier luggage loading, making it more user-friendly. To enhance security, the ZKX10080 integrates biometric identification for operators, preventing unauthorized access. Additionally, the foldable conveyor design allows for reduced volume during storage and transport, helping organizations save on transportation costs. A modern side door design makes maintenance simple and convenient, ensuring the system is always ready for use.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx10080/descriptions/202501-263-66-EaYiGH5E7R.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.282289', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.287394', 263),
(508, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> ZKX10080 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanne</strong>r stands out with its comprehensive security features, including bi-directional scanning and adjustable belt speed, which ensure optimal scanning performance. The scanner is capable of screening both large and small items, making it versatile enough to handle a wide range of inspection needs. The dual-energy technology further enhances the ability to detect materials that are difficult to distinguish using traditional methods. This makes the ZKX10080 a reliable choice for high-security environments such as government buildings, airports, and high-traffic public venues.<br><br>The scanner&rsquo;s innovative biometric identity system provides an additional layer of security, ensuring that operators are authenticated before they can use the system. This reduces the risk of unauthorized access and ensures that sensitive security information remains protected. With its easy-to-maintain design and space-saving features, the ZKX10080 is a practical solution for businesses and organizations looking to increase their security while maintaining operational efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx10080/descriptions/202501-263-55-dusErbOj6D.PNG', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.288800', '2025-01-27 02:49:06.293175', 263),
(509, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX100100 Dual Energy X-Ray Scanner</strong> is engineered to offer high-resolution imaging for superior threat detection. By using a dual-energy X-ray generator, the scanner provides operators with a clear and detailed view of the contents of luggage, parcels, or other scanned objects. This clarity enhances the identification of potential threats, ensuring safety and security in high-traffic environments. The system&rsquo;s advanced image algorithm further refines the visuals, highlighting areas of concern and aiding in quick decision-making.<br><br>In addition to its powerful scanning capabilities, the ZKX100100 is designed with operator convenience in mind. The lowered conveyor height allows for easy loading of luggage, making it accessible to a wide range of operators. This design reduces physical strain and increases the overall speed of operations. The inclusion of biometric identification ensures that only authorized personnel can operate the system, providing a layer of security and accountability. Overall, the ZKX100100 offers a balance of advanced technology and user-friendly features for optimal threat detection.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx100100/descriptions/202501-264-44-XoxGn1hV6i.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.108973', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.114674', 264);
INSERT INTO `aa2000_admin_productdescription` (`id`, `product_description`, `product_image`, `created_at`, `modified_at`, `product_id`) VALUES
(510, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKX100100 </strong>X-ray scanner is a highly reliable and efficient solution for large-scale baggage and parcel screening. With its adjustable belt speed, the system is adaptable to different volumes of scanned items, allowing operators to adjust the speed according to their workload. The foldable conveyor design makes storage and transport more convenient, ensuring that the scanner can fit seamlessly into different operational spaces. The ZKX100100 also offers dual monitor operation, which enhances the user experience by providing operators with more screen real estate for detailed analysis of scanned objects.<br><br>Ergonomically designed for ease of use, the ZKX100100 reduces the physical strain on operators during long shifts. Its advanced features, including biometric identification and intuitive controls, work together to streamline the security process. With its high-quality scanning capabilities and thoughtful design, the ZKX100100 provides an ideal solution for security professionals looking to enhance their screening process while maintaining a high level of efficiency and accuracy.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-zkx100100/descriptions/202501-264-55-WP2lycucnk.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.116914', '2025-01-27 03:00:57.120884', 264),
(511, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The BLADE6040 Dual Energy X-ray Scanner is an advanced security device tailored for baggage inspection. With its 610*420mm tunnel size, it allows for the efficient screening of various items, including luggage, mail, and handheld bags. The scanner leverages dual energy X-ray technology to distinguish between materials based on their atomic number, helping operators quickly detect and identify potential threats such as explosives, firearms, and toxic substances. This process streamlines the security workflow, minimizing delays while maximizing safety.<br><br>Its high-quality imaging system enables the clear visualization of both organic and inorganic materials, making it an indispensable tool for security teams. The inclusion of automatic identification features further accelerates the detection process by highlighting suspicious objects, allowing operators to make informed decisions swiftly. This combination of speed and accuracy ensures a smooth, secure, and efficient baggage screening process in high-traffic areas.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-blade6040/descriptions/202501-265-66-54SSS74nb6.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.732603', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.738445', 265),
(512, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The BLADE6040 scanner stands out with its superior steel penetration, capable of identifying threats hidden behind up to 35mm of steel (with typical penetration up to 40mm). This feature ensures that even the most well-concealed hazardous materials are detected. Moreover, the system is equipped with four layers of lead curtain shielding, which enhances safety for operators by reducing radiation exposure during screening. The dual energy scanning system provides a detailed view of items, improving threat detection without compromising efficiency.<br><br>Built to operate in demanding security environments, the BLADE6040 X-ray Scanner is equipped with an uninterruptible power supply, ensuring continuous operation even in the event of power failures. This makes it a reliable choice for critical applications where downtime could pose significant risks. Whether used in airports, government facilities, or other high-security locations, the BLADE6040 delivers consistent performance and superior safety, offering peace of mind in every inspection.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-blade6040/descriptions/202501-265-55-uvv4BW5NEH.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.740101', '2025-01-27 03:06:48.743448', 265),
(513, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> PB4000 Series Telescopic Parking Barrier </strong>is built to meet the demanding needs of vehicle access control with an innovative and durable design. Constructed from die-casting aluminum alloy, it features a robust motor and advanced structural integrity that ensure the barrier will provide reliable service for years. The system is engineered to minimize maintenance needs, offering a cost-effective solution for managing high-traffic areas. With multiple boom options, the PB4000 series can be customized for specific requirements, providing flexibility for both small and large installations.<br><br>One of the key highlights of the PB4000 Series is its telescopic boom, which offers a compact solution for areas where space is limited. Additionally, the PB4130 3M 90&deg; Folding Boom and PB4030-LED 4M Straight Boom with LED provide enhanced versatility, allowing for easier integration into various environments. The LED option is especially beneficial for enhancing visibility in low-light conditions, improving safety and efficiency. The barrier\'s long lifecycle and superior reliability make it an investment that reduces operational costs over time, ensuring smooth management of vehicle access points.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-pb4000-series/descriptions/202501-266-33-xgLPtruBRx.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.161268', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.167319', 266),
(514, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>PB4000 Series Telescopic Parking Barrier </strong>is ideal for securing vehicle entrances and controlling access points with ease. It boasts exceptional build quality, with a die-casting aluminum alloy motor that provides not only longevity but also minimizes the need for frequent maintenance. Designed for high reliability, this barrier is well-suited for a variety of applications, including residential complexes, commercial spaces, and industrial environments. Its motor and structural design ensure a smooth operation even in high-traffic situations, contributing to an overall secure and efficient parking management solution.<br><br>In addition to its durability, the PB4000 Series is equipped with versatile boom options such as the PB4060 6M Telescopic Boom, ideal for wider entrances. The inclusion of LED lighting in the PB4030-LED model also enhances the system\'s functionality by providing visibility at night or in dark conditions. Whether you\'re looking for a compact or extended solution, the PB4000 Series can accommodate your needs. It is a long-term investment that delivers quality, dependability, and ease of use.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-pb4000-series/descriptions/202501-266-44-9yo7VnZJ8l.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.168879', '2025-01-27 03:36:04.171912', 266),
(515, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UHF 10 Series Long Distance Card Reader System</strong> is a versatile, high-performance solution for various management applications. Designed for use in personnel, goods, and vehicle management systems, the UHF 10 series offers an impressive reading range of up to 12 meters. This allows for efficient access control without the need for close-range scanning, enhancing workflow and productivity. The system is built to withstand a wide range of environmental conditions, with an IP66-rated weatherproof enclosure that protects it from water, dust, and other environmental factors.<br><br>Its low working current and stable performance make the UHF 10 Series an energy-efficient choice for long-term operation. The reader is designed for ease of installation and maintenance, with a maximum cable distance of 100 meters, providing flexibility in setup across large facilities. The Wiegand 26-bit interface ensures compatibility with various access control systems, making the UHF 10 Series a versatile addition to any security infrastructure</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-uhf-10-series/descriptions/202501-267-44-oAXQxsZekA.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.192973', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.198190', 267),
(516, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UHF 10 Series Card Reader System</strong> is ideal for businesses looking for reliable and long-distance access control. It supports a wide range of applications, including personnel management, goods tracking, and vehicle access, ensuring that security and operational workflows remain streamlined and secure. With a powerful read range of up to 12 meters, the UHF 10 series allows for seamless entry without requiring users to approach the reader closely. Additionally, its waterproof, weatherproof design ensures that the reader can operate effectively in even the most challenging environmental conditions, including extreme temperatures, humidity, and outdoor exposure.<br><br>With low power consumption and a long service life, the UHF 10 Series minimizes the need for frequent maintenance and replacement. The reader&rsquo;s Wiegand 26-bit interface ensures broad compatibility with existing security systems. This allows businesses to integrate the reader into their current infrastructure without requiring costly upgrades. Whether used for controlling access to a facility or tracking inventory and vehicles, the UHF 10 Series provides a robust and cost-effective solution.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-uhf-10-series/descriptions/202501-267-77-A7nMDQ9BKX.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.199809', '2025-01-27 03:44:54.203348', 267),
(517, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>UR20RW-F UHF Card Issue Reader</strong> is engineered for businesses seeking reliable and high-performance solutions for UHF tag and card management. It provides the ability to read and write data for both the User Area and EPC Area of UHF tags, ensuring complete versatility for different tracking and identification systems. With its easy-to-use USB interface, the UR20RW-F eliminates the need for complicated installation processes, offering a seamless plug-and-play experience with no drivers required. This makes it an ideal choice for users who need quick and hassle-free setup.<br><br>This reader supports the EPC global UHF Class1 Gen 2 and ISO 18000-6C standards, offering excellent compatibility with various UHF tags and cards on the market. The working frequency range of 902MHz to 928MHz ensures a broad operational spectrum, which helps users maximize efficiency across various industrial and commercial settings. The UR20RW-F&rsquo;s compact design and fast processing speed make it a standout tool for both small and large-scale enterprises, improving workflows and operational productivity.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ur20rw-f/descriptions/202501-268-44-7TCbrN2Ire.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.114678', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.119716', 268),
(518, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">With its ability to read and write UHF tags and cards with high precision, the<strong> UR20RW-F</strong> UHF Card Issue Reader is perfect for environments where accuracy and speed are essential. It features a flexible working range of 0 to 5 cm, making it suitable for a wide range of use cases, including inventory control, access management, and asset tracking. This device ensures that your operations run smoothly, whether in retail, logistics, or manufacturing.<br><br>The UR20RW-F offers exceptional value for businesses that need to streamline their operations by integrating UHF technology. It operates at a frequency range of 902MHz to 928MHz, ensuring that it complies with various global standards. Thanks to its efficient USB interface, businesses can seamlessly connect the reader to computers and other devices, making it a simple yet powerful solution for any setup.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-ur20rw-f/descriptions/202501-268-55-1ZHudzToK2.PNG', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.121571', '2025-01-27 03:56:07.125599', 268),
(519, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The<strong> VR10 PRO Parking Barrier Radar</strong> offers an innovative solution to improve the security and functionality of parking barrier gates. Developed by ZKTeco, this radar system uses cutting-edge technology to detect and identify a wide range of vehicles such as motorcycles, cars, trucks, and pedestrians. It ensures that your parking area operates smoothly by preventing accidents caused by premature gate closures, while also offering precise monitoring of vehicle and pedestrian movement.<br><br>With adjustable detection distances between 1 meter and 6 meters, the VR10 PRO can be fine-tuned to suit various environments, whether it\'s a crowded commercial space or a quiet residential area. The system features easy setup through an app, making it user-friendly and adaptable to different installations. The VR10 PRO is a highly effective tool for businesses and homes looking to enhance their parking lot\'s safety and operational efficiency.</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-vr10-pro/descriptions/202501-269-22-9F5LDP44AA.PNG', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.471259', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.477184', 269),
(520, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The <strong>ZKTeco VR10 PRO Parking Barrier Radar</strong> is the perfect upgrade for any parking management system. This advanced radar system is designed to detect vehicles and pedestrians with high accuracy, ensuring barrier gates only close when it is safe to do so. Whether monitoring small cars, large trucks, or pedestrians walking nearby, the VR10 PRO guarantees precision in all its detections. Its ability to detect vehicles and pedestrians makes it an invaluable safety tool for busy parking lots and high-traffic areas.<br><br>Installation and customization are made simple through the app, which allows users to adjust settings, including detection distance, to best suit the environment. With a detection range from 1 meter to 6 meters, the radar can be fine-tuned to avoid false detections while ensuring optimal coverage. The VR10 PRO is a highly reliable and adaptable solution for preventing accidents and improving the efficiency of parking system</span></p>', 'products/zkteco-vr10-pro/descriptions/202501-269-55-vOtc8rPEF4.PNG', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.487471', '2025-01-27 04:02:39.494525', 269),
(521, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">The MATRIX Project Series Bullet IP Cameras are designed to offer top-tier surveillance performance in outdoor environments. With a rugged metal body, they are built to endure harsh weather conditions, ensuring uninterrupted security monitoring. Equipped with a 2MP resolution and a high-performance SONY STARVIS CMOS sensor, these cameras provide sharp and detailed images in any lighting condition. True WDR technology enhances visibility in high-contrast environments, allowing for clear video capture even in the most challenging lighting situations.<br><br>Additionally, these cameras are equipped with an advanced infrared system, offering a powerful 50m IR range for night surveillance. They support adaptive streaming technology, reducing bandwidth and storage requirements without sacrificing image quality. With built-in audio support, they enhance monitoring capabilities, capturing both video and sound. Designed to meet rigorous security standards, they are NDAA-compliant and certified with BIS, CE, FCC, RoHS, IK10, IP67, UL, and NEMA 4X ratings. These cameras are the perfect choice for organizations that require robust and cyber-secure surveillance solutions.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-project-series-bullet-network-cameras/descriptions/202501-270-33-ZxewX68oJq.PNG', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.587029', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.592743', 270),
(522, '<p><span data-sheets-root=\"1\">Built for durability and high performance, the MATRIX Project Series Bullet Network Cameras offer unmatched security in outdoor environments. The 2MP resolution, paired with a 1/2.8\" SONY STARVIS CMOS sensor, delivers crisp and detailed video footage, ensuring optimal surveillance quality. True WDR technology corrects lighting imbalances, providing clear images even in areas with strong backlighting or shadows. With a noise reduction of &gt;70dB SNR, these cameras ensure superior image clarity, minimizing distortion and interference.<br><br>Engineered for reliability, these cameras boast an IR range of up to 50m, delivering enhanced night vision for round-the-clock monitoring. Their rugged metal housing is rated IK10 and IP67, making them resistant to impact, dust, and water. Additionally, they meet industry-leading certifications, including BIS, CE, FCC, RoHS, UL, and NEMA 4X, ensuring compliance with global security standards. Cybersecurity is a top priority, as these cameras are NDAA-compliant and designed with advanced data protection features. Whether used in industrial zones, parking lots, or educational campuses, these cameras provide a dependable and intelligent surveillance solution.</span></p>', 'products/matrix-project-series-bullet-network-cameras/descriptions/202501-270-55-des1No0MFz.png', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.594863', '2025-01-30 02:43:09.598942', 270);
